NK127(jo)001:1: // snga 'gyur bka' ma'i chos sde'i glegs bam brgya dang nyer drug pa bzhugs so //
NK127(jo)001:3: // ma ni m+aa la n+aa m+aa sh+aa ma h+aa b+ho
NK127(jo)001:4: d+hi sa t+wa pa pu t+aa r+t+aa na pa d+aa
NK127(jo)001:5: na bi ha ra ti sma ////
NK127(jo)001:6: byang chub sems dpa' chen po nye ba'i sras brgyad
NK127(jo)001:7: kyi rtogs brjod nor bu'i phreng ba zhes bya ba
NK127(jo)001:8: bzhugs so // byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen
NK127(jo)001:9: po 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa la phyag 'tshal
NK127(jo)001:10: bzhugs so // lo // mchod do skyabs su mchi'o //
NK127(jo)001:11: mgon po mkhyen rab kyi mnga' bdag 'di ni dus
NK127(jo)001:12: gsum gyi sangs rgyas thams cad kyi rnam par mi
NK127(jo)001:13: rtog pa'i ye shes kyi sku gcig pur gyur pa
NK127(jo)001:14: byang chub sems dpa'i tshul gyis nam mkha' dang chos
NK127(jo)001:15: kyi dbyings ji srid du bzhugs nas /
NK127(jo)001:16: la lar yon tan ma lus pa rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas dang /
NK127(jo)001:17: la lar rgyal ba'i sras kyi thu bo dang /
NK127(jo)001:18: la lar yon tan yongs su ma rdzogs pa lam la slob pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:19: la lar phal pa'i gzugs kyis mdzad pa sna tshogs
NK127(jo)001:20: pa'i sgo nas rgyal ba dang rgyal sras thams cad
NK127(jo)001:21: kyi mdzad pa ji snyed pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:22: sems can gyi khams ji snyed par 'jug pas rnam
NK127(jo)001:23: par thar pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa la gnas
NK127(jo)001:24: pa ste dpa' bar 'gro ba'i ting nge 'dzin gyi
NK127(jo)001:25: mdo las sngar sangs rgyas pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:26: sor mo'i phreng bas phan pa'i mdo las de ltar sangs rgyas te 'tsho zhing gzhes pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:27: 'jam dpal zhing gi yon tan bkod pa las ma
NK127(jo)001:28: 'ongs pa'i bskal pa grangs med pa na mgon po
NK127(jo)001:29: kun tu gzigs zhes par 'tshang rgya bar ston pa
NK127(jo)001:30: gsungs te / de ltar sangs rgyas dang byang chub
NK127(jo)001:31: sems dpa'i mdzad pa sna tshogs pa'i tshul ston kyang
NK127(jo)001:32: gsungs te / / nam yang zad pa dang 'phel
NK127(jo)001:33: ba med par nam mkha' lta bu'i ye shes kyi
NK127(jo)001:34: skus mdzad pa sna tshogs sems can gyi mtha' dang
NK127(jo)001:37: nga ni dus gsum sngon du byung //
NK127(jo)001:38: sangs rgyas kun gyi sngon du byung //
NK127(jo)001:39: nga ni dus gsum phyis kyang 'byung //
NK127(jo)001:40: nga ni dus gsum da ltar 'byung //
NK127(jo)001:42: nga ni dus gsum 'byung pa'i sku //
NK127(jo)001:43: bstan pa thams cad nub pa'i tshe //
NK127(jo)001:44: de tshe nga yi bstan pa 'byung //
NK127(jo)001:45: ji lta bur ni zhir gyur kyang //
NK127(jo)001:46: nga ni thams cad zhi ba'i sku //
NK127(jo)001:47: ji lta bur ni khros gyur kyang //
NK127(jo)001:48: thams cad khros pa nga yi sku //
NK127(jo)001:50: de'i phyir 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa de'i rnam
NK127(jo)001:51: par rol pa 'ga' zhig de bzhin gshegs pa'i bka'
NK127(jo)001:52: lung tshad mar gyur pa las byung ba rnams tshig
NK127(jo)001:53: mdor bsdus shing don gsal bar brjod na /
NK127(jo)001:54: 'phags pa dkon mchog 'byung gnas zhes bya ba theg pa chen po'i mdo las /
NK127(jo)001:55: byang chub sems dpa' thams cad zil gyis gnon pa zhes bya bas zhus pa /
NK127(jo)001:56: bcom ldan 'das 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa chos
NK127(jo)001:57: kyi dbyings la gnas te mi chags par chos 'chad
NK127(jo)001:58: lags so // 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa 'di chos kyi dbyings la zhugs nas ji srid lags /
NK127(jo)001:60: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
NK127(jo)001:61: sangs rgyas bye ba khrag khrig 'bum phrag dpag tu
NK127(jo)001:62: med pa gang ngag yongs su mya ngan las 'das
NK127(jo)001:63: pa yang 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pas bla med
NK127(jo)001:65: de thams cad zhing yang dag par sangs rgyas nas yongs su mya ngan las 'das so //
NK127(jo)001:66: sngon byung ba bskal pa dpag med grangs med bsam
NK127(jo)001:67: gyis mi khyab mtshungs pa med pa brjod du med
NK127(jo)001:68: pa de'i pha rol gyi yang ches pha rol na
NK127(jo)001:69: sangs rgyas ye shes dpal zhes bya ba 'jig rten
NK127(jo)001:70: du byung ngo // de'i pha rol gyi yang ches
NK127(jo)001:71: pha rol na de bzhin gshegs pa ye shes 'byung
NK127(jo)001:73: de bzhin du de'i pha rol gyi yang ches pha rol zhes kun la sbyar te /
NK127(jo)001:74: de bzhin gshegs pa ye shes bla ma dang /
NK127(jo)001:80: seng ge rnam par gnon pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:86: mchog tu dga' ba'i rgyal po dang /
NK127(jo)001:87: stobs kyi shugs rnam par gnon pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:88: rab tu zhi bar spyod pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:89: zhi ba'i 'od zer tog gi rgyal po dang /
NK127(jo)001:93: dri ma med pa'i zhal dang /
NK127(jo)001:95: dri ma med pa'i 'od zer dang /
NK127(jo)001:96: dogs pa thams cad legs par 'joms pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:98: thams cad zil gyis gnon pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:101: dri ma med pa'i spyan dang /
NK127(jo)001:103: dri ma med pa'i mig dang /
NK127(jo)001:109: mtha' yas snang ba'i spyan dang /
NK127(jo)001:111: mngon par 'phags pa'i ri rgyal ba brgyan pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:113: tshangs pas skyabs zhes bya ba byung ngo //
NK127(jo)001:114: de'i pha rol gyi yang ches pha rol na bskal
NK127(jo)001:115: pa gcig la sangs rgyas drug khri 'jig rten du
NK127(jo)001:116: byung ste de dag gi thog ma ni 'od ces
NK127(jo)001:117: bya / tha ma ni de bzhin gshegs pa grags pa'i 'od ces bya ba byung ngo //
NK127(jo)001:118: de'i pha rol gyi yang ches pha rol na sangs
NK127(jo)001:119: rgyas bye ba phrag bzhi 'jig rten du byung ste
NK127(jo)001:120: / de dag gi thog ma ni de bzhin gshegs pa mar me mdzad ces bya ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:121: tha ma ni de bzhin gshegs pa spyan rig zhes bya ba 'jig rten du byung ngo //
NK127(jo)001:122: de'i pha rol gyi yang ches pha rol na bskal
NK127(jo)001:123: pa gcig la sangs rgyas bye ba phrag dgu byung
NK127(jo)001:124: ste / de dag gi thog mar de bzhin gshegs pa bde spyan zhes bya ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:125: tha mar de bzhin gshegs pa rnam par 'byed pas rnam par phye ba zhes bya ba byung ngo //
NK127(jo)001:126: de'i pha rol gyi yang ches pha rol na de
NK127(jo)001:127: bzhin gshegs pa dga' mchog ces bya ba 'jig rten
NK127(jo)001:128: du byung ngo // sangs rgyas de'i zhing na grags sbyin zhes bya ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:129: dpa' mkhas zhes bya ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:138: 'grogs na bde zhes bya ba'i byang chub sems dpa'
NK127(jo)001:139: chen po des shing 'grogs na bde ba yon tan
NK127(jo)001:140: 'bum phrag mang po dang ldan pa bcu gcig tshangs
NK127(jo)001:142: de'i tshe bram ze rigs kyi shing s+aa la chen
NK127(jo)001:143: po lta bu nyi mas byin pa zhes bya ba
NK127(jo)001:144: mkhas shing yid rno ba shes rab kyi rang bzhin
NK127(jo)001:145: can de / grogs po bram ze chen po lnga
NK127(jo)001:146: brgya tsam dang lhan cig tu rin chen ldan zhes
NK127(jo)001:147: bya ba'i grong khyer nas phyi rol du byung nas
NK127(jo)001:148: can de / / dga' ba sna tshogs zhes pa'i
NK127(jo)001:149: tshal du phyin pa dang de na byang chub sems
NK127(jo)001:150: dpa' bcu gcig po 'khod pa mthong nas de dag
NK127(jo)001:151: la sems rab tu dang par gyur ro //
NK127(jo)001:152: de na skyes bu dam pa grags byin des drang
NK127(jo)001:153: srong nyi mas byin gyi spyod lam la bltas nas
NK127(jo)001:154: skyes bu dam pa 'di bla med byang chub kyi
NK127(jo)001:155: snod du 'gyur ro snyam nas skyes bu dam pa
NK127(jo)001:156: bcu gcig po de dag la smras pa /
NK127(jo)001:157: tshe dang ldan pa dag nyi mas byin 'di ni
NK127(jo)001:158: sangs rgyas kyi sras kyi tshul du 'gro ba bla
NK127(jo)001:159: med sangs rgyas kyi chos rnams kyi snod du gyur
NK127(jo)001:160: pa 'ong gis / 'di la snying brtse bas gdams
NK127(jo)001:161: pa bstan na 'dis skye bo phal po che'i don
NK127(jo)001:162: byed cing snang bar bya ba'i phyir legs par dgongs
NK127(jo)001:163: pa 'ong gis / shig / de nas bram ze
NK127(jo)001:164: nyi mas byin gyis skyes bu dam pa bcu gcig
NK127(jo)001:165: gi gan du song nas ston pa'i 'du shes kyis
NK127(jo)001:166: phyag 'tshal zhing phyogs gcig tu 'grengs te shin tu
NK127(jo)001:167: gus shing dga' ba'i ri mor byed do //
NK127(jo)001:168: de nas rigs kyi bu grags byin gyis nyi mas
NK127(jo)001:169: byin la sangs rgyas 'jig rten du 'byung dka' ba
NK127(jo)001:170: dang de'i chos zab mo ni rtogs par dka' ba
NK127(jo)001:171: 'jig rten thams cad las 'das pa yin la /
NK127(jo)001:172: de'i chos ni nam mkha' la bris pa ni ma
NK127(jo)001:173: byung mi 'byung ba bzhin du chos thams cad ma
NK127(jo)001:174: skyes ma 'gag brjod du med pa'i rang bzhin yin
NK127(jo)001:175: par bstan pas / bram ze de dag shin tu
NK127(jo)001:176: yi rangs shing dga' nas sangs rgyas kyi chos zab
NK127(jo)001:177: mo mthar phyin par gyur to //
NK127(jo)001:178: de nas bram ze nyi mas byin dang skyes bu
NK127(jo)001:179: dam pa bcu gcig po de dag de bzhin gshegs
NK127(jo)001:180: pa dga' mchog gi drung du song ste phyag 'tshal
NK127(jo)001:181: zhing phyogs gcig tu 'khod nas de bzhin gshegs pa
NK127(jo)001:182: las chos thams cad mtshan nyid med par mtshan nyid
NK127(jo)001:183: gcig pa'i chos bstan pa thos pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:184: bram ze nyi mas byin de dge ba'i rtsa ba'i
NK127(jo)001:185: shugs thob pas ta la bdun srid du 'phags nas
NK127(jo)001:186: phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten gyi khams dpag tu med pa
NK127(jo)001:187: na / byang chub sems dpa' dpag tu med pa
NK127(jo)001:188: rnams thabs mkhas pa rnam pa tha dad pa yang
NK127(jo)001:189: dag par sgrub pa rnams mthong /
NK127(jo)001:190: de bzhin du byang chub sems dpa' dpag med dga' ldan nas 'pho ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:191: lhums su zhugs pa nas sangs rgyas pa dang mya
NK127(jo)001:192: ngan las 'das pa'i bar du yang bar snang de
NK127(jo)001:194: de nas bram ze nyi mas byin gyis mchog tu
NK127(jo)001:195: dga' ba'i yid kyis sangs rgyas la don dang mthun
NK127(jo)001:196: pa'i tshigs su bcad pas bstod pa byas pa'i dge
NK127(jo)001:198: bskal pa brjod du med par nams kyang smyos pa
NK127(jo)001:199: dang glen par ma gyur la gang dang gang du
NK127(jo)001:200: skyes pa der 'dren pa skyes bu chen por gyur
NK127(jo)001:201: to // nams kyang log par ltung ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:202: gzhan gyi dring la 'jog pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:203: gzhan gyi ngor lta bar ma gyur la /
NK127(jo)001:204: tha na se gol gtogs pa tsam gyi bar du
NK127(jo)001:205: sems can rnams yongs su smin par ma byas par
NK127(jo)001:206: ma gyur to // de'i tshe rigs kyi bu grags
NK127(jo)001:207: byin zhes bya ba de ni rigs kyi bu bzang
NK127(jo)001:209: de bzhin du mkhas pa'i snying por gyur pa ni
NK127(jo)001:210: da lta byang chub sems dpa' dkon mchog 'byung gnas
NK127(jo)001:212: bram ze nyi mas byin ni 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa nyid yin te /
NK127(jo)001:213: de ltar byang chub sems dpa' ni gzhan gyi dring la mi 'jog pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:214: gzhan gyis mi bkri bar 'dod pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:215: gzhan gyi ngor mi lta bar 'dod na chos kyi
NK127(jo)001:216: dbyings la rab tu 'jug pa'i phyir dge ba'i bshes
NK127(jo)001:217: gnyen rnams la bsten par bya /
NK127(jo)001:220: chos zab mo mnyan pa'i phyir yongs su 'dri ba'i ngang tshul can du bya'o //
NK127(jo)001:222: dpa' bar 'gro ba'i ting nge 'dzin ces bya ba theg pa chen po'i mdo las /
NK127(jo)001:223: 'khor der byang chub sems dpa'i theg pa pa'i srog chags nyis brgya sems zhum nas /
NK127(jo)001:224: thams cad mkhyen pa'i gnas ni thob dka' bas bdag
NK127(jo)001:225: cag rang sangs rgyas kyi theg pas yongs su mya
NK127(jo)001:227: de gdul ba'i phyir 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pas bcom ldan 'das la 'di skad du gsol ba /
NK127(jo)001:228: 'das pa'i dus bskal pa rnam par snang ba zhes
NK127(jo)001:229: bya ba zhig byung ba de la bdag lan bye
NK127(jo)001:230: ba khrag khrig brgya stong phrag sum cu rtsa drug
NK127(jo)001:231: tu rang sangs rgyas kyi theg pas yongs su mya
NK127(jo)001:232: ngan las 'das so zhes gsol to //
NK127(jo)001:233: de la 'khor de the tshom du gyur pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:234: sh+aa ri'i bus mya ngan las 'das pa la nying
NK127(jo)001:235: mtshams sbyor ba med na de lta bu ci zhes
NK127(jo)001:236: bcom ldan 'das la zhus pa na /
NK127(jo)001:238: de ni 'jam dpal nyid la dris dang lan ldon par 'gyur ro zhes gsungs pas /
NK127(jo)001:239: de ltar smras pa'i don de ji ltar blta bar
NK127(jo)001:240: bya zhes sh+aa ri'i bus 'jam dpal la dris pa
NK127(jo)001:242: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad mkhyen pa nyid ni kho bo'i dbang ste /
NK127(jo)001:243: gal te kho bos gzhan du smras na de bzhin gshegs pa bslus par 'gyur ro //
NK127(jo)001:244: de ltar na bskal pa rnam par snang ba la
NK127(jo)001:245: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rgyal ba zhes bya ba byung
NK127(jo)001:246: nas yongs su mya ngan las 'das te dam pa'i
NK127(jo)001:247: chos lo 'bum du gnas pa nub pa na /
NK127(jo)001:248: sems can de dag rkyen gyi stobs can du gyur
NK127(jo)001:249: te rang sangs rgyas kyi spyod lam gyis 'dul nus
NK127(jo)001:251: sangs rgyas brgya stong gis chos bshad kyang mos par
NK127(jo)001:252: mi 'gyur zhing rang sangs rgyas la mos pa sha
NK127(jo)001:253: stag go // de'i tshe de dag gi yon dbul
NK127(jo)001:254: ba'i gnas su rang sangs rgyas 'ga' yang ma byung
NK127(jo)001:255: stag go // nas / kho bos sems can de
NK127(jo)001:256: dag smin pa'i phyir rang sangs rgyas su khas 'ches
NK127(jo)001:257: stag go // nas / te / grong dang pho
NK127(jo)001:258: brang yul 'khor sogs gang du gnas pa der de
NK127(jo)001:259: dag gis rang sangs rgyas su 'du shes shing /
NK127(jo)001:260: rang sangs rgyas kyi cha byad dang spyod lam bstan
NK127(jo)001:261: pas sems can de dag gus shing rim gro byed
NK127(jo)001:262: pa dang bsod snyoms byin pa de dag slad nas
NK127(jo)001:263: snod du gyur pa la chos bshad cing kho bo
NK127(jo)001:264: dad pa'i rgyal po ltar bar snang la 'phags pas
NK127(jo)001:265: de dag dad cing de 'dra'i lam thob par smon
NK127(jo)001:266: lam btab bo // rnam grangs de lta bus sems
NK127(jo)001:267: can mang po'i dge ba'i rtsa ba yongs su smin
NK127(jo)001:268: lam btab bo // par byas so // yang sems
NK127(jo)001:269: can de dag bsod snyoms kyis skyo'o snyam pa'i tshe
NK127(jo)001:270: bdag mya ngan las 'da' ba'i dus la bab po
NK127(jo)001:272: sems can de dag mchod pa sna tshogs thogs nas
NK127(jo)001:273: 'ongs pa dang kho bo ni 'du shes dang tshor
NK127(jo)001:274: ba 'gog pa'i snyoms 'jug la zhugs nas smon lam
NK127(jo)001:275: gyi dbang gis yongs su mya ngan las 'das so
NK127(jo)001:276: // de dag gi kho bo'i lus bsreg la mchod
NK127(jo)001:277: rten byas te mchod pa'i las byed cing kho bo
NK127(jo)001:278: mya ngan las 'das par 'du shes byed do //
NK127(jo)001:279: de ltar rgyal po'i pho brang sogs su bskal pa
NK127(jo)001:280: bar ma de la kho bo lan bye ba khrag
NK127(jo)001:281: khrig brgya stong phrag sum cu rtsa drug tu rang
NK127(jo)001:282: sangs rgyas kyi theg pas yongs su mya ngan las
NK127(jo)001:283: 'das te / tshul des srog chags bye ba phrag
NK127(jo)001:284: sum cu rtsa drug rang sangs rgyas kyi theg pa
NK127(jo)001:285: 'das te / la btul lo // de ltar rang
NK127(jo)001:286: sangs rgyas kyi theg pas yongs su mya ngan las
NK127(jo)001:287: 'da' ba yin mod kyi shin tu yongs su mya
NK127(jo)001:289: zhes tshul 'di bshad pa na sa chen po rnam
NK127(jo)001:290: pa drug tu g.yos shing snang ba chen pos khyab
NK127(jo)001:291: pa dang / lha rnams kyis mchod pa'i phyir me
NK127(jo)001:292: tog gi char phab cing rmad du byung ba'i chos
NK127(jo)001:294: lha de dag gis de bzhin gshegs pa dang 'jam
NK127(jo)001:295: dpal gzhon nur gyur pa mthong la dpa' bar 'gro
NK127(jo)001:296: ba'i ting 'dzin de yang thos pa rnyed pa legs
NK127(jo)001:297: par rnyed do zhes ched du brjod nas bcom ldan
NK127(jo)001:299: 'jam dpal ni 'di ltar bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i chos dang ldan pa ngo mtshar lags na /
NK127(jo)001:300: ting nge 'dzin gang la gnas nas bsam gyis mi
NK127(jo)001:301: khyab pa'i chos 'di lta bu ston ces gsol ba
NK127(jo)001:303: 'dis ni dpa' bar 'gro ba'i ting nge 'dzin la gnas nas chos nyid 'di lta bu ston te /
NK127(jo)001:304: ting 'dzin 'di la gnas pas dad pa'i rjes su
NK127(jo)001:305: 'brang ba nas dgra bcom dang rang sangs rgyas kyang
NK127(jo)001:306: yin la yongs su mya ngan las 'das pa'i bar
NK127(jo)001:307: ston kyang de ltar gnas pa med par skye ba
NK127(jo)001:310: gnas brtan 'od srung chen pos sangs rgyas la zhus pa /
NK127(jo)001:311: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa'i don bdag gis
NK127(jo)001:312: 'tshal ba ltar na 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa
NK127(jo)001:313: 'di ni sngon sangs rgyas kyi mdzad pa bgyis shing
NK127(jo)001:314: byang chub snying po bstan pa chos kyi 'khor lo
NK127(jo)001:315: bskor / yongs su mya ngan las 'das pa bstan snyam bgyid ngo zhes gsol ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:318: sngon 'das pa'i dus bskal pa ches grangs med pa'i
NK127(jo)001:319: yang grangs med pa yangs pa tshad med pa bsam
NK127(jo)001:320: gyis mi khyab pa de'i pha rol gyi yang ches
NK127(jo)001:321: pha rol tu phyin pa de'i dus na /
NK127(jo)001:322: lho phyogs su sangs rgyas kyi zhing 'di nas sangs
NK127(jo)001:323: rgyas kyi zhing sum stong 'das pa na 'jig rten
NK127(jo)001:324: gyi khams mnyam pa zhes bya ba /
NK127(jo)001:325: ri dang rdo dang bong pa sogs med la 'jam zhing mnyam pa na /
NK127(jo)001:326: bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa klu'i rigs mchog
NK127(jo)001:327: ces bya ba byung ste sku tshe'i tshad ni lo
NK127(jo)001:329: der byang chub sems dpa'i theg pa la ni sems can bye ba phrag bdun cu smin par byas /
NK127(jo)001:330: bye ba phrag brgyad cu nyan thos kyi theg pas smin par byas /
NK127(jo)001:331: bye ba brgya stong phrag dgu bcu rtsa drug ni
NK127(jo)001:332: rang sangs rgyas kyi theg pas smin par byas nas
NK127(jo)001:333: / phyis de bzhin gshegs pa de'i nyan thos kyi dge 'dun dpag tu med par gyur to //
NK127(jo)001:334: de ltar lha dang mi yi 'jig rten gyi don
NK127(jo)001:335: byas nas yongs su mya ngan las 'das te de'i
NK127(jo)001:336: sku gdung yang rgyas par gyur to //
NK127(jo)001:337: de'i mchod rten bye ba phrag sum cu rtsa drug
NK127(jo)001:338: tu gyur te sems can de dag gis mchod par
NK127(jo)001:339: byas shing de'i chos ni lo 'bum du gnas so
NK127(jo)001:340: // de bzhin gshegs pa des nga 'das pa'i 'og
NK127(jo)001:341: tu byang chub sems dpa' ye shes 'od ces bya
NK127(jo)001:343: de bzhin gshegs pa ye shes 'od ces bya bar 'gyur ro zhes lung bstan to //
NK127(jo)001:344: de ltar de bzhin gshegs pa klu'i rigs mchog de
NK127(jo)001:345: ni 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa 'di yin te
NK127(jo)001:346: dpa' bar 'gro ba'i ting nge 'dzin gyi mthu la
NK127(jo)001:347: ltos dang / 'di ltar mngal du 'jug pa nas
NK127(jo)001:348: sangs rgyas pa dang mya ngan las 'das pa'i bar
NK127(jo)001:349: ltos dang / du ston kyang / byang chub sems
NK127(jo)001:350: dpa'i chos nyid de yang mi 'dor la shin tu
NK127(jo)001:351: yongs su mya ngan las kyang mi 'ada'o zhes gsungs
NK127(jo)001:352: ltos dang / du ston kyang / pa na /
NK127(jo)001:353: 'od srung chen pos 'jam dpal la khyod 'di ltar
NK127(jo)001:354: bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i gnas dag ston pa dka'
NK127(jo)001:355: ba byed pa'o zhes smras pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:357: chos thams cad ni rgyu rkyen gyis bcos pa'i bdag
NK127(jo)001:358: po med pa'i phyir ji ltar 'dod pa bzhin du
NK127(jo)001:359: 'grub ste bden pa mthong bas 'di la bya dka'
NK127(jo)001:362: sor mo'i phreng ba la phan pa'i mdo las /
NK127(jo)001:363: zhing 'di nas lho phyogs 'jig rten gyi khams rin
NK127(jo)001:364: chen thams cad kyis brgyan pa zhes bya ba ni
NK127(jo)001:365: / de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom pa yang dag
NK127(jo)001:366: par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas 'jig rten thams cad mthong
NK127(jo)001:367: na dga' ba mngon par 'phags pa brtson pa chen
NK127(jo)001:368: po zhes bya ba da ltar 'tsho zhing gzhes pa
NK127(jo)001:369: de ni sor mo'i phreng ba yin te /
NK127(jo)001:370: sangs rgyas de'i zhing gi sems can rnams rga ba
NK127(jo)001:371: dang na ba sogs mi bde ba thams cad med
NK127(jo)001:372: la tshe dang gzi brjid dpag tu med do //
NK127(jo)001:373: 'di nas byang phyogs su 'jig rten gyi khams rtag
NK127(jo)001:374: par rab tu dga' ba sdug cing mos pa zhes
NK127(jo)001:375: bya ba na / de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom
NK127(jo)001:376: pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas mos pa
NK127(jo)001:377: rab tu dga' ba'i snying po nor bu rin po
NK127(jo)001:378: che brtsegs pa'i rgyal po zhes bya ba da ltar
NK127(jo)001:379: 'tsho zhing gzhes la chos ston pa de ni 'jam
NK127(jo)001:380: dpal gzhon nur gyur pa 'di yin no //
NK127(jo)001:381: sangs rgyas de'i zhing na nyan rang med la rga
NK127(jo)001:382: ba dang na ba sogs sdug bsngal med cing sems
NK127(jo)001:383: can thams cad bde ba thams cad dang ldan la
NK127(jo)001:384: tshe dang gzi brjid dpag tu med do //
NK127(jo)001:385: gang gis sor mo'i phreng ba dang 'jam dpal gzhon
NK127(jo)001:386: nur gyur pa 'di gnyis kyi ming thos sam de
NK127(jo)001:388: sems can de'i khyim du dga' ba can gyi 'jig
NK127(jo)001:389: rten mthong ste ngan 'gro bzhi'i sgo bcad par 'gyur
NK127(jo)001:390: ro // de gnyis kyi ming thos nas phyi rol pa rnams dang /
NK127(jo)001:392: mtshams med par gyur pas 'phya ba'am /
NK127(jo)001:396: rnyed pa dang bkur sti dang tshigs bcad kyi phyir
NK127(jo)001:397: yang rung ste de dag gi ngan 'gro bzhi'i sgo
NK127(jo)001:399: rigs kyi bu'am bu mo gang gis 'di gnyis kyi ming gis srung bar byas na /
NK127(jo)001:400: dgon pa thams cad dang 'jigs pa thams cad zhi zhing srung ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:401: lha klu gnod sbyin sha za sogs kyis mi tshugs par gsungs so //
NK127(jo)001:402: snying rje pad+ma dkar po las /
NK127(jo)001:403: rgyal po rtsibs kyi mu khyud kyi bu gsum pa
NK127(jo)001:404: dbang po'i tshogs zhes bya bas de bzhin gshegs pa
NK127(jo)001:405: rin chen snying po la gsol ba /
NK127(jo)001:406: bdag ni sangs rgyas kyi zhing dag pa 'dzin zhing myur du 'tshang rgya bar yang mi bgyi ste /
NK127(jo)001:407: ji srid du byang chub sems dpa'i spyad pa spyod
NK127(jo)001:408: pa na phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten gyi khams mtha' yas
NK127(jo)001:409: mu med pa'i sangs rgyas rnams mthong ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:410: der yang bdag gis dang por sems bskyed du bcug
NK127(jo)001:411: pa dang pha rol tu phyin pa la rab tu
NK127(jo)001:412: bkod nas / sangs rgyas par gyur pa de lta
NK127(jo)001:413: bu zhing mtha' yas pa'i rdul snyed dang mnyam pa
NK127(jo)001:414: mthong ba de ltar sangs rgyas kyi mdzad pa byed
NK127(jo)001:415: bkod nas / pa dang / bdag gi zhing der
NK127(jo)001:416: skyes pa'i sems can rnams tshangs ris kyi lha rnams
NK127(jo)001:418: stong chen po'i 'jig rten gang+g+aa'i klung gi bye ma
NK127(jo)001:419: snyed kyi sangs rgyas kyi zhing zhing gcig tu 'gyur
NK127(jo)001:420: ba'i yon tan gyi bkod pa 'dzin pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:421: zhing de'i rwa ba dag kyang srid rtsi'i mthar thug
NK127(jo)001:422: cing rin chen du ma gnas shing spras par 'gyur
NK127(jo)001:423: ba dang / sa gzhi thams cad beed+aur+ya 'ba' zhig
NK127(jo)001:424: las bgyis pa rdul sogs rnyog pa med pa dang
NK127(jo)001:425: ba dang / / der mi khoms pa brgyad dang
NK127(jo)001:426: sdug bsngal dang bslab pa dang ltung ba las bslang
NK127(jo)001:427: ba dang / / dgos pa dang / bud med
NK127(jo)001:428: dang nyan rang dang nyon mongs pa can gyi sems
NK127(jo)001:429: can ming tsam yang ma mchis pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:430: kham zas kyi 'tshal ba ma mchis par dga' ba'i zas dang chos kyi zas dang ldan pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:431: bardzusa te skye ba dang tshangs par spyod pa yongs su dag pa la gnas pa'i byang chub sems dpa'/
NK127(jo)001:432: bsam pa dag pa dang skye ba gcig gis thogs pa 'ga' zhig gis gang ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:433: de thams cad skra dang kha spu bregs shing chos
NK127(jo)001:434: gos ngur smig gyon pa skyes ma thag tu 'od
NK127(jo)001:435: chen po dang ldan pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:436: de dag gi sug par rin po che'i lhung bzed
NK127(jo)001:437: ro bro ba sna tshogs kyis gtams pa dag 'byung
NK127(jo)001:438: zhing / de'i tshe de dag gis bdag cag kham
NK127(jo)001:439: gyi zas za ba cha min gyi 'jig rten gyi
NK127(jo)001:440: khams gzhan du sangs rgyas bzhugs pa 'khor dang bcas
NK127(jo)001:441: pa la 'bul zhing sems can thams cad la sbyin
NK127(jo)001:443: bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i spyod pa dang ldan pa'i
NK127(jo)001:444: ting 'dzin thob nas phyogs bcu'i zhing dpag med du
NK127(jo)001:445: thogs pa med par phyin te sangs rgyas dang nyan
NK127(jo)001:446: thos rnams dang sems can thams cad la dga' bas
NK127(jo)001:447: phul zhing chos kyi gtam bgyis te de nyid kyi
NK127(jo)001:448: snga dro rang gi sangs rgyas kyi zhing du mchi
NK127(jo)001:449: ba dang / gos rin po che la'ang de bzhin du byed pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:450: zhing de'i byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyi longs spyod
NK127(jo)001:451: ji snyed pa des sangs rgyas rnams dang nyan thos
NK127(jo)001:452: dang sems can gzhan dag dang thun mong bgyis nas
NK127(jo)001:453: slad kyis bdag yongs su spyod pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:454: zhing der nor bu rin po che kun du snang
NK127(jo)001:455: ba 'bum phrag du ma bsags shing spras pa de
NK127(jo)001:456: lta bu phyogs bcu rnams su sngon ma mthong ma
NK127(jo)001:457: thos pa'i khyad par ldan la /
NK127(jo)001:458: de'i ming tsam brjod na'ang lo bye bas mi zad pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:459: zhing de gser dang dngul dang shel dang bee d+aur+ya
NK127(jo)001:460: sogs dngos po gang dang gang du 'dod pa de
NK127(jo)001:461: ltar so so'i bsam pa bzhin snang zhing phan tshun
NK127(jo)001:463: de bzhin longs spyod dang yongs su spyod pa ji ltar bsam pa de bzhin 'byung ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:464: zhing der nyi zla med kyang byang chub sems dpa'
NK127(jo)001:465: de dag gi 'od 'gyed cing ji ltar 'dod pa
NK127(jo)001:466: bzhin sangs rgyas kyi zhing bye ba khrag khrig 'bum
NK127(jo)001:467: tshun chad du 'od gtong ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:468: zhing der pad+mo kha bye ba ma gtogs par nyin mtshan gyi ming med pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:469: zhing de'i byang sems 'tshang rgya bar 'tshal ba de
NK127(jo)001:470: dga' ldan nas 'phos te zhing gzhan du 'tshang rgya
NK127(jo)001:472: zhing de nas zhing gzhan du skye ba dang tsha
NK127(jo)001:473: grang dang nad dang mi bde ba dang rga ba
NK127(jo)001:474: dang 'chi ba ma mchis pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:475: zhing de na 'gum pa ma mchis par steng gi
NK127(jo)001:476: bar snang la de bzhin gshegs pa ltar bla na
NK127(jo)001:477: med pa'i byang chub tu yongs su mya ngan las
NK127(jo)001:478: 'da' ba dang / nam mkha'i dkyil nas sil snyan
NK127(jo)001:479: bye ba du ma'i sgra sgrogs cing de las pha
NK127(jo)001:480: rol tu phyin pa dang dkon mchog gsum dang byang
NK127(jo)001:481: chub sems dpa'i sde snod kyi sgra dang /
NK127(jo)001:482: rang ji ltar mos pa'i sgra 'byung ba las 'dod pa dang ldan pa'i sgra mi thos pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:483: zhing der ri rab dang khor yug dang rdul gyi
NK127(jo)001:484: ri dang rgya mtsho chen po dang shing gzhan ma
NK127(jo)001:485: mchis par lha'i las shin tu 'das pa'i shing ljon
NK127(jo)001:487: lha'i me tog man+da ra ba dang man+da ra ba chen po dag gis kun du gang ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:488: de na dri nga ba med par spos rgya che zhing yangs pa sna tshogs kyis khyab pa sogs /
NK127(jo)001:489: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas kyi zhing grangs med dpag tu
NK127(jo)001:490: med pa dag gi zhing gi yon tan bkod pa
NK127(jo)001:492: nyan rang dang snyigs ma lnga dang ldan pa'i bkod
NK127(jo)001:493: pa rnams ma gtogs par de dag gi rgyan dang
NK127(jo)001:494: mtshan ma dang ngo mtshar dang smon lam ji mchis
NK127(jo)001:495: pa de thams cad bdag gi zhing de na mchis
NK127(jo)001:496: pa de lta bur bdag gis byang chub sems dpa'i
NK127(jo)001:497: spyad pa spyod par bgyis nas zhing de grub pa
NK127(jo)001:498: na / bdag gis dang por byang chub tu sems
NK127(jo)001:499: bskyed du bcug pa dang pha rol tu phyin pa
NK127(jo)001:500: 'dzin du bcug pa'i byang chub sems dpa' thams cad
NK127(jo)001:502: sangs rgyas kyi zhing 'di yang zhing de'i khongs su
NK127(jo)001:503: gtogs shing 'di dag thams cad kyi sdug bsngal yang
NK127(jo)001:504: zhi ba dang / zhing der bdag sangs rgyas pa
NK127(jo)001:505: na byang chub kyi shing rin po che sna bdun
NK127(jo)001:506: rnam par bkra ba zhes bya ba spoms su gling
NK127(jo)001:507: bzhi pa khri yi tshad dang /
NK127(jo)001:508: khor yug tu ni stong gsum pa bcu mchis pa'i
NK127(jo)001:509: shing de'i dri dang 'od kyis sangs rgyas kyi zhing
NK127(jo)001:511: shing de'i drung du rin chen sna tshogs kyis spras
NK127(jo)001:512: pa'i rdo rje'i gdan rab tu zhi ba bkod pa'i
NK127(jo)001:513: ye shes shin tu 'byed pa'i dri la yang dag
NK127(jo)001:514: par gzhol ba zhes bgyi ba gling bzhi pa'i 'jig
NK127(jo)001:516: 'phang du dpag tshad brgya stong bzhi brgya pa mchis
NK127(jo)001:517: pa de la bdag skyil mo krung bcas nas yud
NK127(jo)001:518: tsam de nyid la sangs rgyas te yongs su mya
NK127(jo)001:519: ngan las 'das pa'i bar du skyil mo krung mi
NK127(jo)001:520: 'jig cing mi ldang bar gnas bzhin du /
NK127(jo)001:521: sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa'i sprul pa dag
NK127(jo)001:522: sangs rgyas kyi zhing bgrang ba las 'das par 'gyed
NK127(jo)001:523: cing sangs rgyas re res kyang snga dro gcig la'ang
NK127(jo)001:524: sems can grangs las 'das par bla med byang chub
NK127(jo)001:526: rab tu 'god pa dang phyir mi ldog par byed pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:527: byang chub sems dpa'i sprul pa de dag gis kyang byang chub sems dpa'i bya ba byed pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:528: phyogs bcu'i zhing bgrang du med par bdag gi lus snang ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:529: gang gis de mthong ba thams cad bla med byang chub tu nges pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:530: sems can de dag bla med byang chub tu mya
NK127(jo)001:531: ngan las 'da' ba'i bar du sangs rgyas dang mi
NK127(jo)001:532: 'bral la dbang po tshang ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:533: byang chub sems dpa' gang bdag blta bar 'dod pa
NK127(jo)001:534: des sems de bskyed ma thag tu gang du 'gro
NK127(jo)001:535: zhing mchis pa der bdag byang chub shing drung na
NK127(jo)001:536: 'dug pa mthong ma thag tu chos la the tshom
NK127(jo)001:537: thams cad bral zhing ma bstan pa'i don kyang 'tshal
NK127(jo)001:538: ba dang / zhing de'i sems can de dag gi
NK127(jo)001:539: grangs dang tshe ni dpag tu med pa ste thams
NK127(jo)001:540: cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes ma gtogs par sus kyang
NK127(jo)001:541: bgrang bar rngo mi thogs pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:542: bdag sangs rgyas nas mya ngan las 'das pa'i bar
NK127(jo)001:543: du zhing de'i sems can de thams cad skra ring
NK127(jo)001:544: zhing gos dkar po 'tshal bar mi 'gyur par skra
NK127(jo)001:545: bregs shing gos ngur smig gyon pa dge sbyong gi
NK127(jo)001:546: kha dog 'chang zhing dge sbyong gi tshul la gnas
NK127(jo)001:547: par gyur cig ces smon lam btab pa na /
NK127(jo)001:548: de bzhin gshegs pa rin chen snying pos bka' stsal pa /
NK127(jo)001:549: skyes bu dam pa legs so khyod mkhas shing gsal
NK127(jo)001:550: la yon tan ldan zhing ye shes dang ldan pas
NK127(jo)001:551: sems can gyi don gyi phyir smon lam shin tu
NK127(jo)001:552: bzang po btab pas rab dang mchog gi blo gros
NK127(jo)001:554: sangs rgyas kyi zhing gi yon tan mchog dam pa
NK127(jo)001:555: yongs su bzung ba khyod 'jam dpal zhes bya bar
NK127(jo)001:556: gyur cig /'jam dpal khyod ni ma 'ongs pa'i dus
NK127(jo)001:557: bskal pa grangs med pa gang+g+aa'i klung gi bye ma
NK127(jo)001:558: snyed gnyis 'das nas gsum par bab pa'i tshe /
NK127(jo)001:559: lho phyogs su 'jig rten gyi khams rdul bral yang
NK127(jo)001:560: dag bsags pa zhes bya ba mi mjed kyi 'jig
NK127(jo)001:561: rten kyang de'i khongs su 'dus shing chud pa der
NK127(jo)001:562: / de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom pa yang dag
NK127(jo)001:563: par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun tu gzigs zhes bya
NK127(jo)001:564: / bar 'gyur ro // khyod byang chub sems dpa'
NK127(jo)001:565: gyur pa na smon lam ji ltar btab pa de
NK127(jo)001:567: de lta bas na khyod sangs rgyas bye ba phrag
NK127(jo)001:568: mang po las dge rtsa bskyed zhing sems can rnams
NK127(jo)001:570: bsam pa yongs su spyod pa dang nyon mongs pa
NK127(jo)001:571: 'joms shing dge ba'i phyogs rnam par 'phel bar byed
NK127(jo)001:573: dkon mchog brtsegs pa'i le'u bco lnga pa 'jam dpal zhing gi yon tan bkod pa las /
NK127(jo)001:574: sngon 'das pa'i bskal pa grangs med pa brgya stong
NK127(jo)001:575: gang+g+aa'i klung gi bye ma snyed phrag bdun 'das pa
NK127(jo)001:576: de'i pha rol gyi yang ches pha rol de'i tshe
NK127(jo)001:577: de'i dus na / 'di nas shar phyogs su 'jig
NK127(jo)001:578: rten gyi khams 'byung ba bzang po zhes bya ba
NK127(jo)001:579: zhig byung ba der de bzhin gshegs pa 'brug sgra'i
NK127(jo)001:580: dbyangs kyi rgyal po zhes bya ba sangs rgyas nas
NK127(jo)001:581: de'i dus na / chos ston to // de'i tshe
NK127(jo)001:582: 'jam dpal 'di rgyal po nam mkha' zhes bya ba
NK127(jo)001:583: 'khor los sgyur ba'i rgyal por gyur to //
NK127(jo)001:584: de bu dang chung ma gnyen dang 'khor du bcas
NK127(jo)001:585: pas de bzhin gshegs pa de nyan thos dang byang
NK127(jo)001:586: chub sems dpa'i dge 'dun dang bcas pa lo brgyad
NK127(jo)001:587: khri bzhi stong du zhal zas sogs yo byad thams
NK127(jo)001:588: cad kyis bsnyen bkur phun sum tshogs pa byas nas
NK127(jo)001:589: rgyal po des dben par 'dug ste bsams pa /
NK127(jo)001:590: bdag gi dge rtsa 'di tshangs pa dang brgya byin
NK127(jo)001:591: dang 'khor los sgyur ba dang nyan rang ngam gang
NK127(jo)001:593: bar snang las lha rnams kyis rgyal po chen po
NK127(jo)001:594: de ltar dman pa'i sems ma bskyed par khyod kyis
NK127(jo)001:595: dge rtsa yangs pa byas kyis bla med byang chub
NK127(jo)001:596: tu sems skyed cig ces pa'i sgra byung bas /
NK127(jo)001:597: rgyal po dga' ste bdag byang chub las phyir mi
NK127(jo)001:598: ldog go snyam du rgyal po de srog chags bye
NK127(jo)001:599: ba khrag khrig brgya stong phrag brgyad cus bskor te
NK127(jo)001:600: / de bzhin gshegs pa 'brug sgra dbyangs kyi rgyal
NK127(jo)001:601: po'i drung du song nas thal mo sbyar te rang
NK127(jo)001:602: gi bsam pa ji ltar skyes pa'i tshul sogs tshigs
NK127(jo)001:605: chos rnams thams cad rkyen bzhin te //
NK127(jo)001:606: 'dun pa'i rtse la rab tu gnas //
NK127(jo)001:607: gang gis smon lam ci btab pa //
NK127(jo)001:609: zhes sogs tshigs su bcad pas rdzogs pa'i byang chub tu sems bskyed par gdams pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:610: rgyal pos bla med byang chub tu sems bskyed nas de thob byed kyi thabs rnams zhus te /
NK127(jo)001:611: bdag deng nas bzung ste nam byang chub kyi bar du phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas dpang du bzhag ste /
NK127(jo)001:612: nyon mongs kyi sems mi skyed pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:613: mi dge'i las mtha' dag spangs te tshangs par spyod
NK127(jo)001:614: pa'i tshul khrims rnam dag dang ldan pas sangs rgyas
NK127(jo)001:615: kyi rjes su slob par byed cing /
NK127(jo)001:616: bdag myur du 'tshang rgya bar mi spro ste phyi
NK127(jo)001:617: ma'i mu mthar thug gi bar du sems can gcig
NK127(jo)001:618: gi phyir yang spyad pa spyod par bgyi la /
NK127(jo)001:619: tshad med bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i sangs rgyas kyi
NK127(jo)001:620: zhing sbyar bar bgyi zhing phyogs bcu po thams cad
NK127(jo)001:621: du bdag gi ming thos shing grags par gyur cig
NK127(jo)001:622: ces byas pas / rgyal po'i rjes su 'brang ba'i
NK127(jo)001:623: srog chags bye ba nyi shus kyang sangs rgyas su
NK127(jo)001:624: ces byas pas / sems bskyed do // de ltar
NK127(jo)001:625: 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa 'dis byang chub tu
NK127(jo)001:626: sems bskyed phyin chad bskal pa gang g+aa'i klung grangs
NK127(jo)001:627: med pa brgya stong phrag bdun gyi bye ma snyed
NK127(jo)001:629: mi skye ba'i chos la bzod pa thob nas kyang
NK127(jo)001:630: bskal pa gang+g+aa'i klung drug cu rtsa bzhi'i bye ma
NK127(jo)001:631: snyed 'das so // de nas nye bar bzung nas
NK127(jo)001:632: 'di de bzhin gshegs pa'i stobs bcu yongs su rdzogs
NK127(jo)001:633: te byang chub sems dpa'i sa bcu thams cad rdzogs
NK127(jo)001:634: nas sangs rgyas kyis yongs su rdzogs so //
NK127(jo)001:635: 'dis sangs rgyas kyi chos thams cad yongs su rdzogs
NK127(jo)001:636: mod kyi bar 'ga' yang bdag byang chub mngon par
NK127(jo)001:637: rdzogs par sangs rgya bar 'gyur ram mi 'gyur snyam
NK127(jo)001:638: pa'i sems gcig kyang bskyed par ma gyur to //
NK127(jo)001:639: sngar rgyal po nam mkha' dang lhan cig sems bskyed
NK127(jo)001:640: pa'i srog chags bye ba nyi shu po thams cad
NK127(jo)001:641: kyang sangs rgyas nas sems can tshad med pa'i don
NK127(jo)001:642: byas te gcig ma gtogs pa thams cad yongs su
NK127(jo)001:644: de thams cad kyang 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa 'dis phar phyin drug la btsud de /
NK127(jo)001:645: thams cad la bsnyen bkur byas shing dam pa'i chos kyang bzung ngo //
NK127(jo)001:646: de bzhin gshegs pa gcig ma gtogs pa ni /
NK127(jo)001:647: 'di nas 'og gi phyogs su zhing gang+g+aa'i klung bzhi
NK127(jo)001:648: khri bzhi stong gi bye ma snyed 'das pa na
NK127(jo)001:649: / 'jig rten gyi khams sa'i dbyangs zhes bya bar /
NK127(jo)001:650: de bzhin gshegs pa sa'i lha zhes bya ba byang chub sems dpa'i dge 'dun tshad med pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:651: sku tshe'i tshad dpag tu med par da lta bzhugs
NK127(jo)001:652: so zhes bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa dang
NK127(jo)001:653: / byang chub sems dpa' seng ge'i rtsal gyis mngon
NK127(jo)001:654: par bsgrags pa'i sgras 'jam dpal la khyod de ltar
NK127(jo)001:655: byang chub sems dpa'i sa yongs su rdzogs nas sangs
NK127(jo)001:656: rgyas kyi chos thams cad thob na ci'i phyir sangs
NK127(jo)001:657: mi rgya zhes smras pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:658: 'jam dpal gyis sangs rgyas kyi chos yongs su rdzogs
NK127(jo)001:659: na yang nas yang du byang chub pa med de
NK127(jo)001:661: de bzhin nyid kyi ngo bos chos thams cad dang
NK127(jo)001:662: mnyam pa nyid kyi phyir skye 'gag med pa la
NK127(jo)001:663: byang chub par byar med pa'i don gyis lan smras
NK127(jo)001:664: so // de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis kyang 'jam
NK127(jo)001:665: dpal la khyod kyi zhing gi yon tan bkod pa'i
NK127(jo)001:666: smon lam sten cig ces gsungs pas /
NK127(jo)001:667: 'jam dpal gyis rang gi smon lam ston par bzhed
NK127(jo)001:668: nas pus mo g.yas pa'i lha nga sa la btsugs
NK127(jo)001:669: te thal mo sbyar bas bcom ldan 'das kyi logs
NK127(jo)001:670: su btud pa dang 'jig rten gyi khams gang+g+aa'i klung
NK127(jo)001:671: gi bye ma snyed rnam pa drug tu g.yos par
NK127(jo)001:672: gyur to // de nas 'jam dpal gyis gsol pa /
NK127(jo)001:673: bcom ldan 'das bskal pa bye ba khrag khrig phrag
NK127(jo)001:674: 'bum phrag grangs ma mchis pa nas nye bar bzung
NK127(jo)001:675: ste bdag gis smon lam btab pa ni /
NK127(jo)001:676: nam bdag gis phyogs bcu mtha' yas mu med pa'i
NK127(jo)001:677: 'jig rten gyi khams su sangs rgyas kyi spyan sgrib
NK127(jo)001:678: pa med pas bltas pa na /
NK127(jo)001:679: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das ji snyed pa de thams
NK127(jo)001:680: cad bdag gis byang chub la btsud de byang chub
NK127(jo)001:681: sems dang phar phyin la bkod de bskul zhing rjes
NK127(jo)001:682: su bstan par gyur par ma mthong ba de srid
NK127(jo)001:683: du bdag bla med byang chub tu 'tshang rgya bar
NK127(jo)001:684: mi bya'o // phyogs bcur bdag gis sangs rgyas nyid
NK127(jo)001:685: la ma bkod pa'i de bzhin gshegs pa de lta
NK127(jo)001:686: bu gang yang ma mthong ba de'i tshe bdag bla
NK127(jo)001:687: med byang chub tu mngon par rdzogs par 'tshang rgya'o
NK127(jo)001:689: de nas 'khor de'i byang chub sems dpa' dag 'di
NK127(jo)001:690: snyam du 'jam dpal 'dis sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das
NK127(jo)001:691: ji snyed cig mthong bar 'gyur snyam pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:692: bcom ldan 'das kyis de dag gi rtog pa thugs su chud nas bka' stsal pa /
NK127(jo)001:693: rigs kyi bu 'di lta ste dper na skyes bu
NK127(jo)001:694: la las stong chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khams 'di
NK127(jo)001:695: rdul phra rab tu bshigs te thal bar byas na
NK127(jo)001:696: / rdul phra rab kyi grangs de rtsis la mkhas
NK127(jo)001:697: pas brgya stong 'bum la sogs pas bgrang pa'am tshad
NK127(jo)001:698: gzung mi nus pa de snyed kyi grangs kyi sangs
NK127(jo)001:699: rgyas ni 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pas sangs rgyas
NK127(jo)001:700: kyi spyan sgrib pa med pas bltas na /
NK127(jo)001:701: phyogs bcu'i phyogs re re na yang mthong bar 'gyur ro zhes bka' stsal to //
NK127(jo)001:702: de nas bcom ldan 'das la 'jam dpal gyis gsol ba /
NK127(jo)001:703: bdag gi zhing gcig la sangs rgyas kyi zhing gang+g+aa'i
NK127(jo)001:704: klung du ma'i bye ma snyed kyi tha gru ltar
NK127(jo)001:705: yangs shing rin po che brgya stong du mas spras
NK127(jo)001:706: pa srid pa'i rtse mo'i tshad tsam du gyur la
NK127(jo)001:707: / der stong chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khams bcu'i
NK127(jo)001:708: tshad tsam gyi byang chub kyi shing gi 'od kyis
NK127(jo)001:709: sangs rgyas kyi zhing de thams cad khyab pa de'i
NK127(jo)001:711: sangs rgyas nas mya ngan las 'das pa'i bar du
NK127(jo)001:712: de nas ma langs kyang sprul pas phyogs bcu re
NK127(jo)001:713: rer yang zhing grangs med pa dag tu sems can
NK127(jo)001:715: zhing der nyan rang gi ming yang med la bud
NK127(jo)001:716: med dang mngal skyes med par ngur smig gyon pa
NK127(jo)001:717: skyil mo krung bcas nas bardzusa te byung ba'i byang
NK127(jo)001:718: chub sems dpa' zhe sdang dang tha ba dang 'chab
NK127(jo)001:719: pa'i skyon med pa tshangs spyod yongs su dag pa
NK127(jo)001:720: sha stag gis gang ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:721: zhing der zas ni bde ba can na dga' ba'i
NK127(jo)001:722: zas dang ldan par 'gyur ba de lta bu'ang ma
NK127(jo)001:723: yin te / zhing der kha zas kyi 'du shes
NK127(jo)001:724: skyes pa na de dag gi lag pa g.yas par
NK127(jo)001:725: ro bro ba brgya phrag du mar ldan pa'i zas
NK127(jo)001:726: kyis gang ba'i snod thogs nas /
NK127(jo)001:727: dang por phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas nyan thos dang bcas
NK127(jo)001:728: pa dang de nas sems can phongs shing ltogs pa
NK127(jo)001:729: yi dwags su skyes pa sogs thams cad la mngon
NK127(jo)001:730: shes lnga dang ldan pa'i rdzu 'phrul gyis skad cig
NK127(jo)001:731: gis bkyes nas tshim par byed cing sems can rnams
NK127(jo)001:732: la chos bstan pa'i rjes su rang gis longs spyod
NK127(jo)001:733: pa dang / de bzhin du dge sbyong gi tshul
NK127(jo)001:734: dang mthun pa'i gos rin po che sna tshogs kyis
NK127(jo)001:735: kyang de bzhin du byed pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:736: de bzhin du byang chub sems dpa' de dag gi
NK127(jo)001:737: longs spyod dang yongs su spyad pa gang ji snyed
NK127(jo)001:738: pa de thams cad kyang de bzhin du 'byung zhing
NK127(jo)001:740: zhing der mi khoms pa brgyad dang mi dge ba
NK127(jo)001:741: dang sdug bsngal dang skyon du gyur pa dang gzugs
NK127(jo)001:742: sogs yid du mi 'ong ba'i sgra tsam yang ma
NK127(jo)001:743: mchis pa dang / zhing der phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten
NK127(jo)001:744: na sngon ma mthong zhing mi srid pa'i nor bu
NK127(jo)001:745: rin po che bye ba khrag khrig 'bum phrag du
NK127(jo)001:746: mas gang zhing de dag gi ming brjod na yang
NK127(jo)001:747: lo bye ba brgya stong thogs par 'gyur ba de
NK127(jo)001:748: lta bus yongs su gang ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:749: zhing der skyes pa thams cad la tsha grang gi
NK127(jo)001:750: zug rngu dang na ba dang rga ba dang 'chi
NK127(jo)001:751: ba ming tsam yang ma mchis par 'gyur ba dang
NK127(jo)001:752: / byang chub sems dpa' gang 'tshang rgya bar 'dod
NK127(jo)001:753: pas zhing gzhan du mchis nas dga' ldan gyi gnas
NK127(jo)001:754: su tshe zad par bgyis te slar 'tshang rgya bar
NK127(jo)001:755: / 'gyur ba dang / zhing de ni byang chub
NK127(jo)001:756: sems dpa' la las gser las grub par mthong bar
NK127(jo)001:757: 'dod pa sogs so so'i ji ltar 'dod pa bzhin
NK127(jo)001:758: de dang der snang ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:759: zhing der byang chub sems dpa' dang byang chub shing
NK127(jo)001:760: gi 'od las gzhan pa'i nyi zla skar ma glog
NK127(jo)001:761: gi 'od sogs mi mngon la pad+ma phye zum gyis
NK127(jo)001:762: nyin mtshan 'byed pa ma gtogs nyin mtshan gyis ming
NK127(jo)001:763: med pa dang / 'od de dag gis sangs rgyas
NK127(jo)001:764: kyi zhing bye ba khrag khrig phrag 'bum snyed du
NK127(jo)001:766: steng gi bar snang las sil snyan bltar mi gda'
NK127(jo)001:767: ba bye ba khrag khrig 'bum rtag tu rgyun mi
NK127(jo)001:769: de'i sgras phar phyin dang dkon mchog gsum dang byang
NK127(jo)001:770: chub sems dpa'i sde snod kyi chos kyi sgra dang
NK127(jo)001:771: byang chub sems dpa' rang rang gi ji ltar mos
NK127(jo)001:772: pa'i chos kyi sgra 'byin pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:773: zhing der gang gis sangs rgyas blta bar 'dod pa'i
NK127(jo)001:774: tshe de bzhin gshegs pa de nyid byang chub shing
NK127(jo)001:775: gi drung na bzhugs pa de nyid de ma thag
NK127(jo)001:776: tu mthong bas the tshom soms nyi thams cad med
NK127(jo)001:777: par bstan mi dgos par don shes pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:778: 'di ltar phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten gyi khams bye ba
NK127(jo)001:779: khrag khrig 'bum phrag tshad med grangs med pa na
NK127(jo)001:780: bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas rnams kyi zhing gi yon tan
NK127(jo)001:781: bkod pa'i rgyan dang smon lam dang mtshan nyid la
NK127(jo)001:782: sogs pa ji snyed cig mthong ba las /
NK127(jo)001:783: nyan thos pa'i bkod pa dang snyigs ma lnga'i 'jig
NK127(jo)001:784: rten du sangs rgyas pa rnams kyi ma gtogs par
NK127(jo)001:785: de thams cad zhing gcig po der 'dus shing khong
NK127(jo)001:787: bskal pa gang+g+aa'i klung gi bye ma snyed du sangs
NK127(jo)001:788: rgyas kyi zhing de'i yon tan bkod pa las brtsams
NK127(jo)001:789: te bya ba gzhan med par bshad dam de bas
NK127(jo)001:790: ring bar bshad kyang mthar thug par mi 'gyur ba
NK127(jo)001:791: ste / de la de bzhin gshegs pa ye shes
NK127(jo)001:792: thogs pa med pa dbang lags so zhes gsol ba
NK127(jo)001:795: de bzhin gshegs pas thugs su chud do zhes gsungs so //
NK127(jo)001:797: sgyu ma sprul par yang bgyid la sgyu ma ma
NK127(jo)001:798: mchis pa bzhin du chos thams cad skye zhing 'gag
NK127(jo)001:799: par snang la skye 'gag ma mchis pa de ni
NK127(jo)001:800: mnyam pa nyid de zhes sogs smras pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:801: ye shes bla ma la sogs pa byang chub sems
NK127(jo)001:802: dpa' gzi brjid chen po rnams kyis rang rang gi
NK127(jo)001:803: spobs pa bstan pas sems can du ma'i don byas
NK127(jo)001:804: so // de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis 'khor de'i
NK127(jo)001:805: byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyi rtog pa thugs su
NK127(jo)001:807: zhing de'i ming ni yongs su rdzogs shing ngag la
NK127(jo)001:808: rdul med pa bsags pa zhes bya bar 'gyur te
NK127(jo)001:809: / de ni lho phyogs su 'byung zhing 'jig rten
NK127(jo)001:810: gyi khams mi mjed 'di yang de'i nang du gtogs
NK127(jo)001:811: / so // 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa de
NK127(jo)001:812: ltar sangs rgyas pa de'i tshe ming ni de bzhin
NK127(jo)001:813: gshegs pa kun tu gzigs pa zhes bya bar 'gyur
NK127(jo)001:814: / so // ro // gang gis phyogs bcu'i 'jig
NK127(jo)001:815: rten gyi khams bye ba khrag khrig brgya stong tshad
NK127(jo)001:816: med grangs med pa kun gyis sangs rgyas bcom ldan
NK127(jo)001:818: sems can gang gis de bzhin gshegs pa de mthong
NK127(jo)001:819: bar gyur pa de thams cad bla med byang chub
NK127(jo)001:821: de'i mtshan gang gis thos pa de mi 'gyur ba la zhugs pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:822: mos pa chung ba rnams ma gtogs pa thams cad
NK127(jo)001:823: bla med byang chub tu 'tshang rgya ba de'i phyir
NK127(jo)001:824: mtshan de skad du bya'o zhes gsungs pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:825: 'khor de'i byang chub sems dpa' bye ba khrag khrig 'bum phrag du mas mgrin gcig tu smras pa /
NK127(jo)001:826: gang 'di kun tu gzigs pa zhes pa'i mtshan de ni tshul dang 'dra ste /
NK127(jo)001:827: sems can gang dag gis sangs rgyas de'i mtshan thos
NK127(jo)001:828: pa dag kyang rnyed pa legs par rnyed pa yin
NK127(jo)001:829: na zhing der skyes par gyur pa lta ci smos
NK127(jo)001:830: / gang dag gis lung bstan pa'i chos kyi rnam
NK127(jo)001:831: grangs 'di dang 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa'i ming
NK127(jo)001:832: thos pa de dag gis ni sangs rgyas mngon sum
NK127(jo)001:833: du mthong bar blta'o zhes smras pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:834: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
NK127(jo)001:835: rigs kyi bu dag de de bzhin no //
NK127(jo)001:836: ji skad smras pa de bzhin te /
NK127(jo)001:837: gang gis sangs rgyas bye ba khrag khrig phrag 'bum
NK127(jo)001:838: gyi mtshan brjod pa bas ni 'jam dpal gzhon nur
NK127(jo)001:839: gyur pa'i ming brjod na 'di nyid de bas bsod
NK127(jo)001:840: nams ches mang du skyed na /
NK127(jo)001:841: de bzhin gshegs pa kun tu gzigs de'i mtshan brjod pa lta smos kyang ci dgos /
NK127(jo)001:842: de ci'i phyir zhe na 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur
NK127(jo)001:843: pas bskal pa re re zhing sems can gyi don
NK127(jo)001:844: ji snyed byas pa'i don de ni sangs rgyas bye
NK127(jo)001:845: ba khrag khrig phrag 'bum gyis kyang ma mdzad do
NK127(jo)001:846: // zhes gsungs pas 'khor de'i lha la sogs pa
NK127(jo)001:847: 'bum phrag du mas 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa
NK127(jo)001:848: dang de bzhin gshegs pa kun tu gzigs la phyag
NK127(jo)001:850: srog chags bye ba khrag khrig 'bum phrag brgyad cu
NK127(jo)001:851: rtsa bzhi rdzogs pa'i byang chub tu sems skyes shing
NK127(jo)001:852: / sems can tshad med pa dag dge ba'i rtsa
NK127(jo)001:853: ba yongs su smin pa dang bla med byang chub
NK127(jo)001:854: las phyir mi ldog par gyur to //
NK127(jo)001:855: de nas 'khor de'i byang chub sems dpa' kha cig 'di snyam du /
NK127(jo)001:856: 'jam dpal gyi zhing dang bde ba can gyi yon
NK127(jo)001:857: tan bkod pa 'dra'o snyam du bsam pa'i rtog pa
NK127(jo)001:858: bcom ldan 'das kyis mkhyen nas bka' stsal pa /
NK127(jo)001:859: dper na mi la las skra'i rtse mo brgyar gshags
NK127(jo)001:860: pa'i chas rgya mtsho chen po las thigs pa blangs
NK127(jo)001:861: pa de bzhin du bde ba can gyi zhing gi
NK127(jo)001:862: yon tan bkod pa lta la /
NK127(jo)001:863: rgya mtsho chen po na chu'i lhag ma lus pa
NK127(jo)001:864: tsam du de bzhin gshegs pa kun tu gzigs kyi
NK127(jo)001:865: zhing gi yon tan bkod pa lta'o zhes gsungs pa
NK127(jo)001:866: dang / byang chub sems dpa' seng ge'i rtsal gyis mngon par bsgrags pa'i sgras gsol pa /
NK127(jo)001:867: zhing 'di dang mtshungs pa gzhan mnga' 'am /
NK127(jo)001:869: shar phyogs 'jig rten gyi khams smon lam la rab
NK127(jo)001:870: tu gnas pas mngon par 'phags pa zhes bya ba
NK127(jo)001:871: na de bzhin gshegs pa kun nas 'od zer yon
NK127(jo)001:872: tan rtag tu mang pa rgya mtsho'i rgyal po zhes
NK127(jo)001:873: bya ba da lta 'tsho zhing gzhes la sku tshe'i
NK127(jo)001:874: tshad dpag tu med pa yod de de'i zhing dang
NK127(jo)001:875: kun tu gzigs pa'i zhing ni 'dra ste chad lhag
NK127(jo)001:876: med do // byang chub sems dpa' bsam gyis mi
NK127(jo)001:877: khyab pa'i go bgos pa 'jam dpal gyi spyod pa
NK127(jo)001:878: 'di la gnas pa bzhi yod de de dag gi
NK127(jo)001:879: zhing gi bkod pa yang 'di 'dra ste /
NK127(jo)001:883: smon lam blo gros zhes bya'o //
NK127(jo)001:884: de nas byang chub sems dpa' seng ge'i rtsal gyis
NK127(jo)001:885: mngon par bsgrags pa'i sgras 'jam dpal khyod ji srid
NK127(jo)001:886: cig nas 'tshang rgya zhes dris pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:887: smras pa gang gi tshe nam mkha'i khams gzugs can du gyur pa de'i tshe bdag 'tshang rgya'o //
NK127(jo)001:888: de bzhin du sgyu ma'i skyes bu sogs 'tshang rgya ba de'i tshe 'tshang rgya'o //
NK127(jo)001:889: 'jam dpal nyid kyang byang chub byang chub nyid kyang
NK127(jo)001:890: 'jam dpal te stong pa nyid de ni byang chub
NK127(jo)001:892: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
NK127(jo)001:893: rigs kyi bu de bzhin gshegs pa 'od dpag med
NK127(jo)001:894: kyi byang chub sems dpa' dang nyan thos 'dus pa
NK127(jo)001:896: dper na yul ma ga d+h+aa'i til gyi dong nas
NK127(jo)001:897: til 'bru gcig blangs pa lta bu bde ba can
NK127(jo)001:899: til lhag ma lta bu de bzhin gshegs pa kun
NK127(jo)001:900: tu gzigs kyi zhing gi 'dus par lta ste de
NK127(jo)001:901: ltar khyad che'o // de bzhin gshegs pa kun tu
NK127(jo)001:902: gzigs de sku tshe'i tshad ji tsam bzhugs pa ni
NK127(jo)001:903: 'di ltar stong chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khams 'di
NK127(jo)001:904: rdul phra rab tu byas pa de snyed kyi bskal
NK127(jo)001:905: pa'i grangs kyis kyang brgya stong gi cha nas rgyur
NK127(jo)001:906: yang smos par mi 'gyur ba'i bar du 'gyur ro
NK127(jo)001:907: ltar khyad che'o // // de'i tshul gyis de bzhin
NK127(jo)001:908: gshegs pa de'i tshe yi tshad ni grangs med tshad
NK127(jo)001:910: de nas yang 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa 'tshang rgya ba'i dus de'i tshad bka' stsal pa /
NK127(jo)001:911: dper na stong chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khams 'di skyes bu la las rdul du byas te /
NK127(jo)001:912: de las skyes bu la las rdul phra rab gcig
NK127(jo)001:913: khyer te rdul phra rab ji snyed pa de snyed
NK127(jo)001:914: kyi stong chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khams 'das nas
NK127(jo)001:915: rdul phra rab gcig bzhag ste tshul des shar phyogs
NK127(jo)001:916: su rdul de thams cad zad par bkod la /
NK127(jo)001:917: de bzhin du skyes bu gnyis pas lho phyogs su
NK127(jo)001:918: rdul de ltar bor ba sogs phyogs bcur tshul des
NK127(jo)001:919: brtsis pa'i phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten gyi khams de dag
NK127(jo)001:920: brgya stong bye ba 'bum phrag la sogs pas bgrang
NK127(jo)001:921: mi nus so // de ltar rdul bor ba dang
NK127(jo)001:922: ma bor pa'i 'jig rten de thams cad rdul phra
NK127(jo)001:924: de'i grangs rtsis la mkhas pas brgya stong bye ba
NK127(jo)001:925: la sogs pa'i tshul du shes pa'am bgrang bar mi
NK127(jo)001:926: nus te grangs de la sems can rnams myos par
NK127(jo)001:927: 'gyur ro // de bzhin gshegs pas ni rdul phra
NK127(jo)001:928: rab de la brgya phrag 'di snyed cig yod do
NK127(jo)001:929: 'gyur ro // zhe'am / de bzhin du stong la
NK127(jo)001:930: sogs pa'i dbang du byas na 'di snyed cig yod
NK127(jo)001:931: do zhes bgrang ba'i tshul gyis thugs su chud la
NK127(jo)001:932: 'gyur ro // zhe'am / / de bas lhag pa'i
NK127(jo)001:933: grangs rnams kyang rnam pa thams cad du mkhyen no
NK127(jo)001:935: byang chub sems dpa' byams pas gsol pa /
NK127(jo)001:936: bcom ldan 'das gal te ye shes chen po de
NK127(jo)001:937: lta bu'i slad du byang chub sems dpa' phyi ma'i
NK127(jo)001:938: matha'i mur thug par sems can dmyal ba chen por
NK127(jo)001:939: bsregs kyang bzod par bgyi ste ye shes de lta
NK127(jo)001:941: bka' stsal pa de de bzhin te de de bzhin no //
NK127(jo)001:942: sems can mos pa dang brtson 'grus chung zhing le
NK127(jo)001:943: lo che ba ma gtogs su zhig de lta bu'i
NK127(jo)001:944: ye shes la 'dod pa mi skyed /
NK127(jo)001:945: gong du bstan pa phyogs bcur rdul bor ba dang
NK127(jo)001:946: ma bor ba'i zhing de dag thams cad rdul du
NK127(jo)001:947: byas pa'i grangs de las kyang mang ba'i bskal par
NK127(jo)001:948: da dung 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa byang chub
NK127(jo)001:949: kyi spyad pa spyod par 'gyur te /
NK127(jo)001:950: de'i smon lam dang yang dag par 'jug pa ni bsam gyis mi khyab pas /
NK127(jo)001:951: de'i byang chub thob pa'i tshe'i tshad dang byang chub
NK127(jo)001:952: sems dpa'i dge 'dun yang bsam gyis mi khyab par
NK127(jo)001:954: byang chub sems dpa' seng ge'i rtsal gyis mngon par bsgrags pa'i sgras 'di skad du /
NK127(jo)001:955: 'jam dpal 'di bskal pa 'di snyed du yang skyo
NK127(jo)001:956: ba mi skyed pa'i 'jug pa chen po de ngo
NK127(jo)001:957: mtshar zhing spyod pa chen po ngo mtshar ro zhes
NK127(jo)001:958: bcom ldan 'das la gsol pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:959: 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pas smras pa /
NK127(jo)001:960: nam mkha'i khams 'di bskal pa 'di tsam 'das so
NK127(jo)001:961: zhes mi rtog pa bzhin du byang chub sems dpa'
NK127(jo)001:962: yang chos gang la yang de'i 'du shes 'jug pa
NK127(jo)001:963: med pas skyo ba dang skye ba dang 'pho ba
NK127(jo)001:965: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
NK127(jo)001:966: rigs kyi bu byang chub sems dpa' gang la las
NK127(jo)001:967: de bzhin gshegs pa'i spyan sgrib pa med pas phyogs
NK127(jo)001:968: bcur sangs rgyas kyi zhing ji snyed cig gzigs pa
NK127(jo)001:969: de thams cad rin po che sna bdun gyis bkang
NK127(jo)001:970: ste / de bzhin gshegs pa re re la phul
NK127(jo)001:971: ba dang de bzhin du sems can thams cad la
NK127(jo)001:972: snyoms pa'i sems kyis tshul khrims kyi sdom pa thams
NK127(jo)001:973: cad yang dag par blang ba la gnas te phyi
NK127(jo)001:974: ma'i matha'i mur thug gi bar du sbyin pa byin
NK127(jo)001:975: ste / pa bas / byang chub sems dpa' gang
NK127(jo)001:976: gis chos kyi rnam grangs 'di 'dzin pa dang 'chang
NK127(jo)001:978: 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa'i rjes su bslab par
NK127(jo)001:979: bya'o zhes bya ba'i bar du sems bskyed cing gom
NK127(jo)001:981: bsod nams kyi phung po snga mas brgya'i cha nas
NK127(jo)001:982: dpe dang rgyur yang mi bzod pa'i bar du gsungs
NK127(jo)001:983: so // de nas 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa
NK127(jo)001:984: ting nge 'dzin kun nas snang ba sgyu ma lta
NK127(jo)001:985: bu 'byung ba zhes bya ba la snyoms par zhugs
NK127(jo)001:986: ma thag tu 'khor der 'dus pa'i byang chub sems
NK127(jo)001:987: dpa' ji snyed pas phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten gyi khams
NK127(jo)001:988: mtha' yas mu med pa dag gi sangs rgyas rnams
NK127(jo)001:989: so // mthong ste / de kun gyi spyan snga
NK127(jo)001:990: na 'jam dpal gzhon nu 'dug ste rang gi sangs
NK127(jo)001:991: rgyas kyi zhing gi yon tan bkod pa ston par
NK127(jo)001:992: mthong nas de dag 'di snyam du 'jam dpal 'di
NK127(jo)001:993: de ltar 'jig rten gyi khams mang por cig char
NK127(jo)001:994: snang ba ni smon lam dang ting nge 'dzin dang
NK127(jo)001:995: ye shes kyi khyad par ngo mtshar che'o snyam du
NK127(jo)001:996: ngo mtshar gyi 'du shes skyes par gyur to //
NK127(jo)001:998: ma skyes dgra'i 'gyod pa bsal pa'i mdo las /
NK127(jo)001:999: bcom ldan 'das bya rgod kyi phung po'i ri la 'khor gyis kun nas bskor zhing bzhugs ba'i tshe /
NK127(jo)001:1000: 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa ri rab kyi bang
NK127(jo)001:1001: rim gyi ngos na skyes bu dam pa nyi shu
NK127(jo)001:1002: rtsa lnga dang dga' ldan gyi lha'i bu bzhi sogs
NK127(jo)001:1003: 'khor mang po dang lhan cig chos kyi gtam smra
NK127(jo)001:1004: zhing 'jam dpal gyis sprul pa'i de bzhin gshegs pas
NK127(jo)001:1005: chos bstan pa sogs kyis sems can mang po smin
NK127(jo)001:1006: par byas nas / bcom ldan 'das kyis 'jam dpal
NK127(jo)001:1007: la 'ong ba'i phyir mtshan ma mdzad pa na 'jam
NK127(jo)001:1008: dpal 'khor dang bcas pa sangs rgyas kyi drung du
NK127(jo)001:1009: 'ongs nas chos sna tshogs bgros pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:1010: 'khor de na lha'i bu sngon spyod pa dang ldan
NK127(jo)001:1011: pa byang chub kyi sems stong ba nyis brgyas bdag
NK127(jo)001:1012: cag gis bla med byang chub bsgrub mi nus kyi
NK127(jo)001:1013: nyan rang gi mya ngan las 'ada'o snyam pa de
NK127(jo)001:1014: dag bla med byang chub tu gzhug pa'i phyir /
NK127(jo)001:1015: bcom ldan 'das kyis 'khor gyi phyi rol du khyim bdag zhig sprul te /
NK127(jo)001:1016: des lhung bzed kha zas ro brgyas gang ba zhig sangs rgyas la phul ba bzhes pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:1017: 'jam dpal gyis bcom ldan 'das la zhus pa /
NK127(jo)001:1018: zhal zas 'di las bdag la ma stsol par gsol
NK127(jo)001:1019: na byas pa gzo bar mi mdzad par 'gyur ro
NK127(jo)001:1021: sh+aa ri'i bus 'jam dpal gyis sngon bcom ldan 'das
NK127(jo)001:1022: la phan ci zhig btags na da byas pa mi
NK127(jo)001:1023: gzo bas rgol snyam pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:1024: de'i rtog pa mkhyen nas sangs rgyas kyis bka' stsal pa /
NK127(jo)001:1025: sh+aa ri'i bu de bzhin gshegs pa dus mkhyen te
NK127(jo)001:1026: khyod la bka' stsol gyi sdod cig ces gsungs nas
NK127(jo)001:1027: lhung bzed de sa chen po'i nang du btang ba
NK127(jo)001:1028: dang / de ma thag 'og phyogs sangs rgyas kyi
NK127(jo)001:1029: zhing na sangs rgyas bzhugs pa de dag gi spyan
NK127(jo)001:1030: snga nas song ste zhing gang+g+aa'i klung gi bye snyed
NK127(jo)001:1031: dang / 'das nas / 'jig rten gyi khams snang
NK127(jo)001:1032: ba dang ldan zhes bya ba na de bzhin gshegs
NK127(jo)001:1033: pa 'od zer rgyal po bzhugs pa'i zhing na lhung
NK127(jo)001:1034: bzed de bar snang la 'dug par gyur ro //
NK127(jo)001:1035: sangs rgyas de rnams la lhung bzed de'i rgyu mtshan 'khor gyis zhus pa na /
NK127(jo)001:1036: steng phyogs mi mjed kyi zhing nas de bzhin gshegs
NK127(jo)001:1037: pa sh+aakya thub pas byang chub sems dpa' gdul ba'i
NK127(jo)001:1038: don du btang ba yin no zhes gsungs so //
NK127(jo)001:1039: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis sh+aa ri'i bu la lhung bzed de tshol zhes gsungs pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:1040: des ting nge 'dzin stong phrag bcu la zhugs nas
NK127(jo)001:1041: rang gi shes rab kyi stobs dang sangs rgyas kyi
NK127(jo)001:1042: mthus sangs rgyas kyi zhing stong phrag bcur song yang
NK127(jo)001:1043: ma mthong nas slar sangs rgyas kyi spyan sngar 'dug
NK127(jo)001:1044: go // de bzhin moo gal bu dang /
NK127(jo)001:1046: nyan thos chen po lnga brgya tsam gyi rdzu 'phrul
NK127(jo)001:1047: dang lha'i mig gis btsal kyang lhung bzed de ma
NK127(jo)001:1048: mthong nas / rab 'byor gyis byang chub sems dpa'
NK127(jo)001:1049: byams pa la lhung bzed tshol cig ces smras pa
NK127(jo)001:1050: mthong nas / dang / byams pas smras pa /
NK127(jo)001:1051: bdag ni de bzhin gshegs pas bla med byang chub
NK127(jo)001:1052: tu skye ba gcig gis thogs par lung bstan mod
NK127(jo)001:1053: kyi / bdag gis ni ting 'dzin de'i ming yang
NK127(jo)001:1054: mi shes pa'i ting nge 'dzin de la 'jam dpal
NK127(jo)001:1055: gzhon nur gyur pas ni 'jug ldang byed do //
NK127(jo)001:1056: bdag byang chub thob pa na 'jam dpal dang 'dra
NK127(jo)001:1057: ba'i byang sems dag gis kyang de bzhin gshegs pa'i
NK127(jo)001:1058: gom pa 'dor 'jog tsam yang mi shes pa'i dus
NK127(jo)001:1060: de bas na 'jam dpal la gsol cig dang des 'byin nus so zhes smras pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:1061: rab 'byor gyis 'jam dpal la lhung bzed de 'byin
NK127(jo)001:1062: par gsol ba dang bcom ldan 'das kyis kyang de
NK127(jo)001:1063: ltar gyis zhes gsung gnang bas /
NK127(jo)001:1064: 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa kun gyi rjes su
NK127(jo)001:1065: song ba zhes bya ba'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms
NK127(jo)001:1066: par zhugs nas stan de las ma g.yos la /
NK127(jo)001:1067: 'khor de na snang bzhin du lag pa g.yas pa
NK127(jo)001:1068: brkyangs nas 'og phyogs kyi sangs rgyas kyi zhing de
NK127(jo)001:1069: thams cad du lag pa des sangs rgyas rnams la
NK127(jo)001:1070: phyag 'tshal zhing bsnyun dri ba'i sgra dang bcas te
NK127(jo)001:1071: / lag pa'i ba spu'i khung bu kun nas 'od
NK127(jo)001:1072: zer bye ba brgya stong 'phro ba'i rtser pad+ma'i snying
NK127(jo)001:1073: po la de bzhin gshegs pa'i sku bzhugs pa de
NK127(jo)001:1074: dag gis de bzhin gshegs pa sh+aakya thub pa'i basngagasa
NK127(jo)001:1075: / pa brjod cing / gang du song ba'i sangs
NK127(jo)001:1076: rgyas kyi zhing de dag gis yang rnam pa drug
NK127(jo)001:1077: tu g.yos te snang ba chen pos khyab pa dang
NK127(jo)001:1078: gdugs dang rgyal mtshan ba dan dag gis brgyan par
NK127(jo)001:1079: / pa brjod cing / gyur to // de nas
NK127(jo)001:1080: lag pa g.yas pa des sangs rgyas kyi zhing gang+g+aa'i
NK127(jo)001:1081: klung gi bye ma snyed bdun cu rtsa gnyis 'das
NK127(jo)001:1082: / pa brjod cing / gyur to // nas /
NK127(jo)001:1083: de bzhin gshegs pa 'od zer rgyal po'i zhing snang
NK127(jo)001:1084: ldan du phyin nas bsnyun dri ba dang 'od zer
NK127(jo)001:1086: sangs rgyas de'i bsnyen bkur byed pa byang chub sems
NK127(jo)001:1087: dpa' 'od kyi dpal zhes pas 'di lta bu'i rdzu
NK127(jo)001:1088: 'phrul ldan pa'i lag pa lta na sdug pa 'di
NK127(jo)001:1089: ltar dga' bar bgyid pa de su'i lags zhes gsol
NK127(jo)001:1090: pa dang / steng phyogs mi mjed nas byung ba'i rgyu mtshan bka' stsal pas /
NK127(jo)001:1091: zhing de'i byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyis mi mjed
NK127(jo)001:1092: 'di dang de bzhin gshegs pa sh+aakya thub pa dang
NK127(jo)001:1093: byang chub sems dpa' 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa
NK127(jo)001:1094: mthong bar gsol ba btab pas /
NK127(jo)001:1095: de bzhin gshegs pa 'od zer gyi rgyal po'i smin
NK127(jo)001:1096: mtshams nas 'od btang ba des reg pa'i sems can
NK127(jo)001:1097: rnams 'khor los sgyur ba'i bde ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:1098: rnal 'byor spyod pa rnams 'bras bu thob pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:1099: byang chub sems dpa' rnams ting nge 'dzin nyi ma
NK127(jo)001:1100: lta bu'i sgron ma thob par gyur cing zhing de'i
NK127(jo)001:1101: sems can rnams kyis mi mjed kyi zhing 'di mthong
NK127(jo)001:1102: bar gyur to // de mthong nas byang chub sems
NK127(jo)001:1103: dpa' 'od kyi dpal gyis mchi ma 'byin bzhin 'di
NK127(jo)001:1104: bar gyur to // skad du / rin thang ma
NK127(jo)001:1105: mchis pa'i nor bu 'dam du stsal ba bzhin du
NK127(jo)001:1106: bar gyur to // skad du / / bcom ldan
NK127(jo)001:1107: 'das byang chub sems dpa' chen po de dag mi
NK127(jo)001:1108: mjed der bzhugs zhes gsol pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:1109: sangs rgyas des bka' stsal pa /
NK127(jo)001:1111: zhing 'dir bskal pa bcur bsam gtan la gnas shing
NK127(jo)001:1112: spyod pa bas mi mjed der snga dro gcig byams
NK127(jo)001:1113: pa bsgom pa bsod nams mang du 'phel te /
NK127(jo)001:1114: mi mjed der dam chos srung ba'i sems dpa' chen
NK127(jo)001:1115: po de dag gi las sgrib dang nyon mongs thams
NK127(jo)001:1116: cad byang bar 'gyur ro zhes gsungs so //
NK127(jo)001:1117: de ltar sangs rgyas 'od zer rgyal pos btang ba'i
NK127(jo)001:1118: 'od de zhing 'di'i sems can rnams kyis mthong zhing
NK127(jo)001:1119: bcom ldan 'das kyis de'i rgyu mtshan de lta bu
NK127(jo)001:1120: gsungs so // de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis zhing
NK127(jo)001:1121: 'di'i sems can rnams kyis 'od phyogs kyi zhing de
NK127(jo)001:1122: mthong ba de lta bu'i rdzu 'phrul mdzad de 'od
NK127(jo)001:1124: 'od des reg pa'i byang chub sems dpa' thams cad
NK127(jo)001:1125: ri rab lhun po lta bu'i sgron ma zhes bya
NK127(jo)001:1126: ba'i ting nge 'dzin thob cing zhing 'dir gnas pa
NK127(jo)001:1127: dag gis 'og phyogs kyi sangs rgyas kyi zhing de
NK127(jo)001:1129: 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa'i lag pa g.yas pa des zhing de nas lhung bzed blangs te /
NK127(jo)001:1130: byang chub sems dpa' bye ba khrag khrig brgya stong du mas bskor nas steng du phyung ngo //
NK127(jo)001:1131: lag pa de gang nas gang du phyung ba'i zhing
NK127(jo)001:1132: der 'od zer nub par gyur cing sangs rgyas bcom
NK127(jo)001:1133: ldan 'das sh+aakya thub pa'i spyan sngar lhung bzed de
NK127(jo)001:1134: nam mkha' la 'phangs nas bcom ldan 'das kyi zhabs
NK127(jo)001:1135: la phyag 'tshal te lhung bzed bzhes shig par gsol
NK127(jo)001:1136: ba dang bzhes par mdzad do //
NK127(jo)001:1137: de nas 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa'i lag pa
NK127(jo)001:1138: g.yas pa dang lhan cig 'ongs pa'i byang chub sems
NK127(jo)001:1139: dpa' de dag gis bcom ldan 'das la phyag 'tshal
NK127(jo)001:1140: zhing bsnyun gsol nas rang rang gi stan la 'khod
NK127(jo)001:1141: do // de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis sh+aa ri'i bu la sngon gyi byung ba bka' stsal pa /
NK127(jo)001:1142: 'das pa'i dus bskal pa bye ba khrag khrig brgya
NK127(jo)001:1143: stong grangs med pa de'i pha rol gyi yang pha
NK127(jo)001:1145: 'jig rten gyi khams mi smod pa dang ldan pa
NK127(jo)001:1146: zhes bya bar de bzhin gshegs pa mi thub pa'i
NK127(jo)001:1147: rgyal mtshan zhes bya ba byung ste theg pa gsum
NK127(jo)001:1148: las brtsams nas chos ston to //
NK127(jo)001:1149: der dge slong chos smra ba ye shes rgyal mtshan
NK127(jo)001:1150: zhes bya ba gos bgos te rgyal po'i pho brang
NK127(jo)001:1151: rgya chen po dad ldan pa zhes par bsod snyoms
NK127(jo)001:1152: la song nas zas ro brgya dang ldan pa khyer
NK127(jo)001:1154: tshong dpon gyi bu dri ma med pa'i dpung pa
NK127(jo)001:1155: zhes pha ma'i pang na 'dug pa des dge slong
NK127(jo)001:1156: de mthong bas ma'i pang nas dge slong de'i drung
NK127(jo)001:1157: du brgyugs shing bza' ba bslangs pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:1158: dge slong des de la mod ka zhig stsal lo //
NK127(jo)001:1159: des bza' ba snyogs nas dge slong de yi phyi
NK127(jo)001:1160: bzhin 'brangs te song nas de bzhin gshegs pa mi
NK127(jo)001:1161: thub pa'i rgyal mtshan gyi drung du phyin pa dang
NK127(jo)001:1162: / dge slong des bsod snyoms ci rnyed pa de
NK127(jo)001:1163: khye'u de la byin nas khye'u 'di de bzhin gshegs
NK127(jo)001:1164: pa la gsol cig ces byas pas /
NK127(jo)001:1165: khye'u des de bzhin gshegs pa'i lhung bzed bkang yang
NK127(jo)001:1166: zad par ma gyur nas nyan thos brgyad khri dang
NK127(jo)001:1167: byang chub sems dpa' khri nyis stong dang bcas pa
NK127(jo)001:1168: la bstabs te / sangs rgyas 'khor dang bcas pa
NK127(jo)001:1169: la zhag bdun du ngoms par bstabs kyang zad par
NK127(jo)001:1170: ma gyur nas khye'u de rab tu dga' zhing tshigs
NK127(jo)001:1172: de'i tshe dge slong des khye'u de mchog gsum la skyabs su 'gro bar byas shing khrims phog nas /
NK127(jo)001:1173: nyes pa mthol ba dang rjes su yi rangs pa
NK127(jo)001:1174: dang gsol ba gdab pa dang bla na med pa'i
NK127(jo)001:1175: byang chub tu sems skyed du bcug go //
NK127(jo)001:1176: khye'u de'i pha mas kyang khye'u tshol ba'i slad du
NK127(jo)001:1177: de bzhin gshegs pa de'i drung du phyin nas de
NK127(jo)001:1178: dag dang sems can mang pos kyang bla med byang
NK127(jo)001:1179: chub tu sems bskyed cing rab tu byung bar byas
NK127(jo)001:1180: so // de'i tshe dge slong chos smra ba ye
NK127(jo)001:1181: shes rgyal mtshan de ni 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur
NK127(jo)001:1182: so // pa yin la / tshong dpon gyi bu
NK127(jo)001:1183: dri ma med pa'i dpung pa zhes bya ba de
NK127(jo)001:1184: nyid da lta sh+aakya thub pa nga yin te nga
NK127(jo)001:1185: la de ltar bsod snyoms byin nas byang chub tu
NK127(jo)001:1187: de ni ngas byang chub kyi sems thog mar bskyed
NK127(jo)001:1188: pa yin la rnam grangs des na de bzhin gshegs
NK127(jo)001:1189: pa'i sangs rgyas kyi che ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:1190: stobs bcu mi 'jigs pa la sogs pa'i chos thams
NK127(jo)001:1191: cad 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pas sems skyed du
NK127(jo)001:1193: nga ji 'dra ba phyogs bcu na sh+aakya thub pa
NK127(jo)001:1194: zhes bya ba'i sangs rgyas grangs med dpag tu med
NK127(jo)001:1195: pa dang / de bzhin du ti sha zhes bya ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:1196: rgyal ba zhes bya ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:1197: gtsug ldan zhes bya ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:1198: mar me mdzad ces bya ba dag mthong ste /
NK127(jo)001:1199: gang 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pas byang chub la
NK127(jo)001:1200: bzhag nas da ltar chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba'i
NK127(jo)001:1201: de bzhin gshegs pa de dag gi mtshan kyang bskal
NK127(jo)001:1202: pa'am bskal pa'i lhag ma ma lus par brjod par
NK127(jo)001:1203: gyur kyang zad par mi 'gyur na /
NK127(jo)001:1204: gang byang sems kyi spyad pa spyod pa dang dga'
NK127(jo)001:1205: ldan na gnas pa sogs dang byang chub snying por
NK127(jo)001:1206: 'dug pa'i bar dag ni shin tu mang ba lta
NK127(jo)001:1207: ci smos te / rnam grangs des na /
NK127(jo)001:1208: gang dag byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyi mgon no //
NK127(jo)001:1211: byed du 'jug pa'o zhes byang chub sems dpa' rnams
NK127(jo)001:1212: kyis 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa la yang dag
NK127(jo)001:1214: zhes gsungs pas lha'i bu nyis brgya po 'di snyam du /
NK127(jo)001:1215: chos thams cad rgyu'i rjes su 'gro zhing rkyen la rag las pa /

NK127(jo)001:1503: byed do // de nas bskal pa grangs med pa
NK127(jo)001:1504: stong phrag brgyad brgya'i bar du sems can smin par
NK127(jo)001:1505: byed cing sbyong ba'i spyad pa spyod do //
NK127(jo)001:1506: des smin par byas pa'i sems can de dag las
NK127(jo)001:1507: dang nyon mongs pa'i sgrib pa med par 'gyur zhing
NK127(jo)001:1508: / dbang po rno la 'gyod pa dang the tshom med par 'gyur ro //
NK127(jo)001:1509: ma skyes dgra 'di bskal pa grangs med pa stong phrag brgyad brgya na 'tshang rgya bar 'gyur te /
NK127(jo)001:1510: bskal pa mthong na dga' ba zhes bya ba la
NK127(jo)001:1511: 'jig rten gyi khams 'dam gyi rnyog pa med par
NK127(jo)001:1512: de bzhin gshegs pa yul shin tu rnam par dag
NK127(jo)001:1514: zhing der su yang 'gyod pa la gnas bzhin 'chi ba'i dus mi byed pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:1517: de nas zhing gzhan nas 'jam dpal dang 'grogs te
NK127(jo)001:1518: zhing 'dir phyin pa'i byang chub sems dpa' thams cad
NK127(jo)001:1519: kyis gsol pa / bcom ldan 'das phyogs gang na
NK127(jo)001:1520: 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa gnas pa de na
NK127(jo)001:1521: de bzhin gshegs pas stongs pa ma lags te /
NK127(jo)001:1522: der ni bcom ldan 'das kyis dgongs par bgyid mi 'tshal lo //
NK127(jo)001:1523: de ci'i slad du na 'jam dpal gyis smin par
NK127(jo)001:1524: byas pa'i sems can rnams ni ngan 'gro dang mi
NK127(jo)001:1525: khom pa dang bdud kyi las dang nyon mongs pa'i
NK127(jo)001:1528: rigs kyi bu ji skad smras pa de de bzhin no zhes bka' stsal to //
NK127(jo)001:1529: phyogs bcu nas 'dus pa'i byang chub sems dpa' rnams
NK127(jo)001:1530: kyis 'jig rten gyi khams gang ba'i me tog gis
NK127(jo)001:1531: de bzhin gshegs pa dang 'jam dpal la gtor te
NK127(jo)001:1532: / thub pa chen po'i chos kyi sgron ma yun ring du 'bar bar gyur cig /
NK127(jo)001:1533: bcom ldan 'das bdag cag gi sha dang khrag gis
NK127(jo)001:1534: 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa la sman yon thogs
NK127(jo)001:1536: mchod pa gzhan gyis lta smos kyang ci 'tshal zhes
NK127(jo)001:1537: pa sogs ched du brjod nas bcom ldan 'das la
NK127(jo)001:1538: lan gsum bskor te 'jam dpal la yang mchod nas
NK127(jo)001:1539: rang gi sangs rgyas kyi zhing du chos kyi rnam
NK127(jo)001:1540: grangs des sems can dpag med rdzogs byang la nges
NK127(jo)001:1541: par byas so // sher phyin bdun brgya pa las /
NK127(jo)001:1542: bcom ldan 'das 'jam dpal 'di ni bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i dpal lo //
NK127(jo)001:1543: de ci'i slad du zhe na /
NK127(jo)001:1544: 'di ltar 'di'i spobs pa gang dag gang lags pa'i
NK127(jo)001:1545: spobs pa de dang de nyid bsam gyis mi khyab
NK127(jo)001:1546: pa nyid lags so zhes zhus pa la de de
NK127(jo)001:1548: dkon mchog ta la la'i mdo las /
NK127(jo)001:1549: sh+aa ri'i bus 'jam dpal la smras pa /
NK127(jo)001:1551: dper na rdo rje ngan ngon gyi sa kyang ri brag chen po rnam par 'jig go //
NK127(jo)001:1552: rigs kyi bu de bzhin du khyod kyi ba spu'i
NK127(jo)001:1553: khung bu gcig na shes rab 'dug pa gang yin
NK127(jo)001:1554: pa de ni kho bo lta bu'i sems can rdul
NK127(jo)001:1555: phra rab kyi rdul snyed rnams la med do //
NK127(jo)001:1557: klu'i rgyal po ma dros pas zhus pa'i mdo las /
NK127(jo)001:1558: bcom ldan 'das klu'i rgyal po ma dros pas spyan
NK127(jo)001:1559: drangs nas der chos kyi bka' mchid mdzad pa'i tshe
NK127(jo)001:1560: / mtsho chen po ma dros pa nas rin po
NK127(jo)001:1561: che'i me tog shing rta'i 'khor lo tsam dri rab
NK127(jo)001:1562: tu zhim pa 'dab ma brgya stong dang ldan pa
NK127(jo)001:1563: / / rin po che'i d+r+wa bas g.yogs pas gang
NK127(jo)001:1564: ba de dag gi nang nas rin po che'i pad+ma
NK127(jo)001:1565: gcig shin tu mdzes shing lta na sdug la mchog
NK127(jo)001:1567: kun dga' bos mthong nas bcom ldan 'das la 'di su'i snga ltas lags zhes gsol pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:1569: cung zhig sdod dang mthong bar 'gyur ro gsungs nas
NK127(jo)001:1570: ring por ma lon par zhing 'di nas chu bo
NK127(jo)001:1571: gang+g+aa'i klung drug cu'i bye ma snyed kyi zhing 'das
NK127(jo)001:1572: pa na / 'og phyogs 'jig rten gyi khams rin
NK127(jo)001:1573: chen tog gi sangs rgyas kyi zhing rin po che
NK127(jo)001:1574: bkod pa'i 'jig rten gyi khams nas /
NK127(jo)001:1575: byang chub sems dpa' drug khris bskor ba'i 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa /
NK127(jo)001:1576: klu'i rgyal po ma dros pa'i rnam par dag pa'i
NK127(jo)001:1577: lam gyi chos kyi sgo'i le'u nyan pa'i phyir 'ongs
NK127(jo)001:1578: te / pad+ma de dag la skyil mo krung bcas
NK127(jo)001:1579: nas 'khod pa la thams cad dang ldan pa'i 'khor
NK127(jo)001:1580: de ngo mtshar zhing byang chub sems dpa' de dag
NK127(jo)001:1582: 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa nam mkha' la 'phags
NK127(jo)001:1583: pa tshangs pa dang brgya byin sogs lha rnams kyis
NK127(jo)001:1584: steng nas rin po che'i gdugs 'dzin cing phyag 'tshal
NK127(jo)001:1585: bar byed la / 'jam dpal dang byang chub sems
NK127(jo)001:1586: dpa' de dag t+aa la bdun tsam du nam mkhar
NK127(jo)001:1587: 'phags nas bcom ldan 'das la mchod pa'i phyir sngon
NK127(jo)001:1588: ma mthong ma thos pa'i me tog gi char phab
NK127(jo)001:1589: cing me tog de las sangs rgyas rin chen tog
NK127(jo)001:1590: gis bcom ldan 'das la snyun gsol ba sogs kyi
NK127(jo)001:1591: bar byed la / sgra byung zhing / slar bab
NK127(jo)001:1592: nas bcom ldan 'das la phyag 'tshal te rang rang
NK127(jo)001:1594: de nas gnas brtan 'od srung gis bcom ldan 'das
NK127(jo)001:1595: la de bzhin gshegs pa rin chen tog gi zhing
NK127(jo)001:1596: de gang na mchi zhes zhus pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:1598: rdzu 'phrul gyi stobs phun sum tshogs pa khyod 'jig
NK127(jo)001:1599: rten gyi khams der 'gro na tshe zad de yongs
NK127(jo)001:1600: su mya ngan las 'das kyang zhing der mi phyin
NK127(jo)001:1602: de nas gnas brtan 'od srung dang 'jam dpal dag sems rnam par grol ba'i gnas las bgros pas /
NK127(jo)001:1603: 'od srung gis smras pa 'jam dpal khyod spobs par gyis shig /
NK127(jo)001:1604: kho bo la ni khyod la lan gdab pa'i nus pa med do //
NK127(jo)001:1605: byang chub sems dpa' shes rab brtsegs kyis 'jam dpal la smras pa /
NK127(jo)001:1606: gnas brtan 'od srung 'di ci'i phyir sems zhing dman pa lta bur ston /
NK127(jo)001:1608: 'di ni nyan thos te 'jigs pa med pa ma yin no //
NK127(jo)001:1610: rnam thar gsum la ci'i phyir nyi tshe'i 'du shes su mdzad /
NK127(jo)001:1612: de bzhin gshegs pa thabs mkhas pas rnam thar sgo
NK127(jo)001:1613: gsum tshad med pa la nyi tshe ba'i 'du shes
NK127(jo)001:1615: de nas ma dros pa dang 'jam dpal gyis /
NK127(jo)001:1616: gzugs la sogs pa'i chos thams cad de bzhin gshegs par blta ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:1617: sha la sogs pa'i mig gis de bzhin gshegs pa lta ba med kyang /
NK127(jo)001:1618: mi mnyam pa dang mnyam pa 'dus ma byas pa
NK127(jo)001:1619: rang bzhin gyis zhi ba'i don la rtog pa med
NK127(jo)001:1620: par 'jug pas de bzhin gshegs pa blta bar bshad
NK127(jo)001:1621: pas byang chub sems dpa' der lhags pa thams cad
NK127(jo)001:1623: 'jam dpal gyis bstan pa zhes bya ba'i mdo las /
NK127(jo)001:1624: bcom ldan 'das rgyal byed kyi tshal na 'khor nyan
NK127(jo)001:1625: thos dang byang chub sems dpa'i tshogs kyis bskor nas
NK127(jo)001:1626: bzhugs pa'i tshe / 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pas
NK127(jo)001:1627: rin po che'i gdugs dpag tshad bcus 'khor ba tsam
NK127(jo)001:1628: thogs nas bcom ldan 'das kyi dbu'i gtsug tu 'dzin
NK127(jo)001:1629: bzhugs pa'i tshe / zhing 'dug go // der lha'i
NK127(jo)001:1630: bu mtshams bzang zhes bya bas 'jam dpal khyod bcom
NK127(jo)001:1631: ldan 'das mchod pa mdzad pas da dung thugs ma
NK127(jo)001:1632: tshim lags sam zhes smras pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:1634: lha'i bu rgya mtsho chen po ni chu bab pas mi tshim pa bzhin du /
NK127(jo)001:1635: thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyi rgya mtsho gting
NK127(jo)001:1636: dpag dka' ba tshol bar 'dod pa'i byang chub sems
NK127(jo)001:1637: dpa' chen po de bzhin gshegs pa mchod par bya
NK127(jo)001:1638: ba 'dod pas gzhar yang chog par 'dzin par mi
NK127(jo)001:1640: 'jam dpal ci la dmigs nas de bzhin gshegs pa mchod par bya /
NK127(jo)001:1642: lha'i bu dmigs pa bzhis de bzhin gshegs pa mchod par bya ste /
NK127(jo)001:1643: byang chub kyi sems la dmigs pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:1644: sems can thams cad rab tu thar bar bya ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:1645: dkon mchog gsum gyi gdung rgyun mi 'chad par bya ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:1646: sangs rgyas kyi zhing thams cad yongs su dag par bya ba la dmigs pa ste /
NK127(jo)001:1647: bzhi po de dag gis de bzhin gshegs pa mchod
NK127(jo)001:1648: par bya'o zhes gsungs pas 'khor thams cad yi rangs
NK127(jo)001:1649: so // bzhi pa sgrub pa zhes bya ba'i mdo las kyang tshul 'di dang mthun par bstan la /
NK127(jo)001:1650: der 'jam dpal gyis chos bzhi pa sgrub pa'i chos
NK127(jo)001:1651: kyi rnam grangs bstan pas lha'i bu dpal bzang ldan
NK127(jo)001:1653: 'khor dang bcas pas 'jam dpal la mchod pa'i phyir
NK127(jo)001:1654: lha'i me tog man+dara ba la sogs pas gtor ma
NK127(jo)001:1655: thag tu sangs rgyas kyi mthus steng gi bar snang
NK127(jo)001:1656: la me tog pad+ma shing rta'i 'phang lo tsam gyi
NK127(jo)001:1657: lta na sdug pa dri bsung dang ldan pa dag
NK127(jo)001:1658: gi dbus su byang chub sems dpa' mtshan so gnyis
NK127(jo)001:1659: dang ldan pa dag byung ngo //
NK127(jo)001:1660: de'i tshe bcom ldan 'das 'dzum pa mdzad pa'i zhal
NK127(jo)001:1661: gyi sgo nas 'od sna tshogs byung bas 'jig rten
NK127(jo)001:1662: kun snang bar byas te slar zhal du nub pa
NK127(jo)001:1663: dang / de'i rgyu mtshan lha'i bu dpal bzang ldan gyis zhus pa na /
NK127(jo)001:1665: steng gi bar snang la seng ge'i khrir pad+ma'i snying
NK127(jo)001:1666: po la 'khod pa'i byang chub sems dpa' phyogs bcu
