NK127(jo)001:1667: nas 'dus pa 'di dag thams cad 'jam dpal gzhon
NK127(jo)001:1668: nur gyur pas smin par byas pa ste 'dir deng
NK127(jo)001:1669: yang chos nyan du lhags so //
NK127(jo)001:1670: 'di thams cad skye ba gcig gis thogs pa ste
NK127(jo)001:1671: phyogs bcu'i zhing sna tshogs su sangs rgya bar 'gyur
NK127(jo)001:1672: ro // sh+aa ri'i bus gsol pa /
NK127(jo)001:1673: bcom ldan 'das bdag gis stong gsum gyi stong chen
NK127(jo)001:1674: po'i 'jig rten gyi khams kyi skar ma'i gzugs de
NK127(jo)001:1675: dag skad cig gcig gis bgrang spro'i /
NK127(jo)001:1676: byang chub sems dpa' 'di dag gi grangs ni lo brgyar yang bgrang bar mi nus so //
NK127(jo)001:1678: sh+aa ri'i bu 'dzam bu'i gling 'di rdul phra rab
NK127(jo)001:1679: kyi rdul gyis gang ba mtha' rtogs nus kyi byang
NK127(jo)001:1680: sems 'di dag gi grangs ni mtha' rtogs mi nus
NK127(jo)001:1682: byang sems 'di snyed sangs rgya ba'i zhing de snyed mchis dka' 'o //
NK127(jo)001:1684: sangs rgyas mi bzhugs pa'i zhing tshad med pa de
NK127(jo)001:1685: bzhin gshegs pas gzigs tshul dpe dang bcas te gsungs
NK127(jo)001:1686: pas thams cad dang ldan pa'i 'khor des bdag cag
NK127(jo)001:1687: gi ston pa ye shes kyi gzigs pa chen po
NK127(jo)001:1688: dang ldan pa bdag cag gi rnyed pa legs par
NK127(jo)001:1690: de nas lha'i bu dpal bzang ldan gyis 'jam dpal la smras pa /
NK127(jo)001:1691: 'jam dpal khyod kyis mdzad pa mdzad cing sems can
NK127(jo)001:1692: tshad med pa byang chub tu yongs su smin par
NK127(jo)001:1693: mdzad pa legs so legs so //
NK127(jo)001:1694: khyod phyogs gang na gnas pa dang chos kyi rnam
NK127(jo)001:1695: grangs 'di gang na spyod pa der ni sangs rgyas
NK127(jo)001:1696: 'byung ba dang chos kyi 'khor lo bskor bar blta'o
NK127(jo)001:1698: bcom ldan 'das kyis de de bzhin no zhes basngagasa par mdzad do //
NK127(jo)001:1699: 'phags pa kun rdzob dang don dam pa'i bden pa bstan pa zhes bya ba'i mdo las /
NK127(jo)001:1700: bcom ldan 'das rgyal po'i khab bya rgod phung po'i
NK127(jo)001:1701: ri la nyan thos dang byang chub sems dpa' dang
NK127(jo)001:1702: lha rnams kyis bskor zhing chos ston pa'i tshe /
NK127(jo)001:1703: der lha'i bu rab tu zhi ba rnam par dul
NK127(jo)001:1704: ba'i dbang phyug ces bya bas bcom ldan 'das la
NK127(jo)001:1705: gsol pa / bcom ldan 'das 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa de da lta ga na mchis /
NK127(jo)001:1706: bdag dang 'khor mang po 'di rnams skyes bu dam pa des chos bstan pa rab tu 'dod do //
NK127(jo)001:1708: zhing 'di nas shar phyogs su sangs rgyas kyi zhing stong phrag bco brgyad 'das pa na /
NK127(jo)001:1709: 'jig rten gyi khams rin po che dang ldan pa na /
NK127(jo)001:1710: de bzhin gshegs pa rin chen tog gi drung na 'dug go //
NK127(jo)001:1712: bcom ldan 'das 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa de 'dir mchi ba'i mtshan ma mdzad du gsol /
NK127(jo)001:1714: 'jam dpal las thos pa de lta bu nyan rang
NK127(jo)001:1715: thams cad dang byang sems dmigs pa can rnams las
NK127(jo)001:1716: mi thos te / de bzhin gshegs pa ma gtogs
NK127(jo)001:1717: par gzhan su yang de lta bur chos ston mi
NK127(jo)001:1718: mi thos te / nus so // bcom ldan 'das
NK127(jo)001:1719: nam 'jam dpal chos ston pa de na bdud kyi
NK127(jo)001:1720: gnas thams cad mog mog bor gyur /
NK127(jo)001:1721: bdud kun gyis glags mi rnyed cing /
NK127(jo)001:1722: pha rol rgol ba thams cad kyang shin tu tshar chod pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:1723: dmigs pa can rnams dmigs pa ma mchis par 'gyur ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:1724: dam pa'i chos kyang yun ring du gnas pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:1725: de bzhin gshegs pa yang de'i rjes su yi rangs shing rab tu gzung ba mdzad do //
NK127(jo)001:1727: de bzhin gshegs pas lha'i bus gsol ba btab par mkhyen nas /
NK127(jo)001:1728: zhal gyi mdzod spu las byung ba'i 'od zer gyis
NK127(jo)001:1729: 'jig rten 'di snang bar byas te 'jig rten gyi
NK127(jo)001:1730: khams rin po che dang ldan pa'i zhing khyab par
NK127(jo)001:1731: byas nas 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa sbran pa
NK127(jo)001:1732: des / 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa byang chub
NK127(jo)001:1733: sems dpa' stong phrag bcu dang lhan cig skyes bu'i
NK127(jo)001:1734: lag pa brkyang bskum tsam la bcom ldan 'das kyi
NK127(jo)001:1735: drung du phyin nas lus mi snang bar mkha' las
NK127(jo)001:1736: me tog gi char babs pas stong chen po'i 'jig
NK127(jo)001:1737: rten 'di kun pus nub tsam du gang ba la
NK127(jo)001:1738: 'khor thams cad ngo mtshar te de'i rgyu mtshan ci
NK127(jo)001:1740: bcom ldan 'das kyis 'jam dpal la sogs pa byang chub sems dpa' de dag gis mthur gsungs pas /
NK127(jo)001:1741: 'khor de dag gis 'jam dpal dang byang chub sems dpa' de dag lta 'dod pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:1742: 'jam dpal 'khor dang bcas pa nam mkha' las bab
NK127(jo)001:1743: ste bcom ldan 'das la phyag 'tshal nas rang rang
NK127(jo)001:1745: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis bkas gnang ba'i skabs phye ste lha'i bus dris pa la /
NK127(jo)001:1746: 'jam dpal gyis don dam par ma skyes shing brjod
NK127(jo)001:1747: du med pa'i rang bzhin bstan pas byang chub sems
NK127(jo)001:1748: dpa' chen po bgrang ba las 'das pa rnams kyis
NK127(jo)001:1749: mi skye ba'i chos la bzod pa thob pa sogs
NK127(jo)001:1750: sems can mang po'i don byas shing /
NK127(jo)001:1751: 'jam dpal dang lhan cig 'ong ba'i byang chub sems
NK127(jo)001:1752: dpa' de dag gis rang gi zhing dag tu 'gro
NK127(jo)001:1753: bar 'dod pa'i smra ba las brtsams te /
NK127(jo)001:1754: 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pas 'jig rten gyi khams
NK127(jo)001:1755: 'di de bzhin gshegs pa rin chen tog gi zhing
NK127(jo)001:1756: rin po che dang ldan pa ji 'dra bar chad
NK127(jo)001:1757: lhag med par byin gyis brlabs mdzad pas byang chub
NK127(jo)001:1758: sems dpa' rnams kyis rang gi zhing der 'du shes
NK127(jo)001:1760: slar byang chub sems dpa' de dag ting nge 'dzin
NK127(jo)001:1761: la mnyam par bzhag ste bltas pas mi mjed 'di
NK127(jo)001:1762: nas ma g.yos par mthong ste /
NK127(jo)001:1763: 'jam dpal gyi byin rlabs la ched du brjod par byas shing smon lam btab bo //
NK127(jo)001:1764: de nas 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa stan de
NK127(jo)001:1765: la 'dug bzhin du ting nge 'dzin la mnyam par
NK127(jo)001:1766: bzhag ste / spyi bo'i gtsug nas sems can kun
NK127(jo)001:1767: gyi dmigs pa dang mi shes pa sel ba zhes
NK127(jo)001:1768: bya ba'i 'od zer byung bas phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas
NK127(jo)001:1769: kyi zhing rab 'byams snang bar byas nas bcom ldan
NK127(jo)001:1770: 'das sh+aakya thub pas chos bshad pa bden pa gnyis
NK127(jo)001:1771: la brten pa de dag mi thos pa'i tshul gyis
NK127(jo)001:1772: bzhag ste / thos par byas / phyogs bcu mu
NK127(jo)001:1773: med pa'i zhing gi sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems
NK127(jo)001:1774: dpa' thams cad la mchod pa'i phyir lha'i me tog
NK127(jo)001:1775: dang bdug pa la sogs pa rnam pa thams cad
NK127(jo)001:1776: kyi mchog dang ldan pa'i bla na med pa bde
NK127(jo)001:1777: ba chen po thams cad phun sum tshogs pa'i char
NK127(jo)001:1778: 'bebs pa'i mchod pa'i sprin gyis khyab par byas nas
NK127(jo)001:1779: ting nge 'dzin de las langs te bcom ldan 'das
NK127(jo)001:1780: sh+aakya thub pa la lan brgya stong du mar mi
NK127(jo)001:1781: dmigs pa'i tshul gyis bskor ba byas nas mi mjed
NK127(jo)001:1784: 'phags pa chos thams cad 'byung ba med pa zhes bya ba'i mdo las /
NK127(jo)001:1785: bcom ldan 'das dang 'jam dpal gyis chos thams cad
NK127(jo)001:1786: ma skyes pa'i phyir thams cad mnyam pa nyid kyi
NK127(jo)001:1789: phur pa'i tshig rnams bstan pa na /
NK127(jo)001:1790: steng gi bar snang las lha'i bu stong phrag bcus
NK127(jo)001:1791: de bzhin gshegs pa dang 'jam dpal la lha rdzas
NK127(jo)001:1792: kyi me tog ut+pala la sogs pas gtor nas phyag
NK127(jo)001:1794: bcom ldan 'das 'di ni chags pa ma mchis pa'i dpal te /
NK127(jo)001:1796: bcom ldan 'das 'di ni mi gnas pa'i dpal te /
NK127(jo)001:1798: bcom ldan 'das 'di ni dngos po ma mchis pa'i dpal te /
NK127(jo)001:1800: bcom ldan 'das 'di ni nyon mongs pa ma mchis pa'i dpal te /
NK127(jo)001:1802: bcom ldan 'das 'di ni de bzhin nyid kyi dpal te /
NK127(jo)001:1804: bcom ldan 'das 'di ni ma nor ba de bzhin nyid kyi dpal te /
NK127(jo)001:1806: bcom ldan 'das 'di ni chos kyi dbyings kyi dpal te /
NK127(jo)001:1808: bcom ldan 'das 'di ni yang dag pa'i matha'i dpal te /
NK127(jo)001:1810: bcom ldan 'das 'di ni dam pa'i dpal te /
NK127(jo)001:1812: bcom ldan 'das 'di ni mchog gi dpal te /
NK127(jo)001:1814: bcom ldan 'das 'di ni phul gyi dpal te /
NK127(jo)001:1816: bcom ldan 'das 'di ni bla na ma mchis pa'i dpal te de ni 'jam dpal lo //
NK127(jo)001:1817: de skad ces smras pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:1818: 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pas de dag la smras pa /
NK127(jo)001:1819: lha'i bu dag chog gis bdag la ma rtog rnam par ma rtog cig /
NK127(jo)001:1820: kho bos ni chos gang yang dam pa zhes bya ba'am /
NK127(jo)001:1822: phul zhes bya ba de lta bu yang dag par rjes su ma mthong ngo //
NK127(jo)001:1823: lha'i bu dag kho bo ni 'dod chags kyi dpal te /
NK127(jo)001:1824: de'i phyir kho bo 'jam dpal lo //
NK127(jo)001:1825: de bzhin du zhe sdang dang gti mug gi dpal te /
NK127(jo)001:1826: de'i phyir kho bo 'jam dpal lo //
NK127(jo)001:1827: kho bo ni 'dod chags sogs las 'das pa ma yin te /
NK127(jo)001:1828: byis pa so so'i skye bo ni 'da' zhing yongs su 'da' ba byed kyi /
NK127(jo)001:1829: byang chub sems dpa' rnams ni chos gang la yang 'pho ba'am 'gro ba'am 'da' ba med do //
NK127(jo)001:1830: chos thams cad ni sgyu ma ltar 'da' ba med
NK127(jo)001:1831: pa zhes sogs gsungs pas lha'i bu stong phrag bcu
NK127(jo)001:1832: po de dag gis mi skye ba'i chos la bzod
NK127(jo)001:1834: lha mo dri ma med pa'i 'od kyis zhus pa'i mdo las /
NK127(jo)001:1835: li yul du ma 'ongs pa'i dus su mi rgod
NK127(jo)001:1836: de dag 'khor ba las grol bar byed pa dge
NK127(jo)001:1837: slong zla ba dag pa zhes pa 'byung ste /
NK127(jo)001:1838: de ni byang chub sems dpa' 'jam dpal sngon gyi
NK127(jo)001:1839: sangs rgyas rnams kyi yab kyi bya ba byed pa
NK127(jo)001:1840: 'di yin te / de bzhin du 'jam dpal 'di
NK127(jo)001:1841: ni ma 'ongs pa'i dus na 'byung bar 'gyur ba'i
NK127(jo)001:1842: skal bzang gi sangs rgyas rnams kyi sku gdung yang
NK127(jo)001:1844: gang tshe bcom ldan 'das mya ngan las 'das pa
NK127(jo)001:1845: de'i tshe yang 'jam dpal 'di bram ze dro nas
NK127(jo)001:1846: go tra zhes bya ba chos ldan zhig tu gyur
NK127(jo)001:1847: te rgyal po rnams phan tshun 'gyed par chas pa'i
NK127(jo)001:1848: tshe / bram ze des bum pa mang po blangs nas sku gdung rnams 'ged par byed do //
NK127(jo)001:1849: gang tshe li yul du byang sems phal mo che ma byung ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:1850: mchod rten dang sangs rgyas kyi sku gzugs dge 'dun
NK127(jo)001:1851: gyi kun dga' ra ba ma byung ba de'i tshe
NK127(jo)001:1852: / 'jam dpal ni grong khyer der rigs dang ldan pa'i bud med du 'gyur ro //
NK127(jo)001:1853: 'jam dpal gyi spyod pa ji lta bu zhe na /
NK127(jo)001:1854: thams cad du 'dod dgur bsgyur ba'i gzugs can yin te /
NK127(jo)001:1855: byang chub sems dpa'i gzugs dang rgyal po rgyal mo
NK127(jo)001:1856: dge sbyong bram ze la sogs 'dod pa'i khams su
NK127(jo)001:1857: gtogs pa'i sems can rnams kyi gzugs thams cad du
NK127(jo)001:1858: 'jug ste / rol mo mkhan rol mo'i gnas la mkhas pas gzugs sna tshogs ston pa bzhin no //
NK127(jo)001:1859: chags pa'i sems dang ldan pa'i sems can gyi thad du shin tu lhag par ston te /
NK127(jo)001:1860: ci'i phyir 'jam dpal bud med kyi gzugs su ston ce na /
NK127(jo)001:1861: bud med ni lhag par chags pa'i sems dang ldan
NK127(jo)001:1862: la shin tu gleng zhing ser sna che ba'i phyir
NK127(jo)001:1863: 'jam dpal ni lhag par bud med du ston to
NK127(jo)001:1864: // bud med byang chub kyi spyad pa spyod pa
NK127(jo)001:1865: da ga kyang yod pa de'i phyir du yang de
NK127(jo)001:1866: ltar bstan te tshul des bud med du skyes nas
NK127(jo)001:1867: snying rje chen po thob par 'gyur ba'i dus kyang
NK127(jo)001:1868: // yod do // bud med rnams 'dzem pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:1870: skyes pa gzhan spong bar 'gyur ba dag kyang yod do //
NK127(jo)001:1872: nye ba 'khor gyi zhus pa'i mdo las /
NK127(jo)001:1873: 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pas nye ba 'khor la smras pa /
NK127(jo)001:1874: nye ba 'khor chos thams cad ni shin tu dul
NK127(jo)001:1875: ba ste rang gi sems gdul ba'i phyir shin tu
NK127(jo)001:1876: dul ba kun tu ston no //
NK127(jo)001:1877: chos thams cad ni kun nas nyon mongs pa can
NK127(jo)001:1878: ma yin pa ste bdag ma dmigs pa'i phyir 'gyod
NK127(jo)001:1879: pa 'dul ba kun du ston to //
NK127(jo)001:1881: bcom ldan 'das la nye bar 'khor gyis gsol pa /
NK127(jo)001:1882: bcom ldan 'das 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa ni
NK127(jo)001:1883: gang dang gang ston pa de thams cad bsam gyis
NK127(jo)001:1884: mi khyab pa kho na las brtsam ste ston lags
NK127(jo)001:1886: nye ba 'khor 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pas chos
NK127(jo)001:1887: ston pa ni rnam par grol ba'i rgyu mthun pa
NK127(jo)001:1888: yin te / bsam gyis mi khyab pa nyid la
NK127(jo)001:1889: ma brten par rnam par grol ba med pas na
NK127(jo)001:1890: yin te / / de phyir 'jam dpal gzhon nur
NK127(jo)001:1891: gyur pa ni rnam par rtog pa thams cad dang
NK127(jo)001:1892: yin te / / bral ba dang / sems pa
NK127(jo)001:1893: la mos pa lhag pa'i nga rgyal can gyi lhag
NK127(jo)001:1894: pa'i nga rgyal med par bya ba'i phyir chos ston
NK127(jo)001:1895: yin te / / bral ba dang / to // zhes gsungs so //
NK127(jo)001:1896: phyir mi ldog pa'i 'khor lo'i mdo las /
NK127(jo)001:1897: nam langs khar sh+aa ri'i bu 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa'i gnas khang du zhugs pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:1898: 'jam dpal skyil mo krung bcas te sh+aa ri'i bu
NK127(jo)001:1899: dang gnas khang dang bcas pa shar phyogs gang g+aa'i
NK127(jo)001:1900: klung gi bye ma snyed kyi zhing 'das te /
NK127(jo)001:1901: 'jig rten gyi khams phyir mi ldog pa'i dbyings zhes par song ste /
NK127(jo)001:1902: de bzhin gshegs pa 'od zer gyis khebs pa'i pad+ma
NK127(jo)001:1903: rab tu rgyas pa'i sku zhes bya ba las phyir
NK127(jo)001:1904: mi ldog pa'i chos kyi 'khor lo thos pa de
NK127(jo)001:1905: bzhin phyogs gzhan dgu por yang /
NK127(jo)001:1906: gang g+aa'i klung gi bye ma snyed rnams su de
NK127(jo)001:1907: ltar chos de thos nas slar mi mjed 'dir nam
NK127(jo)001:1908: ma langs par slebs par mdzad pa na /
NK127(jo)001:1909: rgyal byed kyi tshal du chu dwangs pas khebs shing
NK127(jo)001:1910: pad+ma dang rol mo'i sgra dang 'od chen po la
NK127(jo)001:1911: sogs pa mthong nas kun dga' bo ngo mtshar zhing
NK127(jo)001:1912: bcom ldan 'das la phyag 'tshal te zhus pa dang
NK127(jo)001:1913: / bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
NK127(jo)001:1915: 'di yis gang phyir dris pa yi //
NK127(jo)001:1916: ye shes 'di ni rnyogs pa med //
NK127(jo)001:1917: sangs rgyas ye shes bla na med //
NK127(jo)001:1918: ces sogs kyis chos zab mo ston pa'i ltas yin par gsungs shing /
NK127(jo)001:1919: der 'jam dpal gyis chos kun skye med du mnyam
NK127(jo)001:1920: par bstan pas srog chags brgya stong mang po soms
NK127(jo)001:1922: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
NK127(jo)001:1923: 'di dag ni sngon 'jam dpal gyis byang chub tu
NK127(jo)001:1924: smin par byas shing da ni byang chub las phyir
NK127(jo)001:1925: mi ldog ste 'di ltar dge ba'i bshes gnyen 'jam
NK127(jo)001:1926: dpal gzhon nus yongs su bzung ba'i phyir ro zhes
NK127(jo)001:1927: gsungs / de ltar chos gsungs pa'i tshe 'jam dpal
NK127(jo)001:1928: gyi byin gyi rlabs kyis bdud bcings pas ci yang
NK127(jo)001:1930: slar byin rlabs bsdus pa'i tshe bdud sdig can 'ongs
NK127(jo)001:1931: nas sangs rgyas la phyir mi ldog pa'i 'khor lo'i
NK127(jo)001:1932: sgra dang bcom ldan 'das sh+aakya thub pa'i mtshan thos
NK127(jo)001:1933: pas bdud rgas shing 'khogs la skrag par gyur to
NK127(jo)001:1934: zhes zhus so // dam pa'i chos pad+ma dkar po las /
NK127(jo)001:1935: bcom ldan 'das kyis byang chub sems dpa' shes rab brtsegs pa la bka' stsal pa /
NK127(jo)001:1936: rigs kyi bu yud tsam sdod la nga'i byang chub
NK127(jo)001:1937: sems dpa' 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa dang chos
NK127(jo)001:1938: rnam par gtan la dbab pa 'ga' zhig gyi sa
NK127(jo)001:1939: la phyis bdag gi sangs rgyas kyi zhing du song
NK127(jo)001:1940: shig ces gsungs pa de'i tshe /
NK127(jo)001:1941: 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa pad+ma 'dab ma stong
NK127(jo)001:1942: dang ldan pa tshad shing rta'i 'phang lo tsam la
NK127(jo)001:1943: 'dug ste byang chub sems dpa' du mas bskor ba
NK127(jo)001:1944: / rgya mtsho'i nang gi klu'i rgyal po rgya mtsho'i
NK127(jo)001:1945: khang pa nas steng gi bar snang la 'phags te
NK127(jo)001:1946: bya rgod kyi phung po'i rir bcom ldan 'das kyi
NK127(jo)001:1948: bcom ldan 'das sh+aakya thub pa dang de bzhin gshegs
NK127(jo)001:1949: pa rin chen mang gi zhabs la phyag 'tshal te
NK127(jo)001:1950: / byang chub sems dpa' shes rab brtsegs dang mgu
NK127(jo)001:1951: ba'i gtam byas nas phyogs 'ga' zhig tu 'dug ga
NK127(jo)001:1952: / // de nas byang sems shes rab brtsegs kyis
NK127(jo)001:1953: 'jam dpal la khyod rgya mtshor zhugs te sems can
NK127(jo)001:1954: ji snyed btul zhes dris pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:1956: ji tsam tshig gis brjod mi nus sems kyis bsam
NK127(jo)001:1957: mi nus pa de snyed btul te skad cig la
NK127(jo)001:1958: sdod dang mthong bar 'gyur ro zhes smras ma thag
NK127(jo)001:1959: tu pad+ma stong phrag du ma rgya mtsho'i steng nas
NK127(jo)001:1960: nam mkhar la byung ste der sems can stong phrag
NK127(jo)001:1962: de nas byang chub sems dpa' de dag nam mkha'
NK127(jo)001:1963: las bya rgod kyi phung po ri'i nam mkha' la
NK127(jo)001:1964: 'khod do // de thams cad kyang 'jam dpal gyis
NK127(jo)001:1965: bla med byang chub la btul ba sha stag go
NK127(jo)001:1966: 'khod do // // byang chub sems dpa' gang sngon
NK127(jo)001:1967: theg chen la zhugs pa dag la pha rol tu
NK127(jo)001:1969: sngon nyan thos byed pa'i byang chub sems dpa' de
NK127(jo)001:1970: dag la ni nyan thos kyi theg pa brjod do
NK127(jo)001:1971: // de thams cad kyang chos thams cad stong pa
NK127(jo)001:1972: nyid dang theg pa chen po'i mngon par shes pa
NK127(jo)001:1973: // sha stag ste / 'jam dpal gyis pad+ma dkar po'i chos bshad nas btul ba'o //
NK127(jo)001:1974: shes rab brtsegs kyis smras pa /
NK127(jo)001:1975: mdo 'di ni zab cing phra la rtogs dka' bas
NK127(jo)001:1976: 'di dang mtshungs pa'i mdo gzhan med na sems can
NK127(jo)001:1977: gang dag mdo 'di khong du chud pa'am mngon par
NK127(jo)001:1978: rdzogs par 'tshang rgya nus pa yod dam zhes dris
NK127(jo)001:1979: pa la / 'jam dpal gyis smras pa /
NK127(jo)001:1980: yod de klu'i rgyal po rgya mtsho'i bu mo skyes
NK127(jo)001:1981: nas lo brgyad lon pa shes rab che ba dbang
NK127(jo)001:1982: po rno ba ye shes dang gzungs dang ting nge
NK127(jo)001:1983: 'dzin dang smon lam rgya che ba /
NK127(jo)001:1984: bzhin 'dzum la kha dog rgyas pa mchog dang ldan
NK127(jo)001:1985: pa byams pa'i sems dang ldan pa snyan pa'i tshig
NK127(jo)001:1986: smra ba des 'tshang rgya bar nus so zhes smras
NK127(jo)001:1987: pa dang / shes rab brtsegs kyis smras pa /
NK127(jo)001:1988: de bzhin gshegs pa sh+aakya thub pas kyang bla med
NK127(jo)001:1989: byang chub kyi phyir bskal pa mang por brtson 'grus
NK127(jo)001:1990: brtsam ste / tha na yungs kar tsam gyi phyogs
NK127(jo)001:1991: gang du yang sku srog ma bor ba med pa
NK127(jo)001:1992: de lta bu'i tshul gyis bsod nams du mas gdod
NK127(jo)001:1993: brtsam ste / sangs rgyas na / des yud tsam
NK127(jo)001:1994: gyis bla med byang chub tu 'tshang rgya bar nus
NK127(jo)001:1995: zhes pa de la su zhig yid ches zhes smras
NK127(jo)001:1996: brtsam ste / sangs rgyas na / pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:1997: de'i tshe bu mo de yang der 'dug pas bcom
NK127(jo)001:1998: ldan 'das la phyag 'tshal nas tshigs su bcad pas
NK127(jo)001:1999: bstod pa'i tshul bzhin bdag khyod lta bur 'tshang rgya
NK127(jo)001:2000: bar bgyid do zhes zhus pa na /
NK127(jo)001:2001: sh+aa ri'i bus che zhe khyod phyir mi ldog par
NK127(jo)001:2002: byang chub tu sems bskyed cing shes rab dpag med
NK127(jo)001:2003: yod du zad de rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas ni rnyed
NK127(jo)001:2004: daka'o // bskal pa du mar pha rol tu phyin
NK127(jo)001:2005: pa rdzogs par byas kyang da dung sangs rgyas mi
NK127(jo)001:2007: bud med kyis da dung gnas lnga ma thob pa'i phyir ro //
NK127(jo)001:2009: tshangs pa'i gnas dang brgya byin gyi gnas dang rgyal
NK127(jo)001:2010: chen bzhi'i gnas dang 'khor los sgyur ba'i gnas dang
NK127(jo)001:2011: phyir mi ldog pa'i byang chub sems dpa'i gnas so
NK127(jo)001:2013: bu mo des stong chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khams
NK127(jo)001:2014: ma lus pa'i rin du chog pa'i nor bu gcig
NK127(jo)001:2015: yod pa de sangs rgyas la phul nas sangs rgyas
NK127(jo)001:2016: kyis thugs brtse bas bzhes so //
NK127(jo)001:2017: de nas klu'i bu mo des shes rab brtsegs dang sh+aa ri'i bu la smras pa /
NK127(jo)001:2018: bdag gis bcom ldan 'das la nor bu phul ba
NK127(jo)001:2019: de myur du bzhes pa de bas kyang ches myur
NK127(jo)001:2020: bar bdag gis rdzu 'phrul gyis 'tshang rgya'o zhes byas
NK127(jo)001:2021: nas / 'jig rten thams cad dang sh+aa ri'i bu
NK127(jo)001:2022: dang bcas pa'i mngon sum du bu mo des bud
NK127(jo)001:2023: med kyi dbang po mi snang bar byas shing skyes
NK127(jo)001:2024: pa'i dbang po byung ste byang chub sems dpar gyur
NK127(jo)001:2025: pas lho phyogs su song nas 'jig rten gyi khams
NK127(jo)001:2026: dri ma med pa zhes bya bar /
NK127(jo)001:2027: rin chen sna bdun pa'i shing drung du sangs rgyas
NK127(jo)001:2028: te mtshan dper ldan pa'i skyes bu chen po'i gzugs
NK127(jo)001:2029: kyi 'od kyis phyogs bcur khyab ste chos ston pa
NK127(jo)001:2030: mi mjed 'di'i sems can de dag gis mthong la
NK127(jo)001:2031: / de bzhin gshegs pa des chos bstan pa'i sems
NK127(jo)001:2032: can thams cad bla med byang chub las phyir mi
NK127(jo)001:2035: byams pa'i seng ge sgra chen po zhes bya ba dkon mchog brtsegs pa'i chos kyi rnam grangs las /
NK127(jo)001:2036: gnas brtan 'od srung chen pos bcom ldan 'das la gsol pa /
NK127(jo)001:2037: bcom ldan 'das slad ma'i dus lnga brgya tha ma
NK127(jo)001:2038: la byang chub sems dpa' tshul 'chos pa ji snyed
NK127(jo)001:2039: cig 'byung bar 'gyur zhes gsol ba na bka' stsal
NK127(jo)001:2040: pa / 'od srung gang dag sdig pa'i grogs pos
NK127(jo)001:2041: zin cing lhag pa'i bsam pa nyam chung ba zas
NK127(jo)001:2042: gos lhur len pa'i byang chub sems dpa' mang du
NK127(jo)001:2043: pa / 'byung ste / de dag de bzhin gshegs
NK127(jo)001:2044: pa'i sku gdung rnams la me tog la sogs pas
NK127(jo)001:2045: mchod pa'i las la brtson par 'gyur ro //
NK127(jo)001:2046: 'od srung ngas ni shes pa dang mi ldan pa
NK127(jo)001:2047: rnams kyi dge ba'i rtsa ba sgrub pa'i phyir mchod
NK127(jo)001:2049: dge slong rnams la zhi ba dang dul ba'i sbyor bar rjes su gnas par gyis shig /
NK127(jo)001:2050: bram ze dang khyim bdag dad pa can gyis ni
NK127(jo)001:2051: sku gdung rnams la mchod pa byed par 'gyur ro
NK127(jo)001:2053: mi blun po de dag rnal 'byor dang spong ba
NK127(jo)001:2054: dang lung nod pa dang kha ton bya ba spangs
NK127(jo)001:2055: nas mchod pa'i las la brtson pa de dag la
NK127(jo)001:2056: ltos / 'od srung byang chub sems dpa' gang gis
NK127(jo)001:2057: stong chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khams 'di chu'i phung
NK127(jo)001:2058: po nas bzung ste tshangs pa'i 'jig rten gyi bar
NK127(jo)001:2059: du 'bru mar gyis yongs su bkang ste /
NK127(jo)001:2060: mar me'i snying po ri rab tsam btsugs nas de
NK127(jo)001:2061: bzhin gshegs pa la mchod pa'i phyir mar me phul
NK127(jo)001:2062: ba bas / byang chub sems dpa' lhag bsam phun
NK127(jo)001:2063: sum tshogs pa tshul khrims la gnas pas mkhan po'am
NK127(jo)001:2064: slob dpon gyi drung nas tshig bzhi pa'i tshigs bcad
NK127(jo)001:2065: gcig lung mnos te kha ton byed cing gom pa
NK127(jo)001:2066: bdun 'dor ba gang yin pa de de bas ches
NK127(jo)001:2067: bsod nams mang du skyed par 'gyur ro //
NK127(jo)001:2068: 'od srung byang chub sems dpa' gang gis stong chen
NK127(jo)001:2069: po'i 'jig rten gyi khams 'di me tog dang bdug
NK127(jo)001:2070: pa dang phye ma dang spos kyis rab tu bkang
NK127(jo)001:2071: ste de bzhin gshegs pa la mchod pa'i las kyi
NK127(jo)001:2072: phyir lo 'bum gyi bar nyin lan gsum mtshan lan
NK127(jo)001:2074: byang chub sems dpa' 'du 'dzi'i gtam gyis 'jigs shing
NK127(jo)001:2075: skrag pa gzhan zhig khams gsum thams cad kyis 'jigs
NK127(jo)001:2076: shing sems can gyi don mngon par 'dod pas dgon
NK127(jo)001:2077: pa la mngon par phyogs te gom pa bdun 'dor
NK127(jo)001:2078: bar byed pa gang yin pa de ni de bas
NK127(jo)001:2079: ches bsod nams mang du skyed par 'gyur ro //
NK127(jo)001:2081: de bzhin gshegs pas kyal ka'i ched dam brjod pa'i
NK127(jo)001:2082: ched du de skad gsung ba ma yin grang snyam
NK127(jo)001:2083: na / khyod kyis de ltar mi blta ste /
NK127(jo)001:2085: de ni nga la mngon sum yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK127(jo)001:2086: 'od srung sngon byung ba 'das pa'i dus bskal pa
NK127(jo)001:2087: grangs med pa ches shin tu grangs med pa rgya
NK127(jo)001:2088: che ba tshad med bsam gyis mi khyab dpag tu
NK127(jo)001:2089: med pa dag byung ba de'i tshe de'i dus na
NK127(jo)001:2090: / de bzhin gshegs pa me tog sna tshogs zhes
NK127(jo)001:2091: bya ba 'jig rten du byung ste de'i sku tshe'i
NK127(jo)001:2092: tshad na bskal pa brgyad dang dam pa'i chos bskal
NK127(jo)001:2093: pa gcig gi bar du gnas par gyur to //
NK127(jo)001:2094: de'i dus na gling bzhi'i 'khor los sgyur ba mu
NK127(jo)001:2095: khyud ces bya ba la bu stong yod pa'i rjes
NK127(jo)001:2096: la / de'i pang par chos zhes bya ba dang
NK127(jo)001:2097: chos bzangs zhes bya ba'i khye'u gnyis shig bardzusa te
NK127(jo)001:2099: rgyal po des de bzhin gshegs pa dge slong gi
NK127(jo)001:2100: dge 'dun dang bcas pa la lo brgyad khri bzhi
NK127(jo)001:2101: stong gi bar du las gzhan yid la byed pa
NK127(jo)001:2103: na bza' dang zhal zas sogs khyad par 'phags pa'i
NK127(jo)001:2104: yo byad kun gyis bsnyen bkur byas te lo de
NK127(jo)001:2105: dag rdzogs pa'i phyi de nyin par de bzhin gshegs
NK127(jo)001:2106: pas zhal zas kyi bya ba mdzad pa'i 'og tu
NK127(jo)001:2107: / khye'u chos dang chos bzang gnyis dpung tshogs bzhi
NK127(jo)001:2108: dang bcas te de bzhin gshegs pa de'i spyan sngar
NK127(jo)001:2109: btud de yid kyis zhu ba 'di skad zhus so
NK127(jo)001:2110: / // bcom ldan 'das rgyal po mu khyud 'dis
NK127(jo)001:2111: yun ring mo srid du dge rtsa bskrun pa rnam
NK127(jo)001:2112: pa mang po 'di lta bu zil gyis gnon pa'i
NK127(jo)001:2113: dge rtsa gzhan mchis lags sam zhes yid kyis gsol
NK127(jo)001:2114: zhing lus kyis btud ma thag tu sa chen po
NK127(jo)001:2116: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa de'i bsnyen bkur ba
NK127(jo)001:2117: thub dka' zhes bya bas sa g.yos pa'i rgyu gang
NK127(jo)001:2118: yin zhus pa dang bka' stsal pa /
NK127(jo)001:2119: rigs kyi bu gtam de lta bus khyod la ci zhig bya /
NK127(jo)001:2120: khye'u 'di gnyis kyi lhag bsam dang zab mo la
NK127(jo)001:2121: bzod pa sgom pa dang snying rje chen po ji
NK127(jo)001:2122: lta bus de bzhin gshegs pa'i zhabs gnyis la gtugs
NK127(jo)001:2123: pa'i gnas de bshad na lha dang bcas pa'i 'jig
NK127(jo)001:2125: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa de'i rdzu 'phrul dang
NK127(jo)001:2126: ldan pa'i mchog sred med kyi bu zhes bya ba
NK127(jo)001:2128: khyod longs la khye'u 'di gnyis slongs te rang gi rdzu 'phrul ston cig ces gsungs pas /
NK127(jo)001:2129: sred med kyi bu des lag pa gnyis kyis khye'u
NK127(jo)001:2130: de gnyis blangs te gyen du 'phang ngo snyam pa
NK127(jo)001:2131: dang 'degs par yang ma nus so //
NK127(jo)001:2132: de nas des mthu dang rdzu 'phrul rgya chen po
NK127(jo)001:2133: bskyed de gyen du 'phang ngo snyam na'ang tha na
NK127(jo)001:2134: de gnyis kyi skra'i rtse mo yang g.yo bar ma
NK127(jo)001:2135: nus par stong chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khams thams
NK127(jo)001:2136: cad g.yos kyang khye'u de gnyis bslang ma nus so
NK127(jo)001:2137: // de nas de bzhin gshegs pa des nyan thos
NK127(jo)001:2138: chen po'i sems bzung ba dang rdzu 'phrul gyi mthu
NK127(jo)001:2140: sred med kyi bu des 'og gi phyogs kyi sangs
NK127(jo)001:2141: rgyas kyi zhing gang+g+aa'i klung gi bye ma snyed 'gul
NK127(jo)001:2142: zhing rab tu g.yos la bla 'og tu 'gul bar
NK127(jo)001:2143: byas kyang khye'u de gnyis kyi skra'i rtse mo'i cha
NK127(jo)001:2145: sred med kyi bu des de bzhin gshegs pa la
NK127(jo)001:2146: bdag rdzu 'phrul gyi stobs las yongs su nyams par
NK127(jo)001:2148: de ci'i phyir na khye'u skyes nas ring por ma
NK127(jo)001:2149: lon pa'i byis pa bong chung ngu 'di gnyis dog
NK127(jo)001:2150: sa la gtugs pa yang bslad par rngo ma thogs
NK127(jo)001:2151: pa'i slad du'o zhes gsol pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:2153: sred med bu khyod rang gi rdzu 'phrul las ma
NK127(jo)001:2154: nyams mod kyi 'on kyang byang chub sems dpa'i byin
NK127(jo)001:2155: gyis rlabs 'di ni bsam gyis mi khyab pas nyan
NK127(jo)001:2156: rang gis dkrugs pa'am bsam par sla ba ma yin
NK127(jo)001:2157: te / stong chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khams 'di'i
NK127(jo)001:2158: sems can thams cad khyod lta bu'i rdzu 'phrul gyi
NK127(jo)001:2159: stobs dang ldan par gyur la /
NK127(jo)001:2160: de thams cad kyis bskal pa bye ba snyed du
NK127(jo)001:2161: rdzu 'phrul gyi rnam pa sna tshogs byas kyang des
NK127(jo)001:2162: khye'u 'di gnyis bslang ba'am bsgul bar mi nus so
NK127(jo)001:2163: // zhes gsungs pas 'khor de'i srog chags 'bum phrag
NK127(jo)001:2164: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis kyis bla med byang chub tu
NK127(jo)001:2165: sems bskyed cing 'di snyam du byang chub sems dpa'
NK127(jo)001:2166: rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes ma thob
NK127(jo)001:2167: // kyang / nyan thos chen po 'di dag rdugs
NK127(jo)001:2168: par byas te rdzu 'phrul gyi cho 'phrul de lta
NK127(jo)001:2169: bu dang ldan pa ni ngo mtshar te bdag cag
NK127(jo)001:2170: gis kyang byin gyis rlabs de lta bu dang sangs
NK127(jo)001:2171: rgyas kyi ye shes kyang thob par bya'o snyam mo
NK127(jo)001:2172: // kyang / // de nas 'khor der byang chub
NK127(jo)001:2173: sems dpa' blo gros bzang po zhes bya ba zhig
NK127(jo)001:2174: 'dug pas de bzhin gshegs pa la khye'u 'di gnyis
NK127(jo)001:2175: bslang bar mdzad cing 'di gnyis kyis zhus pa rnam
NK127(jo)001:2176: par dbye ba bstan du gsol zhes zhus pa dang
NK127(jo)001:2177: // kyang / // / de bzhin gshegs pa des
NK127(jo)001:2178: se gol gyi sgra mdzad pas phyogs bcu'i zhing gang+g+aa'i
NK127(jo)001:2179: klung gi bye ma snyed du grags shing de snyed
NK127(jo)001:2180: du sa g.yo ba dang snang bas khyab par mdzad
NK127(jo)001:2182: gnyis kyis sgra de thos nas de bzhin gshegs pa'i
NK127(jo)001:2183: zhabs drung nas langs par gyur pa dang stong chen
NK127(jo)001:2184: po'i 'jig rten de'i lha dang mi yi sil snyan
NK127(jo)001:2185: ji snyed pa ma dkrol bar sgra 'byin cing me
NK127(jo)001:2186: tog gi char babs par gyur to //
NK127(jo)001:2187: khye'u de gnyis langs te de bzhin gshegs pa'i zhabs
NK127(jo)001:2188: la phyag 'tshal zhing bskor ba byas nas thal mo
NK127(jo)001:2189: sbyar te de bzhin gshegs pa'i zhal du blta zhing
NK127(jo)001:2191: de nas de bzhin gshegs pas blo gros bzang po la bka' stsal pa /
NK127(jo)001:2192: khye'u 'di gnyis kyis nga'i zhabs la gtugs nas yid
NK127(jo)001:2193: kyis zhu ba gong na bshad pa 'di lta bu
NK127(jo)001:2195: de nas byang chub sems dpa' blo gros bzang pos
NK127(jo)001:2196: skye bo mang po la phan pa dang bde ba'i
NK127(jo)001:2197: phyir khye'u 'di gnyis kyis zhus pa bshad du gsol
NK127(jo)001:2200: rigs kyi bu rgyal po mu khyud 'dis bsod nams
NK127(jo)001:2201: kyi sbyin pa yongs su gtong ba de bas byang
NK127(jo)001:2202: chub sems dpa' dben par gnas pa zhig dgon pa
NK127(jo)001:2203: dang rab tu dgon pa la gnas shing se gol
NK127(jo)001:2204: gtogs pa tsam du chos thams cad ma skyes pa'o
NK127(jo)001:2205: zhes bzod pa thob pa gang yin pa de bsod
NK127(jo)001:2206: nams kyi phung po ches che bar rig par bya'o
NK127(jo)001:2207: // rgyal po mu khyud 'di'i sbyin pa lta zhog gi /
NK127(jo)001:2208: stong chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khams na sems can
NK127(jo)001:2209: ji snyed pa de thams cad las sems can re
NK127(jo)001:2210: res kyang rgyal po mu khyud 'di'i sbyin pa ji
NK127(jo)001:2211: snyed pa de snyeed cig byin pa'i bsod nams las
NK127(jo)001:2212: / byang chub sems dpa' lhag pa'i bsam pa yang
NK127(jo)001:2213: dag pa'i lam du zhugs pa tshul bzhin rab tu
NK127(jo)001:2214: brtson pa zhig chos thams cad stong pa dang 'gro
NK127(jo)001:2215: 'ong med pa zhes bya bar se gol gtogs pa
NK127(jo)001:2216: tsam zhig bzod cing gnas pa'i bsod nams la brgya
NK127(jo)001:2217: stong 'bum gyi cha dang rgyu'i bar du yang mi
NK127(jo)001:2218: / 'agro'o // stong chen po'i sems can thams cad
NK127(jo)001:2219: kyi bsod nams kyi phung po lta zhog /'jig rten
NK127(jo)001:2220: gyi khams gang+g+aa'i klung gi bye ma snyed kyi sems
NK127(jo)001:2221: can re res kyang skad cig thang cig yud tsam
NK127(jo)001:2222: se gol gtogs pa tsam la rgyal po mu khyud
NK127(jo)001:2223: kyi sbyin pa byin pa dang dge ba 'dus byas
NK127(jo)001:2224: pa ji snyed pa de snyed byas shing /
NK127(jo)001:2225: rnam grangs de lta bus sems can de dag thams
NK127(jo)001:2226: cad kyis bskal pa gang+g+aa'i bye snyed du sbyin pa
NK127(jo)001:2227: dang dge ba mngon par 'dus byas pa des khye'u
NK127(jo)001:2228: 'di gnyis kyi lhag pa'i bsam pas de bzhin gshegs
NK127(jo)001:2229: pa'i zhabs la gtugs shing phyag 'tshal ba'i bsod nams
NK127(jo)001:2230: kyi brgya yi cha nas rgyu'i bar du yang mi
NK127(jo)001:2232: 'khor de'i dge slong brgyad khri bzhi stong gis tshul
NK127(jo)001:2233: de lta bu'i ye shes dang sems bskyed pa la
NK127(jo)001:2234: yi rangs pa brjod par byas so //
NK127(jo)001:2235: de la sangs rgyas kyis bka' stsal pa /
NK127(jo)001:2236: gal te khyed cag gi sems rnam par grol bar
NK127(jo)001:2237: ma gyur du zin na khyed cag dge rtsa des
NK127(jo)001:2238: 'khor los sgyur ba'i rgyal srid gang+ga'i bye snyed byas
NK127(jo)001:2239: nas rdzogs pa'i byang chub tu 'tshang rgya bar 'gyur
NK127(jo)001:2241: de nas khye'u de gnyis kyis de bzhin gshegs pa
NK127(jo)001:2242: la yongs su zhus pa'i don bzhin stong pa nyid
NK127(jo)001:2243: la mos pa dang dben par gnas pa dang chos
NK127(jo)001:2244: kyi sbyin pa'i gtam basngagasa pa brjod pas /
NK127(jo)001:2245: khye'u de gnyis t+aa la bdun srid tsam du mngon
NK127(jo)001:2246: par 'phags te tshigs su bcad pas zab mo'i chos
NK127(jo)001:2247: la ched du brjod pas srog chags brgyad khri bzhi
NK127(jo)001:2248: stong gis bla med byang chub tu sems bskyed cing
NK127(jo)001:2249: sems can tshad med pa'i dge ba'i rtsa ba sna
NK127(jo)001:2250: tshogs yongs su sgrub pa'i rgyu skyed do //
NK127(jo)001:2251: de nas khye'u de gnyis nam mkha' las babs te
NK127(jo)001:2252: mnyam pa nyid kyi rang bzhin du sems bskyed pa
NK127(jo)001:2253: nyid brjod pas byang chub sems dpa' khris mi skye
NK127(jo)001:2254: ba'i chos la bzod pa thob cing rgyal po mu
NK127(jo)001:2255: khyud bu stong dang rgyal po lnga stong dang bcas
NK127(jo)001:2256: pas bla med byang chub tu sems bskyed do //
NK127(jo)001:2257: de nas khye'u de gnyis rab tu byung bas rgyal
NK127(jo)001:2258: po mu khyud kyis kyang bu thu po rgyal srid
NK127(jo)001:2259: la bzhag nas bu gzhan thams cad dang bud med
NK127(jo)001:2260: brgyad khri bzhi stong dang rgyal po lnga stong dang
NK127(jo)001:2261: srog chags bye ba tham pa dang bcas par rab
NK127(jo)001:2262: tu byung ngo // bu thu bo rgyal srid la bzhag pa des kyang zhag bdun song ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:2263: gcig pur dben par song ste rgyal srid la mi
NK127(jo)001:2264: dga' bar rab tu byung ba'i sems skyes te zla
NK127(jo)001:2265: ba nya la gling bzhi po dag tu rgyu ba'i
NK127(jo)001:2266: tshe tshigs su bcad pas rab tu byung ba'i gnas
NK127(jo)001:2268: gling bzhi po dag na khyim na gnas pa la
NK127(jo)001:2269: dga' ba'i sems can gcig kyang ma byung bar thams
NK127(jo)001:2270: cad rab tu byung ba'i bsam pa la gnas pa
NK127(jo)001:2271: de bzhin gshegs pa de'i thugs su chud nas gling
NK127(jo)001:2272: bzhi pa'i 'jig rten thams cad kyi grong dang yul
NK127(jo)001:2273: 'khor du dge slong gi dge 'dun dang bcas par
NK127(jo)001:2274: sprul nas thams cad rab tu byung ngo //
NK127(jo)001:2275: de ltar rab tu byung ba de dag la ma
NK127(jo)001:2276: rmos pa 'bras s+aa lu'i 'bru byung zhing dpag bsam
NK127(jo)001:2277: shing las ras bcos bu'i gos rin po che byung
NK127(jo)001:2278: ste lha rnams kyi g.yog byed par gyur to //
NK127(jo)001:2279: de nas khye'u de gnyis kyis rab tu byung nas
NK127(jo)001:2280: brtson 'grus brtsam pa la gnas te lo bye ba
NK127(jo)001:2281: phrag drug cu rtsa gsum gyi bar du nam yang
NK127(jo)001:2282: rmug pa dang gnyid kyis non par ma gyur cing
NK127(jo)001:2283: / zas za ba ma gtogs par 'dug par yang
NK127(jo)001:2284: ma gyur te 'gro ba dang ldog pa thams cad
NK127(jo)001:2285: du thams cad mkhyen pa nyid kyi sems bskyed cing
NK127(jo)001:2286: sems de la'ang rlom sems byed par ma gyur to
NK127(jo)001:2287: / // de dag tu kun gyi rjes su song
NK127(jo)001:2288: ba zhes bya ba dang rdo rje'i gnas dang ldan
NK127(jo)001:2289: pa zhes bya ba'i ting nge 'dzin kyang bsgrubs te
NK127(jo)001:2290: de gnyis phyogs gang du skyil mo krung bcas pa'i
NK127(jo)001:2291: sa phyogs de rdo rje'i rang bzhin du kun tu
NK127(jo)001:2293: phyogs bcu kun gyi sangs rgyas bye ba khrag khrig
NK127(jo)001:2294: 'bum phrag dag gis chos ston pa thos shing bzung
NK127(jo)001:2295: nas gzhan dag la yang rgya cher bstan par gyur
NK127(jo)001:2296: te / gling bzhi pa'i 'jig rten khams kyi sems
NK127(jo)001:2297: can de dag las nyan thos kyi theg pa par
NK127(jo)001:2298: gyur pa'i sems can gang yin pa de dag las
NK127(jo)001:2299: sems can gcig tsam yang so so'i skye bor gyur
NK127(jo)001:2300: bzhin 'chi ba'i dus byas par ma gyur la /
NK127(jo)001:2301: gang dag thams cad kyi nang na le lo can
NK127(jo)001:2302: du gyur pa de dag kyang phyir mi 'ong bar
NK127(jo)001:2303: gyur pa shi 'phos nas gnas gtsang mar skyes so
NK127(jo)001:2304: // gang dag rang sangs rgyas kyi theg pa par
NK127(jo)001:2305: gyur pa de dag shi 'phos nas sangs rgyas mi
NK127(jo)001:2306: bzhugs pa'i zhing du phyug po'i khyim du skyes shing
NK127(jo)001:2307: sngon gyi dge ba'i rtsa bas rab tu byung nas
NK127(jo)001:2308: zhag bdun na rang byang chub thob ste de dag
NK127(jo)001:2309: gis kyang sems can tshad med grangs med pa dag
NK127(jo)001:2310: gi don byas nas mya ngan las 'das so //
NK127(jo)001:2311: gang dag byang chub sems dpa'i theg pa par gyur
NK127(jo)001:2312: ba de dag gis mngon shes lnga dang tshangs pa'i
NK127(jo)001:2313: gnas bzhi bsgrubs te mi 'phrog pa'i spobs pa dang
NK127(jo)001:2315: de'i dus kyi rgyal po mu khyud ces bya ba ni ston pa sh+aakya'i rgyal po nyid yin la /
NK127(jo)001:2316: byang chub sems dpa' byams pa ni rgyal bu gzhon nu thu bo dang /
NK127(jo)001:2317: de bzhin gshegs pa 'od srung ni byang chub sems dpa' blo gros bzang po dang /
NK127(jo)001:2318: 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa ni khye'u chos zhes bya ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:2319: byang chub sems dpa' nyi ma'i snying po ni khye'u chos bzangs zhes bya bar gyur to //
NK127(jo)001:2320: de ltar dge slong chos dang chos bzang gnyis su
NK127(jo)001:2321: bya ba nyung zhing bdag gi don la sbyor ba'i
NK127(jo)001:2322: rjes su brtson par gnas shing bcom ldan 'das de'i
NK127(jo)001:2323: sku gdung la mchod par mi byed mchod rten gyi
NK127(jo)001:2325: de nas lha 'bum phrag mang po dang dge slong
NK127(jo)001:2326: las dang po pa dag gis dge slong 'di gnyis
NK127(jo)001:2327: de bzhin gshegs pa'i sku gdung la mchod pa dang
NK127(jo)001:2328: bskor ba mi byed pas ma dad pa dang ma
NK127(jo)001:2329: gus pa yin no zhes kha zer bar gyur pa
NK127(jo)001:2330: la / dge slong de gnyis kyis smras pa /
NK127(jo)001:2331: grogs po dag ji ltar na de bzhin gshegs pa
NK127(jo)001:2332: mchod par 'gyur zhing rgyu gang gis sku gdung sems
NK127(jo)001:2333: pa med pas kyang mchod pa brnyes par 'gyur snyam
NK127(jo)001:2334: / dge slong dang lha de dag gis smras pa /
NK127(jo)001:2335: sku gdung 'di dag ni tshul khrims la sogs pa'i
NK127(jo)001:2336: phung pos phye ba yin pa de'i phyir 'di dag
NK127(jo)001:2337: ni mchod par 'os pa yin no //
NK127(jo)001:2338: dge slong de gnyis kyis smras pa /
NK127(jo)001:2339: 'o na tshul khrims dang ting 'dzin dang shes rab
NK127(jo)001:2340: dang rnam par grol ba dang rnam par grol ba'i
NK127(jo)001:2341: ye shes mthong ba nyid mchod pa'i 'os yin gyi
NK127(jo)001:2342: sku gdung mchod par 'os par mi 'gyur ba ma
NK127(jo)001:2343: yin nam / dge slong dang lha de dag gis smras pa /
NK127(jo)001:2345: dge slong de gnyis kyis smras pa /
NK127(jo)001:2346: grogs po dag 'o na tshul khrims la sogs pa de'i mtshan nyid gang yin /
NK127(jo)001:2347: lha dang dge slong de dag gis smras pa /
NK127(jo)001:2348: de dag ni mngon par 'du byed pa med pa'i mtshan nyid yin no //
NK127(jo)001:2349: dge slong de gnyis kyis smras pa /
NK127(jo)001:2350: 'o na mngon par 'du byed pas mngon par 'du byed med pa mchod par nus sam /
NK127(jo)001:2351: dge slong dang lha de dag gis smras pa /
NK127(jo)001:2353: dge slong de gnyis kyis smras pa /
NK127(jo)001:2354: grogs po dag de lta bas na khyed kyang bdag
NK127(jo)001:2355: tu mngon par 'du ma byed cig dang des ni
NK127(jo)001:2357: sangs rgyas su 'du shes pa la ni sangs rgyas
NK127(jo)001:2358: mthong ba yang med na mchod pa'i las lta smos
NK127(jo)001:2359: kyang ci dgos te gnas med do //
NK127(jo)001:2360: gzhan yang de bzhin gshegs pa mchod par 'dod pas ni bdag nyid mchod par bya'o //
NK127(jo)001:2361: dge slong dang lha de dag gis smras pa /
NK127(jo)001:2362: ji ltar de bzhin gshegs pa mchod par 'dod pas bdag nyid mchod par bya /
NK127(jo)001:2363: dge slong chos dang chos bzangs gnyis kyis smras pa /
NK127(jo)001:2364: grogs po dag de bzhin gshegs pas mchod pa gang
NK127(jo)001:2365: gis bdag nyid sems can thams cad kyis mchod pa'i
NK127(jo)001:2366: gnas su 'os par mdzad pa de ltar bdag nyid
NK127(jo)001:2367: mchod par bya'o // ji ltar de bzhin gshegs pas
NK127(jo)001:2368: bslab pa de ltar bslab cing des rlom sems su
NK127(jo)001:2369: mchod par bya'o // mi bya la / chos rab
NK127(jo)001:2370: tu dbye bar bya zhing rab tu phye nas kyang
NK127(jo)001:2371: chos 'ga' yang bsam par mi bya ste /
NK127(jo)001:2372: gang gi tshe khyed cag de ltar bdag nyid mchod
NK127(jo)001:2373: par byed pa de'i tshe na de bzhin gshegs pa
NK127(jo)001:2375: khyed cag kyang mchod par 'os par 'gyur ro //
NK127(jo)001:2376: de bzhin gshegs pa'i sku gdung rnams mchod par 'dod
NK127(jo)001:2377: pas ji ltar de bzhin gshegs pas bdag nyid mchod
NK127(jo)001:2378: par mdzad pa de ltar mchod par bya zhing yon
NK127(jo)001:2379: tan gang dang ldan pas sku gdung rnams kyang mchod
NK127(jo)001:2380: pa brnyes par 'gyur ba'i yon tan de dag bdag
NK127(jo)001:2381: nyid kyis bsgrub par bya ste /
NK127(jo)001:2382: de ltar na de bzhin gshegs pa mchod par 'gyur ro //
NK127(jo)001:2383: gang 'du shes dang mtshan ma skyed par mi byed
NK127(jo)001:2384: cing bdag tu rtog pa dang rnam par rtog pa
NK127(jo)001:2385: dang rtag chad dang 'gro 'ong la sogs pa'i mtshan
NK127(jo)001:2386: ma thams cad bral ba des mtshan mar mi byed
NK127(jo)001:2387: pa de ni de bzhin gshegs pa mchod pa yin
NK127(jo)001:2388: te / de bzhin gshegs pa'i sku mi skye ba
NK127(jo)001:2389: dang mngon par 'du mi byed pa dang gnyis su
NK127(jo)001:2390: med pa la sogs pa'i mtshan nyid yin pas skye
NK127(jo)001:2391: ba la sogs pa'i tshul gyis mchod par sla ba
NK127(jo)001:2392: te / ma yin no // zhes chos bstan pas
NK127(jo)001:2393: 'khor de las byang chub sems dpa' bzhi khri nyis
NK127(jo)001:2394: stong gis mi skye ba'i chos la bzod pa thob
NK127(jo)001:2395: te / ma yin no // par gyur / srog
NK127(jo)001:2396: chags brgyad khri bzhi stong gis shes pa dang mthong
NK127(jo)001:2397: ba bskyed de 'dod chags dang bral ba dang phyir
NK127(jo)001:2398: mi 'ong ba rjes su thob par gyur to //
NK127(jo)001:2399: sngon sems ma bskyed pa'i srog chags nyi khri sum
NK127(jo)001:2400: stong gis bla med byang chub tu sems bskyed do
NK127(jo)001:2401: // dge slong dang lha de dag de phyin chad
NK127(jo)001:2402: bdag gi don la sbyor ba'i rjes su brtson pa
NK127(jo)001:2403: dang bya ba nyung ngur gnas pas mchod rten mchod
NK127(jo)001:2404: pa sogs la mi brtson te /
NK127(jo)001:2405: de ci'i phyir na chos zab mo bla na med
NK127(jo)001:2406: pa la yang dag par zhugs par gyur pa'i phyir
NK127(jo)001:2407: ro // bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
NK127(jo)001:2408: 'od srung skyes bu dam pa de lta bu dag
NK127(jo)001:2409: gi zab mo la bzod pa dang thabs la mkhas
NK127(jo)001:2410: pa de la bslab par bya'o //
NK127(jo)001:2412: byang chub snying po rgyan 'bum gyi gzungs las /
NK127(jo)001:2413: 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pas lhung bzed gcig bsnams
NK127(jo)001:2414: nas bcom ldan 'das kyis gsungs pa'i chos kyi dbyings
NK127(jo)001:2415: thams cad der bsdus te bcom ldan 'das la phul
NK127(jo)001:2416: lo // bcom ldan 'das kyis phyag gser gyi mdog
NK127(jo)001:2417: can brkyangs nas phyag tu bzhes te mdun gyi nam
NK127(jo)001:2418: mkhar bor bas lhung bzed des nam mkha'i dbyings kyi
NK127(jo)001:2419: khyon gang ba'i de bzhin gshegs pa'i skur gyur te
NK127(jo)001:2420: lo // / stong chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khams
NK127(jo)001:2421: yongs su gang par gyur nas de dag gis bcom
NK127(jo)001:2422: ldan 'das sh+aakya thub pa la legs so zhes gsungs
NK127(jo)001:2423: lo // / shing / de dag thams cad re
NK127(jo)001:2424: re'i spyan sngar bcom ldan 'das sh+aakya thub pa 'khor
NK127(jo)001:2425: gyi tshogs dang bcas pa dang sh+aakya thub pa so
NK127(jo)001:2426: so'i mdun du 'jam dpal lhung bzed 'bul bzhin pa
NK127(jo)001:2427: re re snang bar gyur to //
NK127(jo)001:2428: de nas byang chub sems dpa' chen po phyag na
NK127(jo)001:2429: rdo rjes 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa la smras
NK127(jo)001:2430: pa / 'jam dpal ngo mtshar rmad du byung ba'i
NK127(jo)001:2431: rdzu 'phrul chen po de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad
NK127(jo)001:2432: 'ubs kyis 'dus shing rnam par spros pa 'di su'i
NK127(jo)001:2433: pa / don du yin / 'di'i rgyu rkyen ni gang /
NK127(jo)001:2434: ci'i phyir 'od zer 'gyed pa rnam par 'phrul pa 'di bstan /
NK127(jo)001:2436: ci phyag na rdo rje khyod kyis 'od kyi snang
NK127(jo)001:2437: ba dang rdzu 'phrul gyi rgyu rkyen mi shes sam
NK127(jo)001:2438: / phyag na rdo rjes smras pa /
NK127(jo)001:2440: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad 'dus pa dang rnam
NK127(jo)001:2441: par spros pa'i rdzu 'phrul chen po 'di 'dra ba
NK127(jo)001:2442: bdag gis sngon chad ma mthong ma thos shing de
NK127(jo)001:2443: ring bdag la thog mar ro //
NK127(jo)001:2444: de nas phyag na rdo rjes rdo rje gsor zhing
NK127(jo)001:2445: bcom ldan 'das la bskor ba lan gsum byas nas
NK127(jo)001:2447: chos gang zhig bstan par brtsams pas deng 'dir sngon
NK127(jo)001:2448: chad mthong thos ma myong ba'i rdzu 'phrul ngo mtshar
NK127(jo)001:2449: rmad du phyung ba 'di lta bu zhig go //
NK127(jo)001:2450: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
NK127(jo)001:2451: lag na rdo rje re zhig sgu gcig /
NK127(jo)001:2452: skad cig yud tsam na mngon du 'gyur ro zhes
NK127(jo)001:2453: gsungs ma thag tu rin chen bdun las grub pa'i
NK127(jo)001:2454: mchod rten dpang du dpag tshad bdun stong dang rgyar
NK127(jo)001:2455: dpag tshad lnga stong yod pa rgyan gyi bkod pa
NK127(jo)001:2456: phun sum tshogs pa zhig brtol te byung pa la
NK127(jo)001:2457: bar snang las lha'i tshogs kyis mchod cing phyag byed
NK127(jo)001:2458: do // de nas bcom ldan 'das kyi phyag na
NK127(jo)001:2459: rdo rje la mchod rten de'i sgo 'byed par bsgos
NK127(jo)001:2460: pas phyag na rdo rjes phyag g.yas pas mchod rten
NK127(jo)001:2461: de'i sgo phyes pa dang de'i nang na 'dzam bu'i
NK127(jo)001:2462: chu bo'i gser gyi khri rin po che sna bdun
NK127(jo)001:2463: gyis mdzes pa lha rdzas gos kyis khebs pa'i stan
NK127(jo)001:2464: do // la / bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs
NK127(jo)001:2465: pa dgra bcom pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs
NK127(jo)001:2466: rgyas shin tu rgyas pa'i gser zhal mchog tu dpa'
NK127(jo)001:2467: ba'i 'od zer rgyal mtshan gyi tog ces bya ba
NK127(jo)001:2468: bsam gtan la snyoms par zhugs bzhin pa snang bar
NK127(jo)001:2469: do // la / gyur to // de nas de
NK127(jo)001:2470: bzhin gshegs pa des bcom ldan 'das sh+aakya thub pa
NK127(jo)001:2471: la khyod kyi 'di lta bu'i rdzu 'phrul ngo mtshar
NK127(jo)001:2472: do // la / gyur to // che ba /
NK127(jo)001:2473: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad 'dus pa dang spros
NK127(jo)001:2474: do // la / gyur to // che ba /
NK127(jo)001:2475: par mdzad cing / don dam par chos thams cad
NK127(jo)001:2476: 'du 'bral yong ye mi mnga' bzhin 'jig rten 'di
NK127(jo)001:2477: na rdzu 'phrul ngo mtshar ba 'di lta bu bstan
NK127(jo)001:2478: pa 'di ni sngon gyi sangs rgyas rnams la'ang ma
NK127(jo)001:2479: do // la / gyur to // che ba /
NK127(jo)001:2480: par mdzad cing / byung ngo // da ltar khyed
NK127(jo)001:2481: kyis rtog pa'i rgyal po byang chub rgyan 'bum gyi
NK127(jo)001:2482: gzungs bshad du gsol zhes bskul bas bcom ldan 'das
NK127(jo)001:2484: de nas gsang ba ba'i bdag po phyag na rdo
NK127(jo)001:2485: rjes bcom ldan 'das la gzungs de'i phan yon zhus
NK127(jo)001:2486: pa na / bcom ldan 'das kyis 'jam dpal la
NK127(jo)001:2487: dris shig gsungs pa bzhin dris pas 'jam dpal gyis
NK127(jo)001:2488: de'i phan yon bshad pa'i tshig thos pas 'khor der
NK127(jo)001:2489: 'dus pa ma lus pa bla med byang chub las
NK127(jo)001:2490: phyir mi ldog par gyur la la las bla med
NK127(jo)001:2491: byang chub tu lung bstan pa thob par gyur to
NK127(jo)001:2493: 'phags pa dkon mchog gi za ma tog ces bya ba theg pa chen po'i mdo las /
NK127(jo)001:2495: kho bo ni 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa las
NK127(jo)001:2496: chos nyan par 'dod kyi bstan par mi 'dod do
NK127(jo)001:2498: 'jam dpal 'dis ni sngon sangs rgyas mang po'i spyan
NK127(jo)001:2499: sngar chos bshad cing nyan thos chen po dag kyang
NK127(jo)001:2500: cang mi smra ba la bzhag pa mthong ste /
NK127(jo)001:2501: shar phyogs sangs rgyas kyi zhing brgya stong phrag mang
NK127(jo)001:2502: po 'das pa na 'jig rten gyi khams dang ba
NK127(jo)001:2503: can zhes par de bzhin gshegs pa 'od kyi tog
NK127(jo)001:2504: ces bya ba da ltar bzhugs pa de'i nyan thos
NK127(jo)001:2505: chen po shes rab sgron ma zhes shes rab chen
NK127(jo)001:2506: po'i mchog tu basngagasa pa yod pa'i zhing der kho
NK127(jo)001:2507: bo dang 'jam dpal lhan cig song ba na /
NK127(jo)001:2508: byang chub sems dpa' brgya stong mang po dang lha'i
NK127(jo)001:2509: bu brgya stong mang po yang 'jam dpal gyi phyi
NK127(jo)001:2511: de nas 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa 'od gsal
NK127(jo)001:2512: gyi lha'i ris su 'dug ste mgul pa bsal ba'i
NK127(jo)001:2513: tshe / stong chen po'i 'jig rten thams cad du
NK127(jo)001:2514: sgras go zhing bdud kyi gnas thams cad dpa' bkod
NK127(jo)001:2515: pa'i sgra byung ba de thos nas /
NK127(jo)001:2516: nyan thos chen po des sgra de'i shugs ma bzod
NK127(jo)001:2517: par 'thor klung gis bus pa'i bya bzhin sa la
NK127(jo)001:2518: lhung zhing dngang pa na ngo mtshar du bzung ste
NK127(jo)001:2519: / de bzhin gshegs pa 'od kyi tog la sgra de sus bgyis zhes zhus pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:2520: 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa'i mathu'o zhes gsungs shing /
NK127(jo)001:2521: der 'jam dpal gyis de bzhin gshegs pa la phyag
NK127(jo)001:2522: byas te chos kyi gtam bgyis nas nyan thos chen
NK127(jo)001:2523: po shes rab sgron ma la 'jam dpal gyis chos
NK127(jo)001:2525: 'khor der 'dus pa'i lha'i bu dag gis me tog
NK127(jo)001:2526: sna tshogs kyis 'jam dpal la gtor nas 'di skad
NK127(jo)001:2527: du / gang na 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa
NK127(jo)001:2528: snang ba der ni de bzhin gshegs pa mngon sum
NK127(jo)001:2530: 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa gang du gnas pa'i sa phyogs de yang mchod rten du 'gyur ro //
NK127(jo)001:2531: gang 'jam dpal gyis chos bstan pa shes sam shes
NK127(jo)001:2532: par 'gyur ba'i sems can de dag gis kyang bsod
NK127(jo)001:2533: nams thams cad yongs su bzung ba yin no //
NK127(jo)001:2535: de nas 'jam dpal gyis nyan thos chen po shes rab sgron ma la /
NK127(jo)001:2536: khyod shes rab che ba'i mchog tu bstan na ci
NK127(jo)001:2537: shes rab de 'dus byas sam 'dus ma byas gang
NK127(jo)001:2538: yin las brtsams te dris pas cang mi smra ba
NK127(jo)001:2539: la bkod do // de nas de bzhin gshegs pa
NK127(jo)001:2540: des rjes su gnang ba ltar 'jam dpal gyis 'khor
NK127(jo)001:2541: der chos thams cad dben pa'i sgor bstan pas byang
NK127(jo)001:2542: chub sems dpa' brgyad brgya mi skye ba'i chos la
NK127(jo)001:2543: bzod pa thob par gyur to //
NK127(jo)001:2544: de de lta bus na nyan thos sam rang sangs
NK127(jo)001:2545: rgyas gang gis kyang 'jam dpal gyi spobs pa rgyun
NK127(jo)001:2546: gcod mi nus pas skabs ma phye bar bdag lta
NK127(jo)001:2547: bus 'jam dpal dang lhan cig smra mi nus so
NK127(jo)001:2549: tshe dang ldan pa rab 'byor gyis smras pa /
NK127(jo)001:2550: sh+aa ri'i bus 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa sangs
NK127(jo)001:2551: rgyas kyi zhing du spyad pa spyod pa na rdzu
NK127(jo)001:2552: 'phrul gyi rnam 'phrul ji ltar mthong zhes dris pa
NK127(jo)001:2553: na / sh+aa ri'i bus smras pa /
NK127(jo)001:2554: kho bo 'jam dpal dang lhan cig sangs rgyas kyi zhing du song ba na /
NK127(jo)001:2555: zhing gang dag tshig pa de pad+ma'i chus gang ba
NK127(jo)001:2556: dang me de yang tsan+dana sprul snying dang ka tsa
NK127(jo)001:2557: li di'i gos ltar reg na 'jam par gyur pa
NK127(jo)001:2558: dang / stong pa nam mkha' dag kyang tshangs pa'i
NK127(jo)001:2559: gzhal med khang na bsam gtan la zhugs pa'i byang
NK127(jo)001:2560: chub sems dpas gang bar gnas pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:2561: gang 'chags pa de dag ni 'jig par snang ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:2562: gang ngan song gis gang ba de dag ngan song dang bral ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:2563: sems can de dag byang chub yan lag gi rnam pas bskyed pa'i byams pa thob pa ste /
NK127(jo)001:2564: de gang zhe na gang la snyoms par zhugs na
NK127(jo)001:2565: sems can chags sogs nyon mongs pas gzer ba la
NK127(jo)001:2566: de spang phyir chos ston pa'o //
NK127(jo)001:2567: de'i tshe kho bo'i sems la 'jam dpal dang kho bo'i rdzu 'phrul mnyam mo snyam pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:2568: rtog pa de 'jam dpal gyis rig nas stong chen
NK127(jo)001:2569: po'i 'jig rten gyi khams 'dir me 'bar ba na
NK127(jo)001:2570: 'jig rten gyi bar du 'dug ste ci sh+aa ri'i
NK127(jo)001:2571: bu'am kho bo'i rdzu 'phrul gyi mthus brgal zhes smras
NK127(jo)001:2572: pa'i tshe / bdag gis kho bo'i mthus brgal lo
NK127(jo)001:2573: zhes byas nas rdzu 'phrul gyi mthus mgyogs pa'i cho
NK127(jo)001:2574: 'phrul thams cad bstan te 'dom gang tsam khor yug
NK127(jo)001:2575: tu me de zhi bar byas nas 'jam dpal dang
NK127(jo)001:2576: lhan cig tu zhag bdun gyis 'jig rten gyi khams
NK127(jo)001:2577: pa'i tshe / de brgal lo // de nas dus
NK127(jo)001:2578: gzhan zhig na de bas kyang shin tu rgya che
NK127(jo)001:2579: zhing yangs pa'i 'jig rten gyi khams su me 'bar
NK127(jo)001:2580: ba na 'jig rten gyi bar du 'jug ste /
NK127(jo)001:2581: 'jam dpal gyis kho bo la sh+aa ri'i bu su'i rdzu 'phrul gyi mthus 'di las brgal bar bya /
NK127(jo)001:2582: kho bos khyod kyi mthus brgal lo zhes smras pa na /
NK127(jo)001:2583: sems bskyed pa gcig gis 'jig rten gyi khams de pad+ma'i d+r+wa bas g.yogs te brgal bar gyur to //
NK127(jo)001:2584: de nas 'di skad du bdag cag las su'i mthu mgyogs zhes zer ba na /
NK127(jo)001:2585: kho bos bya lang gu li dang bya'irgyala po nam
NK127(jo)001:2586: mkha' lding gi mgyogs pa bzhin du bdag las khyod
NK127(jo)001:2587: kyi rdzu 'phrul gyi mgyogs pa de bas ches lhag
NK127(jo)001:2588: go // nyan thos rnams bag chags kyi mtshams sbyor
NK127(jo)001:2589: ma bcad pas mi mnyam kyang sngar ni khyod kyi
NK127(jo)001:2590: rdzu 'phrul dang mnyam mo snyam zhes smras pa dang
NK127(jo)001:2591: go // / sngon rgya mtsho'i 'gram na mngon shes lnga thob pa'i drang srong chos 'dod dang /
NK127(jo)001:2592: rig sngags kyi mthus mkha' la 'gro ba drang srong
NK127(jo)001:2593: ku na byin zhes pa gnyis gnas pa las kun
NK127(jo)001:2594: byin gyis nged gnyis rdzu 'phrul mnyam snyam pa dang
NK127(jo)001:2595: / kun byin rgya mtsho'i pha rol tu song ba
NK127(jo)001:2596: srin mo'i gling du song bas srin mo dag gi
NK127(jo)001:2597: yid du 'ong ba'i sgra dang de dag gi gzugs
NK127(jo)001:2598: mthong bas sa la lhungs te rig pa dang sngags
NK127(jo)001:2599: / nyams pa na / chos 'dod kyis snying rje
NK127(jo)001:2600: ba'i sems kyis lag pa nas bzung ste rang gnas
NK127(jo)001:2601: / nyams pa na / su bzhag go // de'i
NK127(jo)001:2602: tshe nga ni chos 'dod dang khyod kun byin zhes
NK127(jo)001:2603: bya bar gyur pa der yang mi mnyam bzhin du
NK127(jo)001:2606: yang sh+aa ri'i bu kho bo dang 'jam dpal lhan
NK127(jo)001:2607: cig lho phyogs su sangs rgyas kyi zhing du spyad
NK127(jo)001:2609: sangs rgyas kyi zhing bye ba khrag khrig brgya stong mang po 'das pa na /
NK127(jo)001:2610: 'jig rten gyi khams rgyan thams cad kyis bklubs pa zhes bya ba na /
NK127(jo)001:2611: de bzhin gshegs pa rin chen srog shing zhes bya ba'i zhing du phyin te /
NK127(jo)001:2613: btsun pa sh+aa ri'i bu khyod kyis bdag cag gis brgal ba'i zhing de ji ltar mthong /
NK127(jo)001:2614: kho bos smras pa kha cig mes gang pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:2616: kha cig nam mkhar gyur pa /
NK127(jo)001:2620: kha cig ngan song gis gang ba /
NK127(jo)001:2621: kha cig ngan song dang bral ba'o zhes smras pa na /
NK127(jo)001:2622: de ji ltar blta bar bya zhes dri ba la /
NK127(jo)001:2623: kho bos mes gang ba de mes gang ba de
NK127(jo)001:2624: ltar blta bar bya ba la sogs pa smras shing
NK127(jo)001:2625: / 'jam dpal khyod kyis ji ltar mthong zhes smras pa dang des smras pa /
NK127(jo)001:2626: zhing de thams cad ni nam mkha'i zhing du mthong
NK127(jo)001:2627: ste mes gang ba'am chus gang ba sogs de dag
NK127(jo)001:2628: yang dag min pa glo bur rkyen las byung ba
NK127(jo)001:2630: nam mkha' ni rkyen las ma byung ba rang bzhin du gnas pa'o //
NK127(jo)001:2631: de bzhin du glo bur gyi nyon mongs pas sems
NK127(jo)001:2632: nyon mongs par gyur pa'ang sems kyi rang bzhin nam
NK127(jo)001:2633: yang nyon mongs par gyur pa med de /
NK127(jo)001:2634: dper na 'das pa'i dus su gang g+aa'i klung gi
NK127(jo)001:2635: bye ma snyed kyi sreg pa'i bskal pa byung yang
NK127(jo)001:2636: nam mkha' sngon tshig pa med pa de bzhin du
NK127(jo)001:2637: / sems can re res kyang gang+g+aa'i klung gi bye snyed kyi mi dge ba'i las 'du byas kyang /
NK127(jo)001:2638: sems kyi rang bzhin nam yang nyon mongs par gyur pa med de /
NK127(jo)001:2639: rang bzhin yongs su dag pa'i chos kyi dbyings de
NK127(jo)001:2640: lta bu la 'jug pa de dag ni kun nas
NK127(jo)001:2642: mngon par 'du byed pa kun nas ldang ba cung zad kyang med do //
NK127(jo)001:2643: 'di ni kun nas ldang ba med pa'i chos kyi sgo ste /
NK127(jo)001:2644: 'di la gnas pa'i byang chub sems dpa' rnams chos
NK127(jo)001:2645: kun gyi rang bzhin yongs su dag par zhugs nas
NK127(jo)001:2646: nyes pas nam yang sgrib par mi 'gyur ro //
NK127(jo)001:2648: kho bos 'jam dpal gyi cho 'phrul phyogs tsam zhig
NK127(jo)001:2649: mngon sum gyur ba de lta bu yin no zhes
NK127(jo)001:2650: smras pa na / tshe dang ldan pa kun dga' bos sh+aa ri'i bu la smras pa /
NK127(jo)001:2651: kho bos kyang 'di ltar bcom ldan 'das rgyal byed kyi tshal na bzhugs pa'i tshe /
NK127(jo)001:2652: mnyan yod du dus ma yin pa'i sprin chen pos zhag bdun char chen po babs pa na /
NK127(jo)001:2653: bsam gtan thob pa'i dge slong dag ting nge 'dzin
NK127(jo)001:2654: la snyoms par zhugs pas dus 'da' bar byas kyi
NK127(jo)001:2655: / gang de lta bu ma thob pa dag zhag
NK127(jo)001:2656: bdun zas chad pas nyam chung ba na bcom ldan
NK127(jo)001:2657: 'das blta ba'i phyir 'dong ma nus pa de yi
NK127(jo)001:2658: / tshe / kho bos dge slong dag rdzud par
NK127(jo)001:2659: gyur pa de bcom ldan 'das la gsol ba dang
NK127(jo)001:2660: / tshe / / 'jam dpal la tshul de smos zhes bka' stsal pa na /
NK127(jo)001:2661: bdag 'jam dpal gyi drung du phyin pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:2662: der des tshangs pa dang brgya byin sogs 'jig rten
NK127(jo)001:2663: skyong ba rnams la chos ston par 'dug pa la
NK127(jo)001:2665: kun dga' bo khyod song ste stan things la gdugs
NK127(jo)001:2666: tshod la bab pa na gan+d+ai rdungs shig zer ba
NK127(jo)001:2667: de bzhin bdag gis byas so //
NK127(jo)001:2668: 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa lus thams cad rnam
NK127(jo)001:2669: par 'jig pa zhes bya ba'i ting nge 'dzin la
NK127(jo)001:2670: snyoms par zhugs nas sprul pa gzhan gyis brgya byin
NK127(jo)001:2671: sogs la chos ston bzhin du /
NK127(jo)001:2672: rang nyid gnas de las byung ste mnyan yod du
NK127(jo)001:2673: bsod snyoms la zhugs kyang kho bos ni ma mthong
NK127(jo)001:2674: ngo // der bdud sdig can gyis 'jam dpal 'di
NK127(jo)001:2675: grong 'dir sus mi mthong ba dang bsod snyoms mi
NK127(jo)001:2676: 'bul bar byin gyis brlabs pa byas pa de 'jam
NK127(jo)001:2677: dpal gyis shes nas 'di skad du /
NK127(jo)001:2678: bden pa'i tshig dang bsod nams dang ye shes kyi
NK127(jo)001:2679: tshogs bdag gi ba spu'i khung bu gcig skye ba'i
NK127(jo)001:2680: bsod nams de yang gang+g+aa'i klung gi bye snyed kyi
NK127(jo)001:2681: 'jig rten gyi khams kyi bdud sdig can rnams la
NK127(jo)001:2682: med pa'i bden pa'i tshig des /
NK127(jo)001:2683: bdud kyi byin rlabs 'di med pa dang bdud sdig
NK127(jo)001:2684: can gyis bdag nyid kyi tshul du lam srang dang
NK127(jo)001:2685: sum mdo sogs su 'jam dpal la bsod snyoms phul
NK127(jo)001:2686: cig / gang gis stong chen po'i khams kyi sems
NK127(jo)001:2687: can thams cad la lo 'bum du bde ba'i yo
NK127(jo)001:2688: byad thams cad kyis rim gror byas gus par byas
NK127(jo)001:2689: cig / pa bas / gang gis 'jam dpal gzhon
NK127(jo)001:2690: nur gyur pa la sen mo'i rtse mo gang tsam
NK127(jo)001:2691: phul ba'i phan yon ches mang ngo zhes sgrogs par
NK127(jo)001:2692: gyur cig ces brjod pa na /
NK127(jo)001:2693: de ma thag tu de kho na ltar gyur nas
NK127(jo)001:2694: bsod pa'i zas sna tshogs ma 'dres par lhung bzed
NK127(jo)001:2695: du bcug ste / dge slong lnga brgya dang byang
NK127(jo)001:2696: chub sems dpa' khri nyis stong dag la ji tsam
NK127(jo)001:2697: gyis chog pa'i zas lhung bzed des blang bar 'gyur
NK127(jo)001:2698: ba de ltar byin gyis brlabs nas /
NK127(jo)001:2699: mnyan yod kyi grong khyer gyi phyi rol tu lhung
NK127(jo)001:2700: bzed sa la bzhag ste bdud sdig can la lhung
NK127(jo)001:2701: bzed 'di khyer la sngon du songs shig ces byas
NK127(jo)001:2702: pa dang / bdud kyis lhung bzed de sa las
NK127(jo)001:2703: btegs kyang 'gul ma nus pa de ltar smras pa
NK127(jo)001:2704: pa dang / dang / bdud khyod mthu chen po
NK127(jo)001:2705: dang ldan na rdzu 'phrul gyi stobs kyis theg cig
NK127(jo)001:2706: pa dang / dang / ces smras pas / bdud
NK127(jo)001:2707: kyi rdzu 'phrul thams cad bstan kyang tha na skra'i
NK127(jo)001:2708: rtse mo tsam yang 'degs ma nus nas /
NK127(jo)001:2709: bdud ngo mtshar du gyur te kho bos 'dod na
NK127(jo)001:2710: ri gshol mda' 'dzin lag mthil du blangs te mkha'
NK127(jo)001:2711: la 'dor mod kyi lhung bzed chung ngu 'di sa
NK127(jo)001:2712: 'di'i steng nas 'degs ma nus na ci'i phyir de
NK127(jo)001:2713: ltar gyur / 'jam dpal gyis smras pa /
NK127(jo)001:2714: sems can chen po rnams dang gang zag chen po
NK127(jo)001:2715: rnams kyi stobs drangs pa lhung bzed 'dir bcug pas
NK127(jo)001:2717: de nas 'jam dpal gyis lhung bzed des las blangs
NK127(jo)001:2718: nas sdig can 'di khur la sngon la song zhes
NK127(jo)001:2719: smras pas bdud de slob ma bzhin du lhung bzed
NK127(jo)001:2720: khyer te sngon la song ngo //
NK127(jo)001:2721: dbang bsgyur lha'i bu khri nyis stong gis 'jam dpal la phyag 'tshal te smras pa /
NK127(jo)001:2722: sdig can 'di bran bzhin mdun du 'gro ba ci zhig /'jam dpal gyi mthus bdud kyis smras pa /
NK127(jo)001:2723: bdud kyi stobs ni gti mug gi stobs so //
NK127(jo)001:2724: byang chub sems dpa'i stobs ni shes rab kyi stobs so //
NK127(jo)001:2725: zhes sogs smras pas 'khor de'i lha'i bu lnga brgya bla med byang chub tu sems skyes so //
NK127(jo)001:2726: byang chub sems dpa' nyis brgyas mi skye ba'i chos la bzod pa thob bo //
NK127(jo)001:2727: de nas 'jam dpal dang bdud sdig can lhan cig
NK127(jo)001:2728: pas lhung bzed de 'khor gyi khyams su bzhag ste
NK127(jo)001:2729: song ba kho bos ma mthong ma thos nas /
NK127(jo)001:2730: gdugs tshod la bab kyang 'jam dpal ni gnas khang
NK127(jo)001:2731: de nas byung ba'am zhugs pa ma mthong bas 'jam
NK127(jo)001:2732: dpal gyis dge slong gi dge 'dun ma bslus sam
NK127(jo)001:2733: snyam du bcom ldan 'das la de skad gsol pa
NK127(jo)001:2735: 'khor gyi khyams zlum po der ci ma mthong ngam /
NK127(jo)001:2737: de na lhung bzed zas kyis bkang ba gcig gada'o zhes zhus pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:2739: gan+di rdungs la dge 'dun sdus gsungs pa na bdag gis /
NK127(jo)001:2740: lhung bzed gcig gis ji ltar bya zhes zhus pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:2741: stong chen po'i sems can thams cad kyis lhung bzed
NK127(jo)001:2742: gcig po de las zos kyang mi zad par 'jam
NK127(jo)001:2743: dpal gzhon nur gyur pas byin gyis brlabs pa ste
NK127(jo)001:2744: / de'i sbyin pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa ni bsod nams zad mi shes par 'byung ba'o //
NK127(jo)001:2745: zhes bka' stsal pas bdag gis gan+di brdung ba na /
NK127(jo)001:2746: 'jam dpal kyang lha'i bu de dag dang byang chub
NK127(jo)001:2747: sems dpa' de dag dang 'grogs te rang gi gnas
NK127(jo)001:2748: khang nas byung nas khyams zlum po der 'ong ba
NK127(jo)001:2749: dang / lhung bzed de las bsod pa'i bza' bca'
NK127(jo)001:2750: myang ba ma 'dres pas dge slong mang po thams
NK127(jo)001:2751: cad dang byang chub sems dpa' mang po thams cad
NK127(jo)001:2752: tshim par byas kyang de ni yongs su ma zad
NK127(jo)001:2753: dang / do // de nas bdud sdig can gyis 'jam dpal la bar chad bya ba'i phyir /
NK127(jo)001:2754: sham thabs sogs gos legs par ma bgos pa /
NK127(jo)001:2757: dbang po ma tshang shing ngan pa /
NK127(jo)001:2758: lus ring thung sna tshogs pa sogs yid du mi
NK127(jo)001:2759: 'tshams pa'i dge slong bzhi khri sprul pa de dag
NK127(jo)001:2760: la byin kyang zas de dag ma zad la /
NK127(jo)001:2761: de re res kyang 'bras chan yul ma ga d+h+aa'i
NK127(jo)001:2762: bre bo bcu bcu zos kyang tshim par mi 'gyur
NK127(jo)001:2763: ba de ltar byin gyis brlabs so //
NK127(jo)001:2764: der rung byed rnams yongs su skyo yang de dag tshim par byed ma nus so //
NK127(jo)001:2765: de nas 'jam dpal gyis bdud kyis sprul pa'i dge
NK127(jo)001:2766: slong de dag gi lag na lhung bzed bkang ba
NK127(jo)001:2767: thogs nas lag pa na yang kham thogs la /
NK127(jo)001:2768: khar bcug pa'i kham yang mid mi nus par mgrin
NK127(jo)001:2769: pa btsir ba bzhin du mig log ste sa la
NK127(jo)001:2770: lhung bar byin gyis brlabs nas bdud la smras pa
NK127(jo)001:2771: / sdig can khyod kyi dge slong 'di dag ci'i phyir zas mi za /
NK127(jo)001:2773: 'jam dpal bdag gi dge slong 'di dag ni shi
NK127(jo)001:2774: la thug par gyur na khyod kyis dug dang bsres
NK127(jo)001:2777: gang dag dug spel bar byed pa de dag dug sbyin gyi /
NK127(jo)001:2778: dug med pa rnams dug sbyin par ga la 'gyur /
NK127(jo)001:2779: sdig can dug ces bya ba ni 'dod chags dang zhe sdang dang gti mug ste /
NK127(jo)001:2780: de dag kyang legs par gsungs pa'i chos 'dul ba la med do zhes sogs dang /
NK127(jo)001:2781: sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa ni bdud rtsi bstan pa
NK127(jo)001:2782: dang bde ba bstan pa dang spros pa med pa
NK127(jo)001:2783: bstan pa zhes sogs gsungs pas /
NK127(jo)001:2784: bdud dang lhan cig lhags pa'i lha'i bu lnga brgyas
NK127(jo)001:2785: bla med byang chub tu sems bskyed nas smon lam
NK127(jo)001:2786: btab bo // de'i tshe bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
NK127(jo)001:2787: phyi ma'i tshe lnga brgya'i tha ma dam pa'i chos
NK127(jo)001:2788: 'jig pa na dge slong phal cher 'di bzhin du
NK127(jo)001:2789: gos legs par ma bgos pa /
NK127(jo)001:2793: nad sna tshogs kyis btab pa dag chos kyi phyir
NK127(jo)001:2794: ma yin par rnyed bkur gyi ched du rab tu
NK127(jo)001:2795: byung nas bya ba sna tshogs kyis brel ba dag
NK127(jo)001:2796: 'byung ste / de'i tshe bdud dga' zhing bdud kyi las 'byung bar 'gyur pas na /
NK127(jo)001:2797: chos la brtson pas bdud tshar bcad cing dam pa'i
NK127(jo)001:2798: chos bzung bar bya'o zhes gsungs pas byang chub sems
NK127(jo)001:2799: dpa' sum khri nyis stong gis mi skye bar chos
NK127(jo)001:2800: la bzod pa thob pa sogs su gyur to zhes
NK127(jo)001:2801: brjod do // de nas 'od srung sa chen pos
NK127(jo)001:2802: 'di skad du kho bos kyang 'jam dpal gyi cho
NK127(jo)001:2803: 'phrul kha cig mngon du gyur te /
NK127(jo)001:2804: bcom ldan 'das sangs rgyas nas ring po ma lon
NK127(jo)001:2805: zhing kho bo yang rab tu byung nas ring po
NK127(jo)001:2807: 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa de bzhin gshegs pa
NK127(jo)001:2808: rin chen srog shing gi sangs rgyas kyi zhing nas
NK127(jo)001:2809: bcom ldan 'das la lta ba dang phyag bya ba
NK127(jo)001:2810: dang bsnyen bkur bya ba'i phyir 'jig rten 'dir 'ong
NK127(jo)001:2811: ba na / bcom ldan 'das rgyal bu rgyal byed
NK127(jo)001:2812: kyi tshal mgon med zas sbyin gyi kun dga' ra
NK127(jo)001:2813: ba na dbyar gnas par dam bca' mdzad do //
NK127(jo)001:2814: der 'jam dpal kyang dbyar zla gsum gnas par dam
NK127(jo)001:2815: bcas nas der sangs rgyas kyi spyan snga dang dge
NK127(jo)001:2816: 'dun gyi nang sogs su gso sbyong sogs kyi las
NK127(jo)001:2817: la kho bo cag gis nam yang ma mthong bar
NK127(jo)001:2818: zla ba gsum 'das nas gso sbyong dang dgag dbye'i
NK127(jo)001:2820: kho bos 'jam dpal khyod dbyar zla gsum du gang na 'dug /
NK127(jo)001:2822: btsun pa mnyan yod kyi grong khyer 'dir gsal rgyal gyi btsun ma'i nang na'o //
NK127(jo)001:2823: de la kho bo 'di snyam du /
NK127(jo)001:2824: sems can 'di lta bu ltung ba dang bcas pa
NK127(jo)001:2825: yongs su dag pa'i dge 'dun rnams dang lhan cig
NK127(jo)001:2826: dgag dbye byar mi rung ngo snyam nas /
NK127(jo)001:2827: kho bo 'khor gyi khyams de nas byung ste 'jam
NK127(jo)001:2828: dpal gzhon nur gyur pa bskrad pa'i phyir gan+d+ai brdungs
NK127(jo)001:2829: so // der bcom ldan 'das kyis 'jam dpal la
NK127(jo)001:2830: 'od srungs chen pos gan+d+ai brdungs pa la sems la
NK127(jo)001:2831: khyod la ma dad par mi 'gyur bar rang nyid
NK127(jo)001:2832: tshangs pa dang rang gi spyod yul ston la nyan
NK127(jo)001:2833: thos chen po rnams mgu bar byos shig ces bka'
NK127(jo)001:2834: so // stsal pas / 'jam dpal gyis sangs rgyas
NK127(jo)001:2835: kyi zhing thams cad yang dag par ston pa zhes
NK127(jo)001:2836: bya ba'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs nas
NK127(jo)001:2837: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas kyi zhing gang+g+aa'i klung gi bye
NK127(jo)001:2838: so // stsal pas / ma snyed na / sbyangs
NK127(jo)001:2839: pa'i yon tan smra ba'i dge slong 'od srungs chen
NK127(jo)001:2840: po 'dra ba sha stag 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur
NK127(jo)001:2841: pa bskrad pa'i phyir gan+d+ai brdung ba snang bar gyur
NK127(jo)001:2842: so // stsal pas / ma snyed na / to
NK127(jo)001:2843: // bcom ldan 'das kyis kho bo la 'od srungs
NK127(jo)001:2844: ci'i phyir gan+d+ai rdung zhes bka' stsal pa na kho
NK127(jo)001:2845: bos tshul de zhus pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:2846: bcom ldan 'das kyi sku thams cad las 'od byung
NK127(jo)001:2847: ste kho bo la 'od srungs de phyogs bcu na
NK127(jo)001:2848: ci snang ba je ltos shig gsungs pas /
NK127(jo)001:2849: kho bos bltas pas gong ltar mthong ba dang bka' stsal pa /
NK127(jo)001:2850: khyod ci gang de'i mdun na 'dug pa'i 'jam dpal 'adi'am /
NK127(jo)001:2851: 'on te phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas kyi drung na 'dug pa'am gang bskrad /
NK127(jo)001:2852: de'i tshe kho bo ngo tsha ba'i tshul gyis gan+d+ai
NK127(jo)001:2853: des la bor snyam na'ang dor ma nus par rgyun
NK127(jo)001:2854: ma chad pa'i sgra byung ste /
NK127(jo)001:2855: rgyal byed kyi tshal na ji lta ba bzhin du
NK127(jo)001:2856: sangs rgyas kyi zhing kun la lhag chad med par
NK127(jo)001:2858: de'i tshe kho bos bcom ldan 'das kyi zhabs la phyag btsal nas /
NK127(jo)001:2859: bdag ni shes pa phyogs gcig dang ldan pa ste /
NK127(jo)001:2860: byang chub sems dpa'i yul tshad med pa rnams kyi
NK127(jo)001:2861: spyod yul ma 'tshal nas gan+d+ai brdung ba 'jam dpal
NK127(jo)001:2862: gzhon nur gyur pa la bzod par gsol lo //
NK127(jo)001:2864: 'od srungs sangs rgyas kyi zhing na 'jam dpal 'di
NK127(jo)001:2865: snyed snang ba thams cad khyim pa'i khyim du sems
NK127(jo)001:2866: can smin par bya ba'i phyir dbyar zla gsum gnas
NK127(jo)001:2867: so // mnyan yod 'dir btsun mo'i 'khor du dbyar
NK127(jo)001:2868: gnas par dam bcas pas kyang gsal rgyal gyi btsun
NK127(jo)001:2869: mo'i 'khor las bud med lnga brgya dang /
NK127(jo)001:2873: smad 'tshongs ma lnga brgya dang bcas pa bla med
NK127(jo)001:2874: byang chub las phyir mi ldog par smin par byas
NK127(jo)001:2875: so // sems can mang po dag nyan thos kyi
NK127(jo)001:2876: theg pas btul te mtho ris su 'gro bar byas
NK127(jo)001:2877: so // so // bcom ldan 'das la kho bos gsol pa /
NK127(jo)001:2878: 'jam dpal gyis chos ji lta bu bshad pas smin par byas /
NK127(jo)001:2880: 'jam dpal nyid la dris dang des lan ldon par 'gyur ro //
NK127(jo)001:2881: kho bos 'jam dpal la dris pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:2882: btsun pa 'od srungs chen po sems can de lta
NK127(jo)001:2883: bu de dag ni chos bshad pas smin par mi
NK127(jo)001:2884: 'gyur te / sems can gang dag dga' ba'i rtsed mos smin par 'gyur ba'ang yod /
NK127(jo)001:2885: de bzhin du khab tu bzung ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:2891: tshangs pa sogs gzugs sna tshogs dang /
NK127(jo)001:2895: phan gdags pa sogs kyis smin pa yang yod de /
NK127(jo)001:2896: sems can gyi spyod pa ni khams sna tshogs pa ste /
NK127(jo)001:2897: de bya ba sna tshogs pas smin par 'gyur ba
NK127(jo)001:2898: da ltar smin pa'i sems can rnams la phyis chos
NK127(jo)001:2901: 'jam dpal khyod kyi spyod pa 'dis sems can ji snyed cig smin par byas /
NK127(jo)001:2903: chos kyi dbyings ji snyed pa'o //
NK127(jo)001:2904: chos kyi dbyings dang nam mkha'i khams dang sems can
NK127(jo)001:2905: gyi khams de ni gnyis su med do zhes sogs
NK127(jo)001:2906: dang / byang chub sems dpa'i go cha sum cu
NK127(jo)001:2907: rtsa gnyis bshad pas lha'i bu khri nyis stong gis
NK127(jo)001:2908: bla med byang chub tu sems skyes so zhes 'od
NK127(jo)001:2909: srung gis de skad smras pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:2910: de nas tshe dang ldan pa byams ma'i bu gang pos smras pa /
NK127(jo)001:2911: kho bos kyang 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa'i rdzu 'phrul gyi 'phrul 'ga' zhig mngon du gyur te /
NK127(jo)001:2912: dus gcig na bcom ldan 'das yangs pa can gyi
NK127(jo)001:2913: grong khyer gyi tshal chen po'i khang brtsegs na dge
NK127(jo)001:2914: slong gi dge 'dun chen po dang thabs gcig tu
NK127(jo)001:2915: bzhugs so // de'i tshe gcer bu ma'i bu bden
NK127(jo)001:2916: pa po zhes bya ba gcer bu pa drug khris
NK127(jo)001:2917: bskor te bla mar byas mchod par byas nas yangs
NK127(jo)001:2919: kho bos ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs nas
NK127(jo)001:2920: mu stegs de dag gi dge ba'i rtsa ba la
NK127(jo)001:2921: bltas pas mu stegs can gdul bya mang po zhig
NK127(jo)001:2922: mthong ste / kho bo der song nas de dag la chos bshad kyang sri zhu mi byed /
NK127(jo)001:2923: rna blags te mi nyan par 'phya zhing tshig rtsub mo smra'o //
NK127(jo)001:2924: der kho bos zla ba gsum du sems can 'ga'
NK127(jo)001:2925: yang smin par bya ma nus te skyo bar gyur
NK127(jo)001:2927: der 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pas mu stegs can lnga brgyar sprul te /
NK127(jo)001:2928: bdag nyid slob dpon du bzhag nas 'khor lnga brgya
NK127(jo)001:2929: dang lhan cig gcer bu ma'i bu bden pa po
NK127(jo)001:2930: gang na bar lhags te bden pa po'i rkang pa
NK127(jo)001:2931: gnyis la mgo bos phyag 'tshal nas mdun du 'dug
NK127(jo)001:2933: bdag cag gis 'phags pa'i grags pa rgya chen po
NK127(jo)001:2934: thos nas 'dir mchis te khyod bdag gi ston par
NK127(jo)001:2935: byas nas rjes su bstan pa nod do //
NK127(jo)001:2936: ci nas kyang dge sbyong goo ta ma dang de'i
NK127(jo)001:2937: nyan thos rnams mi mthong ba dang de las mi
NK127(jo)001:2938: mthun pa'i chos mi thos pa de ltar kho bo
NK127(jo)001:2939: cag la mdzod cig ces smras pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:2941: legs so dad pa dang ldan pa khyod myur du nga'i chos bstan pa 'di shes par 'gyur ro //
NK127(jo)001:2942: de nas bden pa pos rang gi 'khor rnams la
NK127(jo)001:2943: bram ze'i bu lnga brgya 'di dang lhan cig dga'
NK127(jo)001:2944: zhing mthun par chos dpyod cig /'di dag gis gang
NK127(jo)001:2945: smras pa khyod kyis legs par zungs shig ces byas
NK127(jo)001:2946: so // de nas 'jam dpal sprul pa dang bcas
NK127(jo)001:2947: pa de dag gis mu stegs can de dag dang
NK127(jo)001:2948: lhan cig 'dug nas dka' thub dang spyod lam sogs
NK127(jo)001:2949: rgyun mi 'chad par lhag par ston cing skabs skabs
NK127(jo)001:2950: su dkon mchog gsum gyi basngagasa pa brjod /
NK127(jo)001:2951: skabs skabs gcer bu mo'i bu bden pa po'i yang dag pa'i yon tan basngagasa pa brjod de /
NK127(jo)001:2952: des de dag yid ches par byas nas 'dug pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:2953: tshod la bab pa'i dus gzhan zhig na 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pas 'di skad ces smras so //
NK127(jo)001:2954: tshe dang ldan pa dag bdag cag gi bstan bcos
NK127(jo)001:2955: dang sngags dang rig byed dang gzhung las byung ba
NK127(jo)001:2956: bzhin dge sbyong goo ta ma'i yon tan basngagasa pa
NK127(jo)001:2957: yod de / de ci'i phyir na goo ta ma
NK127(jo)001:2958: ni 'khor los sgyur ba'i rigs skyon med par skyes
NK127(jo)001:2959: pa bltams pa na brgya byin dang tshangs pas blangs
NK127(jo)001:2960: yod de / pa sogs dang / bram ze dag gis lung bstan tshul /
NK127(jo)001:2961: rab tu byung nas sangs rgyas pa /
NK127(jo)001:2962: dge ba gsum dang tshangs spyod bzhi ldan gyi chos
NK127(jo)001:2963: ston pa sogs kyi basngagasa pa brjod pa'i chos bstan
NK127(jo)001:2964: pas mu stegs can lnga brgya chos kyi mig rnam
NK127(jo)001:2966: gzhan mu stegs can brgya stong ni bla med byang chub tu sems skyes so //
NK127(jo)001:2967: de nas sprul pa lnga brgya bo'i yan lag lngas
NK127(jo)001:2968: gtugs te phyag 'tshal nas sangs rgyas la phyag 'tshal
NK127(jo)001:2969: lo zhes pa'i tshig brjod do //
NK127(jo)001:2970: de dag gi rjes su slob pa'i tshul gyi sa
NK127(jo)001:2971: mu stegs can gyi 'khor kun gyis kyang de ltar
NK127(jo)001:2973: de'i tshe lha'i dbang pos me tog man+da ra ba
NK127(jo)001:2974: byin nas khyed kyis 'dis bcom ldan 'das la mchod
NK127(jo)001:2976: de nas 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa 'khor mang
NK127(jo)001:2977: pos bskor te smyig ma'i ldum bu'i 'khor gyi khyams
NK127(jo)001:2978: ga la bar bcom ldan 'das kyi drung du dong
NK127(jo)001:2979: nas phyag btsal te mu stegs can gyi 'khor rnams
NK127(jo)001:2980: kyis kyang me tog man+da ra bas mchod cing lan
NK127(jo)001:2981: gsum bskor te phyogs gcig 'dug go //
NK127(jo)001:2982: de nas 'jam dpal gyi sprul pa lnga brgya po de dag gis gsol pa /
NK127(jo)001:2983: bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa chos kyi sku
NK127(jo)001:2984: ste bdag cag sangs rgyas la lta ba ngan du
NK127(jo)001:2985: mi gnyer ro // bcom ldan 'das chos ni brjod
NK127(jo)001:2986: du ma mchis pa ste bdag cag bcom ldan 'das
NK127(jo)001:2987: kyi chos nyan pa don du mi gnyer ro //
NK127(jo)001:2988: zhes sogs chos kun rang bzhin med pas don du
NK127(jo)001:2989: mi gnyer bar bstan pa'i chos kyi rnam grangs bshad
NK127(jo)001:2990: pas dge slong nyis brgya ni len pa med par
NK127(jo)001:2991: zag pa rnams las sems rnam par grol lo //
NK127(jo)001:2992: dge slong bsam gtan bzhi thob pa mngon pa'i nga rgyal can nyis brgyas ni /
NK127(jo)001:2993: 'di ni 'jig rten thams cad dang 'gal bar chos
NK127(jo)001:2994: 'chad pa'i zhes tshig de skad smras te stan las
NK127(jo)001:2996: de nas gang po bdag gis 'jam dpal la dge
NK127(jo)001:2997: slong nyis brgya po 'di ltar ma gus par song
NK127(jo)001:3000: btsun pa gang po chos bshad pa 'jig rten kun dang 'gal bar gyur pa yod do //
NK127(jo)001:3001: 'jig rten na phung po sogs su zhen nas de spangs pas myang 'das tshol zhing /
NK127(jo)001:3002: 'khor ba rang bzhin gyis mi dmigs pa myang 'das su mi shes pas 'gal lo //
NK127(jo)001:3003: gang 'khor ba dang myang 'das mnyam pa nyid kyis
NK127(jo)001:3004: gnyis su med pa de ni mi 'gal lo zhes
NK127(jo)001:3005: sogs chos kyi rnam grangs bstan cing /
NK127(jo)001:3006: dge slong de dag lam gang du dong ba der
NK127(jo)001:3007: mes gang bar sprul pas de dag nam mkha' la
