NK127(jo)001:3008: dong pa dang / lcags kyi d+r+wa bas nam mkhar
NK127(jo)001:3009: yog par mthong la 'og tu bltas na chu'i phung
NK127(jo)001:3010: po chen po mthong bas de dag phyogs bslad cing
NK127(jo)001:3011: spu zing byed par gyur nas /
NK127(jo)001:3012: rgyal byed tshal gyi lam du bltas pas pad+ma dang
NK127(jo)001:3013: ut+pala sogs kyis yog cing skye bo mang po bcom
NK127(jo)001:3014: ldan 'das la chos mnyan pa'i phyir dong ba mthong
NK127(jo)001:3015: nas de dag phyir log ste /
NK127(jo)001:3016: rgyal byed kyi tshal gang dang smyig ma'i ldum bu'i
NK127(jo)001:3017: 'khor gyi khyams gang du bcom ldan 'das ga la
NK127(jo)001:3018: ba der dong ste lhags pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:3019: bcom ldan 'das la phyag 'tshal te lan gsum bskor nas phyogs gcig tu 'khod pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:3020: de rnams la gang po bdag gis khyed gar dong gang nas 'ong zhes dris pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:3021: de dag gis bdag cag ni dgra bcom pa zag
NK127(jo)001:3022: pa zad pa bsam gtan thob pa rdzu 'phrul gyi
NK127(jo)001:3023: rkang pa'i pha rol tu son pa ste /
NK127(jo)001:3024: kho bo cag 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa 'di
NK127(jo)001:3025: las mi mthun pa'i chos bshad pa thos nas stan
NK127(jo)001:3027: zhing 'di mes gang ba mthong nas de las brgal ma nus so //
NK127(jo)001:3028: kho bos bcom ldan 'das la zhus pa /
NK127(jo)001:3029: dgra bcom pa zag pa zad pa'i sa de gang lags /
NK127(jo)001:3031: gang po 'dod chags dang zhe sdang dang gti mug
NK127(jo)001:3032: gi me la spyod pas me yi phung po las
NK127(jo)001:3033: 'da' ba ni gnas ma yin no //
NK127(jo)001:3034: lta ba'i d+r+wa bas bsgribs pas lcags kyi d+r+wa ba bcad pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:3035: srid pa'i chur zhugs nas chu'i phung po la brgal ba ni gnas ma yin no //
NK127(jo)001:3036: me'i phung po sogs gang nas ma 'ongs gang du
NK127(jo)001:3037: ma song ste 'jam dpal gyi byin gyi rlabs kyis
NK127(jo)001:3038: snang ngo // de bzhin du chags sogs kyang 'gro
NK127(jo)001:3039: 'ong med na yang phyin ci log gi rtog pa
NK127(jo)001:3040: la bdag po med pa la bdag tu sgro 'dogs
NK127(jo)001:3041: snang ngo // par zad de / de la rnal
NK127(jo)001:3042: 'byor spyod pas sems rtse gcig pa'i zhi gnas ba
NK127(jo)001:3043: sgrubs te bsam gtan thob kyang rlom pa dang mngon
NK127(jo)001:3044: snang ngo // par zad de / zhen mi bya
NK127(jo)001:3045: / bsam gtan las su rung ba'i sems kyis chos
NK127(jo)001:3046: thams cad kyi rgyu dang rkyen la so sor rtog
NK127(jo)001:3047: pas rten 'brel bcu gnyis kyi dbyung ldog shes shing
NK127(jo)001:3048: snang ngo // par zad de / zhen mi bya
NK127(jo)001:3049: / / chos thams cad rang bzhin gyis ma skyes
NK127(jo)001:3050: pa'i don dam pa rtogs par 'gyur ro zhes gsungs
NK127(jo)001:3051: pas dge slong de dag zag pa thams cad las
NK127(jo)001:3053: de nas gcer bu ma'i bu bden pa po 'khor
NK127(jo)001:3054: dmas par gyur pas g.yog lnga brgya bcas bcom ldan
NK127(jo)001:3055: 'das kyi drung du lhags nas 'di skad du /
NK127(jo)001:3056: dge sbyong goo ta ma ni gzhan gyi 'khor sgyus
NK127(jo)001:3057: kha 'dren to zhes yang yang thos na sa da
NK127(jo)001:3059: 'jam dpal gyis bdag gi 'khor phye nas goo ta
NK127(jo)001:3060: ma la phul ba des kyang bzung nas slar kho
NK127(jo)001:3061: bo'i drung du mi 'ongs so zhes smras pa'i tshe
NK127(jo)001:3062: / kun tu rgyu rgyal ba'i blo gros zhes bya
NK127(jo)001:3063: ba 'khor der 'dus pas bden pa po la smras
NK127(jo)001:3064: / pa / bcom ldan 'das dang de'i nyan thos
NK127(jo)001:3065: dang 'jam dpal la ma dad par ma byed cig
NK127(jo)001:3066: khyod la yun ring por don med pa dang sdug
NK127(jo)001:3068: phyi rol pa'i ya mtshan can gyi sgom pa sogs
NK127(jo)001:3069: ni chu bsrubs pas mar 'dod pa ltar log pa
NK127(jo)001:3070: dang / bcom ldan 'das kyi chos 'dul ba ni
NK127(jo)001:3071: 'o ma bsrubs pas mar 'dod pa ltar phyin ci
NK127(jo)001:3073: 'jim pa las byas pa'i snod bzhag ste rin po
NK127(jo)001:3074: che'i snod byin pa ltar mu stegs can bzhag nas
NK127(jo)001:3075: de bzhin gshegs pa'i bstan pa'i snod du byas na
NK127(jo)001:3076: bslus par mi 'gyur te lam gol bar dong ba
NK127(jo)001:3078: gcer bu pa de lta mod kyi khyod kyis 'khor 'di khrid de songs shig /
NK127(jo)001:3079: de nas bden pa po gcer bu pa khri nyis stong dang lhan cig dong ngo //
NK127(jo)001:3080: lhag mas mngon shes thob nas bcom ldan 'das kyis tshur shog gis rab tu byung ngo //
NK127(jo)001:3081: de'i tshe bcom ldan 'das kyis rgyal ba'i blo gros la bka' stsal pa /
NK127(jo)001:3082: bden pa po dang lhan cig dong ba'i gcer bu
NK127(jo)001:3083: pa khri nyis stong de dag chos zab mo 'di
NK127(jo)001:3084: thos pas na byams pa'i 'dus pa dang po'i grangs
NK127(jo)001:3086: bden pa po ni byams pa'i shes rab can gyi
NK127(jo)001:3087: mchog ste da lta nga'i sh+aa ri'i bu bzhin no
NK127(jo)001:3088: // de ni da ltar nga la mos pa yod
NK127(jo)001:3089: kyang lhag pa'i nga rgyal gyis lta ba yongs su
NK127(jo)001:3090: // mi gtong ngo // de nas rgyal ba'i blo
NK127(jo)001:3091: gros la 'jam dpal dang bcom ldan 'das kyis mngon
NK127(jo)001:3092: pa'i nga rgyal med pa sogs kyi tshul dang brtson
NK127(jo)001:3093: 'grus dang bag yod las brtsams te chos bstan pas
NK127(jo)001:3094: // mi gtong ngo // / byang chub tu sems
NK127(jo)001:3095: bskyed pa mi skye ba'i chos la bzod pa thob
NK127(jo)001:3096: nas de bzhin gshegs pa ye shes phung po zhes
NK127(jo)001:3098: zhes gang pos brjod pa de bzhin du bcom ldan
NK127(jo)001:3099: 'das kyi spyan sngar 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa'i
NK127(jo)001:3100: rdzu 'phrul rnam par rtse ba'i cho 'phrul dang /
NK127(jo)001:3101: chos bstan pa rnam par 'phrul pa'i cho 'phrul ji
NK127(jo)001:3102: ltar mngon sum du gyur pa dag phan tshun rjod
NK127(jo)001:3103: par byed do // zhes gsungs so //
NK127(jo)001:3104: sangs rgyas phal po che las /
NK127(jo)001:3105: de nas 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa gnas pa med pa'i khang brtsegs na 'dug 'dug pa las /
NK127(jo)001:3106: skal ba mthun pa'i byang chub sems dpa' de dag dang /
NK127(jo)001:3107: rtag tu phyi bzhin 'brangs pa lag na rdo rje dang /
NK127(jo)001:3108: lus kyi ris su gtogs pa'i lha dang /
NK127(jo)001:3109: rkang gis 'gro ba'i ris su gtogs pa'i lha dang /
NK127(jo)001:3110: sa'i lha la sogs pa dang klu dang gnod sbyin dri za la sogs pa'i dbang po dang /
NK127(jo)001:3111: brgya byin dang tshangs pa'i dbang po rnams kyis rim gro chen pos mngon par bstod cing mchod de /
NK127(jo)001:3112: de lta bu'i byang chub sems dpa'i rnam par gnon
NK127(jo)001:3113: pa'i rgyan phun sum tshogs pa dang ldan pas rang
NK127(jo)001:3115: bcom ldan 'das la lan brgya phrag du mar bskor
NK127(jo)001:3116: nas mchod pa rnam pa du mas mchod de bcom
NK127(jo)001:3117: ldan 'das kyi spyan snga nas phyir byung nas lho
NK127(jo)001:3118: phyogs su yul rgyu zhing song ngo //
NK127(jo)001:3119: de nas sangs rgyas kyi byin gyis rlabs kyis sh+aa
NK127(jo)001:3120: ri'i bus 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa byang chub
NK127(jo)001:3121: sems dpa'i rnam 'phrul gyi rgyan phun sum tshogs pas
NK127(jo)001:3122: dze ta'i tshal nas lho phyogs su 'gro ba mthong
NK127(jo)001:3123: nas / de 'di snyam du 'jam dpal gzhon nur
NK127(jo)001:3124: gyur pa dang lhan cig yul rgyu zhing 'agro'o snyam
NK127(jo)001:3125: nas de dge slong drug cu tsam gyis bskor zhing
NK127(jo)001:3126: mdun du byas te rang gi gnas nas byung zhing
NK127(jo)001:3127: bcom ldan 'das gan ba der song ste phyag 'tshal
NK127(jo)001:3128: nas / nas / bcom ldan 'das la zhus shing
NK127(jo)001:3129: gnang nas phyir byung ste 'jam dpal dang lhan cig
NK127(jo)001:3130: nas / nas / tu song ngo // der sh+aa
NK127(jo)001:3131: ri'i bu dang lhan cig tu 'gro ba'i dge slong
NK127(jo)001:3132: nas / nas / tu song ngo // ni / 'di ltar dge slong rgya mtsho'i blo dang /
NK127(jo)001:3133: legs par byin pa chen po dang /
NK127(jo)001:3134: bsod nams kyi 'od la sogs pa rab tu byung
NK127(jo)001:3135: nas ring po ma lon pa gsar bu sha stag
NK127(jo)001:3136: ste / de thams cad sngon gyi rgyal ba la bya ba byas pa /
NK127(jo)001:3137: mos pa zab cing de bzhin gshegs pa'i yon tan
NK127(jo)001:3138: dang chos kyi ngo bo nyid la lta zhing mos
NK127(jo)001:3139: pa'i sems rgya chen pos spyod pa /
NK127(jo)001:3140: gzhan la phan par 'gyur ba'i blo can 'jam dpal
NK127(jo)001:3141: gzhon nur gyur pas chos bstan pas 'dul ba sha
NK127(jo)001:3142: stag go // de nas tshe dang ldan pa sh+aa
NK127(jo)001:3143: ri'i bus de ltar lam du 'dod pa'i tshe dge
NK127(jo)001:3144: slong kun la bltas nas dge slong rgya mtsho'i blo
NK127(jo)001:3145: stag go // la smras pa / rgya mtsho'i blo
NK127(jo)001:3146: byang chub sems dpa' 'jam dpal gyi lus mtshan dang
NK127(jo)001:3147: dpe byad bzang pos rnam par brgyan cing yongs su
NK127(jo)001:3148: stag go // la smras pa / dag pa /
NK127(jo)001:3149: lha dang mir bcas pas bsam gyis mi khyab pa
NK127(jo)001:3150: stag go // la smras pa / dag pa /
NK127(jo)001:3151: / 'od kyi dkyil 'khor yongs su dag cing sems
NK127(jo)001:3152: can tshad med pa 'i dga' ba yongs su skyed
NK127(jo)001:3153: stag go // la smras pa / dag pa /
NK127(jo)001:3154: / pa / 'od zer gyi dra ba'i rgyan sems
NK127(jo)001:3155: can dpag tu med pa'i sdug bsngal zhi bar byed
NK127(jo)001:3156: stag go // la smras pa / dag pa /
NK127(jo)001:3157: / pa / pa / 'khor phun sum tshogs pa
NK127(jo)001:3158: sngon gyi dge rtsas yongs su bzung ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:3159: lam gyi rgyan 'gro na lam mig mang ris su gnas pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:3160: lam rnam par gnon pa'i rgyan phyogs kyi dkyil 'khor
NK127(jo)001:3161: thams cad la mngon par lta bar gnas pa dang
NK127(jo)001:3162: / bsod nams phun sum tshogs pa'i rgyan g.yas g.yon nas gter chen pho mngon par 'thon pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:3163: sngon gyi sangs rgyas la rim gro byas pa'i dge
NK127(jo)001:3164: rtsa dang rgyu mthun pas shing gi gseb thams cad
NK127(jo)001:3165: nas rgyan mang po 'byung ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:3166: 'jig rten gyi dbang po thams cad kyis btud de mchod pa'i sprin gyi char 'bebs pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:3167: phyogs bcu'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi 'od
NK127(jo)001:3168: zer gyi d+r+wa ba'i dkyil 'khor mang po bkye bas
NK127(jo)001:3169: sangs rgyas kyi chos thams cad sgrogs shing spyi bor
NK127(jo)001:3171: de dag la sogs pa 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur
NK127(jo)001:3172: pa lam du zhugs pa'i yon tan gyi rgyan tshad
NK127(jo)001:3173: med pa dag / tshe dang ldan pa sh+aa ri'i
NK127(jo)001:3174: bus dge slong de dag la yongs su bstan cing
NK127(jo)001:3175: dkrol te gsal bar byas so //
NK127(jo)001:3176: de ltar 'jam dpal gyi yon tan ci tsam du
NK127(jo)001:3177: brjod pa de tsam du dge slong de dag sems
NK127(jo)001:3178: rnam par dag cing dngas la skyon dang bral zhing
NK127(jo)001:3179: / sgrib pa thams cad phyir mi ldog pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:3180: sangs rgyas dang chos la sems mos shing gzhol ba
NK127(jo)001:3181: dang byang chub sems dpa'i dbang po yongs su dag
NK127(jo)001:3182: ste dad pa dang snying rje'i shugs 'phel zhing pha
NK127(jo)001:3183: rol du phyin pa'i dkyil 'khor gnon pa dang phyogs
NK127(jo)001:3184: bcu'i sangs rgyas rgya mtsho yongs su snang bar gyur
NK127(jo)001:3185: to // de ltar de dag thams cad mkhyen pa
NK127(jo)001:3186: nyid du mos pa'i shugs thob pas 'di ltar 'dzin
NK127(jo)001:3187: to // te / mkhan po bdag cag skyes bu
NK127(jo)001:3188: dam pa de'i drung du phyin par mdzad du gsol
NK127(jo)001:3189: to // te / / de nas sh+aa ri'i bus
NK127(jo)001:3190: dge slong de dag dang 'grogs te 'jam dpal ga
NK127(jo)001:3191: na bar song nas 'di skad smras so //
NK127(jo)001:3192: 'jam dpal dge slong 'di dag ni khyod la lta bar 'dod pa dag go //
NK127(jo)001:3193: de nas 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pas dge slong
NK127(jo)001:3194: de dag dang 'khor gyi dkyil 'khor gyi sa'i phyogs
NK127(jo)001:3195: de tsam dang bcas par glang po'i lta stangs kyi
NK127(jo)001:3196: gzi dang ldan par khyab par bltas pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:3197: de'i rjes la dge slong de dag gis 'jam dpal
NK127(jo)001:3198: gyi rkang pa gnyis la spyi bos phyag 'tshal nas
NK127(jo)001:3199: thal mo sbyar te 'di skad ces smras so //
NK127(jo)001:3200: skyes bu dam pa khyod mthong ba dang khyod la
NK127(jo)001:3201: phyag 'tshal ba'i dge rtsa 'di dang dge rtsa gzhan
NK127(jo)001:3203: mkhan po'i thugs su chud pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:3204: gang yang de bzhin gshegs pa sh+aakya thub pas mngon
NK127(jo)001:3205: du gzigs pa'i dge rtsa des khyod ji 'dra ba
NK127(jo)001:3207: rnam pa 'di 'dra'i lus dang dbyangs dang mtshan dang
NK127(jo)001:3208: rnam par 'phrul pa dag kyang thob par shog cig
NK127(jo)001:3210: 'jam dpal gyis de dag la smras pa /
NK127(jo)001:3211: dge slong dag yongs su mi skyo ba'i sems bskyed
NK127(jo)001:3212: pa bcu dang ldan pa'i rigs kyi bu'am bu mo
NK127(jo)001:3213: theg pa chen po la zhugs pas ni byang chub
NK127(jo)001:3214: sems dpa'i sa lta ci smos kyi de bzhin gshegs
NK127(jo)001:3215: pa'i sa yang gnon par 'gyur ro //
NK127(jo)001:3217: de bzhin gshegs pa blta ba dang mchod pa sogs
NK127(jo)001:3218: la yongs su mi skyo ba'i sems bskyed pa dang
NK127(jo)001:3219: / de bzhin du dge rtsa bsags pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:3221: byang sems kyi phar phyin la sbyor ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:3223: dus thams cad du 'jug pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:3224: zhing rgya mtsho dag par bya ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:3225: sems can thams cad yongs su smin pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:3226: zhing dang bskal pa thams cad du byang chub sems dpa'i spyod pa mngon par sgrub pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:3227: zhing thams cad kyi rdul phran snyed kyi phar phyin
NK127(jo)001:3228: sbyar bas sems can gcig smin par bya ba'i tshul
NK127(jo)001:3229: du sems can thams cad yongs su smin par bya
NK127(jo)001:3230: bas de bzhin gshegs pa'i stobs gcig yongs su bsgrub
NK127(jo)001:3231: pa la mi skyo ba ste /
NK127(jo)001:3232: 'di bcu dang ldan pas dge rtsa thams cad yongs su 'grub cing /
NK127(jo)001:3233: 'khor ba'i rgyud thams cad las gyen du 'phags nas nyan rang gis thams cad las 'da' zhing /
NK127(jo)001:3234: de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs dang rgyud du 'byung la /
NK127(jo)001:3235: byang chub sems dpa'i spyod pa yongs su dag pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:3236: de bzhin gshegs pa'i stobs la 'jug cing bdud dang phas rgol 'dul ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:3237: byang chub sems dpa'i sa gnon cing de bzhin gshegs
NK127(jo)001:3238: pa'i sa dang shin tu nye bar 'gyur ro zhes
NK127(jo)001:3239: gsungs pas / dge slong de dag gis de thos
NK127(jo)001:3240: nas sangs rgyas thams cad mthong ba la chags pa
NK127(jo)001:3241: med pa'i mig gi yul zhes bya ba'i ting nge
NK127(jo)001:3243: de'i mthus phyogs bcu mtha' yas mu med pa'i zhing gi de bzhin gshegs pa mthong ngo //
NK127(jo)001:3244: zhing der skyes pa'i sems can ma lus pa dang
NK127(jo)001:3245: de dag gi sdug bsngal shin tu phra ba'i bar
NK127(jo)001:3247: de bzhin gshegs pa de dag gi dbyangs kyi yan
NK127(jo)001:3248: lag rgya mtsho dang chos bstan pa'i tshig dang yi
NK127(jo)001:3250: sems can de dag gi sems dang dbang po bsam pa la rnam par lta bar gyur /
NK127(jo)001:3251: sngon dang phyi matha'i tshe rabs bcu dran pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:3252: de bzhin gshegs pa de dag gi chos 'khor bcu'i nges tshig sgrub pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:3253: rdzu 'phrul gyi rnam 'phrul sgrub pa bcu dang /
NK127(jo)001:3254: bstan pa'i tshul mngon par sgrub pa bcu dang /
NK127(jo)001:3255: rjes su bstan pa'i tshig mngon par sgrub pa bcu dang /
NK127(jo)001:3256: so so yang dag rig pa'i tshul sgrub pa bcu la rab tu zhugs par gyur to //
NK127(jo)001:3257: ting nge 'dzin de thob ma thag tu byang chub sems kyi yan lag stong phrag bcu dang /
NK127(jo)001:3258: ting nge 'dzin stong phrag bcu rdzogs te pha rol
NK127(jo)001:3259: tu phyin pa'i yan lag stong phrag bcu yang rnam
NK127(jo)001:3260: par dag go // snang ba chen po shes rab
NK127(jo)001:3261: kyi dkyil 'khor gyi snang ba de dag gi mthus
NK127(jo)001:3262: byang chub sems dpa'i mngon par shes pa bcu thob
NK127(jo)001:3263: par dag go // bo // de ltar mngon shes
NK127(jo)001:3264: kyi myu gu gzhon zhing phra ba thob ste byang
NK127(jo)001:3265: chub tu sems bskyed pa brtan pa de dag /'jam
NK127(jo)001:3266: dpal gyis kun tu bzang po'i spyod pa la 'god
NK127(jo)001:3267: pas smon lam chen po rgya mtsho la zhugs shing
NK127(jo)001:3268: mngon par sgrub par gyur to //
NK127(jo)001:3269: de'i stobs kyis sems rnam par dag cing lus yongs su dag pa dang yang ba thob la /
NK127(jo)001:3270: des mngon par shes pa'i sgo yangs shing mi nyams
NK127(jo)001:3271: par rjes su 'brang ba thob pas 'jam dpal gyi
NK127(jo)001:3272: zhabs drung nas kyang mi g.yo la /
NK127(jo)001:3273: sangs rgyas kyi chos thams cad sgrub pa'i phyir phyogs
NK127(jo)001:3274: bcur yang de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku'i
NK127(jo)001:3275: phrin las kyi sprin mngon par sgrub par gyur to
NK127(jo)001:3276: // de nas 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pas dge
NK127(jo)001:3277: slong de dag bla med rdzogs pa'i byang chub la
NK127(jo)001:3278: bkod nas mthar gyis yul rgyu zhing lho phyogs logs
NK127(jo)001:3279: su skyid pa'i 'byung gnas zhes bya ba'i grong rdal
NK127(jo)001:3281: de'i shar phyogs su nags tshal chen po shing s+aa
NK127(jo)001:3282: la sna tshogs kyi rgyal mtshan gyi rgyan zhes bya
NK127(jo)001:3283: ba der de bzhin gshegs pa'i mchod rten gyi drung
NK127(jo)001:3284: du lha klu gnod sbyin la sogs pa rtag par
NK127(jo)001:3285: 'du ba der / mdo sde chos kyi dbyings kyi
NK127(jo)001:3286: tshul rab tu snang ba zhes bya ba mdo sde
NK127(jo)001:3287: bye ba khrag khrig brgya stong phrag bcu 'byung ba
NK127(jo)001:3288: 'du ba der / bstan to // chos de thos
NK127(jo)001:3289: nas rgya mtsho chen po nas klu bye ba khrag
NK127(jo)001:3290: khrig brgya stong du ma de bzhin gshegs pa la
NK127(jo)001:3291: mos par gyur nas klu'i rgyud las bzlog ste lha
NK127(jo)001:3292: dang mir skye ba yongs su 'dzin par gyur nas
NK127(jo)001:3293: 'du ba der / bstan to // / der klu
NK127(jo)001:3294: stong phrag bcu bla med byang chub las phyir mi
NK127(jo)001:3296: chos de bstan pas sems can gyi khams mtha' dang
NK127(jo)001:3297: dbus med pas theg pa gsum gyis dus gzhan dang
NK127(jo)001:3298: gzhan du rnam par dul bar gyur to //
NK127(jo)001:3299: de nas grong skyid pa'i 'byung gnas kyi mi rnams
NK127(jo)001:3300: kyis 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa s+aa la sna
NK127(jo)001:3301: tshogs kyi rgyan gyi gzhi der rnam par spyod do
NK127(jo)001:3302: zhes thos nas / dge bsnyen tshong dpon shes rab chen po /
NK127(jo)001:3303: dge bsnyen bzang pos byin la sogs pa dge bsnyen lnga brgyas bskor ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:3304: dge bsnyen ma shes rab chen mo /
NK127(jo)001:3305: dge bsnyen ma 'od bzang mo sogs dge bsnyen ma lnga brgyas bskor ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:3306: tshong dpon gyi bu nor bzangs tshong dpon gyi bu
NK127(jo)001:3307: brtul zhugs bzang po sogs tshong dpon gyi bu lnga
NK127(jo)001:3309: khyim bdag shes rab chen po'i bu mo dge ba
NK127(jo)001:3310: bzang mo ni bu mo bzang mo la sogs pa
NK127(jo)001:3311: bu mo lnga brgyas bskor te /
NK127(jo)001:3312: de thams cad kyis 'jam dpal gyi zhabs la phyag
NK127(jo)001:3313: 'tshal nas lan gsum bskor ba byas te phyogs gcig
NK127(jo)001:3314: 'khod do // de nas 'jam dpal gyis 'khor de
NK127(jo)001:3315: zil gyis mnan te byams pas tshem par byas nas
NK127(jo)001:3316: snying rjes chos bstan pa sgrub cing ye shes kyi
NK127(jo)001:3317: sems dang bsam pa phye nas so so yang dag
NK127(jo)001:3318: par rig pa chen pos chos bstan par dga' ste
NK127(jo)001:3319: tshong dpon gyi bu nor bzangs la bltas so //
NK127(jo)001:3320: de ltar sngon gyi rgyal ba la bya ba byas
NK127(jo)001:3321: shing dge rtsa bskyed pa mos pa rgya chen po
NK127(jo)001:3322: sogs yon tan mchog dang ldan pa'i tshong dpon gyi
NK127(jo)001:3323: bu nor bzangs la bltas te dga' ba'i gtam byas
NK127(jo)001:3324: nas / sangs rgyas kyi chos thams cad dang /
NK127(jo)001:3325: chos thams cad bsdu zhing thob par bya ba sogs
NK127(jo)001:3326: las brtsams te chos bstan pas nor bzangs dang skye
NK127(jo)001:3327: bo'i tshogs chen po de dag bla med byang chub
NK127(jo)001:3328: tu sems bskyed du bcug ste sngon gyi dge rtsa
NK127(jo)001:3329: dran par byas nas dong ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:3330: tshong dpon gyi bu nor bzangs kyis rgyal ba'i yon
NK127(jo)001:3331: tan dang che ba thos pas rdzogs pa'i byang chub
NK127(jo)001:3332: tu mos shing brtson pas 'jam dpal gyi phyi bzhin
NK127(jo)001:3333: 'brangs te tshigs su bcad pa'i bstod pa'i sgo nas
NK127(jo)001:3334: byang chub sems dpa'i spyod pa zhus pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:3335: 'jam dpal gyis 'di skad ces smras so //
NK127(jo)001:3336: rigs kyi bu de ltar khyod bla med byang chub
NK127(jo)001:3337: tu sems bskyed de dge ba'i bshes gnyen gyi rjes
NK127(jo)001:3338: su 'brangs shing byang chub sems dpa'i lam yongs su
NK127(jo)001:3339: rdzogs par bya bar 'dod pas byang chub sems dpa'i
NK127(jo)001:3340: spyod pa 'di bar bsam pa legs so legs so
NK127(jo)001:3341: // rigs kyi bu dge ba'i bshes gnyen la bsten
NK127(jo)001:3342: cing 'dri ba ni thams cad mkhyen par grub pa'i
NK127(jo)001:3343: gzhi yin gyis khyod dge ba'i bshes gnyen la bsnyen
NK127(jo)001:3344: bkur bas yongs su mi skyo bar gyis shig /
NK127(jo)001:3346: ji ltar byang chub sems dpa'i spyod pa la bslab par bgyi /
NK127(jo)001:3347: ji ltar nan tan du bgyi ba sogs zhus pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:3348: 'jam dpal gyis legs so'i basngagasa pa dang bcas te
NK127(jo)001:3349: dge ba'i bshes gnyen 'tshol zhing bstan par gdams nas
NK127(jo)001:3350: / lho phyogs kyi rgyud 'di nyid na yul mi mo gya noms mchog ces bya bar /
NK127(jo)001:3351: mgul legs pa zhes bya ba'i ri la dge slong
NK127(jo)001:3352: sprin gyi dpal zhes pa 'dug gi de'i drung du
NK127(jo)001:3353: song la byang chub sems dpa'i spyod pa la ji
NK127(jo)001:3355: des khyod la kun tu bzang po'i spyod pa'i dkyil 'khor ston to zhes lung bstan pa byas so //
NK127(jo)001:3356: de nas tshong dpon gyi bu nor bzangs des 'jam
NK127(jo)001:3357: dpal gyis bstan pa bzhin du dge slong sprin gyi
NK127(jo)001:3358: dpal la sogs pa byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyi
NK127(jo)001:3359: drung du skyo ba med par byang chub sems dpa'i
NK127(jo)001:3361: byang chub sems dpa' chen po'i rnam par 'phrul pa
NK127(jo)001:3362: 'gro ba kun na dkon zhing ngo mtshar ba rnams
NK127(jo)001:3363: mthong nas / snga ma snga mas lung bstan pa
NK127(jo)001:3364: ltar dge ba'i bshes gnyen de rnams gyi drung du
NK127(jo)001:3365: brgyud mar song bas byang chub sems dpa' de dag
NK127(jo)001:3366: gis kyang bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i rnam thar gyi
NK127(jo)001:3367: sgo so so tha dad pas smin par byas shing
NK127(jo)001:3368: byin gyis brlabs par byas pas /
NK127(jo)001:3369: byang chub sems dpa' gzhan gyis bskal pa khrag khrig
NK127(jo)001:3370: bye bar byang chub sems dpa' rnams dang 'grogs par
NK127(jo)001:3371: gyur kyang spyod yul de lta bu mi shes pa'i
NK127(jo)001:3372: yon tan gyi rnam pa rgya che ba de lta
NK127(jo)001:3373: bu thob nas mthar khye'u dpal 'byung dang bu mo
NK127(jo)001:3374: dpal gyi blo gros mas lung bstan pa ltar byang
NK127(jo)001:3375: chub sems dpa' byams pa'i drung du song ba dang
NK127(jo)001:3376: / des byang chub sems kyi basngagasa pa brjod cing
NK127(jo)001:3377: khang pa brtsegs pa las sangs rgyas dang byang chub
NK127(jo)001:3378: sems dpa'i rnam par thar ba rgya mtsho bstan te
NK127(jo)001:3379: byin gyis brlabs pas gzungs dang ting nge 'dzin la
NK127(jo)001:3380: sogs pa yon tan gyi khyad par rgya che ba
NK127(jo)001:3382: byams pa'i zhal nas rigs kyi bu da dung du'ang
NK127(jo)001:3383: 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa'i gan du song la
NK127(jo)001:3384: byang chub sems dpas ji ltar bslab par bya ba
NK127(jo)001:3385: sogs dris shig dang dge ba'i bshes gnyen des khyod
NK127(jo)001:3387: de ci'i phyir zhe na 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur
NK127(jo)001:3388: pa'i spyod pa mngon par sgrub pa de lta bu'i
NK127(jo)001:3389: smon lam gyi khyad par ni byang chub sems dpa'
NK127(jo)001:3390: bye ba khrag khrig brgya phrag stong la yang med
NK127(jo)001:3391: do // de'i smon lam mngon par sgrub pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:3392: byang chub sems dpa'i yon tan gyi khyad par thams cad mngon par sgrub pa ni tshad med do //
NK127(jo)001:3393: 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa de ni sangs rgyas
NK127(jo)001:3394: bye ba khrag khrig brgya phrag stong gi yum lta
NK127(jo)001:3395: bu'o // byang chub sems dpa' bye ba khrag khrig brgya phrag stong la gdams ngag ston pa'o //
NK127(jo)001:3396: sems can gyi khams thams cad yongs su smin par
NK127(jo)001:3397: bya ba dang 'dul ba la rab tu brtson pa'o
NK127(jo)001:3398: // phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten gyi khams su ming gi 'khor los rnam par rgyal bar gyur ba'o //
NK127(jo)001:3399: de bzhin gshegs pa'i 'khor gyi dkyil 'khor thams cad du gtam gyi skyes bur gyur pa'o //
NK127(jo)001:3400: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis basngagasa shing bstod pa'o //
NK127(jo)001:3401: chos thams cad yang dag pa ji lta ba bzhin
NK127(jo)001:3402: du mthong ba'i zab mo'i ye shes la rnam par
NK127(jo)001:3403: spyod pa'o // rnam par thar pa'i tshul thams cad
NK127(jo)001:3404: la ring du song ba'i spyod yul dang ldan pa
NK127(jo)001:3405: ste byang chub sems dpa'i spyod pa kun tu bzang
NK127(jo)001:3407: rigs kyi bu dge ba'i bshes gnyen de ni khyod de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs su skyed pa'o //
NK127(jo)001:3408: dge ba'i rtsa ba thams cad yongs su 'phel ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:3409: byang chub sems dpa'i tshogs mang po rab tu sgrub pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:3410: yang dag pa'i dge ba'i bshes gnyen sten pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:3411: yon tan thams cad la yang dag par skul bar byed pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:3412: smon lam chen po'i d+r+wa ba thams cad du 'jug pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:3413: smon lam mngon par sgrub pa thams cad la rab tu gzhog pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:3414: byang chub sems dpa' thams cad kyi gsar pa thos pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:3415: byang chub sems dpa'i bsam gyis mi khyab pa thams cad yang dag par ston par byed pa ste /
NK127(jo)001:3416: sngon gyi tshe'i gnas su bskal pa mthun par spyod pa'o //
NK127(jo)001:3417: rigs kyi bu de bas na khyod da ltar yang 'jam dpal gyi rkang pa'i drung na 'dug gis /
NK127(jo)001:3418: yon tan gyi gdams ngag thams cad thob par bya
NK127(jo)001:3419: ba la yongs su skyo ba dang sgyid lug par
NK127(jo)001:3420: ma byed cig / de ci'i phyir zhe na /
NK127(jo)001:3421: nor bzangs khyod kyis dag pa'i bshes gnyen ji snyed cig mthong ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:3422: spyod pa'i khyad par ji snyed cig thos pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:3423: rnam par thar ba'i tshul ji snyed cig la zhugs pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:3424: smon lam gyi khyad par ji snyed cig khong du
NK127(jo)001:3425: chud pa de thams cad kyang 'jam dpal gzhon nur
NK127(jo)001:3426: gyur pa'i mthu dang byin gyi rlabs su blta ste
NK127(jo)001:3427: / 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa ni thams cad
NK127(jo)001:3428: la yang pha rol tu phyin pa'i mchog thob pa'o
NK127(jo)001:3429: / // zhes gsungs pas tshong dpon gyi bu nor
NK127(jo)001:3430: bzangs kyis byams pa'i zhabs la spyi bos phyag 'tshal
NK127(jo)001:3431: zhing lan brgya stong du mar bskor nas yang dang
NK127(jo)001:3432: yang lta zhing de'i drung nas dong ste /
NK127(jo)001:3433: grong khyer brgya rtsa bcu kun tu rgyus nas phyogs
NK127(jo)001:3434: kyi gnas yid bde ba mngon du 'byung ba zhes
NK127(jo)001:3435: bya ba zhig na 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa
NK127(jo)001:3436: la sems shing phrad par dga' bas sdod cing 'dug
NK127(jo)001:3437: pa la / 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pas dpag
NK127(jo)001:3438: tshad brgya rtsa bcu'i pha rol nas phyag brkyangs te
NK127(jo)001:3439: tshong dpon gyi bu nor bzangs de na 'dug pa'i
NK127(jo)001:3441: rigs kyi bu legs so legs so //
NK127(jo)001:3442: dad pa'i dbang po dang mi ldan pa sems skyo
NK127(jo)001:3443: ba bsam pa zhum pa brtson 'grus ldog pa yon
NK127(jo)001:3444: tan cung zad kyis chog par rtsi ba /
NK127(jo)001:3445: dge rtsa gcig la zhen pa thabs mi mkhas pa
NK127(jo)001:3446: dge ba'i bshes gnyen gyis ma zin pa sangs rgyas
NK127(jo)001:3447: kyis ma dgongs pa rnams kyis chos nyid 'di lta
NK127(jo)001:3448: bu yongs su shes pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:3449: spyod yul 'di lta bu'i gnas 'di 'dra khong du
NK127(jo)001:3450: chud pa'am yid ches pa'am thob par bya mi nus
NK127(jo)001:3451: so zhes de la chos kyi gtam yang dag par
NK127(jo)001:3452: bstan pa dang gzengs bstod pa dang dga' bar byas
NK127(jo)001:3453: te / chos kyi sgo grangs med pa dang ldan
NK127(jo)001:3454: pa dang ye shes mtha' yas pa'i snang ba chen
NK127(jo)001:3456: byang chub sems dpa'i gzungs dang ting nge 'dzin dang
NK127(jo)001:3457: spobs pa dang mngon par shes pa dang ye shes
NK127(jo)001:3458: mtha' yas pas byin gyis brlabs par byas te kun
NK127(jo)001:3459: tu bzang po'i spyod pa'i dkyil 'khor la bzhag /
NK127(jo)001:3460: bdag gi yul la'ang rab tu bzhag nas tshong dpon gyi bu nor bzangs kyi drung nas gshegs so //
NK127(jo)001:3461: de nas tshong dpon gyi bu nor bu bzang pos
NK127(jo)001:3462: de bzhin gshegs pa rnam par snang mdzad kyi drung
NK127(jo)001:3463: na bzhugs pa'i byang chub sems dpa' kun tu bzang
NK127(jo)001:3464: po'i yongs su dag pa'i sku'i cha shas gcig la'ang
NK127(jo)001:3465: chos kyi dbyings kyis klas pa'i rnam thar rgya mtsho
NK127(jo)001:3466: bsam gyis mi khyab pa mthong zhing /
NK127(jo)001:3467: de'i byin gyi rlabs kyis de dag la mnyam pa nyid du 'jug pa'i spyod yul thob pa'i tshe /
NK127(jo)001:3468: 'phags mchog kun tu bzang po nyid kyis bzang po'i
NK127(jo)001:3469: spyod pa'i tshul de lta bu la 'jug pa smon
NK127(jo)001:3470: lam gyi rnam par tshigs su bcad pa'i dbyangs kyis
NK127(jo)001:3471: brjod par mdzad pa las kyang /
NK127(jo)001:3472: 'jam dpal ji ltar mkhyen cing dpa' ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:3473: kun tu bzang po de yang de bzhin te /
NK127(jo)001:3474: de dag gi ni rjes su bdag slob cing //
NK127(jo)001:3475: dge ba 'di dag thams cad rab tu bsngo //
NK127(jo)001:3477: 'phags pa dkon mchog brtsegs pa'i chos kyi rnam grangs
NK127(jo)001:3478: sangs rgyas kyi yul bsam gyis mi khyab par bstan
NK127(jo)001:3479: pa'i mdo las / 'jam dpal gyis sangs rgyas kyi
NK127(jo)001:3480: yul dmigs su med pa mnyam pa nyid du bstan
NK127(jo)001:3481: pas sems can tshad med pa'i don byas so //
NK127(jo)001:3482: de nas lha'i bu dpal bzangs zhes bya bas /
NK127(jo)001:3483: 'jam dpal khyod rgyun du 'dzam bu'i gling na chos ston tam /
NK127(jo)001:3484: dga' ldan gyi gnas su bzhud nas der dga' ldan gyi lha'i ris rnams la chos gsung du gsol /
NK127(jo)001:3485: der lha'i bu sngon gyi rgyal ba la bya ba
NK127(jo)001:3486: byas pa dge ba'i rtsa ba bskyed pa dag yod
NK127(jo)001:3487: pa de dag yul phun sum tshogs pas bag med
NK127(jo)001:3488: pa'i dbang gis bcom ldan 'das dang khyod las chos
NK127(jo)001:3489: nyan pa las nyams par gyur pa de dag khyod
NK127(jo)001:3490: las chos thos nas dge ba'i rtsa ba 'phel bar
NK127(jo)001:3492: lha'i bu dpal bzangs dang thams cad dang ldan pa'i
NK127(jo)001:3493: 'khor des dga' ldan gyi gnas su zhugs par bdag
NK127(jo)001:3495: nyams dga' ba'i kun dga' ra ba dang khang bzang
NK127(jo)001:3496: sogs bkod pa'i khyad par rab tu mdzes pa de
NK127(jo)001:3498: de nas lha'i bu dpal bzang gis rang gi gnas rgyan gyis brgyan pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:3499: g.yog rnams kyang mthong nas ngo mtshar te 'jam dpal la smras pa /
NK127(jo)001:3500: 'di ltar myur du dga' ldan gyi gnas su phyin
NK127(jo)001:3501: te khang bzang dang kun dga' ra ba sogs dang
NK127(jo)001:3502: rang gi gnas g.yog dang bcas pa'i bar du snang
NK127(jo)001:3504: de nas tshe dang ldan pa rab 'byor gyis lha'i bu dpal bzang la smras pa /
NK127(jo)001:3505: lha'i bu khyod ni 'khor 'di las ma g.yos la dga' ldan gyi gnas su yang ma phyin te /
NK127(jo)001:3506: 'on kyang thams cad dang ldan pa'i 'khor 'di dga'
NK127(jo)001:3507: ldan gyi gnas su zhugs par bdag nyid kyis shes
NK127(jo)001:3508: pa 'di ni 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa'i rdzu
NK127(jo)001:3509: 'phrul dang byin gyi rlabs kyi stobs so //
NK127(jo)001:3510: de nas lha'i bu dpal bzang gis bcom ldan 'das la gsol ba /
NK127(jo)001:3511: bcom ldan 'das 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa'i rdzu
NK127(jo)001:3512: 'phrul gyi stobs dang ting nge 'dzin gyi byin gyi
NK127(jo)001:3513: rlabs kyi stobs 'di ni bsam gyis mi khyab ste
NK127(jo)001:3514: / 'khor 'di dag gis phyogs 'di nas ma g.yos
NK127(jo)001:3515: par bdag cag dga' ldan gyi gnas su phyin to
NK127(jo)001:3516: snyam pa ni ngo mtshar to //
NK127(jo)001:3518: lha'i bu 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa'i rdzu 'phrul
NK127(jo)001:3519: rnam par 'phrul pa ji snyed cig ngas shes pa
NK127(jo)001:3520: las khyod kyis ji tsam zhig shes te /
NK127(jo)001:3521: lha'i bu 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pas 'dod na
NK127(jo)001:3522: sangs rgyas kyi zhing gang+g+aa'i bye ma snyed kyi yon
NK127(jo)001:3523: tan bkod pa gang yod pa de thams cad zhing
NK127(jo)001:3524: gcig tu yang dag par ston to //
NK127(jo)001:3525: zhing gang+g+aa'i klung gi bye ma snyed de dag gtsug
NK127(jo)001:3526: phud kyis phug ste steng gi bar snang la 'jog
NK127(jo)001:3527: go // zhing de dag na rgya mtsho chen por
NK127(jo)001:3528: gyur pa'i chu'i phung po ji snyed pa thams cad
NK127(jo)001:3529: ba spu'i khung bu gcig tu blugs kyang sems can
NK127(jo)001:3530: rnams la gnod pa med de /
NK127(jo)001:3531: thams cad kyang rang rang gi rgya mtsho chen po na gnas par bdag nyid kyis shes so //
NK127(jo)001:3532: zhing de dag na ri'i rgyal po ri rab gang
NK127(jo)001:3533: dag yod pa thams cad ri gcig tu byin gyis
NK127(jo)001:3534: brlabs te / ri de yungs kar gyi 'bru'i nang
NK127(jo)001:3535: du btsud kyang ri rab la gnas pa'i lha de
NK127(jo)001:3536: dag la yang gnod pa med de thams cad rang
NK127(jo)001:3537: gi gnas na 'khod par shes so //
NK127(jo)001:3538: zhing de dag na 'gro ba lngar skyes pa'i sems
NK127(jo)001:3539: can gang dag yod pa thams cad lag pa'i mthil
NK127(jo)001:3540: du bzhag ste / 'jig rten gyi khams bde ba
NK127(jo)001:3541: thams cad kyis rab tu brgyan pa'i sems can rnams
NK127(jo)001:3542: kyi bde bar spyad pa ci 'dra ba de lta
NK127(jo)001:3543: bu de dag la sgrub bo //
NK127(jo)001:3544: zhing gang+g+aa'i bye ma snyed sreg par byed pa'i me
NK127(jo)001:3545: de thams cad mar me snying po gcig gi me
NK127(jo)001:3546: lce tsam gyi mer byin gyis brlabs te des bya
NK127(jo)001:3547: ba byed pa gang yin pa de byed do //
NK127(jo)001:3548: sangs rgyas kyi zhing gang+g+aa'i klung gi bye ma snyed
NK127(jo)001:3549: dag na nyi ma dang zla ba'i 'od gang yod
NK127(jo)001:3550: pa de dag thams cad ba spu'i khung bu gcig
NK127(jo)001:3551: gi 'od kyis zil du brlag par byed do //
NK127(jo)001:3552: lha'i bu 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa'i rdzu 'phrul
NK127(jo)001:3553: rnam par 'phrul pa'i cho 'phrul las brtsams nas nga
NK127(jo)001:3554: bskal pa'am bskal pa las lhag par yang chos ston
NK127(jo)001:3555: te / 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa ni rdzu
NK127(jo)001:3556: 'phrul dang byin gyi rlabs kyi stobs bsam gyis mi
NK127(jo)001:3557: khyab pa 'di lta bu dang ldan no zhes bka'
NK127(jo)001:3558: te / stsal to // de nas bdud sdig can
NK127(jo)001:3559: 'khor der 'dus par gyur nas 'dug pas bdag nyid
NK127(jo)001:3560: dge slong gi gzugs su bsgyur nas bcom ldan 'das
NK127(jo)001:3561: te / stsal to // la gsol pa / bcom
NK127(jo)001:3562: ldan 'das 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa'i rdzu 'phrul
NK127(jo)001:3563: rnam par 'phrul ba'i cho 'phrul de bdag gis blta
NK127(jo)001:3564: te / stsal to // la gsol pa / bar
NK127(jo)001:3565: bagyi'o // bcom ldan 'das kyis tshig tsam du gsungs
NK127(jo)001:3566: pas ci sman gyi bdag la mngon sum du gyur
NK127(jo)001:3567: te / stsal to // la gsol pa / bar
NK127(jo)001:3568: bagyi'o // cig / de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis
NK127(jo)001:3569: bdud sdig can du mkhyen bzhin sems can tshad med
NK127(jo)001:3570: pa'i dge ba'i rtsa ba rnam par spel ba'i phyir
NK127(jo)001:3572: 'jam dpal khyod la ngas bskul gyi khyod kyis 'khor
NK127(jo)001:3573: 'di dag la rang gi rdzu 'phrul gyi stobs dang
NK127(jo)001:3574: cho 'phrul ston cig dang sems can tshad med pa'i
NK127(jo)001:3576: de nas 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pas bcom ldan
NK127(jo)001:3577: 'das kyis bskul par shes nas chos thams cad sems
NK127(jo)001:3578: kyis dbang sgyur ba rnam par 'phrul pa zhes bya
NK127(jo)001:3579: ba'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs so //
NK127(jo)001:3580: snyoms par zhugs ma thag tu thams cad dang ldan
NK127(jo)001:3581: pa'i 'khor des 'jam dpal gyi rdzu 'phrul gyi cho
NK127(jo)001:3582: 'phrul bcom ldan 'das kyis ji ltar gsungs pa de
NK127(jo)001:3583: bzhin du chad lhag med par mthong nas ngo mtshar
NK127(jo)001:3584: du gyur te / sangs rgyas byung ba legs so legs so //
NK127(jo)001:3585: sangs rgyas byung ba ni sems can rnams la don chen por nye bar gnas so //
NK127(jo)001:3586: de byung bas skyes bu dam pa 'di lta bu dag kyang 'jig rten du byung ba yin no //
NK127(jo)001:3587: cho 'phrul bsam gyis mi khyab pa 'di lta bu
NK127(jo)001:3588: yang 'jig rten na snang ba yin no zhes ched
NK127(jo)001:3589: du brjod pa ched du brjod do //
NK127(jo)001:3590: de nas bdud sdig can gyis cho 'phrul chen po
NK127(jo)001:3591: de mthong bas ngo mtshar du gyur nas thal mo
NK127(jo)001:3592: sbyar te 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa la phyag
NK127(jo)001:3594: 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa'i rdzu 'phrul gyi cho 'phrul bsam gyis mi khyab pa ngo mtshar to //
NK127(jo)001:3595: sems can gang dag cho 'phrul bshad pa 'di thos
NK127(jo)001:3596: nas mos pa de dag ngo mtshar che bar bdag
NK127(jo)001:3597: gis bsams so // bcom ldan 'das gal te bdud
NK127(jo)001:3598: sdig can gang+g+aa'i klung gi bye ma snyed du gyur
NK127(jo)001:3599: kyang de ltar mos pa'i sems can de dag la
NK127(jo)001:3600: bar chad bgyi ba'i rngo mi thogs lags so //
NK127(jo)001:3601: bcom ldan 'das bdud sdig can bdag ni rtag tu
NK127(jo)001:3602: rgyun ma 'chad par de bzhin gshegs pa la glags
NK127(jo)001:3603: lta zhing skabs tshol pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:3604: sems can thams cad la gtse bar sems pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:3605: brtson pa'i gang zag rnams kyi dge ba'i bar chad bgyi ba'i slad du zhugs pa lags te /
NK127(jo)001:3606: de slan chad gang na chos kyi rnam grangs 'di
NK127(jo)001:3607: spyod pa de'i khor yug dpag tshad brgya tshun chad
NK127(jo)001:3608: du mig gis rtsol bar bgyi ba'i slad du bdag
NK127(jo)001:3609: mi mchi bar yi dam blang bar bagyi'o //
NK127(jo)001:3610: gang dag 'chang cing 'chang ba sogs la ston pa la bgyi ba ltar gus pa bskyed par bagyi'o //
NK127(jo)001:3611: 'on kyang bdag gi 'khor gang dag de bzhin gshegs pa'i bstan pa'i bar chad bgyi ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:3612: brtson pa rnam g.yengs par bgyi pa'i slad du zhugs
NK127(jo)001:3613: pa dag chad pas gcod pa'i slad du gsang sngags
NK127(jo)001:3614: kyi tshig 'di zhes smras te phul bar byas pa
NK127(jo)001:3615: la / bcom ldan 'das kyis legs so zhes bya ba gnang nas /
NK127(jo)001:3616: 'dir khyod kyi gsang sngags kyi tshig bstan pas 'jig
NK127(jo)001:3617: rten gyi khams gang+g+aa'i klung gi bye ma snyed rnam
NK127(jo)001:3619: khyod kyi spobs pa de thams cad ni 'jam dpal
NK127(jo)001:3620: gzhon nur gyur pa'i byin gyi rlabs su rig par
NK127(jo)001:3622: de nas lha'i bu dpal bzangs dang lhan cig tu
NK127(jo)001:3623: 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa byang chub sems dpa'
NK127(jo)001:3624: dang nyan thos la sogs pa'i 'khor dang bcas te
NK127(jo)001:3625: dga' ldan gyi gnas su gshegs pa na /
NK127(jo)001:3626: rgyal chen bzhi'i lha rnams nas 'og min pa'i bar gyi lha rnams der 'dus pa la /
NK127(jo)001:3627: 'jam dpal gyis chos bstan pas sems can tshad med pa'i don mdzad do //
NK127(jo)001:3628: de nas lha'i bu dpal bzang gis zhus pa ltar
NK127(jo)001:3629: 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa dri ma med pa'i
NK127(jo)001:3630: 'od ces bya ba'i ting nge 'dzin la zhugs nas
NK127(jo)001:3631: steng gi phyogs su sangs rgyas kyi zhing gang+g+aa'i klung
NK127(jo)001:3632: bcu gnyis kyi bye ma snyed 'das pa na 'jig
NK127(jo)001:3633: rten gyi khams yon tan thams cad kyi 'od ces
NK127(jo)001:3634: bya bar de bzhin gshegs pa kun tu bzang po
NK127(jo)001:3635: zhes bya ba bzhugs pa'i bar gyi zhing thams cad
NK127(jo)001:3637: de'i rgyu mtshan 'khor gyis zhus pa na tshul de
NK127(jo)001:3638: lta bu de bzhin gshegs pa kun tu bzang pos
NK127(jo)001:3639: lung bstan pas zhing de'i byang chub sems dpa' rnams
NK127(jo)001:3640: kyis mi mjed 'di dang sh+aakya thub pa dang 'jam
NK127(jo)001:3641: dpal gzhon nur gyur pa de blta bar 'tshal zhes
NK127(jo)001:3642: zhus pas / de bzhin gshegs pa kun tu bzang
NK127(jo)001:3643: po'i zhabs mthil gyi 'od btang bas zhing 'di khyab
NK127(jo)001:3644: zhus pas / nas / mi mjed 'di dang zhing
NK127(jo)001:3645: de'i byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyis zhing de dag
NK127(jo)001:3646: phan tshun mthong bar gyur to //
NK127(jo)001:3647: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa kun tu bzang pos
NK127(jo)001:3648: byang chub sems dpa' de dag la rigs kyi bu
NK127(jo)001:3649: dag mi mjed der chos kyi gtam chen po 'byung
NK127(jo)001:3650: bar 'gyur bas na khyed las su 'gro bar spro
NK127(jo)001:3652: byang chub sems dpa' chen po ye shes sgron ma
NK127(jo)001:3653: 'dzin zhes bya ba byang chub sems dpa' bye ba
NK127(jo)001:3654: phrag bcus bskor nas skyes bu'i lag pa brkyang bskum
NK127(jo)001:3655: gyi tshod tsam la 'jam dpal gyi drung du phyin
NK127(jo)001:3657: de bzhin gshegs pa kun tu bzang pos 'dir btang
NK127(jo)001:3658: ngo zhes smras pas 'khor de dag gis byang chub
NK127(jo)001:3659: sems dpa'i rdzu 'phrul la ngo mtshar nas ched du
NK127(jo)001:3661: de nas 'jam dpal gyis 'khor chen po 'dus pa de la chos bstan nas /
NK127(jo)001:3662: sems kyi 'gyu ba tsam du dga' ldan nas mi
NK127(jo)001:3663: snang bar gyur te byang chub sems dpa' ye shes
NK127(jo)001:3664: sgron ma 'dzin 'khor dang bcas pa dang lhan cig
NK127(jo)001:3665: tu bcom ldan 'das kyi spyan sngar phyin te phyag
NK127(jo)001:3666: 'tshal nas rang rang gi stan la 'khod do //
NK127(jo)001:3667: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis 'khor de dag la bka' stsal pa /
NK127(jo)001:3668: grogs po dag skyes bu dam pa 'di dag dang 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:3669: byang chub sems dpa' ye shes sgron ma 'dzin gyi
NK127(jo)001:3670: rnam 'phrul dang byin rlabs dang sems can smin par
NK127(jo)001:3671: byed pa dang / thabs dang rig pa dang ye shes dang spobs pa la ltos /
NK127(jo)001:3672: grogs po dag byang chub sems dpa' 'di dag ni
NK127(jo)001:3673: bskal pa grangs med pa nas bzung ste sangs rgyas
NK127(jo)001:3674: kyi mdzad pas sems can rnams la nye bar gnas
NK127(jo)001:3675: pa dag go // sems can gang dag gi dbang
NK127(jo)001:3676: po drug po dag la skyes bu dam pa 'di
NK127(jo)001:3677: dag mngon par gyur pa de dag ni phyis bdud
NK127(jo)001:3678: kyi yul la gnas par mi 'gyur ro zhes brjod
NK127(jo)001:3679: pa dag go // par bya'o // zhes gsungs so //
NK127(jo)001:3680: dkon mchog brtsegs pa'i chos kyi dbyings dbyer med par bstan pa las /
NK127(jo)001:3681: 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pas chos thams cad chos
NK127(jo)001:3682: kyi dbyings kyi rang bzhin kun byang dang bcing grol
NK127(jo)001:3683: med pa'i don zab mo bstan pa la /
NK127(jo)001:3684: 'khor de nas dge slong nyis brgyas su yang grol
NK127(jo)001:3685: ba med na 'u bu cag gi rab tu byung
NK127(jo)001:3686: ba dang lam la brtson pa don ci yod ces
NK127(jo)001:3687: yi chad nas 'khor de nas phyir don de song
NK127(jo)001:3688: ba'i lam du 'jam dpal gyis dge slong zhig sprul
NK127(jo)001:3689: te de dag la smras pa /
NK127(jo)001:3690: kho bo 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pas chos bstan
NK127(jo)001:3691: pa la ma mos yid ma ches nas dong ngo
NK127(jo)001:3692: zhes smras pas / de dag gis kho bo cag kyang de ltar gyur pa smras pa na /
NK127(jo)001:3693: sprul pa'i dge slong des smras pa /
NK127(jo)001:3694: ci khyed cag ma mos nas dong bar zad dam /
NK127(jo)001:3695: 'on te spangs shing mi snyan par brjod nas dong /
NK127(jo)001:3697: kho bo cag ni ma mos nas dong bar zad kyi /
NK127(jo)001:3698: spangs pa dang mi snyan par brjod pa yang med do //
NK127(jo)001:3699: sprul pa'i dge slong des smras pa /
NK127(jo)001:3700: tshe dang ldan pa dag rtsod pa med pa ni
NK127(jo)001:3701: dge sbyong gi chos kyi mchog yin pas mi snyan
NK127(jo)001:3703: brtsod par mi bya'i re zhig je 'gro bar bya'o //
NK127(jo)001:3705: ci sems 'di sngon po zhig gam /
NK127(jo)001:3706: de bzhin du ser po sogs dang /
NK127(jo)001:3707: yang dag pa dang yang dag min pa /
NK127(jo)001:3708: rtag mi rtag gzugs can gzugs can min pa zhig gam zhes rtogs shig /
NK127(jo)001:3709: sems ni gzugs can min pa /
NK127(jo)001:3714: rnam par rig byed ma yin pa'o //
NK127(jo)001:3715: de lta bu'i sems de nang na gnas so zhes bya ba'am /
NK127(jo)001:3717: gnyis ka'i bar na gnas so zhes dmigs su yod dam /
NK127(jo)001:3718: dge slong de dag gis smras pa /
NK127(jo)001:3720: 'o na de lta bu la yang dag par yongs su grub pa yod dam /
NK127(jo)001:3724: gang yang dag pa ma yin zhing yongs su grub
NK127(jo)001:3725: pa ma yin pa de la rnam par grol ba
NK127(jo)001:3726: yod snyam mam / de dag gis smras pa /
NK127(jo)001:3728: sprul pa'i dge slong gis smras pa /
NK127(jo)001:3729: tshe dang ldan pa dag 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur
NK127(jo)001:3730: pas chos kyi dbyings kyi rang bzhin la kun nyon
NK127(jo)001:3731: dang rnam byang med pa'i tshul ni de la bsams
NK127(jo)001:3732: nas bstan te / byis pa so so'i skye bo
NK127(jo)001:3733: phyin ci log gis bslad pa rnams la nga dang
NK127(jo)001:3734: nga yir 'dzin pa 'byung zhing de la gnas nas
NK127(jo)001:3736: sems des rab tu byung ba dang lam sgom par dmigs kyang /
NK127(jo)001:3737: de lta bu'i sems de ni rang bzhin gyis med la skye 'jig gnas gsum dang bral ba ste /
NK127(jo)001:3738: de la ni kun byang dang thob pa dang mngon
NK127(jo)001:3739: par rtogs pa med pas de la bsams nas 'jam
NK127(jo)001:3740: dpal gzhon nur gyur pas de ltar bshad do zhes
NK127(jo)001:3741: smras pa / dge slong nyis brgya po de dag
NK127(jo)001:3742: len pa med par zag pa rnams las sems rnam
NK127(jo)001:3743: smras pa / par grol lo // de nas de
NK127(jo)001:3744: dag 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa ga la ba
NK127(jo)001:3745: der dong ste phyin pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:3746: rang rang gi bla gos 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa la mngon par bkab nas /
NK127(jo)001:3747: 'jam dpal khyod kyis kho bo rnams yongs su bskyabs so //
NK127(jo)001:3748: 'di ltar kho bo cag kyang dam pa'i chos spang
NK127(jo)001:3749: bar ma zhugs pas da phyin chad chos 'dul ba
NK127(jo)001:3750: zab mo la 'jug pa las phyi rol tu gyur
NK127(jo)001:3752: de nas gnas brtan rab 'byor gyis dge slong de dag la smras pa /
NK127(jo)001:3753: tshe dang ldan pa dag gis ci zhig thob cing
NK127(jo)001:3754: ci zhig mngon par rtogs na rang rang gi bla
NK127(jo)001:3755: gos 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa la dgab /
NK127(jo)001:3757: btsun pa rab 'byor kho bo cag gis ni ci
NK127(jo)001:3758: yang thob pa med cing mngon par rtogs pa med
NK127(jo)001:3759: pas / de'i phyir kho bo cag gis rang rang
NK127(jo)001:3760: gi bla gos 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur ba la
NK127(jo)001:3761: pas / bkab bo // btsun pa rab 'byor gang
NK127(jo)001:3762: gi tshe kho bo cag thob pa'i 'du shes yod
NK127(jo)001:3763: par gyur pa de'i tshe kho bo cag stan las
NK127(jo)001:3764: langs te 'khor de nas dong ngo //
NK127(jo)001:3765: kho bo cag thob pa'i 'du shes de dang bral bar gyur pa de'i tshe sar lhags so //
NK127(jo)001:3766: thob pa zhes bya ba de ni g.yo ba rlom
NK127(jo)001:3767: sems yin te de la thob pa dang mngon par
NK127(jo)001:3772: thob pa med pa dang skye ba med pa dang
NK127(jo)001:3773: sems g.yeng ba dang mnyam par bzhag pa med pa
NK127(jo)001:3774: des btul lo // smras pa ci khyed cag btul ba yin nam /
NK127(jo)001:3776: 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa la dris shig /
NK127(jo)001:3777: de nas kun dga' bos 'jam dpal la dge slong de dag sus btul dris pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:3778: don dam par sus kyang btul ba med pa dang
NK127(jo)001:3779: tha snyad du sgyu ma lta bu'i sprul pas btul
NK127(jo)001:3780: bar bstan to // de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis lha'i bu rin chen mchog lung bstan pa na /
NK127(jo)001:3781: de'i sgras bdud kyi gnas bskyod cing sgra de lta
NK127(jo)001:3782: bur byung bas sdig can dpung dang bcas pa bcom
NK127(jo)001:3784: stong gsum gyi sems can thams cad dgra bcom pa nyid du lung bstan kyang bdag yi rangs kyi /
NK127(jo)001:3785: byang chub sems dpa' gcig cig lung bstan kyang de lta ma yin te /
NK127(jo)001:3786: de'i tshe bdag gi gnas spa bkong zhing byang chub
NK127(jo)001:3787: sems dpa' des sems can grangs med pa byang chub
NK127(jo)001:3788: gsum la bzhag pas khams gsum nas nges par 'byin
NK127(jo)001:3789: pa'i phyir bdag yid la gcags pa chen por 'gyur
NK127(jo)001:3793: ma 'ongs kyang rung ste lhag bsam gyis zhugs shing
NK127(jo)001:3794: thabs mkhas pa dang ldan pa shes rab kyi pha
NK127(jo)001:3795: rol tu phyin pas nges par byung ba'i byang chub
NK127(jo)001:3796: sems dpa' la bar chad bya mi nus so //
NK127(jo)001:3798: sangs rgyas kyi mthus bdud sdig can gyis 'jam dpal
NK127(jo)001:3799: la lhag pa'i bsam pa dang thabs mkhas dang shes
NK127(jo)001:3800: rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa dris shing lan
NK127(jo)001:3802: de nas lha'i bu rin chen mchog gis chos 'dzin
NK127(jo)001:3803: pa rnams la bar chad bya ba'i bdud sdig can
NK127(jo)001:3804: 'di dpung dang bzhon pa gnas dang bcas par rang
NK127(jo)001:3805: gi lto ba'i nang du bcug go zhes 'jam dpal
NK127(jo)001:3808: de ni byang chub sems dpa'i cha ma yin gyi /
NK127(jo)001:3809: kho bos bdud sdig can 'di sangs rgyas kyi gzugs
NK127(jo)001:3810: mtshan gyis brgyan pas seng ge'i khri la 'dug nas
NK127(jo)001:3811: sangs rgyas kyi spobs pas chos ston par 'gyur ba
NK127(jo)001:3812: de ltar byin gyis brlab par bya'o zhes smras pa'i
NK127(jo)001:3813: tshig de bdud kyis thos pas gnas de nas mi
NK127(jo)001:3814: snang bar 'bros par 'dod kyang ma nus nas /
NK127(jo)001:3815: bdud sangs rgyas kyi gzugs kyis seng ge'i khri la 'dug par 'khor de dag gis mthong ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:3816: 'jam dpal gyis bdud sdig can la smras pa /
NK127(jo)001:3817: sdig can khyod ni de bzhin gshegs pa rnams kyi
NK127(jo)001:3818: byang chub thob ste khyod ni sangs rgyas kyi gzugs
NK127(jo)001:3819: kyis seng ge'i khri la 'dug go zhes smras pa
NK127(jo)001:3820: dang / 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa'i byin gyi
NK127(jo)001:3821: rlabs kyis bdud sdig can gyis 'di skad ces smras
NK127(jo)001:3822: dang / so // 'jam dpal bcom ldan 'das nyid
NK127(jo)001:3823: kyis kyang byang chub ma brnyes na kho bos lta
NK127(jo)001:3826: byang chub ni 'thob pa'i 'dod chags dang bral ba'i mtshan nyid yin pas na /
NK127(jo)001:3827: 'dod chags dang bral ba la ni 'thob pa yang med /
NK127(jo)001:3828: mngon par rtogs pa yang med de /
NK127(jo)001:3829: byang chub ni 'dus ma byas pa thob pa yin la /
NK127(jo)001:3830: de yang thob pa med pa nyid kyi mtshan nyid yin pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:3831: de bzhin du rnam thar sgo gsum gyi rang bzhin dang /
NK127(jo)001:3835: bdag med pa'i ngo bo nyid yin pas de la
NK127(jo)001:3836: mngon par rdzogs par 'tshang rgya ba gang yang med
NK127(jo)001:3837: pa dang / de thob nas chos thams cad ngo
NK127(jo)001:3838: bo nyid kyi mtshan nyid 'khrugs par mi byed pa
NK127(jo)001:3839: de ni sangs rgyas nyid yin par brjod par bya'o
NK127(jo)001:3840: pa dang / zhes / bdud kyis bstan pa 'di
NK127(jo)001:3841: bshad pas byang chub sems dpa' lnga brgyas mi skye
NK127(jo)001:3842: ba'i chos la bzod pa thob par gyur to //
NK127(jo)001:3843: de nas sh+aa ri'i bus 'jam dpal khyod kyi byin
NK127(jo)001:3844: gyi rlabs kyis bdud sdig can de bzhin gshegs pa'i
NK127(jo)001:3845: gzugs kyis zab mo'i gnas 'di lta bu ston pa
NK127(jo)001:3846: ngo mtshar ro // 'jam dpal gyis smras pa /
NK127(jo)001:3847: sh+aa ri'i bu kho bos sems med pa'i dngos po
NK127(jo)001:3848: shing la sogs pa'ang de ltar byin gyis rlob par
NK127(jo)001:3849: 'gyur la / kho bos gnas brtan sh+aa ri'i bu
NK127(jo)001:3850: nyid la'ang de ltar byin gyis brlabs nas de ltar
NK127(jo)001:3852: sh+aa ri'i bu 'di snyam du bdag kyang 'jam dpal
NK127(jo)001:3853: gyis de ltar byin gyis rlob par byas na nyan
NK127(jo)001:3854: thos ston pa'i gzugs su gnas pa mi mthun pa
NK127(jo)001:3855: yin pas bdag 'khor 'di nas mi snang bar bya
NK127(jo)001:3856: snyam yang 'jam dpal gyi mthus de ltar bya ma
NK127(jo)001:3857: nus pa'i sems 'jam dpal gyis shes nas /
NK127(jo)001:3858: sh+aa ri'i bu sangs rgyas kyi gzugs kyis seng ge'i
NK127(jo)001:3859: khri la 'dug pa 'khor kun gyis mthong bar byin
NK127(jo)001:3860: gyis brlabs so // de nas 'jam dpal gyis sh+aa ri'i bu la smras pa /
NK127(jo)001:3861: btsun pa sh+aa ra dwa ti'i bu ji ltar de
NK127(jo)001:3862: bzhin gshegs pas chos ston par mdzad pa de bzhin
NK127(jo)001:3863: du bdud sdig can dang lhan cig tu chos ston
NK127(jo)001:3864: cig / de nas sh+aa ri'i bu sangs rgyas kyi
NK127(jo)001:3865: gzugs su gnas pas bdud sdig can sangs rgyas kyi
NK127(jo)001:3866: gzugs su gnas pa la smras pa /
NK127(jo)001:3867: sdig can de bzhin gshegs pa rnams kyi byang chub ci zhig gis rab tu phye ba yin /
NK127(jo)001:3869: btsun pa sh+aa ra dwa ti'i bu bcom ldan 'das
NK127(jo)001:3870: rnams kyi byang chub ni chos thams cad mnyam pa
NK127(jo)001:3871: nyid du rtogs pas rab tu phye ba yin no
NK127(jo)001:3872: // zhes sogs bstan cing slar sha ri'i bu la smras pa /
NK127(jo)001:3873: sh+aa ri'i bu de bzhin gshegs pas ci zhig la gnas pa yin /
NK127(jo)001:3875: sdig can de bzhin gshegs pa ni 'khor ba mnyam pa nyid la gnas pa yin no //
NK127(jo)001:3876: zhes sogs bstan pas dge slong brgyad brgya len pa
NK127(jo)001:3877: med par zag pa rnams las sems rnam par grol
NK127(jo)001:3878: lo // sh+aa ri'i bu la dad pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:3879: bdud kyi ris la dad pa'i lha'i bu rnams las
NK127(jo)001:3880: srog chags sum khri nyis stong gis bla med rdzogs
NK127(jo)001:3881: pa'i byang chub tu sems bskyed do //
NK127(jo)001:3882: de ltar lha'i bu de dag 'dul ba'i phyir 'jam
NK127(jo)001:3883: dpal gzhon nur gyur pas bdud sdig can dang gnas
NK127(jo)001:3884: brtan sh+aa ri'i bu gnyis sangs rgyas kyi gzugs dang
NK127(jo)001:3885: sku'i mtshan gyis brgyan nas chos ston pa de ltar
NK127(jo)001:3886: byin gyis brlabs pa'i byin rlabs de slar bsdus pas
NK127(jo)001:3887: rang rang gi gzugs dang ldan par gyur to //
NK127(jo)001:3888: de nas sangs rgyas kyi zhing tha dad pa nas
NK127(jo)001:3889: byang chub sems dpa' stong phrag mang po dag 'dus
NK127(jo)001:3890: pa thams cad 'jam dpal gyis chos kyi dbyings kyi
NK127(jo)001:3891: rang bzhin dbyer med par bstan pa'i chos kyi rnam
NK127(jo)001:3892: grangs 'dis yongs su smin par byas pa dag gis
NK127(jo)001:3893: chos 'di 'dzin cing 'das pa'i 'og tu chos kyi
NK127(jo)001:3894: rnam grangs 'di 'dzam bu'i gling du rgyas par byed
NK127(jo)001:3895: par 'gyur ro zhes bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal
NK127(jo)001:3896: to // dkon mchog brtsegs pa'i cho 'phrul chen po bstan pa'i chos kyi rnam grangs las /
NK127(jo)001:3897: sngon 'das pa'i dus bskal pa ches grangs med pa'i
NK127(jo)001:3898: pha rol na bskal pa mngon par dga' ba zhes
NK127(jo)001:3899: bya ba la / de bzhin gshegs pa ri rab
NK127(jo)001:3900: lta bu zhes bya ba'i gsung rab la 'jam dpal
NK127(jo)001:3901: gzhon nur gyur pa 'di chos smra ba'i dge slong
NK127(jo)001:3902: chos kyi rgyal mtshan zhes bya bar gyur pas /
NK127(jo)001:3903: 'khor los sgyur ba'i rgyal po dge ba'i bkod pa
NK127(jo)001:3904: zhes bya ba gling bzhi'i dbang phyug chos kyi rgyal
NK127(jo)001:3905: po bu stong dang bcas pa la /
NK127(jo)001:3906: byang chub kyi ngo bo stong pa nyid dang rlom
NK127(jo)001:3907: sems med pa'i tshul byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyi
NK127(jo)001:3908: spyod pa zab mo bstan pas yid mchog tu dga'
NK127(jo)001:3909: nas gos dang rgyan thams cad kyis chos smra ba
NK127(jo)001:3911: des smras pa mchod pa de las khyad par du
NK127(jo)001:3912: 'phags pa ni byang chub tu sems bskyed pa dang
NK127(jo)001:3913: rgyal ba'i bstan pa la rab tu byung ba yin
NK127(jo)001:3915: rgyal po des 'dod pa'i dga' ba dang rgyal srid
NK127(jo)001:3916: kyi dbang phyug la mi lta bar de bzhin gshegs
NK127(jo)001:3917: pa ri rab lta bu la bdag legs par gsungs
NK127(jo)001:3918: pa'i chos 'dul ba la rab tu byung bar 'tshal
NK127(jo)001:3919: zhes zhus pa'i skabs phye ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:3920: rgyal pos bu stong po la smras pa /
NK127(jo)001:3921: khyed cag las rgyal srid bsgrub pa dang sems can
NK127(jo)001:3922: rnams la chos yang dag par 'dzin du 'jug par
NK127(jo)001:3924: de thams cad kyis smras pa /
NK127(jo)001:3925: yab bdag cag kyang rab tu 'byung bar gnang zhes smras pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:3926: de dag gi nang nas rgyal bu gzhon nu snying
NK127(jo)001:3927: rje cher sems zhes bya bas rgan rabs de dag
NK127(jo)001:3928: la tshigs su bcad de smras pa /
NK127(jo)001:3929: rab byung yon tan du ma bsags pa zhes //
NK127(jo)001:3930: de bzhin gshegs pa rnams kyis gsungs mod kyi //
NK127(jo)001:3931: de lta lags kyang snying rjer gyur pas na //
NK127(jo)001:3932: 'gro la phan phyir rgyal srid bdag gis bsgrub //
NK127(jo)001:3933: ji srid 'tsho bar bdag ni tshangs spyod cing //
NK127(jo)001:3934: gso sbyong yan lag brgyad pa blang bar bgyi //
NK127(jo)001:3935: me tog rnams dang dri dang byug pa dang //
NK127(jo)001:3936: de bzhin chang yang myang bar mi bagyi'o //
NK127(jo)001:3937: zhes sogs tshigs su bcad de rang don la ma
NK127(jo)001:3938: chags shing sems can yongs su smin par bgyi bar
NK127(jo)001:3939: zhus pa na / de bzhin gshegs pas legs so zhes bya ba byin te /
NK127(jo)001:3940: skyes bu dam pa legs so legs so bslab pa
NK127(jo)001:3941: brgyad kyi tshul khrims yang dag par blangs pa'i chos
NK127(jo)001:3942: kyi yon tan des na khyim par gyur pa'i byang
NK127(jo)001:3943: chub sems dpa' yang rab tu byung ba dang yon
NK127(jo)001:3945: khyod kyi snying rje chen po des na rab tu
NK127(jo)001:3946: byung ba'i yon tan ma lus pa yang sgrub par
NK127(jo)001:3948: zhes gsungs shing rgyal bu de rgyal srid la bzhag
NK127(jo)001:3949: nas bu stong du gcig gis ma tshangs pa dang
NK127(jo)001:3950: yab rgyal po dang bcas pa rab tu byung nas
NK127(jo)001:3951: / mngon shes lnga dang gzungs dang dran pa dang chos mnyan pa'i shes pa skyed par gyur to //
NK127(jo)001:3952: rgyal bu snying rje cher sems kyis zla ba nya
NK127(jo)001:3953: 'o cog tu gling bzhi po dag tu chos ston
NK127(jo)001:3954: par byas pas srog chags dung phyur dgu dang bye
NK127(jo)001:3955: ba phrag gnyis bla med byang chub tu sems bskyed
NK127(jo)001:3957: de thams cad de bzhin gshegs pa de'i bstan par
NK127(jo)001:3958: dad pas rab tu byung nas bla med byang chub
NK127(jo)001:3959: las mi ldog par gyur to //
NK127(jo)001:3960: de'i tshe 'khor los sgyur ba'i rgyal po dge ba'i
NK127(jo)001:3961: bkod pa ni da lta 'jam dpal gyis rjes su
NK127(jo)001:3962: bzung ba'i lha'i bu ded dpon 'di yin la /
NK127(jo)001:3963: bu stong ni bskal bzang 'di'i sangs rgyas stong yin cing /
NK127(jo)001:3964: rgyal bu gzhon nu snying rje cher sems ni ston pa sh+aakya'i rgyal po nyid yin par gsungs so //
NK127(jo)001:3965: de nas sh+aa ri'i bus smras pa /
NK127(jo)001:3966: 'jam dpal khyod ni lha'i bu ded dpon 'di dang
NK127(jo)001:3967: lhan cig yun ring po nas tshangs par sbyong pa
NK127(jo)001:3968: spyad pa dang / sangs rgyas mang po la bsnyen
NK127(jo)001:3969: bkur byas shing dge ba'i rtsa ba bskyed pa yin
NK127(jo)001:3970: spyad pa dang / no // 'jam dpal gyis smras pa /
NK127(jo)001:3971: sh+aa ri'i bu tshangs par spyod pa zhes bya ba 'phags lam brgyad kyi tshig bla dwags yin la /
NK127(jo)001:3972: lam ni 'dus byas yin gyi kho bo ni 'dus
NK127(jo)001:3973: ma byas su gtogs pa de'i phyir kho bo yun
NK127(jo)001:3974: ring po nas tshangs par spyod pa ma yin no
NK127(jo)001:3975: // de bzhin du tshangs par spyod pa ni spyod pa'i bdag nyid yin gyi /
NK127(jo)001:3976: kho bo ni spyod pa med pa yin pas tshangs par spyod pa ma yin no //
NK127(jo)001:3978: de bzhin gshegs pa ni gzugs med cing bstan du
NK127(jo)001:3979: med pa sogs phung po skye mched thams cad las
NK127(jo)001:3980: 'das pa / de bzhin nyid dang yang dag pa'i
NK127(jo)001:3981: mtha' dang chos kyi dbyings dang mnyam pa nyid dang
NK127(jo)001:3982: spros pa las 'das pa la sogs pa'i ngo bo
NK127(jo)001:3983: nyid yin pas bsnyen bkur bya bar mi nus pa
NK127(jo)001:3984: 'das pa / dang / yang dge ba'i rtsa ba
NK127(jo)001:3985: zhes pa kun nyon gyi phyogs thams cad dang rlom
NK127(jo)001:3986: pa'i lam thams cad dang nyan rang gi 'bras bu
NK127(jo)001:3987: 'dod pa'i rtsa ba ma yin pa dag ni dge
NK127(jo)001:3989: thams cad mkhyen pa nyid kyi sems mi 'dor ba
NK127(jo)001:3990: dang sems can smin par byed pa dang dam pa'i
NK127(jo)001:3992: phar phyin dang gzungs spobs rig pa stobs bcu la
NK127(jo)001:3993: sogs pa sgrub pa'i rtsa ba ni byang chub sems
NK127(jo)001:3994: dpa'i dge ba'i rtsa ba yin no zhes /
NK127(jo)001:3995: don gyi gzhi rnam par nges par bstan pa gsum
NK127(jo)001:3996: po 'di bshad pas thams cad dang ldan pa'i 'khor
NK127(jo)001:3997: des legs so zhes bya ba byin nas /
NK127(jo)001:3998: bcom ldan 'das dang 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa
NK127(jo)001:3999: la me tog sna tshogs kyis gtor nas 'di skad
NK127(jo)001:4000: du / sangs rgyas kyi zhing gang na 'jam dpal
NK127(jo)001:4001: gzhon nur gyur pa gnas pa der ni de bzhin
NK127(jo)001:4002: gshegs pa gnyis pa byung ba yin par rig par
NK127(jo)001:4003: du / bya'o // sems can gang dag 'jam dpal
NK127(jo)001:4004: gyis bstan pa 'di la mi skrag mi dngangs pa
NK127(jo)001:4005: de dag ni dge ba'i rtsa ba ngan ngon dang
NK127(jo)001:4007: de dag gis ni bdud kyi las thams cad bkag
NK127(jo)001:4008: pa dang theg pa chen po 'di la snang ba
NK127(jo)001:4009: thob pa yin no zhes kyang smras so //
NK127(jo)001:4010: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis 'khor de dag gis
NK127(jo)001:4011: smras pa la thugs rangs par mdzad nas lha'i bu
NK127(jo)001:4012: ded dpon la bka' stsal pa /
NK127(jo)001:4013: lha'i bu gang dag 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pas
NK127(jo)001:4014: bshad pa de thos nas mos par gyur pa de
NK127(jo)001:4015: yang cho 'phrul chen po yin te /
NK127(jo)001:4016: de dag ni de las gzhan pa'i cho 'phrul rnams kyis skrag par mi 'gyur ro //
NK127(jo)001:4017: de ci'i phyir zhe na lha'i bu 'di lta ste /
NK127(jo)001:4018: rtag par 'du shes pa'i sems can rnams la mi
NK127(jo)001:4019: rtag par bshad pa dang bde bar 'du shes pa
NK127(jo)001:4020: rnams la sdug bsngal bar bshad pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:4021: de bzhin du bdag tu 'du shes pa la bdag med dang /
NK127(jo)001:4022: sdug par 'du shes pa la mi sdug pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:4023: dngos por 'du shes pa la dngos med dang /
NK127(jo)001:4024: lta bar 'du shes pa la stong pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:4025: mtshan mar 'du shes pa la mtshan ma med pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:4026: khams gsum par 'du shes pa la smon pa med pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:4027: nga dang nga yir 'dzin pa 'du shes pa rnams
NK127(jo)001:4028: la lta ba'i rnam pa thams cad dang bral bar
NK127(jo)001:4029: bshad pa de ni 'jig rten gyi 'jigs pa chen
NK127(jo)001:4030: po yin te / gang dag de la mi skrag pa ni yang dag par dul ba yin pas /
NK127(jo)001:4031: yang dag par dul ba rnams ni gang la'ang skrag par mi 'gyur te /
NK127(jo)001:4032: de gang las skrag par 'gyur ba'i chos nga dang
NK127(jo)001:4033: nga yir 'dzin pas yongs su ma bzung bas rten
NK127(jo)001:4034: med la g.yo 'gul dang blang dor sogs med pas
NK127(jo)001:4035: phyin ci log med par yang dag par grub pas
NK127(jo)001:4036: lta ba dang ting nge 'dzin sogs sgrib pa med
NK127(jo)001:4037: pa mngon du gyur te sangs rgyas kyi chos thams
NK127(jo)001:4038: cad mngon du 'gyur ba'i bar du 'gyur ro //
NK127(jo)001:4039: gang byas pa med cing skye ba med pa'i chos
NK127(jo)001:4040: rnams la chos kyi go rim gyis mtshams sbyar ba
NK127(jo)001:4041: de ltar ston pa yang cho 'phrul chen po yin
NK127(jo)001:4043: de nas sh+aa ri'i bus 'jam dpal la 'di skad ces smras so //
NK127(jo)001:4044: kho bo cag 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa la
NK127(jo)001:4045: ci dang ci 'dri ba de dang de nyid kyi
NK127(jo)001:4046: tshig gi mtshams las sangs rgyas kyi chos thams cad
NK127(jo)001:4047: snang ngo // 'jam dpal gyis smras pa /
NK127(jo)001:4048: sh+aa ri'i bu chos thams cad ni bdag po med
NK127(jo)001:4049: pa mi zad pa ther zug tu mi gnas pa
NK127(jo)001:4050: sogs yin pas ji ltar 'dod pa bzhin du sgrub
NK127(jo)001:4051: cing ston la rnam par 'jog pa sogs su byed
NK127(jo)001:4052: do // chos de dag gang nas ma blangs /
NK127(jo)001:4054: de dag ni bsags pa dang spungs pa ma yin no //
NK127(jo)001:4055: de dag ni bshad kyang rung ma bshad kyang rung
NK127(jo)001:4056: ste chos kyi de bzhin nyid de mi 'dor ba
NK127(jo)001:4057: yin no // sems can thams cad dang sangs rgyas
NK127(jo)001:4058: thams cad kyi chos bstan pa'i yi ge 'byung ba
NK127(jo)001:4059: gang yin pa'i yi ge de thams cad lus dang
NK127(jo)001:4060: sems re re las ma byung ste /
NK127(jo)001:4061: rgyu rkyen las byung zhing yi ge rnams la bsags
NK127(jo)001:4062: pa med pa de bzhin du sems dang sems las
NK127(jo)001:4063: byung ba'i chos rnams la yang bsags pa med la
NK127(jo)001:4064: / de bzhin du nyon mongs pa'i dmigs pa dang
NK127(jo)001:4065: nyon mongs spangs pa'i ye shes la yang bsags pa
NK127(jo)001:4066: / med de / gang mi gnas pa'i shes pas
NK127(jo)001:4067: mi gnas pa'i nyon mongs rnams spangs pa de yang
NK127(jo)001:4070: de nas lha'i bu ded dpon dang 'jam dpal gzhon
NK127(jo)001:4071: nur gyur pa dag chos kyi gtam gleng bas sems
NK127(jo)001:4072: can mang po'i don byas so //
NK127(jo)001:4073: 'phags pa dkon mchog brtsegs pa'i chos kyi rnam grangs
NK127(jo)001:4074: su gyur pa lha'i bu blo gros rab gnas kyis
NK127(jo)001:4076: 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa rang gi gnas na
NK127(jo)001:4077: 'dug pa gcig pu dben par gyur cing nang du
NK127(jo)001:4078: yang dag par 'jog pa la zhugs pa /
NK127(jo)001:4079: nyon mongs pa med pa sems med cing sems dang
NK127(jo)001:4080: bral ba zhes bya ba'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms
NK127(jo)001:4081: par zhugs pa de las langs ma thag tu phyogs
NK127(jo)001:4082: bcu'i sangs rgyas kyi zhing dpag tu med pa rnam
NK127(jo)001:4084: de nas 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa 'di snyam du /
NK127(jo)001:4085: de bzhin gshegs pa ni 'jig rten du 'byung dka'
NK127(jo)001:4086: zhing de las chos mnyan pas sems can rnams kyi
NK127(jo)001:4087: sdug bsngal zad pa yin pas na /
NK127(jo)001:4088: bdag de bzhin gshegs pa'i spyan sngar song ste sems can rnams kyi dge rtsa 'grub pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:4089: byang chub sems dpa'i gang zag rnams sangs rgyas kyi
NK127(jo)001:4090: chos bsam gyis mi khyab pa la the tshom med
NK127(jo)001:4091: par byang chub yongs su rdzogs pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:4092: zhing 'di'i sems can rnams dug gsum che zhing blun
NK127(jo)001:4093: la ma gus pa mi dge'i chos dang ldan zhing
NK127(jo)001:4094: sangs rgyas dang chos dang dge 'dun dang bral ba
NK127(jo)001:4095: yin pas de dag gis chos thos nas shes rab
NK127(jo)001:4096: kyi mig rnam par dag par 'gyur ba de lta
NK127(jo)001:4097: bu'i zhu ba zhu snyam mo //
NK127(jo)001:4099: bdag gis phyogs bcu'i byang chub sems dpa' gang dag de bzhin gshegs pa las chos nyan pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:4100: zab mo'i bzod pa 'di la lus kyis mngon du
NK127(jo)001:4101: byed par 'gyur ba 'bum phrag mang po dag kyang
NK127(jo)001:4102: bsdu bar bya'o snyam du kun tu snang ba dri
NK127(jo)001:4103: ma med pa bkod pa zhes bya ba'i ting nge
NK127(jo)001:4105: de'i mod la phyogs bcu'i zhing gang+g+aa'i klung gi bye
NK127(jo)001:4106: ma snyed du mnyen pa 'jam pa dri ma med
NK127(jo)001:4107: pa 'od gsal ba'i snang ba chen pos khyab ste
NK127(jo)001:4108: / 'jig rten gyi bar gyi mun pa mun nag
NK127(jo)001:4109: dang ri dang khor yug ljon pa lhun po la
NK127(jo)001:4110: sogs pa thams cad snang ba des gsal bar gyur
NK127(jo)001:4111: / pa dang / phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten de dag
NK127(jo)001:4112: na 'tsho zhing gzhes pa'i sangs rgyas rnams la rang
NK127(jo)001:4113: rang gi bsnyen bkur ba dag gis zhus pa /
NK127(jo)001:4114: sngon chad nam yang ma mthong ba'i 'od yid du 'ong ba 'di'i rgyu rkyen gang lags /
NK127(jo)001:4115: 'od 'di'i bdag cag gi lus sems sim zhing sems
NK127(jo)001:4116: can rnams kyi 'dod chags dang zhe sdang dang gti
NK127(jo)001:4117: mug dag kyang kun tu mi 'byung lags na 'di
NK127(jo)001:4118: su'i mthu dang byin gyi rlabs lags zhes gsol ba
NK127(jo)001:4119: dang sangs rgyas de dag cang mi gsung bar gyur
NK127(jo)001:4120: to // sangs rgyas kyi mthus phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten
NK127(jo)001:4121: na lha klu gnod sbyin lha min mi dang bya
NK127(jo)001:4122: dang ri dwags la sogs pa'i sgra gang yod pa
NK127(jo)001:4124: de bzhin du chu dang rlung dang rgya mtsho chen
NK127(jo)001:4125: po dang rol mo dang glu dbyangs kyi sgra gang
NK127(jo)001:4126: yod pa thams cad kyang mi grag par 'ga' yang
NK127(jo)001:4127: skad mi 'byin cing zhi ba dang rab tu zhi
NK127(jo)001:4128: bar gyur to // yang sangs rgyas de dag la
NK127(jo)001:4129: bsnyen bkur ba dag gis lan gsum du 'od 'di
NK127(jo)001:4130: su'i mthu lags pa lha dang mi'i skye bo mang
NK127(jo)001:4131: po la phan pa dang bde ba'i don du bshad
NK127(jo)001:4132: du gsol zhes zhus pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:4133: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas de dag thams cad kyi gsung
NK127(jo)001:4134: dbyangs gcig tu bsdus nas gsung gi phrin las brjod
NK127(jo)001:4135: de / de bzhin gshegs pa gcig ji lta ba
NK127(jo)001:4136: gzhan yang de bzhin du gsung zhing de dag gi
NK127(jo)001:4137: gsung gi phrin las sgra dbyangs gcig tu bsdus pa
NK127(jo)001:4139: gsung des zhing thams cad du khyab ste lha mi'i
NK127(jo)001:4140: rol mo rnams kyang ma bkrol bar sgra 'byin cing
NK127(jo)001:4141: sgra de las kyang mi rtag sdug bsngal bdag med
NK127(jo)001:4142: stong pa dang de bzhin nyid dang pha rol tu
NK127(jo)001:4143: phyin pa la sogs pa chos sgo 'bum phrag du
NK127(jo)001:4144: ma dag gi sgra byung ba dag gis /
NK127(jo)001:4145: sems can bye ba khrag khrig 'bum phrag dpag tu
NK127(jo)001:4146: med pa grangs med pa dag theg pa gsum gyi
NK127(jo)001:4147: byang chub dang tshangs pa dang dbang po 'khor los
NK127(jo)001:4148: sgyur ba'i rgyal srid yongs su 'grub pa las phyir
NK127(jo)001:4150: de nas sangs rgyas de dag gis bsnyen bkur ba de dag la bka' stsal pa ni /
NK127(jo)001:4151: rigs kyi bu dag 'di lta bu'i gtam dris pas
NK127(jo)001:4152: khyed la ci bya thongs shig /'od 'di ni ji
NK127(jo)001:4153: tsam du bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i dge ba'i rtsa
NK127(jo)001:4154: ba dang sbyin pa la sogs pa'i tshogs kyis yongs
NK127(jo)001:4155: su sbyangs pa byas pa yin te 'di ni nyan
NK127(jo)001:4156: rang thams cad kyis ma yin no //
NK127(jo)001:4157: gal te de bzhin gshegs pa 'od 'di'i basngagasa pa
NK127(jo)001:4158: brjod na lha dang bcas pa'i 'jig rten thams cad
NK127(jo)001:4160: 'od 'di byams pa la sogs pas yongs su bsgos
NK127(jo)001:4161: pas tshim par byed pa ste 'od 'di'i basngagasa pa
NK127(jo)001:4162: brjod na bskal pa'am bskal pa las lhag par brjod
NK127(jo)001:4163: kyang mthar phyin par sla ba ma yin no //
NK127(jo)001:4164: de lta mod kyi legs par nyon dang bshad par bya'o //
NK127(jo)001:4165: bsnyen bkur bdag gis kyang lan gnyis lan gsum du bshad par slar yang gsol pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:4167: rigs kyi bu dag 'jig rten gyi khams mi mjed
NK127(jo)001:4168: ces bya ba na de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom
NK127(jo)001:4169: pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas sh+aakya thub
NK127(jo)001:4170: pa zhes bya ba rig pa dang zhabs su ldan
NK127(jo)001:4171: pa / bde bar gshegs pa 'jig rten mkhyen pa
NK127(jo)001:4172: skyes bu 'dul ba'i kha lo sgyur ba bla na
NK127(jo)001:4173: pa / med pa / lha dang mi rnams kyi
NK127(jo)001:4174: ston pa sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das bzhugs te 'tsho
NK127(jo)001:4175: pa / med pa / zhing gzhes la / snyigs
NK127(jo)001:4176: ma lnga dang ldan pa'i 'jig rten nyon mongs che
NK127(jo)001:4177: zhing dbang po rtul ba ngo tsha khrel yod dang
NK127(jo)001:4178: pa / med pa / zhing gzhes la / bral
NK127(jo)001:4179: ba / mi gus pa nyon mongs can gyi las
NK127(jo)001:4180: la spyod pa de lta bu'i sems can rnams kyi
NK127(jo)001:4181: nang du bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs
NK127(jo)001:4182: pa'i byang chub mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas te
NK127(jo)001:4183: pa / med pa / zhing gzhes la / bral
NK127(jo)001:4184: ba / chos ston to // rigs kyi bu dag
NK127(jo)001:4185: bcom ldan 'das de'i zhing na byang chub sems dpa'
NK127(jo)001:4186: 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa zhes bya ba mthu
NK127(jo)001:4187: che ba shes pa che ba brtson 'grus che ba
NK127(jo)001:4188: pa / med pa / zhing gzhes la / bral
NK127(jo)001:4189: ba / chos ston to // / byang chub sems
NK127(jo)001:4190: dpa' rnams la yang dag par ston par byed pa
NK127(jo)001:4191: pa / med pa / zhing gzhes la / bral
NK127(jo)001:4192: ba / chos ston to // / / yang dag
NK127(jo)001:4194: yang dag par gzengs bstod pa /
NK127(jo)001:4195: yang dag par rab tu dga' bar byed pa /
NK127(jo)001:4196: byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyi pha'i go 'byed pa /
NK127(jo)001:4198: chos thams cad kyi gzhi rab tu 'byed pa'i shes pa la mkhas pa /
NK127(jo)001:4199: chags pa med pa'i shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa thob pa /
NK127(jo)001:4200: thogs pa med pa'i spobs pa dang ldan pa /
NK127(jo)001:4202: byang chub sems dpa'i yon tan bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang ldan pa zhig 'dug pa de /
NK127(jo)001:4203: 'di ltar sems can rnams kyi dge rtsa grub pa
NK127(jo)001:4204: dang byang chub sems dpa' chos bsam gyis mi khyab
NK127(jo)001:4205: pa yongs su rdzogs pa'i phyir de bzhin gshegs pa
NK127(jo)001:4206: sh+aakya thub pa la chos kyi zhu ba zhus te
NK127(jo)001:4207: der nyan cing 'du bar 'gyur ba'i phyogs bcu'i byang
NK127(jo)001:4208: chub sems dpa' bsdu ba'i phyir 'od 'di bkye ste
NK127(jo)001:4209: / snang ba chen po'i rgyu dang rkyen ni de yin no zhes bka' stsal pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:4210: bsnyen bkur ba de dag gis zhus pa /
NK127(jo)001:4211: 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa ting nge 'dzin gang
NK127(jo)001:4212: la gnas nas 'od 'di lta bu bgyid pa lags
NK127(jo)001:4214: 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa de ni ting nge
NK127(jo)001:4215: 'dzin kun tu snang ba dri med bkod pa zhes
NK127(jo)001:4216: bya ba la gnas nas 'od 'di 'gyed do //
NK127(jo)001:4218: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams ni 'di ltar gsal
NK127(jo)001:4219: zhing rnam par dag la lus sems dga' zhing mchog
NK127(jo)001:4220: tu dga' bar byed pa'i 'od 'di lta bu ci'i
NK127(jo)001:4223: rigs kyi bu dag byang chub sems dpa' bsdu ba
NK127(jo)001:4224: dang byang chub sems dpa' bskul ba'i chos kyi rnam
NK127(jo)001:4225: grangs 'chad pa ni res 'ga' las rtag tu 'byung
NK127(jo)001:4226: ba ma yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK127(jo)001:4227: de nas phyogs bcu'i zhing dpag tu med pa dag
NK127(jo)001:4228: gi zhing re re nas byang chub sems dpa' dkrigs
NK127(jo)001:4229: phrag bye ba khrag khrig 'bum phrag grangs med dpag
NK127(jo)001:4230: med bsam gyis mi khyab pa dag gis sangs rgyas
NK127(jo)001:4233: su'i 'od lags zhes zhus pas snga ma ltar lung bstan pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:4234: byang chub sems dpa' de dag gis ci de bzhin
NK127(jo)001:4235: gshegs pa sh+aakya thub pa dang byang chub sems dpa'
NK127(jo)001:4236: 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa dang byang chub sems
NK127(jo)001:4237: dpa' gzhan yang blta ba'i phyir mi mjed der mchi'o
NK127(jo)001:4239: de bzhin gshegs pa de dag gis de'i dus la
NK127(jo)001:4240: bab par shes na dengs shig ces gsungs pas byang
NK127(jo)001:4241: chub sems dpa' de dag mi stobs po che'i lag
NK127(jo)001:4242: pa brkyang ba'am bskum pa tsam la rang rang gi
NK127(jo)001:4243: sangs rgyas kyi zhing nas mi snang bar mi mjed
NK127(jo)001:4245: de na byang chub sems dpa' la la dag me
NK127(jo)001:4246: tog gi char 'bebs shing de bzhin gshegs pa sh+aakya
NK127(jo)001:4247: thub pa ga la ba der lhags so //
NK127(jo)001:4248: de bzhin du phye ma dang byug pa dang me
NK127(jo)001:4249: tog phreng ba dang spos kyi char la sogs pa
NK127(jo)001:4251: la la ni sil snyan 'bum phrag du ma dag rab tu gsil ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:4252: la la ni de bzhin gshegs pa la bstod pa'i
NK127(jo)001:4253: sgra dbyangs re res kyang stong chen po'i 'jig rten
NK127(jo)001:4254: gyi khams thams cad du khyab par byed pa la
NK127(jo)001:4255: sogs pa bkod pa sna tshogs pa dag gis lhags
NK127(jo)001:4256: so // byang chub sems dpa' de dag zhing 'dir
NK127(jo)001:4257: mchis pa de'i mdo la stong chen po'i 'jig rten
NK127(jo)001:4258: gyi khams 'dir dmyal ba dang dud 'gro'i skye gnas
NK127(jo)001:4259: dang gshin rje'i 'jig rten gyi sems can gang ji
NK127(jo)001:4260: snyed yod pa de thams cad nye bar zhi bar
NK127(jo)001:4261: so // gyur to // sems can gang la yang
NK127(jo)001:4262: 'dod chags dang zhe sdang dang gti mug dang nga
NK127(jo)001:4263: rgyal sogs nyon mongs pas yongs su gdung ba med
NK127(jo)001:4264: so // gyur to // par / sems can thams
NK127(jo)001:4265: cad la byams pa'i sems dang mchog tu dga' ba'i
NK127(jo)001:4266: sems dang ldan par gyur to //
NK127(jo)001:4267: de nas byang chub sems dpa'i 'dus pa chen po
NK127(jo)001:4268: bsam gyis mi khyab pa de dag gis de bzhin
NK127(jo)001:4269: gshegs pa sh+aakya thub pa'i zhabs la mgo bos phyag
NK127(jo)001:4270: 'tshal te lan gsum bskor ba byas nas steng gi
NK127(jo)001:4271: bar snang la lus mi snang bar byas te /
NK127(jo)001:4272: lus thams cad rnam par 'jig pa zhes bya ba'i
NK127(jo)001:4273: ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs nas rang rang
NK127(jo)001:4274: gi smon lam las byung ba'i pad+ma kha dog sna
NK127(jo)001:4275: tshogs 'dab ma 'bum phrag du ma dang ldan pa'i
NK127(jo)001:4276: pad+ma'i snying po la skyil mo krung bcas te 'dug
NK127(jo)001:4277: par gyur to // de nas gnas brtan 'od srung
NK127(jo)001:4278: chen pos chos kyi cho 'phrul chen po ngo mtshar
NK127(jo)001:4279: rmad du byung ba de dang /
NK127(jo)001:4280: me tog dang spos dang phye ma'i char dang /
NK127(jo)001:4281: sil snyan 'bum phrag mang po'i sgra dang /
NK127(jo)001:4282: snang ba chen po de yang mthong /
NK127(jo)001:4283: gling bzhi pa'i 'jig rten gyi khams 'di me tog dag gis pus mo nub tsam khebs pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:4284: 'khor phal po che dang lha klu mi la sogs
NK127(jo)001:4285: pa dang dge slong dang dge bsnyen pha ma'i 'khor
NK127(jo)001:4286: thams cad lus gser gyi mdog tu snang ba dag
NK127(jo)001:4287: kyang mthong bas / stan las langs te chos gos
NK127(jo)001:4288: phrag pa gcig tu gzar nas pus mo g.yas pa'i
NK127(jo)001:4289: lha nga sa la btsugs te /
NK127(jo)001:4290: bcom ldan 'das ga la ba der logs su thal
NK127(jo)001:4291: mo sbyar bas btud cing tshigs su bcad pa'i dbyangs
NK127(jo)001:4292: kyis bstod nas / snang ba chen po dang ngo
NK127(jo)001:4293: mtshar rmad du byung ba'i mtshan ma rgya chen po
NK127(jo)001:4294: 'di lta bu gda' ba'i rgyu dang rkyen gang lags
NK127(jo)001:4296: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
NK127(jo)001:4297: 'od srung 'di lta bu'i gtam gyis khyod la ci
NK127(jo)001:4298: zhig bya thongs shig /'di ni nyan rang thams cad
NK127(jo)001:4300: gal te de bzhin gshegs pas gnas 'di bstan na
NK127(jo)001:4301: lha dang bcas pa'i 'jig rten 'di rmongs shing bslad
NK127(jo)001:4303: bcom ldan 'das skye bo mang po la sman pa dang bde ba'i slad du bshad du gsol /
NK127(jo)001:4305: 'od srung 'di na 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa
NK127(jo)001:4306: kun tu snang ba dri med bkod pa'i ting 'dzin
NK127(jo)001:4307: la zhugs nas 'od zer bkye bas /
NK127(jo)001:4308: phyogs bcu'i byang chub sems dpa' bkrigs phrag bye ba
NK127(jo)001:4309: khrag khrig 'bum phrag dpag tu med grangs med bsam
NK127(jo)001:4310: gyis mi khyab pa yang dag par bskul te mi
NK127(jo)001:4311: mjed 'dir lhags nas nga'i rkang pa la mgo bos
NK127(jo)001:4312: phyag 'tshal zhing lan gsum bskor ba byas nas steng
NK127(jo)001:4313: gi bar snang la ta la bdun srid tsam na
NK127(jo)001:4315: byang chub sems dpa' de dag gi mthus me tog gi char la sogs pa 'di byung ngo //
NK127(jo)001:4316: gsol ba bcom ldan 'das 'di na byang chub sems dpa' 'ga' yang mi gada'o //
NK127(jo)001:4318: 'od srung de dag ni nyan rang gis blta bar mi nus so //
NK127(jo)001:4319: de ci'i phyir zhe na nyan rang rnams ni byang
NK127(jo)001:4320: chub sems dpa' rnams snying rje chen po dang byams
NK127(jo)001:4321: pa dang phan par 'dod pa dang pha rol tu
NK127(jo)001:4322: phyin pa dang spyod pa gang la gnas pa de
NK127(jo)001:4323: la mi gnas shing lhag pa'i bsam pa de la
NK127(jo)001:4324: yang mi spyod pa'i phyir ro //
NK127(jo)001:4325: 'od srung byang chub sems dpa' de dag ni lus
NK127(jo)001:4326: thams cad rnam par 'jig pa shes bya ba'i ting
NK127(jo)001:4327: nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs pas /
NK127(jo)001:4328: de dag ni nyan rang gis lta bar mi nus
NK127(jo)001:4329: te de bzhin gshegs pa rnams kyi gzigs pa kho
NK127(jo)001:4330: nar zad do // rigs kyi bu de dag ni
NK127(jo)001:4331: 'di ltar sa la gnas pa'i byang chub sems dpa'
NK127(jo)001:4332: rnams dang theg pa la gsar du zhugs pas byang
