NK127(jo)001:4333: chub sems dpa' rnams kyis kyang re zhig mi mthong
NK127(jo)001:4334: na nyan rang rnams kyis mthong bar 'gyur ba lta
NK127(jo)001:4335: ci smos te de ni gnas med do //
NK127(jo)001:4336: de nas 'od srung chen pos ting nge 'dzin de thob pa'i rgyu zhus pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:4337: chos bcu dang ldan na ting nge 'dzin de thob
NK127(jo)001:4338: par 'gyur la nyan rang rnams kyis ting nge 'dzin
NK127(jo)001:4339: de la snyoms par 'jug mi nus te de'i ming
NK127(jo)001:4340: yang mi shes na snyoms par 'jug pa lta ci
NK127(jo)001:4342: de nas yang 'od srungs chen pos gsol pa /
NK127(jo)001:4343: bcom ldan 'das bdag gis byang chub sems dpa' de dag blta bar bgyi ste /
NK127(jo)001:4344: de ci'i slad du na skyes bu dam pa de dag mthong bar dka' ba'i slad du'o //
NK127(jo)001:4346: 'od srung 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa 'ongs kyi bar du khyod re shig sdod cig dang /
NK127(jo)001:4347: de nas byang chub sems dpa' de dag ting nge
NK127(jo)001:4348: 'dzin de las ldang zhing gdong mthong bar 'gyur ro
NK127(jo)001:4349: // 'od srung de lta mod kyi khyod ting nge
NK127(jo)001:4350: 'dzin rnams kyi gnas pa thob pa yin gyis byang
NK127(jo)001:4351: chub sems dpa' de dag spyod lam ji lta bus
NK127(jo)001:4353: de nas gnas brtan 'od srung chen pos bcom ldan 'das kyi ltar mnyan nas /
NK127(jo)001:4354: sangs rgyas kyi mthu dang rang gi stobs bskyed pas
NK127(jo)001:4355: ting nge 'dzin khri phrag gcig la snyoms par zhugs
NK127(jo)001:4356: shing langs kyang de dag ma mthong ste /
NK127(jo)001:4357: de dag gi 'gro 'ong dang gnas pa dang rab
NK127(jo)001:4358: tu gnas pa dang ci byed pa dang ci ston
NK127(jo)001:4359: pa dag kyang thams cad kyis thams cad du ma
NK127(jo)001:4360: shes ma mthong nas byang chub sems dpa' de dag
NK127(jo)001:4361: gi gnas la ngo mtshar zhing de las lhag pa'i
NK127(jo)001:4362: thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes la spro ba'i tshul
NK127(jo)001:4364: de nas gnas brtan sha ri'i bu 'di snyam du
NK127(jo)001:4365: bdag ni de bzhin gshegs pas shes rab can rnams
NK127(jo)001:4366: kyi mchog tu bstan pa yin gyis byang chub sems
NK127(jo)001:4367: dpa' de dag spyod lam ji lta bus gnas pa
NK127(jo)001:4368: brtag par bya snyam du ting nge 'dzin sum khri
NK127(jo)001:4369: la zhugs kyang de dag gi mtshan ma yang shes
NK127(jo)001:4371: de nas gnas brtan rab 'byor gyis byang chub sems
NK127(jo)001:4372: dpa' de dag blta ba'i phyir sangs rgyas kyi mthu
NK127(jo)001:4373: dang rang gi stobs bskyed pas ting nge 'dzin bzhi
NK127(jo)001:4374: khri la 'jug ldang byas kyang de dag gi spyod
NK127(jo)001:4375: lam blta bar ma nus nas bcom ldan 'das la
NK127(jo)001:4376: gsol pa / bcom ldan 'das bdag de bzhin gshegs
NK127(jo)001:4377: pas nyon mongs pa med pa la gnas pa rnams
NK127(jo)001:4378: kyi mchog tu bstan te bdag zhi ba'i ting 'dzin
NK127(jo)001:4379: thob pa lags pas gal te gling bzhi pa'i 'jig
NK127(jo)001:4380: rten gyi khams rnga bo che'i sbubs gcig tu gyur
NK127(jo)001:4381: pa de lta bu gnyis la /
NK127(jo)001:4382: ri rab tsam gyi rnga shing thogs te bdag zhi
NK127(jo)001:4383: ba'i ting 'dzin la gnas pa'i mdun du bskal pa'i
NK127(jo)001:4384: bar du rgyun mi 'chad par brdungs kyang /
NK127(jo)001:4385: bdag zhi ba'i ting 'dzin thob pa la re shig
NK127(jo)001:4386: bskal pa 'das par gnas pa'i rnga bo che de
NK127(jo)001:4387: gnyis kyi sgra bdag gi rna ba'i rnam par rig
NK127(jo)001:4388: pa tsam du'ang grags par mi 'gyur na ting 'dzin
NK127(jo)001:4389: de las slong ba lta smos kyang ci dgos te
NK127(jo)001:4390: gnas med na / bdag gnas pa de lta bu
NK127(jo)001:4391: dang ye shes de lta bu dang ldan pas ting
NK127(jo)001:4392: nge 'dzin bzhi khri la zhugs shing langs kyang de
NK127(jo)001:4393: dag gi gnas kyang ma 'tshal lags na /
NK127(jo)001:4394: gal te byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyi ye shes de lta bu yongs su tshol ba na /
NK127(jo)001:4395: sems can re re'i slad du bskal pa gang+g+aa'i klung
NK127(jo)001:4396: gi bye ma snyed du dmyal ba chen por bsregs
NK127(jo)001:4397: par gyur kyang spro bsdu bgyi zhing ye shes de
NK127(jo)001:4398: lta bu yongs su gtang bar mi bya'o //
NK127(jo)001:4399: bcom ldan 'das gal te bdag len pa med par
NK127(jo)001:4400: zag pa rnams las sems rnam par grol bar ma
NK127(jo)001:4401: gyur na bdag slad ma'i mur thug par 'khor bar
NK127(jo)001:4402: spyod cing de lta bu'i theg pa chen po yang
NK127(jo)001:4403: yongs su spong bar mi bgyid do //
NK127(jo)001:4404: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis gnas brtan rab 'byor la legs so zhes bya ba byin te /
NK127(jo)001:4405: rab 'byor khyod kyis lhag pa'i bsam pa de lta
NK127(jo)001:4406: bus tshig de gang smras pa legs so legs so
NK127(jo)001:4407: // rab 'byor khyod gal te phung po 'di nyid
NK127(jo)001:4408: kyis yongs su mya ngan las 'das par ma gyur
NK127(jo)001:4409: du zin na khyod dge ba'i rtsa ba 'dis 'khor
NK127(jo)001:4410: los sgyur ba'i rgyal srid gang+g+aa'i klung gi bye ma
NK127(jo)001:4411: snyed du 'jug cing bla med rdzogs pa'i byang chub
NK127(jo)001:4413: rab 'byor stong chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khams kyi sems can mang ba yin nam /
NK127(jo)001:4417: rab 'byor yongs su brtag pa'i phyir gal te sems
NK127(jo)001:4418: can de dag thams cad dge slong rab 'byor dang
NK127(jo)001:4419: sh+aa ri'i bu dang 'od srung chen po ji 'dra
NK127(jo)001:4420: ba de lta bu'i shes pa dang ldan par gyur
NK127(jo)001:4421: la / de dag gis bskal pa bye ba khrag
NK127(jo)001:4422: khrig 'bum phrag du mar byang chub sems dpa' de
NK127(jo)001:4423: dag brtags kyang mthong bar mi nus so //
NK127(jo)001:4425: nyan rang rnams ni byang chub sems dpa' gang la
NK127(jo)001:4426: spyod pa'i chos de dag la mi spyod pa'i phyir
NK127(jo)001:4427: nyan rang gi gnas ma yin no //
NK127(jo)001:4428: zhes gsungs pas lha mi'i skye dgu rnams las srog
NK127(jo)001:4429: chags brgyad khri bzhi stong bla med byang chub tu
NK127(jo)001:4430: sems skyes so // de nas 'jam dpal gzhon nur
NK127(jo)001:4431: gyur pas byang chub sems dpa' mang po 'di dag
NK127(jo)001:4432: sems skyes so // 'dus kyis / bdag gis lha
NK127(jo)001:4433: 'bum phrag mang po bsdu'o snyam du rdzu 'phrul mngon
NK127(jo)001:4435: pad+ma shing rta'i 'phang lo tsam 'dab ma gser sdong
NK127(jo)001:4436: bu dngul snying po ni rin po che dpal gyi
NK127(jo)001:4437: snying po ze ba beed+aur+ya las byas pa bye ba
NK127(jo)001:4438: khrag khrig 'bum phrag brgyad cu rtsa bzhi mngon par
NK127(jo)001:4439: sprul zhing / pad+ma de dag la byang chub sems
NK127(jo)001:4440: dpa' lus gser gyi mdog lta bu skyes bu chen
NK127(jo)001:4441: po'i mtshan sum cu rtsa gnyis dang ldan pa /
NK127(jo)001:4442: dpal dang ldan pa gzi brjid dang kha dog dang
NK127(jo)001:4443: 'od gsal ba dag pad+ma'i snying por skyil mo krung
NK127(jo)001:4444: gis 'dug pa'i gzugs dag kyang sprul nas /
NK127(jo)001:4445: pad+ma de dag rgyal chen bzhi'i ris nas 'og min gyi bar dang /
NK127(jo)001:4446: de bzhin du stong chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khams
NK127(jo)001:4447: kyi rgyal chen bzhi'i lha'i ris ther 'bum nas 'og
NK127(jo)001:4448: min gyi lha'i ris kyi bar gyi 'dod pa dang
NK127(jo)001:4449: gzugs na spyod pa'i lha rnams kyi gnas ji snyed
NK127(jo)001:4450: pa thams cad du 'bod cing sgra sgrogs par byed
NK127(jo)001:4452: yang dag par skul bar byed /
NK127(jo)001:4453: byang chub sems dpa'i gzugs de dag stong chen po'i
NK127(jo)001:4454: 'jig rten gyi khams 'dir rgyu ba'i tshe 'di skad
NK127(jo)001:4455: du / sangs rgyas nyi ma'i rtsa lag rnams //
NK127(jo)001:4457: u dum w+aa ra'i me tog ltar //
NK127(jo)001:4458: sangs rgyas de bzhin shin tu dkon //
NK127(jo)001:4459: sh+aakya seng ge mi yi mchog /
NK127(jo)001:4461: sdug bsngal thams cad zad byed pa'i //
NK127(jo)001:4462: chos ni yang dag de ston mdzad //
NK127(jo)001:4463: lha yi 'dod pa yid dga' la //
NK127(jo)001:4464: ji snyed yun ring spyad byas na //
NK127(jo)001:4465: gang du tshor ba myong 'gyur ba'i //
NK127(jo)001:4467: ji srid 'dod pa rnams bsten pa //
NK127(jo)001:4468: sred pa phyir zhing rab tu 'phel //
NK127(jo)001:4469: khams gsum 'khor ba'i srog chags la //
NK127(jo)001:4470: bde ba yod pa ma yin no //
NK127(jo)001:4471: sangs rgyas 'byung ba rab dkon dang //
NK127(jo)001:4472: khom pa dam pa rnyed nas ni //
NK127(jo)001:4473: gang dag bdag med mi rtogs pa //
NK127(jo)001:4474: de dag sdug bsngal zad mi 'gyur //
NK127(jo)001:4475: sangs rgyas blta phyir deng la ni //
NK127(jo)001:4476: chos kyi dam pa nyan par gyis //
NK127(jo)001:4477: zhes pa la sogs pa sangs rgyas 'byung ba rnyed
NK127(jo)001:4478: dka' zhing des stong pa nyid zab mo'i chos bstan
NK127(jo)001:4479: pa la bag med pa spangs te nyan par skul
NK127(jo)001:4480: ba'i tshigs su bcad pa zab mo'i chos kyi don
NK127(jo)001:4481: dang ldan pa brjod pas 'dod gzugs kyi lha'i bu
NK127(jo)001:4482: rnams las lha bye ba phrag dgu bcu rtsa drug
NK127(jo)001:4483: ni chos kyi mig rdul med cing dri ma dang
NK127(jo)001:4484: bral ba rnam par dag go //
NK127(jo)001:4485: lha'i bu khri nyis stong gis 'dod chags dang bral ba rjes su thob bo //
NK127(jo)001:4486: lha'i bu sa ya phrag gsum dang nyis 'bum ni byang chub tu sems skyes so //
NK127(jo)001:4487: byang chub sems dpa'i theg par yang dag par zhugs
NK127(jo)001:4488: pa'i lha'i bu khris mi skye ba'i chos la bzod
NK127(jo)001:4490: lha'i bu 'bum phrag dpag med grangs med pa dag
NK127(jo)001:4491: skad cig gis bcom ldan 'das sh+aakya thub pa'i drung
NK127(jo)001:4492: du lhags nas phyag 'tshal zhing phyogs gcig tu 'khod
NK127(jo)001:4493: de lha'i me tog dang spos kyis gtor nas steng
NK127(jo)001:4494: gi bar snang la lha'i glu dbyangs mang po rab
NK127(jo)001:4496: de'i tshe gling bzhi pa'i 'jig rten 'dir lha'i bu
NK127(jo)001:4497: gzi brjid che ba dag gis khyab par ma gyur
NK127(jo)001:4498: ba'i phyogs tha na 'khar ba gzugs pa'i gtos tsam
NK127(jo)001:4499: med pa de snyed kyi lha'i bu dag 'dus shing
NK127(jo)001:4500: 'jig rten gyi khams 'di me tog gis pus mo
NK127(jo)001:4501: nub tsam du khebs par gyur to //
NK127(jo)001:4502: de nas lha'i bu blo gros rab gnas dang /
NK127(jo)001:4505: ngo tsha shes pa'i nor can bzhi lha bye ba
NK127(jo)001:4506: phrag dgu bcu rtsa drug po byang chub sems dpa'i
NK127(jo)001:4507: theg par yang dag par zhugs pa sha stag gis
NK127(jo)001:4508: bskor nas 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa'i gnas ga
NK127(jo)001:4509: na ba der dong ste gnas kyi phyi rol nas
NK127(jo)001:4510: bskor ba lan bdun byas shing me tog man+d+aa ra
NK127(jo)001:4511: ba'i char rab tu phab bo //
NK127(jo)001:4512: char de dag me tog gi phung po dpag tshad bcu bar gnas par gyur to //
NK127(jo)001:4513: de nas 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pas byin gyi
NK127(jo)001:4514: rlabs 'di lta bus stong chen po'i 'jig rten gyi
NK127(jo)001:4515: khams 'di'i steng gi bar snang la me tog gi
NK127(jo)001:4516: d+r+wa ba kun nas bkram pa'i 'od des stong chen
NK127(jo)001:4517: po'i 'jig rten gyi khams 'di kun nas khyab par
NK127(jo)001:4518: byas shing / rang gi gnas nas byung ste smon lam las byung ba'i stan la 'dug pa la /
NK127(jo)001:4519: lha'i bu blo gros rab gnas dang lha'i bu de thams cad kyis rkang pa la phyag byas so //
NK127(jo)001:4520: de nas 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa 'di snyam
NK127(jo)001:4521: du bcom ldan 'das kyi spyan sngar bdag su dang
NK127(jo)001:4522: lhan cig tu dri ba bstan pa bshad par bya
NK127(jo)001:4523: / bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i gzhi rnams dang zab
NK127(jo)001:4524: mo spros pa dang bral ba brjod du med pa'i
NK127(jo)001:4525: chos kyi dbyings kyi gzhi la sogs pa rnams bstan
NK127(jo)001:4526: pa na snod du gyur pa su yod snyam pa
NK127(jo)001:4527: / dang / lha'i bu blo gros rab gnas 'di
NK127(jo)001:4528: ni sngon gyi rgyal ba la lhag par bya ba
NK127(jo)001:4529: / dang / byas pa / zab mo la bzod pa /
NK127(jo)001:4530: thogs pa med pa'i spobs pa can yin pas 'di
NK127(jo)001:4531: dang lhan cig 'dri ba dang bstan pa bshad par
NK127(jo)001:4532: bya'o snyam nas lha'i bu blo gros rab gnas la
NK127(jo)001:4533: khyod zab mo'i bzod pa dang ldan pas bcom ldan
NK127(jo)001:4534: 'das kyi spyan sngar kho bo dang lhan cig 'dri
NK127(jo)001:4535: ba bstan pa bshad par nus sam zhes smras pa
NK127(jo)001:4537: 'jam dpal khyod gsung bar mi mdzad brjod par mi
NK127(jo)001:4538: mdzad yi ge mi rjod sgra yang mi gsan pa
NK127(jo)001:4539: lta na bdag gis de bzhin bstan par bagyi'o //
NK127(jo)001:4541: lha'i bu gal te khyod nyan par mi byed 'dzin
NK127(jo)001:4542: par mi byed 'chang bar mi byed rig par mi
NK127(jo)001:4543: byed ston par mi byed pa lta na kho bos
NK127(jo)001:4544: bstan par bya'o // de ci'i phyir zhe na /
NK127(jo)001:4545: sangs rgyas kyi byang chub ni yi ge med pa
NK127(jo)001:4546: sems med pa sems dang bral ba ste ming gis
NK127(jo)001:4547: brjod cing ming de yang g.yo ba med pa'i phyir
NK127(jo)001:4549: 'jam dpal lha'i bu 'di dag ni khyod las chos
NK127(jo)001:4550: nyan par 'tshal gyi phyogs 'di nyid du khyod kyis
NK127(jo)001:4551: chos kyi bka' mchid gsungs shig /'jam dpal gyis smras
NK127(jo)001:4552: pa / lha'i bu kho bo nyan pa dang 'dzin
NK127(jo)001:4553: par 'dod pa rnams la chos ston par mi byed
NK127(jo)001:4554: pa / de / de ci'i phyir na bdag dang
NK127(jo)001:4555: sems can sogs su 'dzin na nyan par 'dod par
NK127(jo)001:4557: zhes sogs 'khor gsum yongs su dag pa'i chos bstan
NK127(jo)001:4558: pas lha'i bu khris mi skye ba'i chos la bzod
NK127(jo)001:4560: de nas lha'i bu blo gros rab gnas kyis /
NK127(jo)001:4561: 'jam dpal la de bzhin gshegs pa'i spyan sngar bzhud ces smras pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:4563: rnam par rtog pa la ma spyod cig /
NK127(jo)001:4564: de bzhin gshegs pa ni kho bos blangs zin to //
NK127(jo)001:4566: de bzhin gshegs pa de gang na bzhugs /
NK127(jo)001:4568: kho bo'i mdun na bzhugs so //
NK127(jo)001:4569: zhes sogs dri ba dang lan bstan pa'i sgo nas
NK127(jo)001:4570: de bzhin gshegs pa nam mkha' dang mnyam pa mnyam
NK127(jo)001:4571: pa nyid kyi skur khong du chud pas de bzhin
NK127(jo)001:4572: gshegs pa blta bar bya ba'i don zab mo bstan
NK127(jo)001:4573: to // de nas 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pas
NK127(jo)001:4574: khang pa brtsegs pa gru bzhi lham pa ka ba
NK127(jo)001:4575: bzhi pa cha mnyam pa shin tu mdzes pa lta
NK127(jo)001:4576: na sdug pa sum khri nyis stong rin po che'i
NK127(jo)001:4577: khri stan lha'i dpag bsam gyi shing las byung ba'i
NK127(jo)001:4579: de re re la yang byang chub sems dpa' lus
NK127(jo)001:4580: mtshan sum cu rtsa gnyis dang ldan pa dag kyang
NK127(jo)001:4581: sprul te / 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa'i byin
NK127(jo)001:4582: gyi rlabs kyis stong chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khams
NK127(jo)001:4583: 'di na rnam par spyod pa'i pad+ma gang yin pa
NK127(jo)001:4584: sprul te / de dag dang / khang pa brtsegs
NK127(jo)001:4585: pa de dag de bzhin gshegs pa ga la ba
NK127(jo)001:4586: der dong ste bcom ldan 'das dge slong gi dge
NK127(jo)001:4587: 'dun dang bcas pa la lan gsum bskor ba byas
NK127(jo)001:4588: sprul te / de dag dang / nas / steng
NK127(jo)001:4589: gi bar snang la 'khor gyi dkyil 'khor la snang
NK127(jo)001:4590: bar byed cing phyogs bzhi kun nas 'khor bar 'khod
NK127(jo)001:4591: sprul te / de dag dang / nas / do
NK127(jo)001:4592: // pad+ma la 'khod pa'i byang chub sems dpa' de
NK127(jo)001:4593: dag dang khang pa brtsegs pa na 'khod pa'i byang
NK127(jo)001:4594: chub sems dpa' de dag thams cad sgra dbyangs mthun
NK127(jo)001:4596: gang+g+aa'i bye snyed bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i //
NK127(jo)001:4597: sangs rgyas bye ba phrag mang khyod kyis mchod //
NK127(jo)001:4598: byang chub mchog gi spyod pa btsal mdzad pas //
NK127(jo)001:4599: de slad mi mchog khyod ni mdzes pa lags //
NK127(jo)001:4600: thub pa mtshan gyis yongs su spras gyur pa //
NK127(jo)001:4601: sku mchog srid pa gsum na lhang nge ste //
NK127(jo)001:4602: 'dren pa gang la mi dang srog dang ni //
NK127(jo)001:4603: gang zag chos ni ma mchis 'gro la ston //
NK127(jo)001:4604: rnam par 'dren pas sbyin dang tshul khrims spyad //
NK127(jo)001:4605: bzod pa brtson 'grus de bzhin bsam gtan bsten //
NK127(jo)001:4606: khyod kyi shes rab srid gsum thogs mi mnga' //
NK127(jo)001:4607: ye shes mthar phyin khyod la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK127(jo)001:4608: gang zhig chos rje lha dang mis mchod pa'i //
NK127(jo)001:4610: stong pa nyid la mos par bgyid pa yi //
NK127(jo)001:4611: mi de 'jig rten dag gi 'dren par 'gyur //
NK127(jo)001:4612: gang dag sngon byung de bzhin gshegs pa dang //
NK127(jo)001:4613: gang dag phyogs rnams bzhugs pa'i 'dren pa dag /
NK127(jo)001:4614: de dag gis ni mtshan med ston pa'i chos //
NK127(jo)001:4615: rang bzhin mtshan nyid ma mchis rtag tu bsgoms //
NK127(jo)001:4616: 'di la rang bzhin sems can gang yang ni //
NK127(jo)001:4617: skye dang 'chi ba dmigs su ma mchis shing //
NK127(jo)001:4618: 'ong ba ma mchis 'gro ba ma mchis te //
NK127(jo)001:4619: chos rnams thams cad nam mkha' ji bzhin no //
NK127(jo)001:4620: ji ltar mi yis sgyu ma bstan gyur pa //
NK127(jo)001:4621: snang yang de bzhin nyid du ma mchis ltar //
NK127(jo)001:4622: de bzhin chos rnams sgyu ma 'dra ba dang //
NK127(jo)001:4623: rmi lam lta bur de bzhin gshegs pas bstan //
NK127(jo)001:4624: gang zag la las gang+g+aa'i bye snyed kyi //
NK127(jo)001:4625: 'jig rten khams rnams 'dir ni sbyin byas dang //
NK127(jo)001:4626: 'dus byas stong par bzod pa gang lags pa //
NK127(jo)001:4627: bzod pa de ni sbyin las khyad par 'phags //
NK127(jo)001:4628: zhes pa la sogs pa tshigs su bcad pa dag
NK127(jo)001:4629: gis rang bzhin 'od gsal stong pa nyid zab mo'i
NK127(jo)001:4630: don la basngagasa pa dang de la nan tan gyis
NK127(jo)001:4631: 'jug par skul ba'i dbyangs byung bas 'khor de'i srog
NK127(jo)001:4632: chags nyi khri nyis stong bla med byang chub tu
NK127(jo)001:4633: sems skyes so // dge slong lnga brgya len pa
NK127(jo)001:4634: med par zag pa rnams las sems rnam par grol
NK127(jo)001:4635: sems skyes so // lo // dge slong sum brgya dang /
NK127(jo)001:4636: dge slong ma sum stong dang /
NK127(jo)001:4639: lha'i bu nyi khri bdun stong ni chos rnams la
NK127(jo)001:4640: chos kyi mig rdul med cing dri ma dang bral
NK127(jo)001:4642: byang chub sems dpa' sum brgyas ni mi skye ba'i chos la bzod pa thob bo //
NK127(jo)001:4643: stong chen po'i 'jig rten 'di yang rnam pa drug tu rab tu g.yos shing 'gul la ldeg go //
NK127(jo)001:4644: de nas bcom ldan 'das la gnas brtan sh+aa ri'i
NK127(jo)001:4645: bus 'khor 'dir snang ba chen pos khyab pa dang
NK127(jo)001:4646: sa g.yo ba la sogs pa de dag su'i mthu
NK127(jo)001:4649: der 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa lha'i bu blo
NK127(jo)001:4650: gros rab gnas dang lhan cig tu de bzhin gshegs
NK127(jo)001:4651: pa la sangs rgyas kyi chos bsam gyis mi khyab
NK127(jo)001:4652: pa yongs su sgrub pa'i phyir /
NK127(jo)001:4653: bdud kyi dkyil 'khor thams cad rnam par 'jig par
NK127(jo)001:4654: byed pa zhes bya ba'i chos kyi rnam grangs zhu
NK127(jo)001:4655: zhing zhu blag byed par 'gyur ba'i phyir ro zhes
NK127(jo)001:4657: bcom ldan 'das 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa 'khor 'dus pa 'di na mi gada'o //
NK127(jo)001:4659: khyod re shig sdod cig dang 'jam dpal gzhon nur
NK127(jo)001:4660: gyur pa de bdud kyi dkyil 'khor thams cad zil
NK127(jo)001:4661: gyis mnan te bkod pa chen pos de bzhin gshegs
NK127(jo)001:4662: pa ga la ba der 'ong bar 'gyur ro //
NK127(jo)001:4663: de nas 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa de bdud
NK127(jo)001:4664: kyi dkyil 'khor thams cad rnam par 'jig par byed
NK127(jo)001:4665: pa zhes bya ba'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par
NK127(jo)001:4666: zhugs pa'i mod la stong chen po'i 'jig rten gyi
NK127(jo)001:4667: khams 'di na bdud kyi gnas bye ba brgya phrag
NK127(jo)001:4668: ji snyed pa de thams cad mog mog par gyur
NK127(jo)001:4669: cing / bdud sdig can de dag thams cad kyang
NK127(jo)001:4670: rgas shing gtugs pa 'khogs par gyur nas 'khar ba
NK127(jo)001:4671: la shin tu brten cing 'gro bar gyur te /
NK127(jo)001:4672: bdud kyi bu mo rnams kyang rgas 'khogs pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:4673: rang rang gi gzhal med khang dag kyang rnyings shing
NK127(jo)001:4674: rab tu 'jig la mun pa mun nag tu gyur
NK127(jo)001:4675: par mthong ngo // de nas bdud sdig can de
NK127(jo)001:4676: dag skrag cing sngangs la yi chad cing sgyid lug
NK127(jo)001:4677: ste spu'i khung bu zing zhes byed par gyur nas
NK127(jo)001:4678: par mthong ngo // 'di snyam du / gang gis
NK127(jo)001:4679: bdag cag bdud kyi gnas rnams 'di lta bu'i gnas
NK127(jo)001:4680: skabs su gyur pa rgyu dang rkyen gang yin /
NK127(jo)001:4681: bdag cag 'di nas 'chi 'pho zhing med pa'am gcig tu mi 'gyur grang snyam mo //
NK127(jo)001:4682: bdud de dag gi rtog pa de lta bu skyes
NK127(jo)001:4683: ma thag tu 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pas lha'i
NK127(jo)001:4684: bu ther 'bum sprul te bdud de dag gi mdun
NK127(jo)001:4686: grogs po dag 'di ni byang chub sems dpa' phyir
NK127(jo)001:4687: mi ldog pa 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa zhes
NK127(jo)001:4688: bya ba bdud kyi dkyil 'khor thams cad rnam par
NK127(jo)001:4689: 'jig par byed pa zhes bya ba'i ting nge 'dzin
NK127(jo)001:4690: la snyoms par zhugs pa de'i mthus yin te /
NK127(jo)001:4691: khyod la 'tshe ba 'ga' yang 'byung bar mi 'gyur gyis ma skrags shig ces smras ma thag tu /
NK127(jo)001:4692: bdud sdig can de dag gis sgra de yang thos /
NK127(jo)001:4693: 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa'i ming yang thos nas yang rgya cher dngangs shing skrag ste /
NK127(jo)001:4694: bdud kyi gnas de dag thams cad kyang g.yos so //
NK127(jo)001:4695: de nas bdud sdig can de dag gis sprul pa'i lha'i bu de dag la smras pa /
NK127(jo)001:4696: grogs po dag bdag yongs su skyobs shig ces byas pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:4697: sprul pa'i lha'i bu dag gis smras pa /
NK127(jo)001:4699: khyed cag deng la bcom ldan 'das sh+aakya thub pa ga la ba der songs shig dang /
NK127(jo)001:4700: de bzhin gshegs pa thugs rje chen po de ni
NK127(jo)001:4701: sems can 'jigs par gyur pa rnams la mi 'jigs
NK127(jo)001:4702: par stsol bar mdzad do zhes smras nas mi snang
NK127(jo)001:4703: bar gyur to // de nas bdud sdig can 'khor
NK127(jo)001:4704: bdud sdig can 'bum phrag ther 'bum du ma dang
NK127(jo)001:4705: bcas pa de dag rgas shing 'khogs nas gzer zhing
NK127(jo)001:4706: lag pa 'khar ba la brten bzhin 'dong zhing skad
NK127(jo)001:4707: cig thang cig yud tsam cig la de bzhin gshegs
NK127(jo)001:4708: pa sh+aakya thub pa ga la ba der dong ste
NK127(jo)001:4709: lhags nas sgra skad gcig tu 'di skad ces gsol
NK127(jo)001:4710: bar gyur to // to // bcom ldan 'das bdag
NK127(jo)001:4711: cag mi sdug pa'i rnam pa 'di lta bu las
NK127(jo)001:4713: bde bar gshegs pa bdag cag yongs su bskyab tu gsol /
NK127(jo)001:4714: bcom ldan 'das sangs rgyas bye ba phrag 'bum gyi
NK127(jo)001:4715: mtshan yongs su bsgrags pa ni mi mngon lags kyi
NK127(jo)001:4716: / 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa gcig pu'i ming ni de lta ma lags so //
NK127(jo)001:4717: de ci'i slad du zhe na /
NK127(jo)001:4718: 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa'i ming thos na bdag cag 'jigs shing dngangs la skrag par 'gyur te /
NK127(jo)001:4719: 'chi 'pho ba snyam du 'tshal zhing med par 'gyur ba snyam du 'tshal ba'i slad du'o //
NK127(jo)001:4720: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
NK127(jo)001:4721: sdig can de de bzhin no //
NK127(jo)001:4722: ji skad smras pa de bzhin te /
NK127(jo)001:4723: 'di ltar 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pas yongs su smin pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:4724: rnam par dbye ba med par sems can rnams kyi don byas pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:4725: byed par 'gyur ba de ltar sangs rgyas bye ba
NK127(jo)001:4726: phrag 'bum gyis kyang sems can rnams kyi don ma
NK127(jo)001:4727: mdzad mi mdzad pa de'i phyir /
NK127(jo)001:4728: 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa gcig pu'i ming yongs
NK127(jo)001:4729: yongs su bsgrags pa de ltar sangs rgyas bye ba
NK127(jo)001:4730: phrag 'bum gyi mtshan yongs su bsgrags pas ni khyed
NK127(jo)001:4731: cag sdug bsngal zhing rnam par 'jig par mi 'gyur
NK127(jo)001:4732: ro // de nas bcom ldan 'das la bdud sdig can de dag gis gsol ba /
NK127(jo)001:4733: bcom ldan 'das bdag cag 'di ltar lus 'khogs pa
NK127(jo)001:4734: 'dis nyam thag cing ngo tsha lags pas bdag cag
NK127(jo)001:4735: sngon bzhin du kha dog rgyas par gyur pa de
NK127(jo)001:4738: khyed cag 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa 'ongs kyi
NK127(jo)001:4739: bar du re shig 'di nyid du sdod cig dang
NK127(jo)001:4740: / des khyed cag mi sdug pa'i rnam pa 'di las yongs su thar par byed par 'gyur ro //
NK127(jo)001:4741: de nas 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa ting nge
NK127(jo)001:4742: 'dzin de las ldang ste stan las langs nas byang
NK127(jo)001:4743: chub sems dpa' du mas bskor zhing mdun du bdar
NK127(jo)001:4744: / lha'i bu 'bum phrag du ma dang klu dang
NK127(jo)001:4745: gnod sbyin dang dri za dang lha ma yin dang
NK127(jo)001:4746: nam mkha' lding dang mi'am ci dang lto 'phye chen
NK127(jo)001:4747: po 'bum phrag du ma sil snyan 'bum phrag mang
NK127(jo)001:4748: po rab tu gsil zhing me tog pad+ma dang ut+pala
NK127(jo)001:4749: la sogs pa'i char rab tu 'bebs pa sha stag
NK127(jo)001:4750: gis bskor nas bkod pa chen po dang rnam par
NK127(jo)001:4751: rtse ba chen pos bcom ldan 'das ga la ba
NK127(jo)001:4752: der dong ste phyin nas bcom ldan 'das kyi zhabs
NK127(jo)001:4753: la mgo bos phyag 'tshal te lan gsum bskor ba
NK127(jo)001:4754: byas nas phyogs gcig tu 'dug go //
NK127(jo)001:4755: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa la 'di skad ces bka' stsal to //
NK127(jo)001:4756: 'jam dpal khyod bdud kyi dkyil 'khor thams cad rnam
NK127(jo)001:4757: par 'jig par byed pa zhes bya ba'i ting nge
NK127(jo)001:4760: bcom ldan 'das snyoms par 'jug lags so //
NK127(jo)001:4762: 'jam dpal khyod kyis ting 'dzin bsgrubs pa de de bzhin gshegs pa gang las thos /
NK127(jo)001:4763: khyod kyis ting 'dzin de bsgrubs nas ji srid cig lon /
NK127(jo)001:4765: bcom ldan 'das gang gi tshe bdag gis ting nge
NK127(jo)001:4766: 'dzin bsgrub pa de thos shing ting nge 'dzin de
NK127(jo)001:4767: bsgrub pa de'i tshe na bcom ldan 'das nyid kyis
NK127(jo)001:4768: byang chub tu thugs bskyed par yang ma gyur lags
NK127(jo)001:4770: 'jam dpal khyod kyis ting nge 'dzin bsgrub pa de thos pa'i de bzhin gshegs pa de'i mtshan ci /
NK127(jo)001:4772: bcom ldan 'das sngon byung ba 'das pa'i dus bskal
NK127(jo)001:4773: pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i yang ches bsam gyis
NK127(jo)001:4774: mi khyab pa / grangs ma mchis pa'i yang ches
NK127(jo)001:4775: grangs ma mchis pa 'das pa de'i tshe de'i dus
NK127(jo)001:4776: mi khyab pa / na / de bzhin gshegs pa
NK127(jo)001:4777: me tog man+d+aa ra ba'i dri zhes bya ba'i sangs
NK127(jo)001:4778: rgyas las ting nge 'dzin bsgrub pa de thos lags
NK127(jo)001:4779: mi khyab pa / na / so // bka' stsal pa /
NK127(jo)001:4780: 'jam dpal bsgrub pa de gang yin /
NK127(jo)001:4782: bcom ldan 'das byang chub sems dpa' rnam pa nyi shu dang ldan na ting nge 'dzin thob ste /
NK127(jo)001:4784: 'dod chags rnam par 'jig cing 'dod chags kyi sems rnam par 'jig par bgyid pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:4785: de bzhin du zhe sdang dang gti mug dang nga
NK127(jo)001:4786: rgyal dang phrag dog dang 'chab pa dang khro ba
NK127(jo)001:4787: dang yongs su gdung ba dang 'du shes dang lta
NK127(jo)001:4788: ba dang rtog pa dang len pa dang 'dzin pa
NK127(jo)001:4789: dang mtshan ma dang srid pa dang rtag pa dang
NK127(jo)001:4790: chad pa dang phung po dang khams dang skye mched
NK127(jo)001:4791: dang khams gsum pa rnam par 'jig cing khams gsum
NK127(jo)001:4792: po la dmigs pa'i sems rnam par 'jig par bgyid
NK127(jo)001:4793: pa ste rnam pa nyi shu po de dang ldan
NK127(jo)001:4794: na ting nge 'dzin de thob bo //
NK127(jo)001:4795: gzhan yang ting nge 'dzin de thob pa'i chos bzhi tshan gyi rnam grangs drug dag kyang smras so //
NK127(jo)001:4796: bcom ldan 'das de ltar de bzhin gshegs pa me
NK127(jo)001:4797: tog man+d+aa ra ba'i dri de'i 'og tu de bzhin
NK127(jo)001:4798: gshegs pa nor bu dang rin po che dang glog
NK127(jo)001:4799: dang nyi zla thams cad zil gyis gnon pa'i 'od
NK127(jo)001:4800: ces bgyi ba de'i spyan sngar ting nge 'dzin de
NK127(jo)001:4802: zhes bstan pa 'di bshad pas 'khor de'i byang chub sems dpa' khris ting nge 'dzin de bsgrubs so //
NK127(jo)001:4803: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis gnas brtan sh+aa ri'i bu la bka' stsal pa /
NK127(jo)001:4804: sh+aa ri'i bu 'di ci snyam du sems /
NK127(jo)001:4805: stong gsum gyi stong chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khams
NK127(jo)001:4806: 'di 'ba' zhig gi bdud sdig can 'di ltar mi
NK127(jo)001:4807: sdug pa'i rnam par byas so snyam na khyod de
NK127(jo)001:4809: 'di ltar 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa'i byin gyi
NK127(jo)001:4810: rlabs kyis phyogs bcu kun gyi sangs rgyas kyi zhing
NK127(jo)001:4811: gang+g+aa'i klung gi bye ma snyed dag na bdud sdig
NK127(jo)001:4812: can gang dag 'khod pa de thams cad 'di lta
NK127(jo)001:4813: bu'i gnas skabs su gyur pa'i phyir ro //
NK127(jo)001:4814: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa la bka' stsal pa /
NK127(jo)001:4815: 'jam dpal khyod kyis byin gyi rlabs 'di thongs la
NK127(jo)001:4816: ci nas bdud sdig can 'di dag sngon gyi kha
NK127(jo)001:4817: dog rgyas pa dang ldan par gyis shig /
NK127(jo)001:4818: de nas 'jam dpal gyis byin gyi rlabs de btang
NK127(jo)001:4819: ma thag tu bdud sdig can de dag sngon gyi
NK127(jo)001:4820: kha dog rgyas pa dang ldan par gyur pa de
NK127(jo)001:4821: dag 'khor dang bcas pa la 'jam dpal gyis smras
NK127(jo)001:4822: pa / sdig can gang la mig dang mig gi
NK127(jo)001:4823: 'du shes dang mig tu chags pa dang mig gi
NK127(jo)001:4824: mtshan ma dang dmigs pa dang 'dzin pa dang rlom
NK127(jo)001:4825: pa sogs yod pa de la bdud kyi bar chad
NK127(jo)001:4827: de bzhin du rna ba sogs dang gzugs sogs kyi
NK127(jo)001:4828: mngon zhen dang blang dor sogs yod pa de la
NK127(jo)001:4829: yang bdud kyi bar chad byed pa'i yul yod kyi
NK127(jo)001:4830: / gang la mig sogs kyi 'dzin pa de thams
NK127(jo)001:4831: cad med pa la ni bdud kyi bar chad byed
NK127(jo)001:4832: pa'i gnas med bdag po med stobs dang dbang phyug
NK127(jo)001:4833: med mthus bzung ba med do zhes de ltar chos
NK127(jo)001:4834: bstan pa des bdud kyi 'khor de las bdud khri
NK127(jo)001:4835: bla med byang chub tu sems skyes so //
NK127(jo)001:4836: bdud brgyad khri chos rnams la chos kyi mig rdul
NK127(jo)001:4837: med cing dri ma bral ba rnam par dag go
NK127(jo)001:4838: // de nas bcom ldan 'das la 'od srung chen pos gsol pa /
NK127(jo)001:4839: bcom ldan 'das 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa 'dir
NK127(jo)001:4840: mchis lags kyis bdag cag byang chub sems dpa' de
NK127(jo)001:4841: dag blta bar bgyi ste skyes bu dam pa de
NK127(jo)001:4842: dag mthong bar dka' ba'i slad du'o //
NK127(jo)001:4843: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
NK127(jo)001:4844: 'jam dpal 'khor 'dis phyogs bcu nas 'dus pa'i byang
NK127(jo)001:4845: chub sems dpa' de dag blta bar 'dod kyi khyod
NK127(jo)001:4846: kyis ston cig / de nas 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pas /
NK127(jo)001:4847: byang chub sems dpa' chos dang chos 'phags dang chos
NK127(jo)001:4848: kyi blo gros dang nyi ma dang bdud kyi mtshon
NK127(jo)001:4849: cha dang / 'jam dbyangs dang sdig pa zhi dang
NK127(jo)001:4850: zhi ba srung dang rnam rgyal srung dang chos rgyal
NK127(jo)001:4851: cha dang / rnam bsgrags dang / de dag dang byang chub sems dpa' gzhan dag la smras pa /
NK127(jo)001:4852: rigs kyi bu dag khyed cag rang gi sangs rgyas
NK127(jo)001:4853: kyi zhing dag na byang chub sems dpa' de dag
NK127(jo)001:4854: gi lus ci 'dra ba de lta bur rang rang
NK127(jo)001:4855: gi lus ston cig ces smras ma thag tu byang
NK127(jo)001:4856: chub sems dpa' de dag ting nge 'dzin de las
NK127(jo)001:4857: langs te rang rang gi lus bstan to //
NK127(jo)001:4858: byang chub sems dpa' kha cig gi lus ni ri rab tsam mo //
NK127(jo)001:4859: kha cig gi lus ni dpag tshad brgyad khri tsam mo //
NK127(jo)001:4860: de bzhin du dpag tshad bdun khri nas khri'i bar dang /
NK127(jo)001:4861: kha cig gi lus dpag tshad lnga stong nas stong gi bar dang /
NK127(jo)001:4862: yang dpag tshad lnga brgya nas brgya'i bar dang /
NK127(jo)001:4863: dpag tshad lnga bcu nas gcig gi bar dang /
NK127(jo)001:4864: kha cig gi lus ni mi mjed 'di'i sems can
NK127(jo)001:4865: rnams kyi lus ji tsam par khru phyed dang bzhi
NK127(jo)001:4866: tsam ste de dag gi lus de lta bu dag
NK127(jo)001:4868: de'i tshe stong chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khams 'di
NK127(jo)001:4869: byang chub sems dpa' gzi brjid che ba mthu che
NK127(jo)001:4870: ba sha stag gis ma khyab pa'i phyogs tha na
NK127(jo)001:4871: 'khar ba gzugs pa'i khyon tsam yang med do //
NK127(jo)001:4872: byang chub sems dpa' de dag gi 'od kyis phyogs
NK127(jo)001:4873: bcu'i sangs rgyas kyi zhing bye ba phrag 'bum dag
NK127(jo)001:4875: de nas 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa stan las
NK127(jo)001:4876: langs te bcom ldan 'das la btud nas thams cad
NK127(jo)001:4877: dang ldan pa'i 'khor dang bcas pas /
NK127(jo)001:4878: bcom ldan 'das byang chub sems dpa' zhes bgyi na
NK127(jo)001:4879: ci'i slad du de skad bgyi zhes gsol ba dang
NK127(jo)001:4881: 'jam dpal chos thams cad rtogs pa'i phyir byang chub sems dpa' zhes bya'o //
NK127(jo)001:4882: byang chub sems dpas mig rtogs par byed /
NK127(jo)001:4883: de bzhin du rna ba sogs dang gzugs sogs rang
NK127(jo)001:4884: bzhin gyis stong par rtogs kyang rtogs so snyam du
NK127(jo)001:4885: mi rtog go zhes sogs chos thams cad stong zhing
NK127(jo)001:4886: spros pa med pa'i rang bzhin rtogs par bstan to
NK127(jo)001:4887: // de nas 'jam dpal dang lha'i bu blo gros
NK127(jo)001:4888: rab gnas kyis dri ba dang lan gyi tshul du
NK127(jo)001:4889: // dang / bcom ldan 'das la zhus pa dang
NK127(jo)001:4890: 'khor gyi gtso bo rnams kyis kyang dri zhing zhu
NK127(jo)001:4891: ba'i sgo nas dgongs te gsungs pa'i don zab mo
NK127(jo)001:4892: // dang / gleng ste / mdor na nyon mongs
NK127(jo)001:4893: dang 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga dang khams gsum du
NK127(jo)001:4894: gtogs pa'i chos dang chos thams cad ye nas ma
NK127(jo)001:4895: // dang / gleng ste / skyes pa'i phyir /
NK127(jo)001:4896: mnyam pa nyid kyis rol pa'i don byang chub sems
NK127(jo)001:4897: dpa'i ye shes kyi thabs mkhas pa zab mo 'jam
NK127(jo)001:4899: byang chub sems dpa'i sems dang po skye ba'i tshul
NK127(jo)001:4900: can skye med zab mo bstan pas byang chub sems
NK127(jo)001:4901: dpa' sum khri nyis stong gis mi skye ba'i chos
NK127(jo)001:4903: dge slong lnga brgya len pa med par zag pa rnams las sems rnam par grol lo //
NK127(jo)001:4904: lha'i bu dung phyur phrag drug gi chos rnams la
NK127(jo)001:4905: chos kyi mig rdul med cing dri ma dang bral
NK127(jo)001:4907: de'i tshe 'od srung chen pos bcom ldan 'das la gsol pa /
NK127(jo)001:4908: 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pas chos bstan pas sems
NK127(jo)001:4909: can 'di snyed kyi don bgyis pa dka' ba bgyid
NK127(jo)001:4910: pa lags so // 'jam dpal gyis smras pa /
NK127(jo)001:4911: kho bo dka' ba byed pa ma yin te chos
NK127(jo)001:4912: thams cad byed pa med pas kho bos ni sems
NK127(jo)001:4913: can 'ga' yang bcings pa'am grol bar mi byed de
NK127(jo)001:4914: sems can med pa'i phyir ro //
NK127(jo)001:4915: sems can rnams ni dka' ba byed pa ste sangs
NK127(jo)001:4916: rgyas thams cad kyi ma brnyes shing nyan rang thams
NK127(jo)001:4917: cad kyis ma rnyed rnyed par mi 'gyur ba gang
NK127(jo)001:4918: yin pa de dag byis pa so so'i skye bo
NK127(jo)001:4919: rnams kyis rnyed pa'i phyir te /
NK127(jo)001:4920: sangs rgyas thams cad kyis ma brnyes pa ni bdag
NK127(jo)001:4921: dang sems can dang gzugs la sogs pa'i chos thams
NK127(jo)001:4922: cad yin la / sangs rgyas rnams kyis ma mdzad /
NK127(jo)001:4923: nyan rang thams cad kyis ma byas pa gang yin pa de dag byis pa rnams kyis byed de /
NK127(jo)001:4924: rtag pa dang chad pa dang kun tu sbyor ba dang rlom pa sogs su byed do zhes dang /
NK127(jo)001:4925: de bzhin du 'jam dpal gyis mi skye ba'i chos
NK127(jo)001:4926: la bzod pa thob pa ci lta bu zhes bcom
NK127(jo)001:4928: chos thams cad thob pa med pa sogs su bzod
NK127(jo)001:4929: pa'i tshul las brtsams te gleng nas srog chags drug
NK127(jo)001:4930: khri nyis stong bla med byang chub tu sems skyes
NK127(jo)001:4931: so // byang chub sems dpa' khri nyis stong gis
NK127(jo)001:4932: ni mi skye ba'i chos la bzod pa thob par
NK127(jo)001:4933: so // gyur to // de nas lha'i bu blo
NK127(jo)001:4934: gros rab gnas kyis 'jam dpal la sa nas sar
NK127(jo)001:4935: 'phar ba ji lta bu zhes dris pa na /
NK127(jo)001:4936: chos thams cad 'pho ba med pa dang sgyu ma lta bur bstan la /
NK127(jo)001:4937: dgongs pa'i skad kyis kyang ci rigs bstan pas bcom
NK127(jo)001:4938: ldan 'das kyis 'jam dpal la legs so zhes bya
NK127(jo)001:4939: ba byin te / 'jam dpal legs so legs so //
NK127(jo)001:4940: gal te bstan par bya na de skad bstan par bya'o zhes gsungs so //
NK127(jo)001:4941: de nas lha'i bu blo gros rab gnas la 'jam
NK127(jo)001:4942: dpal gzhon nur gyur pas rang bzhin med pa'i don
NK127(jo)001:4943: las brtsams te dgongs te gsungs pa zab mo bshad
NK127(jo)001:4944: pa las / byang phyogs kyi chos thams cad dang
NK127(jo)001:4945: rnam thar gsum dmigs pa dang sgom pa dang mngon
NK127(jo)001:4946: du bya ba med pa'i don zab mo bstan pa
NK127(jo)001:4947: pa las / la / 'khor de'i dge slong stong phrag mang pos 'di snyam du /
NK127(jo)001:4948: bcom ldan 'das kyi rnam thar gsum dang byang phyogs
NK127(jo)001:4949: kyis chos sum cu rtsa bdun mngon sum byas pas
NK127(jo)001:4950: mya ngan las 'da' bar 'gyur ro zhes gsungs pa
NK127(jo)001:4951: de yang 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa 'dis bkag
NK127(jo)001:4952: par gyur na / 'dis bstan pa 'di ji ltar
NK127(jo)001:4953: rung 'gal bar bstan par ma gyur grang snyam du
NK127(jo)001:4954: the tshom skyes pa'i rtog pa 'jam dpal gyis shes
NK127(jo)001:4955: par gyur na / nas / sh+aa ri'i bu la
NK127(jo)001:4956: khyod shes rab chen po rnams kyi mchog tu bstan
NK127(jo)001:4957: pa yin na 'dod chags dang bral ba'i tshe btsun
NK127(jo)001:4958: pas bden pa bzhi dang rnam thar gsum dang byang
NK127(jo)001:4959: phyogs kyi chos rnams dmigs pa'am mngon du bya ba'am
NK127(jo)001:4962: 'jam dpal de ni med de chos thams cad blang
NK127(jo)001:4963: du med pa ma skyes pa stong pa nyid yin
NK127(jo)001:4964: pas mngon sum mi byed pa'i phyir ro //
NK127(jo)001:4965: zhes bstan pa 'di bshad pas dge slong sum stong
NK127(jo)001:4966: len pa med par zag pa rnams las sems rnam
NK127(jo)001:4967: par grol lo // de nas lha'i bu blo gros
NK127(jo)001:4968: rab gnas dang 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa dri
NK127(jo)001:4969: ba dang lan gyi sgo nas gdod nas ma skyes
NK127(jo)001:4970: pas dmigs su med pa'i don zab mo gleng ba
NK127(jo)001:4971: par grol lo // na / 'khor de'i dge slong
NK127(jo)001:4972: lnga brgya tsam chos kyi rnam grangs de ma rtogs
NK127(jo)001:4973: nas spangs shing 'gal bar byas te lus de nyid
NK127(jo)001:4974: kyis sems can dmyal ba chen po rnams su ltung
NK127(jo)001:4975: par grol lo // na / ba na / sh+aa ri'i bus 'jam dpal la smras pa /
NK127(jo)001:4976: dge slong lnga brgya chos kyi rnam grangs 'di ma
NK127(jo)001:4977: rtogs te spangs pas sems can dmyal bar ltung bar
NK127(jo)001:4978: gyur gyis de lta bu'i gnas zab mo dag ma
NK127(jo)001:4979: ston par so sor rtog ste ston cig /'jam dpal
NK127(jo)001:4980: gyis smras pa / btsun pa sh+aa ri'i bu khyod ma rtog cig /
NK127(jo)001:4981: gang sems can dmyal bar 'gro ba'i chos de lta bu 'ga' yang dmigs su med de /
NK127(jo)001:4982: de ci'i phyir zhe na chos thams cad skye ba med pa'i phyir ro //
NK127(jo)001:4983: so sor rtog ste ston cig ces zer ba ni /
NK127(jo)001:4984: rigs kyi bu'am rigs kyi bu mo bdag tu lta
NK127(jo)001:4985: ba la brten pa gang gis de bzhin gshegs pa
NK127(jo)001:4986: dge slong gi dge 'dun dang bcas pa gang+g+aa'i klung
NK127(jo)001:4987: gi bye ma snyed cig la ji srid 'tsho'i bar
NK127(jo)001:4988: du bde ba'i yo byad thams cad kyis bsnyen bkur
NK127(jo)001:4989: byas pa bas / gang gis chos zab mo shes
NK127(jo)001:4990: par dka' ba 'jig rten thams cad dang mi mthun
NK127(jo)001:4991: pa stong pa nyid la sogs pa'i tshul 'di lta
NK127(jo)001:4992: bu thos nas spangs te sems can dmyal ba chen
NK127(jo)001:4993: por lhung bar gyur pa ni ches myur bar de
NK127(jo)001:4994: nas ldang zhing thar bar 'gyur gyi /
NK127(jo)001:4995: gang bdag tu lta ba rten pa chos 'di ma
NK127(jo)001:4996: thos par de bzhin gshegs pa la bsnyen bkur byed
NK127(jo)001:4997: pa de lta ma yin no zhes smras pa na
NK127(jo)001:4998: / bcom ldan 'das kyis 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa la /
NK127(jo)001:4999: 'jam dpal legs so legs so ji skad smras pa
NK127(jo)001:5000: de bzhin te thos pa 'di ni sangs rgyas byung
NK127(jo)001:5001: ba dang 'dra'o // de bzhin du rgyun du zhugs
NK127(jo)001:5002: pa nas dgra bcom pa dang 'dra ba'i bar du
NK127(jo)001:5003: ba dang 'dra'o // ste / ci'i phyir na /
NK127(jo)001:5004: bdag tu lta ba la brten pa dang dmigs pa
NK127(jo)001:5005: can la thob pa'am mngon par rtogs pa med pa'i
NK127(jo)001:5006: phyir ro // de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis sh+aa ri'i bu la bka' stsal pa /
NK127(jo)001:5008: dge slong de dag ni dmyal ba de dag nas
NK127(jo)001:5009: ches myur bar ldang zhing yongs su mya ngan las
NK127(jo)001:5011: mi gti mug can dmigs pa'i lta ba dang ldan
NK127(jo)001:5012: pa the tshom du gyur pa gang dag de bzhin
NK127(jo)001:5013: gshegs pa la mchod pa byed pa ni de lta
NK127(jo)001:5014: ma yin no // sh+aa ri'i bu de lta mod
NK127(jo)001:5015: kyi de ni de dag yongs su mya ngan las
NK127(jo)001:5016: 'da' ba'i rgyur 'gyur kyang myur du rnam par thar
NK127(jo)001:5017: ba ni mi 'gyur te 'di ltar chos zab mo
NK127(jo)001:5020: der lha'i bu blo gros rab gnas kyis 'jam dpal khyod tshangs pa mtshungs par spyod pa bzhed dam /
NK127(jo)001:5022: lha'i bu gal te tshangs spyod mi len zhing tshangs
NK127(jo)001:5023: par spyod par mi byed pa de lta na kho
NK127(jo)001:5024: bo khyod dang tshangs par mtshungs par spyod 'dod do
NK127(jo)001:5025: // lha'i bus 'jam dpal khyod ci la dgongs te de skad ston /
NK127(jo)001:5027: lha'i bu gang len par byed pa de ni spyod
NK127(jo)001:5028: par byed kyi len par mi byed pa de ni
NK127(jo)001:5029: ci yang spyod par mi byed do //
NK127(jo)001:5030: tshangs par spyod pa dmigs par byed pa de ni
NK127(jo)001:5031: spyod par byed kyi dmigs par mi byed pa de
NK127(jo)001:5032: ni ci yang spyod par mi byed do //
NK127(jo)001:5034: 'o na 'jam dpal khyod tshangs par mi spyod lags sam /
NK127(jo)001:5036: lha'i bu de de bzhin te kho bo tshangs par mi spyod do //
NK127(jo)001:5037: kho ni tshangs pa yang ma yin la spyod pa yang ma yin pa de'i phyir ro //
NK127(jo)001:5038: zhes sogs dri ba dang lan gyi sgo nas gang
NK127(jo)001:5039: dang gang dmigs pa de ni de dang de'i don
NK127(jo)001:5040: dang mi mthun la dmigs pa med pa nyid de
NK127(jo)001:5041: dang de'i don la legs par zhugs pa yin par
NK127(jo)001:5042: bstan pa dang / gzhan yang dgongs te gsungs pa
NK127(jo)001:5043: 'gal ba ltar snang ba'i tshig gi zab mo skye
NK127(jo)001:5044: ba med pa'i don bstan pa'i skabs su /
NK127(jo)001:5045: 'khor der byang chub sems dpa' bsam gtan bzhi sgom
NK127(jo)001:5046: pa mngon shes lnga thob pa lnga zhig 'dus par
NK127(jo)001:5047: gyur pa de dag da dung bzod pa thob pa
NK127(jo)001:5048: min pas gnas shing ting nge 'dzin 'jug ldang byed
NK127(jo)001:5049: pa de dag gis sngon pha ma dang dgra bcom
NK127(jo)001:5050: bsad pa'i sngon gnas rjes su dran zhing las kyi
NK127(jo)001:5051: rnam smin lhag ma yod pas de dag sems gdung
NK127(jo)001:5052: ba des zab mo dag la mi bzod cing /
NK127(jo)001:5053: bdag nyid la rten cing rnam par rtog pa kho
NK127(jo)001:5054: nar byed pa de dag gis kun nas ldang ba
NK127(jo)001:5055: de rnam par gnon ma nus pa de dag 'dul
NK127(jo)001:5057: bcom ldan 'das kyis 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa'i sems bsdu bar mdzad pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:5058: 'jam dpal stan las langs shing bla gos phrag pa
NK127(jo)001:5059: gcig tu gzar nas lag pa g.yas pas ral gri
NK127(jo)001:5060: blangs te legs par brdar nas bcom ldan 'das ga
NK127(jo)001:5061: la ba der logs su brgyugs so //
NK127(jo)001:5062: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis 'jam dpal la bka' stsal pa /
NK127(jo)001:5063: 'jam dpal nga ni bsad zin cing legs par bsad zin gyis thongs shig /
NK127(jo)001:5065: 'jam dpal skyes bu gang dag gis gang gi tshe
NK127(jo)001:5066: gsod snyam pa'i sems skyed par byed pa'i sems skyes
NK127(jo)001:5067: pa de'i tshe de dag gis yun ring po nas
NK127(jo)001:5069: de nas dge slong lnga po de dag 'di snyam du /
NK127(jo)001:5070: chos thams cad ni sgyu ma lta bu ste 'di
NK127(jo)001:5071: la bdag gam sems can sogs 'ga' yang med do
NK127(jo)001:5072: // 'di la pha dang ma dang sangs rgyas dang chos dang dge 'dun kyang med do //
NK127(jo)001:5073: 'di la mtshams med pa byed par 'gyur ba 'ga' yang med do //
NK127(jo)001:5075: 'jam dpal gzhon nu 'di ni mkhas pa mdzangs pa yid gzhungs pa /
NK127(jo)001:5076: sangs rgyas thams cad kyis bstod cing basngagasa pa zab
NK127(jo)001:5077: mo la bzod pa sangs rgyas mang po la bsnyen
NK127(jo)001:5078: bkur byas pa / chos thams cad rab tu 'byed pa'i shes rab la mkhas pa /
NK127(jo)001:5079: ji lta ba bzhin du chos ston pa /
NK127(jo)001:5081: de bzhin gshegs pa la gus pa dang bcas pa
NK127(jo)001:5082: yin na des mtshon rnon po thogs te de bzhin
NK127(jo)001:5083: gshegs pa ga la ba der brgyugs shing /
NK127(jo)001:5084: de bzhin gshegs pas kyang 'di skad ces 'jam dpal
NK127(jo)001:5085: nga ni bsad zin cing legs par bsad zin gyis
NK127(jo)001:5086: thongs shig ces gsungs pa'i phyir te /
NK127(jo)001:5087: gal te 'di la sangs rgyas sogs ther zug tu
NK127(jo)001:5088: gnas pa 'ga' zhig grub na mtshams med 'dzin pa
NK127(jo)001:5089: de la nges par 'byung ba yang yod par mi
NK127(jo)001:5091: gang gi phyir chos de dag ni med pa /
NK127(jo)001:5093: sgyu ma lta bu stong pa 'di la gang byed pa'am /
NK127(jo)001:5094: gang la byed 'ga' yang med do snyam mo //
NK127(jo)001:5095: byang chub sems dpa' lnga po dag gis de ltar
NK127(jo)001:5096: shes pas mi skye ba'i chos la bzod pa thob
NK127(jo)001:5097: par gyur nas dga' ba dang mchog tu dga' bas
NK127(jo)001:5098: ta la bdun srid tsam gyi mkha' la 'phags te
NK127(jo)001:5099: / rang gi sngon gnas dran pa dang zab mo'i
NK127(jo)001:5100: don ji ltar rtogs pa'i tshul gyis bcom ldan 'das
NK127(jo)001:5101: la tshigs su bcad pas mngon par bstod do //
NK127(jo)001:5102: mtshon thogs pa'i chos kyi rnam grangs 'di bshad pa
NK127(jo)001:5103: na phyogs bcu'i zhing gang+g+aa'i klung gi bye ma snyed
NK127(jo)001:5104: rnam pa drug tu rab tu g.yos par gyur to
NK127(jo)001:5105: // de nas phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten khams kyi sangs
NK127(jo)001:5106: rgyas kyi zhing dag gi sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das
NK127(jo)001:5107: gang dag bzhugs pa de dag la rang rang gi
NK127(jo)001:5108: bsnyen bkur ba de dag gis gang gis dog sa
NK127(jo)001:5109: chen po g.yos pa 'di su'i mthu lags /
NK127(jo)001:5110: sangs rgyas de dag gis bka' stsal pa /
NK127(jo)001:5111: mi mjed kyi zhing na 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur
NK127(jo)001:5112: pas 'dul ba'i dbang gis shes rab kyi ral gri'i
NK127(jo)001:5113: mtshon rnon po thogs te bcom ldan 'das sh+aakya thub
NK127(jo)001:5114: pa ga la ba der brgyugs pa las so //
NK127(jo)001:5115: de nas sangs rgyas de dag gis shes rab kyi
NK127(jo)001:5116: mtshon las brtsams te ci nas kyang sems can dpag
NK127(jo)001:5117: tu med pa'i mig rnam par dag pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:5118: sems rnam par grol ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:5120: byang chub la zhugs par gyur pa de lta de ltar chos bstan to //
NK127(jo)001:5121: de'i tshe bcom ldan 'das kyis 'khor de na sems
NK127(jo)001:5122: can las dang po pa dge rtsa chung ba rnam
NK127(jo)001:5123: par rtog pa mang pa gang dag 'khod pa de
NK127(jo)001:5124: dag gis mtshon de mi mthong zhing chos bstan pa
NK127(jo)001:5125: de yang mi thos pa de ltar byin gyis brlabs
NK127(jo)001:5126: so // de nas gnas brtan sh+aa ri'i bus 'jam dpal la smras pa /
NK127(jo)001:5127: 'jam dpal khyod kyis ston pa 'grong ba'i phyir brtul
NK127(jo)001:5128: ba'i las mi bzad pa 'dus byas pa de khyod
NK127(jo)001:5129: la gang du rnam par smin par 'gyur /
NK127(jo)001:5131: btsun pa sh+aa ri'i bu de de bzhin te /
NK127(jo)001:5132: kho bo las mi bzang pa de lta bu ni
NK127(jo)001:5133: byas na de gang du rnam par smin par 'gyur
NK127(jo)001:5134: ba'i gnas ni mi shes so //
NK127(jo)001:5135: de lta mod kyi sgyu ma'i skyes bu'i las gang
NK127(jo)001:5136: du smin par 'gyur ba der kho bo'i yang rnam
NK127(jo)001:5139: sgyu ma'i skyes bu yang mi rtag rnam par mi
NK127(jo)001:5140: rtog la chos thams cad kyang mi rtog rnam par
NK127(jo)001:5142: 'di ltar de ni btsun pa sh+aa ri'i bu nyid
NK127(jo)001:5143: la 'dri yi khyod kyis ji ltar bzod pa de
NK127(jo)001:5144: ltar ston cig / btsun pa mtshon dang las dang rnam par smin pa dmigs su yod dam /
NK127(jo)001:5149: mtshon yang med las kyang med rnam par smin pa
NK127(jo)001:5150: yang med na 'o na las de gang du smin
NK127(jo)001:5151: par 'gyur / sh+aa ri'i bus smras pa /
NK127(jo)001:5152: 'jam dpal khyod kyi bsam pa des bstan pa ltar
NK127(jo)001:5153: na las de ni gang du yang rnam par smin
NK127(jo)001:5155: de ci'i phyir zhe na chos thams cad la las dang rnam smin med pa'i phyir ro //
NK127(jo)001:5156: de nas bcom ldan 'das la phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten
NK127(jo)001:5157: gyi khams nas 'dus pa'i byang chub sems dpa' dag
NK127(jo)001:5158: gis gsol pa / 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa
NK127(jo)001:5159: 'di ci nas kyang bdag cag gi sangs rgyas kyi
NK127(jo)001:5160: zhing dag tu mchi zhing chos ston par 'gyur ba
NK127(jo)001:5161: de ltar thugs brtse bas spro bar mdzad du gsol
NK127(jo)001:5162: gis gsol pa / // de nas 'jam dpal gzhon
NK127(jo)001:5163: nur gyur pas byang chub sems dpa' de dag la
NK127(jo)001:5164: gis gsol pa / // smras pa / rigs kyi
NK127(jo)001:5165: bu dag khyed cag je rang rang gi sangs rgyas
NK127(jo)001:5166: kyi zhing rnams su ltos shig /
NK127(jo)001:5167: de dag gis phyogs bcu kun gyi rang rang gi sangs rgyas kyi zhing rnams su bltas pas /
NK127(jo)001:5168: zhing de dag nas 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur ba'i sgra snyan pa yang thos /
NK127(jo)001:5169: sangs rgyas de dag gi spyan snga na 'jam dpal
NK127(jo)001:5170: gzhon nur gyur pa 'dug cing lha'i bu blo gros
NK127(jo)001:5171: rab gnas dang chos kyi rnam grangs 'di nyid 'dri
NK127(jo)001:5172: ba la chos ston pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:5173: de dag tu byang chub sems dpa' 'dus pa dang lha'i bu 'dus pa de snyed kyang mthong bas /
NK127(jo)001:5174: 'jam dpal gzhon nu 'di ni sangs rgyas kyi zhing 'di nas kyang mi g.yo la /
NK127(jo)001:5175: thams cad du yang bzhin nye bar ston pa ni
NK127(jo)001:5176: ngo mtshar te ngo mtshar to snyam du ngo mtshar
NK127(jo)001:5178: de nas 'jam dpal gyis byang chub sems dpa' de dag la smras pa /
NK127(jo)001:5179: rigs kyi bu dag 'di lta ste dper na sgyu
NK127(jo)001:5180: ma mkhan mi sgyu ma shin tu bslabs pa'i phyir
NK127(jo)001:5181: stan las mi g.yo bar gzugs sna tshogs ston pa
NK127(jo)001:5182: bzhin du byang chub sems dpa' shes rab kyi pha
NK127(jo)001:5183: rol tu phyin pa la legs par bslabs pa yang
NK127(jo)001:5184: sgyu ma lta bu'i chos rnams la sangs rgyas kyi
NK127(jo)001:5185: zhing ji snyed du bzhin nye bar ston par 'dod
NK127(jo)001:5186: pa de snyed du sprul pa dag sprul par byed
NK127(jo)001:5187: de / de ci'i phyir zhe na /
NK127(jo)001:5188: chos 'di sgyu ma lta bur rig pa'i phyir ro //
NK127(jo)001:5189: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa la bka' stsal pa /
NK127(jo)001:5190: 'jam dpal chos kyi rnam grangs 'di thos pa de ni sangs rgyas 'byung ba dang 'dra'o //
NK127(jo)001:5191: 'di thos pa de ni rgyun du zhugs pa'i 'bras
NK127(jo)001:5192: bu dang phyir 'ong dang phyir mi 'ong ba'i 'bras
NK127(jo)001:5193: bu dang dgra bcom pa nyid dang 'dra ste /
NK127(jo)001:5194: chos 'di la mos shing yid ches pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:5195: byang chub kyi snying po la 'dug pa gang yin pa de ni 'dra ba yin no //
NK127(jo)001:5197: bcom ldan 'das de de bzhin lags te /
NK127(jo)001:5198: de ni stong pa nyid dang mtshan ma med pa
NK127(jo)001:5199: dang smon pa ma mchis pa dang de bzhin nyid
NK127(jo)001:5200: dang chos kyi dbyings dang yang dag pa'i mtha' dang
NK127(jo)001:5201: mnyam pa nyid dang rnam par grol ba dang dben
NK127(jo)001:5202: pa ji lta ba de ltar 'dra ba lags so
NK127(jo)001:5203: // de nas 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pas bcom
NK127(jo)001:5204: ldan 'das la ci nas kyang chos kyi rnam grangs
NK127(jo)001:5205: 'di ma 'ongs pa'i dus lnga brgya tha mar gyur
NK127(jo)001:5206: ba na spyod par 'gyur zhing rigs kyi bu'am bu
NK127(jo)001:5207: mo dag gi rna lam du grags par 'gyur ba
NK127(jo)001:5208: de ltar byin gyis brlab tu gsol /
NK127(jo)001:5210: stong chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khams 'di na lha
NK127(jo)001:5211: dang mi'i rol mo'i sgra ji snyed pa de thams
NK127(jo)001:5212: cad ma bkrol bar sgra grag cing /
NK127(jo)001:5213: ljon pa thams cad las kyang me tog rgyas shing lhags pa /
NK127(jo)001:5214: rdzing bu dag nas pad+ma mang po dag 'thon par gyur la /
NK127(jo)001:5215: stong chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khams 'di rnam pa
NK127(jo)001:5216: drug tu g.yos shing snang ba chen pos khyab pas
NK127(jo)001:5217: nyi zla 'di dag kyang mi snang bar gyur te
NK127(jo)001:5218: / lha 'bum phrag mang po dag kyang dga' zhing
NK127(jo)001:5219: mgu la yi rangs te steng gi bar snang la
NK127(jo)001:5220: 'khod nas me tog dang phye ma dang spos dang
NK127(jo)001:5221: byug pa'i char mngon par rab tu 'phebs so //
NK127(jo)001:5222: sil snyan dang lha'i glu dbyangs mang po dag kyang
NK127(jo)001:5223: bsgrags nas thams cad thal mo sbyar te kha mthun
NK127(jo)001:5225: a la la 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pas bstan pa'i chos /
NK127(jo)001:5228: 'jig rten du chos kyi 'khor lo gnyis pa yang bskor ba mthong ngo //
NK127(jo)001:5229: sems can gang dag chos kyi rnam grangs 'di thos
NK127(jo)001:5230: pa dang thos nas mos par gyur pa de dag
NK127(jo)001:5231: ni dge ba'i rtsa ba ngan ngon dang ldan pa
NK127(jo)001:5232: ma yin no // chos 'di thos nas mi skrag
NK127(jo)001:5233: pa de ni sngon gyi rgyal ba la lhag par
NK127(jo)001:5234: bya ba byas pa zab mo la bzod pa yin
NK127(jo)001:5236: de nas 'jam dpal gyis bcom ldan 'das la chos
NK127(jo)001:5237: kyi rnam grangs 'di byin gyis brlabs pa'i slad du
NK127(jo)001:5238: snga ltas 'di dag byung ba lags na /
NK127(jo)001:5239: de ni ma 'ongs pa'i dus na spyod par 'gyur ro //
NK127(jo)001:5243: chos kyi rnam grangs 'di byin gyis brlabs pa'i phyir snga ltas 'di dag byung ba yin no //
NK127(jo)001:5245: bcom ldan 'das chos kyi rnam grangs 'di yun ring
NK127(jo)001:5246: du gnas par bgyi ba'i slad du bcom ldan 'das
NK127(jo)001:5247: kyis bden pa'i byin gyis rlabs mdzad du gsol /
NK127(jo)001:5248: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
NK127(jo)001:5249: 'jam dpal bden pa dang bden pa'i tshig gang gis
NK127(jo)001:5250: rnam par thar ba'i sgo gsum la brten nas rnam
NK127(jo)001:5251: par grol ba'i bden pa dang bden pa'i tshig des
NK127(jo)001:5252: chos kyi rnam grangs 'di ma 'ongs ba'i dus lnga
NK127(jo)001:5253: brgya tha ma na spyod par gyur cig /'jam dpal
NK127(jo)001:5254: gyis gsol pa / bcom ldan 'das bden pa dang
NK127(jo)001:5255: bden pa'i tshig gang gis bdag ma mchis pa dang
NK127(jo)001:5256: sems can dang kun nyon dang rnam byang ma mchis
NK127(jo)001:5257: pa'i bden pa dang bden pa'i tshig des chos kyi
NK127(jo)001:5258: rnam grangs 'di ma 'ongs pa'i dus lnga brgya tha
NK127(jo)001:5259: ma na spyod par gyur cig /
NK127(jo)001:5260: de bzhin du 'dod chags la sogs pa rnams de
NK127(jo)001:5261: bzhin gshegs pas chos dang ming du gdags pa ma
NK127(jo)001:5262: mchis pa des / bstan pa 'di dang dus gsum
NK127(jo)001:5263: gyi sangs rgyas dag gis 'ga' yang ma spyad ma
NK127(jo)001:5264: grol la mi 'grol gang yang ma bstan ma nyan
NK127(jo)001:5265: ma thob ma spyod pa la sogs pa'i bden pa'i
NK127(jo)001:5266: tshig gis chos kyi rnam grangs 'di dus lnga brgya
NK127(jo)001:5267: tha ma na 'dzam bu'i gling du spyod par gyur
NK127(jo)001:5268: cig ces byin gyis brlabs so //
NK127(jo)001:5269: de'i tshe stong chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khams 'di rnam pa drug tu g.yos par gyur pa na /
NK127(jo)001:5270: de'i rgyu rkyen gang lags zhes bcom ldan 'das la
NK127(jo)001:5271: byang chub sems dpa' byams pas zhus pa la bka'
NK127(jo)001:5272: stsal pa / byams pa dman pa la mos pa'i
NK127(jo)001:5273: sems can 'di dang 'dzin par ma gyur na mi
NK127(jo)001:5276: bcom ldan 'das skye bo mang po la sman pa
NK127(jo)001:5277: dang bde ba dang lha dang mi rnams kyi dge
NK127(jo)001:5278: ba'i slad du bshad du gsol /
NK127(jo)001:5279: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
NK127(jo)001:5280: byams pa chos kyi rnam grangs 'di ni sa phyogs
NK127(jo)001:5281: 'di nyid du sangs rgyas bye ba khrag khrig 'bum
NK127(jo)001:5282: phrag bdun cu rtsa bzhis bstan te /
NK127(jo)001:5283: thams cad du yang 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa
NK127(jo)001:5284: dang lha'i bu blo gros rab gnas kyis zhus so
NK127(jo)001:5286: bcom ldan 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa dang lha'i
NK127(jo)001:5287: bu blo gros rab gnas kyis chos kyi rnam grangs
NK127(jo)001:5288: 'di thos nas ji srid cig lags /
NK127(jo)001:5289: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
NK127(jo)001:5290: byams pa rigs kyi bu 'di dag gis bskal pa grangs med pa phrag gsum 'das pa na /
NK127(jo)001:5291: de bzhin gshegs pa kun nas me tog mngon par
NK127(jo)001:5292: 'phags pa seng ge'i rtsal gyi yon tan phung po
NK127(jo)001:5293: zhes bya ba las chos kyi rnam grangs 'di thos
NK127(jo)001:5294: so // chos kyi rnam grangs 'di bshad pa na
NK127(jo)001:5295: sems can gang+g+aa'i klung gi bye ma snyed dag bla
NK127(jo)001:5296: na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub
NK127(jo)001:5298: de'i nyis 'gyur snyed kyis ni phyir mi ldog pa'i bzod pa thob bo //
NK127(jo)001:5299: de'i nyis 'gyur snyed kyis ni chos rnams la chos
NK127(jo)001:5300: kyi mig rdul med cing dri ma dang bral ba
NK127(jo)001:5303: gzhan yang 'jam dpal rnam par rol pa'i mdo las
NK127(jo)001:5304: smad 'tshong ma'i bu mo gser mchog 'od dpal zhes
NK127(jo)001:5305: bya ba gser gyi mdog dang ldan zhing de 'gro
NK127(jo)001:5306: ba'i phyogs dang gos thams cad kyang gser gyi mdog
NK127(jo)001:5307: tu byed pa rgyal po dang blon po tshong dpon
NK127(jo)001:5308: sogs kun gyi yid du 'ong ba slad bzhin 'brang
NK127(jo)001:5309: zhing lta bar 'os pa de tshong dpon gyi bu
NK127(jo)001:5310: 'jigs byin zhes bya bas nor gyis glas te shing
NK127(jo)001:5311: rta la 'dug nas skyed mos tshal gyi sar phyin
NK127(jo)001:5312: pa'i lam du 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pas 'dul
NK127(jo)001:5313: ba'i dbang gis rang gi lus kyi 'od kyis nyi
NK127(jo)001:5314: zla zil gyis gnon cing gos las 'od byung bas
NK127(jo)001:5315: dpag tshad khyab pa dang rgyan thams cad kyis brgyan
NK127(jo)001:5316: par bstan pas / bu mo gser mchog kyang rang
NK127(jo)001:5317: gi lus la dman pa'i 'du shes dang 'jam dpal
NK127(jo)001:5318: la dga' zhing chags pa'i tshul gyis 'di dang lhan
NK127(jo)001:5319: cig rtse bar bya'o snyam pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:5320: 'jam dpal gyi mthus rgyal po rnam thos bu mi'i gzugs su sprul pas bu mo la /
NK127(jo)001:5321: 'di ni 'dod pa don du mi gnyer te byang
NK127(jo)001:5322: chub sems dpa' 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa zhes
NK127(jo)001:5323: bya ba sems can gyi bsam pa rdzogs par byed
NK127(jo)001:5324: cing slong ba kun gtong ba'o //
NK127(jo)001:5325: zhes smras pas bu mo'i bsam par /
NK127(jo)001:5326: 'o na gos 'di bslangs na sbyin no snyam nas gos bslangs pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:5327: des byang chub la zhugs na gos sbyin no zhes gsungs pas /
NK127(jo)001:5328: bu mos byang chub ces pa ci zhes dris pa la /
NK127(jo)001:5329: rang bzhin med pa mnyam pa nyid kyi don bstan
NK127(jo)001:5330: pas nam mkha'i lha'i bu lnga 'bum gyis bla med
NK127(jo)001:5331: byang chub tu sems bskyed do //
NK127(jo)001:5332: bu mo gser mchog gi phyi bzhin 'brang ba'i skyes
NK127(jo)001:5333: pa dang bud med dang khye'u dang bu mo rnams
NK127(jo)001:5334: las srog chags nyis brgyas kyang bla med rdzogs byang
NK127(jo)001:5336: lha dang mi drug cus chos kyi mig rnam par dag pa thob bo //
NK127(jo)001:5337: bu mo gser mchog 'od dpal gyis yan lag lngas
NK127(jo)001:5338: phyag 'tshal te bslab pa'i gzhi rnams blangs shing lhag
NK127(jo)001:5339: pa'i bsam pas bla med byang chub tu sems bskyed
NK127(jo)001:5340: nas nyon mongs pa rang bzhin ma grub par shes
NK127(jo)001:5341: pa'i sgo nas sems can 'dul ba'i thabs la brtson
NK127(jo)001:5342: par dam bcas shing byang chub sems dpa'i nyon mongs
NK127(jo)001:5343: pa ma mchis pa las brtsams te 'jam dpal la
NK127(jo)001:5344: dris shing / 'jam dpal gyis kyang stong pa nyid
NK127(jo)001:5345: la rtog cing thabs mkhas pa dang ldan pa'i chos
NK127(jo)001:5346: zab mo bstan pa de'i tshe bcom ldan 'das bya
NK127(jo)001:5347: rgod kyi phung po'i ri ngos kyi sman ljongs zhig
NK127(jo)001:5348: na kun dga' bo dang thabs cig ring du 'chag
NK127(jo)001:5349: pas 'chag cing bzhugs pas 'jam dpal la legs so
NK127(jo)001:5350: byin pa'i sgra des stong chen po'i 'jig rten 'dir
NK127(jo)001:5351: khyab cing sa chen po rnam pa drug tu g.yos
NK127(jo)001:5352: pas lha klu gnod sbyin sogs bskul te bcom ldan
NK127(jo)001:5353: 'das kyi drung du 'dus nas legs so'i sgra yis
NK127(jo)001:5354: 'jig rten 'dir khyab cing go bar mdzad pa de
NK127(jo)001:5355: su la stsal zhes zhus pa na /
NK127(jo)001:5356: 'jam dpal gyis bu mo gser mchog la chos bstan
NK127(jo)001:5357: pa la'o zhes gsungs pas lha sogs thams cad 'jam
NK127(jo)001:5358: dpal gyi drung du 'dus pa dang rgyal po ma
NK127(jo)001:5359: skyes dgra sogs 'dus pa dag gis bu mo gser
NK127(jo)001:5360: mchog 'od dpal 'dod chags kyi kun nas sdang ba
NK127(jo)001:5361: bral te dbang po zhi bar mthong nas de la
NK127(jo)001:5362: sngar ltar su yang chags par mi byed par mthong
NK127(jo)001:5363: nas / 'jam dpal gyis bu mo khyod kyi nyon
NK127(jo)001:5364: mongs pa de gang du bzhag ces dris pa la
NK127(jo)001:5366: nyon mongs pa thams cad chos kyi dbyings la gnas pas ma bskyed ma bkag ma bsgyur ba ste /
NK127(jo)001:5367: nyon mongs pa'i rang bzhin gang yin pa de bdag gis rtogs so //
NK127(jo)001:5368: zhes sogs dang 'jam dpal gyis kyang nyon mongs pa'i rang bzhin byang chub tu bstan pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:5369: bu mo gser mchog 'od dpal gyis kyang rang gi
NK127(jo)001:5370: dge rtsa bsags pa'i shes rab kyis gzugs chu nang
NK127(jo)001:5371: gi zla ba ltar blta ba sogs chos bstan pas
NK127(jo)001:5372: srog chags khri nyis stong gis bla med byang chub
NK127(jo)001:5373: tu sems bskyed / lha dang mi lnga brgyas mi skye ba'i chos la bzod pa thob /
NK127(jo)001:5374: srog chags sum khri nyis stong gis chos kyi mig dag pa thob /
NK127(jo)001:5375: bu mo de yang chos nyan pa'i mchog tu dga'
NK127(jo)001:5376: bas chos rnams la rjes su mthun pa'i bzod pa
NK127(jo)001:5377: thob par gyur nas 'jam dpal la rab tu dbyung
NK127(jo)001:5380: sring mo mgo'i skra 'breg pa ni byang chub sems dpa'i rab tu byung ba ma yin gyi /
NK127(jo)001:5381: sems can thams cad kyi nyon mongs pa bcad pa'i
NK127(jo)001:5382: phyir brtson pa byang chub sems dpa'i rab tu byung
NK127(jo)001:5383: ba yin no zhes sogs bdag don la ma chags
NK127(jo)001:5384: par gzhan don byed pa byang chub sems dpa'i rab
NK127(jo)001:5385: tu byung ba'i tshul yin par bstan zhing /
NK127(jo)001:5386: bu mo khyod shing rta zhon la tshong dpon gyi
NK127(jo)001:5387: bu 'jigs byin la snying brtse ba'i phyir smin par
NK127(jo)001:5388: gyis dang de nyid khyod kyi rab byung dang bsnyen
NK127(jo)001:5390: de ltar chos bstan pa de yang tshong dpon gyi
NK127(jo)001:5391: bu 'jigs byin sogs re shig snod du ma gyur
NK127(jo)001:5392: pa dag gis ni cung zad kyang mi thos par
NK127(jo)001:5394: de nas skye bo phal mo che des 'di snyam du /
NK127(jo)001:5395: chags bral dang chags bcas gnyis lhan cig gnas su
NK127(jo)001:5396: ji ltar rung snyam pa'i rtog pa bu mo des
NK127(jo)001:5398: grogs po dag 'dod chags dang bral ba'i byang chub
NK127(jo)001:5399: sems dpa' 'dod chags dang bcas pa'i sems can rnams
NK127(jo)001:5400: dang lhan cig gnas kyang kha na ma tho ba
NK127(jo)001:5401: med la / 'dod chags dang bcas pa'i sems can rnams kyang 'dul bar byed do //
NK127(jo)001:5402: de bzhin du zhe sdang sogs la sbyar te nyon
NK127(jo)001:5403: mongs pa can 'dul ba'i tshul bstan nas 'jam dpal
NK127(jo)001:5404: gyi zhabs la phyag byas te shing rta la zhon
NK127(jo)001:5405: nas 'jigs byin dang lhan cig tu skyed mos tshal
NK127(jo)001:5406: du song nas rtse bar byed pa las /
NK127(jo)001:5407: bu mo des 'jigs byin gyi pang du sngas byas
NK127(jo)001:5408: te rang gi lus rnyis shing 'chi bar gyur nas
NK127(jo)001:5409: myags la dri nga ba dang bu ga rnams nas
NK127(jo)001:5410: khrag dang rnag dang dri nga ba sogs mi gtsang
NK127(jo)001:5411: ba'i rang bzhin bstan pas tshong dpon gyi bu 'jigs
NK127(jo)001:5412: phyin sngangs shing skrag pa na 'jam dpal gyi mthus
NK127(jo)001:5413: shing ljon pa las dbugs dbyung zhing sangs rgyas kyi
NK127(jo)001:5414: drung du 'deng bar bskul ba dang 'dul ba'i dus
NK127(jo)001:5415: la bab par gzigs nas de bzhin gshegs pas kyang
NK127(jo)001:5416: 'od zer bkye bas snang bar byas te ro myags
NK127(jo)001:5417: pa de bor nas sangs rgyas kyi zhabs drung du
NK127(jo)001:5418: lhags te skyabs su dong zhing rgyal bas chos bstan
NK127(jo)001:5419: pas chos rnams la rjes su mthun pa'i bzod pa
NK127(jo)001:5420: skyes so // de ltar tshong dpon gyi bu dul
NK127(jo)001:5421: par rig nas bu mo gser mchog 'od dpal lha'i
NK127(jo)001:5422: bu mo lnga brgya tsam gyis bskor te sil snyan
NK127(jo)001:5423: dang glu dbyangs bcas bcom ldan 'das kyi drung du
NK127(jo)001:5424: phyin pa la bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa
NK127(jo)001:5425: skyes so // / smad 'tshong ma'i bu mo gser
NK127(jo)001:5426: mchog 'od dpal 'di sngon 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur
NK127(jo)001:5427: pas rdzogs pa'i byang chub 'dzin du bcug ste 'dis
NK127(jo)001:5428: 'di las rjes su mthun pa'i bzod pa thob la
NK127(jo)001:5429: skyes so // / / tshong dpon gyi bu 'jigs
NK127(jo)001:5430: byin 'di ngas sngon bla med byang chub 'dzin du
NK127(jo)001:5432: nga las chos thos nas rjes su mthun pa'i bzod
NK127(jo)001:5433: skyes so // / / bcug ste / pa thob
NK127(jo)001:5434: bo // bu mo gser mchog 'di bskal pa 'bum
NK127(jo)001:5435: phrag dgu bcu rtsa gnyis 'das pa'i 'og tu bskal
NK127(jo)001:5436: pa rin chen 'byung ba zhes bya ba la 'jig
NK127(jo)001:5437: rten gyi khams rin chen 'byung ba zhes bya bar
NK127(jo)001:5438: de bzhin gshegs pa rin chen 'od ces bya bar
NK127(jo)001:5439: 'gyur la zhing de'i longs spyod ni sum cu rtsa
NK127(jo)001:5441: de na byang chub sems dpa'i rin po che ma gtogs par rin chen gzhan mi 'byung ngo //
NK127(jo)001:5442: de bzhin gshegs pa de'i tshe tshad ni dpag tu med par 'gyur ro //
NK127(jo)001:5443: de sangs rgyas nas 'jigs byin 'di byang chub sems
NK127(jo)001:5444: dpa' yon tan rin chen 'od ces bya ba de
NK127(jo)001:5445: bzhin gshegs pa de'i chos mdzod 'dzin par byed do
NK127(jo)001:5446: // de bzhin gshegs pa des 'di nga'i 'og tu
NK127(jo)001:5447: 'tshang rgya'o zhes lung ston te 'di ni de bzhin
NK127(jo)001:5448: gshegs pa rin chen 'od 'phro zhes bya bar 'gyur
NK127(jo)001:5449: ro zhes lung bstan pas 'jig rten gyi khams rnam
NK127(jo)001:5450: pa drug tu g.yos shing snang ba chen pos khyab
NK127(jo)001:5451: la srog chags brgya stong gis bla med byang chub
NK127(jo)001:5452: tu sems bskyed par gyur to //
NK127(jo)001:5453: zhes pa 'di lta bu'i tshul gyis 'dod chags dang
NK127(jo)001:5454: ldan pa rnams 'dul ba'i thabs mkhas bsam gyis mi
NK127(jo)001:5455: khyab pa dang / yang 'jam dpal rnam par 'phrul pa'i mdo las /
NK127(jo)001:5456: bcom ldan 'das rgyal bu rgyal byed kyi tshal mgon
NK127(jo)001:5457: med zas sbyin gyi kun dga' ra ba na 'khor
NK127(jo)001:5458: mang po dang lhan cig bzhugs pa'i tshe /
NK127(jo)001:5459: lha'i bu 'od mang pos 'jam dpal la byang chub
NK127(jo)001:5460: sems dpa' rnams kyi bdud kyi las gang yin zhes
NK127(jo)001:5462: lha'i bu ji tsam du las rnams 'byung ba de tsam du bdud kyi las so //
NK127(jo)001:5463: ji tsam du smon pa dang log par 'dzin pa dang mchog tu 'dzin pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:5464: ji tsam du 'dod pa dang 'du shes pa dang
NK127(jo)001:5465: rlom sems pa dang yongs su rtog pa de tsam
NK127(jo)001:5467: gzhan yang byang chub kyi sems dang sbyin pa sogs
NK127(jo)001:5468: la mngon par zhen pa sogs bdud kyi las su
NK127(jo)001:5469: bstan cing thabs shes kyi sbyor ba yang dag phul
NK127(jo)001:5470: gyi chos bstan pas lha'i bu brgyad stong ni bla
NK127(jo)001:5471: med byang chub tu sems skyes so //
NK127(jo)001:5472: byang chub sems dpa' lnga stong ni mi skye ba'i chos la bzod pa thob bo //
NK127(jo)001:5473: bcom ldan 'das kyis 'jam dpal la legs so byin no //
NK127(jo)001:5474: lha'i bu 'od mang pos 'jam dpal khyod de bzhin gshegs pas legs so byin pas dga' 'am /
NK127(jo)001:5475: 'jam dpal gyis sprul pas sprul pa la legs so
NK127(jo)001:5476: byin pa ltar rang bzhin med pas chags pa med
NK127(jo)001:5477: pa sogs kyi chos zab mo bstan pa'i tshe /
NK127(jo)001:5479: 'jam dpal gtam 'di lta bu brjod pa'i tshe mig
NK127(jo)001:5480: gis mi rtsol bar bya ba'i phyir bdud sdig can
NK127(jo)001:5481: 'dir mi 'ong ba ni ngo mtshar to //
NK127(jo)001:5482: tshig de skad smras nas ring po ma lon pa
NK127(jo)001:5483: de'i mod la bdud sdig can steng gi bar snang
NK127(jo)001:5484: la sprin chen po 'khrugs par mngon par sprul nas
NK127(jo)001:5485: sgra chen po'i nga ro byung ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:5486: 'khor de skrag nas skad kyi nga ro 'di lta bu su zhig gi yin snyam mo //
NK127(jo)001:5487: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis 'jam dpal la bka' stsal pa /
NK127(jo)001:5488: 'jam dpal khyod kyis bdud sdig can gyi 'gyur ba mthong ngam /
NK127(jo)001:5489: gsol pa bcom ldan 'das mthong lags so //
NK127(jo)001:5490: bde bar gshegs pa mthong lags so //
NK127(jo)001:5491: de'i tshe 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pas bdud sdig
NK127(jo)001:5492: to can bcing ba dam pos bcings te sa'i steng
NK127(jo)001:5493: du lhung bar byas pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:5494: bdud kyis bdag bcing ba dam pos bcings so zhes sgra 'byin pa la 'jam dpal gyis smras pa /
NK127(jo)001:5495: sdig can bcing ba 'di bas ches dam pa gzhan yod de /
NK127(jo)001:5496: des khyod rtag tu bcings kyang khyod kyis khong du ma chud do //
NK127(jo)001:5497: gang zhe na nga'o snyam pa'i nga rgyal dang phyin
NK127(jo)001:5498: ci log dang sred pa dang lta ba'i 'ching ba
NK127(jo)001:5499: de lta bus khyod bcings kyang khyod kyis mi shes
NK127(jo)001:5501: 'jam dpal thongs shig dang bdag gi gnas su 'agro'o //
NK127(jo)001:5502: yang bdud kyi las mi bya'o //
NK127(jo)001:5504: sdig can khyod sangs rgyas kyi mdzad pa bya dgos na ci'i phyir btang /
NK127(jo)001:5506: bdag sangs rgyas kyi chos rnams la bar chad byed
NK127(jo)001:5507: par zhugs pa yin na bdag gis sangs rgyas kyi
NK127(jo)001:5510: sdig can gang sangs rgyas kyi mdzad pa bdud la
NK127(jo)001:5511: byed du gzhug pa 'di ni byang chub sems dpa'
NK127(jo)001:5512: rnams kyi thabs dang shes rab kyi shes pa rnam
NK127(jo)001:5513: par sprul pa'o // gang sangs rgyas kyis sangs rgyas
NK127(jo)001:5514: kyi mdzad pa mdzad pa 'di ni ngo mtshar ma
NK127(jo)001:5515: par sprul pa'o // yin te / bdud sangs rgyas
NK127(jo)001:5516: kyi mdzad pa byed pa 'di ni rab tu ngo
NK127(jo)001:5517: par sprul pa'o // yin te / mtshar ro //
NK127(jo)001:5518: de nas 'jam dpal gyis de'i tshe bdud sangs rgyas
NK127(jo)001:5519: kyi gzugs dang ldan pa seng ge'i khri la 'dug
NK127(jo)001:5520: cing sangs rgyas kyi spobs pa dang ldan par byin
NK127(jo)001:5521: par sprul pa'o // yin te / mtshar ro //
NK127(jo)001:5522: gyis brlabs so // de nas bdud sdig can gyis
NK127(jo)001:5523: tshe dang ldan pa dag ci 'dod pa kho bo
NK127(jo)001:5524: la dris dang lung bstan pas sems rangs par bya'o
NK127(jo)001:5526: gnas brtan 'od srung chen pos bdud la smras pa /
NK127(jo)001:5527: sdig can dge slong rnal 'byor spyod pa'i 'ching ba gang yin /
NK127(jo)001:5529: btsun pa 'od srung chen po bsam gtan gyi ro myong bar byed pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:5530: zhi gnas de la chags pa sogs dang /
NK127(jo)001:5531: mya ngan las 'das pa la snying por 'du shes pa /
NK127(jo)001:5532: 'khor ba la bsal bar 'du shes pa 'di dag ni rnal 'byor spyod pa'i 'ching ba'o //
NK127(jo)001:5533: de ci'i phyir zhe na lta bar song ba bsal
NK127(jo)001:5534: nas stong pa nyid bsgom par bya ba ma yin
NK127(jo)001:5535: gyi / lta bar stong pa nyid stong pa nyid do //
NK127(jo)001:5536: mtshan ma bsal nas mtshan med sgom pa ma yin gyi /
NK127(jo)001:5537: mtshan ma'i ngo bo nyid mtshan ma med pa'o //
NK127(jo)001:5538: smon lam bsal nas smon pa med pa nyid bsgom par bya ba ma yin gyi /
NK127(jo)001:5539: smon lam gyi ngo bo nyid smon pa med pa'o //
NK127(jo)001:5540: 'khor ba bsal nas mya ngan las 'das pa bsgom par bya ba ma yin gyi /
NK127(jo)001:5541: 'khor ba dmigs pa nyid mya ngan las 'das pa'o //
NK127(jo)001:5542: btsun pa 'od srung chen po mya ngan las 'das
NK127(jo)001:5543: pa ni 'du shes dang rlom sems dang mtshan ma
NK127(jo)001:5544: la dmigs pa thams cad la mi spyod pa ste
NK127(jo)001:5545: / skye ba dang 'jig pa dang zad pa las ma yin gyi /
NK127(jo)001:5546: rang bzhin gyis skye ba med pa nyid mya ngan las 'das pa'o //
NK127(jo)001:5547: bstan pa 'di bshad pa na dge slong lnga brgya
NK127(jo)001:5548: len pa med par zag pa rnams las sems rnam
NK127(jo)001:5549: par grol lo // gnas brtan rab 'byor gyis dge
NK127(jo)001:5550: slong de dag la tshe dang ldan pa dag sus
NK127(jo)001:5553: gang thob pa med pa mngon par sangs rgyas pa yang med pas so //
NK127(jo)001:5555: btul ba de ji lta bu /
NK127(jo)001:5557: ji ltar gnas pa nyid kyi phyir cung zad kyang khrid pa yang med /
NK127(jo)001:5559: ji ltar gnas pa bzhin du shes pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:5562: mnyam pa nyid du shes pa de ltar bdag cag btul to //
NK127(jo)001:5563: dge slong de dag gis bstan pa 'di bshad pa
NK127(jo)001:5564: na lha'i bu stong nyis brgya chos rnams la chos
NK127(jo)001:5565: kyi mig rdul med cing dri ma dang bral ba
NK127(jo)001:5567: de nas rab 'byor gyis bdud la smras pa /
NK127(jo)001:5568: ji ltar na dge slong sbyin gnas yin /
NK127(jo)001:5570: rab 'byor nam len pa yang med nod pa yang
NK127(jo)001:5571: med la dad cing dad pa thams cad las kyang
NK127(jo)001:5574: sh+aa ri'i bus bdud la smras pa /
NK127(jo)001:5575: bcom ldan 'das kyis ting 'dzin 'khrugs pa med par gsungs pa gang yin /
NK127(jo)001:5577: ting 'dzin gang la gnas nas shin tu zad pa'i phyir zad pa yang zad par mi byed /
NK127(jo)001:5578: rang bzhin gyis ma skyes pha'i phyir ma skyes pa yang mi skyed /
NK127(jo)001:5579: myong ba med par yang myong par mi byed de /
NK127(jo)001:5580: chos thams cad rang bzhin gyis snyoms par zhugs par shes la /
NK127(jo)001:5581: shes nas tshor ba thams cad 'gog pa la snyoms par 'jug cing mnyam par yang mthong la /
NK127(jo)001:5582: cung zad mthong ba yang med /
NK127(jo)001:5583: ma mthong ba yang med pa 'di ni bcom ldan
NK127(jo)001:5584: 'das kyis ting 'dzin 'khrugs pa med par gsungs pa'o
NK127(jo)001:5585: // moong gal gyi bus smras pa /
NK127(jo)001:5586: ji ltar dge slong sems thams cad la dbang thob pa yin /
NK127(jo)001:5588: chos thams cad la sems rnam par grol ba'i mtshan nyid du shes la /
NK127(jo)001:5589: der mngon zhen med cing sems gzod nas rnam par grol bas 'ching grol du mi byed /
NK127(jo)001:5590: sems gzugs med pa dang 'dzin pa dang gnas pa
NK127(jo)001:5591: med pas chos thams cad gzugs med pa dang 'dzin
NK127(jo)001:5592: pa dang gnas pa med par shes shing /
NK127(jo)001:5593: sems kyi ngo bo nyid kyi rang bzhin gyis chos
NK127(jo)001:5594: thams cad chos kyi dbyings su shes la chos kyi
NK127(jo)001:5595: dbyings kyi ngo bo nyid kyi rang bzhin gyis gzhan
NK127(jo)001:5596: dring la mi 'jog pa'i dbang thob pa ni mos
NK127(jo)001:5597: pa'i rdzu 'phrul dang ldan pa ste sems thams cad
NK127(jo)001:5598: la dbang thob pa yin no //
NK127(jo)001:5600: ji ltar na dge slong yongs su dag pas chos ston pa yin /
NK127(jo)001:5602: dge slong gang gis gzhan las chos kun shes kyang
NK127(jo)001:5603: gzhan dang gzhan ma yin pa'i sems la mngon zhen
NK127(jo)001:5604: yang med / chos thams cad kyang sgro btags par yang ston /
NK127(jo)001:5605: yi ge dang skad dang dbyangs dang tshig gi lam thams cad brag cha lta bur shes /
NK127(jo)001:5606: chos nyan pa rnams sgyu ma'i skyes bu ltar mthong /
NK127(jo)001:5607: gang gi lus kyang chu zla 'dra bar mthong /
NK127(jo)001:5608: nyon mongs pa thams cad kyang yongs su rtog pa las byung bar shes /
NK127(jo)001:5612: thob par bya ba'i phyir yang chos mi ston /
NK127(jo)001:5613: so so yang dag rig pa bzhi la dbang thob cing /
NK127(jo)001:5614: so so zhes bya ba la yang re ba med la zang zing med par chos ston te /
NK127(jo)001:5615: rang gi sems rang bzhin gyis yongs su dag pas
NK127(jo)001:5616: sems can kun gyi sems kyang de ltar shes nas
NK127(jo)001:5617: phung po'i bdud la dben par mthong /
NK127(jo)001:5618: nyon mongs pa'i bdud la bcos mar 'du shes /
NK127(jo)001:5619: 'chi bdag gi bdud la ma skyes pa dang mi skye bar gnas pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:5620: lha'i bu'i bdud la g.yo ba dang rlom sems thams
NK127(jo)001:5621: cad dang bral bar gyur pa de lta bu ni
NK127(jo)001:5622: yongs su dag par chos ston pa yin no //
NK127(jo)001:5624: sdig can ji ltar na dge slong 'dul ba 'dzin pa yin /
NK127(jo)001:5626: btsun pa nye bar 'khor dge slong gang gis nam chos thams cad shin tu dul bar shes te /
NK127(jo)001:5627: nyes pa rnams kyi sngon mtha' dben bar shes la nyes pa byung ba rnams kyi 'gyod pa sel /
NK127(jo)001:5628: glo bur gyi nyon mongs pa rnams sprin dang chu zla ltar rang bzhin ma grub par shes nas /
NK127(jo)001:5629: nyon mongs pa yang mi sel /
NK127(jo)001:5630: nyon mongs med pa yang mi sgrub par /
NK127(jo)001:5631: tshul min yid byed mun pa dang choms rkun la
NK127(jo)001:5632: sogs pa dang 'dra ba rnams tshul bzhin brtags pas
NK127(jo)001:5633: gang du 'gro ba dang gnas pa med par shes
NK127(jo)001:5634: shing sems can nyon mongs can la snying rje zhing
NK127(jo)001:5635: / bdag dang sems can med pa mngon du gyur
NK127(jo)001:5636: na 'dul ba 'dzin pa yang dag pa zhes bya'o
NK127(jo)001:5637: / // de ltar nyan thos de dag gi dri
NK127(jo)001:5638: ba la bdud kyis gtan la phab pa'i lan bstan
NK127(jo)001:5639: pas de kun sems rangs par byas so //
NK127(jo)001:5640: de nas lha'i bu mtshams bzang gis bdud la smras pa /
NK127(jo)001:5641: 'jam dpal gyis byang chub sems dpa'i bdud las bshad zin gyis khyod kyang spobs par gyis shig /
NK127(jo)001:5643: rnal 'byor spyod pa rnam par grol bar 'dod cing
NK127(jo)001:5644: 'khor bas skrag pa rnams la bsten cing bsnyen bkur
NK127(jo)001:5645: byed pa ni bdud kyi las so //
NK127(jo)001:5646: stong pa nyid la rtog cing sems can yal bar 'dor ba yang bdud kyi las so //
NK127(jo)001:5647: 'dus ma byas la so sor rtog cing 'dus byas
NK127(jo)001:5648: kyi dge bas yongs su skyo ba yang bdud kyi
NK127(jo)001:5649: las so // zhes sogs bdud kyi las yang dag
NK127(jo)001:5650: phul nyi shu bstan pa la bcom ldan 'das kyis
NK127(jo)001:5651: legs so zhes byin te gang dag bdud kyi las
NK127(jo)001:5652: 'di dag thos nas spong ba de dag byams pa
NK127(jo)001:5653: chen po la sogs pa byang chub yongs su smin
NK127(jo)001:5654: par byed pa'i chos nyi shu thob par gsungs so
NK127(jo)001:5655: las so // // lha'i bu mtshams bzangs kyis bdud
NK127(jo)001:5656: sdig can khyod la bcom ldan 'das kyis legs so
NK127(jo)001:5657: gnang ba ni rnyed pa legs par rnyed do zhes
NK127(jo)001:5658: las so // // smras pa dang / bdud kyis smras pa /
NK127(jo)001:5659: kho bos ci zhig legs par rnyed de mi la
NK127(jo)001:5660: 'byung po babs pas bstan pa bzhin du kho bo
NK127(jo)001:5661: yang 'jam dpal gyis byin gyis brlabs pa'i mthus ston
NK127(jo)001:5662: gyi rang gi rtsal gyis ma yin no //
NK127(jo)001:5664: sdig can khyod sangs rgyas kyi gzugs dang spobs pa
NK127(jo)001:5665: ldan pas seng ge'i khri la 'dug ste chos ston
NK127(jo)001:5666: pas dga' 'am / bdud kyis smras pa /
NK127(jo)001:5667: khyod kyis ni kho bo brgyan par mthong ba lta
NK127(jo)001:5668: na kho bos ni bdag bcing ba dam pos bcings
NK127(jo)001:5669: par shes so // lha'i bus smras pa /
NK127(jo)001:5670: sdig can 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa la bzod
NK127(jo)001:5671: par gsol cig dang de nas gtong bar 'gyur ro
NK127(jo)001:5672: // de nas 'jam dpal gyi mthus bdud kyis smras pa /
NK127(jo)001:5673: byang chub sems dpa' chen po theg chen la zhugs pa rnams la bzod par gsol mi dgos te /
NK127(jo)001:5674: de dag la 'khrugs pa dang khro ba med pa'i phyir ro //
NK127(jo)001:5675: lha'i bus byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyi bzod pa ci 'dra zhes dris pa la /
