NK127(jo)001:5676: bdud kyis bcos ma ma yin pas bsam pa'i bzod pa sogs bcu gnyis bstan no //
NK127(jo)001:5677: de nas lha'i bus sdig can khyod gal te bkrol na dga' bar 'gyur ram /
NK127(jo)001:5679: kho bo dga' ste mchog tu daga'o //
NK127(jo)001:5680: de'i tshe lha'i bu mtshams bzangs kyis 'jam dpal la
NK127(jo)001:5681: bdud sdig can thongs shig dang rang gi gnas su
NK127(jo)001:5682: 'agro'o // 'jam dpal gyis bdud la smras pa /
NK127(jo)001:5683: sdig can khyod su zhig gis bcings /
NK127(jo)001:5686: 'jam dpal bdag ni sus bcings mi shes so //
NK127(jo)001:5688: sdig can khyod bcings pa med pa la bcings par
NK127(jo)001:5689: 'du shes pa de bzhin du byis pa so so'i
NK127(jo)001:5690: skye bo thams cad kyang mi rtag pa la rtag
NK127(jo)001:5691: par 'du shes / de bzhin du bdag dang bde
NK127(jo)001:5692: ba dang sdug pa dang phung po lngar 'du shes
NK127(jo)001:5693: par 'du shes / so // sdig can khyod dgrol na gang nas dgrol /
NK127(jo)001:5695: bdag ni gang las kyang mi dgrol lo //
NK127(jo)001:5697: sdig can de bzhin du gang dag rnam par grol
NK127(jo)001:5698: ba yang yang dag min pa'i 'du shes yongs su
NK127(jo)001:5699: shes pa ma gtogs par gang las kyang rnam par
NK127(jo)001:5701: de dag yongs su shes pas rnam par grol ba zhes bya'o //
NK127(jo)001:5702: de nas 'jam dpal gyis byin rlabs de bsdus pa
NK127(jo)001:5703: dang sdig can de'ang rang gi gzugs dang ldan par
NK127(jo)001:5705: 'od srung chen pos bdud la khyod kyis sangs rgyas
NK127(jo)001:5706: kyi mdzad pa byas pa legs so zhes smras pa
NK127(jo)001:5708: 'di ni kho bo'i yul ma yin gyi 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa'i yul du blta'o //
NK127(jo)001:5709: de nas lha'i bu mtshams bzangs kyis 'jam dpal la smras pa /
NK127(jo)001:5710: sangs rgyas kyi mdzad pa gang du btsal bar bya /
NK127(jo)001:5712: lha'i bu sangs rgyas kyi mdzad pa ni sems can
NK127(jo)001:5713: thams cad kyi nyon mongs pa rnams su btsal bar
NK127(jo)001:5714: bya ste / sems can nyon mongs pas gzir ba
NK127(jo)001:5715: med na sangs rgyas kyis kyang mdzad pa mi 'byung
NK127(jo)001:5716: bya ste / ba'i phyir ro // zhes dang skye
NK127(jo)001:5717: rga na 'chi spang ba'i don du sangs rgyas 'byung
NK127(jo)001:5718: bya ste / ba'i phyir ro // ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:5719: de bzhin gshegs pas byang chub brnyes nas chos gang
NK127(jo)001:5720: yang bskyed pa yang med bkag pa med de chos
NK127(jo)001:5721: gang yang skye 'gag med pa'i phyir /
NK127(jo)001:5722: sangs rgyas 'byung ba zhes bya ba ngo bo nyid kyis skye ba med pa'i don yin pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:5723: gang dmigs pa'i lta bas chos gang la yang mi
NK127(jo)001:5724: spyod pa byang chub sems dpa'i bsam pa phun sum
NK127(jo)001:5725: tshogs pa dang / nang dang phyi'i chos rnams la
NK127(jo)001:5726: mi chags pa lhag pa'i bsam pa phun sum tshogs
NK127(jo)001:5727: tshogs pa dang / pa dang / nyon mongs pa
NK127(jo)001:5728: thams cad kyang 'dor la sems can yongs su mi
NK127(jo)001:5729: gtong ba sbyin pa phun sum tshogs pa yin pa
NK127(jo)001:5730: tshogs pa dang / pa dang / sogs bstan to
NK127(jo)001:5731: // de nas bdud sdig can sdug bsngal zhing yid
NK127(jo)001:5732: mi bde ste gdong mchi mas gang nas 'di skad
NK127(jo)001:5733: tshogs pa dang / pa dang / sogs bstan to
NK127(jo)001:5734: // du / gang na chos kyi rnam grangs 'di
NK127(jo)001:5735: spyod pa de na bdud rnams kyi skabs med de
NK127(jo)001:5736: tshogs pa dang / pa dang / sogs bstan to
NK127(jo)001:5738: bdud kyi las thams cad bkag par 'gyur ro zhes
NK127(jo)001:5739: smras nas de nyid du mi snang bar gyur ro
NK127(jo)001:5740: tshogs pa dang / pa dang / sogs bstan to
NK127(jo)001:5741: // du / / // de ltar sdang zhing phrag
NK127(jo)001:5742: dog chen pos bskul ba nga rgyal dang ldan pa'i
NK127(jo)001:5743: bdud sdig can kyang chos la bar chad bya ma
NK127(jo)001:5744: tshogs pa dang / pa dang / sogs bstan to
NK127(jo)001:5746: tu zab pa'i theg pa chen po bstan pas sangs
NK127(jo)001:5747: rgyas kyi mdzad pa sgrub pa 'di lta bu'i byang
NK127(jo)001:5748: chub sems dpa'i thabs mkhas dang stobs bsam gyis mi
NK127(jo)001:5749: tshogs pa dang / pa dang / sogs bstan to
NK127(jo)001:5751: yang 'jam dpal gnas pa zhes bya ba theg pa
NK127(jo)001:5753: 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa 'chag cing dge slong
NK127(jo)001:5754: lnga brgya po rnams kyi gnas khang nas gnas khang
NK127(jo)001:5755: du byung ste sh+aa ri'i bu'i gnas khang du phyin
NK127(jo)001:5756: nas de dben par bsam gtan byed pa mthong ste
NK127(jo)001:5757: sh+aa ri'i bu la bsam gtan byed pa las gleng
NK127(jo)001:5758: bslangs te chos thams cad dmigs su med pa'i de
NK127(jo)001:5759: kho na nyid zab mo bshad pa na 'khor de'i
NK127(jo)001:5760: dge slong lnga brgya bo stan las langs nas 'di
NK127(jo)001:5761: skad ces 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur ba la mi
NK127(jo)001:5762: blta mi nyan phyogs gang na gnas pa'i phyogs de
NK127(jo)001:5764: ci'i phyir na ston pa mngon sum du gyur bzhin
NK127(jo)001:5765: du 'jam dpal 'dis kun nyon dang rnam byang gcig
NK127(jo)001:5766: tu ston pa chos ma yin pa smra'o snyam nas
NK127(jo)001:5767: 'phya smod mi snyan pa zer zhes dong ngo //
NK127(jo)001:5769: dge slong lnga brgya pos de ltar smras pa ni legs par smras pa ste /
NK127(jo)001:5770: de ci'i phyir na 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa
NK127(jo)001:5771: ni yod pa ma yin te dmigs su med na
NK127(jo)001:5772: des blta ba dang mnyan par mi nus so //
NK127(jo)001:5773: de dmigs su med na de'i gnas kyang dmigs su
NK127(jo)001:5774: med pas de gnas pa'i phyogs kyang bsten par bya
NK127(jo)001:5776: zhes smras pas dge slong de dag gis thos nas slar log ste /
NK127(jo)001:5777: 'di skad du 'jam dpal bdag cag ni khyod kyis bstan pa de ltar mi shes so //
NK127(jo)001:5779: dge slong dag legs so legs so //
NK127(jo)001:5780: de lta bur ston pa ni ston pa'i nyan thos rnams kyi bya ba ste /
NK127(jo)001:5781: dge slong dag 'di la kun shes pa dang rnam par shes pa bya ba med de /
NK127(jo)001:5782: chos kyi dbyings 'di ni gnas pa nyid do zhes
NK127(jo)001:5783: dang de dmigs su med pa nyid la sogs par
NK127(jo)001:5784: bshad pas dge slong bzhi brgya ni len pa med
NK127(jo)001:5785: par zag pa rnams las sems rnam par grol lo
NK127(jo)001:5786: // dge slong brgya ni sems cher 'khrugs nas lus
NK127(jo)001:5787: de nyid kyis dmyal ba chen po ngu 'bod du
NK127(jo)001:5788: // lhung ngo // de nas sh+aa ri'i bus 'jam
NK127(jo)001:5789: dpal la khyod sems can rjes su srung ba'i chos
NK127(jo)001:5790: mi ston pas dge slong brgya po de dag chud
NK127(jo)001:5791: zos te ngo mtshar byas so zhes smras pa dang
NK127(jo)001:5792: // lhung ngo // / bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
NK127(jo)001:5793: sh+aa ri'i bu khyod de skad ma zer cig /
NK127(jo)001:5794: dge slong brgya po de dag dmyal ba chen po
NK127(jo)001:5795: ngu 'bod du reg pa thang gcig reg nas dga'
NK127(jo)001:5797: de dag gis chos 'di ma thos su zin na
NK127(jo)001:5798: gdon mi za bar sems can dmyal bar 'gro zhing
NK127(jo)001:5799: las de zad nas mir skye bar 'gyur ba zhig
NK127(jo)001:5800: na chos 'di la brten nas bskal pa sems can
NK127(jo)001:5801: dmyal bar myong ba'i las de yang cung zad cig
NK127(jo)001:5802: myong bas byang nas byams pa'i 'dus pa thog mar
NK127(jo)001:5803: dgra bcom pa thob par 'gyur bas na /
NK127(jo)001:5804: chos kyi rnam grangs 'di lta bu soms nyi dang bcas par thos pa mchog yin gyi /
NK127(jo)001:5805: bsam gzugs kyi snyoms 'jug thob pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:5806: tshad med bzhis ni de lta ma yin te /
NK127(jo)001:5807: chos kyi rnam grangs 'di lta bu ma thos par
NK127(jo)001:5808: 'khor ba las yongs su mi grol ba'i phyir ro
NK127(jo)001:5809: // zhes gsungs pas sh+aa ri'i bus 'jam dpal la
NK127(jo)001:5810: sems can yongs su smin pa'i phyir chos kyi rnam
NK127(jo)001:5811: grangs 'di legs par bshad pa ngo mtshar to //
NK127(jo)001:5812: zhes byas pa na 'jam dpal gyis smras pa /
NK127(jo)001:5813: de bzhin nyid dang chos kyi dbyings dang sems can
NK127(jo)001:5814: gyi khams ni 'phel 'bri med pa dang kun nyon
NK127(jo)001:5815: dang rnam byang ma yin te /
NK127(jo)001:5816: dmigs su med pa gang la 'di mi gnas pa
NK127(jo)001:5817: 'gag pa med pa de ni byang chub dang thar
NK127(jo)001:5818: pa dang mya ngan las 'das pa'o zhes smras pa
NK127(jo)001:5819: na / bcom ldan 'das kyis kyang 'jam dpal gzhon
NK127(jo)001:5820: nur gyur pas ji skad bstan pa de bzhin du
NK127(jo)001:5821: na / bstan cing / chos thams cad ming gis
NK127(jo)001:5822: gdags pa tsam ste dmigs su med par bstan pas
NK127(jo)001:5823: srog chags 'bum chos mig rdul bral dri ma med
NK127(jo)001:5824: na / bstan cing / pa thob / dge slong
NK127(jo)001:5825: lnga brgya zag pa thams cad las sems rnam par
NK127(jo)001:5826: na / bstan cing / pa thob / grol /
NK127(jo)001:5827: gzugs na spyod pa'i lha'i bu brgyad khris bla med
NK127(jo)001:5828: byang chub tu sems bskyed pa de dag rdzogs pa'i
NK127(jo)001:5829: byang chub tu lung bstan par gyur te /
NK127(jo)001:5830: de ltar gti mug dang ldan pas chos zab mo
NK127(jo)001:5831: spong ba dag kyang dngos sam brgyud pa'i sgo nas
NK127(jo)001:5832: yongs su smin par mdzad pa de dag gis mtshon
NK127(jo)001:5833: nas / mdo sde rnams su 'jam dpal gzhon nur
NK127(jo)001:5834: gyur pas de bzhin gshegs pa la zhu ba dang
NK127(jo)001:5835: nas / / byang chub sems dpa' gzhan dang 'gro ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:5836: nyan thos rnams dang phan tshun 'dri zhing bshad pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:5837: lha dang mi'i skye dgu rnams la chos ston pa
NK127(jo)001:5838: sogs thabs tshul sna tshogs kyis sems can smin par
NK127(jo)001:5839: byed pa mtha' yas pa'i mdzad pa ni mdo sde
NK127(jo)001:5840: rnams su yang nas yang du 'byung ngo //
NK127(jo)001:5841: 'jam dpal rtsa ba'i rtog pa las /
NK127(jo)001:5842: bcom ldan 'das gnas gtsang ma'i steng gi nam mkha'i
NK127(jo)001:5843: dkyil na byang chub sems dpa' 'dus pa'i tshogs dang
NK127(jo)001:5845: 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pas byang chub sems dpa'i
NK127(jo)001:5846: rnam par 'phrul pa dang sngags kyi gzhi gsungs pa'i
NK127(jo)001:5847: tshe / de bzhin gshegs pa'i mdzod spu nas 'od zer byung bas /
NK127(jo)001:5848: byang shar gyi phyogs su 'jig rten gyi khams gang+g+aa'i
NK127(jo)001:5849: klung brgya stong gi bye ma snyed 'das pa na
NK127(jo)001:5850: / me tog dang ldan pa zhes bya ba'i 'jig rten gyi khams gang du /
NK127(jo)001:5851: de bzhin gshegs pa me tog kun tu skyes pa'i
NK127(jo)001:5852: rgyal po'i dbang po zhes bya ba'i drung na 'jam
NK127(jo)001:5853: dpal gzhon nur gyur pa gnas pa bskul bar gyur
NK127(jo)001:5854: pa dang / 'jam dpal gzhon nu ting nge 'dzin
NK127(jo)001:5855: gang la snyoms par zhugs pas phyogs bzhi mtha' yas
NK127(jo)001:5856: mu med pa'i phyogs thams cad sangs rgyas kyis yang
NK127(jo)001:5857: dag par gang bar gyur to //
NK127(jo)001:5858: 'jig rten gyi khams de dang sangs rgyas rnams kyis rgyal ba'i sras legs so legs so //
NK127(jo)001:5859: 'di lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs
NK127(jo)001:5860: pa ni nyan rang dang byang chub sems dpa' spyod
NK127(jo)001:5862: sa bcu la gnas pa dag gis kyang mi nus so zhes gsungs so //
NK127(jo)001:5863: de nas 'jam dpal gzhon nu rdzu 'phrul gyi rol
NK127(jo)001:5864: pas mchod pa'i bkod pa tshad med pa dang bcas
NK127(jo)001:5865: te bcom ldan 'das sh+aakya thub pa'i zhabs kyi drung
NK127(jo)001:5866: du lhags nas phyag 'tshal zhing bstod pas bstod de
NK127(jo)001:5867: 'dug go // de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis 'jam
NK127(jo)001:5868: dpal la khyod kyi sngags kyi las rnams ston cig
NK127(jo)001:5869: 'dug go // ces gsungs pas / 'jam dpal gzhon
NK127(jo)001:5870: nur gyur pa sangs rgyas thams cad kyi byin gyis
NK127(jo)001:5871: brlabs pa'i 'od kyi snang ba bkod pa'i rgyan yang
NK127(jo)001:5872: dag par bsdus pa zhes bya ba byang chub sems
NK127(jo)001:5873: dpa'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs ma thag
NK127(jo)001:5874: tu 'od kyi snang bas gang+g+aa'i klung gi bye ma
NK127(jo)001:5875: snyed du ma'i zhing gi 'og min nas mnar med
NK127(jo)001:5877: sems can thams cad kyi sdug bsngal mtha' dag zhi bar byas nas /
NK127(jo)001:5878: nyan rang dang byang chub sems dpa' thams cad dang
NK127(jo)001:5879: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams yang dag par bskul
NK127(jo)001:5880: nas 'od de 'jam dpal gyi spyi gtsug tu nub
NK127(jo)001:5882: zhing mtha' yas pa'i de bzhin gshegs pa byang chub
NK127(jo)001:5883: sems dpa' dang nyan thos kyi 'khor dang bcas pa
NK127(jo)001:5884: 'dus te / der de bzhin gshegs pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:5886: gtsug tor dang rig pa'i rgyal mo rnams dang /
NK127(jo)001:5887: rig pa'i rgyal po chen po de bzhin gshegs pa
NK127(jo)001:5888: dang rdo rje dang pad+ma'i rigs su gyur pa thams
NK127(jo)001:5889: cad dang / rang sangs rgyas dang nyan thos dang
NK127(jo)001:5890: sems can phal pa'i bar gyi 'khor gyi 'dus pa
NK127(jo)001:5891: chen po re re'i yang mtha' dpag tu med pa
NK127(jo)001:5892: bsdus nas rdzu 'phrul gyi rnam par rol pa dang
NK127(jo)001:5893: bcas te sngags kyi spyod pa dang las rab 'byams
NK127(jo)001:5895: der bcom ldan 'das kyi zhal nas 'di skad du /
NK127(jo)001:5896: thub pa'i zla ba rab nub cing //
NK127(jo)001:5897: sa yi dkyil 'khor stongs pa na //
NK127(jo)001:5899: bstan pa'i don ni ston par 'gyur //
NK127(jo)001:5900: 'jam pa'i dbyangs ni rtag tu dge //
NK127(jo)001:5901: 'byung po kun la gzhon nu ni //
NK127(jo)001:5902: de tshe sangs rgyas mdzad pa ni //
NK127(jo)001:5904: cho ga'i rgyal po'i mthu la ni //
NK127(jo)001:5905: yun ring dus su 'dod pa rnams //
NK127(jo)001:5906: lan gcig thos kyang grol 'gyur te //
NK127(jo)001:5909: gzhon nu 'di ni dngos don khyab rgyu zhing //
NK127(jo)001:5910: ma byung 'jig rten phan pa sgrub byed la //
NK127(jo)001:5911: 'gro ba kun la phan pa dge phyir ston //
NK127(jo)001:5912: thar pa shes shing dag pa'i gnas su 'dug /
NK127(jo)001:5913: bden dang brtse dang bzod pa phan sems dang //
NK127(jo)001:5914: gang zhig rtag tu byams dang sbyin la dga' //
NK127(jo)001:5915: de dag rtag tu grub pa thob par byed //
NK127(jo)001:5916: kye ma gzhan la grub pa'ang yod ma yin //
NK127(jo)001:5917: rtag tu sngags mchog la ni dga' dad dam //
NK127(jo)001:5918: bstan dang 'khor lo 'dzin dang 'jam mchog dang //
NK127(jo)001:5919: de ni bdud 'dul chos kyi 'khor lo bskor //
NK127(jo)001:5920: 'khor lo 'dzin par 'dir ni rigs pa yin //
NK127(jo)001:5921: gang gi gsung ni bzang po yid 'ong zhing //
NK127(jo)001:5922: rtag tu byis pa'i skye bo rnam spangs yin //
NK127(jo)001:5923: yid 'ong bzang po rnar ni snyan pa dang //
NK127(jo)001:5924: dga' skyid nyan pa dang ni rjes su mthun //
NK127(jo)001:5925: sems ni tshim byed bde ba rab tu sbyin //
NK127(jo)001:5926: 'jam zhes bya bar sangs rgyas yang dag gsungs //
NK127(jo)001:5927: de dag de bzhin gshegs pa'i khyad par gyis //
NK127(jo)001:5928: gang gi mthu ni mkhyen par mi spyod de //
NK127(jo)001:5929: de dag gi sras de bzhin sar zhugs pa //
NK127(jo)001:5930: 'jig rten 'das pa de bzhin bcu yi grangs //
NK127(jo)001:5931: khyod kyang lha yi dbang phyug 'jig rten khyad par gyis //
NK127(jo)001:5932: thub bzang shes par nus pa ma yin no //
NK127(jo)001:5933: gzugs dang gzugs med de bzhin sar gnas dang //
NK127(jo)001:5934: 'dod ldan lha dang mi ni yid las skyes //
NK127(jo)001:5935: rnal 'byor grub pa thob dang 'jig rten na //
NK127(jo)001:5936: khyad par can kun de bzhin mi yi gtso //
NK127(jo)001:5937: de yi che ba gang gis shes gyur pa //
NK127(jo)001:5938: sems can gang de yod pa ma yin te //
NK127(jo)001:5939: khyod kyi che ba 'di ni yongs shes pa //
NK127(jo)001:5940: 'jam zhes bya bar rab shes sangs rgyas yin //
NK127(jo)001:5941: 'jam dpal zhes byar yongs su brtag pa ni //
NK127(jo)001:5942: khyod kyi ming ni sngon gyi rgyal bas mdzad //
NK127(jo)001:5943: khyod kyi ming du 'di ltar btags byas pa //
NK127(jo)001:5944: 'das dang ma byon da ltar sangs rgyas kyi //
NK127(jo)001:5945: gzhan du ma yengs rtse gcig yid dag pas //
NK127(jo)001:5946: khyod kyi ming ni 'khor gyi nang du thos //
NK127(jo)001:5947: des ni 'di la shes dang zhi ba thob //
NK127(jo)001:5948: srid mthar byang chub mchog ni khyad par thob //
NK127(jo)001:5949: sngags rnams ma lus 'grub par 'gyur ba dang //
NK127(jo)001:5950: 'gro ba'i skye gnas mchog ni rab thob cing //
NK127(jo)001:5951: rtag tu chos mchog la ni yang dag gnas //
NK127(jo)001:5952: bgegs rnams rnam par spangs shing grub pa thob //
NK127(jo)001:5953: 'dod pa'i sngags rnams ma lus 'grub par byed //
NK127(jo)001:5954: byang chub shing dbang drung du myur du 'gro //
NK127(jo)001:5955: song nas byang chub mchog ni thob par byed //
NK127(jo)001:5956: song nas sems can phan phyin der 'dug ste //
NK127(jo)001:5957: sangs rgyas byang chub 'khor lo rab tu bskor //
NK127(jo)001:5958: de ltar rgyal ba'i gtso bos yon tan gsungs //
NK127(jo)001:5959: 'jam dpal zhes ni khyod kyi ming dran pa //
NK127(jo)001:5960: yon tan bsam mi khyab ces rgyal bas gsungs //
NK127(jo)001:5961: rgyal ba'i gtso bo sngar gshegs thams cad kyis //
NK127(jo)001:5962: rtag tu khyod kyi mthu ni bstan pa yin //
NK127(jo)001:5963: gzhon nu dag pa khyod kyi sngags rtog pa //
NK127(jo)001:5964: bskal pa grangs med rtag tu'ang ston mi nus //
NK127(jo)001:5965: 'jam dpal khyod kyi sngags kyi spyod pa ni //
NK127(jo)001:5966: sangs rgyas ma lus dag gis rab tu bshad //
NK127(jo)001:5967: gzhon nu 'di ni thams cad kun tu 'gro //
NK127(jo)001:5968: nga yi bstan la khyod ni mi mchog bstan //
NK127(jo)001:5969: dag pa'i gnas la gnas pa'i skye bo rnams //
NK127(jo)001:5970: 'dir ni ma lus mtha' dag zhi bar 'gyur //
NK127(jo)001:5971: khyod kyi sngags ni nam yang 'da' ma gyur //
NK127(jo)001:5972: khyod kyi sngags ni nam yang nyams ma gyur //
NK127(jo)001:5974: gzhon nu 'di ni sogs kyi don 'jam dpal dbyangs
NK127(jo)001:5975: nyid gzhon nu'i gzugs kyis zhing thams cad du khyab
NK127(jo)001:5976: par ma 'ongs pa'i sems can gyi don bsgrub pa
NK127(jo)001:5977: bstan / bden dang brtse dang sogs kyis sngags sgrub
NK127(jo)001:5978: pa po'i gang zag gi yon tan gyi khyad par
NK127(jo)001:5979: bstan / bstan / gang gi gsung ni sogs kyis 'jam dpal gyi yon tan bstan te /
NK127(jo)001:5980: gsung tshangs pa'i dbyangs yid du 'ong bas chos kyi
NK127(jo)001:5981: mdzod ston pa las 'jam zhes bya bar mtshan du
NK127(jo)001:5982: grags pa de dag gi yon tan gyi mtha' ni
NK127(jo)001:5983: / de bzhin gshegs pa'i gtso bo'am mchog rnams kyis kyang mkhyen par mi spyod pa'i tshul mdzad la /
NK127(jo)001:5984: de bzhin du sa bcu po la gnas pa'i sems dpa' 'jig rten las 'das pa rnams dang /
NK127(jo)001:5985: 'jig rten na khyad par 'phags pa lha yi dbang phyug dang /
NK127(jo)001:5986: srid pa gsum gyi lha mi rnal 'byor rnams dang
NK127(jo)001:5987: nyan rang dang bcas pa'i sems can sus kyang 'jam
NK127(jo)001:5988: dpal zhes bya ba khyod kyi che ba shes nus
NK127(jo)001:5989: pa med de / sangs rgyas kho nas mkhyen no
NK127(jo)001:5990: zhes pa ste 'gyur shin tu 'khrugs pas don gyi
NK127(jo)001:5992: 'jam dpal zhes byar sogs kyis ni sangs rgyas rnams
NK127(jo)001:5993: kyis gang la 'jam dpal zhes mtshan btags pa'i mtshan
NK127(jo)001:5994: de ni / yid dag cing ma yengs pa'i sems
NK127(jo)001:5995: can rnams kyis sangs rgyas kyi 'khor gyi nang du
NK127(jo)001:5996: thos kyi gzhan du thos dka' la /
NK127(jo)001:5997: 'jam dpal zhes pa'i mtshan rna bar thos pa de'i
NK127(jo)001:5998: phan yon ni tshe 'di la bkra shis pa dang
NK127(jo)001:5999: sgrib pa sogs mi mthun pa'i phyogs mtha' dag zhi
NK127(jo)001:6000: ba dang / mthar thug bla med byang chub thob po zhes mdor bstan nas /
NK127(jo)001:6001: slar yang gsungs pa mtshan thos pa tsam gyis sngags
NK127(jo)001:6002: thams cad 'grub par 'ag+r+yuba ba dang tshe rabs thams
NK127(jo)001:6003: cad du gnas ngan par skye ba spangs te skye
NK127(jo)001:6004: gnas mchog tu gyur pa thob pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:6005: rtag tu yang dag pa dge ba'i phyogs kyi yon
NK127(jo)001:6006: tan gyi chos mchog rnams la rab tu gnas pa
NK127(jo)001:6007: dang / bgegs dang bar chad ci yang mi 'byung bar dngos grub rnams thob pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:6008: rang gi yid la 'dod pa'i sngags ma lus pa
NK127(jo)001:6009: grub nas rig pa 'dzin par 'gyur ba ni gnas
NK127(jo)001:6011: mthar thug byang chub shing gi dbang po'i drung du
NK127(jo)001:6012: song nas sems can rnams la phan phyir der 'dug
NK127(jo)001:6013: pa'i mod la bla na med pa'i byang chub mngon
NK127(jo)001:6014: du byas nas / sangs rgyas byang chub kyi rgyu
NK127(jo)001:6015: mthun pa'i chos kyi 'khor lo rab tu bskor bar
NK127(jo)001:6016: 'gyur ro zhes de ltar rgyal ba'i gtso bos 'jam
NK127(jo)001:6017: dpal gyi mtshan gyi yon tan gsungs te /
NK127(jo)001:6019: 'jam dpal zhes ni khyod kyi ming dran pa tsam
NK127(jo)001:6020: la'ang phan pa'i yon tan bsam gyis mi khyab ces
NK127(jo)001:6023: rgyal ba'i gtso bo sngar gshegs zhes pa la sogs
NK127(jo)001:6024: pas sngar 'das pa'i sangs rgyas rnams kyis 'jam dpal
NK127(jo)001:6025: gyi mathu'am yon tan rgya cher bstan par mdzad la
NK127(jo)001:6026: / khyod kyi sngags dang rtog pa ni tshad med
NK127(jo)001:6027: pas bskal pa grangs med du bstan kyang zad mi
NK127(jo)001:6028: / nus la / dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas ma
NK127(jo)001:6029: lus pa rnams kyis ci rigs par rab tu bshad
NK127(jo)001:6030: / nus la / do // rtag tu bgres rgud
NK127(jo)001:6031: dang bral ba ye shes kyi sku can 'jam dpal
NK127(jo)001:6032: gzhon nu 'di ni dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas kyi
NK127(jo)001:6033: zhing thams cad kun tu yang 'gro zhing snang bar
NK127(jo)001:6034: / nus la / do // byed pa ste /
NK127(jo)001:6035: de ltar sh+aakya'i rgyal po nga yi bstan pa 'di
NK127(jo)001:6036: la yang 'jam dpal khyod ni mi mchog byang chub
NK127(jo)001:6037: sems dpa'i tshul du bstan nas sems can gyi don
NK127(jo)001:6038: / nus la / do // byed pa ste /
NK127(jo)001:6039: byed do // tshul des dag pa'i gnas la bzhugs
NK127(jo)001:6040: pa'i skye bo 'phags pa'i tshogs bsam gyis mi khyab
NK127(jo)001:6041: pa mtha' dag zhi ba'i dbyings su mya ngan las
NK127(jo)001:6043: 'jam dpal khyod kyi sngags ni dus gsum po kun
NK127(jo)001:6044: tu yang nam yang dus las 'da' ba dang nyams
NK127(jo)001:6046: de la go bde bar tshig bcos na //
NK127(jo)001:6047: de bzhin de dag gi sras sa yi grangs //
NK127(jo)001:6048: bcu la zhugs pa 'jig rten 'das rnams dang //
NK127(jo)001:6049: 'jig rten mchog gyur lha yi dbang phyug gis //
NK127(jo)001:6050: thub bzang khyod ni shes par nus ma yin //
NK127(jo)001:6051: zhes dang 'jam zhes bya bar rab shes khyod nyid kyi //
NK127(jo)001:6052: che ba 'di ni yongs shes sangs rgyas yin //
NK127(jo)001:6054: khyod kyi ming ni 'di ltar brtags byas pa //
NK127(jo)001:6055: gzhan du ma yengs rtse gcig yid dag pas //
NK127(jo)001:6056: 'das dang ma byon da ltar sangs rgyas kyi //
NK127(jo)001:6057: 'khor gyi nang du khyod kyi ming ni thos //
NK127(jo)001:6058: zhes pa ltar byas na bade'am snyam mo //
NK127(jo)001:6060: dus kyi tha ma de la ni /
NK127(jo)001:6061: sngags rnams grub par nges pa yin //
NK127(jo)001:6062: de nyid kyis ni thub dbang gis //
NK127(jo)001:6063: gzhon nu yongs su brtags pa ni //
NK127(jo)001:6064: shes rab chen po 'jam pa'i dbyangs //
NK127(jo)001:6065: byis pa gzhon nu'i gzugs dang ldan //
NK127(jo)001:6067: sems can rjes su gzung bar bzod //
NK127(jo)001:6068: de yi dus su 'jam pa'i dbyangs //
NK127(jo)001:6069: grub pa dag ni rab tu mthong //
NK127(jo)001:6070: rgyu skar skar ma'i dpyad shes pa //
NK127(jo)001:6072: nyi shu rtsa bdun rgyu skar dang //
NK127(jo)001:6073: yud tsam dag tu rab tu bsgrags //
NK127(jo)001:6074: dus kyi tha ma de la ni //
NK127(jo)001:6075: bcu gnyis khyim yang yod pa yin //
NK127(jo)001:6076: rgyu skar tshogs la brten nas ni //
NK127(jo)001:6077: de dag gza' ni rnam par dbye //
NK127(jo)001:6078: thams cad so sor gyur pa ni //
NK127(jo)001:6079: 'jam dpal gyis ni so sor mdzad //
NK127(jo)001:6081: sh+aakya seng ge skyob pa yi //
NK127(jo)001:6082: bstan pa nub par gyur pa yi //
NK127(jo)001:6083: dus ni mi bzad 'jigs pa na //
NK127(jo)001:6084: de tshe grub par 'gyur ba yin //
NK127(jo)001:6086: de bas dus kun 'jam pa'i dpal //
NK127(jo)001:6087: gzhon nu khyod ni de yi tshe //
NK127(jo)001:6088: sdig pa'i las la rjes 'jug pa'i //
NK127(jo)001:6090: khyod ni rdzu 'phrul bsam mi khyab //
NK127(jo)001:6091: gdul bya dag kyang bsam mi khyab //
NK127(jo)001:6092: 'byung po'i tshogs rnams ma lus pa //
NK127(jo)001:6094: sangs rgyas dpa' bos de gsungs nas //
NK127(jo)001:6096: gnas gtsang steng bzhugs de tshe gzigs //
NK127(jo)001:6097: rkang gnyis dam pa rdzogs sangs rgyas //
NK127(jo)001:6098: smra ba'i mchog gis de la gsungs //
NK127(jo)001:6099: bskal pa mang po 'das pa na //
NK127(jo)001:6100: khyod ni rdzogs sangs rgyas par 'gyur //
NK127(jo)001:6101: grangs kyis mnyam med bsam mi khyab //
NK127(jo)001:6102: mi yis grangs dang mnyam med par //
NK127(jo)001:6103: 'jam pa'i rgyal mtshan zhes bya ba //
NK127(jo)001:6105: rtag tu yang ni mthar gyis ni //
NK127(jo)001:6106: sangs rgyas mdzad pa de tshe byed //
NK127(jo)001:6107: sems can mang po rnam bkrol nas //
NK127(jo)001:6110: gsang sngags snga 'gyur gyi chos sde snying gzer drag po chen po'i rgyud las /
NK127(jo)001:6112: lha mo'i nang nas 'od zer can //
NK127(jo)001:6113: 'di gnyis ma gtogs dngos grub gzhan //
NK127(jo)001:6114: rig 'dzin kun kyang dngos grub yal //
NK127(jo)001:6115: nga yi lto nas srid gsum 'byin //
NK127(jo)001:6116: ji lta bus ni zhi gyur yang //
NK127(jo)001:6117: thams cad zhi ba nga yi sku //
NK127(jo)001:6118: ji lta bus ni khros gyur kyang //
NK127(jo)001:6119: thams cad khros pa nga yi sku //
NK127(jo)001:6121: rdo rje snying po rgyan gyi rgyud las /
NK127(jo)001:6122: sangs rgyas ye shes rab stsol byed //
NK127(jo)001:6123: sangs rgyas rnams kyi ye shes mchog /'jam pa'i dbyangs zhes rab tu grags //
NK127(jo)001:6124: 'di ni bsgrubs pa tsam gyis ni //
NK127(jo)001:6125: shes rab dri ma med par 'gyur //
NK127(jo)001:6126: bstan bcos thams cad rab smra zhing //
NK127(jo)001:6127: dbang phyug thams cad mdun na gnas //
NK127(jo)001:6128: kun gyi rgyal po sngags pa nyid //
NK127(jo)001:6129: rang nyid kun gyi rgyal po mtshungs //
NK127(jo)001:6130: rig pa 'dzin pa thams cad dang //
NK127(jo)001:6131: byang chub kun gyi pha rol son //
NK127(jo)001:6132: dbang phyug kun dang bde ba che //
NK127(jo)001:6133: chos rnams kun gyi yon tan mchog /
NK127(jo)001:6134: rdo rje 'dzin pa thams cad dang //
NK127(jo)001:6135: yang na sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK127(jo)001:6136: kun tu 'gro ba thob gyur na //
NK127(jo)001:6137: dngos grub gzhan lta smos ci dgos //
NK127(jo)001:6138: dngul chu bcud len de nyid dang //
NK127(jo)001:6139: rkang pas spyod pa dri med mchog /
NK127(jo)001:6140: ril bu dang ni mi snang ba //
NK127(jo)001:6141: thams cad du ni ster ba la //
NK127(jo)001:6143: chos kyi gsung gi mchog las 'khrungs //
NK127(jo)001:6144: sangs rgyas rnams kyi tshangs pa'i dbyangs //
NK127(jo)001:6145: 'jam pa'i dbyangs zhes rab tu grags //
NK127(jo)001:6146: 'di ni bsgrubs pa tsam gyis ni //
NK127(jo)001:6147: bsams pa'i phun sum tshogs kun gyi //
NK127(jo)001:6148: sangs rgyas kun tu brtan 'gro na //
NK127(jo)001:6149: gzhan pa'i lha lta smos ci dgos //
NK127(jo)001:6151: gzhan yang 'jig rten gsum las rnam par rgyal ba'i
NK127(jo)001:6152: rtog pa las rig sngags kyi rgyal po a ra
NK127(jo)001:6153: pa tsa na'i phan yon mdor bsdus te gsungs pa
NK127(jo)001:6154: lta bus mtshon te 'jam dpal zhi khro'i lha sngags
NK127(jo)001:6155: kyi rnam grangs rmad du byung ba'i yon tan gyi
NK127(jo)001:6156: khyad par mnga' ba du ma dag gsar rnying gi
NK127(jo)001:6157: rgyud sde rnams nas yang yang bstan to //
NK127(jo)001:6158: dpal dus kyi 'khor lo'i rgyud las /
NK127(jo)001:6159: 'dzam bu'i gling la yul drug tu grags pa'i nang
NK127(jo)001:6160: tshan byang phyogs su sham b+ha la zhes pa yul
NK127(jo)001:6161: gyi bkod pa khyad par 'phags pa der /
NK127(jo)001:6162: sa bcu'i sems dpa' chen po rnams rgyal po'i tshul
NK127(jo)001:6163: 'dzin pa brgyud mar byon pa las thog ma'i rgyal
NK127(jo)001:6164: po zla ba bzang po zhes bya ba phyag na
NK127(jo)001:6165: rdo rje'i sprul pa de la bcom ldan 'das nyid
NK127(jo)001:6166: dpal dus kyi 'khor lo'i skur bzhengs pas rtsa rgyud
NK127(jo)001:6167: stong phrag bcu gnyis pa gsungs /
NK127(jo)001:6168: de nas rgyal po bdun 'das pa'i gdan rabs brgyad
NK127(jo)001:6169: pa la rje btsun 'jam pa'i dbyangs nyid rigs ldan
NK127(jo)001:6170: 'jam dpal grags pa'i rnam par byon nas /
NK127(jo)001:6171: yul de'i bram ze rig byed pa'i gzhung smra ba
NK127(jo)001:6172: sogs rig pa sna tshogs kyi brtul zhugs 'dzin pa
NK127(jo)001:6173: thams cad la bla med rdo rje theg pa'i dbang
NK127(jo)001:6174: bskur byin te theg pa mchog gi rigs gcig tu
NK127(jo)001:6175: byas pas rgyal po de'i ring nas rigs ldan zhes
NK127(jo)001:6177: rigs ldan grags pa de la rtsa ba'i rgyud kyi
NK127(jo)001:6178: don bsdus pa bsdus rgyud le'u lnga pa mdzad pa
NK127(jo)001:6179: yin te / bsdus pa'i rgyud chen po las /
NK127(jo)001:6180: dpal ldan sh+aakya'i rigs la rab gsal mi yi bdag po bdun te brgyad pa grags pa yang /
NK127(jo)001:6181: 'di ni dpal ldan 'jam pa'i rdo rje lha yi
NK127(jo)001:6182: mchog gis btud pa rdo rje'i rigs kyi rigs ldan
NK127(jo)001:6183: te / rdo rje'i dbang bskur byin nas mtha' dag
NK127(jo)001:6184: thub pa'i rigs rnams dag ni rigs gcig dag tu
NK127(jo)001:6185: te / byed par 'gyur / yang dag theg par
NK127(jo)001:6186: mngon 'dzegs lha min rigs la 'jigs ster dpal ldan
NK127(jo)001:6187: grags pa phyag na mdung thung can /
NK127(jo)001:6188: sems can rnams kyi thar pa'i slad du sa la
NK127(jo)001:6189: dus kyi 'khor lo rab tu gsal bar byed par
NK127(jo)001:6191: rgyud de'i ye shes le'u las /
NK127(jo)001:6192: chos kyi rgyal po grags pas bram ze nyi ma'i shing rta la gsungs pa /
NK127(jo)001:6193: de ltar 'jig rten dbang phyug bdag ni srid pa
NK127(jo)001:6194: gsum gyi gnas su las kyi sar gnas nyi ma
NK127(jo)001:6195: kye / sems can rnams la lam ni sbyin byed
NK127(jo)001:6196: dmyal ba'i 'jigs 'phrog lha gzhan dag ni nam yang
NK127(jo)001:6197: kye / ma yin no // zhes dang bram ze nyi ma'i shing rtas bstod pa /
NK127(jo)001:6198: khyod ni rgan yang gzhon nu mtha' dag rgyal ba'i
NK127(jo)001:6199: sras po yin yang thog mar dang po'i sangs rgyas
NK127(jo)001:6200: khyod // bud med sbyor zhing tshangs par spyod ldan
NK127(jo)001:6201: mchog gi thugs rje dag gis 'jig rten gnyen te
NK127(jo)001:6202: khyod // gshin rje'i dgra // khyod ni zhi yang
NK127(jo)001:6203: rdo rje bzang po 'chi ba'i 'jigs pa 'phrog pa
NK127(jo)001:6204: khyod ni rtag tu bdud kyi bdud //
NK127(jo)001:6205: khyod ni grol yang srid pa 'dir ni 'gro ba
NK127(jo)001:6206: smin pa'i don du grags pa khyod ni rab tu
NK127(jo)001:6208: rgyal po 'jam dpal grags pa de nyid kyi sras
NK127(jo)001:6209: spyan ras gzigs kyi sprul pa rigs ldan pad+ma dkar
NK127(jo)001:6210: pos bsdus pa'i rgyud la 'grel chen dri ma med
NK127(jo)001:6211: pa'i 'od mdzad / rgyal po zla ba bzang po
NK127(jo)001:6212: nas brtsis pa'i gdan rabs sum cu rtsa gnyis pa
NK127(jo)001:6213: pa'i 'od mdzad / dang / rigs ldan grags pa
NK127(jo)001:6214: nas brtsis pa'i gdan rabs nyer lnga pa la slar
NK127(jo)001:6215: yang rje btsun 'jam dpal dbyangs dngos rgyal po grags
NK127(jo)001:6216: pa nyid rigs ldan drag po 'khor lo can gyi
NK127(jo)001:6217: rnam par bzhengs nas kla klo'i phyogs 'joms par 'gyur
NK127(jo)001:6218: pa'i 'od mdzad / dang / ba yin te / bsdus pa'i rgyud kyi 'jig rten le'u las /
NK127(jo)001:6219: sum cu rtsa gnyis gdan gyi mthar ni lha min
NK127(jo)001:6220: dgra bo tshe lo brgya ba phyag na 'khor lor
NK127(jo)001:6222: de yi dbus su gdan ni nyi shu rtsa lnga
NK127(jo)001:6223: rim par yongs su bgrangs pa dag gi dus kyi
NK127(jo)001:6224: mthar // rigs ldan rigs la lha yi dbang po
NK127(jo)001:6225: lha yi mchog gis btud pa drag po'i rigs ldan
NK127(jo)001:6226: mthar // 'byung bar 'gyur // dam pa rnams la
NK127(jo)001:6227: zhi ba'i gzugs te bde ster zhes pa de bzhin
NK127(jo)001:6228: kla klo'i rigs la mthar byed nyid //
NK127(jo)001:6229: rdo yi rta bcibs 'khor lo can ni phyag na
NK127(jo)001:6230: mdung thung mtha' dag dgra la snun byed nyi ma'i
NK127(jo)001:6232: rigs ldan drag po dmag gi dpung rgya chen po
NK127(jo)001:6233: dang lha chen po bcu gnyis kyi dpung grogs bcas
NK127(jo)001:6234: te 'dzam bu'i gling gi lho phyogs kyi rgyud thams
NK127(jo)001:6235: cad du 'khrugs pa drag po'i tshul gyis kla klo'i
NK127(jo)001:6236: phyogs ma lus pa bcom nas sangs rgyas kyi bstan
NK127(jo)001:6237: pa spyi dang rdo rje'i theg pa gsal bar mdzad
NK127(jo)001:6238: / sras tshangs pa sham b+ha la'i rgyal sa dang /
NK127(jo)001:6239: dbang po 'dzam gling gzhan gyi rgyal por bkod nas
NK127(jo)001:6240: dam pa'i chos 'phel bar mdzad pas mi rnams kyi
NK127(jo)001:6241: tshe dang bde ba gong du 'phel zhing /
NK127(jo)001:6242: rigs ldan nyid sham b+ha la'i pho brang du phyin
NK127(jo)001:6243: nas phyag rgya chen po'i dngos grub brnyes pa'i tshul
NK127(jo)001:6244: gyis de dus kyi 'khor rnams dang 'brel ba thogs
NK127(jo)001:6245: pa dang bcas pa thams cad bde ba'i gnas su
NK127(jo)001:6248: dpung ni thams cad dag gis g.yul du kla klo
NK127(jo)001:6249: bcom nas khyab 'jug drag po dang bcas rigs ldan
NK127(jo)001:6250: ni // kee l+aa sha yi ri bo lha yis
NK127(jo)001:6251: bkod pa'i grong khyer gang du 'khor lo can dag
NK127(jo)001:6252: ni // gnas par 'gro // de yi dus su
NK127(jo)001:6253: 'dzin ma dag la mtha' dag skye bo'i rigs ni
NK127(jo)001:6254: chos dang 'dod pa nor rnams rdzogs //
NK127(jo)001:6255: 'bru rnams dgon par skye ba dang ni shing rnams
NK127(jo)001:6256: 'bras bu brtan pos dud pa de dag 'byung bar
NK127(jo)001:6257: 'gyur // kla klo'i tshogs ni 'khor gyi skye bo
NK127(jo)001:6258: dang bcas rab tu bcad nas mi yi lo ni
NK127(jo)001:6259: 'gyur // brgya phyed na // rigs ldan grub par
NK127(jo)001:6260: 'gyur te lha yis bkod pa'i pho brang mtho ba
NK127(jo)001:6261: kee l+aa sha yi rgyab tu'o //
NK127(jo)001:6262: zhes pa la sogs pa rgya cher gsungs so //
NK127(jo)001:6263: tshul 'dis mtshon nas 'jam pa'i dbyangs nyid gang 'dul
NK127(jo)001:6264: sna tshogs pa'i gzugs kyis mkha' dang mnyam pa'i zhing
NK127(jo)001:6265: thams cad du sprul pa'i rol pa chu zla ltar
NK127(jo)001:6266: mu med par 'char ba la gus pa'i sems bskyed
NK127(jo)001:6267: par bya'o // gshin rje gshed nag po'i rgyud las /
NK127(jo)001:6268: bcom ldan 'das mngon par byang chub pa'i dus su
NK127(jo)001:6269: thub pa chen po la bdud kyi bar chad kyi
NK127(jo)001:6270: phyir dpung chen po lhags pa na /
NK127(jo)001:6271: bcom ldan 'das bdud chen po las rnam par rgyal ba'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs te /
NK127(jo)001:6272: sku gsung thugs rdo rje las khro bo gshin rje gshed byung nas /
NK127(jo)001:6273: lag na rdo rje la khyod kyang 'di lta bu'i
NK127(jo)001:6274: khro bo'i gzugs su byas te bdud la sogs pa
NK127(jo)001:6275: choms shig chings shig rtogs shig ces gsung zhing rgyud
NK127(jo)001:6276: kyang phyag na rdo rjes gzung ngo //
NK127(jo)001:6278: rdo rje 'jigs byed chen po'i gtam rgyud kyi rtog pa las /
NK127(jo)001:6279: lho phyogs rgya mtsho'i phar rgal na //
NK127(jo)001:6280: de nas gshin rje'i grong khyer ni //
NK127(jo)001:6281: ga la ba yi gnas su byon //
NK127(jo)001:6282: mi bzad zhabs ni bcu drug gis //
NK127(jo)001:6283: lcags mkhar sgo med bcu drug bardzisa //
NK127(jo)001:6284: ye shes rtse gcig mtshan ma yis //
NK127(jo)001:6285: dbus kyi lcags mkhar chen po bardzisa //
NK127(jo)001:6286: de tshe bdud chen las rgyal nas //
NK127(jo)001:6287: ha ha hi'i hi'i sgra sgrogs pas //
NK127(jo)001:6288: chos kyi rgyal po la sogs pa //
NK127(jo)001:6289: gzir bzhin du ni rab smras pa //
NK127(jo)001:6290: dpa' bo chen po ga la ci //
NK127(jo)001:6291: dpa' bo'i dgos pa bdag gis bgyi //
NK127(jo)001:6292: bdag cag srog gi snying po rnams //
NK127(jo)001:6293: tshul bzhin 'bul gyis dpa' bos bzhes //
NK127(jo)001:6295: snga 'gyur gyi chos sde 'phags pa 'jam dpal dri ma med pa gsang ba'i rgyud las /
NK127(jo)001:6296: sngon chu'i dkyil 'khor gyi 'og rlung dkyil gyi steng
NK127(jo)001:6297: du gshin rje'i lcags mkhar che ba bcu bdun sgo
NK127(jo)001:6298: med yid kyis rgyu ba na /
NK127(jo)001:6299: gsod gcod kyi las dang zhe sdang drag po'i mthu
NK127(jo)001:6300: las grub pa'i gshin rje nag po mthar byed bye
NK127(jo)001:6301: ba dgu ring zhes bya ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:6302: de'i chung ma dus mtshan nag mo zhes bya ba
NK127(jo)001:6303: gnyis yi dwags thams cad kyi gtso bo byed cing
NK127(jo)001:6305: zas su sha khrag rlon pa za /
NK127(jo)001:6306: srid gsum lto na yod pa de lta bu dbus kyi khang pa na gnas so //
NK127(jo)001:6307: de gnyis kyi sprul pa chos kyi rgyal po sogs las kyi gshed chen bzhi dang /
NK127(jo)001:6308: de bzhi'i bka' nyan gshin rje phya sangs la sogs pa bzhi dang /
NK127(jo)001:6309: gzhan yang 'jig rten gyi dregs pa lha ma srin
NK127(jo)001:6310: sde brgyad kyi 'khor dang thabs gcig pas 'jig rten
NK127(jo)001:6311: gyi khams phung bar byed pa la /
NK127(jo)001:6312: bcom ldan 'das 'phags pa 'jam dpal chos kyi dbyings
NK127(jo)001:6313: las bzhengs te dregs pa can tshar gcod pa'i ting
NK127(jo)001:6314: nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs ma thag tu gtum
NK127(jo)001:6315: chen gnyen po'i lhar gyur te /
NK127(jo)001:6316: btso ma gser gyi kha dog las /
NK127(jo)001:6317: stang zil 'dra ba'i mdog tu bstan //
NK127(jo)001:6318: ut+pala sngon po'i phyag mtshan ni //
NK127(jo)001:6319: gshin rje'i dbyug pa nag por bstan //
NK127(jo)001:6320: 'jam dpal zhi ba'i sprul pa ni //
NK127(jo)001:6321: gshin rjer khros pa'i sku ru bstan //
NK127(jo)001:6323: der ro langs gtum mo g.yon dang /
NK127(jo)001:6324: e ka dz+aa t+ai g.yas nas 'khril ba'i yab yum
NK127(jo)001:6325: gnyis su med pa'i 'khor gshin rje chen po bzhi
NK127(jo)001:6327: phyogs skyong ba'i gshin rje yab yum bcu dang /
NK127(jo)001:6328: sgo ma bzhi la sogs pa 'khor bsam gyis mi
NK127(jo)001:6329: khyab pa dang bcas pa shin tu 'bar ba'i skur
NK127(jo)001:6330: bstan te / khams gsum dbang du sdud pa'i ting
NK127(jo)001:6331: nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs pas 'jig rten gyi
NK127(jo)001:6332: khams thams cad rab tu g.yo 'gul 'khrugs shing 'chi
NK127(jo)001:6333: bdag gi grong khyer zhabs 'og tu bardzisa nas /
NK127(jo)001:6334: las kyi gshin rje'i srog snying sdig pa kha brgyad
NK127(jo)001:6335: pas mtshan par gnas pa gnang nas drangs te phrogs
NK127(jo)001:6336: pas / gshin rje thams cad kyi rang gi srog
NK127(jo)001:6337: snying mdongs gsol du phul nas lnga brgya tha ma
NK127(jo)001:6338: la bstan pa srung ba'i las gnyer du blang bar
NK127(jo)001:6339: pas / dam bcas so // zhes gsungs shing /
NK127(jo)001:6340: snga 'gyur gyi chos sder gtogs pa gshin rje gshed
NK127(jo)001:6341: pra khog snang gi brtag pa phyi ma'i rgyal po
NK127(jo)001:6342: las / khro bo'i ming ni gshin rje gshed //
NK127(jo)001:6344: drag la mthu rtsal drag ldan pa //
NK127(jo)001:6345: de mthong nas ni khro bo gzhan //
NK127(jo)001:6346: thams cad kun gyis lag cha shor //
NK127(jo)001:6347: de bzhin du ni 'jig rten pa'i //
NK127(jo)001:6348: lha rnams lus kyi 'dud par byed //
NK127(jo)001:6349: gzhan yang thal mo sbyar byas te //
NK127(jo)001:6350: skrag nas bstod pa mang po byed //
NK127(jo)001:6352: nges pa'i don du dus gsum gyi rgyal ba thams
NK127(jo)001:6353: cad kyi ye shes kyi sku gcig pu rigs kyi
NK127(jo)001:6354: khyab bdag dam pa yin te /
NK127(jo)001:6355: bstod pa glur blangs kyi le'u las /
NK127(jo)001:6356: bcom ldan 'das kyi ye shes sku //
NK127(jo)001:6357: gtsug tor chen po tshig gi bdag /
NK127(jo)001:6358: ye shes sku ste rang byung ba //
NK127(jo)001:6359: 'jam dpal ye shes sems dpa' yi //
NK127(jo)001:6362: ye shes sku bdag sangs rgyas te //
NK127(jo)001:6363: sangs rgyas dus gsum bzhugs rnams kyi'o //
NK127(jo)001:6365: mchog gi dang po sku gsum 'chang //
NK127(jo)001:6366: sangs rgyas sku lnga'i bdag nyid can //
NK127(jo)001:6367: khyab bdag ye shes lnga yi bdag /
NK127(jo)001:6369: sangs rgyas thams cad skyed pa po //
NK127(jo)001:6370: sangs rgyas sras po dam pa mchog /
NK127(jo)001:6372: sangs rgyas kun bdag sku yi mchog /
NK127(jo)001:6374: dus gsum sangs rgyas las byed pa //
NK127(jo)001:6375: sangs rgyas thog ma tha ma med //
NK127(jo)001:6376: dang po'i sangs rgyas ris med pa //
NK127(jo)001:6377: ye shes mig gcig dri ma med //
NK127(jo)001:6379: sangs rgyas kun gyi rgyal po che //
NK127(jo)001:6380: sangs rgyas kun gyi sku 'chang ba //
NK127(jo)001:6382: sangs rgyas kun gyi thugs che ba //
NK127(jo)001:6383: sangs rgyas kun gyi thugs la gnas //
NK127(jo)001:6384: sangs rgyas kun gyi sku che ba //
NK127(jo)001:6385: sangs rgyas kun gyi gsung yang yin //
NK127(jo)001:6387: kun mkhyen ye shes mdzod 'dzin pa //
NK127(jo)001:6389: sangs rgyas kun gyi sprul pa'i sku //
NK127(jo)001:6390: bye ba dpag med 'gyed pa po //
NK127(jo)001:6392: sangs rgyas kun gyi rang bzhin 'chang //
NK127(jo)001:6394: sangs rgyas kun gyis rtogs bya ba //
NK127(jo)001:6395: sangs rgyas byang chub bla na med //
NK127(jo)001:6397: sangs rgyas kun gyi snying po che //
NK127(jo)001:6400: sangs rgyas sprul pa'i rgyud 'chang ba //
NK127(jo)001:6401: phyogs bcur sprul pa sna tshogs 'gyed //
NK127(jo)001:6403: dper bya kun las 'das pa ste //
NK127(jo)001:6404: shes dang shes bya'i bdag po mchog /
NK127(jo)001:6406: nges 'byung gsum po bgrod rnams kyi //
NK127(jo)001:6407: don gyi dam pa rnam dag dpal //
NK127(jo)001:6409: sangs rgyas byang chub khyod la 'dud //
NK127(jo)001:6410: ces pa la sogs pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:6411: phreng ba'i sngags don las kyang /
NK127(jo)001:6412: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi ye shes kyi
NK127(jo)001:6413: sku 'jam dpal yongs su dag par gzung bar bya'o
NK127(jo)001:6414: zhes gsungs shing / snga 'gyur gyi chos sde 'jam dpal sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i rgyud phyi ma las /
NK127(jo)001:6415: 'jam dpal 'di ni dpal gyur rdzogs pa'i sku //
NK127(jo)001:6416: thun mongs ma yin gnyis med khyab pa'i chos //
NK127(jo)001:6417: dus gsum mnyam rdzogs rgyal ba kun gyi yab //
NK127(jo)001:6418: chos dbyings yum nyid sems dpa' sras mchog ston //
NK127(jo)001:6420: stong nyid ci la'ang ma reg lhun gyis grub //
NK127(jo)001:6421: don kun 'byor bas blang dor med pa yi //
NK127(jo)001:6422: bdag nyid rang bzhin bzhag dang 'jam dpal nyid //
NK127(jo)001:6423: bsam gyis mi khyab mi gnas mi sems na //
NK127(jo)001:6424: 'jam dpal nyid dang yon tan rdzogs par mnyam //
NK127(jo)001:6426: 'jam dpal ye shes rdo rje rdzogs //
NK127(jo)001:6429: mi gnas rdo rje rtse mo ste //
NK127(jo)001:6430: bsam tshul sgrub pa med pa yi //
NK127(jo)001:6431: dbyings nyid bzhag na yongs su gnas //
NK127(jo)001:6432: zhes pa la sogs pa gsungs pa bzhin du gnyis
NK127(jo)001:6433: su med pa rang byung ye shes kyi sku shes
NK127(jo)001:6434: dang shes bya thams cad mnyam pa nyid kyi bdag
NK127(jo)001:6435: nyid kyis dus gsum gyi rgyal ba thams cad kyi
NK127(jo)001:6436: rigs kyi khyab bdag nges pa don gyi 'jam dpal
NK127(jo)001:6437: gzhon nur gyur pa'i rang bzhin la mkhas par byas
NK127(jo)001:6438: nas mi phyed pa'i dad pa bskyed par bya'o //
NK127(jo)001:6439: 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa'i rtogs pa brjod pa'i skabs te dang po'o ////
NK127(jo)001:6440: byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po spyan ras
NK127(jo)001:6441: gzigs dbang phyug thugs rje chen po la phyag 'tshal
NK127(jo)001:6442: lo // mchod do skyabs su mchi'o //
NK127(jo)001:6443: 'phags mchog 'di'i yon tan ni ches bsam gyis mi khyab ste /
NK127(jo)001:6444: za ma tog bkod pa'i mdo las gsungs pa /
NK127(jo)001:6445: sems can dmyal ba mnar med pa'i lcags kyi khang
NK127(jo)001:6446: pa 'bar ba'i gnas su spyan ras gzigs kyi dbang
NK127(jo)001:6447: po zhugs pa na gnas de bsil zhing pad+mas khebs
NK127(jo)001:6448: pa'i rdzing bur gyur te sems can rnams thar bar
NK127(jo)001:6449: bgyid pa'i mthu de lta bu mthong nas gshin rje'i
NK127(jo)001:6451: de nas yi dwags kyi drung du byon pas gnas
NK127(jo)001:6452: de bsil zhing thams cad byams pa la gnas te
NK127(jo)001:6453: sdug bsngal thams cad rgyun chad la /
NK127(jo)001:6454: phyag zhabs kyi sor mo nyi shu las chu'i rgyun chen po dang /
NK127(jo)001:6455: ba spu'i khung bu nas kyang chu bo byung ste
NK127(jo)001:6456: yi dwags thams cad tshim zhing sdug bsngal ba thams
NK127(jo)001:6457: cad bral te dkon mchog gi rgyal po za ma
NK127(jo)001:6458: tog bkod pa'i sgra byung bas 'jigs tshogs la lta
NK127(jo)001:6459: ba ye shes kyi rdo rjes bcom nas bde ba
NK127(jo)001:6461: spyan ras gzigs des nyi ma re re zhing sems
NK127(jo)001:6462: can bye ba khrag khrig brgya stong du ma yongs
NK127(jo)001:6463: su smin par byed de de'i spobs pa de 'dra
NK127(jo)001:6464: ba ni de bzhin gshegs pa rnams la med do
NK127(jo)001:6465: // spyan ras gzigs de'i mig las nyi zla /
NK127(jo)001:6466: dpral ba las dbang phyug chen po /
NK127(jo)001:6469: mche ba gnyis las dbyangs can /
NK127(jo)001:6472: lto ba las chu'i lha byung ngo //
NK127(jo)001:6473: spyan ras gzigs gang du byon pa der me tog gi char dang /
NK127(jo)001:6474: rdzing bu dang ljon shing rgyas pa la sogs pa
NK127(jo)001:6475: rmad du byung ba'i ngo mtshar sna tshogs snang bar
NK127(jo)001:6476: byed do // spyan ras gzigs ni gang gis 'dul ba la de lta bu'i gzugs su ston te /
NK127(jo)001:6480: mi dang mi ma yin pa sogs rnam pa sna
NK127(jo)001:6481: tshogs su bstan pas sems can rnams yongs su smin
NK127(jo)001:6482: par byed do // spyan ras gzigs kyi yul de
NK127(jo)001:6483: lta bu ni de bzhin gshegs pa la'ang ma mchis
NK127(jo)001:6484: par byed do // so // gzhan yang 'dzam gling
NK127(jo)001:6485: 'di na rdo rje'i mngal zhes pa'i phug na gnas
NK127(jo)001:6486: pa'i lha ma yin rnams la lha min gyi gzugs
NK127(jo)001:6487: su byas nas chos bstan pas bde ba can du
NK127(jo)001:6489: de bzhin du gser gyi sa la song nas sems can spyi tshugs su 'jug pa rnams dang /
NK127(jo)001:6490: dngul gyi sa la gang zag rkang bzhi pa rnams dang /
NK127(jo)001:6491: lha ma yin gtor ma'i gnas su song nas chos
NK127(jo)001:6492: bstan pas phyir mi ldog pa'i lam du gzung ngo
NK127(jo)001:6493: // de nas mun pa mun nag gi nang na
NK127(jo)001:6494: gnod sbyin dang srin po gnas pa der song ste
NK127(jo)001:6495: // chos bstan nas / gnas gtsang mar bram ze'i
NK127(jo)001:6496: gzugs su sprul te lha'i bu rna cha mchog ces
NK127(jo)001:6497: bya ba dbul po de chos dang zang zing gis
NK127(jo)001:6498: // chos bstan nas / btul nas / sing ga
NK127(jo)001:6499: la'i gling gi srin mo rnams kyi mdun du 'dod
NK127(jo)001:6500: pa'i gzugs su sprul te chos la bkod /
NK127(jo)001:6501: de nas yul khor mo 'jig gi grong chen po
NK127(jo)001:6502: na bshang gci'i nang na srin bu'i rigs brgya stong
NK127(jo)001:6503: du ma gnas pa der bung ba'i gzugs su sprul
NK127(jo)001:6504: nas sangs rgyas la phyag 'tshal lo zhes pa'i sgra
NK127(jo)001:6505: byung bas de thams cad spos kyi dri zhes bya
NK127(jo)001:6506: ba'i byang chub sems dpar gyur te bde ba can
NK127(jo)001:6507: du skyes so // de nas yul ma ga d+h+aar
NK127(jo)001:6508: dgon par gnas pa'i sems can gcig la gcig za
NK127(jo)001:6509: ba der zas kyi char dbab cing de dag gi
NK127(jo)001:6510: basngagasa pa thos nas dga' bar byas so //
NK127(jo)001:6511: spyan ras gzigs de ni rnam par byed ces bya ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:6512: 'od ces bya ba la sogs pa'i ting nge 'dzin du ma la mnyam par bzhag ste /
NK127(jo)001:6513: de'i ba spu'i khung bu re re na yang ting nge 'dzin brgya stong dag gnas so //
NK127(jo)001:6514: spyan ras gzigs kyi bsod nams kyi tshogs de 'dra
NK127(jo)001:6515: ba ni de bzhin gshegs pa dag la yang med
NK127(jo)001:6516: na byang chub sems dpa' dag la lta ci smos
NK127(jo)001:6517: / sngon de bzhin gshegs pa log par dad sel
NK127(jo)001:6518: gyi drung du byang chub sems dpa' kun tu bzang
NK127(jo)001:6519: po rdo rje gyen du 'phags pa'i ting nge 'dzin
NK127(jo)001:6520: la zhugs pa de yi tshe /
NK127(jo)001:6521: spyan ras gzigs kyi dbang po 'thor ba zhes bya ba'i ting nge 'dzin la zhugs so //
NK127(jo)001:6522: kun tu bzang po zla ba dam pa'i mig ces bya ba'i ting nge 'dzin la zhugs pa na /
NK127(jo)001:6523: spyan ras gzigs kyi dbang po nyi ma dam pa'i
NK127(jo)001:6524: mig ces bya ba'i ting nge 'dzin la zhugs pa
NK127(jo)001:6525: sogs ji srid ting nge 'dzin du mas 'gyes pa
NK127(jo)001:6526: na kun tu bzang pos spyan ras gzigs kyi dbang
NK127(jo)001:6527: po la rigs kyi bu khyod kyi spobs pa de
NK127(jo)001:6528: 'dra ba legs so zhes smras pa na /
NK127(jo)001:6529: de bzhin gshegs pa log par dad sel gyis kun
NK127(jo)001:6530: tu bzang po la rigs kyi bu khyod kyis spyan
NK127(jo)001:6531: ras gzigs kyi dbang po'i spobs pa cung zad cig
NK127(jo)001:6533: spyan ras gzigs kyi dbang po'i spobs pa ci 'dra
NK127(jo)001:6534: ba de lta bu ni de bzhin gshegs pa la
NK127(jo)001:6535: yang mi mnga' 'o zhes bka' stsal to //
NK127(jo)001:6536: bcom ldan 'das sh+aakya'i rgyal pos byang chub sems dpa'
NK127(jo)001:6537: sgrib pa thams cad rnam par sel ba la bka'
NK127(jo)001:6538: stsal pa / spyan ras gzigs kyi dbang po'i bsod nams kyi tshogs ni ngas bgrang mi nus so //
NK127(jo)001:6539: ba spu re re'i gtam cung zad bshad na /
NK127(jo)001:6540: gser zhes bya ba'i ba spu'i khung bu de na
NK127(jo)001:6541: dri za bye ba khrag khrig brgya stong dag gnas
NK127(jo)001:6542: te / de dag sdug bsngal dang nyon mongs pas mi 'tshe la /
NK127(jo)001:6543: chos la gnas shing yid bzhin gyi nor bu las de dag gis gang bsam pa 'grub bo //
NK127(jo)001:6544: de las 'das nas nag po zhes bya ba'i ba
NK127(jo)001:6545: spu'i khung bu na drang srong bye ba brgya stong
NK127(jo)001:6546: du ma gnas te de thams cad mngon /
NK127(jo)001:6547: shes gcig nas drug gi bar dang ldan pa /
NK127(jo)001:6548: der dngul gyi sa gzhi la gser gyi ri dngul
NK127(jo)001:6549: gyi rtse mo pad+ma dmar pos brgyan pa de 'dra
NK127(jo)001:6550: ba'i ri bdun cu rtsa bdun la re re zhing
NK127(jo)001:6551: drang srong brgyad khri gnas so //
NK127(jo)001:6552: de dag gi dpag bsam gyi shing sdong po dmar po 'dab ma gser dngul las byas pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:6553: de bzhin du rdzing dang dpag bsam gyi shing gzhan
NK127(jo)001:6554: rgyan sna tshogs pas spras par lha'i gos dang zas
NK127(jo)001:6555: dang dri zhim po dag ji ltar bsam pa bzhin
NK127(jo)001:6556: 'byung ba dang chos kyi sgra thos pa la sogs
NK127(jo)001:6557: pa'i yon tan du ma dang ldan pa'o //
NK127(jo)001:6558: de bzhin du ba spu'i khung bu rin po che'i
NK127(jo)001:6559: rna cha zhes bya ba na dri za'i bu mo
NK127(jo)001:6560: gzugs bzang ba du ma gnas te de dag chags
NK127(jo)001:6561: sogs kyis mi gzir zhing spyan ras gzigs kyi mtshan
NK127(jo)001:6562: dran pas ji 'dod pa'i rdzas thams cad 'byung ngo
NK127(jo)001:6563: // ba spu'i khung bu de ni nam mkha'i khams ltar gzung ba dang reg par mi nus te /
NK127(jo)001:6564: byang chub sems dpa' kun tu bzang po ba spu'i
NK127(jo)001:6565: khung bu der lo bcu gnyis su kun tu song
NK127(jo)001:6566: yang ba spu'i khung bu de ma mthong la /
NK127(jo)001:6567: ba spu'i khung bu re re na gnas pa des
NK127(jo)001:6568: kyang ma mthong na byang chub sems dpa' gzhan gyis
NK127(jo)001:6569: lta ci smos / spyan ras gzigs de'i rang bzhin
NK127(jo)001:6570: gyi lus ni de bzhin gshegs pa nyid kyis kyang
NK127(jo)001:6571: mi gzigs na kun tu bzang po sogs byang chub
NK127(jo)001:6572: sems dpa' gzhan gyis lta ci smos /
NK127(jo)001:6573: ba spu'i khung bu bdud rtsi thigs pa zhes bya
NK127(jo)001:6574: ba na lha'i bu sa gcig pa nas bcu pa'i
NK127(jo)001:6575: bar la gnas pa'i byang chub sems dpa' rnams yod
NK127(jo)001:6576: pa'i gnas de na ri dang khang bzang chu bo
NK127(jo)001:6577: dpag bsam gyi shing la sogs pa'i bkod pa tshad
NK127(jo)001:6579: de bzhin du rdo rje'i sgo zhes bya ba'i ba
NK127(jo)001:6580: spu'i khung bu na mi'am ci du ma gnas pa
NK127(jo)001:6581: dang / nyi ma'i 'od dang dbang po'i rgyal po
NK127(jo)001:6582: la sogs pa ba spu'i khung bu sna tshogs pa'i
NK127(jo)001:6583: bkod pa tshad med pa yod pa de dag tu
NK127(jo)001:6584: spyan ras gzigs kyi mtshan dang yi ge drug pa
NK127(jo)001:6586: 'khor bar slar mi ldog par mya ngan las 'da'
NK127(jo)001:6587: ba'i bar du ba spu'i khung bu nas khung bur
NK127(jo)001:6589: gzhan yang spyan ras gzigs kyi dbang po'i rkang pa
NK127(jo)001:6590: g.yas pa'i mthe bo las mtsho chen po bzhi 'byung
NK127(jo)001:6591: ste gting dpog mi nus pa /
NK127(jo)001:6592: chu byung ba rta rgod ma'i gdong lta bur 'bab
NK127(jo)001:6593: pa sogs spyan ras gzigs de'i byin rlabs ni bsam
NK127(jo)001:6594: gyis mi khyab pas sems can tshad med pa yongs
NK127(jo)001:6595: su smin par byed cing byang chub kyi lam la
NK127(jo)001:6596: 'jog go // sngon de bzhin gshegs pa gtsug ldan
NK127(jo)001:6597: gyis byang chub sems dpa' lag na rin po che
NK127(jo)001:6599: de bzhin gshegs pa gang+g+aa'i klung gi bye ma snyed
NK127(jo)001:6600: la lha'i bskal par na bza' dang bshos dang yo
NK127(jo)001:6601: byad kyis bsnyen bkur byas pa'i bsod nams ni spyan
NK127(jo)001:6602: ras gzigs kyi ba spu gcig gi rtse la gnas
NK127(jo)001:6603: pa'i bsod nams dang mnyam mo //
NK127(jo)001:6604: gling bzhir zla ba bcu gnyis kyi lor char chen po babs pa'i thigs pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:6605: rgya mtsho mching rnam chen po'i thigs pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:6606: gling bzhir gnas pa'i ri dwags gcan gzan la sogs
NK127(jo)001:6607: pa'i spu re re nas bgrang nus kyang spyan ras
NK127(jo)001:6608: gzigs kyi dbang po'i bsod nams kyi tshogs bgrang bar
NK127(jo)001:6609: mi nus so // rdul phra rab kyi rdul snyeed
NK127(jo)001:6610: kyi de bzhin gshegs pa'i sku gzugs gser las byas
NK127(jo)001:6611: nas nyin gcig bzhin du ring bsrel bcug pa'i bsod
NK127(jo)001:6612: mi nus so // nams dang / shing sh+ri sha
NK127(jo)001:6613: pa'i tshal gyi lo ma dag bgrang nus kyi spyan
NK127(jo)001:6614: ras gzigs kyi bsod nams ni bgrang nus pa ma
NK127(jo)001:6615: mi nus so // nams dang / yin no //
NK127(jo)001:6616: ri'i rgyal po khor yug dang 'khor yug chen po
NK127(jo)001:6617: la sogs pa srang la btab pas grangs shes par
NK127(jo)001:6618: rung gi spyan ras gzigs kyi dbang po'i bsod nams
NK127(jo)001:6620: 'dzam gling gi skyes pa dang bud med thams cad
NK127(jo)001:6621: yi ge par gyur pas ri'i rgyal po mtha' yas
NK127(jo)001:6622: mu med pa gro gar gyur la rgya mtsho'i mching
NK127(jo)001:6623: rnam chen po snag tshar gyur pas /
NK127(jo)001:6624: yi ger bris pa'i 'brum bu re re nas bgrang
NK127(jo)001:6625: nus kyi spyan ras gzigs kyi dbang po'i bsod nams
NK127(jo)001:6626: kyi tshogs ni bgrang mi nus so //
NK127(jo)001:6627: dper na de bzhin gshegs pa gang+g+aa'i klung gi bye ma snyed phrag bcu gnyis dang mnyam pa la /
NK127(jo)001:6628: na bza' dang bshos dang mal stan dang na ba'i
NK127(jo)001:6629: rkyen gyi sman gyi yo byad thams cad kyis sangs
NK127(jo)001:6630: rgyas de dag la bsnyen bkur byas pa'i bsod nams
NK127(jo)001:6631: kyi phung po ni byang chub sems dpa' spyan ras
NK127(jo)001:6632: gzigs kyi skra nyag ma gcig gi rtse mo la
NK127(jo)001:6633: gnas pa'i bsod nams dang mnyam mo //
NK127(jo)001:6634: gling bzhi pa'i skyes pa dang bud med thams cad
NK127(jo)001:6635: dgra bcom pa dang rang byang chub la bkod pa'i
NK127(jo)001:6636: bsod nams ni spyan ras gzigs kyi ba spu'i rtse
NK127(jo)001:6637: mo gcig la gnas pa'i bsod nams kyi phung po
NK127(jo)001:6638: dang mnyam mo // de bzhin gshegs pa nga 'dra
NK127(jo)001:6639: ba'i sangs rgyas rnams gnas gcig tu bsnyen bkur byas
NK127(jo)001:6640: te spyan ras gzigs kyi bsod nams kyi phung po
NK127(jo)001:6641: bgrangs kyang bgrang mi nus na nga gcig pus lta
NK127(jo)001:6643: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
NK127(jo)001:6644: byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po spyan ras
NK127(jo)001:6645: gzigs kyi ming 'dzin pa dkon la de'i yi ge
NK127(jo)001:6646: drug pa'i rig sngags chen po ni de bzhin gshegs
NK127(jo)001:6647: pa thams cad kyis kyang bskal pa bcu drug tu
NK127(jo)001:6649: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi yum chen mos kyang rig sngags 'di la phyag byas pa'o //
NK127(jo)001:6650: de 'dzin cing zlos pas bsod nams tshad med pa 'thob ste /
NK127(jo)001:6651: zlos pa'i tshe de bzhin gshegs pa dang byang chub
NK127(jo)001:6652: sems dpa' rdul phra rab kyi grangs dang mnyam pa
NK127(jo)001:6653: 'du zhing de'i lus kyi ba spu re la sangs
NK127(jo)001:6654: rgyas bye ba dag bzhugs nas rigs kyi bu khyed
NK127(jo)001:6655: kyis rnyed pa legs par thob pa ste /
NK127(jo)001:6656: lto na gnas pa'i srog chags thams cad kyang phyir
NK127(jo)001:6657: mi ldog pa'i byang chub sems dpar 'gyur ro zhes
NK127(jo)001:6659: lha klu gnod sbyin la sogs pas srung bar 'gyur ro //
NK127(jo)001:6660: gang gi lus la 'chang ba de rdo rje'i lus
NK127(jo)001:6661: su 'gyur ba dang sangs rgyas kyi ye shes bye
NK127(jo)001:6663: spobs pa dang ye shes dang byams pa dang pha
NK127(jo)001:6664: rol tu phyin pa sogs yon tan thams cad rdzogs
NK127(jo)001:6665: par byed cing bla med byang chub tu myur du
NK127(jo)001:6667: gang gis de la reg pa dang mthong ba'i sems
NK127(jo)001:6668: can thams cad byang chub sems dpa' srid pa tha
NK127(jo)001:6670: rig sngags chen po 'di ni 'khor ba'i rtsa ba 'byin pa /
NK127(jo)001:6671: thar pa dang thams cad mkhyen par 'jug par bgyid
NK127(jo)001:6672: pa lags pas 'di rtsol ba de la 'dzam bu'i
NK127(jo)001:6673: gling rin po che bdun gyis bkang ste yon du
NK127(jo)001:6675: gal te 'brir 'dod pas snag tsha mchis na bdag
NK127(jo)001:6676: gi khrag las snag tsha dang pags pa las gro
NK127(jo)001:6677: ga dang rus pa'i smyu gu bgyis nas bri bar
NK127(jo)001:6678: bya ste de ni bla mar gyur pa'i phyir ro
NK127(jo)001:6679: // 'di bzlas pas nor bu rin po che 'dzin
NK127(jo)001:6680: zhes bya ba la sogs pa'i ting nge 'dzin brgya
NK127(jo)001:6682: gang zhig dran pa tsam gyis sdig pa thams cad
NK127(jo)001:6683: byang bar byed pa 'di lan gcig bzlas pa'i bsod
NK127(jo)001:6684: nams ni dper bya mi nus te /
NK127(jo)001:6685: rdul phra rab thams cad kyi grangs dang /
NK127(jo)001:6686: rgya mtsho mching rnam gyi bye ma dang /
NK127(jo)001:6687: 'phang du dpag tshad lnga brgya dang zheng du dpag
NK127(jo)001:6688: tshad brgya pa'i khyim til 'brus phyur bur bkang ba
NK127(jo)001:6690: 'bru re re phyung na zad par bgrang nus kyi
NK127(jo)001:6691: rig sngags 'di bzlas pa'i bsod nams phung po bgrang
NK127(jo)001:6692: mi nus so // de bzhin du 'dzam bu'i gling
NK127(jo)001:6693: gi 'bru thams cad legs par smin pa'i grangs dang
NK127(jo)001:6694: mi nus so // / chu bo gang g+aa sogs
NK127(jo)001:6695: bcu gcig re re zhing 'khor lnga brgya yod pa
NK127(jo)001:6696: nyid mtshan du rgya mtshor babs pa'i thigs pa dang
NK127(jo)001:6697: mi nus so // / / ri dwags g.yung dwags
NK127(jo)001:6698: gcan gzan thams cad kyi spu yi grangs bgrang ba
NK127(jo)001:6699: mi nus so // / / dang / ri'i rgyal
NK127(jo)001:6700: po rdo rje lcags kyu zhes pa 'phang du dpag
NK127(jo)001:6701: tshad dgu khri dgu stong 'og tu brgyad khri bzhi
NK127(jo)001:6702: stong ngos rer brgyad khri bzhi stong yod pa de
NK127(jo)001:6704: pa gcig 'das pa'i rjes su ka sha'i ras kyis
NK127(jo)001:6705: lan re phyis na nam zhig zad nus kyang /
NK127(jo)001:6706: yi ge drug pa lan gcig bzlas pa'i bsod nams bgrang mi nus so //
NK127(jo)001:6707: de bzhin du rgya mtsho mching rnam chen po skra rtses thigs par gzhal ba'i thigs pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:6708: lo'am zla ba bcu gsum gyi bar du nyin mtshan
NK127(jo)001:6709: bar ma chad du char chen po babs pa'i thigs
NK127(jo)001:6710: pa bgrang nus kyi yi ge drug pa lan gcig
NK127(jo)001:6711: bzlas pa'i bsod nams kyi phung po ni bgrang mi
NK127(jo)001:6712: nus so // gling bzhi na gnas pa'i skyes pa
NK127(jo)001:6713: bud med khye'u bu mo thams cad byang chub sems
NK127(jo)001:6714: dpa' sa bdun pa la gnas pa'i bsod nams kyi
NK127(jo)001:6715: phung po de bas yi ge drug pa lan gcig
NK127(jo)001:6716: bzlas pa'i bsod nams kyi phung po shin tu che
NK127(jo)001:6717: nus so // ste / de bzhin gshegs pa bye
NK127(jo)001:6718: bas gnas gcig tu lha'i bskal par bshad kyang yi
NK127(jo)001:6719: ge drug pa'i rig sngags kyi bsod nams kyi phung
NK127(jo)001:6720: po bgrang mi nus na de bzhin gshegs pa nga
NK127(jo)001:6721: gcig pu 'jig rten khams 'di na gnas pas lta
NK127(jo)001:6722: nus so // ste / ci smos / gang yi
NK127(jo)001:6723: ge drug pa 'brir 'jug pa des chos kyi phung
NK127(jo)001:6724: po brgyad khri bzhi stong 'brir 'jug par 'gyur ro
NK127(jo)001:6725: nus so // ste / ci smos / // ma ni pad+me h'u /
NK127(jo)001:6726: de bzhin gshegs pa'i sku rdul phra rab dang mnyam
NK127(jo)001:6727: pa lha'i gser las byas nas nyin bzhin ring bsrel
NK127(jo)001:6728: 'jug pa de'i rnam smin gyi 'bras bu ni yi
NK127(jo)001:6729: ge drug pa'i yi ge 'bru gcig gi 'bras bu'i
NK127(jo)001:6731: de ltar bsam gyis mi khyab la 'di 'chang ba
NK127(jo)001:6732: de spyod pa dang tshul khrims nyams pa ji ltar
NK127(jo)001:6733: gyur kyang nyon mongs pa thams cad kyis gos par
NK127(jo)001:6734: mi 'gyur te / 'di ni rdo rje mi phyed
NK127(jo)001:6735: pa'i tshig dang bla na med pa'i ye shes kyi
NK127(jo)001:6736: tshig ste thams cad kyi snying por gyur pa'o //
NK127(jo)001:6737: de bzhin gshegs pa sh+aakya'i rgyal pos byang chub sems dpa' sgrib pa rnam sel la gsungs pa /
NK127(jo)001:6738: rigs kyi bu yige drug pa'i rigs sngags 'di'i phyir
NK127(jo)001:6739: ngas sngon 'jig rten gyi khams rdul phra rab dang
NK127(jo)001:6740: mnyam par phyin te sangs rgyas bye ba khrag khrig
NK127(jo)001:6741: brgya stong du ma la bsnyen bkur byas kyang de
NK127(jo)001:6743: sangs rgyas dmar po'i mchog ces bya ba'i drung du mchi ma phyung ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:6745: rigs kyi bu mchi ma ma 'byin par de bzhin
NK127(jo)001:6746: gshegs pa pad+ma dam pa'i drung du song na des
NK127(jo)001:6747: rig sngags chen mo 'di mkhyen gyis song zhig ces
NK127(jo)001:6748: gsungs pa ltar phyin te sangs rgyas de la phyag
NK127(jo)001:6749: 'tshal zhing thal mo sbyar nas yi ge drug pa'i
NK127(jo)001:6750: rig sngags chen mo ming rjes su dran pa tsam
NK127(jo)001:6751: gyis sdig pa thams cad byang ba /
NK127(jo)001:6752: byang chub sems dpa'i thos pa rnyed dka' bar de
NK127(jo)001:6753: 'tshal lags te de'i slad du 'jig rten gyi khams
NK127(jo)001:6754: du mar phyin kyang ma thob bo //
NK127(jo)001:6756: de bzhin gshegs pa de'i rig sngags chen mo de'i basngagasa pa rgya cher gsungs shing /
NK127(jo)001:6757: rigs kyi bu ngas kyang 'jig rten gyi khams bye
NK127(jo)001:6758: ba khrag khrig brgya stong du mar song nas de
NK127(jo)001:6759: bzhin gshegs pa snang ba mtha' yas kyi spyan sngar
NK127(jo)001:6760: thal mo sbyar te chos kyi shugs kyis mchi ma
NK127(jo)001:6761: phyung ba dang / de bzhin gshegs pa des spyan ras gzigs la bka' stsal pa /
NK127(jo)001:6762: rigs kyi bu ltos de bzhin gshegs pa pad+ma'i mchog
NK127(jo)001:6763: yi ge drug pa'i rig sngags chen mo'i phyir 'jig
NK127(jo)001:6764: rten gyi khams bye ba khrag khrig brgya stong du
NK127(jo)001:6765: mar gshegs kyis rigs kyi bu yi ge drug pa
NK127(jo)001:6766: rig sngags kyi rgyal mo gsol cig /
NK127(jo)001:6767: de bzhin gshegs par gyur bzhin du yang kun tu gshegs so //
NK127(jo)001:6768: de nas byang chub sems dpa' spyan ras gzigs kyis
NK127(jo)001:6769: dkyil 'khor gyi cho ga dang bcas pa'i rig sngags
NK127(jo)001:6770: kyi rgyal po yi ge drug pa sangs rgyas pad+ma'i
NK127(jo)001:6771: mchog la byin pa dang sa chen po rgya mtsho
NK127(jo)001:6772: dang bcas pa g.yos nas bgegs dang gnod sbyin thams
NK127(jo)001:6773: cad bros so // sangs rgyas pad+ma'i mchog gis phyag
NK127(jo)001:6774: glang po che'i sna ltar brkyangs nas mu tig gi
NK127(jo)001:6775: do shal brgya stong ri ba spyan ras gzigs la
NK127(jo)001:6776: cad bros so // phul lo // des kyang blangs
NK127(jo)001:6777: nas sangs rgyas snang ba mtha' yas la phul lo
NK127(jo)001:6778: cad bros so // phul lo // // des kyang
NK127(jo)001:6779: blangs nas sangs rgyas pad+ma'i mchog la slar phul lo
NK127(jo)001:6780: cad bros so // phul lo // // // de
NK127(jo)001:6781: nas de bzhin gshegs pa pad+ma'i mchog yi ge drug
NK127(jo)001:6782: pa'i rig sngags thob nas 'jig rten gyi khams pad+ma
NK127(jo)001:6784: rigs kyi bu de ltar sngon ngas de bzhin gshegs pa pad+ma'i mchog las rig sngags 'di thos so //
NK127(jo)001:6786: sgrib pa rnam sel gyis gsol pa /
NK127(jo)001:6787: bcom ldan 'das bdag gang du mchi na yi ge drug pa'i rig sngags thob par 'gyur /
NK127(jo)001:6789: rigs kyi bu yul 'khor mo 'jig pa'i grong khyer
NK127(jo)001:6790: chen mo na yi ge drug pa'i rig sngags 'dzin
NK127(jo)001:6791: pa'i chos smra ba yod de /
NK127(jo)001:6792: gang yi ge drug pa'i rig sngags 'dzin pa'i chos smra ba de dag ni dkon pa'o //
NK127(jo)001:6793: chos smra ba de dag ni de bzhin gshegs pa dang mnyam par blta bar bya'o //
NK127(jo)001:6794: 'gro ba'i bsod nams kyi 'gram lta bu dang phung po lta bur blta bar bya'o //
NK127(jo)001:6795: de bzhin du phyin ci ma log par gsung ba lta bu dang /
NK127(jo)001:6796: rin po che'i phung po lta bu dang /
NK127(jo)001:6797: dam pa sbyin par byed pa'i yid bzhin gyi nor bu lta bu dang /
NK127(jo)001:6798: chos kyi mdzod lta bu dang /
NK127(jo)001:6799: 'gro ba sgrol bar byed pa bzhin du blta bar bya'o //
NK127(jo)001:6800: rigs kyi bu chos smra ba de dag ni tshul
NK127(jo)001:6801: khrims nyams pa spyod pa ma bsdams pa chung ma
NK127(jo)001:6802: dang bu dang bu mos bskor ba /
NK127(jo)001:6803: ngur smrig kyang gshang ba dang gci bas yongs su
NK127(jo)001:6804: gang ba yin kyang de dag gi byed pa mthong
NK127(jo)001:6805: nas the tshom skye bar mi bya ste /
NK127(jo)001:6806: byang chub sems dpa'i sa nas 'phos shing ngan song du skyes sa re /
NK127(jo)001:6807: zhes gsungs pas byang chub sems dpa' sgrib pa thams
NK127(jo)001:6808: cad rnam par sel ba 'khor brgya stong du mas
NK127(jo)001:6809: bskor nas mchod pa'i yo byad sna tshogs thogs shing
NK127(jo)001:6810: yul 'khor mo 'jig ga la ba der song ste
NK127(jo)001:6811: / chos smra ba de dag gi rkang pa la spyi bos phyag 'tshal nas /
NK127(jo)001:6812: de dag tshul khrims nyams pa /
NK127(jo)001:6814: spyod lam ma bsdams par mthong yang gdugs dang rgyan
NK127(jo)001:6815: dang byug pa la sogs pas mchod cing thal mo
NK127(jo)001:6816: sbyar te / kye ma ho chos kyi gter myong bar mdzad pa /
NK127(jo)001:6817: bdud rtsi'i gter bsags pa rgya mtsho dang mnyam pa khyod la dpag mi nus so //
NK127(jo)001:6818: zhes sogs basngagasa pa rgya cher mdzad pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:6819: chos smra ba des smras pa /
NK127(jo)001:6820: rigs kyi bu khyod 'gyod pa ma skyed cig /
NK127(jo)001:6821: grogs po nyon mongs pa ni chags pa spyad pa
NK127(jo)001:6822: dang 'khor ba'i mtshan ma dang skye dgu'i 'khor lo
NK127(jo)001:6824: gang yi ge drug pa'i rig sngags shes pa de
NK127(jo)001:6825: ni 'dod chags dang zhe sdang dang gti mug gis
NK127(jo)001:6826: mi gos te 'dzam bu'i chu bo'i gser dri mas
NK127(jo)001:6828: de nas sgrib pa rnam sel gyis de'i rkang pa la 'jus te /
NK127(jo)001:6829: dbang po nyams pa'i mig tu gyur cig /
NK127(jo)001:6830: lam ston pa la lam ston par mdzod cig /
NK127(jo)001:6831: bdag chos kyis skom pa la chos kyi ros ngoms par mdzod cig /
NK127(jo)001:6832: ces sogs yi ge drug pa'i rig sngags stsol bar gsol ba btab pa na /
NK127(jo)001:6833: chos smra ba des de la 'di skad ces smras so //
NK127(jo)001:6834: yi ge drug pa'i rig sngags kyi rgyal mo ni dkon pa'i tshig ste /
NK127(jo)001:6835: rdo rje'i tshig dang rdo rje mi phyed pa'i tshig
NK127(jo)001:6836: dang bla na med pa'i ye shes kyi tshig dang
NK127(jo)001:6837: mi zad pa'i ye shes kyi tshig dang gong na
NK127(jo)001:6839: zhes pa la sogs pa'i basngagasa pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:6840: gzhan yang 'di la cung zad bzlas kyang theg pa
NK127(jo)001:6841: chen po'i gsung rab yan lag bcu gnyis bstan pa
NK127(jo)001:6842: dang zhi ba dang thar pa thob par 'gyur ro
NK127(jo)001:6843: // sa'i nang du gtogs pa la 'bras ni snying
NK127(jo)001:6844: por gyur pa ltar rnal 'byor gzhan phub ma dang
NK127(jo)001:6845: 'dra la kun gyi nang nas rig sngags kyi rgyal
NK127(jo)001:6847: rigs kyi bu byang chub sems dpa' rnams pha rol
NK127(jo)001:6848: tu phyin pa drug gi phyir tshegs chen po byed
NK127(jo)001:6849: de / 'di lan gcig bzlas pas phar phyin drug yongs su rdzogs par byed do //
NK127(jo)001:6850: rig sngags 'di'i ming 'dzin pa tsam yang dkon te ming lan gcig bzung na /
NK127(jo)001:6851: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad la na bza' sogs
NK127(jo)001:6852: yo byad thams cad kyis bkur stir byas par 'gyur
NK127(jo)001:6853: ro // de nas sgrib pa rnam par sel bas
NK127(jo)001:6854: chos smra ba de la yi ge drug pa'i rig
NK127(jo)001:6855: sngags gnang bar gsol ba btab pa dang chos kyi
NK127(jo)001:6856: mkhan po des sems shing 'dug pa las /
NK127(jo)001:6857: nam mkha' las yi ge drug pa'i rig sngags chen
NK127(jo)001:6858: mo byin cig ces pa'i sgra byung ba ga las
NK127(jo)001:6860: yang nam mkha' las byang chub sems dpa' 'dis dka'
NK127(jo)001:6861: spyad du ma la brtson par byas kyis yi ge
NK127(jo)001:6862: drug pa'i rig sngags byin cig ces sgra byung bas
NK127(jo)001:6863: / chos smra ba des nam mkha' la bltas pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:6864: spyan ras gzigs kyi dbang po'i sku mthong bas gnang
NK127(jo)001:6865: ba byin par rig nas des de la yi ge
NK127(jo)001:6866: drug pa'i rig sngags byin pa'i mod la sa rnam
NK127(jo)001:6867: pa drug tu g.yos shing sgrib pa rnam sel gyis
NK127(jo)001:6868: mi zad pa'i chos nyid ces bya ba la sogs
NK127(jo)001:6869: pa'i ting nge 'dzin du ma thob par gyur to
NK127(jo)001:6870: // de nas sgrib pa thams cad rnam par sel
NK127(jo)001:6871: bas mkhan po la chos kyi yon du gling bzhi
NK127(jo)001:6872: rin po che sna bdun gyis bkang ba 'bul bar
NK127(jo)001:6873: // brtsams pa dang / chos kyi mkhan po des smras pa /
NK127(jo)001:6874: yi ge gcig gi yon yang med na yi ge drug pa'i lta ci smos /
NK127(jo)001:6875: rigs kyi bu nga ni khyod las len pa yang
NK127(jo)001:6876: med la khyod ni byang chub sems dpar gyur pa
NK127(jo)001:6877: ste khyod ni ngas 'dul ba yin no //
NK127(jo)001:6878: des de la mu tig gi phreng ba brgya stong ri ba phul ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:6880: nga'i tshig gis de bzhin gshegs pa sh+aakya thub pa la phul cig ces smras so //
NK127(jo)001:6881: de nas sgrib pa thams cad rnam par sel bas
NK127(jo)001:6882: chos smra ba de'i zhabs la phyag 'tshal te song
NK127(jo)001:6883: ngo // rnyed par bya ba rnyed cing bsam pa
NK127(jo)001:6884: yongs su rdzogs nas dze ta'i tshal du bcom ldan
NK127(jo)001:6885: 'das sh+aakya thub pa'i drung du 'ongs te phyag 'tshal
NK127(jo)001:6886: nas rnyed pa legs par rnyed pa'i tshul zhus so
NK127(jo)001:6887: ngo // // gzhan yang bcom ldan 'das sh+aakya thub pas bka' stsal pa /
NK127(jo)001:6888: nga sngon byang chub sems dpar gyur pa na tshong
NK127(jo)001:6889: pa lnga brgya dang bcas te rgya mtshor zhugs pa
NK127(jo)001:6890: mi mthun pa'i rlung gis srin mo'i gling du 'phangs
NK127(jo)001:6891: pa na / srin mo lnga brgya gzhon nu ma'i
NK127(jo)001:6892: gzugs su bsgyur te dga' zhing slu ba'i tshig gis
NK127(jo)001:6893: so so'i gnas su skyes pa re khrid nas song
NK127(jo)001:6894: pa na / ngo // der srin mo rgan pa
NK127(jo)001:6895: des bdag khrid pa rtse bar brtsam ste mo gnyid
NK127(jo)001:6896: log log pa dang gad mo dgod pa la ci'i
NK127(jo)001:6898: de na re 'di ni sing ga la'i gling na
NK127(jo)001:6899: gnas pa'i srin mo ste khyed srog bcad ta re
NK127(jo)001:6900: / yid mi ches na g.yas phyogs kyi lam srang du bzhud dang zer ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:6901: de ltar byas pas lcags kyi grong khyer na sngar
NK127(jo)001:6902: srin mos bzung ba'i tshong pa dag mthong ba na
NK127(jo)001:6903: / de dag gis bdag cag ni nyi ma re
NK127(jo)001:6904: re zhing mi brgya brgya re khrid de za'o zhes
NK127(jo)001:6906: ston par byed pa de la thabs dris pa na /
NK127(jo)001:6907: rta'i rgyal po ba la ha zhes bgyi ba dman
NK127(jo)001:6908: pa dang phongs pa la phan pa zhig mchis te
NK127(jo)001:6909: / des sman thams cad sbed ces pa 'tshal te
NK127(jo)001:6910: gser gyi bye ma'i thang la phar tshur 'gro zhing
NK127(jo)001:6911: lus sprugs nas pha rol tu su 'gro zhes smra
NK127(jo)001:6912: / ba la / bdag pha rol tu mchi zhes
NK127(jo)001:6913: bgyis na des pha rol tu sgrol lo zhes thos
NK127(jo)001:6914: pa de bzhin tshong pa gzhan la gtam de dag
NK127(jo)001:6915: gsang thabs su smras nas zhag gsum na 'gro bar
NK127(jo)001:6916: / ba la / bgros te / slar sing ga
NK127(jo)001:6917: la'i gling du mi blta bar dam bcas pa bzhin
NK127(jo)001:6918: chas te rta'i rgyal po'i lus sprugs pas sing ga'i
NK127(jo)001:6919: gling 'dul bar byas nas pha rol tu su 'gro
NK127(jo)001:6920: zhes lan gsum smras pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:6921: tshong pa de dag gis bdag cag pha rol tu mchi zhes smras so //
NK127(jo)001:6922: de nas rta'i rgyal po des khyod sus kyang sing
NK127(jo)001:6923: ga la'i gling la mig gis mi lta bar bya'o
NK127(jo)001:6924: zhes smras te / thog mar bdag dang de rjes
NK127(jo)001:6925: tshong pa lnga brgya zhon pa de'i tshe srin mo
NK127(jo)001:6926: dag phyi bzhin bsnyags nas snying rje rje ltar smra
NK127(jo)001:6927: zhes smras te / ba dang / de dag gi
NK127(jo)001:6928: ngo slar log ste bltas pas kha sbub tu chu'i
NK127(jo)001:6929: nang du lhung ba srin mo dag gis drangs shing
NK127(jo)001:6930: zhes smras te / ba dang / zos la / nga gcig pu 'dzam bu'i gling du phyin no //
NK127(jo)001:6931: de'i tshe 'gram du nye ba dang rta'i rgyal po
NK127(jo)001:6932: ba la has nga la lan gsum bskor te phyag
NK127(jo)001:6933: byas nas de nyid du song ngo //
NK127(jo)001:6934: nga yang rim gyis bdag gi khyim du pha ma dang 'phrad pas dga' bar gyur to //
NK127(jo)001:6935: nga ded dpon du gyur pa ni 'di lta bu'i
NK127(jo)001:6936: sdug bsngal dang 'chi ba'i 'jigs pa las spyan ras
NK127(jo)001:6937: gzigs kyi dbang po rta ba la har gyur pas
NK127(jo)001:6939: de ltar spyan ras gzigs kyi dbang po ni mgon med pa rnams kyi mgon /
NK127(jo)001:6940: skyabs med pa rnams kyi skyabs /
NK127(jo)001:6941: 'jigs shing skrags pa rnams la mi 'jigs pa'i sbyin pa /
NK127(jo)001:6942: mun par gyur pa rnams kyi sgron mar gyur pa /
NK127(jo)001:6943: nyi mas gdung ba rnams kyi gdugs su gyur pa /
NK127(jo)001:6944: nad kyis btab pa rnams kyi sman /
NK127(jo)001:6945: sdug bsngal ba rnams kyi pha ma /
NK127(jo)001:6946: bstir med par skyes pa rnams kyi mya ngan las 'das pa ston par byed pa ste /
NK127(jo)001:6947: spyan ras gzigs kyi dbang po de'i ming dran pa
NK127(jo)001:6948: de dag ni bde ba dang ldan pa yin no
NK127(jo)001:6949: // de dag ni rga na 'chi ba'i sdug bsngal
NK127(jo)001:6950: las thar te 'khor ba'i tha mar 'gyur zhing bde
NK127(jo)001:6951: ba can du skyes nas snang ba mtha' yas las
NK127(jo)001:6952: chos nyan cing rtag tu de na gnas par 'gyur
NK127(jo)001:6954: snying rje pad+ma dkar po las /
NK127(jo)001:6955: sngon bskal pa grangs med pa gang g+aa'i klung gcig gi bye ma snyed 'das pa na /
NK127(jo)001:6956: sangs rgyas kyi zhing 'dir bskal pa chen po 'dzin
NK127(jo)001:6957: pa zhes bya ba la de bzhin gshegs pa rin
NK127(jo)001:6958: chen snying po zhes bya ba 'jig rten du byung
NK127(jo)001:6959: ngo // zhing der 'khor los sgyur brtsibs kyi mu
NK127(jo)001:6960: khyud ces pa bu stong dang ldan par byung bas
NK127(jo)001:6961: de bzhin gshegs pa 'khor dang bcas pa la bsnyen
NK127(jo)001:6962: bkur rgya chen po byas so //
NK127(jo)001:6963: de'i tshe bdag cag gi ston pa 'di rgyal po
NK127(jo)001:6964: de'i mdun na 'don bram ze rgya mtsho'i rdul zhes
NK127(jo)001:6965: bya ba de bzhin gshegs pa rin chen snying po
NK127(jo)001:6967: des rgyal po de dang sras stong dang sems can
NK127(jo)001:6968: gzhan shin tu mang po dag dman pa'i bsam pa
NK127(jo)001:6969: las bzlog ste bla med byang chub 'dzin du bcug
NK127(jo)001:6970: pa las / der rgyal po'i bu thu bo mig
NK127(jo)001:6971: mi 'dzum pas de bzhin gshegs pa rin chen snying
NK127(jo)001:6973: bcom ldan 'das bdag gis ngan song dang mtho ris
NK127(jo)001:6974: kyi sems can thams cad la bltas nas de dag
NK127(jo)001:6975: gi ched du go cha bgos nas dge ba'i rtsa
NK127(jo)001:6976: ba thams cad bla med byang chub tu bsngo zhing
NK127(jo)001:6977: / bdag byang chub sems dpa'i spyad pa spyod pa na /
NK127(jo)001:6978: sems can gang dag sdug bsngal gyis gzir ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:6980: chos kyi mu ges mun par zhugs pa rnams dang /
NK127(jo)001:6981: zhum pa dang zhan pa dang skyabs dang dpung gnyen
NK127(jo)001:6982: ma mchis pa rnams kyis bdag rjes su dran zhing
NK127(jo)001:6983: ming brjod na / bdag gi lha'i rna bas thos
NK127(jo)001:6984: shing lha'i mig gis mthong nas de dag sdug bsngal
NK127(jo)001:6985: las thar bar ma bgyis par bdag bla med byang
NK127(jo)001:6986: chub tu 'tshang rgya bar ma gyur cig /
NK127(jo)001:6987: bdag gi smon lam gyi khyad par gyis sems can
NK127(jo)001:6988: gyi don du yun ring por byang chub sems dpa'i
NK127(jo)001:6989: spyod pa spyad pa'i tshe bdag gi re ba yongs
NK127(jo)001:6991: rgyal po rtsibs kyi mu khyud 'di bde ba can
NK127(jo)001:6992: du de bzhin gshegs pa tshe dpag tu med par
NK127(jo)001:6993: sangs rgyas nas mya ngan las 'da' ba'i bar du
NK127(jo)001:6994: bdag byang chub sems dpa'i spyod pa spyad nas /
NK127(jo)001:6995: de'i 'og tu 'tshang rgya bar gyur cig ces smon
NK127(jo)001:6996: lam btab pas de bzhin gshegs pa rin chen snying
NK127(jo)001:6998: rigs kyi bu khyod kyis sems can thams cad sdug
NK127(jo)001:6999: bsngal dang nyon mongs pa las thar bar bya ba'i
NK127(jo)001:7000: phyir snying rje'i sems bskyed pas spyan ras gzigs dbang
NK127(jo)001:7002: khyod byang chub sems dpar gyur pa na yang sangs rgyas kyi mdzad pa byed par 'gyur la /
NK127(jo)001:7003: sangs rgyas 'od dpag med mya ngan las 'das nas
NK127(jo)001:7004: bskal pa grangs med pa gang+g+aa'i klung gi bye ma
NK127(jo)001:7005: snyed gnyis pa lus pa na nam gang gi srod
NK127(jo)001:7006: la dam pa'i chos nub pa'i tho rangs la /
NK127(jo)001:7007: byang chub shing bkod pa du ma'i drung du rdo
NK127(jo)001:7008: rje'i gdan la khyod bla na med pa'i byang chub
NK127(jo)001:7010: de bzhin gshegs pa 'od zer kun nas 'phags pa dpal brtsegs rgyal po zhes bya bar 'gyur ro //
NK127(jo)001:7011: de'i tshe tshad ni bskal pa bye ba khrag khrig 'bum phrag dgu bcu rtsa drug tu 'gyur ro //
NK127(jo)001:7013: 'phags pa sgyu ma lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin zhes bya ba'i mdo las /
NK127(jo)001:7014: de bzhin gshegs pa sh+aakya thub pa'i 'od zer gyis
NK127(jo)001:7015: bskul bas bde ba can gyi zhing nas byang chub
NK127(jo)001:7016: sems dpa' chen po spyan ras gzigs dang mthu chen
NK127(jo)001:7017: thob gnyis zhing 'dir mchis pa na /
NK127(jo)001:7018: rnam par 'phrul ba'i bkod pa du ma dang khang
NK127(jo)001:7019: pa brtsegs pa bye ba phrag brgyad cu rtsa bzhi
NK127(jo)001:7020: bkod pa mchog tu 'phags pa du mas brgyan pa
NK127(jo)001:7021: sprul zhing / der byang chub sems dpa' de snyed
NK127(jo)001:7022: kyi 'khor dang bcas pa gshegs te sangs rgyas kyi
NK127(jo)001:7023: zhabs la phyag byas nas tshigs su bcad pas bstod
NK127(jo)001:7024: sprul zhing / pa ni / de bzhin gshegs pas
NK127(jo)001:7025: byang chub sems dpa' pad+ma'i dpal gyi snying po la
NK127(jo)001:7026: sprul zhing / pa ni / bka' stsal pa /
NK127(jo)001:7027: rigs kyi bu skyes bu dam pa 'di gnyis ni
NK127(jo)001:7028: bskal pa grangs med pa nas dge ba'i rtsa ba
NK127(jo)001:7030: sgyu ma lta bu'i ting 'dzin thob nas rdzu 'phrul sna tshogs ston pas /
NK127(jo)001:7031: khyod kyis shar phyogs su ci snang ba ltos shig ces bka' stsal pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:7032: pad+ma'i dpal gyi snying pos bltas pas shar phyogs sangs
NK127(jo)001:7033: rgyas kyi zhing gang+g+aa'i klung gi bye ma snyed na
NK127(jo)001:7034: sangs rgyas de snyed kyi drung du byang chub sems
NK127(jo)001:7035: dpa' spyan ras gzigs dang mthu chen thob gnyis de
NK127(jo)001:7036: snyed kyis bsnyun gsol ba la sogs pa /
NK127(jo)001:7037: phyogs bcu re re zhing yang de snyed du mthong
NK127(jo)001:7038: zhing ngo mtshar nas skyes bu dam pa 'di gnyis
NK127(jo)001:7039: kyis de bzhin gshegs pa gang las sems bskyed nas
NK127(jo)001:7040: ji srid cig lags zhes zhus pa na /
NK127(jo)001:7042: sngon 'das pa'i bskal pa grangs med pa'i yang ches
NK127(jo)001:7043: grangs med pa'i 'jig rten gyi khams brgya stong gi
NK127(jo)001:7044: rdul phra rab kyi grangs ji snyed pa de bas
NK127(jo)001:7045: kyang ches bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i bskal pa la
NK127(jo)001:7046: / 'jig rten gyi khams rin chen bsags pa dpag
NK127(jo)001:7047: tu med pa bde ba kun tu ston pa zhes
NK127(jo)001:7048: / bya bar / de bzhin gshegs pa gser 'od
NK127(jo)001:7049: seng ge rnam par rol pa'i rgyal po zhes bya
NK127(jo)001:7050: / bya bar / ba byung ste / de'i sangs
NK127(jo)001:7051: rgyas kyi zhing ni yon tan tshad med de dpe
NK127(jo)001:7053: da ltar bde ba can gyi zhing gi bkod pa
NK127(jo)001:7054: ni skra rtse brgyar gshags pa'i rtse mos blangs pa'i
