NK127(jo)001:7056: sangs rgyas de'i zhing gi bkod pa ni rgya mtsho
NK127(jo)001:7057: chen po'i chu'i phung po lhag ma dang 'dra la
NK127(jo)001:7058: zhing de'i yon tan gyi basngagasa pa ni bskal pa
NK127(jo)001:7059: gang+g+aa'i bye snyed du brjod kyang mi zad do //
NK127(jo)001:7060: zhing der 'jig rten gyi khams stong gi dbang phyug
NK127(jo)001:7061: chos kyi rgyal po dpal gyi gzi brjid ces bya
NK127(jo)001:7062: ba bu bye ba phrag brgya yod pa /
NK127(jo)001:7063: thams cad bla med byang chub la zhugs pa de
NK127(jo)001:7064: dag lhan cig pas sangs rgyas de la lo bye
NK127(jo)001:7065: ba stong phrag brgyad khri bzhi stong gi bar du
NK127(jo)001:7066: bsnyen bkur byas zhing tshad med pa'i phyag rgya zhes
NK127(jo)001:7067: bya ba'i chos kyi tshul bzung ngo //
NK127(jo)001:7068: dus gzhan zhig na rgyal po de skyed mos tshal
NK127(jo)001:7069: na bsam gtan la gnas pa'i glo g.yas g.yon nas
NK127(jo)001:7070: tsan+dana sbrul gyi snying po'i pad+ma bkra ba lta na
NK127(jo)001:7072: khye'u rin chen sems dang rin chen mchog ces bya
NK127(jo)001:7073: ba gnyis bardzusa te byung nas 'dug pa mthong bas
NK127(jo)001:7074: de dag dang phan tshun 'dri ba dang lan gyi
NK127(jo)001:7075: sgo nas rgyal pos kyang mngon par shes pa lnga
NK127(jo)001:7076: bsgrubs te / khye'u de gnyis rgyal po dang lhan
NK127(jo)001:7077: cig pas bcom ldan 'das gser 'od seng ge rnam
NK127(jo)001:7078: par rol pa'i rgyal po ga la ba der dong
NK127(jo)001:7080: khye'u gnyis kyis rgyal ba ji ltar mchod par bya zhes tshigs su bcad pa zhus pa'i tshe /
NK127(jo)001:7081: byang chub tu sems bskyed na mchod pa'i dam par 'gyur zhes basngagasa pa bka' stsal pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:7082: khye'u de gnyis kyis sngon gyi mtha' mi dmigs pa
NK127(jo)001:7083: de snyed kyi bskal par sems can gyi don du
NK127(jo)001:7085: deng phan chad nyon mongs pa'i sems dang mi dge ba'i sems mi skyed pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:7086: sangs rgyas kyi zhing 'di bzhin dag pa'i zhing yongs
NK127(jo)001:7087: su sbyong bar bgyi zhes gsol bas sa g.yo ba
NK127(jo)001:7089: de la rgyal po gzi brjid dpal ni de bzhin gshegs pa 'od dpag med yin la /
NK127(jo)001:7090: khye'u rin chen mchog ni spyan ras gzigs dang /
NK127(jo)001:7091: rin chen sems ni mthu chen thob ste dang por sems bskyed pa de yin la /
NK127(jo)001:7092: gang+g+aa'i klung gi bye ma mtha' rtogs nus kyi skyes
NK127(jo)001:7093: bu dam pa 'di gnyis kyis de bzhin gshegs pa
NK127(jo)001:7094: de'i pha rol na sangs rgyas la bsnyen bkur byas
NK127(jo)001:7095: pa'i sangs rgyas de dag ni de lta ma yin
NK127(jo)001:7096: te de srid du 'di gnyis sems bskyed do //
NK127(jo)001:7097: 'di gnyis ni bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i go cha bgos pa /
NK127(jo)001:7098: yon tan dpag tu med pa /
NK127(jo)001:7099: yon tan gyi mtha' rtogs par mi nus pa'o //
NK127(jo)001:7100: byang chub sems dpa' spyan ras gzigs ni bde ba
NK127(jo)001:7101: can gyi zhing 'di rin chen kun nas bsags pa
NK127(jo)001:7102: zhes bya ba'i 'jig rten du ming 'gyur ba der
NK127(jo)001:7103: / de bzhin gshegs pa 'od zer kun nas 'phags
NK127(jo)001:7104: pa'i dpal brtsegs rgyal po zhes bya bar 'tshang rgya
NK127(jo)001:7105: / bar 'gyur te / de'i zhing gi bkod pa
NK127(jo)001:7106: ni de bzhin gshegs pas bskal pa gang+g+aa'i klung gi
NK127(jo)001:7107: bye ma snyed du bstan kyang mtha' rtogs par mi
NK127(jo)001:7108: / bar 'gyur te / nus so // sngar bstan
NK127(jo)001:7109: pa gser 'od seng ge rnam par rol pa'i rgyal
NK127(jo)001:7110: po'i zhing gi bkod pas kyang zhing 'di'i brgya stong
NK127(jo)001:7111: gi cha dang dpe tsam yang mi bzod do //
NK127(jo)001:7112: byang chub sems dpa' mthu chen thob ni dpal brtsegs
NK127(jo)001:7113: rgyal po 'das pa'i 'og tu chos nub pa na
NK127(jo)001:7115: de bzhin gshegs pa yon tan shin tu gnas pa
NK127(jo)001:7116: nor bu brtsegs pa'i rgyal po zhes bya bar 'gyur
NK127(jo)001:7117: la / zhing dang byang chub sems dpa' ni dpal brtsegs rgyal po de ji 'dra bar 'gyur ro //
NK127(jo)001:7118: sangs rgyas 'di gnyis kyi mtshan thos pa de dag
NK127(jo)001:7119: bla med byang chub las phyir mi ldog par 'gyur
NK127(jo)001:7120: ro // 'das pa'i sangs rgyas gser 'od seng ge rnam par rol pa'i rgyal po de dang /
NK127(jo)001:7121: ma 'ongs pa'i sangs rgyas 'di gnyis kyi mtshan thos na bud med du mi 'gyur /
NK127(jo)001:7122: bskal pa bye ba phrag bzhi bcur 'khor ba phyir bsnyil bar 'gyur /
NK127(jo)001:7123: bla med byang chub las phyir mi ldog pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:7126: dge 'dun la bsnyen bkur byed pa dang mi 'bral bar 'gyur /
NK127(jo)001:7127: tshe barjesa nas kyang rab tu byung ba thob pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:7129: spobs pa thogs pa med pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:7132: dam pa'i chos pad+ma dkar po las /
NK127(jo)001:7133: bcom ldan 'das la byang chub sems dpa' blo gros mi zad pas /
NK127(jo)001:7134: ci'i phyir spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug ces bgyi zhes gsol ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:7136: sems can bye ba khrag khrig brgya stong ji snyed pa gang dag sdug bsngal gang myong ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:7137: me chen por lhung ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:7138: chu klung gis khyer ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:7139: rin po che'i phyir rgya mtshor dong ba /
NK127(jo)001:7140: rlung nag pos srin mo'i gling du bdas pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:7141: gshed mas gsad par gzas pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:7142: ri yi rtse nas 'phangs pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:7143: lcags sgrog sogs kyis bcings pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:7144: sman dang sngags dang ro langs dang 'byung po sogs kyi 'jigs pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:7145: gcan gzan ma rungs pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:7146: thog dang ser ba drag po byung ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:7147: sha za ma rungs pa la sogs te 'jigs pa
NK127(jo)001:7148: dang sdug bsngal ci byung yang spyan ras gzigs kyi
NK127(jo)001:7149: dbang po'i mtshan thos na 'jigs pa dang nyam nga
NK127(jo)001:7150: ba de dag las myur du thar bar 'gyur te
NK127(jo)001:7151: / stong gsum 'di gnod sbyin dang srin pos gang
NK127(jo)001:7152: bar gyur kyang de thams cad kyis spyan ras gzigs
NK127(jo)001:7153: kyi mtshan 'dzin pa la sdang ba'i sems kyis lta
NK127(jo)001:7155: gsang ba'i phyir rdo rje'i ri chen po spyi bor
NK127(jo)001:7156: bab kyang spyan ras gzigs kyi dbang po dran na
NK127(jo)001:7157: de'i ba spu'i khung bu tsam yang gtse bar mi
NK127(jo)001:7158: nus so // de bzhin du stong gsum 'di mtshon
NK127(jo)001:7159: thogs pa'i dgras gang bar gyur kyang spyan ras gzigs
NK127(jo)001:7160: kyi mtshan thos na 'jigs pa de las thar bar
NK127(jo)001:7161: nus so // 'gyur ro // gang 'dod chags dang
NK127(jo)001:7162: zhe sdang dang gti mug gis gzir bas de'i mtshan
NK127(jo)001:7163: bzung na nyon mongs pa de dag dang bral bar
NK127(jo)001:7165: bzhin du mi khoms pa dang 'thab cing rtsod pa
NK127(jo)001:7166: dang 'chi ba'i dus sogs shin tu nyam thag pa'i
NK127(jo)001:7167: tshe byams shing snying rje chen po'i mnga' bdag 'di
NK127(jo)001:7168: ni mgon dang dpung gnyen dam par gyur pa'o //
NK127(jo)001:7169: bu dang bu mo sogs 'dod pas de'i mtshan bzung
NK127(jo)001:7170: na gzugs bzang ba'i khye'u dang bu mo 'byung zhing
NK127(jo)001:7171: dge ba'i rtsa ba skyed par byed do //
NK127(jo)001:7172: gang zhig sangs rgyas gang+g+aa'i klung drug cu rtsa gnyis
NK127(jo)001:7173: kyi bye ma snyed la phyag 'tshal zhing mtshan 'dzin
NK127(jo)001:7174: pa dang / sangs rgyas de snyed tsam 'tsho zhing
NK127(jo)001:7175: gzhes pa la na bza' bsod snyoms sogs yo byad
NK127(jo)001:7176: thams cad kyis mchod pa byas pa nas gang zhig
NK127(jo)001:7177: tha na spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug la phyag lan
NK127(jo)001:7179: ming 'dzin pa'i bsod nams mngon par 'du byed pa
NK127(jo)001:7180: gnyis mnyam ste lhag pa dang 'phags pa yang med
NK127(jo)001:7181: do // de'i bsod nams bskal pa bye ba khrag
NK127(jo)001:7182: khrig tu yang zad par sla ba ma yin te
NK127(jo)001:7183: do // / de ltar bsod nams dpag tu med do //
NK127(jo)001:7184: spyan ras gzigs ni sangs rgyas nas phal pa'i bar
NK127(jo)001:7185: gyi gzugs sna tshogs pa gang gis 'dul pa la
NK127(jo)001:7186: de ltar snang zhing chos ston te /
NK127(jo)001:7187: sems can thams cad la mi 'jigs pa sbyin pa
NK127(jo)001:7188: yin pas mi mjed 'di na'ang mi 'jigs pa sbyin
NK127(jo)001:7189: pa zhes kun gyis shes so //
NK127(jo)001:7190: zhes dang slar yang tshigs su bcad pa'i sgo nas
NK127(jo)001:7191: kyang spyan ras gzigs kyi basngagasa pa rgya cher gsungs
NK127(jo)001:7192: so // sangs rgyas phal po che las /
NK127(jo)001:7193: tshong dpon gyi bu nor bu bzang po gru 'dzin
NK127(jo)001:7194: gyi ri la song nas spyan ras gzigs kyi dbang
NK127(jo)001:7195: po la phyag 'tshal te byang chub sems dpa'i spyod
NK127(jo)001:7197: spyan ras gzigs kyi phyag g.yas pa 'dzam bu chu
NK127(jo)001:7198: bo'i gser gyi mdog can 'od kyi d+r+wa ba sna
NK127(jo)001:7199: tshogs tshad med pa'i rgyan gyi sprin 'gyed pa brkyangs
NK127(jo)001:7200: te nor bzangs kyi spyi bor bzhag nas /
NK127(jo)001:7201: rigs kyi bu bdag byang chub sems dpa'i spyod pa'i sgo snying rje chen po la gnas pas /
NK127(jo)001:7202: de bzhin gshegs pa'i zhabs drung nas kyang mi g.yo
NK127(jo)001:7203: la sems can thams cad kyi dgos pa la nye
NK127(jo)001:7204: bar gnas te / bsdu pa'i dngos po dang gzugs
NK127(jo)001:7205: dang mdog sna tshogs dang 'od 'gyed pa dang dbyangs
NK127(jo)001:7206: dang spyod lam dang chos bstan pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:7207: bsam pa dang mthun pa'i rdzu 'phrul sna tshogs kyis
NK127(jo)001:7208: kyang sems can rnams yongs su sgrub pa dang yongs
NK127(jo)001:7210: sems can rnams kyi rgyud kyi 'jigs pa sna tshogs
NK127(jo)001:7211: pa g.yang sa dang mgo rmongs pa dang bcings pa
NK127(jo)001:7212: dang srog la bab pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:7213: yo byad kyis phongs pa dang 'tsho ba med pa
NK127(jo)001:7214: dang grags pa med pa dang 'khor du bag tsha
NK127(jo)001:7215: ba dang 'chi ba dang ngan song dang lam du
NK127(jo)001:7216: mun pas nyam nga ba dang skal pa mi mnyam
NK127(jo)001:7218: sdug pa dang bral ba dang mi sdug pa dang
NK127(jo)001:7219: 'grogs pa dang lus dang sems mi bde ba dang
NK127(jo)001:7220: 'khor ba'i 'jigs pa dang sems can thams cad kyi
NK127(jo)001:7221: sdug bsngal dang yid mi bde ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:7222: 'khrugs pa las yongs su bzla ba'i phyir dang 'gro
NK127(jo)001:7223: ba thams cad rab tu rten pa'i phyir smon lam
NK127(jo)001:7224: 'di mngon par sgrub par byas so //
NK127(jo)001:7225: sems can thams cad kyi 'jigs pa rnam par zhi
NK127(jo)001:7226: ba'i phyir 'jig rten du yang rjes su dran pa'i
NK127(jo)001:7228: sems can 'jigs pa thams cad dang bral bar bya
NK127(jo)001:7229: ba'i phyir rang gi ming yang 'jig rten du dmigs
NK127(jo)001:7230: par byas so // dus ji lta ba bzhin du
NK127(jo)001:7231: 'gro bas dmigs par bya ba'i phyir 'gro ba thams
NK127(jo)001:7232: cad kyi rnam pa'i bye brag mtha' yas pa dang
NK127(jo)001:7233: mnyam par lus kyang de snyed du byin gyis brlabs
NK127(jo)001:7234: par byas so // so // nga yi lus 'dis
NK127(jo)001:7235: sems can thams cad 'jigs pa las bkrol zhing sangs
NK127(jo)001:7236: rgyas kyi chos thams cad thob par bya ba'i phyir
NK127(jo)001:7237: bla med rdzogs pa'i byang chub tu sems bskyed cing
NK127(jo)001:7238: phyir mi ldog par byed do //
NK127(jo)001:7240: spyan ras gzigs kyi dbang po mkhas pas tshig 'di smras /
NK127(jo)001:7241: sangs rgyas sras po nga ni rnam thar gcig sgo shes //
NK127(jo)001:7242: ye shes snying po rgyal ba kun gyi thugs rje'i shugs //
NK127(jo)001:7243: 'gro ba thams cad bskyab cing yongs su bzla phyir byung //
NK127(jo)001:7244: kun tu bdag nyid rang la byams pa bzhin du rgyu //
NK127(jo)001:7245: 'gro ba mang po thams cad sdug bsngal kun las skyob //
NK127(jo)001:7246: gang rnams dam du bcings shing dgra la'ang byin pa dang //
NK127(jo)001:7247: lus la gzer zhing de bzhin brtson rar chud pa yang //
NK127(jo)001:7248: nga yi ming thos bcings shing bzung ba thar bar 'gyur //
NK127(jo)001:7249: rgyal po dag la nyes pa'i g.yon byas gsad spangs pa //
NK127(jo)001:7250: de tshe de dag nga yi ming yang dran gyur na //
NK127(jo)001:7251: mda' 'phang de yi lus la phog par mi 'gyur te //
NK127(jo)001:7252: mtshon rnon btab kyang de dag mi 'dzugs rgal bar 'gyur //
NK127(jo)001:7253: dbang po'i 'khor du phyin kyang gang rnams rtsod gyur pa //
NK127(jo)001:7254: dgra rnams kun las rgyal 'gyur grags pa thob par 'gyur //
NK127(jo)001:7255: grags dang grogs dang rigs dang nor rnams 'phel bar 'gyur //
NK127(jo)001:7256: nga yi ming dran de dag thub pa med par 'gyur //
NK127(jo)001:7257: gang gis nga yi ming ni rjes su dran byas pa //
NK127(jo)001:7258: de dag rkun pos 'jigs dogs dgras 'jigs nags phyin te //
NK127(jo)001:7259: seng ge dom gzig gcan gzan g.yag rgod sprul gang yang //
NK127(jo)001:7260: dgra rnams kun las rgyal zhing 'jigs pa med par 'gyur //
NK127(jo)001:7261: gang rnams la las nga yi ming zhig dran byas na //
NK127(jo)001:7262: sdang ba'i sems kyis ri chen ltongs su bor gyur tam //
NK127(jo)001:7263: sol mdag lci me rab tu 'bar bar bor gyur kyang //
NK127(jo)001:7264: me rnams pad+mosa gang ba'i chu yi gter du 'gyur //
NK127(jo)001:7265: nga yi ming ni skad 'ga' yud tsam rjes dran na //
NK127(jo)001:7266: rgya mtsho'i chur bor de yi nang du 'chi mi 'gyur //
NK127(jo)001:7267: chu bos mi 'khyer me yi dbus su tshig mi 'gyur //
NK127(jo)001:7268: don med kun tu mi 'gyur don rnams grub par 'gyur //
NK127(jo)001:7269: shing sgrog dbyig chings lcags sgrog de bzhin lhung rnams dang //
NK127(jo)001:7270: brnyas shing khyad bsad de bzhin brid cing bslus pa dang //
NK127(jo)001:7271: spyos shing bsdigs te gshe dang sma phab rnam pa las //
NK127(jo)001:7272: nga yi ming tsam dran par byas na thar pa thob //
NK127(jo)001:7273: gang rnams shar gnyer sna tshogs blags lta ji snyed dang //
NK127(jo)001:7274: gang rnams rtag tu zhe sdang mi snyan brjod pa'i rnams //
NK127(jo)001:7275: nga yi ming thos dran byas snyan par brjod par 'gyur //
NK127(jo)001:7276: mthong ba tsam gyi mod la byams pa'i sems kyang skye //
NK127(jo)001:7277: nga yi ming tsam la la gang gis dran byas na //
NK127(jo)001:7278: gnod pa'i don du ro langs sngags dang byad byed pa'i //
NK127(jo)001:7279: dgra rnams rtag tu de yis zil gyis gnon par 'gyur //
NK127(jo)001:7280: ma lus dug gis de yi lus la mi tshugs so //
NK127(jo)001:7281: la la gang gis nga yi ming tsam dran byas na //
NK127(jo)001:7282: klu dbang srin tshogs mkha' lding sha za thams cad dang //
NK127(jo)001:7283: grul bum srul po 'tshe byed gtum po'i sems dang ldan //
NK127(jo)001:7284: mdangs 'phrog 'jigs byed rmi lam 'ong ba'ang zhi bar 'gyur //
NK127(jo)001:7285: nga yi ming ni skad cig yud tsam dran byas kyang //
NK127(jo)001:7286: pha dang ma dang gnyen bshes mdza' ba kun dang yang //
NK127(jo)001:7287: 'bral bar mi 'gyur sdang dang 'grogs par de bzhin min //
NK127(jo)001:7288: nor zad mi 'gyur phongs pa'i dngos su mi 'gyur ro //
NK127(jo)001:7289: nga yi ming ni rjes su la la dran byed na //
NK127(jo)001:7290: 'di nas shi 'phos mnar med sems dmyal mi 'gro ste //
NK127(jo)001:7291: byol song skye gnas yi dwags mi khoms gnas su min //
NK127(jo)001:7292: sems can dag pa lha dang mi yi gnas su skye //
NK127(jo)001:7293: nga yi ming ni la la gang gis dran byas na //
NK127(jo)001:7294: dmus long zhar ba 'on pa zha bor mi 'gyur te //
NK127(jo)001:7295: 'theng po long par mi 'gyur gsal smra blta sdug 'gyur //
NK127(jo)001:7296: bskal pa bye ba mang por dbang po kun ldan 'gyur //
NK127(jo)001:7297: la la gang gis nga yi ming ni rjes dran na //
NK127(jo)001:7298: sems can dag pa 'di nas shi 'phos phyogs bcu yi //
NK127(jo)001:7299: 'jig rten khams su sangs rgyas mngon sum skye bar 'gyur //
NK127(jo)001:7300: sangs rgyas mthong 'gyur de dag chos kyang thos par 'gyur //
NK127(jo)001:7301: 'di dang de bzhin gzhan dag thabs mang ji snyed kyis //
NK127(jo)001:7302: 'gro bar sems can de 'dul gzhal dang zad mi nus //
NK127(jo)001:7305: gal te de la gnod pa byed pa nye bar gnas //
NK127(jo)001:7306: gshed mas mtshon rnams kyis ni gdab par gzas pa las //
NK127(jo)001:7307: spyan ras gzigs kyi dbang po rjes su dran na ni //
NK127(jo)001:7308: mtshon cha de dag dum bu dum bur chag cing 'brul //
NK127(jo)001:7309: gal te mtshon cha rnams ni thogs par gyur na yang //
NK127(jo)001:7310: lag pa chag nas sa la rab tu lhung bar 'gyur //
NK127(jo)001:7311: de yi lus la cung zad 'bab par mi 'gyur te //
NK127(jo)001:7312: sngon chad byas pa gang yin pa ni ma gtogs so //
NK127(jo)001:7314: thugs rje chen po gzungs kyi phan yon mdor bsdus pa las /
NK127(jo)001:7315: gang zhig ri dang 'brog dgon song ba las //
NK127(jo)001:7316: stag dang spyang ki gcan gzan gtum po dang //
NK127(jo)001:7317: rtsangs pa sbrul dang 'dre srin phrad gyur kyang //
NK127(jo)001:7318: gzungs 'di 'don pa thos na gnod mi 'gyur //
NK127(jo)001:7319: gang zhig chu bo rgya mtshor zhugs pa las //
NK127(jo)001:7320: gdug pa'i klu dang chu srin ma rungs dang //
NK127(jo)001:7321: gnod sbyin srin po nya dang rus sbal dag /
NK127(jo)001:7322: gzungs 'di thos nas so sor 'byer bar 'gyur //
NK127(jo)001:7323: gang zhig g.yul sprad dgra yis bskor ba'am //
NK127(jo)001:7324: chom rkun ma rungs nor ni 'phrog pa'i tshe //
NK127(jo)001:7325: rtse gcig thugs rje chen po'i gzungs bzlas na //
NK127(jo)001:7326: de dag brtse sems skyes nas ldog par 'gyur //
NK127(jo)001:7327: gang zhig rgyal po'i gyod la thogs pa dang //
NK127(jo)001:7328: lcags sgrog khong sgril brtson rar chud pa'i tshe //
NK127(jo)001:7329: rtse gcig thugs rje chen po'i gzungs bzlas na //
NK127(jo)001:7330: rgyal po brtse sems skyes nas gtong bar 'gyur //
NK127(jo)001:7331: gang zhig byad stems dug ma'i khyim zhugs te //
NK127(jo)001:7332: zas skom dug can gyis ni gsod pa'i tshe //
NK127(jo)001:7333: rtse gcig thugs rje chen po'i gzungs bzlas na //
NK127(jo)001:7334: dug ni zil dngar zas skom nyid du 'gyur //
NK127(jo)001:7335: bud med sbrum ma bu ni btsa' ba'i tshe //
NK127(jo)001:7336: bdud kyis bgegs byas sdug bsngal mi bzod tshe //
NK127(jo)001:7337: rtse gcig thugs rje chen po'i gzungs bzlas na //
NK127(jo)001:7338: 'dre gdon byer nas bde bar btsa' bar 'gyur //
NK127(jo)001:7339: klu gdon gtum pos gdugs pa'i dbugs btang bas //
NK127(jo)001:7340: tsha ba'i nad kyis nyen nas 'chir nye tshe //
NK127(jo)001:7341: rtse gcig thugs rje chen po'i gzungs bzlas na //
NK127(jo)001:7342: rims nad bsal nas tshe ni ring bar 'gyur //
NK127(jo)001:7343: klu gdon rgyu bas gtses te skrangs pa dang //
NK127(jo)001:7344: shu 'bras mi bzang rnag khrag 'dzag pa'i tshe //
NK127(jo)001:7345: rtse gcig thugs rje chen po'i gzungs bzlas nas //
NK127(jo)001:7346: mchil ma lan gsum byugs pas skrangs pa zhi //
NK127(jo)001:7347: sems can rnyogs pa mi dge spyod pas na //
NK127(jo)001:7348: byad stems sngags dang dgras ni gtses pa'i tshe //
NK127(jo)001:7349: rtse gcig thugs rje chen po'i gzungs bzlas na //
NK127(jo)001:7350: byad stems gdon de gtong ba'i mi la 'du //
NK127(jo)001:7351: sdig 'phal snyigs ma dam chos 'jig pa'i tshe //
NK127(jo)001:7352: 'dod pa'i me mched sems ni rmongs log pas //
NK127(jo)001:7353: khyo shug so sor gzhan la 'dod zhen gyis //
NK127(jo)001:7354: nyin mtshan bsam log rgyun ni mi 'chad tshe //
NK127(jo)001:7355: gang zhig thugs rje chen po'i gzungs bzlas na //
NK127(jo)001:7356: 'dod pa'i me zhi log pa'i sems bsal 'gyur //
NK127(jo)001:7357: bdag gis gzungs 'di'i mthu stobs rgyas brjod na //
NK127(jo)001:7358: bskal par brjod kyang mthar thug yod mi 'gyur //
NK127(jo)001:7359: zhes gsungs pa dngos su phyag stong spyan stong gi
NK127(jo)001:7360: gzungs kyi phan yon yin yang spyan ras gzigs kyi
NK127(jo)001:7361: mtshan bzung ba la'ang phan yon de ltar blta bar
NK127(jo)001:7363: spyan ras gzigs kyi rtsa rgyud pad+ma d+r+wa ba las /
NK127(jo)001:7364: spyan ras gzigs kyis sngon byang chub sems dpa'i spyad
NK127(jo)001:7365: pa spyod pa'i tshul dang rig sngags kyi tshul gsungs
NK127(jo)001:7366: pas 'jam dbyangs dang kun tu bzang po'i sgrib pa
NK127(jo)001:7367: rnam sel sogs byang chub sems dpa' dang sems ma
NK127(jo)001:7368: rnams kyis bstod par byas shing /
NK127(jo)001:7369: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas kyis zhing brjod kyis mi lang
NK127(jo)001:7370: pa nas gtso bo spyan ras gzigs mtshan dang rnam
NK127(jo)001:7371: 'gyur tha dad pa rnams 'khor dang bcas pa zhing
NK127(jo)001:7372: 'dir lhags shing so so'i rig sngags chen po gsungs
NK127(jo)001:7373: pas / phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas thams cad kyis phyag
NK127(jo)001:7374: rgya rnams spyi bor bzhag cing legs so zhes pa'i
NK127(jo)001:7375: pas / gsungs dbyangs bsgrags / khro bor rgyal po'i tshogs kyis gar byed cing bgegs bsal /
NK127(jo)001:7376: 'jig rten skyong ba'i tshogs 'khor dang bcas pas bstan pa srung bar dam bcas par gsungs so //
NK127(jo)001:7377: spyan ras gzigs phyag stong spyan stong gi cho ga zhib mo las /
NK127(jo)001:7378: byang chub sems dpa' chen po spyan ras gzigs dbang
NK127(jo)001:7379: phyug de'i rdzu 'phrul gyi mthu ni bsam gyis mi
NK127(jo)001:7380: khyab bo // 'di ni 'das pa'i bskal pa dpag
NK127(jo)001:7381: tu med pa'i snga logs su byang chub mngon par
NK127(jo)001:7382: rdzogs par sangs rgyas te chos snang ba'i sangs rgyas
NK127(jo)001:7384: de ni snying rje chen po dang smon lam gyi
NK127(jo)001:7385: dbang gis sems can la phan pa dang bde ba'i
NK127(jo)001:7386: phyir 'dir byang chub sems dpa'i gzugs su snang ngo
NK127(jo)001:7387: // lha dang mi rnams kyis rtag tu mchod pa gyis shig /
NK127(jo)001:7388: ming yang rjood cig dang dge ba'i rtsa ba skye
NK127(jo)001:7389: zhing sdig pa du ma byang nas shi ba'i 'og
NK127(jo)001:7390: tu bde ba can du skye bar 'gyur ro //
NK127(jo)001:7392: shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa yi ge
NK127(jo)001:7393: nyung ngu zhes bya ba theg pa chen po'i mdo
NK127(jo)001:7394: las / bcom ldan 'das kyis spyan ras gzigs la bka' stsal pa /
NK127(jo)001:7395: khyod de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom pa yang dag
NK127(jo)001:7396: par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas 'od zer kun nas 'phags
NK127(jo)001:7397: pa dpal brtsegs rgyal po zhes bya bar 'gyur ro
NK127(jo)001:7398: // gang dag khyod kyi ming nyan pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:7400: gzhan dag la yang rgya cher ston pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:7401: glegs bam du bris nas mchod pa byed pa de
NK127(jo)001:7402: dag thams cad ma 'ongs pa'i dus na de bzhin
NK127(jo)001:7405: 'phags pa chos thams cad kyi yon tan bkod pa'i rgyal po zhes bya ba'i mdo las /
NK127(jo)001:7406: lag na rdo rjes gsol pa /
NK127(jo)001:7407: bcom ldan 'das spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug ces bgyi ba ci'i slad du de skad bgyi /
NK127(jo)001:7409: gang gi phyir 'di ltar 'jig rten thams cad la lta bar byed /
NK127(jo)001:7413: yang dag par dbugs 'byin par byed /
NK127(jo)001:7417: snying brtse ba'i sems dang ldan la bsam pa thams
NK127(jo)001:7418: cad yongs su rdzogs par byed pas na de'i phyir
NK127(jo)001:7419: spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug ces bya'o //
NK127(jo)001:7420: lag na rdo rjes gsol pa /
NK127(jo)001:7421: bcom ldan 'das spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug gi ming
NK127(jo)001:7422: tsam la rtog pa gang gnas pa de yang bsam
NK127(jo)001:7423: pa thams cad yongs su rdzogs par 'gyur /
NK127(jo)001:7425: spyan ras gzigs kyi mtshan brgya rtsa brgyad pa bstan pa las /
NK127(jo)001:7426: gang zhig rtag tu bde ba 'dod pa yis //
NK127(jo)001:7427: 'gro kun skye dgu'i bdag po spyan ras gzigs //
NK127(jo)001:7428: pad+mo las byung rtag tu bstod par gyis //
NK127(jo)001:7430: rje btsun snying rje'i dbang phyug gi rtogs pa brjod pa'i skabs te gnyis pa'o ////
NK127(jo)001:7431: byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po phyag na rdo rje la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK127(jo)001:7433: de bzhin gshegs pa'i sku gsung thugs kyi gsang ba
NK127(jo)001:7434: kun gyi mdzod 'dzin pa gsang ba'i bdag po lag
NK127(jo)001:7435: na rdo rje 'di ni bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i
NK127(jo)001:7436: bdag nyid de / dkon mchog brtsegs pa'i gsang ba bsam gyis mi khyab pa las gsungs pa /
NK127(jo)001:7437: bcom ldan 'das kyi g.yas phyogs na lag na rdo rje rdo rje thogs nas 'dug pa la /
NK127(jo)001:7438: byang chub sems dpa' zhi ba'i blo gros kyis gsang
NK127(jo)001:7439: ba'i bdag po khyod ni de bzhin gshegs pa'i zhabs
NK127(jo)001:7440: 'bring ba nye ba na 'dug pa yin pas /
NK127(jo)001:7441: de bzhin gshegs pa'i gsang ba'i gnas nyan rang gi
NK127(jo)001:7442: yang yul las 'das na sems can phal ba'i lta
NK127(jo)001:7443: ci smos pa'i gnas la spobs par gyis zhes bskul
NK127(jo)001:7444: ba dang / de bzhin gshegs pa sh+aakya thub pas
NK127(jo)001:7445: kyang lag na rdo rje la de ltar bshad par
NK127(jo)001:7446: bskul bas gsang ba'i bdag pos smras pa /
NK127(jo)001:7447: gang tshun chad bcom ldan 'das 'di sngon byang chub
NK127(jo)001:7448: sems dpar gyur pa mar me mdzad kyis lung bstan
NK127(jo)001:7449: pa de tshun chad kho bo byang chub sems dpa'i
NK127(jo)001:7451: byang chub sems dpa'i sku gsung thugs kyi gsang ba
NK127(jo)001:7452: mthong ba rnams kyi phyogs tsam 'di dang 'di lta
NK127(jo)001:7453: bu'o zhes bshad pas sems can tshad med pa'i don
NK127(jo)001:7454: byas so // de'i tshe 'khor gyi byang chub sems
NK127(jo)001:7455: dpa' kha cig gis 'di lta bu'i spobs pa dang
NK127(jo)001:7456: ldan pa gsang ba'i bdag po 'dis dge ba'i rtsa
NK127(jo)001:7458: sangs rgyas ji snyed cig la bsnyen bkur byas /
NK127(jo)001:7459: smon lam ci 'dra btab pas 'di ltar gyur snyam
NK127(jo)001:7460: pa'i bsam pa bzhin du bcom ldan 'das kyis bka'
NK127(jo)001:7461: stsal pa / sngon 'das pa'i dus kyi bskal pa
NK127(jo)001:7462: ches grangs med bsam gyis mi khyab pa na bskal
NK127(jo)001:7463: pa mdzes par snang ba zhes bya ba la /
NK127(jo)001:7464: 'jig rten gyi khams rnam par brgyan pa zhes bya
NK127(jo)001:7465: bar de bzhin gshegs pa yon tan mtha' yas rin
NK127(jo)001:7466: chen sna tshogs bkod pa'i rgyal po zhes bya ba
NK127(jo)001:7467: byung ngo // de'i tshe sku tshe'i tshad ni lo bye ba phrag sum cu rtsa drug thub la /
NK127(jo)001:7468: mi rnams kyang dus min du 'chi ba med pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:7469: 'jig rten gyi khams de yang shin tu 'byor zhing
NK127(jo)001:7470: bde ba dang sems can rnams nyon mongs chung zhing
NK127(jo)001:7471: legs par bshad pa shes pa'i mthu dang ldan pa
NK127(jo)001:7473: 'jig rten gyi khams der mdzes par snang ba zhes
NK127(jo)001:7474: bya ba'i gling bzhi pa'i 'jig rten par ma rab
NK127(jo)001:7475: tu 'byor pa bde ba tha gru yangs pa der
NK127(jo)001:7476: / pho brang grong khyer rnam par dag pa can
NK127(jo)001:7477: zhes bya ba rgya chen po'i 'byor pas brgyan par
NK127(jo)001:7478: 'khor los sgyur ba'i rgyal po yul 'khor srung zhes
NK127(jo)001:7479: bya ba gling bzhi la dbang ba bla med byang
NK127(jo)001:7480: chub las phyir mi ldog pa zhig byung ngo //
NK127(jo)001:7481: de la bud med rin po che dang 'dra ba'i btsun mo'i 'khor bdun 'bum dang /
NK127(jo)001:7482: dpa' zhing yan lag mchog gi gzugs dang ldan pa'i
NK127(jo)001:7483: bu stong yod pa thams cad kyang rdzogs pa'i byang
NK127(jo)001:7484: chub tu zhugs pa sha stag go //
NK127(jo)001:7485: de'i tshe bcom ldan 'das yon tan mtha' yas rin
NK127(jo)001:7486: chen sna tshogs bkod pa'i rgyal po dge slong gi
NK127(jo)001:7487: dge 'dun dang thabs gcig tu rgyal po'i pho brang
NK127(jo)001:7488: rnam par dag pa dang ldan par bzhugs te /
NK127(jo)001:7489: rgyal po yul 'khor srung gis lo bye ba tshang
NK127(jo)001:7490: bar yid du 'ong ba'i longs spyod kun gyis bsnyen
NK127(jo)001:7491: bkur byas nas / bag yod pas chos nyan cing mngon par shes pa lha bskyed par byas so //
NK127(jo)001:7492: de'i tshe rgyal bu gzhon nu de dag gis pha
NK127(jo)001:7493: yul 'khor srung la mchod pa'i las kyi phyir lha'i
NK127(jo)001:7494: tsan dan sprul gyi snying po'i khang pa brtsegs pa
NK127(jo)001:7496: chu zheng du dpag tshad bcu yod pa lta na
NK127(jo)001:7497: sdug pa bkod pas legs par brgyan pa tsan+dana de'i
NK127(jo)001:7498: srang phyed kyi rin du 'dzam gling ril pos kyang
NK127(jo)001:7499: mi chog pa de lta bu byas nas /
NK127(jo)001:7500: khang pa der rgyal po yul 'khor srung dang rgyal
NK127(jo)001:7501: bu de dag dang btsun mo'i 'khor g.yog dang gnyen
NK127(jo)001:7502: du bcas pa zhugs nas mchod pa'i yo byad sna
NK127(jo)001:7503: tshogs dang bcas te steng gi bar snang la 'gro
NK127(jo)001:7504: bar sprul te sangs rgyas yon tan mtha' yas rin
NK127(jo)001:7505: chen bkod pa'i rgyal po ga la ba der song
NK127(jo)001:7506: nas khang pa brtsegs pa de sa la bzhag cing
NK127(jo)001:7507: de bzhin gshegs pa la phyag byas te chos nyan
NK127(jo)001:7508: to // de bzhin gshegs pas chos kyi gtam gyis
NK127(jo)001:7509: yang dag par mgu bar mdzad nas rgyal po des
NK127(jo)001:7510: rgyal srid thams cad sangs rgyas la phul lo //
NK127(jo)001:7511: der zla ba nya ba'i dus zhig na rgyal po
NK127(jo)001:7512: yul 'khor srung skyed mos tshal du rol mo'i tshogs
NK127(jo)001:7513: kyis rtse zhing dga' bar byed pa na /
NK127(jo)001:7514: chung ma dam pa ma smad pa zhes bya ba
NK127(jo)001:7515: dang dpe med ma zhes bya ba gnyis khrus byas
NK127(jo)001:7516: te seng ge'i khri pad+ma'i 'byung gnas bzang po la
NK127(jo)001:7517: 'dug pa dang / de gnyis kyi pang du rgyal
NK127(jo)001:7518: bu gzhon nu mdzes pa lta na sdug pa gnyis
NK127(jo)001:7519: skyil mo krung bcas par bardzusa te byung ngo //
NK127(jo)001:7520: der skad cig de la steng gi bar snang las
NK127(jo)001:7521: lha rnams kyis kye ma khye'u 'di ni chos sems
NK127(jo)001:7522: pa'o // 'di ni chos kyi blo gros so zhes
NK127(jo)001:7523: sgra byung bas khye'u gnyis kyi ming de ltar gyur
NK127(jo)001:7524: pa'o // to // khye'u de gnyis byung ma thag
NK127(jo)001:7525: tu skyil krung ma bshig par chos kyi tshigs bcad
NK127(jo)001:7526: brjod cing ma'i pang pa nas bab ste yab la
NK127(jo)001:7527: pa'o // to // phyag 'tshal nas / de bzhin
NK127(jo)001:7528: gshegs pa'i drung du 'gro bar bskul bas yab yum
NK127(jo)001:7529: sras bcas sangs rgyas kyi drung du song ste chos
NK127(jo)001:7530: nyan pas sems can mang po'i don byas so //
NK127(jo)001:7531: de nas rgyal po yul 'khor srung gis dben par
NK127(jo)001:7532: khang pa brtsegs pa'i nang du 'dug nas bsam pa
NK127(jo)001:7533: / bdag gi gzhon nu 'di dag bla med byang
NK127(jo)001:7534: chub la zhugs pa sha stag yin na 'di thams
NK127(jo)001:7535: cad kyi nang nas thog mar su zhig 'tshang rgya
NK127(jo)001:7537: rin chen sna bdun gyi bum par gzhon nu de
NK127(jo)001:7538: dag gi ming bris nas zhag bdun du mchod pa
NK127(jo)001:7539: byas shing btsun mo sras dang bcas pa'i mdun du
NK127(jo)001:7540: nang gi mis ming de dag phyungs pa ni /
NK127(jo)001:7541: thog mar rgyal bu gzhon nu rnam par dag pa'i
NK127(jo)001:7542: blo gros zhes bya ba de'i ming byung bar gyur
NK127(jo)001:7543: la de ma thag tu sa chen po g.yos shing
NK127(jo)001:7544: sil snyan rnams ma bkrol bar sgra byung ste de
NK127(jo)001:7545: ni de bzhin gshegs pa 'khor ba 'jig yin no
NK127(jo)001:7546: // de bzhin du rnam par rgyal ba'i sde dang /
NK127(jo)001:7548: don thams cad grub pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:7549: ska rabs can zhes bya ba rnams rim par byung ste /
NK127(jo)001:7550: de dag ni gser thub dang /
NK127(jo)001:7552: da ltar gyi ston pa sh+aakya thub pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:7553: ma byon pa'i byams pa rnams yin no //
NK127(jo)001:7554: de bzhin du mchog gi blo gros zhes bya ba
NK127(jo)001:7555: nas cod pan brgyan pa zhes bya ba stong la
NK127(jo)001:7556: gcig gis ma tshang ba'i ming gi bar du byung
NK127(jo)001:7557: ste / rim pa ltar sangs rgyas seng ge nas
NK127(jo)001:7558: yon tan mtha' yas grags pa'i de bzhin gshegs pa'i
NK127(jo)001:7560: rgyal bu thams cad kyi tha chung blo gros mtha'
NK127(jo)001:7561: yas zhes pa'i ming kun gyi tha mar byung ba
NK127(jo)001:7562: na phu bo kun gyis bdag cag gis sems can
NK127(jo)001:7563: thams cad smin par byas pas de'i 'og tu khyod
NK127(jo)001:7564: kyis ci zhig byar yod ces smras pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:7566: sangs rgyas kyi chos nam mkha' dang 'dra la sems
NK127(jo)001:7567: can kyang zad pa med pas bdag gis ni khyed
NK127(jo)001:7568: kun gyi tshe yi tshad la sogs pa kun bsdoms
NK127(jo)001:7569: pa'i sangs rgyas kyi mdzad pa de lta bu byed
NK127(jo)001:7570: par smon lam gdab po zhes smras pa de yi
NK127(jo)001:7571: mod la bar snang las lha rnams kyi legs so
NK127(jo)001:7573: de ni de bzhin gshegs pa mos pa zhes bya ba sangs rgyas stong gi tha ma ste /
NK127(jo)001:7574: bskal pa bzang po 'di'i de bzhin gshegs pa snga
NK127(jo)001:7575: ma rnams kyi tshe tshad dang dge 'dun gyi grangs
NK127(jo)001:7576: dang mdzad pa thams cad bsdoms pa de snyed kyi
NK127(jo)001:7578: de nas gzhon nu stong po de dag gis gzhon
NK127(jo)001:7579: nu chos sems dang chos kyi blo gros la rigs
NK127(jo)001:7580: kyi bu khyed gnyis kyis smon lam ci lta bu
NK127(jo)001:7582: ma smad ma'i bu chos sems pas smras pa /
NK127(jo)001:7583: grogs po dag bdag ni khyed thams cad kyi nang
NK127(jo)001:7584: na spyod cing lag na rdo rjer gyur te de
NK127(jo)001:7585: bzhin gshegs pa'i gsang ba thams cad las phyi rol
NK127(jo)001:7586: tu ma gyur la phyi nang gi sangs rgyas kyi
NK127(jo)001:7587: chos thams cad nyan pa dang mos pa dang rtogs
NK127(jo)001:7588: pa de ltar smon lam 'debs so //
NK127(jo)001:7589: dpe med ma'i bu chos kyi blo gros kyis smras pa /
NK127(jo)001:7590: bdag ni khyed thams cad sangs rgyas pa na chos
NK127(jo)001:7591: kyi 'khor lo bskor bar bskul bar smon lam 'debs
NK127(jo)001:7593: de la rgyal po yul 'khor srung ni sangs rgyas mar me mdzad yin zhing /
NK127(jo)001:7594: bu stong po ni bskal bzang 'di'i sangs rgyas stong dang /
NK127(jo)001:7595: khye'u chos sems pa ni gsang ba pa'i bdag po lag na rdo rje dang /
NK127(jo)001:7596: khye'u chos kyi blo gros ni tshangs pa gtsug phud can yin no zhes gsungs so //
NK127(jo)001:7597: de nas bcom ldan 'das la sh+aa ri'i bus gsol pa /
NK127(jo)001:7598: bcom ldan 'das phyogs bcu'i bskal pa bzang po'i byang
NK127(jo)001:7599: chub sems dpa' gang dag da ltar sangs rgyas kyi
NK127(jo)001:7600: thad na tshangs par spyod pa de thams cad kyi
NK127(jo)001:7601: slad na gsang ba pa'i bdag po mchis lags sam
NK127(jo)001:7603: sh+aa ri'i bu bya ba 'di bsam gyis mi khyab kyis zhog cig /
NK127(jo)001:7604: byang chub sems dpa'i spyod pa 'di la lha dang bcas pa'i 'jig rten mgo rmongs par 'gyur ro //
NK127(jo)001:7605: de lta na'ang gang dag dad cing dge ba'i bshes
NK127(jo)001:7606: gnyen gyis zin pa rnams gnas 'di la mi skrag
NK127(jo)001:7607: par 'gyur ro // sh+aa ri'i bu khyod kyis gsang
NK127(jo)001:7608: ba ba'i bdag po lag na rdo rje nga'i phyi
NK127(jo)001:7609: bzhin rtag tu 'brang ba mthong ngam /
NK127(jo)001:7611: sangs rgyas kyi mthus mthong lags te sngon ni ma mthong ngo //
NK127(jo)001:7613: de ltar bskal pa bzang po'i byang chub sems dpa'
NK127(jo)001:7614: thams cad kyi rgyab na yang lag na rdo rje'i
NK127(jo)001:7615: gzugs kun tu ston te da ltar byams pa'i rgyab
NK127(jo)001:7616: na lag na rdo rje 'dug pa mthong ngam /
NK127(jo)001:7618: bdag gis gdod mthong ste sngon ma mthong ngo //
NK127(jo)001:7620: 'di ni de'i rgyab na rtag tu 'dug pa khyod
NK127(jo)001:7621: kyis ma mthong ba yin te byang chub sems dpa'
NK127(jo)001:7622: dang 'jig rten skyong ba rnams kyis rdo rje thogs
NK127(jo)001:7623: shing rtag tu 'dug pa mthong ngo //
NK127(jo)001:7624: bskal pa bzang po'i byang chub sems dpa' thams cad
NK127(jo)001:7625: kyis sprul pa bye ba khrag khrig brgya stong dag
NK127(jo)001:7626: sprul kyang de thams cad kyi rgyab na lag na
NK127(jo)001:7627: rdo rje gnas par snang ste /
NK127(jo)001:7628: de bzhin du de bzhin gshegs pa'i sprul pa ji
NK127(jo)001:7629: snyed pa thams cad kyi rgyab na yang snang la
NK127(jo)001:7630: byin gyi rlabs de thams cad ni gsang ba pa'i
NK127(jo)001:7632: stong chen po'i 'jig rten na yod pa'i sems can
NK127(jo)001:7633: thams cad kyi rgyab tu lag na rdo rje'i gzugs
NK127(jo)001:7634: kun tu bstan kyang des chos dang ye shes kyi
NK127(jo)001:7635: byin rlabs yongs su rdzogs par bstan par mi 'gyur
NK127(jo)001:7637: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis byang chub sems dpa' zhi ba'i blo gros la bka' stsal pa /
NK127(jo)001:7638: zhi ba'i blo gros lag na rdo rje 'dis rdo
NK127(jo)001:7639: rje thogs nas bskal pa bzang po'i sangs rgyas thams
NK127(jo)001:7640: cad la mchod cing dam pa'i chos 'dzin pa dang
NK127(jo)001:7641: de bzhin gshegs pa gsang ba ba'i chos kyi rnam
NK127(jo)001:7642: grangs rgyas par byed cing sems can tshad med pa
NK127(jo)001:7643: yongs su smin par byas nas de bzhin gshegs pa
NK127(jo)001:7644: mos pa'i dus kyi dam pa'i chos nub pa na
NK127(jo)001:7645: / de bzhin gshegs pa mi 'khrugs pa'i sangs rgyas
NK127(jo)001:7646: kyi zhing mngon par dga' ba der skyes nas de
NK127(jo)001:7647: bzhin gshegs pa de las phyag rgya brgya rtsa bstan
NK127(jo)001:7648: pa bzung zhing sgrub par byed la /
NK127(jo)001:7649: de'i 'og tu de bzhin gshegs pa grangs med dpag
NK127(jo)001:7650: tu med pa mnyes par byed cing de dag gi
NK127(jo)001:7651: chos srung ba dang sems can tshad med pa rdzogs
NK127(jo)001:7652: pa'i byang chub tu smin par byas nas /
NK127(jo)001:7653: bskal pa gang+g+aa'i klung gi bye ma snyed 'das pa
NK127(jo)001:7654: na mngon par rdzogs par 'tshang rgya bar 'gyur te
NK127(jo)001:7655: / bskal pa rnam par sbyong ba zhes bya ba
NK127(jo)001:7656: la 'jig rten gyi khams kun nas yongs su dag
NK127(jo)001:7657: pa zhes bya bar de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom
NK127(jo)001:7658: pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rdo rjes
NK127(jo)001:7659: rnam par gnon pa zhes bya bar 'gyur ro //
NK127(jo)001:7660: de'i zhing na ngan song dang mi khoms pa med
NK127(jo)001:7661: la yongs su dag pa 'byor pas brgyan pa dga'
NK127(jo)001:7662: ldan gyi lha'i longs spyod dang 'dra bar 'gyur zhing
NK127(jo)001:7663: dus min du 'chi ba med do //
NK127(jo)001:7664: der skyes pa'i sems can rnams rgya chen po la
NK127(jo)001:7665: mos pa ste nyan rang gi theg pa'i ming yang
NK127(jo)001:7666: med par byang chub sems dpa'i gtam 'ba' zhig gsung
NK127(jo)001:7667: zhing lha dang mi de dag mtshan nyi shu rtsa
NK127(jo)001:7669: de bzhin gshegs pa de'i sku tshe'i tshad bar gyi bskal pa brgyad thub la /
NK127(jo)001:7670: des chos ston pa na sku las 'od byung bas
NK127(jo)001:7671: 'khor 'dus pa dang steng gi mkha' la t+aa la
NK127(jo)001:7672: 'bum srid du 'phags nas gling bzhi pa'i 'jig rten
NK127(jo)001:7673: khams su skyil mo krung bcas pa'i skus khyab par
NK127(jo)001:7674: mdzad de / phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten du dbyangs kyis go bar mdzad nas chos ston to //
NK127(jo)001:7675: der chos bstan pa dang 'gal bar byed pa dang
NK127(jo)001:7676: zlog par byed pa'i sems can gcig kyang med de
NK127(jo)001:7677: thams cad dbang po rno ba sha stag go //
NK127(jo)001:7678: zhing der de bzhin gshegs pa chos kyi rgyal po
NK127(jo)001:7679: de ma gtogs par rgyal po gzhan med cing sems
NK127(jo)001:7680: can rnams nga yi bdag yongs su 'dzin pa med
NK127(jo)001:7681: do // de bzhin gshegs pa des bsod snyoms blang
NK127(jo)001:7682: bar bzhed pa'i lha dang mi de'i mdun du lhung
NK127(jo)001:7683: bzed thogs te gnas pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:7684: de dag gis bsam pa tsam gyis yo byad thams cad 'byung zhing bsod snyoms 'bul bar byed do //
NK127(jo)001:7685: de bzhin gshegs pa de nang du yang dag 'jog
NK127(jo)001:7686: pa na byang chub sems dpa' de dag kyang ting
NK127(jo)001:7687: nge 'dzin gyi bkod pas gnas par 'gyur ro //
NK127(jo)001:7688: 'jig rten gyi khams de ni yon tan gyi khyad
NK127(jo)001:7689: par 'di dag dang gzhan yang tshad med pa dang
NK127(jo)001:7690: ldan par 'gyur ro zhes lung bstan pa na /
NK127(jo)001:7691: lag na rdo rjes rdo rje nam mkha'i dkyil du
NK127(jo)001:7692: 'phangs pas 'jig rten khams 'di g.yos shing me tog
NK127(jo)001:7693: gi char dang sil snyan gyi sgra byung bar gyur
NK127(jo)001:7694: to // de nas gsang ba pa'i bdag pos pho
NK127(jo)001:7695: brang lcang lo can du bcom ldan 'das 'khor dang
NK127(jo)001:7696: bcas pa dgung bdun du spyan drangs nas /
NK127(jo)001:7697: lag na rdo rjes bkod pa chen po'i rgyal po
NK127(jo)001:7698: zhes bya ba'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs
NK127(jo)001:7699: te shar phyogs kyi sangs rgyas kyi zhing yon tan
NK127(jo)001:7700: rin po che bkod pa mtha' yas pa zhes bya
NK127(jo)001:7701: ba'i bkod pa ci 'dra ba de 'dra ba'i 'khor
NK127(jo)001:7702: gyi khyams sprul nas rgyal po bzhi 'khor dang bcas
NK127(jo)001:7703: pa dang / tshangs ris nas 'og min pa'i bar
NK127(jo)001:7704: gyi lha rnams sbran te der chos nyan par 'dus
NK127(jo)001:7705: shing gsang sngags kyi tshig brjod pas kyang sems can
NK127(jo)001:7706: gyi don tshad med pa byas so //
NK127(jo)001:7707: de nas bcom ldan 'das bya rgod phung po'i rir
NK127(jo)001:7708: slar gshegs nas rgyal po ma skyes dgras zhus pa
NK127(jo)001:7710: rgyal po chen po phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten gyi khams
NK127(jo)001:7711: gang+g+aa'i klung gi bye ma snyed dag bgrang bas mtha'
NK127(jo)001:7712: rtogs nus kyi / gsang ba pa'i bdag po lag
NK127(jo)001:7713: na rdo rjes sangs rgyas ji snyed cig la mchod
NK127(jo)001:7714: cing bsnyen bkur byas pa'i sangs rgyas de dag bgrang
NK127(jo)001:7715: ba'i tshul gyis rtogs mi nus te de dag gi
NK127(jo)001:7716: drung nas tshangs par spyod do //
NK127(jo)001:7717: sngon 'das pa'i bskal pa ches grangs med pa'i snga
NK127(jo)001:7718: rol na de bzhin gshegs pa rnam par zhi spyod
NK127(jo)001:7719: ces bya bas / byang chub sems dpa'i lus dang
NK127(jo)001:7720: srog kyang btang ste brtson 'grus brtsam par bya'o zhes
NK127(jo)001:7721: byang chub sems dpa'i gtam 'ba' zhig bstan pa na
NK127(jo)001:7722: ces bya bas / / de'i tshe lag na rdo
NK127(jo)001:7723: rje 'di 'khor der 'dus pa'i byang chub sems dpa'
NK127(jo)001:7724: dpa' ba'i stobs zhes bya bar gyur pas de bzhin
NK127(jo)001:7725: gshegs pa'i gsung de'i don sems pas myang 'das la
NK127(jo)001:7726: yon tan du mi blta zhing 'khor ba la phan
NK127(jo)001:7727: yon du lta bas 'khor ba spyod yul du bgyis
NK127(jo)001:7728: te byang chub sems dpa'i spyod pa tshad med pa'i
NK127(jo)001:7729: ces bya bas / / don bzung bas / de
NK127(jo)001:7730: bzhin gshegs pas legs so zhes gnang zhing spyod yul
NK127(jo)001:7731: yongs su dag pa'i chos bstan pas /
NK127(jo)001:7732: gzugs thams cad nam mkha'i spyod yul yin pa bzhin
NK127(jo)001:7733: du chos thams cad byang chub sems dpa'i spyod yul
NK127(jo)001:7734: du shes pas go cha brtan po bgos shing sangs
NK127(jo)001:7735: rgyas mang po la bsnyeen bkur byas so //
NK127(jo)001:7736: de nas rgyal po ma skyes dgras lag na rdo
NK127(jo)001:7737: rje'i lag pa g.yas pa na thogs pa'i rdo rje
NK127(jo)001:7738: 'di lci ba'am yang ba zhig yin snyam du bsam
NK127(jo)001:7739: pa'i rtog pa de gsang ba pa'i bdag pos shes
NK127(jo)001:7740: nas 'di skad du rdo rje 'di ni lci ba'ang
NK127(jo)001:7741: yin la yang ba yang yin te /
NK127(jo)001:7742: nga rgyal dang rgyags pa can 'dul ba'i phyir lci la /
NK127(jo)001:7743: nga rgyal med pa dang drang ba rnams la yang
NK127(jo)001:7744: ba yin no zhes smras te sa phyogs de rdo
NK127(jo)001:7745: rjer byin gyis brlabs nas rdo rje de sa'i steng
NK127(jo)001:7746: du bzhag bas sa chen po rnam pa drug tu
NK127(jo)001:7747: g.yos so // de nas gsang ba pa'i bdag pos
NK127(jo)001:7748: ma skyes dgra la rdo rje 'di sa'i steng nas
NK127(jo)001:7750: de lag pa ya gcig gis glang po che 'degs
NK127(jo)001:7751: pa'i stobs dang ldan yang tshan po che'i shugs bskyed
NK127(jo)001:7752: nas btegs kyang rdo rje de skra'i rtse tsam yang
NK127(jo)001:7753: bsgul ma nus pas ngo mtshar te brgya byin la
NK127(jo)001:7755: des kyang bsgul ma nus nas ngo mtshar te bdag
NK127(jo)001:7756: gis lha min dbang po thag bzang ris kyi shing
NK127(jo)001:7757: rta dpag tshad bdun brgya ba yang 'dzin pa'i rngo
NK127(jo)001:7758: thogs mod kyi rdo rje 'di bsgul ba'i rngo yang
NK127(jo)001:7759: ma thogs pa ci lags zhes sangs rgyas la zhus
NK127(jo)001:7761: rdo rje 'di ni rab kyi lci bas kyang dper
NK127(jo)001:7762: mtshon mi nus te rdo rje 'di lag na rdo
NK127(jo)001:7763: rjes rdo rje'i rang bzhin gyi 'khor yug gi ri
NK127(jo)001:7764: la bsnun na phub ma spar gang gtor pa ltar
NK127(jo)001:7766: de nas brgya byin gyis mo gal gyi bu la rdo rje 'degs par bskul ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:7767: des rdo rje de bzung bas sa chen po rnam
NK127(jo)001:7768: pa drug tu g.yos shing chu yang gnam du brgal
NK127(jo)001:7769: rgya mtsho thams cad 'khrug kyang rdo rje de bsgul
NK127(jo)001:7770: ba tsam yang ma nus nas ngo mtshar te /
NK127(jo)001:7772: bdag gi rdzu 'phrul gyis rgya mtsho chen po'i chu lag mthil du 'jog cing /
NK127(jo)001:7773: stong chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khams 'di yang mi
NK127(jo)001:7774: la las kar+sha pa na gcig mdzub mo'i rtse mos
NK127(jo)001:7775: bsgre ldog pa bzhin du byed nus la /
NK127(jo)001:7776: nyi ma dang zla ba yang thogs par bgyid cing
NK127(jo)001:7777: ri'i rgyal po'i ri rab kyang lag pa ya gcig
NK127(jo)001:7778: gis blangs te tshangs pa'i 'jig rten gyi bar du
NK127(jo)001:7780: bdag gis klu'i rgyal po dga' bo dang nye dga' yang btul /
NK127(jo)001:7781: 'jig rten gyi khams 'od zer can du yang mchis /
NK127(jo)001:7782: ri rab tsam gyi khams de dag kyang 'tshal 'tshal na /
NK127(jo)001:7783: bdag gis rdo rje chung ngu 'di bskyod pa'i rngo
NK127(jo)001:7784: yang ma thogs pas bdag rdzu 'phrul las nyams par
NK127(jo)001:7785: ma gyur lags sam zhes gsol ba na /
NK127(jo)001:7787: khyod rdzu 'phrul las nyams pa med mod kyi /
NK127(jo)001:7788: byang chub sems dpa'i byin gyi rlabs 'di nyan rang
NK127(jo)001:7789: thams cad kyis dkrug mi nus na sems can gzhan
NK127(jo)001:7791: sangs rgyas kyi zhing gang+g+aa'i klung gi bye ma snyed
NK127(jo)001:7792: dag gi ri'i rgyal po ri rab ci yod pa
NK127(jo)001:7793: bskyod par nus kyi rdo rje 'di phyogs 'di nas
NK127(jo)001:7795: zhes gsungs pas mo gal gyi bus gsol pa /
NK127(jo)001:7796: rdo rje 'di 'chang ba'i gsang ba'i bdag po ni
NK127(jo)001:7797: stobs kyi shugs chen po ngo mtshar ba lags te
NK127(jo)001:7798: / lag na rdo rje'i stobs de pha ma las byung ba'am 'on te rdzu 'phrul gyi stobs lags /
NK127(jo)001:7800: mo gal gyi bu pha ma las byung ba'i stobs
NK127(jo)001:7801: de ni ci yang rung ste 'jug pa tsam du
NK127(jo)001:7803: gal te byang chub sems dpa'i rdzu 'phrul gyi stobs
NK127(jo)001:7804: ma lus par bstan na lha dang bcas pa'i 'jig
NK127(jo)001:7806: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis lag na rdo rje la rdo rje de theg cig ces gsungs pas /
NK127(jo)001:7807: gsang ba'i bdag pos 'jig rten gyi khams g.yo bar
NK127(jo)001:7808: byas nas rdo rje de nyid lag pa g.yon pas
NK127(jo)001:7809: blangs te steng gi bar snang du 'phangs nas lan
NK127(jo)001:7810: bdun pa skor te lag pa g.yas par bzhag pas
NK127(jo)001:7811: thams cad dang ldan pa'i 'khor de ngo mtshar nas
NK127(jo)001:7812: lag na rdo rje la ched du brjod pa dang
NK127(jo)001:7813: stobs de lta bu'i phyir smon lam 'debs pa dang
NK127(jo)001:7814: stobs de lta bu thob pa'i rgyu yongs su zhus
NK127(jo)001:7815: so // 'jig rten gsum las rnam par rgyal ba rtog pa'i rgyal po chen po las gsungs pa /
NK127(jo)001:7816: bcom ldan 'das ri rab ri'i rtse mor rdo rje
NK127(jo)001:7817: dang nor bu rin po che'i rtse mo'i khang pa
NK127(jo)001:7818: brtsegs pa na / byang chub sems dpa' dang lha
NK127(jo)001:7819: klu gnod sbyin la sogs pa'i 'khor mang po dang
NK127(jo)001:7820: thabs gcig tu bzhugs pa der /
NK127(jo)001:7821: byang chub sems dpa' chen po phyag na rdo rje nam mkha'i dkyil nas babs te /
NK127(jo)001:7822: bcom ldan 'das kyi zhabs la phyag byas nas lan
NK127(jo)001:7823: gsum bskor ba byas shing 'di skad ces gsol to
NK127(jo)001:7824: // bcom ldan 'das bdag gis lha chen po la
NK127(jo)001:7825: sogs pa sems can ma rungs pa de dag la
NK127(jo)001:7826: dam tshig 'dzin du stsal par 'tshal na /
NK127(jo)001:7827: bcom ldan 'das kyis bdag la bka' stsal du gsol /
NK127(jo)001:7828: tshig de gsan nas de bzhin gshegs pa chos kyi rgyal pos bka' stsal pa /
NK127(jo)001:7829: gnod sbyin khyod shin tu khro zhing khengs la gtum pa ste /
NK127(jo)001:7830: ji ltar khyod kyis sems can rnams kyi don gyi phyir 'di lta bu'i sngags kyi tshig smra /
NK127(jo)001:7832: de'i phyir na bcom ldan 'das bdag ma rungs pa 'dul bar bgyid do //
NK127(jo)001:7833: gang gi phyir na bdag gis 'dod pa'i bde ba
NK127(jo)001:7834: can rnams dbang du bgyi ba la sogs pas btul
NK127(jo)001:7835: nas bla na med pa'i bde ba la dgod pa
NK127(jo)001:7836: dang / ma rungs pa bshad pa la sogs pas sbyangs te zhi ba la dgod par 'tshal lo //
NK127(jo)001:7837: bcom ldan 'das kyis phyag na rdo rje la legs so zhes bya ba byin te /
NK127(jo)001:7839: 'jig rten thams cad kyi phan pa dang bde ba'i don gyi phyir snying po smos shig /
NK127(jo)001:7840: de nas phyag na rdo rjes lha dang mi sangs
NK127(jo)001:7841: rgyas pa'i bstan pa la mngon par dad pa de
NK127(jo)001:7843: grogs po dag sangs rgyas la skyabs su dong shig /
NK127(jo)001:7844: nga'i bka' yang rjes su skyongs shig /
NK127(jo)001:7845: de nas phyag na rdo rjes bcom ldan 'das kyis
NK127(jo)001:7846: zhabs la phyag 'tshal nas 'jig rten gsum las rnam
NK127(jo)001:7847: par rgyal ba'i snying po gsungs pa tsam gyis 'jig
NK127(jo)001:7848: rten gsum po thams cad ches cher g.yo 'gul 'phar
NK127(jo)001:7849: nas / lha sogs sems can thams cad 'dar yed
NK127(jo)001:7850: yed bcom ldan 'das ga la ba der lhags nas
NK127(jo)001:7851: khor yug dang khor yug chen po'i ri la sogs
NK127(jo)001:7852: pa tshun chad kyi gling bzhi pa'i 'jig rten gyi
NK127(jo)001:7853: khams thams cad sems can thams cad kyis gang ngo
NK127(jo)001:7854: nas / // de nas bcom ldan 'das phyag na
NK127(jo)001:7855: rdo rje des 'khor gyi tshogs thams cad la gzigs
NK127(jo)001:7857: grogs po rnams sangs rgyas la sogs pa la skyabs
NK127(jo)001:7858: su 'gro bar khas long la nga'i bka' yang rjes
NK127(jo)001:7859: su skyongs shig / de na 'dus pa'i 'khor chen
NK127(jo)001:7860: po thams cad bcom ldan 'das phyag na rdo rje
NK127(jo)001:7861: la skrags te 'dar yed yed nas bcom ldan 'das
NK127(jo)001:7862: de bzhin gshegs pa la skyabs su dong ngo //
NK127(jo)001:7863: de nas sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das la lha chen
NK127(jo)001:7864: po'i lha dang mthu bo che dang tshangs pa rnams
NK127(jo)001:7866: bcom ldan 'das 'di ltar sems can rdzu 'phrul dang
NK127(jo)001:7867: byin che zhing bdag cag la 'chos pa 'di su
NK127(jo)001:7868: lags / de nas bcom ldan 'das kyi don 'di bstan pa'i phyir tshigs su bcad pas gsungs pa /
NK127(jo)001:7869: sems can kun la phan pa'i phyir //
NK127(jo)001:7870: sangs rgyas kun gyis byin gyis brlabs //
NK127(jo)001:7871: kun tu bzang po kun gyi bdag /
NK127(jo)001:7872: sangs rgyas thams cad nyid skyes 'di //
NK127(jo)001:7873: phyag na rdo rje gnod sbyin che //
NK127(jo)001:7874: ma rungs 'chos la dbang ba ste //
NK127(jo)001:7875: gang gi ming barjooda pa yis ni //
NK127(jo)001:7876: sangs rgyas pa yang thob par 'gyur //
NK127(jo)001:7877: de nas phyag na rdo rjes gsungs pa /
NK127(jo)001:7878: kye kye lha dag sangs rgyas la skyabs su dong la nga'i bka' bzhin gyis shig /
NK127(jo)001:7879: rdo rje 'bar ba gcig tu 'bar bar gyur pa
NK127(jo)001:7880: 'dis khyed thams cad gtan sreg par 'gyur ta re
NK127(jo)001:7881: / de nas lha chen po la sogs pa thams cad kyis smras pa /
NK127(jo)001:7882: khyod ni gnod sbyin nged ni lha yin pas nged
NK127(jo)001:7883: kyis gnod sbyin gyi bka' rjes su skyong bar mi
NK127(jo)001:7884: nus so // phyag na rdo rjes de thos nas khros te bcom ldan 'das la gsol pa /
NK127(jo)001:7885: bcom ldan 'das kyis bdag ma rungs pa thams cad 'dul bar dbang bskur te bskos pas na /
NK127(jo)001:7886: gal te bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal na lha chen po 'di 'dul bar 'tshal to //
NK127(jo)001:7887: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis lha chen po la 'di skad ces gsungs pa /
NK127(jo)001:7888: sems can chen po khas longs shig 'dis khyod bsad ta re /
NK127(jo)001:7889: de nas lha chen po la sogs pa 'jig rten
NK127(jo)001:7890: gsum thams cad kyi dbang po lha rnams kyis gsol
NK127(jo)001:7891: pa / bcom ldan 'das gnod sbyin ma rungs pa
NK127(jo)001:7892: 'di'i bka' bzhin du byed pa bdag cag ma lags
NK127(jo)001:7893: pa / so // de nas lha chen pos bcom
NK127(jo)001:7894: ldan 'das kyi zhabs la phyag 'tshal te phyag na
NK127(jo)001:7897: gnod sbyin nga ni thams cad kyi dbang po chen po byed pa po /
NK127(jo)001:7899: skye dgu'i bdag po tshangs pa'i //
NK127(jo)001:7902: de nas byang chub sems dpa' chen po phyag na rdo rje khros nas 'di skad ces gsungs so //
NK127(jo)001:7903: khyod ni lus srul po mi sha za ba ma
NK127(jo)001:7904: rungs pa drag shul gyi las byed pas na gtum
NK127(jo)001:7905: pa ste / sha za'i lus srel ba na ji
NK127(jo)001:7906: ltar tshangs pa dang gtogs 'dod dang dbang phyug chen
NK127(jo)001:7907: po yin te tshangs pa zhes bya ba ni mi
NK127(jo)001:7908: pa ste / 'gyur ba'o // gtogs 'dod ches bya ba ni thar pa'o //
NK127(jo)001:7909: dbang phyug chen po zhes bya ba ni 'dod pa'i
NK127(jo)001:7910: khams kyi dbang po ste sems can thams cad kyi
NK127(jo)001:7911: dbang po de ni nga yin pas 'dul nus so
NK127(jo)001:7912: // zhes gsungs pas lha dbang phyug chen po khros nas /
NK127(jo)001:7913: bcom ldan 'das kyi zhabs la phyag 'tshal te /
NK127(jo)001:7914: 'jigs su rung ba chen po'i gzugs khros pa chen
NK127(jo)001:7915: po'i gad mo bgad nas 'jigs pa chen por byed
NK127(jo)001:7917: stong pa 'jig rten gyi khams mtha' med par gzugs sna tshogs su ni byas /
NK127(jo)001:7918: 'bar ba chen po grub pa mi mtshungs la /
NK127(jo)001:7919: rdo rje dang mdung rtse gsum dang 'khor lo dang shag ti dang be con dang /
NK127(jo)001:7920: mi mtshungs pa'i mtshon cha 'debs shing gtong ba ma
NK127(jo)001:7921: mo rnams kyi tshogs dang 'byung po'i tshogs rnams dang
NK127(jo)001:7923: bdud dang bgegs byed pa'i gzugs sna tshogs su sprul
NK127(jo)001:7924: te khro bo rab tu mi bzad pa ma rungs
NK127(jo)001:7925: pa'i tshogs chen po dang lhan cig tu rab tu
NK127(jo)001:7927: gling bzhi pa'i 'jig rten gyi khams mtshan mo'i mun
NK127(jo)001:7928: nag tu byas nas 'bar ba chen po'i phung pos
NK127(jo)001:7929: klongs te rab tu snang bar byas so //
NK127(jo)001:7930: de nas bcom ldan 'das rdo rje 'chang ba chen po mche ba cung zad gtsigs pa /
NK127(jo)001:7931: smin mtshams khro gnyer gyi rlabs bskyod pa /
NK127(jo)001:7932: mig g.yon pa cher bgrad de khro ba dang bcas pa'i rdo rje'i lta bas /
NK127(jo)001:7933: snying po zab mo 'jig rten gsum las rnam par rgyal ba'i dpal /
NK127(jo)001:7934: h'u zhes bya ba gsungs pa'i h'u de'i sgras 'jig
NK127(jo)001:7935: rten gyi khams kun bkang ste char g.yo zhing 'khrol
NK127(jo)001:7936: lo // de nas dbang phyug lha chen po la
NK127(jo)001:7937: sogs pa lha'i tshogs thams cad kyis bcom ldan 'das
NK127(jo)001:7939: bde bar gshegs pa bskyab tu gsol zhes byas nas skyabs su dong ngo //
NK127(jo)001:7940: de nas bcom ldan 'das phyag na rdo rjes 'jig
NK127(jo)001:7941: rten gsum las rnam par rgyal pa'i snying po gsungs
NK127(jo)001:7942: pa tsam gyis lha chen po la sogs pa lha'i
NK127(jo)001:7943: bdag po thams cad 'khor dang bcas pa phyag na
NK127(jo)001:7944: rdo rje gang na ba der mgo rkang bzlog ste
NK127(jo)001:7945: / ri rab ri'i rtse mo'i dkyil 'khor chen por
NK127(jo)001:7946: btsud nas barlamasa par byas te phyag na rdo rje'i
NK127(jo)001:7948: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis phyag na rdo rje
NK127(jo)001:7949: la legs so zhes bya ba byin te khyod kyis
NK127(jo)001:7950: 'di ltar sems can 'dul bar byed pa legs so
NK127(jo)001:7951: // de bas na thul la dbugs phyungs shig ces gsungs pas /
NK127(jo)001:7952: phyag na rdo rje'i byin gyi rlabs kyis de dag
NK127(jo)001:7953: dran pa rnyed cing dbang du byas te dam la
NK127(jo)001:7954: bzhag nas rdo rje'i ming gis dbang bskur la /
NK127(jo)001:7955: dbang phyug chen po ni rdo rje'i rig sngags mchog go //
NK127(jo)001:7956: mthu bo che ni rdo rje sgyu ma'o //
NK127(jo)001:7957: tshangs pa ni rdo rje mi smra ba'o //
NK127(jo)001:7958: sgra gzhon nu ni rdo rje dril bu'o //
NK127(jo)001:7959: dbang po ni rdo rje 'thab cha ste /
NK127(jo)001:7960: de bzhin du bar snang dang nam mkha' la rgyu ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:7961: sa dang sa 'og gi dbang po thams cad rdo
NK127(jo)001:7962: rje ming gis dbang bskur nas dkyil 'khor du bcug
NK127(jo)001:7963: par mdzad do // zhes pa'i tshul de dang 'dra
NK127(jo)001:7964: bar gdul bar dka' ba 'jig rten gsum gyi bdag
NK127(jo)001:7965: po 'khor dang bcas pa phyag na rdo rjes drag
NK127(jo)001:7966: po'i tshul gyis gdul bar mdzad pa ni rgyud gzhan
NK127(jo)001:7967: rnams kyi gleng gzhir yang rgyu cher 'byung ba yin
NK127(jo)001:7968: par mdzad do // no // lag na rdo rje dbang bskur ba'i rgyud las gsungs pa /
NK127(jo)001:7969: byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po kun tu bzang po zhes bya bas /
NK127(jo)001:7970: 'jig rten gyi khams me tog gi gzhi'i snying po'i
NK127(jo)001:7971: rgyan bkod pa 'di thams cad du bcom ldan 'das
NK127(jo)001:7972: rnam par snang mdzad kyi sngon gyi spyod pa ston
NK127(jo)001:7974: gnod sbyin 'dul ba'i dbang nye bar bzung ste dbus
NK127(jo)001:7975: kyi 'dzam bu'i gling mi mjed 'dir lcang lo can
NK127(jo)001:7976: du gnod sbyin gyi sde dpon chen po 'brog gnas
NK127(jo)001:7977: kyi gnas na gnas pa de /
NK127(jo)001:7978: de bzhin gshegs pa'i 'od zer gyis snang bar gyur
NK127(jo)001:7979: pas mig dang bzhin rgyas par gyur te ched du
NK127(jo)001:7980: brjod pa brjod nas de bzhin gshegs pa'i bsam gyis
NK127(jo)001:7981: mi khyab pa nyid yid la byed cing 'dug pa
NK127(jo)001:7982: la / de bzhin gshegs pas byang chub sems dpa'
NK127(jo)001:7983: kun tu bzang po 'ong bar 'gyur ba'i brda dang
NK127(jo)001:7984: tshigs su bcad pa gsungs pas /
NK127(jo)001:7985: byang chub sems dpa' kun tu bzang pos gnod sbyin
NK127(jo)001:7986: gyi tshogs la de bzhin gshegs pa'i drung du 'dong
NK127(jo)001:7987: bar sbran te rgyan sna tshogs zhes bya ba'i ting
NK127(jo)001:7988: nge 'dzin spyod pa thams cad kyi rgyu mthun pa
NK127(jo)001:7989: ston pa la snyoms par zhugs pa'i mod la /
NK127(jo)001:7990: rnam par snang mdzad kyi rgyan bkod pa'i khang pa
NK127(jo)001:7991: brtsegs pa stong chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khams tsam
NK127(jo)001:7992: du yangs shing nor bu'i ka ba bye ba khrag
NK127(jo)001:7993: khrig brgya stong du ma la sogs pa bsam gyis
NK127(jo)001:7994: mi khyab pa'i bkod pa rgya mtshos mdzes pa'i cho
NK127(jo)001:7996: gnod sbyin gyi tshogs chen pos bskor zhing khang pa
NK127(jo)001:7997: brtsegs pa de lag pa gnyis kas blangs nas bar
NK127(jo)001:7999: shing s+aa la sna tshogs kyi rgyal mtshan bkod pa'i
NK127(jo)001:8000: nags tshal stug po ga la bar bcom ldan 'das
NK127(jo)001:8001: sh+aakya thub pa'i drung du 'ong ngo //
NK127(jo)001:8002: khang pa brtsegs pa de'i 'od kyis phyogs thams cad
NK127(jo)001:8003: khyab cing steng gi nam mkhar dpag tshad 'bum phrag
NK127(jo)001:8004: drug cu rtsa brgyad na me'i phung po chen po
NK127(jo)001:8005: ltar 'bar zhing nyi ma stong ltar lham mer mdzes
NK127(jo)001:8007: 'khor gyi sems dpa' rnams kyis sangs rgyas sh+aakya thub pa la de lta bu ci lags zhus pas /
NK127(jo)001:8008: byang chub sems dpa' kun tu bzang po 'dir 'ong
NK127(jo)001:8009: ba de'i sngon gyi spyod pas bsgrubs pa'i rgyu mthun
NK127(jo)001:8010: pa ste / 'di yi chos gang gi yon tan
NK127(jo)001:8011: bskal pa brgyar yang mtha' rtogs par ma nus pa'i
NK127(jo)001:8013: byang chub sems dpa' kun tu bzang po de yang
NK127(jo)001:8014: theg pa chen po la 'jug pa'i sgo rnam par
NK127(jo)001:8015: dag pa'i gnas zhes bya ba'i chos kyi rnam grangs
NK127(jo)001:8016: kun tu 'adri'o zhes bka' stsal pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:8017: byang chub sems dpa' kun tu bzang po shing t+aa
NK127(jo)001:8018: la bdun srid kyi steng gi bar snang la 'dug
NK127(jo)001:8019: nas tshal de dag tu lha'i me tog dang bdug
NK127(jo)001:8020: spos la sogs pa char phab nas steng gi bar
NK127(jo)001:8022: khang pa brtsegs pa de bcom ldan 'das la phul zhing mngon par bstod pa byas so //
NK127(jo)001:8023: de nas khang brtsegs dang sil snyan dang pheg rdob
NK127(jo)001:8024: pa dag las theg pa chen po'i thog ma'i spyod
NK127(jo)001:8025: pa'i sgra tshigs su bcad pa byung ba'i mod la
NK127(jo)001:8026: / byang chub sems dpa' chen po kun tu bzang
NK127(jo)001:8027: pos bcom ldan 'das la theg pa chen po la
NK127(jo)001:8028: 'jug pa dang de'i spyod pa sogs zhus so //
NK127(jo)001:8029: de nas bcom ldan 'das rdo rje chen po 'byung
NK127(jo)001:8030: gnas zhes bya ba'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par
NK127(jo)001:8032: phyogs thams cad kyi 'jig rten gyi khams rab 'byams
NK127(jo)001:8033: thams cad du de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad rdo
NK127(jo)001:8034: rje chen po'i sgras gsung gcig tu rdo rje chen
NK127(jo)001:8035: po 'bar ba'i 'od 'phro ba'i snying po rdo rje
NK127(jo)001:8036: sems dpa'i yi ge brjod cing /
NK127(jo)001:8037: shing s+aa la sna tshogs kyi rgyal mtshan bkod pa'i
NK127(jo)001:8038: nags tshal stug por bcom ldan 'das sh+aakya thub pa
NK127(jo)001:8039: ga la ba der gshegs te byon nas rdo rje
NK127(jo)001:8040: chen po pad+ma'i gdan la skyil mo krung bcas te
NK127(jo)001:8041: bzhugs shing de bzhin gshegs pa sh+aakya thub pa la
NK127(jo)001:8042: bsnyun gsol to // de nas de bzhin gshegs pa
NK127(jo)001:8043: de thams cad dang bcom ldan 'das sh+aakya thub pas
NK127(jo)001:8044: rdo rje'i dkyil 'khor byin gyis rlob pa'i sngags gsungs
NK127(jo)001:8045: nas sangs rgyas kyi byin gyi rlabs kyi rnam par
NK127(jo)001:8046: 'phrul pa zhes bya ba'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms
NK127(jo)001:8047: bsnyun gsol to // par zhugs so // de nas
NK127(jo)001:8048: thams cad dang ldan pa'i 'khor chen po de ya
NK127(jo)001:8049: mtshan che'o snyam du snying 'dun par gyur te 'jam
NK127(jo)001:8050: dpal gzhon nur gyur pa la lta zhing 'khod do
NK127(jo)001:8051: bsnyun gsol to // par zhugs so // // de
NK127(jo)001:8052: nas 'jam dpal gyis 'khor de dag ya mtshan che'o
NK127(jo)001:8053: snyam du rtse gcig tu gyur par rig nas /
NK127(jo)001:8054: bcom ldan 'das sh+aakya thub pa dang sangs rgyas de
NK127(jo)001:8055: dag la tshigs su bcad pas bde bar gshegs pa'i
NK127(jo)001:8056: sras la dbang bskur bar gsol ba btab pa dang
NK127(jo)001:8057: / de bzhin gshegs pa de dag gis tshal der
NK127(jo)001:8058: rdo rje'i dkyil 'khor gyi khyams rgyan dang bkod pa
NK127(jo)001:8059: gdan dang bcas pa byin gyis brlabs nas /
NK127(jo)001:8060: steng gi gtsug tor nas thams cad du thogs pa
NK127(jo)001:8061: med pa'i stobs zhes bya ba'i 'od zer byung ste
NK127(jo)001:8062: 'khor gyi dkyil 'khor de snang bar byas shing byang
NK127(jo)001:8063: chub sems dpa' chen po kun tu bzang po'i spyi
NK127(jo)001:8064: gtsug tu zhugs ma thag tu de dga' zhing rab
NK127(jo)001:8065: tu dga' ste thogs pa med pa'i stobs zhes bya
NK127(jo)001:8066: ba'i snying po smras pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:8067: de bzhin gshegs pa de dag gi ting nge 'dzin
NK127(jo)001:8068: dang gzungs dang stobs dang byang chub kyi yan lag
NK127(jo)001:8069: dang lam dang 'phags pa'i bden pa dang stong pa
NK127(jo)001:8070: nyid dang sangs rgyas kyi chos ma 'dres pa dang
NK127(jo)001:8071: / stong pa nyid chen po'i mtha' las byas pa
NK127(jo)001:8072: sbyin pa dang dul ba dang yang dag par sdom
NK127(jo)001:8073: pa dang des pa la sogs pa pha rol tu
NK127(jo)001:8074: phyin pa drug gis rnam par bskyed pa'i gzugs can
NK127(jo)001:8075: gyi rdo rje byin gyis brlabs te byang chub sems
NK127(jo)001:8076: dpa' kun tu bzang po'i lag tu byin no //
NK127(jo)001:8077: de'i de ma thag tu phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas kyi
NK127(jo)001:8078: zhing rab 'byams dang 'jig rten thams cad du de
NK127(jo)001:8079: bzhin gshegs pa thams cad dang byang chub sems dpa'
NK127(jo)001:8080: dang nyan rang dang lha klu gnod sbyin mi la
NK127(jo)001:8081: sogs pa thams cad kyis mgrin gcig tu kye ma
NK127(jo)001:8082: byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po 'di ni
NK127(jo)001:8084: lag na rdo rje'o zhes brjod do //
NK127(jo)001:8085: de nas yang de bzhin gshegs pa de dag gis
NK127(jo)001:8086: dam tshig 'di byin gyis brlabs nas gsang ba'i rdo
NK127(jo)001:8087: rje zhes bya ba'i snying po gsungs pas zhing thams
NK127(jo)001:8088: cad du gsang ba'i bdag po zhes bya ba'i sgra
NK127(jo)001:8090: 'di ltar snying po de'i mthu dang de bzhin gshegs
NK127(jo)001:8091: pa thams cad kyi byin gyi rlabs kyis byang chub
NK127(jo)001:8092: sems dpa' lag na rdo rje la de bzhin gshegs
NK127(jo)001:8093: pa thams cad kyi thugs dang ye shes phun sum
NK127(jo)001:8094: tshogs pa dag mngon sum du zhugs so //
NK127(jo)001:8095: yang de bzhin gshegs pa de dag gis bstan pa
NK127(jo)001:8096: srung zhing 'gro ba skyobs pa'i snying po rdo rje
NK127(jo)001:8097: rgya chen po'i gzungs gsungs ma thag tu 'jig rten
NK127(jo)001:8098: gyi khams rab 'byams thams cad dang sangs rgyas kyi
NK127(jo)001:8100: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi zhabs drung dang /
NK127(jo)001:8101: byang chub sems dpa' thams cad dang /
NK127(jo)001:8103: sems dang po bskyed pa rnams dang /
NK127(jo)001:8104: las dang po pa rnams dang /
NK127(jo)001:8105: sems can thams cad kyi rgyab dang mdun du dang /
NK127(jo)001:8106: ma nyal ba'am gnyid log pa'am chos ston pa'am 'tshang
NK127(jo)001:8107: rgya ba'am sems can gyi don byed pa'am sprul pa
NK127(jo)001:8108: rab tu byed pa'i bar du thams cad kyi drung
NK127(jo)001:8109: na lag na rdo rje cod pan can gzugs thams
NK127(jo)001:8110: cad yang dag par ston pa nyid kun tu snang
NK127(jo)001:8111: ngo // yang de bzhin gshegs pa de dag gis
NK127(jo)001:8112: sa phyogs rdo rjes bcing ba'i snying po gsungs pas
NK127(jo)001:8113: sems can ma rungs pa rnams rdo rjes bcing bas
NK127(jo)001:8114: ngo // bcings te / rdo rje phur bu'i snying
NK127(jo)001:8115: po gsungs pas kye ma byang chub sems dpa' chen
NK127(jo)001:8116: po lag na rdo rje 'di rdo rjes rton to
NK127(jo)001:8117: zhes pa'i sgra gcig tu 'ur zhes grags so //
NK127(jo)001:8118: yang rdo rjes 'og gi snying po gsungs pas 'jig
NK127(jo)001:8119: rten khams rab 'byams dang sa 'og gi phrag thams
NK127(jo)001:8120: cad du lag na rdo rje 'di ni sa 'og
NK127(jo)001:8121: gi rdo rje zhes sgra 'ur ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:8122: rig sngags 'chang ba'i 'gro ba gcod pa'i snying po
NK127(jo)001:8123: gsungs pas 'jig rten rab 'byams dang rig sngags 'chang
NK127(jo)001:8124: gi gnas thams cad du mtshan de ltar grags pa
NK127(jo)001:8125: dang / de bzhin du gnod sbyin tshar gcod pa'i rdo rje'i snying po sogs gsungs pas /
NK127(jo)001:8126: gnod sbyin gyi rdo rje dang klu'i rdo rje dri
NK127(jo)001:8127: za'i rdo rje nam mkha' lding gi dbang po'i rdo
NK127(jo)001:8128: rje mi'am ci'i rdo rje lto 'phye chen po'i rdo
NK127(jo)001:8129: rje srin po'i rdo rje mkha' 'gro ma'i rdo rje
NK127(jo)001:8130: 'byung po'i rdo rje sha za'i rdo rje sha za
NK127(jo)001:8131: mo'i rdo rje srin mo'i rdo rje gnon po'i rdo
NK127(jo)001:8132: rje zhes pa'i mtshan gyi sgra 'jig rten gyi khams
NK127(jo)001:8133: thams cad dang so so'i gnas de nyid du 'ur
NK127(jo)001:8134: zhing grags so // de bzhin du grib gnon rab
NK127(jo)001:8135: tu 'jigs pa'i snying po gsungs pa nas 'jig rten
NK127(jo)001:8136: thams cad du rgyud pa thams cad 'gog pa'i rdo
NK127(jo)001:8137: rje zhes grags pa'i bar dang /
NK127(jo)001:8138: stobs thogs pa med pa'i rdo rje'i snying po gsungs
NK127(jo)001:8139: pas zhing rab 'byams kyi gnas thams cad du byang
NK127(jo)001:8140: chub sems dpa' chen po lag na rdo rje 'di
NK127(jo)001:8141: ni rdo rje chen po'i 'khor los sgyur ba zhes
NK127(jo)001:8142: bya ba'i sgra gcig nas gcig tu 'ur zhes grags
NK127(jo)001:8143: so // de nas de bzhin gshegs pa de dag
NK127(jo)001:8144: gis rdo rje chen po'i 'khor los sgyur ba'i snying
NK127(jo)001:8145: po gsungs shing de la sogs pa rdo rje chen
NK127(jo)001:8146: po'i snying po rnams lag na rdo rje la byin
NK127(jo)001:8147: so // te / 'od zer gyi d+r+wa ba chen
NK127(jo)001:8148: po'i sprin gyis tshal de dang 'khor de thams cad
NK127(jo)001:8149: snang bar byas shing byin gyi rlabs kyi stobs kyis
NK127(jo)001:8150: lag na rdo rje byin gyis brlabs nas chos kyi
NK127(jo)001:8151: dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor du chos kyi dbyings kyi rang
NK127(jo)001:8152: bzhin du gyur nas mi snang bar gyur to //
NK127(jo)001:8153: de'i tshe bcom ldan 'das sh+aakya thub pas lag na rdo rje la bka' stsal pa /
NK127(jo)001:8154: rigs kyi bu de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis
NK127(jo)001:8155: 'khor los sgyur ba rdo rje'i dkyil 'khor chen por
NK127(jo)001:8156: lag tu rdo rjes dbang bskur bas khyod dbang bskur
NK127(jo)001:8157: to // ting nge 'dzin bye ba khrag khrig brgya
NK127(jo)001:8158: stong du ma las byas pa'i rdo rje khyod la
NK127(jo)001:8159: to // byin no // 'khor los sgyur ba'i rgyal
NK127(jo)001:8160: po chen po'i rdo rjes khyod byin gyis brlabs so
NK127(jo)001:8161: to // byin no // // rdo rje'i snying po thams cad khyod la bstan to //
NK127(jo)001:8162: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis khyod la bstan
NK127(jo)001:8163: pa thams cad kyi don bya ba dang bsrung bar
NK127(jo)001:8164: gnang ngo // khyod kyi sngon gyi smon lam chen po yongs su rdzogs so //
NK127(jo)001:8165: rigs kyi bu de rang gi rdzu 'phrul nges par ston cig /
NK127(jo)001:8166: rdo rjes dbang bskur ba'i dkyil 'khor chen po shod cig ces bka' stsal pas /
NK127(jo)001:8167: lag na rdo rjes bcom ldan 'das la gsol pa /
NK127(jo)001:8168: chos kyi rjes ji skad bka' stsal pa bzhin du 'tshal lo //
NK127(jo)001:8169: bcom ldan 'das bdag mchog tu ngo mtshar thob pa
NK127(jo)001:8170: dang bdag rnam par rgyal ba'i chos dam pa thob
NK127(jo)001:8171: pa ni bcom ldan 'das kyi bdag la thugs brtse
NK127(jo)001:8172: bar mdzad do // de nas lag na rdo rje
NK127(jo)001:8173: rdo rje brtsegs pa chen po rnam par bsgrags pa'i
NK127(jo)001:8174: snying po zhes bya ba'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms
NK127(jo)001:8175: par zhugs pas 'jig rten gyi khams rab tu g.yos
NK127(jo)001:8176: shing 'gul ldeg chem par gyur la /
NK127(jo)001:8177: snang ba chen pos khyab pas mun pa mun nag
NK127(jo)001:8178: gi nang na gnas pa dang ngan song gsum gyi
NK127(jo)001:8179: sdug bsngal rgyun chad par gyur cing /
NK127(jo)001:8180: lag na rdo rje'i ba spu thams cad nas khro
NK127(jo)001:8181: bo'i rgyal po dag byung ste h'u zhes pa'i sgra
NK127(jo)001:8183: lag na rdo rje ni thogs /
NK127(jo)001:8184: gdong khro gnyer bsnyer te 'jig rten gyi khams 'di
NK127(jo)001:8185: dbyangs gcig gis go bar byas nas ma rungs pa'i
NK127(jo)001:8186: 'byung bo'i tshogs thams cad dam la bzhag cing rang
NK127(jo)001:8187: gi snying po smras pas 'jig rten gyi khams thams
NK127(jo)001:8188: cad du kye ma byang chub sems dpa' chen po
NK127(jo)001:8189: 'di ni lag na rdo rje drag po'o zhes sgra
NK127(jo)001:8191: de nas lag na rdo rje rdo rje me zhes
NK127(jo)001:8192: bya ba la sogs pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi sgo
NK127(jo)001:8193: du ma la snyoms par zhugs pas 'jig rten gyi
NK127(jo)001:8194: khams kun g.yo zhing 'khrugs la rab tu 'bar bar
NK127(jo)001:8195: gyur cig / de'i mig las rdo rje 'jigs 'jigs lta chen po dang /
NK127(jo)001:8196: ba spu'i bu ga dang yan lag gi tshigs thams cad las rdo rje khro bo'i tshogs dang /
NK127(jo)001:8197: gtsug tor nas 'jig rten gsum las rnam par rgyal
NK127(jo)001:8198: ba zhes pa stong chen po'i 'jig rten bcu'i tshad
NK127(jo)001:8199: kyi lus dang ldan pa 'jig dus kyi me dang
NK127(jo)001:8200: 'dra ba dang / dpral ba'i dkyil nas khro bo
NK127(jo)001:8201: zla ba'i thig le zhes bya ba phyag brgya stong
NK127(jo)001:8203: gzhan yang rdo rje be con dang /
NK127(jo)001:8204: stobs po che dang gom pa 'dor ba'i rdo rje dang /
NK127(jo)001:8205: rdo rje lu gu rgyud dang rdo rje rtse mo
NK127(jo)001:8206: re re'i 'khor pho nya mo khri dang bcas pa
NK127(jo)001:8207: dang / rdo rje khu tshur rnams kyang bstan te /
NK127(jo)001:8208: de dag gi snying po'ang bstan to //
NK127(jo)001:8209: gzhan yang lag pa gnyis las gzhon nu lag bzangs dang /
NK127(jo)001:8210: kha nas gzhon nu rdo rje'i sde la sogs pa
NK127(jo)001:8211: lag na rdo rje'i bu gzhon nu khro bo lag
NK127(jo)001:8212: na rdo rje thogs shing sems can gyi don la
NK127(jo)001:8213: brtson pa / 'jig rten gyi khams tha dad pa rnams su mngon par sangs rgyas pa /
NK127(jo)001:8214: stobs la sogs pa'i yon tan gyi lus bskyed pa /
NK127(jo)001:8215: sems can thams cad kyi bsam pa yongs su rdzogs
NK127(jo)001:8216: par byed pa lag na rdo rje'i snying du 'thad
NK127(jo)001:8217: pa mang po rnams kyang spros nas de dag gi
NK127(jo)001:8219: de nas lag na rdo rje sems can thams cad
NK127(jo)001:8220: kyi srog la dbab pa'i tshogs kyis bye ba bsregs
NK127(jo)001:8221: pa zhes bya ba'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par
NK127(jo)001:8222: zhugs shing snying po smras pas /
NK127(jo)001:8223: ri thams cad rgya mtshor bcas pa 'bar zhing skam par mthong la /
NK127(jo)001:8224: thams cad dang ldan pa'i 'khor de na byang chub
NK127(jo)001:8225: sems dpa' sa bcu la gnas pa rnams ma gtogs
NK127(jo)001:8226: pa thams cad rdo rje'i dkyil 'khor gyi steng du
NK127(jo)001:8227: kha sbub tu bsgyel zhing lag na rdo rje'i snying
NK127(jo)001:8228: ga nas khro bo'i rgyal po 'jigs pa'i me lce
NK127(jo)001:8229: chen po zhes bya ba byung nas /
NK127(jo)001:8230: gad mo rta gad chen po rgyas par 'byin cing
NK127(jo)001:8231: thams cad dang ldan pa'i 'khor gyi snying rnams yongs
NK127(jo)001:8232: su bsdus nas nam mkha' dang mtshungs pa nyid du
NK127(jo)001:8233: gyur te lag na rdo rje'i snying gi dkyil 'khor
NK127(jo)001:8234: du zhugs so // lag na rdo rje yang snying
NK127(jo)001:8235: rje chen po'i dkyil 'khor la gnas nas de'i tshe
NK127(jo)001:8236: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad dang mnyam pa nyid
NK127(jo)001:8238: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis lag na rdo rje la legs so zhes basngagasa so //
NK127(jo)001:8239: de nas 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pas thams cad
NK127(jo)001:8240: dang ldan pa'i 'khor de rdo rje'i dkyil 'khor du
NK127(jo)001:8241: 'gyel bar rig nas snying rje cher skyes te mig
NK127(jo)001:8242: gnyis kyis ring du bltas nas lag na rdo rje
NK127(jo)001:8243: la smras pa / rigs kyi bu 'khor 'di la
NK127(jo)001:8244: dam tshig la 'jug pa'i sgo cung zad stsol dang
NK127(jo)001:8245: la smras pa / / des bstan pa 'di la
NK127(jo)001:8246: srog gi re ba thob cing dad nas rang rang
NK127(jo)001:8247: gi gsang sngags kyi snying po 'bul bar 'gyur ro
NK127(jo)001:8249: lag na rdo rjes ched du brjod pa'i tshigs su
NK127(jo)001:8250: bcad pa brjod cing rdo rje mchog gi stobs kyi
NK127(jo)001:8251: gzungs dang lhan cig tu rdo rje de 'jam dpal
NK127(jo)001:8252: gzhon nur gyur pa la byin no //
NK127(jo)001:8253: de nas 'jam dpal gyi 'khor de dag la rigs
NK127(jo)001:8254: kyi bu dag rig pa'i rgyal mo rdo rje mi
NK127(jo)001:8255: pham pa mes rab tu rmongs byed 'di dran par
NK127(jo)001:8256: gyis shig dang / 'dis khyed la phan bde dang
NK127(jo)001:8257: srog thob pa byed par 'gyur ro zhes lag na
NK127(jo)001:8258: rdo rjes rig pa chen po smras pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:8259: 'jam dpal gyi byin gyi rlabs kyis 'khor de langs nas dga' zhing mchog tu dad pa skyes te /
NK127(jo)001:8260: tshangs pa dang drag po dang khyab 'jug dang brgya
NK127(jo)001:8261: byin dang rgyal chen bzhi dang lha klu gnod sbyin
NK127(jo)001:8262: dri za la sogs pa 'jig rten gsum na yod
NK127(jo)001:8263: pa'i dregs pa mthu dang dbang che ba thams cad
NK127(jo)001:8264: kyi rang rang gi snying po sgrub pa'i cho gar
NK127(jo)001:8265: bcas pa phyag na rdo rje la phul zhing lag
NK127(jo)001:8266: na rdo rjes kyang rdo rje'i dam tshig bsgrags par
NK127(jo)001:8267: mdzad do // de nas 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur
NK127(jo)001:8268: pas rdo rje ye shes chen po'i 'od zer 'phro
NK127(jo)001:8269: ba las byung ba zhes bya ba'i ting nge 'dzin
NK127(jo)001:8270: la snyoms par zhugs nas lag pas lag na rdo
NK127(jo)001:8271: rje las rdo rje blangs te /
NK127(jo)001:8272: ye shes las byung ba'i ut+pala dri ma med pa byas nas de la rdo rje de bzhag go //
NK127(jo)001:8273: de'i de ma thag tu 'jig rten gyi khams rab
NK127(jo)001:8274: 'byams thams cad la sangs rgyas kyi dkyil 'khor thams
NK127(jo)001:8275: cad du kye ma 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa
NK127(jo)001:8276: 'di ni dam pa sbyin pa'i rdo rje'o zhes sgra
NK127(jo)001:8277: gcig nas gcig tu 'ur nas grags so //
NK127(jo)001:8278: phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten gyi khams na bzhugs pa'i sangs
NK127(jo)001:8279: rgyas rnams de na bzhugs bzhin du phyag g.yas pa
NK127(jo)001:8280: brkyangs te 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa'i mgo la
NK127(jo)001:8281: byugs nas legs so'i ched du brjod pa dang bcas
NK127(jo)001:8282: te bskul bas 'jam dpal des snying po rnams kyis
NK127(jo)001:8283: dngos grub sgrub pa'i rim par phye ba smras nas
NK127(jo)001:8285: zhi ba'i blo gros de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad
NK127(jo)001:8286: kyi snying po sra ba'i yon tan rnams dang mthu
NK127(jo)001:8288: zhi ba'i blo gros lag na rdo rje 'di ni
NK127(jo)001:8289: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi 'jigs pa'i me
NK127(jo)001:8290: las byung ba'i rdo rje zhes bya ste ma dul
NK127(jo)001:8292: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad dang byang chub sems
NK127(jo)001:8293: dpa' thams cad kyi smon lam yongs su rdzogs par
NK127(jo)001:8294: byed pa / bstan pa mchog tu kun tu bsrung bar smon lam btab pa /
NK127(jo)001:8295: sems can thams cad kyi bsam pa ji lta ba bzhin du yongs su rdzogs par byed pa /
NK127(jo)001:8296: 'jig rten gyi khams mtha' yas rgya mtsho rab 'byams
NK127(jo)001:8297: rnams su de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi smon
NK127(jo)001:8298: lam sgrogs pa'i sgo la 'jug pa /
NK127(jo)001:8299: thams cad sngon du rgyug pa'o //
NK127(jo)001:8301: de nas phyogs bcu'i zhing rab 'byams nas de bzhin
NK127(jo)001:8302: gshegs pa rnams kyi phyag g.yas pa brkyangs te lag
NK127(jo)001:8303: na rdo rje'i mgo la bzhag nas sngags dang dkyil
NK127(jo)001:8304: 'khor gyi gsang ba bshad par bskul bas de bzhin
NK127(jo)001:8305: bshad cing / 'jam dpal la ye shes chen por dbang bskur ba'i gzung sngags bshad pa'i mod la /
NK127(jo)001:8306: 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pas ye shes bye ba
NK127(jo)001:8307: phrag dgu bcu rtsa dgu las nges par byung ba'i
NK127(jo)001:8308: ye shes chen po'i rdo rje rtogs par gyur nas
NK127(jo)001:8309: / de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi dkyil 'khor du mchod pa'i sprin byung zhing /
NK127(jo)001:8310: ye shes chen po'i dbang bskur bas 'jam dpal 'di
NK127(jo)001:8311: la dbang bskur to zhes pa'i sgra stong chen po'i
NK127(jo)001:8312: 'jig rten gyi khams 'dir 'ur zhes grags so //
NK127(jo)001:8313: de'i mthus 'jam dpal gyis sangs rgyas kyi zhing bcu'i
NK127(jo)001:8314: rdul phra rab kyi rdul snyed kyi de bzhin gshegs
NK127(jo)001:8315: pa'i gzugs ut+pala chen po'i nang du zhugs par mthong
NK127(jo)001:8316: zhing / de'i mod la chos kyi sku rtogs pa'i
NK127(jo)001:8317: mthus 'jam dpal gyi ba spu'i khung bu rnams dang
NK127(jo)001:8318: cod pan dang rgyan dang yan lag nying lag thams
NK127(jo)001:8319: cad nas de bzhin gshegs pa'i gzugs rnams byung zhing
NK127(jo)001:8320: zhing / bzhugs te / byang chub sems dpa' sa
NK127(jo)001:8321: chen po bcu la gnas pa sems kyi dbang thams
NK127(jo)001:8322: cad thob pa de dag gis kyang ba spu'i khung
NK127(jo)001:8323: bu gcig gi tshad kyang rtogs par ma nus na
NK127(jo)001:8324: nyan rang dang gzhan 'jig rten pas lta ci smos
NK127(jo)001:8325: zhing / bzhugs te / / de nas 'jam dpal
NK127(jo)001:8326: gzhon nur gyur pas byang chub sems dpa' lag na
NK127(jo)001:8327: rdo rje la mig mi 'dzum par bltas nas ched
NK127(jo)001:8328: du brjod pas ched du brjod par mdzad do //
NK127(jo)001:8330: rig pa mchog gi rgyud chen po las 'byung po'i
NK127(jo)001:8331: bdag po gang gis de bzhin gshegs pa 'bum phrag
NK127(jo)001:8332: gang+g+aa'i klung dgu bcu rtsa gnyis kyi bye ma snyed
NK127(jo)001:8334: gang gis rig pa'i rgyal po chen po'i mchog lag
NK127(jo)001:8335: na rdo rje la yid kyis phyag byas pa de
NK127(jo)001:8336: ni de nyid las bsod nams mang du bskyed do
NK127(jo)001:8337: // de nas byang chub sems dpa' rtogs pa dri ma med pas bcom ldan 'das la gsol pa /
NK127(jo)001:8338: bcom ldan 'das lag na rdo rje 'dis ci srid
NK127(jo)001:8339: ci ga nas rig pa'i rgyal po chen po dang
NK127(jo)001:8340: rigs sngags 'chang gi bdag po chen por bskos pa
NK127(jo)001:8341: thob / 'di ting nge 'dzin gang gis gnas /
NK127(jo)001:8342: 'di'i sngon gyi dge ba'i bshes gnyen ni su lags /
NK127(jo)001:8343: 'di gnas pa gang gis gnas de skad ces gsol pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:8345: sngon 'das pa'i bskal pa gang+g+aa'i klung bcu dgu'i bye
NK127(jo)001:8346: ma snyed 'das pa na gdul dka' zhes bya ba'i
NK127(jo)001:8347: bskal pa chen po la de bzhin gshegs pa ye
NK127(jo)001:8348: shes sgron ma chen po'i 'od zer zhes bya ba
NK127(jo)001:8349: byung ngo // de'i dus na mi mjed kyi 'jig
NK127(jo)001:8350: rten 'di ni rdo rje ldan zhes bya ba'i 'jig
NK127(jo)001:8351: rten gyi khams su gyur to //
NK127(jo)001:8352: de bzhin gshegs pa des byang chub sems dpa' bye
NK127(jo)001:8353: ba khrag khrig brgya stong phrag drug cu la mun
NK127(jo)001:8354: pa mun nag rnam par sel ba rnam par snang
NK127(jo)001:8355: byed ces bya ba'i chos kyi rnam grangs gsang ba
NK127(jo)001:8356: 'chad do // rdo rje 'chang gi rigs 'jig rten
NK127(jo)001:8357: rab 'byams dpag med nas 'dus pa 'jig rten gyi
