NK127(jo)001:8358: khams mtha' yas mu med pa'i rdul snyed la ting
NK127(jo)001:8359: 'dzin dang gzungs kyi basngagasa pa dpag tu med pa
NK127(jo)001:8360: bstan pa'i phyir 'dzum pa mdzad do //
NK127(jo)001:8361: de nas rdo rje 'chang chen po rdo rje chen
NK127(jo)001:8362: po'i khyu mchog tu gyur pa 'jig rten mtha' yas
NK127(jo)001:8363: pa'i dbang phyug gi rgyal po zhes bya ba 'khor
NK127(jo)001:8364: der 'dus pa de stan las langs te bcom ldan
NK127(jo)001:8365: 'das kyi zhabs la btud nas yang langs te /
NK127(jo)001:8366: tog yangs pa chen po rab 'byams kyi 'og gi
NK127(jo)001:8367: phyogs nas phyag rgya chen po bsgyur nas rdo rje
NK127(jo)001:8368: blangs te phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten gyi khams rab 'byams
NK127(jo)001:8369: mtha' yas pa rgya mtsho bcu yang dag par bskul
NK127(jo)001:8370: nas / de dag gis rgyal po bsgyings par bsgyur
NK127(jo)001:8371: bas rgya mtsho chen po bsdu ba'i tshul gyi nga
NK127(jo)001:8372: rgyal chen po des rdo rje gsor nas dus kyi
NK127(jo)001:8373: tha ma 'jig pa'i me lta bu'i mig gis /
NK127(jo)001:8375: gi phyogs kyi phyag rgya bsgyur bas rdo rje de
NK127(jo)001:8376: de bzhin gshegs pa'i zhabs kyi drung du bzhag ste
NK127(jo)001:8377: zhabs gnyis la phyag 'tshal nas de bzhin gshegs pa
NK127(jo)001:8378: la / ci'i slad du 'khor 'dus pa la 'dzum pa bstan /
NK127(jo)001:8379: zhal gyi sgo dang smin mtshams mdzod spu nas sngon
NK127(jo)001:8380: ma byung ba'i 'od zer kha dog sna tshogs byung
NK127(jo)001:8381: / de'i slad du 'khor 'dis bskul nas bdag gis
NK127(jo)001:8382: bcom ldan 'das la zhu na thugs brtse bas bshad
NK127(jo)001:8383: / du gsol / de skad ces zhus pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:8384: de'i tshe bcom ldan 'das kyi mtshan dpal gyi be'u
NK127(jo)001:8385: chen po las ma thon ka chen po dang beed+aurla
NK127(jo)001:8386: lta bu 'od zer nor bu rin po che skar
NK127(jo)001:8387: mdog lta bu'i 'od dang ldan pa /
NK127(jo)001:8388: 'od zer chen po'i dkyil 'khor phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten
NK127(jo)001:8389: gyi khams rab 'byams mtha' yas par cher snang ba'i
NK127(jo)001:8390: 'od zer gyi me lce byung nas /
NK127(jo)001:8391: dri ma med pa'i 'od zer rnam par 'phro ba'i
NK127(jo)001:8392: dkyil 'khor las lag pa g.yon pas rdo rje blangs
NK127(jo)001:8393: pa las gsang ba'i bdag po lag na rdo rje
NK127(jo)001:8394: rig pa'i rgyal po chen po byung ngo //
NK127(jo)001:8395: phyag gi lcags kyu'i mtshan las ni lcags kyu /
NK127(jo)001:8396: nya las ni 'dod pa'i rdo rje ma /
NK127(jo)001:8397: bkra shis las ni lu gu rgyud /
NK127(jo)001:8398: g.yung drung 'khyil pa mchog tu mdzes pa me 'bar ba lta bu las ni me kha la /
NK127(jo)001:8399: bya ma bum las ni ser mo /
NK127(jo)001:8400: gdugs las ni rgyal mtshan drag po /
NK127(jo)001:8401: rdo rje las ni dga' ba ste /
NK127(jo)001:8402: rgyal mo chen po pho nya mo dang 'khor du bcas pa bdun po de dag byung ngo //
NK127(jo)001:8403: de dag gi mdun du ma rungs pa khro bo'i gzugs stobs po che dang /
NK127(jo)001:8404: khro bo k+ai li k+ai li dus kyi tha ma'i
NK127(jo)001:8405: rin po che lta bu rdo rje khu tshur las
NK127(jo)001:8406: byung ngo // lag ngar las ni khu tshur ro //
NK127(jo)001:8407: phrag pa 'bar zhing mdzes pa las ni rdo rje gnam lcags te /
NK127(jo)001:8408: de ltar 'khor dang bcas pa'i pho nya mo bcu'o //
NK127(jo)001:8409: de bzhin du drug cu phrag bzhir basgre'o //
NK127(jo)001:8410: lag na rdo rje g.yog 'khor dang pho nya mo
NK127(jo)001:8411: dang 'khor du bcas pa byung nas dam tshig chen
NK127(jo)001:8413: de bzhin gshegs pa ye shes sgron ma chen po'i
NK127(jo)001:8414: 'od zer la de bzhin gshegs pa'i byin gyi rlabs
NK127(jo)001:8415: kyis gsol ba btab pa na /
NK127(jo)001:8416: de bzhin gshegs pa de dri ma med pa zhes
NK127(jo)001:8417: bya ba'i ting nge 'dzin la mnyam par bzhag ste
NK127(jo)001:8418: / thog mar de bzhin gshegs pa'i sku gsung thugs kyi gsang ba bcu dang /
NK127(jo)001:8419: gsang ba mtha' yas bye ba dkrigs phrag bye ba
NK127(jo)001:8420: dang ldan pa'i mdo sde'i dbang po rgyal po de
NK127(jo)001:8421: / dam tshig can 'dus pa'i dkyil 'khor du gdul
NK127(jo)001:8422: dka' 'dul zhing thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes bstan
NK127(jo)001:8424: de tshun chad ye shes sgron ma chen po'i 'od
NK127(jo)001:8425: zer de la sogs pa sangs rgyas bye ba phrag
NK127(jo)001:8426: dgu bcu rtsa dgu'i gam du bdud pham par mdzad
NK127(jo)001:8427: nas bstan pa kun tu bsrungs par gyur to //
NK127(jo)001:8428: de bzhin gshegs pa ye shes sgron ma chen po'i
NK127(jo)001:8429: 'od zer de'i 'og tu bskal pa dgu bcu rtsa
NK127(jo)001:8430: drug pa la 'jig rten gyi khams mi mjed 'dir
NK127(jo)001:8431: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas don gzigs zhes bya ba 'jig
NK127(jo)001:8433: de'i gsung rab la bdud ci yang mi smra ba
NK127(jo)001:8434: zhes bya ba byung ba de lag na rdo rjes
NK127(jo)001:8435: pham par byas nas don gzigs pa zhes bya ba'i
NK127(jo)001:8436: de bzhin gshegs pa brgyad cu dang /
NK127(jo)001:8437: sangs rgyas bye ba phrag dgu bcu rtsa gcig las
NK127(jo)001:8438: bdud pham par byas te bstan pa bsrungs par byas
NK127(jo)001:8439: so // de tshun chad bskal pa dgu bcu rtsa
NK127(jo)001:8440: drug lhag pa zhig 'das nas sangs rgyas gser du
NK127(jo)001:8441: snang bas rnam par rol pa zhes bya ba bskal
NK127(jo)001:8442: ba bye ba phrag drug cu rtsa brgyad las bdud
NK127(jo)001:8443: pham par byas te bstan pa kun tu srung bar
NK127(jo)001:8444: so // gyur to // de'i 'og tu bskal pa
NK127(jo)001:8445: stong snyed 'das nas lag na rdo rje 'di de
NK127(jo)001:8446: bzhin du de bzhin gshegs pa de dag gi gsang
NK127(jo)001:8447: ba 'dzin pa dang bstan pa srung bar gyur to
NK127(jo)001:8448: so // gyur to // // de bzhin du tha mar de bzhin gshegs pa gtsug tor can dang /
NK127(jo)001:8455: nga'i bstan pa la yang ma dul ba 'dul ba dang gsang ba 'dzin cing /
NK127(jo)001:8456: bskal pa bzang po la mi mjed 'di nyid du sangs rgyas kyi mdzad pa byed de /
NK127(jo)001:8457: bskal pa bzang po'i sangs rgyas ji snyed pa thams
NK127(jo)001:8458: cad la de bzhin du mthar gyis thabs 'dis bstan
NK127(jo)001:8459: pa la bya ba byas nas mngon par rdzogs par
NK127(jo)001:8460: sangs rgyas te / rdo rje'i rtsal gyis 'gro ba
NK127(jo)001:8461: zhes bya ba'i sangs rgyas su 'gyur ro zhes de
NK127(jo)001:8462: bzhin gshegs pa sh+aakya thub pas bka' stsal to //
NK127(jo)001:8463: yang lag na rdo rjes gsol pa /
NK127(jo)001:8464: bcom ldan 'das bdag gi ming thos nas yid kyis
NK127(jo)001:8465: kyang 'khu ba'i sems pa ni lha dang bcas pa
NK127(jo)001:8466: dang tshangs pa dang bcas pa dang bdud dang bcas
NK127(jo)001:8467: pa dang dge sbyong dang bram ze'i skye dgu dang
NK127(jo)001:8468: bcas pa'i 'jig rten na ma mthong ngo //
NK127(jo)001:8470: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
NK127(jo)001:8471: grogs po dag byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen
NK127(jo)001:8472: po lag na rdo rje la gang gis 'di ltar
NK127(jo)001:8473: yid kyis phyag 'tshal na yang des de bzhin gshegs
NK127(jo)001:8474: pa stong phrag dgu la phyag byas par 'gyur ro
NK127(jo)001:8475: zhes dang / lag na rdo rjes gsungs pa /
NK127(jo)001:8476: gdon gang nga'i ming thos nas mi 'bros pa de
NK127(jo)001:8477: la rdo rje drag pos spyi bo gshag par bya'o
NK127(jo)001:8479: bcom ldan 'das kyis lag na rdo rje gtum po la bka' stsal pa /
NK127(jo)001:8480: khyod kyi ming brgyad pa gsang sngags kyi 'khor dang
NK127(jo)001:8481: bcas pa gang thos na mtshams med lnga byas pa'i
NK127(jo)001:8483: lag na rdo rje mthong bar 'gyur ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:8484: bgegs dang log 'dren thams cad dang /
NK127(jo)001:8485: log 'dren bye ba khrag khrig brgya stong phrag brgyad
NK127(jo)001:8486: cu rtsa bzhi rnams kyang phyogs bcur 'byer bar 'gyur
NK127(jo)001:8487: ba dang / gang thos na tshangs par ma spyad pa yang tshangs par spyod par 'gyur ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:8488: thub par ma byas pa yang thub par byas par 'gyur ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:8489: smyung bar ma byas pa yang smyung ba byas par 'gyur ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:8490: dge sbyong ma yin pa yang dge sbyong gi 'bras bu dang ldan par 'gyur ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:8491: sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' thams cad de la srung bar mdzad pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:8492: las kyi dngos grub kyang stsol ba bshad par bya'o //
NK127(jo)001:8494: khyod ni glang po'i rna ba can yin /
NK127(jo)001:8495: khyod ni rgyan bzang po dang ldan pa yin /
NK127(jo)001:8496: khyod ni rnam par gnon pa yin /
NK127(jo)001:8497: khyod ni yon tan rin po che'i 'byung khungs yin /
NK127(jo)001:8498: khyod ni bden pa'i sprin yin /
NK127(jo)001:8499: khyod ni gzugs sdug pa'i rgyan dang ldan pa yin /
NK127(jo)001:8500: khyod ni 'bar ba'i me lce dang ldan pa yin /
NK127(jo)001:8501: khyod ni gzugs mdzes pa yin /
NK127(jo)001:8502: khyod kyi ming 'di dag mkhas pa gang gis thos
NK127(jo)001:8503: na bskal pa bye ba khrag khrig brgya stong phrag
NK127(jo)001:8504: bdun gyi bar du sems can dmyal bar skye bar
NK127(jo)001:8505: mi 'gyur ro // 'chi ba'i tshe sangs rgyas byang
NK127(jo)001:8506: sems thams cad mdun na bzhugs shing chos ston pa
NK127(jo)001:8507: mi 'gyur ro // dang / dga' ldan gyi lha
NK127(jo)001:8508: rnams kyi nang du skye zhing byang chub sems dpa'
NK127(jo)001:8509: rnams dang thabs gcig tu gnas par 'gyur ro //
NK127(jo)001:8511: phyag na rdo rjes gsol pa /
NK127(jo)001:8512: ming brgyad pa 'di bklags nas bstod pas phyag na
NK127(jo)001:8513: rdo rje dang lha rnams dga' nas dngos grub stsol
NK127(jo)001:8514: ba dang bgegs mi 'byung zhing rmi lam ngan pa
NK127(jo)001:8515: mi 'byung ba sogs phan yon rgya cher gsungs so
NK127(jo)001:8516: // rdo rje ri rab chen po'i rtse mo'i khang pa brtsegs pa'i gzungs las /
NK127(jo)001:8517: bcom ldan 'das rdo rje lhun po'i rtse mo'i khang pa brtsegs pa na /
NK127(jo)001:8518: byang chub sems dpa' chen po dang nyan thos chen
NK127(jo)001:8519: po mang po dag dang lha dang mi la sogs
NK127(jo)001:8520: pa'i 'khor rnams dang thabs gcig bzhugs te /
NK127(jo)001:8521: mdzod sbu nas 'od kyi snang ba chen pos gang+g+aa'i
NK127(jo)001:8522: klung gi bye ma snyed kyi zhing snang bar byas
NK127(jo)001:8523: pas bdud kyi gnas thams cad 'bar bas dpa' bkong
NK127(jo)001:8524: pa dang / bdud kyi dmag chen po 'jigs su
NK127(jo)001:8525: rung bas dpag tshad stong phrag brgyad cu rtsa bzhir
NK127(jo)001:8526: khyab pas bcom ldan 'das la tho btsams pa dang
NK127(jo)001:8527: pa dang / / mtshon cha thams cad me tog
NK127(jo)001:8528: gi char dang sgra thams cad sangs rgyas kyi sgra
NK127(jo)001:8529: la sogs par gyur te bdud sdig can zhags pa
NK127(jo)001:8530: lngas bcings pas 'khor gyi khyams der 'gyel to //
NK127(jo)001:8531: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis byams brtse'i thugs kyis lag na rdo rje la bka' stsal pa /
NK127(jo)001:8532: gsang ba pa'i bdag po lag na rdo rje bdud
NK127(jo)001:8533: sdig can 'di 'khor gyi khyams 'di nas slongs la
NK127(jo)001:8535: rdo rje rnam par thar pa'i sgo chen po'i ting
NK127(jo)001:8536: nge 'dzin gyi rnam par 'phrul pa'i byin rlabs bsam
NK127(jo)001:8538: bdud kyi dkyil 'khor 'joms par byed pa /
NK127(jo)001:8539: bdud dang gzhan yang gdug pa can thams cad dkon
NK127(jo)001:8540: mchog gsum la skyabs su 'gro bar byed pa ston
NK127(jo)001:8542: lag na rdo rjes bcom ldan 'das la thal mo
NK127(jo)001:8543: sbyar te tshul dang mthun pa'i tshigs su bcad pa
NK127(jo)001:8544: dag gis bstod pa byas nas rin po che'i pad+ma'i
NK127(jo)001:8545: snying po la 'dug ste ting nge 'dzin la snyoms
NK127(jo)001:8546: par zhugs pas / 'jig rten gyi khams 'di rnam pa drug tu kun tu rab tu g.yos shing /
NK127(jo)001:8547: sku'i yan lag dang nying lag thams cad nas rdo
NK127(jo)001:8548: rje kun tu 'bar ba kun tu rab tu mched
NK127(jo)001:8549: cing 'bar ba me lce gcig tu gyur pa'i rdo
NK127(jo)001:8551: phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten tshad med grangs med dpag tu
NK127(jo)001:8552: med pa'i sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das da ltar bzhugs
NK127(jo)001:8553: pa thams cad kyi 'khor gyi khyams kun tu snang
NK127(jo)001:8554: bar byas shing de dag gi rgyu mtshan kyang sangs
NK127(jo)001:8555: rgyas de rnams kyis gsungs pas byang chub sems dpa'i
NK127(jo)001:8556: 'dus pa chen po yang zhing 'dir lhags so //
NK127(jo)001:8557: phyogs bcu'i zhing gi sangs rgyas tshad med grangs med
NK127(jo)001:8558: pa'i phyag g.yas pa gser gyi mdog can bkra shis
NK127(jo)001:8559: pa'i mtshan gyis brgyan pa brkyangs te lag na rdo
NK127(jo)001:8560: rje'i spyi bor byugs nas dus gcig tu gsung gi
NK127(jo)001:8561: nga ros 'jig rten gyi khams thams cad khyab par
NK127(jo)001:8562: / rigs kyi bu gang gi phyir bdud sdig can
NK127(jo)001:8563: dang de bzhin gshegs pa'i bstan pa la sdang ba'i
NK127(jo)001:8564: ma rungs pa thams cad tshar gcod pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:8565: byang chub sems dpa' las dang po pa rnams gzengs bstod pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:8566: sems can thams cad kyi don gyi phyir ting nge
NK127(jo)001:8567: 'dzin 'di la zhugs pa legs so zhes bka' stsal
NK127(jo)001:8568: to // de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis lag na
NK127(jo)001:8569: rdo rje la bdud sdig can 'di bcing ba 'di
NK127(jo)001:8570: las dgrol la dkon mchog gsum la skyabs su 'gro
NK127(jo)001:8571: to // ba dang / gzhan yang bstan pa la
NK127(jo)001:8572: ma dad pa thams cad bstan pa la gnas par
NK127(jo)001:8573: 'gyur ba de ltar gyis shig ces gsungs pas /
NK127(jo)001:8574: lag na rdo rjes bcom ldan 'das kyi ltar mnyan
NK127(jo)001:8575: nas rdo rje'i rnam par thar pa'i sgo chen po'i
NK127(jo)001:8576: ting nge 'dzin bdud kyi dkyil 'khor thams cad 'joms
NK127(jo)001:8577: par byed pa la snyoms par zhugs ma thag tu
NK127(jo)001:8578: 'jig rten gyi khams rnam pa drug tu g.yos shing
NK127(jo)001:8579: / de'i sku yang me lce kun tu 'bar ba
NK127(jo)001:8580: shin tu mi bzad pa'i khro bo'i lus kyi rnam
NK127(jo)001:8581: 'gyur chen po'i lus kyi tshigs thams cad nas sna
NK127(jo)001:8582: tshogs pa'i khro bo mi bzad pa'i sprin gyi tshogs
NK127(jo)001:8583: byung bas log 'dren thams cad tshig cing 'tshog pa
NK127(jo)001:8584: sogs kyi sdug bsngal mi bzad pas bdud sdig can
NK127(jo)001:8585: dang bgegs dang log 'dren thams cad rlung drag pos
NK127(jo)001:8586: bskyod pa'i shing bzhin 'dar zhing ngu bar 'dod kyang
NK127(jo)001:8587: ngu ma nus par ri mo bzhin du mi g.yo
NK127(jo)001:8588: / bar gnas so // de nas phyag na rdo
NK127(jo)001:8589: rje'i rkang pa gnyis las khro bo 'jigs su rung
NK127(jo)001:8590: ba gnyis byung ste de bzhin gshegs pa la lan
NK127(jo)001:8591: 'bum phrag du mar bskor ba byas shing lag na
NK127(jo)001:8592: rdo rje la ci bgyis bka' stsol cig ces zhus
NK127(jo)001:8593: / bar gnas so // so // de nas gsang
NK127(jo)001:8594: ba pa'i bdag po cang mi smra bar 'dug ste
NK127(jo)001:8595: / bar gnas so // so // / dpral pa'i
NK127(jo)001:8596: dkyil nas khro bo 'jigs pa chen po'i gzugs can
NK127(jo)001:8597: mi bzad pa yan lag thams cad rdo rje 'bar
NK127(jo)001:8598: ba'i snang bas stong chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khams
NK127(jo)001:8599: thams cad khyab pas gzhan gyi gzi brjid zil du
NK127(jo)001:8600: / bar gnas so // so // / brlag pa
NK127(jo)001:8601: / nyi zla gza' skar nor bu la sogs pa'i
NK127(jo)001:8602: 'od mnan nas de bzhin gshegs pa dang byang chub
NK127(jo)001:8603: sems dpa' sa bcu pa la gnas pa'i 'od ma
NK127(jo)001:8604: gtogs pa 'od gzhan thams cad mog mog por byed
NK127(jo)001:8605: / bar gnas so // so // / brlag pa
NK127(jo)001:8606: / pa byung bas / de bzhin gshegs pa la
NK127(jo)001:8607: lan mu med par bskor ba byas shing lag na
NK127(jo)001:8608: rdo rje la rigs kyi bu ci bgyi dka' stsol
NK127(jo)001:8610: de nas lag na rdo rjes khro bo de dag
NK127(jo)001:8611: la bdud sdig can dang gzhan yang bstan pa la
NK127(jo)001:8612: ma dad pa'i bgegs la sogs pa thams cad dkon
NK127(jo)001:8613: mchog gsum la skyabs su 'dzin cing /
NK127(jo)001:8614: dam tshig la gnas par gyis shig ces smras pas /
NK127(jo)001:8615: khro bo de dag gis dus gcig tu seng ge'i
NK127(jo)001:8616: skad kyi nga ros 'jig rten kun tu 'gengs pa'i
NK127(jo)001:8617: gsang sngags kyi gzhi smras pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:8618: 'jig rten gyi khams rnam pa drug tu g.yos shing
NK127(jo)001:8619: phyogs mtshams thams cad du rdo rje'i skar mda' chen
NK127(jo)001:8622: sa chen po grum pa'i ser ka nas chu'i rgyun
NK127(jo)001:8623: gyen du byung bas 'jig dus kyi chu bzhin du
NK127(jo)001:8624: sa chen po kun tu gang zhing sa 'og gi
NK127(jo)001:8625: klu dang lha dang lha min chen po rnams steng
NK127(jo)001:8626: du 'thon / 'byung po dang bgegs dang log 'dren
NK127(jo)001:8627: thams cad kyi lus dang bdud kyi gnas thams cad
NK127(jo)001:8628: me lce gcig tu 'bar bas bsregs shing lha'i khang
NK127(jo)001:8629: pa la sogs pa thams cad 'od med par gyur
NK127(jo)001:8630: du 'thon / ba dang / bdud kyi ris thams
NK127(jo)001:8631: cad kyi mgo bo rdo rje'i khro bo chen po
NK127(jo)001:8632: rnams kyis rdo rjes gzhom par mthong nas /
NK127(jo)001:8633: shin tu sdug bsngal ba'i tshor bas nyam thag cing
NK127(jo)001:8634: skrag la zhum ste bdud sdig can gyis de bzhin
NK127(jo)001:8635: gshegs pa sh+aakya thub pa dang gsang ba'i bdag po
NK127(jo)001:8637: yongs su skyobs shig bdag byang chub snying po la
NK127(jo)001:8638: 'dug gi bar du dkon mchog gsum la skyabs su
NK127(jo)001:8639: 'agro'o // sems can thams cad kyi don gyi phyir
NK127(jo)001:8640: bla med byang chub tu sems bskyed do zhes snying
NK127(jo)001:8642: 'khor rnams ngo mtshar du gyur nas sangs rgyas dang
NK127(jo)001:8643: gsang ba'i bdag po la bstod cing me tog gis
NK127(jo)001:8644: gtor ro // bdud sdig can kyang mchog tu dga'
NK127(jo)001:8645: zhing rang gi mthus rin po che'i gzhal med khang
NK127(jo)001:8646: bkod pa khyad par 'phags pa dang ldan pa byung
NK127(jo)001:8647: gtor ro // ba / dge ba'i bshes gnyen gsang
NK127(jo)001:8648: ba'i bdag po la mchod pa'i phyir phul te tshul
NK127(jo)001:8649: dang 'dra ba'i tshigs su bcad pas bstod do //
NK127(jo)001:8650: de bzhin du gsang ba ba'i bdag pos bkas khro
NK127(jo)001:8651: bo de dag gis lha dang klu dang gnod sbyin
NK127(jo)001:8652: la sogs pa'i ma rungs pa thams cad dam zhig
NK127(jo)001:8654: de nas lag na rdo rje ting nge 'dzin de las langs pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:8655: sh+aa ri'i bus lag na rdo rje la ting nge 'dzin de'i ming dris pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:8656: lag na rdo rjes smras pa /
NK127(jo)001:8657: ting nge 'dzin 'di ni ming dang yi ge dang
NK127(jo)001:8658: sgra skad kyis rtogs par bya ba ma yin te
NK127(jo)001:8659: / gang ming dang gzugs la sogs pa ting nge
NK127(jo)001:8660: 'dzin zhes bya ba'i chos gang yang med pa'i de
NK127(jo)001:8661: bzhin nyid kyi don zab mo las brtsams te chos
NK127(jo)001:8662: kyi rnam grangs bstan pa la /
NK127(jo)001:8663: de bzhin gshegs pa sh+aakya thub pa dang phyogs bcu'i
NK127(jo)001:8664: 'jig rten gyi khams su gtogs pa'i de bzhin gshegs
NK127(jo)001:8665: pa thams cad kyis phyag g.yas pa lag na rdo
NK127(jo)001:8666: rje'i spyi bor bzhag ste legs so dang basngagasa pa
NK127(jo)001:8667: mdzad do // chos kyi rnam grangs de bshad pas
NK127(jo)001:8668: lha'i bu gang+g+aa'i klung tshad med grangs med dpag tu
NK127(jo)001:8669: med pa'i bye ma'i rdul phra rab kyi rdul las
NK127(jo)001:8670: shin tu 'das pa snyed chos rnams la chos kyi
NK127(jo)001:8671: mig rdul med cing dri ma dang bral ba skyes
NK127(jo)001:8673: dge slong ma la sogs pa dang lha la sogs
NK127(jo)001:8674: pa'i sems can rab tu mang po dag gis mi
NK127(jo)001:8675: skye ba'i chos la bzod pa thob bo //
NK127(jo)001:8676: de bas kyang ches mang ba'i sems can rnams ni
NK127(jo)001:8677: phyir mi ldog pa nyid du bya ba'i phyir rdzogs
NK127(jo)001:8678: pa'i byang chub tu sems skyes so //
NK127(jo)001:8679: 'jig rten gyi khams 'di dang sangs rgyas kyi zhing
NK127(jo)001:8680: gzhan grangs med pa dapa ga tu med pa brjod
NK127(jo)001:8681: du med pa'i yang brjod du med pa dag kyang
NK127(jo)001:8682: rnam pa drug tu g.yos so //
NK127(jo)001:8683: lha dang byang chub sems dpa'i mthus phyag na rdo
NK127(jo)001:8684: rje la mchod pa'i sprin rgya mtsho sna tshogs pas
NK127(jo)001:8685: nam mkha' rgyas par bkang zhing /
NK127(jo)001:8686: tshangs dbang khyab 'jug la sogs pa 'jig rten skye
NK127(jo)001:8687: dgu thams cad kyis bcom ldan 'das la btud nas
NK127(jo)001:8690: rgyud kyi rgyal po dpal ye shes thig le las /
NK127(jo)001:8691: phyag na rdo rje mgon chen po //
NK127(jo)001:8692: rdo rje 'dzin pa kun gyi bdag /
NK127(jo)001:8693: mtha' yas pa yi 'jig rten khams //
NK127(jo)001:8694: skye dang 'jig pa'i rgyu yin no //
NK127(jo)001:8695: de la skye ba gang yang med //
NK127(jo)001:8696: rang byung mchog gi dbang phyug go //
NK127(jo)001:8697: de yi phyag gi rdo rje ni //
NK127(jo)001:8698: ye shes bcu gnyis skye ba med //
NK127(jo)001:8699: thog ma yi ni rwa lnga las //
NK127(jo)001:8700: de bzhin gshegs pa lnga 'byung ngo //
NK127(jo)001:8701: mthar nas 'byung ba chen po lnga //
NK127(jo)001:8702: dbus nas 'gro ba rigs drug byung //
NK127(jo)001:8703: lta ba kun gyi srung don phyir //
NK127(jo)001:8704: sna tshogs pa yi gzugs su spyod //
NK127(jo)001:8705: la lar rdo rje 'dzin pa dang //
NK127(jo)001:8706: la lar sangs rgyas kyi ni gzugs //
NK127(jo)001:8707: la lar he ru ka yi gzugs //
NK127(jo)001:8708: la lar de bzhin gshegs pa dang //
NK127(jo)001:8709: la lar byang chub sems dpa'i gzugs //
NK127(jo)001:8710: la lar nyan pa lta bur gzugs //
NK127(jo)001:8712: la lar klog pa'i tshul du bzhugs //
NK127(jo)001:8713: la lar rgyud dang bstan bcos ni //
NK127(jo)001:8714: mdzad pa dang ni la lar 'dzin //
NK127(jo)001:8715: mang du brjod lta ci zhig dgos //
NK127(jo)001:8716: de ston phyag na rdo rje rgyal //
NK127(jo)001:8718: dpal ldan rdo rje 'dzin pa'i rtogs pa brjod pa'i skabs te gsum pa'o ////
NK127(jo)001:8719: byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po mgon po byams pa la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK127(jo)001:8721: 'phags pa byams pa 'jug pa zhes bya ba theg pa chen po'i mdo las /
NK127(jo)001:8722: byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po byams pa
NK127(jo)001:8723: ni yun ring po nas tshangs par spyod cing sngon
NK127(jo)001:8724: gyi rgyal ba la bya ba byas /
NK127(jo)001:8726: zab mo'i bzod pa dang ldan te /
NK127(jo)001:8727: byams pa yang dag par zhugs nas bskal pa brgyad
NK127(jo)001:8728: khri bzhi stong lon pa dang gdod ston pa sh+aakya
NK127(jo)001:8729: thub pas byang chub tu thugs bskyed do //
NK127(jo)001:8730: de yang 'das pa'i dus bskal pa grangs med bsam
NK127(jo)001:8731: gyis mi khyab pa'i snga rol sangs rgyas gser bzang
NK127(jo)001:8732: 'od ces bya ba 'jig rten du byung ste /
NK127(jo)001:8733: de'i gser gyi 'od bzang pos 'jig rten gyi khams rtag tu snang bar byed do //
NK127(jo)001:8734: de'i tshe byams pa 'di gling bzhi ba'i dbang phyug
NK127(jo)001:8735: 'khor los sgyur ba'i rgyal po gser mdog ces bya
NK127(jo)001:8737: sangs rgyas gser bzang 'od byang chub sems dpa'i dge
NK127(jo)001:8738: 'dun chen po dang bcas pa la lo bye ba
NK127(jo)001:8739: phrag brgyad cu rtsa bzhi'i bar du mchod pa dang
NK127(jo)001:8740: bsnyen bkur thams cad kyis mchod pa byas so //
NK127(jo)001:8741: der tshangs pa dang dbang po rgyal chen bzhis kyang bsnyen bkur byed do //
NK127(jo)001:8742: rgyal po des 'khor gyi khyams dpag tshad brgyad cu
NK127(jo)001:8743: pa rin po che'i bkod pa tshad med pa dang
NK127(jo)001:8744: ldan pa dang mchod pa'i bkod pa ches bzang zhing
NK127(jo)001:8745: bsam gyis mi khyab pas bsnyen bkur byas so //
NK127(jo)001:8746: de'i mthar rgyal po gser mdog gis ci bdag gi
NK127(jo)001:8747: dge rtsa 'di brgya byin nam tshangs pa'am 'on te
NK127(jo)001:8748: 'khor los sgyur ba thob pa'i phyir yongs su bsngo'am
NK127(jo)001:8749: snyam pa dang / de'i rtog pa sangs rgyas gser
NK127(jo)001:8750: bzang 'od des mkhyen nas rang 'dra ba'i de bzhin
NK127(jo)001:8751: gshegs pa mdun gyi bar snang la sprul pas tshigs
NK127(jo)001:8752: snyam pa dang / su bcad de / tshangs pa
NK127(jo)001:8753: sogs mi rtag mi brtan pas dman pa'i gnas la
NK127(jo)001:8754: ma 'dod par yon tan tshad med pa sems can
NK127(jo)001:8755: kun la phan pa'i byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed
NK127(jo)001:8756: cig ces brjod pas rgyal po gser mdog gis bla
NK127(jo)001:8757: med byang chub tu sems bskyed nas sangs rgyas la
NK127(jo)001:8758: snyam pa dang / su bcad de / zhus pas
NK127(jo)001:8759: / ji ltar mgo dang rkang lag gtong ba sogs
NK127(jo)001:8760: bskal pa mang po sdug bsngal ni ci yang med
NK127(jo)001:8761: snyam pa dang / su bcad de / zhus pas
NK127(jo)001:8762: / par / theg pa bde ba kho nas bde
NK127(jo)001:8763: blag tu bdud rtsi byang chub mchog thob pa'i lam
NK127(jo)001:8764: bstan du gsol zhes zhus pa na /
NK127(jo)001:8765: sangs rgyas kyis rgyal po de la /
NK127(jo)001:8766: byang chub sems kyis bsod nams tshad med pa 'phel zhing /
NK127(jo)001:8767: bslab pa dang byams pa dang dam bcas pa sogs
NK127(jo)001:8768: yongs su mi gtong ba'i bag yod sogs la brten
NK127(jo)001:8769: nas / lus gtong ba sogs dka' ba med par
NK127(jo)001:8770: theg pa bde bas 'tshang rgya ba'i bslab pa bstan
NK127(jo)001:8771: nas / par mdzad do // rgyal po de rab
NK127(jo)001:8772: tu byung nas lo khri'i bar du tshangs par spyod
NK127(jo)001:8773: cing mngon shes bsgrubs nas mang du thos pa'i mthar
NK127(jo)001:8774: nas / par mdzad do // phyin to // byams pa'i ting nge 'dzin kyang bsgrubs so //
NK127(jo)001:8775: dge rtsa dang lhag bsam des 'khor los sgyur ba'i
NK127(jo)001:8776: rgyal por gyur pas sangs rgyas nyi khri mnyes par
NK127(jo)001:8777: byas shing de dag las rab tu byung ngo //
NK127(jo)001:8778: sngon 'das pa'i bskal pa grangs med tshad med pa'i snga rol na /
NK127(jo)001:8779: de bzhin gshegs pa rin chen gdugs zhes bya ba'i
NK127(jo)001:8780: bstan pa la byang chub sems dpa' byams pa 'di
NK127(jo)001:8781: dge slong blo gros brtan po zhes bya bar gyur
NK127(jo)001:8782: to // de grong du bsod snyoms kyi phyir rgyu
NK127(jo)001:8783: ba na 'dir snyam du nam srog chags brgya tshang
NK127(jo)001:8784: bar bslab gzhi lnga la ma bkod kyi bar du
NK127(jo)001:8785: bdag gis zan mi za'o snyam du bsams nas /
NK127(jo)001:8786: de ltar rgyu ba las lan res 'gar nyi ma
NK127(jo)001:8787: gcig gis srog chags brgya tshang bar bslab gzhi la
NK127(jo)001:8788: bkod pa'ang byung / lan 'gar nyi ma gnyis nas
NK127(jo)001:8789: bdun gyi bar gyis dam bca' rdzogs pa yod la
NK127(jo)001:8790: bkod pa'ang byung / / de ltar gyur pas zhag
NK127(jo)001:8791: bdun du zan chad kyang sems can rnams la snying
NK127(jo)001:8792: rje ba'i phyir sems mi skyo bar zhag brgyad pa
NK127(jo)001:8793: bkod pa'ang byung / / la zan za'o // rnam
NK127(jo)001:8794: grangs de lta bus lo brgyad khri bzhi stong gi
NK127(jo)001:8795: bar du yongs su mi skyo ba'i sems kyis grong
NK127(jo)001:8796: dang grong khyer sogs su sems can de dag bslab
NK127(jo)001:8797: pa'i gzhi lnga la bkod do //
NK127(jo)001:8798: lo de dag tshang ba de'i 'og tu skyes pa
NK127(jo)001:8799: dang bud med khye'u dang bu mo bye ba khrag
NK127(jo)001:8800: khrig 'bum phrag sum bcu rtsa drug bslab pa'i gzhi
NK127(jo)001:8801: lnga la bkod par gyur to //
NK127(jo)001:8802: de nas bdag gis sems can 'di dag bslab gzhi
NK127(jo)001:8803: lnga la bkod zin gyi da bla med rdzogs pa'i
NK127(jo)001:8804: byang chub la gzud par bya'o snyam du /
NK127(jo)001:8805: de dag gis thad du song nas lo bzhi khri
NK127(jo)001:8806: nyis stong gi bar du dkon mchog gsum dang theg
NK127(jo)001:8807: pa chen po'i basngagasa pa brjod pas /
NK127(jo)001:8808: sems can de dag gi nang nas bye ba sum cu ni rdzogs pa'i byang chub la btsud do //
NK127(jo)001:8809: lhag ma nyan rang gi theg par sems bskyed par byas so //
NK127(jo)001:8810: de nas theg gsum la mos par byas pa 'di
NK127(jo)001:8811: dag bag yod par gnas par bya ba'i phyir ting
NK127(jo)001:8812: nge 'dzin 'di la gzud pa bstan no snyam nas
NK127(jo)001:8813: / lo nyi khri chig stong gi bar du srog
NK127(jo)001:8814: chags bye ba khrag khrig 'bum phrag sum cu rtsa
NK127(jo)001:8815: drug po de dag la ting nge 'dzin la dmigs
NK127(jo)001:8816: pa'i lung phog nas de dag ci nas byams pa'i
NK127(jo)001:8817: ting nge 'dzin bsgrub par 'gyur pa de ltar gdams
NK127(jo)001:8819: dge slong blo gros brtan po de grong du 'gro
NK127(jo)001:8820: ba'i tshe byams pa'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par
NK127(jo)001:8821: zhugs te 'agro'o // de'i rkang pa sgo'i them pa
NK127(jo)001:8822: la bzhag pa'i tshe sems can byams pa la gnas
NK127(jo)001:8823: pa de dag kyang byams pa'i ting 'dzin la ji
NK127(jo)001:8824: ltar btsud pa bzhin du snyoms par 'jug go //
NK127(jo)001:8825: dge slong de'i byams pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi rnam
NK127(jo)001:8826: 'phrul de lta bu mthong nas sa bla'i lha rnams
NK127(jo)001:8827: kyis a la la byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa'
NK127(jo)001:8828: chen po 'di ni byams par 'gyur te 'di ltar
NK127(jo)001:8829: grong du 'gro ba na sems can rnams byams pa'i
NK127(jo)001:8830: ting 'dzin la snyoms par 'jug pa'i phyir ro zhes
NK127(jo)001:8831: sgra bsgrags so // sgra des rim bzhin bar snang
NK127(jo)001:8832: gi lha nas gnas gtsang ma'i lha rnams kyi bar
NK127(jo)001:8833: du gcig nas gcig tu de ltar thos shing bsgrags
NK127(jo)001:8834: sgra bsgrags so // so // de'i ming de la
NK127(jo)001:8835: yang de bzhin gshegs pa rin chen gdugs des rjes
NK127(jo)001:8836: su yi rangs par mdzad de /
NK127(jo)001:8837: 'di skad du dge slong blo gros brtan po 'di
NK127(jo)001:8838: ni srid par 'pho zhing skye ba thams cad du
NK127(jo)001:8839: byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po byams pa
NK127(jo)001:8840: zhes bya bar 'gyur te mngon par grags par 'gyur
NK127(jo)001:8841: ro byang chub thob pa'i tshe yang 'di'i ming de
NK127(jo)001:8842: nyid du 'gyur te 'jig rten du nyan thos kyi
NK127(jo)001:8843: dge 'dun dpag tu med pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:8844: rin po che bkod pa'i sangs rgyas kyi zhing gi
NK127(jo)001:8845: bde ba thams cad dang ldan pa'i sems can rnams
NK127(jo)001:8846: 'dus pa'i nang du de bzhin gshegs pa byams pa
NK127(jo)001:8847: zhes bya bar 'gyur ro zhes lung bstan to //
NK127(jo)001:8848: byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po byams pa'i
NK127(jo)001:8849: ming tsam thos pa de dag kyang rnyed pa'i mchog
NK127(jo)001:8850: legs par rnyed pa yin na sha'i mig gis mngon
NK127(jo)001:8851: sum mthong nas dga' ba thob pa lta ci smos
NK127(jo)001:8853: byang chub sems dpa' byams pa dga' ldan gnam du skye ba blang ba'i mdo las /
NK127(jo)001:8854: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad mkhyen pas 'khor 'di'i
NK127(jo)001:8855: nang du byang chub sems dpa' chen po byams pa
NK127(jo)001:8856: 'di rdzogs pa'i byang chub tu lung bstan gyis /
NK127(jo)001:8857: dus 'di nas lo bcu gnyis kyi 'og tu tshe'i
NK127(jo)001:8858: dus byas nas dga' ldan gnam du skye ba lon
NK127(jo)001:8859: par 'gyur ro // der dga' ldan gyi lha'i bu
NK127(jo)001:8860: rnams kyis skye ba gcig gis thogs pa'i byang chub
NK127(jo)001:8861: sems dpa' la mchod pa'i don du rang gi dbu
NK127(jo)001:8862: rgyan la sogs pa'i rgyan las smon lam btab ste
NK127(jo)001:8863: lha'i bsod nams kyi mthus gzhal med khang bkod pa
NK127(jo)001:8864: mchog tu 'phags pas mdzes pa 'byung bar 'gyur ro
NK127(jo)001:8865: par 'gyur ro // // dga' ldan gyi gnas de
NK127(jo)001:8866: yi bsod nams kyi khyad par ni de bzhin gshegs
NK127(jo)001:8867: pa bskal pa chung ngu'i bar du bzhugs nas bshad
NK127(jo)001:8868: kyang rdzogs pa'i mtha' mi mngon no //
NK127(jo)001:8869: gang zhig lha'i gnas der byams pa'i zhabs 'brings byed
NK127(jo)001:8870: par 'dod cing yan lag lnga'i khrims brgyad rdzogs par
NK127(jo)001:8871: nos pa dang / brtson pas dge bcu spyod cing
NK127(jo)001:8872: bde skyid phun sum tshogs par 'dod pa dag ni
NK127(jo)001:8873: yang dag par lta ba zhes bya ste /
NK127(jo)001:8874: gzhan du lta ba ni log par lta ba zhes bya ba'o //
NK127(jo)001:8875: de yang de lta bu'i gnas bde skyid phun sum tshogs pa der /
NK127(jo)001:8876: skyes bu chen po byams pa 'di dus 'di nas
NK127(jo)001:8877: lo bcu gnyis lon pa dpyid zla 'bring po'i tshes
NK127(jo)001:8879: yul ra ni kra pa li'i grong khyer na bram
NK127(jo)001:8880: ze chen po ba ba li zhes bya ba'i khyim
NK127(jo)001:8881: du skye ba blang ba'i sa nas skyil mo krung
NK127(jo)001:8882: bcas te ting nge 'dzin la mnyam par bzhag bzhin
NK127(jo)001:8883: du lus kyi sku gdung yang gser gyi gzugs bzhin
NK127(jo)001:8884: du mi g.yo bar bzhag nas /
NK127(jo)001:8885: dga' ldan du rin po che sna bdun pa'i khang
NK127(jo)001:8886: bzang du seng ge'i khri la pad+ma'i steng du skyil
NK127(jo)001:8887: mo krung bcas pas 'dzam bu chu bo'i gser lta
NK127(jo)001:8888: bu'i lus su bardzusa te skye la /
NK127(jo)001:8889: de'i sku'i tshad ni chur dpag tshad bcu drug pa
NK127(jo)001:8890: mtshan dpes rdzogs par brgyan cing rin po che'i dbu
NK127(jo)001:8891: rgyan las sprul pa'i de bzhin gshegs pa dpag tu
NK127(jo)001:8892: med pa 'khor byang chub sems dpa' dang bcas pa
NK127(jo)001:8893: der ni zhing gzhan gyi byang chub sems dpa' rnams
NK127(jo)001:8894: cho 'phrul bco brgyad ston cing gnas so //
NK127(jo)001:8895: byams pa'i smin mtshams nas 'od zer dkar po byung ba las /
NK127(jo)001:8896: rin po che brgya phrag rab tu mang po'i kha
NK127(jo)001:8897: dog dang ldan pa'i mtshan dpe'i 'od 'bar ba'i lha'i
NK127(jo)001:8899: nyin mtshan rtag par phyir mi ldog pa'i chos kyi
NK127(jo)001:8900: 'khor lo la spyod cing mthar byams pa 'dzam bu'i
NK127(jo)001:8901: gling du skye ba blang ba'i mdo bshad par 'gyur
NK127(jo)001:8902: ro // bcom ldan 'das sh+aakya'i rgyal po mya ngan
NK127(jo)001:8903: las 'das pa'i 'og tu 'khor bzhi po gang gis
NK127(jo)001:8904: sdom pa la gnas shing mchod rten la mchod pa
NK127(jo)001:8905: ro // dang / mdo klog pa dang de bzhin gshegs pa'i sku gzugs byed pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:8906: byams pa'i mtshan brjod pa de lta bu la sogs
NK127(jo)001:8907: pa 'chi ba'i dus byas na dga' ldan du bardzusa
NK127(jo)001:8908: te skye zhing / byams pa'i zhal mthong la chos
NK127(jo)001:8909: thos nas rim gyis bskal pa bzang po'i sangs rgyas
NK127(jo)001:8910: rnams las lung bstan pa thob par 'gyur ro //
NK127(jo)001:8911: gang la la zhig byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa'
NK127(jo)001:8912: chen po byams pa'i mtshan thos nas dga' ba dang
NK127(jo)001:8913: gus par phyag 'tshal ba'i mi de dag tshe'i dus
NK127(jo)001:8914: byas nas / mun pa'i khams su mi ltung /
NK127(jo)001:8915: mtha' 'khob dang log par lta ba dang mi dge ba thams cad spyod par mi skye /
NK127(jo)001:8916: skye ba thams cad du drang por lta ba dang
NK127(jo)001:8917: 'khor phun sum tshogs pa dang dkon mchog gsum la
NK127(jo)001:8919: gang zhig sdom pa bshig pa dang mi dge ba'i
NK127(jo)001:8920: las byas pas byang chub sems dpa' 'di'i mtshan nas
NK127(jo)001:8921: brjod la phyag 'tshal te sems rtse gcig pas bshags
NK127(jo)001:8922: na sdig pa thams cad myur du byang bar 'gyur
NK127(jo)001:8923: ro // sku gzugs byas nas mchod pa dang mtshan
NK127(jo)001:8924: brjod pa de dag tshe'i dus byed pa'i tshe byams
NK127(jo)001:8925: pa'i smin mtshams kyi mdzod spu nas 'od zer gyi
NK127(jo)001:8927: lha'i bu thams cad kyis man d+aa ra ba'i char
NK127(jo)001:8928: phab cing me de bsus nas skad cig yud tsam
NK127(jo)001:8929: la dga' ldan lha'i gnas su skyes te byams pa'i
NK127(jo)001:8930: zhal mthong nas chos thos pas bla med byang chub
NK127(jo)001:8932: ma 'ongs par yang sangs rgyas gang+g+aa'i klung gi bye ma snyed mthong bar 'gyur ro //
NK127(jo)001:8933: ma 'ongs pa'i dus su sems can gang zhig byams
NK127(jo)001:8934: pa la skyabs su 'gro ba de dag bla na
NK127(jo)001:8935: med pa'i lam dang phyir mi ldog pa'i 'khor lo
NK127(jo)001:8936: thob nas byams pa sangs rgyas pa'i dus kyi tshe
NK127(jo)001:8937: de dag gis de bzhin gshegs pa de'i 'od zer
NK127(jo)001:8938: mthong nas lung bstan pa thob par 'gyur ro //
NK127(jo)001:8939: sangs rgyas mya ngan las 'das pa'i 'og tu 'khor
NK127(jo)001:8940: bzhi po dang lha klu gnod sbyin la sogs pa
NK127(jo)001:8941: gang zhig dga' ldan du skyes pa'i dus ni 'di
NK127(jo)001:8943: dga' ldan yid la byed pas de bzhin gshegs pa'i
NK127(jo)001:8944: sdom pa blangs nas nyi ma gcig gam nyi ma
NK127(jo)001:8945: bdun gyi bar du dge bcu'i yid la byed pa
NK127(jo)001:8946: dang dge bcu'i lam la spyod pa'i bsod nams de
NK127(jo)001:8947: dag byams pa'i mdu na du bsngo zhing smon lam
NK127(jo)001:8948: btab pa de dag ni lta ba de dag gis
NK127(jo)001:8949: lha'i bu mthong ba dang pad+ma mthong bar 'gyur ro
NK127(jo)001:8950: // gang la la zhig skad cig tsam du byams
NK127(jo)001:8951: pa'i mtshan nas brjod pa'i mi de dag bskal pa
NK127(jo)001:8952: stong nyis brgya'i skye shi las grol zhing sdig pa
NK127(jo)001:8954: byams pa'i mtshan thos pas thal mo sbyar ba'i mi
NK127(jo)001:8955: de dag ni bskal pa lnga bcu'i skye shi las
NK127(jo)001:8957: byams pa la gus pas phyag 'tshal bas bskal pa
NK127(jo)001:8958: bye ba brgya'i skye shi las grol zhing sdig pa
NK127(jo)001:8960: lha'i gnas la mi chags shing ma 'ongs pa'i dus
NK127(jo)001:8961: su klu'i sdong po byang chub kyi shing drung du
NK127(jo)001:8962: bla med byang chub kyi lam du sems bskyed pa
NK127(jo)001:8965: dpa' bar 'gro ba'i ting nge 'dzin zhes bya ba'i mdo las /
NK127(jo)001:8966: byams pa khyod kyis kyang byang chub sems dpa' rgyal
NK127(jo)001:8967: ba'i blo gros la dpa' bar 'gro ba'i ting nge
NK127(jo)001:8968: 'dzin gyi yul ston cig ces gsungs pa na /
NK127(jo)001:8969: byang chub sems dpa' rgyal ba'i blo gros dang 'khor
NK127(jo)001:8970: de dag gis stong chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khams
NK127(jo)001:8971: na 'dzam bu'i gling ji snyed yod pa thams cad
NK127(jo)001:8973: la la ni lha'i 'jig rten na gnas /
NK127(jo)001:8974: la la ni mi'i 'jig rten na gnas /
NK127(jo)001:8975: la la ni khyim na gnas /
NK127(jo)001:8976: la la ni rab tu byung /
NK127(jo)001:8977: la la ni kun dga' bo bzhin du de bzhin gshegs pa'i g.yog byed /
NK127(jo)001:8978: la lar sh+aa ri'i bu bzhin du shes rab che /
NK127(jo)001:8979: la lar moo 'gal gyi bu bzhin du rdzu 'phrul
NK127(jo)001:8980: che ba sogs nyan thos rnams kyi mchog rnams bzhin
NK127(jo)001:8981: du sna tshogs pa'i gzugs kyis snang ba la 'jig
NK127(jo)001:8982: rten du de dang der 'du shes te grong du
NK127(jo)001:8985: nang du yang dag 'jog par gyur pa mthong nas ngo mtshar bar gyur par gsungs so //
NK127(jo)001:8986: byams pa'i seng ge'i sgra chen po zhes bya ba dkon mchog brtsegs pa'i chos kyi rnam grangs las /
NK127(jo)001:8987: bcom ldan 'das kyis gnas brtan 'od srung chen po
NK127(jo)001:8988: la khyod kyis phyi ma'i dus lnga brgya tha ma
NK127(jo)001:8989: la dam pa'i chos gzung bar spro'am zhes bka' stsal
NK127(jo)001:8990: pa na / 'od srung chen pos 'di skad du gsol to //
NK127(jo)001:8991: bdag gling bzhi pa'i 'jig rten gyi khams grong dang
NK127(jo)001:8992: grong khyer ri brag rgya mtsho nags tshal dang bcas
NK127(jo)001:8993: pa 'di bskal pa'am bskal pa las lhag par phrag
NK127(jo)001:8994: pa'am spyi bo la 'tshal bar ni spro lags kyi
NK127(jo)001:8995: / skyes bu dam pa min pa de dag gi sug las nyan par mi spro lags so //
NK127(jo)001:8996: de bzhin du bdag rgya shug gam til lam 'bras
NK127(jo)001:8997: 'bru gcig gis bskal pa'am bskal pa las lhag par
NK127(jo)001:8999: stong chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khams su bskal pa'i
NK127(jo)001:9000: me chen po kun tu rab tu 'bar ba'i nang
NK127(jo)001:9001: du spyod lam bzhis lo bye ba snyed du gnas
NK127(jo)001:9003: slad ma'i dus kyi skyes bu dam pa min pa
NK127(jo)001:9004: de dag gi log par lta ba'i sug las nyan
NK127(jo)001:9006: bdag sems can thams cad kyi khro ba dang spyo
NK127(jo)001:9007: ba dang smad pa dang brdung brdeg sogs bzod cing
NK127(jo)001:9009: mi blun po chos kyi rkun ma chos ltar bcos
NK127(jo)001:9010: pa de dag gi sug las nyan par mi spro
NK127(jo)001:9011: lags te / bdag nyi tshe ba'i spyod pa dang
NK127(jo)001:9012: shes pa dang ldan pa lags pas de lta bu'i
NK127(jo)001:9013: khur 'degs par rngo mi thogs kyi /
NK127(jo)001:9014: byang chub sems dpas ni de lta bu'i khur 'degs pa'i rngo thogs lags so //
NK127(jo)001:9015: bcom ldan 'das dper na mi rgas shing 'khogs pa
NK127(jo)001:9016: nad kyis thebs shing bu dang bu mo dang 'khor
NK127(jo)001:9017: yang med pa zhig la gzhan gyis gter gtams na
NK127(jo)001:9018: chud za ba bzhin du nyan thos nyi tshe ba'i
NK127(jo)001:9019: shes pa dang spyod par ldan pa zla bo ma
NK127(jo)001:9020: mchis pa la dam pa'i chos kyi gter 'doms par
NK127(jo)001:9021: bgyid na yun ring du gnas par mi 'gyur la
NK127(jo)001:9022: / mi bro nad med pa lo 'bum phrag du
NK127(jo)001:9023: mar 'tsho ba gzhon nu 'khor dang yon tan phun
NK127(jo)001:9024: sum tshogs pa la gzhan zhig gis gter gdams nas
NK127(jo)001:9025: yul gzhan du phyin pa de /
NK127(jo)001:9026: slad kyis 'ong ba de'i tshe gter de slar ster
NK127(jo)001:9027: ba de bzhin byang chub sems dpa' la chos kyi
NK127(jo)001:9028: gter 'doms par bgyid na de ni bskal pa bye
NK127(jo)001:9029: ba 'bum phrag mang por yang chab mi 'tshal zhing
NK127(jo)001:9030: skye bo mang po la phan thogs la dkon mchog
NK127(jo)001:9031: gsum gyi gdung rgyun mi 'chad par 'gyur lags so
NK127(jo)001:9032: // des na byang chub sems dpa' byams pa 'di
NK127(jo)001:9033: la bka' stsal par rigs so zhes zhus pa na
NK127(jo)001:9034: // / bcom ldan 'das kyis tshig de la legs so gnang ste /
NK127(jo)001:9035: bskal pa grangs med pa'i dge ba'i rtsa bas bsgrubs
NK127(jo)001:9036: pa'i phyag g.yas pa gser gyi mdog can byams pa'i
NK127(jo)001:9037: mgo la bzhag nas 'di skad ces /
NK127(jo)001:9038: byams pa khyod kyis phyi ma'i dus lnga brgya tha
NK127(jo)001:9039: ma la dam pa'i chos nub pa'i dus la bab
NK127(jo)001:9040: pa'i tshe / dam pa'i chos srung ba dang yongs
NK127(jo)001:9041: su bzung ba dang yun ring du gnas pa dang
NK127(jo)001:9042: dkon mchog gsum gyi gdung rgyun mi 'chad par spro
NK127(jo)001:9043: bar gyis shig ces phyag bzhag ma thag tu 'jig
NK127(jo)001:9044: rten gyi khams 'di lan gsum g.yos shing snang ba
NK127(jo)001:9046: 'og min pa'i bar gyi lha rnams kyis thal mo
NK127(jo)001:9047: sbyar te sems can mang po'i don du byams pa
NK127(jo)001:9048: khyod spro bar mdzod cig ces kyang smras so //
NK127(jo)001:9049: de nas byams pa stan las langs te bcom ldan 'das la btud nas 'di skad ces gsol to //
NK127(jo)001:9050: bcom ldan 'das bdag ni sems can gcig gi don
NK127(jo)001:9051: gyi slad du yang phyi ma'i matha'i mu'i bar du
NK127(jo)001:9052: 'khor ba na 'khor bar yang spro lags na dam
NK127(jo)001:9053: pa'i chos yongs su gzung pa'i slad du lta smos
NK127(jo)001:9055: de bzhin gshegs pas bskal pa grangs med pas bsgrubs
NK127(jo)001:9056: pa'i bla med byang chub 'di bsrung zhing rgyas par
NK127(jo)001:9057: bgyi lags so // zhes byams pa'i pus mo g.yas
NK127(jo)001:9058: pa'i lha nga sa la btsugs ma thag tu stong
NK127(jo)001:9059: chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khams 'di rnam pa drug
NK127(jo)001:9060: bgyi lags so // tu g.yos so // byams pas gsol pa /
NK127(jo)001:9061: bcom ldan 'das bdag ni su la yang 'gran par mi bgyid /
NK127(jo)001:9062: nga rgyal mi bgyid lags so //
NK127(jo)001:9063: de ci'i slad du zhe na /
NK127(jo)001:9064: dam pa'i chos 'dzin pa 'di ni skyes bu dam
NK127(jo)001:9065: pa'i sug las te byang chub sems dpa'i khur 'di
NK127(jo)001:9066: ni nyan rang gis 'degs par rngo mi thogs pa'i
NK127(jo)001:9067: slad du'o // bcom ldan 'das kyis byams pa la
NK127(jo)001:9068: legs so legs so ji ltar nga'i spyan sngar khyod
NK127(jo)001:9069: dam pa'i chos bzung ba'i phyir seng ge'i sgra 'di
NK127(jo)001:9070: sgrogs par byed pa de bzhin phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas
NK127(jo)001:9071: gang+g+aa'i klung gi bye ma snyed dag gi spyan snga
NK127(jo)001:9072: na yang byang chub sems dpa' rnams seng ge'i sgra
NK127(jo)001:9073: sgrogs shing chos 'dzin par byed do zhes bka' stsal
NK127(jo)001:9074: slad du'o // to // byams pas gsol pa /
NK127(jo)001:9075: bcom ldan 'das kyis skyes bu dam pa min pa
NK127(jo)001:9076: byang chub sems dpa' dang dge slong du khas 'che
NK127(jo)001:9077: ba blun po rnyed bkur la gdu ba dag gi
NK127(jo)001:9079: gzhan nongs pa de las srung ba dang de dag
NK127(jo)001:9080: gis kyang bdag de bzhin gshegs pas mkhyen no zhes
NK127(jo)001:9081: dang ba bskyed pa'i slad du'o //
NK127(jo)001:9083: phyi ma'i tshe lnga brgya tha ma la byang chub
NK127(jo)001:9084: sems dpa' khas 'che ba sdig pa 'dod pa dag
NK127(jo)001:9088: ya nga ba'i 'tsho bas 'tsho ba'i rgyu bzhis byang
NK127(jo)001:9089: chub dpar khas 'che ba khyi'i kun tu spyod pa
NK127(jo)001:9091: khyi ltar gzhan gyi khyim la bdag gir 'dzin cing
NK127(jo)001:9092: gzhan la khro ba dang 'thab cing rtsod la 'gyed
NK127(jo)001:9093: cing tshig rtsub dang mi snyan brjod par byed /
NK127(jo)001:9094: tshig tsam gyi sangs rgyas dang byang sems dang phar
NK127(jo)001:9095: phyin bsdu dngos sogs kyi basngagasa pa brjod pas zas
NK127(jo)001:9096: gos sgrub cing rang nyid de la gnas par mi
NK127(jo)001:9097: byed pa de dag khyim pa dad pa'i don du
NK127(jo)001:9098: ma yin gyi / bdag gi rnyed pa'i slad du
NK127(jo)001:9099: khyim rnams su 'gro ste gzhan gyi rnyed pa la
NK127(jo)001:9100: mi dga' zhing ma rnyed pa la yi rangs pa
NK127(jo)001:9102: gzhan la bde ba bskyed pa snying rje'i ngang tshul
NK127(jo)001:9103: can gyi byang chub sems dpa'i tshul dang mi mthun
NK127(jo)001:9104: pa de dag / lus dang sems dang tshul khrims
NK127(jo)001:9105: dang shes rab ma bsgoms pa dag gi sgo nas
NK127(jo)001:9106: zang zing gi skyes kyis khyim rnams su 'gro yi
NK127(jo)001:9107: chos kyi skyes kyis mi 'gro la 'jig rten pa'i
NK127(jo)001:9108: pa de dag / gtam byed do // sgo gsum
NK127(jo)001:9109: ma bsdams pa de dag gis ltung ba'i las byas
NK127(jo)001:9110: pa de dag bshags pa tsam gyis dag par sems
NK127(jo)001:9111: kyi phyin chad sdom par mi byed pa dag 'byung
NK127(jo)001:9112: pa de dag / gtam byed do // ste /
NK127(jo)001:9113: de ltar de dag zang zing gtso bor byed kyi
NK127(jo)001:9114: chos gtso bor mi byed pa ni shin tu nongs
NK127(jo)001:9115: pa de dag / gtam byed do // ste /
NK127(jo)001:9116: shing / gzhan yang ma 'ongs pa'i dus na dge
NK127(jo)001:9117: slong ma dul ba dag gis de bzhin gshegs pa'i
NK127(jo)001:9118: sku gzugs ri mor bris pas 'tsho bar sems shing
NK127(jo)001:9119: pa de dag / gtam byed do // ste /
NK127(jo)001:9120: shing / / dge sbyong gi las su bya ba
NK127(jo)001:9121: spong ba dang kha thon bya ba bor nas /
NK127(jo)001:9122: khyim pa'i las su bya ba sku gzugs 'bri ba
NK127(jo)001:9123: dang mchod pa'i las la brtson pas bya ba mang
NK127(jo)001:9124: ba dag 'byung ste des 'tsho bar sems so //
NK127(jo)001:9125: rigs kyi bu'am rigs kyi bu mo gang gis de
NK127(jo)001:9126: bzhin gshegs pa'i sku gzugs rin chen sna bdun las
NK127(jo)001:9127: byas pa shin tu zin par byas shing byi dor
NK127(jo)001:9128: legs par byas pa chu zheng du ri rab tsam
NK127(jo)001:9129: yod pa byed du bcug ste /
NK127(jo)001:9130: sku gzugs de lta bus sangs rgyas kyi zhing gang+g+aa'i
NK127(jo)001:9131: klung gi bye ma snyed dag bu ram shing gi
NK127(jo)001:9133: 'bras dang til gyi zhing ltar bkang bar gyur pa'i bsod nams de las /
NK127(jo)001:9134: byang chub sems dpa' gang zhig de bzhin gshegs pa'i
NK127(jo)001:9135: sku la ngo bo stong pa'i mtshan nyid du rig
NK127(jo)001:9136: pa'i tshul gyis rab tu rtogs par byed pa na
NK127(jo)001:9137: / tha na se gol gtogs pa tsam zhig zab mor rtog la bzod par gyur na /
NK127(jo)001:9138: de ches bsod nams mang du skyed la /
NK127(jo)001:9139: de bas kyang gang gi tshul khrims kyi phung po
NK127(jo)001:9140: la gnas na tshigs bzhi pa'i tshigs bcad gcig bzung
NK127(jo)001:9141: ste de'i don gang yin rtogs par byed la /
NK127(jo)001:9142: sems can gcig tsam la ston na de ni ches bsod nams mang du bskyed do //
NK127(jo)001:9144: mi gang gis ni gang+g+aa'i bye snyed kyi //
NK127(jo)001:9145: 'jig rten khams mchog rin chen bkang byas te //
NK127(jo)001:9146: dga' mchog sems kyis rgyal la phul ba dang //
NK127(jo)001:9147: gang gis sems can gcig la tshigs bcad byin //
NK127(jo)001:9148: rin chen sbyin pa shin tu rgya chen des //
NK127(jo)001:9149: tshigs bcad sbyin pa snying rjes bsgrubs de la //
NK127(jo)001:9150: char yang mi phod grangs su'ang ma yin na //
NK127(jo)001:9151: gnyis sam gsum la bsam du ga la yod //
NK127(jo)001:9152: ces pa la sogs pa rgya cher gsungs zhing byams
NK127(jo)001:9153: pa de bzhin gshegs pa'i phyag g.yas pa'i dkyil na
NK127(jo)001:9154: bsod nams thams cad mngon par bsgrubs pa'i rgyu mthun
NK127(jo)001:9155: pas brgyan pa zhes bya ba'i 'od zer mngon par
NK127(jo)001:9157: de bzhin gshegs pas bzhed na stong chen po'i 'jig
NK127(jo)001:9158: rten gyi khams 'di thams cad 'od des yog par
NK127(jo)001:9159: mdzad nas sems can thams cad la bde ba'i yo
NK127(jo)001:9161: zas gos rin chen sogs gang ci 'dod pa thams cad sbyin par spyod mod kyi /
NK127(jo)001:9162: de tsam gyis sems can rnams thog mtha' med pa'i
NK127(jo)001:9163: 'khor ba'i rgya mtsho sdug bsngal gyi chu srin 'dzin
NK127(jo)001:9164: khri'i gnas las thar bar mi 'gyur bas /
NK127(jo)001:9165: ngas ni 'jig rten bde ba'i yo byad de lta
NK127(jo)001:9166: bu spangs nas 'jig rten las 'das pa'i bde ba'i
NK127(jo)001:9167: slad du chos rin po che yang dag par ston
NK127(jo)001:9168: par mdzad pa yin la de thos na sems can
NK127(jo)001:9169: rnams kyi sdug bsngal gtan du zhi bar 'gyur ro
NK127(jo)001:9170: // byams pa de lta bas na khyod kyang nga'i
NK127(jo)001:9171: rjes su bslabs pas zang zing la gdu bar mi
NK127(jo)001:9172: bya'i chos la gdu bar bya'o //
NK127(jo)001:9173: byams pa 'di ltar byang chub sems dpa' dag gis ni bdag brgal nas gzhan bsgral ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:9174: de bzhin du grol ba dang dbugs dbyung ba dang
NK127(jo)001:9175: mya ngan las bzla bar bya'o zhes sems can thams
NK127(jo)001:9177: lha dang bcas pa'i 'jig rten gyi sa'i steng na
NK127(jo)001:9178: byang chub sems dpa'i las dang khur dang dgos pa
NK127(jo)001:9179: ji snyed pa de snyed ni sems can gzhan 'ga'
NK127(jo)001:9181: dper na stong chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khams kyi
NK127(jo)001:9182: ri dang rgya mtsho nags su bcas pa spyi bo'am
NK127(jo)001:9183: phrag par bzhag ste bskal pa 'bum gyi bar du
NK127(jo)001:9184: ngal mi gso bar 'degs pa ni khur che zhing
NK127(jo)001:9185: mi de mthu dang spro ba che mod kyi /
NK127(jo)001:9186: de bas gang gi sems can rnams mya ngan las
NK127(jo)001:9187: 'das pa'i bde ba la 'god par zhugs pa ni
NK127(jo)001:9188: khur che zhing spro ba dang mthu che la /
NK127(jo)001:9189: gang la las stong chen po'i khams kyi sems can
NK127(jo)001:9190: thams cad kyi las ji yod pa de thams cad
NK127(jo)001:9191: se go la gtogs pa tsam gyis yongs su grub
NK127(jo)001:9192: pa'i stobs chen po de bas kyang sems can rnams
NK127(jo)001:9193: 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal las dgrol lo zhes tshig tu
NK127(jo)001:9194: brjod pas las su byed pa de stobs dang ldan
NK127(jo)001:9195: no // dper na khyim bdag gcig la bu sdug pa gcig pu zhig mchis la /
NK127(jo)001:9197: khyim bdag khyod 'di nas dpag tshad 'bum gyi pha
NK127(jo)001:9198: rol tu grong che ge mo na don 'di'i phyir
NK127(jo)001:9199: zhag bdun gyis song la slar nga'i gan du slebs
NK127(jo)001:9200: par byos dang / de lta na khyod kyi bu
NK127(jo)001:9201: dang chung ma 'khor dang nor thams cad khyod la
NK127(jo)001:9202: ster gyi gzhan yang khyod la rgyal srid kyi phyed
NK127(jo)001:9203: par byos dang / sbyin no // gal te grong
NK127(jo)001:9204: de nas cha blangs te nyin mtshan bdun gyis khyod
NK127(jo)001:9205: phyir ma 'ongs na khyod la cung zad kyang mi
NK127(jo)001:9207: khyod bu dang chung ma 'khor dang bcas te chad pas bcad nas bsad do zhes bsgos na /
NK127(jo)001:9208: khyim bdag de stobs dang ldan pa'i rtsom pa dang
NK127(jo)001:9209: mgyogs pas 'gro zhing don ma grub kyi bar du
NK127(jo)001:9210: g.yeng ba dang zas dang rmugs pa dang gnyid kyi
NK127(jo)001:9211: sems mi skyed pa de lta bu'i brtson 'grus chen
NK127(jo)001:9212: po dang ldan par gyur kyang des byang chub sems
NK127(jo)001:9213: dpa'i brtson 'grus chen po'i brgya stong gi cha nas
NK127(jo)001:9214: dpe dang rgyu'i bar du nye bar mi 'agro'o //
NK127(jo)001:9216: byang chub sems dpa' ni rgyun phyogs su ded pa'i
NK127(jo)001:9217: sems can thams cad rgyun las bzlog ste g.yo ba
NK127(jo)001:9218: med pa'i mya ngan las 'das pa'i dbyings su rab
NK127(jo)001:9219: tu 'god par byed pa'i phyir te /
NK127(jo)001:9220: dper na 'di ltar mi stobs shugs dang ldan pa
NK127(jo)001:9221: la la skyes pas rgya mtsho bzhi'i chu'i phung po
NK127(jo)001:9222: ji snyed pa rgya mtshor 'jug pa'i rgyun las bzlog
NK127(jo)001:9223: ste mtsho ma dros pa'i nang du phab pa'i dka'
NK127(jo)001:9224: ba dang ngo mtshar de las /
NK127(jo)001:9225: byang chub sems dpas snying rje chen pos rdzogs byang
NK127(jo)001:9226: du sems bskyed cing nan tan byed pa ni ches
NK127(jo)001:9227: dka' ba byed cing ngo mtshar che ba yin no
NK127(jo)001:9228: // de bas kyang dkon mchog gsum dang las kyi
NK127(jo)001:9229: rnam par smin pa yod par nges par rtogs pa
NK127(jo)001:9230: de dag ches dka' ba byed cing ngo mtshar che'o
NK127(jo)001:9231: // // de bzhin du sbyar te de bas kyang dug gsum gyi sems skyes pa sel ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:9232: de bas mdza' bshes dang longs spyod thams cad spangs
NK127(jo)001:9233: te rab tu byung ba'i phyir khyim gyi gnas nas
NK127(jo)001:9235: de bas kyang gos ngur smrig bgos te legs par
NK127(jo)001:9236: gsungs pa'i chos 'dul ba la dad pas khyim nas
NK127(jo)001:9237: khyim med par rab tu byung ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:9238: de bas kyang gdams ngag dang bslab gzhi la nan tan gyis slob pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:9239: de bas kyang 'du 'dzi la mi dga' bar dben pa 'dod pas gom pa bdun 'dor ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:9240: de bas kyang chos thams cad stong par mos pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:9241: de bas kyang chos zab mo la rjes su mthun pa'i bzod pa thob pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:9242: de bas kyang rnam thar sgo gsum mngon du byas
NK127(jo)001:9243: nas rgyun du zhugs pa'i 'bras bu thob pa nas
NK127(jo)001:9244: dgra bcom pa'i bar du thob par byed pa shin
NK127(jo)001:9245: tu dka' ba byed pa dang ngo mtshar che ba
NK127(jo)001:9246: yin no // de ci'i phyir zhe na 'phags pa'i chos 'dul ba la dad pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:9247: dge slong gi dngos po thob pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:9248: 'bras bu thob pa de ni shin tu dka' ba'i phyir ro //
NK127(jo)001:9249: des na rab tu byung nas ni byang chub sems
NK127(jo)001:9250: dpa'i las spangs te byis pa'i las la gnas par
NK127(jo)001:9251: mi byed par / ser sna'i sems tshar bcad pa sogs byang chub sems dpa'i las nyi shu dang /
NK127(jo)001:9252: dam bca' bzhi dang ldan pas bslab pa'i gzhi las 'da' ba dug ltar spangs la /
NK127(jo)001:9253: byas pa mi gzo ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:9256: bslab pa las 'da' ba ste thams cad mkhyen pa
NK127(jo)001:9257: la bar du gcod pa'i chos bzhi po de dang
NK127(jo)001:9258: / rnyed bkur sdig grogs 'du 'dzi'i gnas spang bar bya zhing /
NK127(jo)001:9259: khyad par du zhe sdang gis rtsod pa dang bcas
NK127(jo)001:9260: pa'i gnas las dpag tshad brgyar 'byol bar bya ste
NK127(jo)001:9261: / zhe sdang gi sems bskyed par mi bya'o //
NK127(jo)001:9262: stong chen po'i 'jig rten khams kyi sems can thams cad la spyos brdegs mtshon gyis btab pa las /
NK127(jo)001:9263: byang chub sems dpa' gzhan la tha ba dang zhe
NK127(jo)001:9264: sdang gi sems gcig bskyed pa de ches nyes pa
NK127(jo)001:9265: che zhing des byang chub sems dpa' rmas pa dang
NK127(jo)001:9267: dper na lcags ni lcags las gzhan bong ba sogs
NK127(jo)001:9268: kyis mi chod pa ltar byang chub sems dpa'i dge
NK127(jo)001:9269: ba'i rtsa ba yang byang chub sems dpa' gcig shos
NK127(jo)001:9270: la zhe sdang bas zad par byed kyi gzhan gyis
NK127(jo)001:9272: gcig gis gcig la zhe sa dang gus pa dang
NK127(jo)001:9273: bcas par bya ste sems dang po bskyed pa'i byang
NK127(jo)001:9274: chub sems dpa' la yang ston pa'i 'du shes bskyed
NK127(jo)001:9275: par bya'o zhes gsungs pa na /
NK127(jo)001:9276: byang chub sems dpa' chen po byams pas 'di skad ces gsol to //
NK127(jo)001:9277: bcom ldan 'das bdag ni sems can thams cad la
NK127(jo)001:9278: yang zhe sa dang gus par bcas pas gnas par
NK127(jo)001:9279: bgyid na byang chub sems dpa' rnams la lta ci
NK127(jo)001:9280: smos te / de ci'i slad du zhe na /
NK127(jo)001:9281: bdag ni gnod sems la dga' bar mi bgyid kyi
NK127(jo)001:9282: bzod pa'i stobs dang mthu phun sum tshogs par bgyid
NK127(jo)001:9283: pa dang / g.yo la mi sten gyi lhag pa'i bsam pa phun sum tshogs par bgyid pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:9284: khyim la mi chags kyi bdag gir 'dzin pa dang yongs su 'dzin pa ma mchis pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:9285: zang zing lhur mi len gyi chos lhur len pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:9286: zas gos lhur mi len gyi pha'i nor yongs su tshol ba bgyid pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:9287: phrag dog dang ser sna'i kun dkris mi bgyid kyi
NK127(jo)001:9288: gzhan 'byor la dga' zhing gtong ba phun sum tshogs
NK127(jo)001:9290: dge sbyong gi ming lhur mi len gyi dge sbyong gi yon tan la slob pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:9291: smra ba lhur mi len gyi sgrub pa snying por bgyid pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:9292: rnyed bkur la lhag par mi chags kyi don dang
NK127(jo)001:9293: bya ba nyung ba dang sangs rgyas kyi yon tan
NK127(jo)001:9295: zang zing gis bgos pa'i sems kyis grong du mi
NK127(jo)001:9296: 'jug gi thams cad mkhyen pa'i sems yid la byed
NK127(jo)001:9298: chos gos dang bsod snyoms kyi phyir tshul 'chos mi
NK127(jo)001:9299: byed kyi tshul 'chos med par 'phags pa'i rigs bzhis
NK127(jo)001:9300: cho ga shes par byed pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:9301: byis pa'i spyod pa la mi slob kyi sangs rgyas kyi spyod pa la slob pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:9302: gzhan gyis bgyis ma bgyis la rtog par mi byed
NK127(jo)001:9303: par bdag dul ba dang zhi pa'i sbyor ba'i rjes
NK127(jo)001:9305: ltung ba gleng bar mi byed kyi ngag gi las kyi mtha' sdom pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:9306: bslab pa thag ring du mi bgyid kyi so sor thar pa la slob pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:9307: sangs rgyas dang chos dang dge 'dun gyi basngagasa pas
NK127(jo)001:9308: bdag 'tsho bar mi sems kyi mchog gsum gyi basngagasa
NK127(jo)001:9309: pa brjod pas de la dga' zhing sgrub la rten
NK127(jo)001:9311: gzhan gyis mthong ba bskyed pa'i slad du tshul 'chos
NK127(jo)001:9312: pas mchi ma 'byin par mi byed kyi chos kyi
NK127(jo)001:9313: shugs kyis mchi ma 'byin par bgyid pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:9314: bgyi ba sna tshogs kyi 'du 'dzis sbags te mi
NK127(jo)001:9315: gnas par chos yongs su tshol ba la brtson pa
NK127(jo)001:9316: dang / 'jig rten pa'i bgyi ba la mi dga'
NK127(jo)001:9317: bar 'jig rten las 'das pa'i chos yongs su tshol
NK127(jo)001:9319: srog 'jog gi zas dang ldan par mi byed kyi tshul 'chos med pa kun tu spyod pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:9320: gnas dang yul gcig yongs su 'dzin par mi bgyid kyi ri dwags ltar rgyu bar bgyid pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:9321: bsod snyoms la sbyor ba'i rjes su mi brtson gyi
NK127(jo)001:9322: sangs rgyas kyi yon tan tshol ba la brtson pa
NK127(jo)001:9323: dang / rmugs pa dang gnyid kyis mi nyal bar
NK127(jo)001:9324: nam gyi cha stod smad la mi nyal bar brtson
NK127(jo)001:9326: 'du 'dzis spyod pa la mi brtson gyi dben par dga' ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:9327: yon tan cung zad kyis cho ga shes par mi
NK127(jo)001:9328: byed kyi yon tan yongs su tshol bas mi ngoms
NK127(jo)001:9329: pa dang / khyi'i chos rnams kun tu spyod pa
NK127(jo)001:9330: ra mi bgyid kyi seng ge'i sgra sgrogs par bgyid
NK127(jo)001:9331: pa dang / pa dang / cung zad tsam gyi
NK127(jo)001:9332: bshes pa dang ldan pa de mi byed kyi mdza'
NK127(jo)001:9333: bshes shiin tu brtan par bgyid pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:9334: byas pa mi gzo bar mi bgyid kyi byas pa
NK127(jo)001:9335: shin tu gzo ba dang byas pa tshor bar bgyid
NK127(jo)001:9336: pa dang / sbyin pa'i lan gyis mdza' bshes su
NK127(jo)001:9337: mi bgyid kyi lhag pa'i bsam pas mdza' bshes su
NK127(jo)001:9338: pa dang / bgyid pa dang / lhag pa'i bsam
NK127(jo)001:9339: pa bcos mar mi bgyid kyi lhag bsam brtan par
NK127(jo)001:9340: pa dang / bgyid pa dang / bgyid pa dang
NK127(jo)001:9341: / dman pa la mos par mi bgyid kyi sangs
NK127(jo)001:9342: rgyas kyi sku yongs su bsgrub pa rgya chen po
NK127(jo)001:9344: de bzhin gshegs pa dang bslab pa la gus pa
NK127(jo)001:9345: med par mi bgyid kyi de bzhin gshegs pa dang
NK127(jo)001:9346: bslab pa la gus pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:9347: sems dang smra ba gzhan du gyur pa'i lce gnyis
NK127(jo)001:9348: su mi bgyid kyi ji skad smras pa de bzhin
NK127(jo)001:9350: tshul 'chos pa'i byang chub sems dpar mi bgyid kyi
NK127(jo)001:9351: lhag pa'i bsam pa phun tshogs dang dul zhing zhi
NK127(jo)001:9352: bar sbyor ba'i rjes su brtson par bgyid pa dang
NK127(jo)001:9353: / nga rgyal gyi nga rgyal bskyed par mi bgyid
NK127(jo)001:9354: kyi gdol pa'i bu dang 'dra bar nga rgyal nges
NK127(jo)001:9356: chags pa dang bcas pas bsod snyoms longs spyad par
NK127(jo)001:9357: mi bgyid kyi tshul khrims yongs su dag pas dad
NK127(jo)001:9358: pas byin pa la lci ba'i 'du shes su bgyid
NK127(jo)001:9359: pa dang / tshul bzhin min pa'i yid byed sngon
NK127(jo)001:9360: du btang nas gdugs pas mtha' kho nar nyal ba
NK127(jo)001:9361: dang rmugs gnyid kyis non par mi bgyid kyi sangs
NK127(jo)001:9362: rgyas kyi chos yongs su bsgrub pa'i slad du brtson
NK127(jo)001:9363: zhing sbyor bar bgyid pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:9364: gang zag tu lta ba la mi brten gyi stong pa nyid la gnas par bgyid pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:9365: rnam par rtog pa dang 'khrul pa smra bar mi
NK127(jo)001:9366: bgyid kyi mtshan ma med pa la gnas par bgyid
NK127(jo)001:9367: pa dang / lus kyi tshul 'chos par mi bgyid
NK127(jo)001:9368: kyi lus ngag yid kyi las kyi mtha' yongs su
NK127(jo)001:9370: zang zing gis bgos pa'i sems kyi rgyud kyis chos
NK127(jo)001:9371: ston par mi bgyid kyi zang zing med pa'i sems
NK127(jo)001:9372: kyis chos ston par bgyid pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:9373: zang zing gis mdza' ba shes su mi bgyid kyi
NK127(jo)001:9374: chos kyi sbyin pas mdza' bshes su bgyid pa dang
NK127(jo)001:9375: / bdag dang gzhan la yongs su gdung ba mi
NK127(jo)001:9376: bgyid kyi bdag dang gzhan la sman pa'i slad du
NK127(jo)001:9378: dgon par gnas pa dang bsod snyoms dang phyag dar
NK127(jo)001:9379: khrod la tshul 'chos par mi bgyid kyi sbyangs pa'i
NK127(jo)001:9380: yon tan bcu gnyis yang dag par blangs te gnas
NK127(jo)001:9381: par bgyid cing de yang rnyed bkur dang tshigs su
NK127(jo)001:9382: bcad pa thams cad la rten pa ma mchis pa'i
NK127(jo)001:9383: slad du'o // de skad ces gsol ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:9384: bcom ldan 'das kyis byang chub sems dpa' chen po
NK127(jo)001:9385: byams pa legs so legs so khyod ji ltar sangs
NK127(jo)001:9386: rgyas kyi yon tan longs su tshol ba la brtson
NK127(jo)001:9387: pa de ltar seng ge'i sgra 'di sgrogs par byed
NK127(jo)001:9388: pa ni khyod sngon gyi rgyal ba la lhag par
NK127(jo)001:9389: bya ba byas shing dge ba'i rtsa ba bskyed pa
NK127(jo)001:9390: dang / chos de dag dang yon tan de dag
NK127(jo)001:9391: la gzhan gyi dring mi 'jog pa yin te legs
NK127(jo)001:9392: so legs so zhes gsungs so //
NK127(jo)001:9393: rgyal tshab chen po'i seng ge'i sgra 'di ni lnga
NK127(jo)001:9394: brgya tha ma'i sems can rnams kyi don du snying
NK127(jo)001:9395: rjes bsgrags pa ste snyigs pa'i dus kyi byang chub
NK127(jo)001:9396: sems dpa' las dang po pa rab tu byung ba
NK127(jo)001:9397: chos smra ba rnams kyis bsam par bya ba gal
NK127(jo)001:9398: po che yin pas 'dir yang rgyas par bris pa'o
NK127(jo)001:9399: // byams pa'i seng ge'i sgra bsgrags pa 'di bshad
NK127(jo)001:9400: pa na 'khor de nas dge slong lnga brgya stan
NK127(jo)001:9401: las langs te song ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:9402: gnas brtan 'od srung chen pos de dag la khyed
NK127(jo)001:9403: cag yo byad bsnyung ba'i gtam brjod pa'i tshe stan
NK127(jo)001:9406: byang chub sems dpa' chen po byams pa'i yo byad
NK127(jo)001:9407: bsnyung ba'i gtam de lta bu srid par dka' ba
NK127(jo)001:9408: lags pas / bdag cag 'di snyam du bdag cag
NK127(jo)001:9409: ni yo byad bsnyung ba'i yon tan de dag mi
NK127(jo)001:9410: snang bas bdag cag khyim du 'dong gor ma chag
NK127(jo)001:9411: ste ci'i phyir na dad pas byin pa reg par
NK127(jo)001:9412: dka' zhing sbyang bar dka' ba'i phyir ro snyam du
NK127(jo)001:9414: de nas 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pas dge slong
NK127(jo)001:9415: de dag la legs so zhes bya ba byin te
NK127(jo)001:9416: / rigs kyi bu dag legs so gang dag dad
NK127(jo)001:9417: pas byin pa la longs spyod par mi spro ba
NK127(jo)001:9418: dag gis de ltar 'dzem pa dang 'gyod pa dang
NK127(jo)001:9420: nyin gcig la lan brgyar rab tu byung ba'i phyir spang ba ni bla'i /
NK127(jo)001:9421: tshul khrims yongs su ma dag pas dad pas byin pa longs spyod pa de lta ma yin no //
NK127(jo)001:9422: de nas bcom ldan 'das la 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pas gsol pa /
NK127(jo)001:9423: bcom ldan 'das ji ltar dad pas stsal ba rjes su gnang bar mdzad lags /
NK127(jo)001:9425: 'jam dpal ngas ni rig pa dang grol ba la dad pas byin pa rjes su gnang ngo //
NK127(jo)001:9426: de nas 'jam dpal gyis dge slong lnga brgya po de la smras pa /
NK127(jo)001:9427: tshe dang ldan pa dag khyed cag sbyor cig /
NK127(jo)001:9429: sangs rgyas 'byung ba rnyed dka' bas rab tu byung ba las phyir ma ldog cig /
NK127(jo)001:9431: 'jam dpal bdag cag gis ji ltar sbyar bar bgyi lags /
NK127(jo)001:9433: dge slong dag khyed kyis ji lta ji ltar sbyor
NK127(jo)001:9434: ba dang 'bad pa dang rtsol bar byed pa na
NK127(jo)001:9435: / chos 'ga' yang sbyor bar mi byed /
NK127(jo)001:9437: de bzhin du chos 'ga' yang skyed pa dang 'gog
NK127(jo)001:9438: pa dang thob pa dang spong ba dang 'bri ba
NK127(jo)001:9439: dang 'phel bar mi byed pa de ltar sbyor bar
NK127(jo)001:9440: gyis shig / dge slong dag de ltar sbyong ba
NK127(jo)001:9441: de ni chos 'ga' yang rtogs par mi 'gyur ro
NK127(jo)001:9442: gyis shig / // chos 'ga' yang rtogs par mi
NK127(jo)001:9443: 'gyur ba de ni gar yang mi 'gro gang nas
NK127(jo)001:9445: gang la 'gro 'ong med pa de ni dge slong
NK127(jo)001:9446: zhes bya ste gang du rten pa'ang ma yin mi
NK127(jo)001:9447: rten pa'ang ma yin no zhes bshad pas dge slong
NK127(jo)001:9448: lnga brgya bo de dag len pa med par zag
NK127(jo)001:9449: pa rnams las sems rnam par grol lo //
NK127(jo)001:9451: dkon mchog brtsegs pa'i chos kyi rnam grangs byams pas zhus pa lung bstan pa las /
NK127(jo)001:9452: byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po byams pas /
NK127(jo)001:9453: bcom ldan 'das la byang chub sems dpa'i spyod pa
NK127(jo)001:9454: zhus pa'i don bka' stsal pa la mchog tu dga'
NK127(jo)001:9455: ba'i yid kyis bcom ldan 'das la tshul dang mthun
NK127(jo)001:9456: pa'i tshigs su bcad pas mngon par bstod pa na
NK127(jo)001:9457: / kun dga' bos byang chub sems dpa' byams pa'i
NK127(jo)001:9458: spobs pa dang chos ston pa la basngagasa pa dang
NK127(jo)001:9459: / / bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
NK127(jo)001:9460: de de bzhin no byang chub sems dpa' byams pa
NK127(jo)001:9461: ni spobs pa phun sum tshogs shing shin tu rnam
NK127(jo)001:9462: par nges pa'i tshig gis chos ston pa sogs ngo
NK127(jo)001:9463: mtshar ro // 'dis da ltar nga la tshul dang
NK127(jo)001:9464: 'dra ba'i tshigs su bcad pas bstod par ma zad
NK127(jo)001:9465: mtshar ro // de / sngon 'das pa'i dus bskal
NK127(jo)001:9466: pa grangs med pa bcur tshangs pa de'i tshe na
NK127(jo)001:9467: de bzhin gshegs pa snang bas rnam par rol ba
NK127(jo)001:9468: mngon par shes pa zhes bya ba 'jig rten du
NK127(jo)001:9469: mtshar ro // de / byung ba'i tshe / byang
NK127(jo)001:9470: chub sems dpa' byams pa 'di bram ze'i khye'u bzang
NK127(jo)001:9471: dag ces bya bar gyur te des de bzhin gshegs
NK127(jo)001:9472: pa'i sku mthong bas dad pa skyes nas bdag kyang
NK127(jo)001:9473: ma 'ongs pa ni 'di lta bu'i lus su gyur
NK127(jo)001:9474: mtshar ro // de / byung ba'i tshe / cig
NK127(jo)001:9475: snyam zhing / gal te de ltar 'gyur na de
NK127(jo)001:9476: bzhin gshegs pa'i zhabs bdag gis lus la reg par
NK127(jo)001:9477: gyur cig ces snyam pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:9478: de bzhin gshegs pa des bram ze'i khye'u de'i bsam
NK127(jo)001:9479: pa mkhyen nas der gshegs te zhabs kyis reg par
NK127(jo)001:9480: mdzad pa dang de ma thag tu de mi skye
NK127(jo)001:9481: ba'i chos la bzod pa thob par gyur to //
NK127(jo)001:9482: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa des snam logs su gzigs nas dge slong rnams la bka' stsal pa /
NK127(jo)001:9483: khyed rnams kyis khye'u 'di'i lus la rkang pas ma bardzi zhig /
NK127(jo)001:9484: de ci'i phyir na 'di mi skye ba'i chos la bzod pa thob pa'i phyir ro //
NK127(jo)001:9485: zhes gsungs shing de'i tshe bram ze'i khye'u bzang dag
NK127(jo)001:9486: des rdzu 'phrul dang mngon par shes pa yang bsgrubs
NK127(jo)001:9487: nas de bzhin gshegs pa la tshul dang 'dra ba'i
NK127(jo)001:9488: tshigs su bcad pas bstod pa byas so //
NK127(jo)001:9489: de tshun chad khye'u bzang dag de'i rdzu 'phrul lam
NK127(jo)001:9490: mngon shes rnams yongs su nyams par ma gyur to
NK127(jo)001:9493: bcom ldan 'das byang chub sems dpa' chen po byams
NK127(jo)001:9494: pa 'di yun ring po de srid nas mi skye
NK127(jo)001:9495: ba'i chos la bzod pa thob lags na ci'i slad
NK127(jo)001:9496: du bla med byang chub tu sangs ma rgyas /
NK127(jo)001:9498: kun dga' bo byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyi bkod
NK127(jo)001:9499: pa dang yongs su bzung ba ni gnyis po 'di
NK127(jo)001:9500: dag ste / gang zhe na sems can bkod pa dang sems can yongs su bzung ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:9501: zhing bkod pa dang zhing yongs su bzung ba gnyis so //
NK127(jo)001:9502: de la byang chub sems dpa' chen po byams pas
NK127(jo)001:9503: ni byang chub kyi spyad pa spyod pa'i tshe zhing
NK127(jo)001:9504: bkod pa rnam par sbyangs shing yongs su bzung ngo
NK127(jo)001:9505: // kun dga' bos ngas ni sems can bkod pa sbyangs shing yongs su bzung la /
NK127(jo)001:9506: zhing bkod pa yang sbyangs shing yongs su bzung bas bzung ngo //
NK127(jo)001:9507: kun dga' bo ngas mngon par shes te /
NK127(jo)001:9508: byang chub sems dpa' byams pa yang dag par zhugs
NK127(jo)001:9509: nas bskal pa bzhi bcu gnyis lon pa'i 'og tu
NK127(jo)001:9510: ngas gdod bla med rdzogs pa'i byang chub tu sems
NK127(jo)001:9511: bskyed de bskal pa bzang po 'di 'das nas bskal
NK127(jo)001:9512: pa dgu bcu rtsa bzhin 'tshang rgya bar rigs pa
NK127(jo)001:9513: la / ngas brtson 'grus rlabs po che 'bar bar byas pas myur du sangs rgyas te /
NK127(jo)001:9514: bdog pa phangs pa dang longs spyod dang rgyal srid
NK127(jo)001:9515: dang bu dang chung ma dang mgo dang mig dang
NK127(jo)001:9516: khrag dang rus rkang dang yan lag phangs pa thams
NK127(jo)001:9517: cad yongs su btang ba'i chos bcu po de dang
NK127(jo)001:9518: / gzhan yang tshul khrims dang bzod pa sogs chos
NK127(jo)001:9519: bcu la gnas nas myur du bla med byang chub
NK127(jo)001:9521: sngon rgyal bu nor thams cad sbyin pa zhes bya
NK127(jo)001:9522: bar gyur pa na nad pa la rang gi lus
NK127(jo)001:9523: kyi khrag thams cad byin te nad las gsos pa
NK127(jo)001:9524: sogs / rgya mtsho bzhi'i chu'i phung po tshad gzung
NK127(jo)001:9525: du yod kyi ngas sngon byang chub kyi phyir khrag
NK127(jo)001:9526: byin pa la ni tshad med do //
NK127(jo)001:9527: rgyal bu gzhon nu me tog ces bya bar gyur
NK127(jo)001:9528: pa na nad kyis nyen pa la rang gi lus
NK127(jo)001:9529: brdungs zhing rkang brus te de'i lus la bskus pas
NK127(jo)001:9530: nad zhi bar byas pa sogs bla med byang chub
NK127(jo)001:9531: kyi phyir rkang byin pa rgya mtsho bzhi'i chu'i phung
NK127(jo)001:9532: po las lhag cing tshad med pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:9533: rgyal po zla 'od ces bya bar gyur pa na
NK127(jo)001:9534: long ba la mig byin pa sogs bla med byang
NK127(jo)001:9535: chub kyi phyir ri'i rgyal po ri rab kyi rdul
NK127(jo)001:9536: gyi grangs las kyang mang ba'i mig gi sbyin pa
NK127(jo)001:9538: byang chub sems dpa' byams pas ni sngon byang chub
NK127(jo)001:9539: sems dpa'i spyad pa spyod pa na theg pa bde
NK127(jo)001:9540: ba 'jug pa bde ba lam bde bas bla med
NK127(jo)001:9541: rdzogs pa'i byang chub yang dag par bsgrubs so //
NK127(jo)001:9542: byams pa sngon byang chub sems dpa'i spyad pa spyod
NK127(jo)001:9543: pa'i tshe lus dang yan lag bu dang chung ma
NK127(jo)001:9544: grogs dang pho brang 'khor yangs pa yongs su btang
NK127(jo)001:9546: thabs mkhas pas yongs su zin pas theg pa bde
NK127(jo)001:9547: pa 'jug pa bde ba lam bde bas bla med
NK127(jo)001:9548: byang chub bsgrubs te sangs rgyas so //
NK127(jo)001:9549: zhes gsungs pa dang kun dga' bos gsol pa /
NK127(jo)001:9550: bcom ldan 'das byang chub sems dpa' byams pas bla
NK127(jo)001:9551: med byang chub bde bar sgrub pa'i thabs mkhas de
NK127(jo)001:9553: byams pas sngon spyad pa spyod pa'i tshe nyin mtshan
NK127(jo)001:9554: lan gsum du gus pa dang bcas pas sangs rgyas
NK127(jo)001:9555: thams cad mngon sum byas te smon lam btab pa'i
NK127(jo)001:9556: tshul gsungs so // byang chub sems dpa' byams pa
NK127(jo)001:9557: sngon byang chub sems dpa'i spyad pa spyod pa'i tshe
NK127(jo)001:9558: sems can rnams dug gsum chung ba dang dge ba
NK127(jo)001:9559: bcu'i las lam dang ldan par gyur la /
NK127(jo)001:9560: phyis bdag nyid sangs rgyas pa de ltar rnam par
NK127(jo)001:9561: sbyang bas dus dang tshod de lta bu byung nas
NK127(jo)001:9562: sems can dag dug gsum chung zhing dge bcu'i las
NK127(jo)001:9563: lam dang ldan pa'i dus na byang chub sems dpa'
NK127(jo)001:9564: chen po byams pa smon lam gyi dbang gis bla
NK127(jo)001:9565: med rdzogs pa'i byang chub tu mngon par rdzogs par
NK127(jo)001:9567: kun dga' bo ngas ni sngon byang chub sems dpa'i
NK127(jo)001:9568: spyad pa spyod pa na snyigs ma lnga dang ldan
NK127(jo)001:9569: pa'i 'jig rten du sems can dug gsum shas che
NK127(jo)001:9570: zhing bdo ba / chos min la chags pa /
NK127(jo)001:9571: chags pa yang bas zil gyis non pa /
NK127(jo)001:9572: chos log pas yongs su zin pa /
NK127(jo)001:9573: pha ma dang spun dang ming sring dang khyo shug dang nye du la 'khu ba /
NK127(jo)001:9574: mkhan slob dang 'phags pa dang bdag dang gzhan la 'khu ba /
NK127(jo)001:9575: mi dri ma can dmu rgod cang shes ma yin
NK127(jo)001:9576: pa rnams kyi nang du bdag bla med byang chub
NK127(jo)001:9577: tu sangs rgyas na ci ma rung zhes de ltar
NK127(jo)001:9578: smon lam yongs su sbyangs shing /
NK127(jo)001:9579: dus yang pa 'di lta bu la gnas nas ngas
NK127(jo)001:9580: snying rje chen po mdun du byas te snying rje
NK127(jo)001:9581: chen po dang ldan pas nga da ltar grong dang
NK127(jo)001:9582: grong khyer yul 'khor dang rgyal po'i pho brang du
NK127(jo)001:9583: 'khor rnams su zhugs te chos ston pa na /
NK127(jo)001:9584: nga la kha ngan zer zhing gshe rgya ste tshogs
NK127(jo)001:9585: par mi dbyung pa rtsub pa barlanga pos smra bar
NK127(jo)001:9586: byed do // kun dga' bo nga la chad par smra ba yin no zhes kyang zer ro //
NK127(jo)001:9587: rtag par smra ba yin no zhes kyang zer ro //
NK127(jo)001:9588: 'khor 'dod pa mang ngo zhes kyang gleng ngo //
NK127(jo)001:9589: 'dod pa che'o zhes kyang gleng ngo //
NK127(jo)001:9590: khyim gyi nang du zhugs na nga la sus kyang 'thor ro //
NK127(jo)001:9591: dug dang bsres pa'i zas kyang sbyin no //
NK127(jo)001:9592: me'i phung po yang nye bar bsgrubs so //
NK127(jo)001:9593: 'di ltar te sangs rgyas su gyur kyang mdzes ldan
NK127(jo)001:9594: ma dang zhes bya ba lta bur 'khrig pa'i chos
NK127(jo)001:9595: dang ldan pas skur pa yang btab bo //
NK127(jo)001:9596: kun dga' bo nga ni snying rje chen po mdun
NK127(jo)001:9597: du byas te snying rje chen po dang ldan pas
NK127(jo)001:9598: da ltar sems can de lta bu dag la chos
NK127(jo)001:9599: ston to zhes bka' stsal pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:9601: bcom ldan 'das sems can de lta bu dag la
NK127(jo)001:9602: chos ston par mdzad pa ni de bzhin gshegs pa
NK127(jo)001:9603: ma dul ba 'dul ba khur chen po bsnams pa
NK127(jo)001:9604: dka' ba mdzad pa lags so zhes zhus pa dang
NK127(jo)001:9606: de de bzhin te de ltar dka' ba mdzad pa
NK127(jo)001:9607: ni 'di ltar snying rje chen pos yongs su zin
NK127(jo)001:9608: pa'i phyir ro // zhes gsungs so //
NK127(jo)001:9609: sangs rgyas phal po che las /
NK127(jo)001:9610: tshong dpon gyi bu nor bu bzang po la khye'u
NK127(jo)001:9611: dpal 'byung dang bu mo dpal gyi blo gros mas
NK127(jo)001:9612: smras pa / rigs kyi bu lto phyogs kyi rgyud
NK127(jo)001:9613: 'di nyid kyi phyogs kyi sgo'i gnas rgya mtsho'i 'gram
NK127(jo)001:9614: zhes bya bar bza' shing gi ra ba rgyal mtshan
NK127(jo)001:9615: chen po zhes bya ba'i nang na /
NK127(jo)001:9616: khang pa brtsegs pa chen po rnam par snang mdzad
NK127(jo)001:9617: kyi brgyan gyis brgyan pa'i snying po zhes bya ba
NK127(jo)001:9618: byang chub sems dpa'i dge rtsa rnam par smin pa
NK127(jo)001:9619: las grub pa de na byang chub sems dpa' byams
NK127(jo)001:9620: pa zhes bya ba skye ba'i sa la gnas pa'i
NK127(jo)001:9621: mi rnams rjes su bzung zhing byang chub sems dpa'
NK127(jo)001:9622: rnams smin par bya ba'i don du 'dug gi de'i
NK127(jo)001:9623: gan du song la byang chub sems dpa'i spyod pa
NK127(jo)001:9624: thams cad dris shig de ci'i phyir na /
NK127(jo)001:9625: byams pa de ni byang chub sems dpa'i spyod pa thams cad la zhugs pa /
NK127(jo)001:9626: sems can thams cad kyi sems rtogs par khong du chud cing spyod pa'i rjes su zhugs pa /
NK127(jo)001:9627: sems can thams cad yongs su smin par byed cing phar phyin rdzogs par byas pa /
NK127(jo)001:9628: byang chub sems dpa'i sa thams cad la rab tu gnas pa sogs yon tan thams cad thob pa /
NK127(jo)001:9629: dge ba'i bshes gnyen des khyod kyi dge ba'i rtsa
NK127(jo)001:9630: ba dang byang chub kyi sems dang byang chub sems
NK127(jo)001:9631: dpa'i dbang po la sogs pa'i yon tan thams cad
NK127(jo)001:9632: 'phel bar byed cing kun tu bzang po'i spyod pa
NK127(jo)001:9634: khyod skyod pa dang smon lam yon tan sogs kyis ngoms par ma byed par /
NK127(jo)001:9635: sems can gyi khams kyi mtha' bzhin du byang chub
NK127(jo)001:9636: sems dpa'i spyod pa tshad med pa rdzogs par bya
NK127(jo)001:9637: dgos pas / de'i phyir dge ba'i bshes gnyen btsal pas yongs su mi spyo bar bya dgos te /
NK127(jo)001:9638: byang chub sems dpa'i spyod pa thams cad ni dge ba'i bshes gnyen la rag las pa /
NK127(jo)001:9640: des bskyed pa la sogs pa yin pa'i yon tan basngagasa pa mang po brjod nas /
NK127(jo)001:9641: des na yid la bya ba rgyun ma chad pas dge ba'i bshes gnyen bsnyen par bya ba'i phyir /
NK127(jo)001:9642: khur thams cad bkur bas mi skyo bas lta bu'i
NK127(jo)001:9643: sems la sogs pas dge ba'i bshes gnyen bsten pa'i
NK127(jo)001:9644: tshul rgya cher bstan pa bzhin du /
NK127(jo)001:9645: byang chub sems dpa' nor bzangs kyis dge ba'i bshes
NK127(jo)001:9646: gnyen la mchog tu dang ba'i rnam par thar pa
NK127(jo)001:9647: phul du byang ba la gnas nas ye shes kyi
NK127(jo)001:9648: spyod yul tshad med pa la zhugs pa'i ye shes
NK127(jo)001:9650: khang brtsegs rnam par snang mdzad kyi rgyan gyi snying
NK127(jo)001:9651: po'i sgo nas lus thams cad kyis phab ste phyag
NK127(jo)001:9652: byas so // de'i lhag bsam dang smon lam gyi
NK127(jo)001:9653: mthus de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi drung dang
NK127(jo)001:9654: byang chub sems dpa' thams cad dang dge ba'i bshes
NK127(jo)001:9655: gnyen gyi gnas thams cad dang mchod rten dang 'phags
NK127(jo)001:9656: pa'i tshogs dang bla ma dang pha ma'i bar gyi
NK127(jo)001:9657: drung du bdag nyid snang zhing /
NK127(jo)001:9658: de'i tshul gyis chos kyi dbyings thams cad rgyas par
NK127(jo)001:9659: 'gengs pas 'dud cing phyag bya ba dang de yang
NK127(jo)001:9660: phyi ma'i matha'i mur thug par rgyun mi 'chad par
NK127(jo)001:9661: byin gyis brlabs cing mnyam pa nyid kyi rjes su
NK127(jo)001:9662: song ba'i byang chub sems dpa'i zab mo'i gnas pa
NK127(jo)001:9663: sna tshogs kyis gnas shing 'di skad du /
NK127(jo)001:9664: 'di la thugs rje chen po brnyes pas rnam dag pa //
NK127(jo)001:9665: byams pa bshes gnyen dpal chen 'jig rten phan brtson pa //
NK127(jo)001:9666: dbang bskur sar gnas rgyal ba'i sras kyi thu bo ste //
NK127(jo)001:9667: sangs rgyas yul la rjes su dgongs shing rnam par spyod //
NK127(jo)001:9668: rgyal ba'i sras po grags pa chen po mnga' ba rnams //
NK127(jo)001:9669: ye shes chen po'i spyod yul rnam thar bzhugs pa dang //
NK127(jo)001:9670: gang rnams chos dbyings kun tu thogs med rnam rgyu ba //
NK127(jo)001:9671: dpe zla med pa de dag gnas ni 'di 'dra yin //
NK127(jo)001:9672: ces pa la sogs pa'i tshigs su bcad pa brjod
NK127(jo)001:9673: nas byams pa mthong bar dga' zhing sdod sdod pa
NK127(jo)001:9674: las / byang chub sems dpa' byams pa khang brtsegs
NK127(jo)001:9675: de'i phyi rol gyi phyogs gzhan nas srog chags brgya
NK127(jo)001:9676: stong du ma'i 'khor dang brgya byin dang tshangs pa
NK127(jo)001:9677: 'jig rten mgon po sogs lha klu gnod sbyin la
NK127(jo)001:9678: sogs pa'i dbang po du mas mchod cing /
NK127(jo)001:9679: bram ze brgya stong mang pos bskor te khang brtsegs
