NK127(jo)001:9680: de'i logs su 'ongs pa mthong nas mchog tu dga'
NK127(jo)001:9681: zhing yid bde ba skyes pas byang chub sems dpa'
NK127(jo)001:9682: byams pa gang na 'dir mngon du bltas nas thag
NK127(jo)001:9683: ring po nas lus kun gyi phab ste phyag byas
NK127(jo)001:9684: so // de nas byang chub sems dpa' byams pas
NK127(jo)001:9685: nor bzang la bltas te 'khor kun la lag pa
NK127(jo)001:9686: g.yas pas bstan nas 'di skad ces /
NK127(jo)001:9687: ltos shig bsam pa yongs su dag pa 'di //
NK127(jo)001:9688: nor bzang nor rnams rab tu brtan pa'i bu //
NK127(jo)001:9689: byang chub spyod pa dam pa yongs tshol zhing //
NK127(jo)001:9690: mkhas pa nga yi drung du nye bar 'ong //
NK127(jo)001:9691: zhes pa la sogs pa yon tan gyi basngagasa pa'i tshigs su bcad pa smras so //
NK127(jo)001:9692: de nas nor bzang byams pa'i mdun du 'dug ste
NK127(jo)001:9693: 'phags pa bdag ni bla med byang chub tu zhugs
NK127(jo)001:9694: na / byang chub sems dpa'i ji ltar bslab pa
NK127(jo)001:9695: dang nan tan du bgyi ba zhu ba'i don du
NK127(jo)001:9696: na / / 'phags pa byams pa ni sku tshe
NK127(jo)001:9697: gcig gis thogs par bla med byang chub tu 'tshang
NK127(jo)001:9698: rgya ba de ni byang chub sems dpa'i rnam par
NK127(jo)001:9699: 'god pa thams cad las yang dag par 'das pa
NK127(jo)001:9700: na / / / byang chub sems dpa' skyon med par rab tu zhugs pa /
NK127(jo)001:9701: phar phyin thams cad dang bzod pa'i sgo dang byang
NK127(jo)001:9702: chub sems dpa'i sa thams cad dang rnam par thar
NK127(jo)001:9703: pa'i sgo thams cad dang ting nge 'dzin gzungs dang
NK127(jo)001:9704: spobs pa mngon shes la sogs pa'i yon tan thams
NK127(jo)001:9706: sangs rgyas kyi chos kyi mdzod dang gsang ba'i mdzod 'dzin pa /
NK127(jo)001:9707: sems can nyon mongs pa'i nad kyis thebs pa thams cad kyi sman par gyur pa /
NK127(jo)001:9708: sems can thams cad kyi phul du phyin pa /
NK127(jo)001:9709: 'jig rten dbang po thams cad kyi dbang po /
NK127(jo)001:9710: 'phags pa'i gang zag thams cad kyi thu bo /
NK127(jo)001:9711: nyan rang thams cad kyi gtso bo /
NK127(jo)001:9712: 'khor ba'i rgya mtshor rgyu ba thams cad kyi mnyan pa /
NK127(jo)001:9713: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi 'khor gyi dkyil 'khor dang 'gro ba'i gnas thams cad du snang ba /
NK127(jo)001:9714: 'jig rten gyi chos thams cad kyis ma gos pa /
NK127(jo)001:9715: bdud kyi yul thams cad las 'das pa /
NK127(jo)001:9716: sangs rgyas kyi yul thams cad kyi rjes su song ba /
NK127(jo)001:9717: byang chub sems dpa'i yul thams cad la sgrib pa med pa brnyes pa /
NK127(jo)001:9718: chos kyi rgyal srid chen po la gnas shing thams
NK127(jo)001:9719: cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyi yul la dbang bskur
NK127(jo)001:9721: thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes la dbang sgyur ba'i thams thob pa lags na /
NK127(jo)001:9722: 'phags pa ji ltar byang chub sems dpa'i spyod pa
NK127(jo)001:9723: la bslab par bgyi ba dang nan tan bgyis na
NK127(jo)001:9724: sangs rgyas kyi chos thams cad 'thob par 'gyur zhing
NK127(jo)001:9725: sems can thams cad kyi bsam pa rdzogs pa dang
NK127(jo)001:9726: dkon mchog gsum gyi rigs rgyun mi gcod par 'gyur
NK127(jo)001:9727: ba bka' stsal du gsol zhes zhus pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:9728: byang chub sems dpa' byams pas 'khor gyi dkyil 'khor
NK127(jo)001:9729: thams cad la bltas te tshong dpon gyi bu nor
NK127(jo)001:9731: tshong dpon gyi bu nor bzang 'di byang chub sems
NK127(jo)001:9732: dpa'i spyod pa bsgrub pa'i phyir lhag bsam dang brtson
NK127(jo)001:9733: 'grus mi ldog pas dge ba'i bshes gnyen tshol zhing
NK127(jo)001:9734: bsnyen bkur ba la mi skyo bar /
NK127(jo)001:9735: 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pas btang na grong khyer dpal gyi 'byung gnas nas nye bar bzung ste /
NK127(jo)001:9736: lho phyogs kyi rgyud thams cad du brgyus shing dge
NK127(jo)001:9737: ba'i bshes gnyen brgya rtsa bcu la yongs su dri
NK127(jo)001:9738: ba byas nas tha ma nga'i drung 'di'i bar du
NK127(jo)001:9739: skyo ba med par lhag pa'i bsam pas phyin te
NK127(jo)001:9740: / 'di ltar theg pa chen po la zhugs pa'i
NK127(jo)001:9741: yi dam chen pos 'gro ba thams cad yongs su
NK127(jo)001:9742: bskyab pa'i don du byung ba'o zhes basngagasa pa rgya
NK127(jo)001:9744: rigs kyi bu byang chub kyi sems ni sangs rgyas kyi chos thams cad kyi sa bon lta bu'o //
NK127(jo)001:9745: zhes sogs dpe'i sgo nas byang chub sems kyi yon
NK127(jo)001:9746: tan basngagasa pa yang dag pa rgya cher bstan te
NK127(jo)001:9747: / rigs kyi bu khyod byang chub sems dpas ji
NK127(jo)001:9748: ltar bslab par bya ba dris pa ni khang pa
NK127(jo)001:9749: brtsegs pa chen po rnam par snang mdzad kyi rgyan
NK127(jo)001:9750: gyis brgyan pa'i snying po 'di nyid kyi nang du
NK127(jo)001:9751: song ste ltos shig dang der shes par 'gyur ro
NK127(jo)001:9752: / zhes gsungs nas / khang brtsegs de'i sgor se
NK127(jo)001:9753: gol gyi sgra mdzad pas sgo rang phye ba'i nang
NK127(jo)001:9755: de nor bzang gis nam mkha'i khams ltar yangs pa'i
NK127(jo)001:9756: khang pa bzang po rgyan gyi bkod pa tshad med
NK127(jo)001:9757: pas brgyan pa / de'i nang na yang khang brtsegs
NK127(jo)001:9758: gzhan brgya stong mang po snga ma ltar snang ba
NK127(jo)001:9759: pas brgyan pa / / de dag phan tshun ma
NK127(jo)001:9760: 'dres pa gcig la ji lta bar thams cad la'ang
NK127(jo)001:9761: gzugs brnyan gyi tshul du snang ba'i bkod pa chen
NK127(jo)001:9762: po mthong nas dga' ba'i shugs rnam par 'phel bas
NK127(jo)001:9764: byams pa'i mthus khang brtsegs de thams cad kyi nang du bdag nyid phyin phyin par shes shing /
NK127(jo)001:9765: khang brtsegs de dag kyang rnam 'phrul bsam gyis mi
NK127(jo)001:9766: khyab pa'i yul can rnam pa sna tshogs mang por
NK127(jo)001:9768: khang pa brtsegs pa la lar ni byang chub sems
NK127(jo)001:9769: dpa' byams pas thog mar rigs gang du skye ba
NK127(jo)001:9770: zhes pa dang ming dang rigs pa la sogs pa
NK127(jo)001:9771: dang / dge ba'i rtsa ba ji ltar bsags pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:9772: de bzhin gshegs pa gang las byang chub tu sems
NK127(jo)001:9773: bskyed pa sogs kyi tshul ma lus pa thams cad
NK127(jo)001:9774: mthong nas shes shing khong du chud la /
NK127(jo)001:9775: de'i tshe sems can de dag dang de bzhin gshegs
NK127(jo)001:9776: pa'i sku tshe'i tshad ji srid pa de tsam du
NK127(jo)001:9777: sangs rgyas de'i drung du bdag nyid 'dug par shes
NK127(jo)001:9778: shing bya ba de dag mthong bar gyur to //
NK127(jo)001:9779: de bzhin du khang brtsegs la lar byams pas thog
NK127(jo)001:9780: mar byams pa'i ting nge 'dzin thob pa gang nas
NK127(jo)001:9781: byams pa zhes bya ba'i ming thob pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:9782: de bzhin du khang brtsegs la lar gang du spyad pa spyod pa /
NK127(jo)001:9783: la lar phar phyin rdzogs pa /
NK127(jo)001:9784: la lar bzod pa la zhugs pa /
NK127(jo)001:9786: la lar sangs rgyas kyi zhing gi rgyan bzung ba /
NK127(jo)001:9787: la lar sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa bzung ba /
NK127(jo)001:9788: la lar mi skye ba'i chos la bzod pa thob pa /
NK127(jo)001:9789: la lar rdzogs byang du lung bstan pa la sogs pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:9790: la lar byang chub sems dpa' byams pa 'khor los
NK127(jo)001:9791: sgyur ba'i rgyal por gyur te sems can rnams dge
NK127(jo)001:9792: bcu'i lam la bkod pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:9793: la lar 'jig rten mgon po dang /
NK127(jo)001:9794: la lar brgya byin du gyur pa sogs sna tshogs
NK127(jo)001:9795: pa'i skye ba'i rabs kyis sems can gyi don byas
NK127(jo)001:9796: pa dang / la lar ngan song gsum gyi gnas
NK127(jo)001:9797: su byams pas sdug bsngal zhi bar mdzad pa dang
NK127(jo)001:9798: pa dang / / de bzhin du lha la sogs
NK127(jo)001:9799: pa'i gnas thams cad du byams pas chos bstan pa
NK127(jo)001:9800: pa dang / / dang / de bzhin du byang
NK127(jo)001:9801: chub sems dpa' las dang po ba rnams nas sa
NK127(jo)001:9802: bcu pa'i bar rnams la chos kyi sgo sna tshogs
NK127(jo)001:9803: pa dang / / dang / ston pa dang / la lar chos 'gro ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:9804: bzo la sogs pa'i gnas byed pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:9805: kha ton du bya ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:9806: dam pa'i chos bri ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:9807: ting nge 'dzin mi 'dra ba tshad med pa la
NK127(jo)001:9808: mnyam par bzhag pa la sogs pa'i spyod pa mtha'
NK127(jo)001:9809: yas pa dang / la lar byang chub sems dpa'
NK127(jo)001:9810: du ma'i lus kyi ba spu'i khung bu la sogs
NK127(jo)001:9811: pa nas lha dang gnod sbyin 'khor los sgyur ba
NK127(jo)001:9812: la sogs pa gzugs sna tshogs nas de bzhin gshegs
NK127(jo)001:9813: pa'i sku'i bar gyi sprin chen po 'byung ba dang
NK127(jo)001:9814: yas pa dang / / chos kyi sgo sna tshogs mtha' yas pa 'byung ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:9815: la lar zhing dang sku la sogs pa rnam pa
NK127(jo)001:9816: tha dad pa'i de bzhin gshegs pa'i 'khor gyi dkyil
NK127(jo)001:9818: khang brtsegs de'i nang na khang pa brtsegs pa gcig
NK127(jo)001:9819: cig gzhan las yangs shing rgyan khyad par 'phags pa
NK127(jo)001:9820: can la stong chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khams thams
NK127(jo)001:9821: cad snang zhing / der gling bzhi pa bye ba
NK127(jo)001:9822: phrag brgya dang dga' ldan gyi gnas bye ba phrag
NK127(jo)001:9823: cad snang zhing / brgya mthong ste / 'dzam bu'i
NK127(jo)001:9824: gling de thams cad na byang chub sems dpa' byams
NK127(jo)001:9825: pa skye ba mngon par skye ba nas sangs rgyas
NK127(jo)001:9826: nas chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:9827: 'dir yang gdung ba sna tshogs pas sems can smin
NK127(jo)001:9828: par byas nas bstan pa gnas pa'i byin gyi rlabs
NK127(jo)001:9829: sna tshogs byas te lha'i gnas su 'gro ba mthong
NK127(jo)001:9830: ste / de thams cad kyi tshe tshong dpon gyi
NK127(jo)001:9831: bu nor bzang nyid kyang de'i drung na 'dug cing
NK127(jo)001:9832: yun de snyed du bya ba byas shing dran pa
NK127(jo)001:9833: ma nyams par rnam pa thams cad khong du chud
NK127(jo)001:9835: khang brtsegs de dag gi dril bu dang /
NK127(jo)001:9837: rol mo dang glu la sogs pa ji snyed dmigs
NK127(jo)001:9838: pa las chos kyi sprin gyi 'brug sgra bsam gyis
NK127(jo)001:9840: 'di ltar la lar ni byang chub kyi sems kyi sgra dang /
NK127(jo)001:9841: la lar ni pha rol tu phyin pa'i spyod pa'i
NK127(jo)001:9842: sgra la sogs pa rnam pa tha dad pa'i chos
NK127(jo)001:9843: kyi sgo'i sgra sna tshogs dang /
NK127(jo)001:9844: byang chub sems dpa' tha dad pa rnams kyis dang
NK127(jo)001:9845: po thugs bskyed pa nas sangs rgyas shing bstan pa
NK127(jo)001:9846: gnas kyi bar du spyod pa sna tshogs pa'i tshul
NK127(jo)001:9847: sna tshogs pa ma lus pa brjod pa'i sgra thos
NK127(jo)001:9848: pas / nor bzang giis gzungs dang spobs pa la
NK127(jo)001:9849: sogs pa'i yon tan gyi sgo tha dad pa mang
NK127(jo)001:9851: khang pa brtsegs pa'i rgyan rnams las kyang 'di ltar
NK127(jo)001:9852: me long gi dkyil 'khor las ni dag pa dang
NK127(jo)001:9853: ma dag pa'i 'jig rten sna tshogs chags 'jig gnas
NK127(jo)001:9854: pa'i tshul thams cad dang der gnas pa'i sems can
NK127(jo)001:9855: thams cad dang byang chub sems dpa' sna tshogs kyi
NK127(jo)001:9856: spyod pa sna tshogs tha dad pa gzugs brnyan gyi
NK127(jo)001:9858: mu tig gi phreng ba de dag las kyang spos
NK127(jo)001:9859: sna tshogs kyis dri zhim par byas pa'i chu yan
NK127(jo)001:9860: lag brgyad ldan gyii char phra mo 'bab par mthong
NK127(jo)001:9861: ngo // de bzhin du beed+aura ya'i phreng ba rnams las mar me'i phreng ba 'bar ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:9862: gdugs rnams las rgyan dang lhab lhub dang rin po che'i shar bu la sogs pa mthong ngo //
NK127(jo)001:9863: rdzing rnams las rin po che'i me tog sna tshogs
NK127(jo)001:9864: tshad sna tshogs pa la lha la sogs pa dang
NK127(jo)001:9865: / nyan rang byang sems kyi gzugs sna tshogs dang
NK127(jo)001:9866: 'gro ba thams cad kyi lus sna tshogs kyis 'dud
NK127(jo)001:9868: de bzhin gshegs pa'i sku skyil krung du bzhugs pa dag mthong ngo //
NK127(jo)001:9869: sa chen po beed+aur+ya las grub pa'i mig mang ris
NK127(jo)001:9870: re re na'ang gzugs brnyan bsam gyis mi khyab pa
NK127(jo)001:9871: tha dad pa dag snang ste /
NK127(jo)001:9872: zhing dang de bzhin gshegs pa dang byang chub sems
NK127(jo)001:9873: dpa' dang rin po che'i shing las sna tshogs du
NK127(jo)001:9874: ma mi 'dra ba'i mchod pa thogs pa'i sems can
NK127(jo)001:9875: gyi lus mi 'dra ba lus phyed tsam byung ba
NK127(jo)001:9876: la sogs pa sna tshogs mthong ngo //
NK127(jo)001:9877: zla gam rnams las nyi zla gza' skar gyi gzugs
NK127(jo)001:9878: brnyan grangs med pa 'thor te phyogs bcur snang bar
NK127(jo)001:9879: byed pa dang / gzhal med khang dang khang brtsegs
NK127(jo)001:9880: kyi rtsig ngos thams cad las byang chub sems dpa'i
NK127(jo)001:9881: spyod pa thams cad rim pas mthong bar gyur te
NK127(jo)001:9882: byed pa dang / / mig mang ris la lar
NK127(jo)001:9883: byang chub sems dpa' byams pas dbu byin pa dang
NK127(jo)001:9884: byed pa dang / / / de bzhin du mig
NK127(jo)001:9885: la sogs pa lus dang yan lag byin pa dang
NK127(jo)001:9886: byed pa dang / / / / bu dang chung
NK127(jo)001:9887: ma yul dang rgyal srid kyi dbang phyug la sogs
NK127(jo)001:9889: sems can brtson ra nas thar bar byas pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:9890: gru dang rta'i rgyal po'i stobs kyis sems can bsgral ba la sogs pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:9891: sangs rgyas dang sems can sna tshogs pa'i gzugs du
NK127(jo)001:9892: ma dang spyod lam du mas sems can 'dul ba'i
NK127(jo)001:9893: rnam 'phrul tshad med pa mthong bar gyur te /
NK127(jo)001:9894: khang brtsegs dang dmigs pa de dag re re las
NK127(jo)001:9895: kyang bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i rgyan dang yul rnam
NK127(jo)001:9896: par 'phrul pa 'di dang gzhan yang grangs med pa
NK127(jo)001:9897: de dag dran pa ma nyams shing byang chub sems
NK127(jo)001:9898: dpa'i ye shes dang byin gyi rlabs kyis mig rnam
NK127(jo)001:9899: par dag pas mthong bar gyur pa ni /
NK127(jo)001:9900: 'di ltar byang chub sems dpa'i byin gyi rlabs dang
NK127(jo)001:9901: khams gsum sgyu ma ltar mthong ba'i ye shes kyis
NK127(jo)001:9902: 'du shes gzhan 'gags nas dper na rmi lam du
NK127(jo)001:9903: yul dang longs spyod sna tshogs mthong zhing yun ring
NK127(jo)001:9904: bar myong ba rmis pa na der nam ring thung
NK127(jo)001:9905: ji tsam yin pa dang gnyid yin par ngo mi
NK127(jo)001:9906: shes kyang sad pa na de thams cad rjes su
NK127(jo)001:9907: dran pa ltar spyod yul de dag mthong ba dang
NK127(jo)001:9908: / byang chub sems dpa'i las kyi yul bsam gyis
NK127(jo)001:9909: mi khyab pas dper na mi nad pa zhig gi
NK127(jo)001:9910: las kyi snang bar srid pa 'di nas 'phos shing
NK127(jo)001:9911: las mi dge ba'i srid pa mngon du gyur te
NK127(jo)001:9912: sems can dmyal ba'i gnas su bsregs pa'i sdug bsngal
NK127(jo)001:9913: dag der skyes pa rnams dang tshe mnyam par myong
NK127(jo)001:9914: / ba'am / las dge ba'i rgyus lha gnas su
NK127(jo)001:9915: lha'i bde ba lha'i tshe srid du myong bar shes
NK127(jo)001:9916: par gyur kyang de 'di nas 'phos te der skyes
NK127(jo)001:9917: pa med kyang de ltar snang ba yod pa ltar
NK127(jo)001:9918: / ba'am / mthong ba dang / byang chub sems
NK127(jo)001:9919: dpa'i byin gyi rlabs kyi mthus mthong ba ni dper
NK127(jo)001:9920: na skyes bu 'byung po'i gdon gyis zin pa na
NK127(jo)001:9921: gzugs sna tshogs mthong zhing ci dris pa lung yang
NK127(jo)001:9923: byang chub sems dpa'i 'du shes kyis snang ba yun
NK127(jo)001:9924: ring por mthong ba ni dper na klu'i khang par
NK127(jo)001:9925: phyin pa'i skyes bu ni klu'i 'du shes kyi rnam
NK127(jo)001:9926: pa la zhugs pas nyi ma gcig nas lo brgya'i
NK127(jo)001:9927: bar gyi 'du shes 'byung yang klu'i 'du shes dang
NK127(jo)001:9928: bral nas mi'i 'du shes kyis yud tsam las ma
NK127(jo)001:9929: lon par mthong ba lta bu yin la /
NK127(jo)001:9930: ji ltar tshangs pa chen po'i gzhal med khang 'gro
NK127(jo)001:9931: ba thams cad na rgyan gyi dam pa phul zhes
NK127(jo)001:9932: bya ba yod pa de'i nang du stong gsum gyi
NK127(jo)001:9933: 'jig rten na yod do cog thams cad gzugs brnyan
NK127(jo)001:9934: gyi tshul du thams cad ma 'dres par gsal bar
NK127(jo)001:9935: snang ba bzhin du khang pa brtsegs pa'i rgyan de
NK127(jo)001:9936: dag gis kyang ma 'dres par snang bar byed pa
NK127(jo)001:9937: dang / ji ltar na dge slong zad par ram
NK127(jo)001:9938: khyab pa'i skye mched la snyoms par zhugs pa de
NK127(jo)001:9939: gang du 'dug gam 'greng yang rung ji ltar snyoms
NK127(jo)001:9940: par zhugs pa bzhin du bsam gtan gyi yul bsam
NK127(jo)001:9941: gyis mi khyab pa mthong zhing nyams su myong ba
NK127(jo)001:9942: bzhin du nor bzang gis kyang yul gang la zhugs
NK127(jo)001:9943: pa'i tshul bzhin du don de mthong ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:9944: ji ltar dri za'i grong khyer gyi rgyan dang lhab
NK127(jo)001:9945: lhub rnams nam mkha' las byung ba ni ci la'ang
NK127(jo)001:9947: gnod sbyin gyi gzhal med khang mi'i khang pa na
NK127(jo)001:9948: 'dug pa'i la mi'i khang pa gnod sbyin gyi khang
NK127(jo)001:9949: pa'i khongs na 'dug pa ni phan tshun tha mi
NK127(jo)001:9950: dad de las kyi yul rnam pa ji ltar dag
NK127(jo)001:9951: pa'i tshul bzhin du snang ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:9952: rgya mtsho chen po la stong chen po'i 'jig rten
NK127(jo)001:9953: thams cad kyang rgyu'i gzugs brnyan ltar snang ba dang
NK127(jo)001:9954: / sgyu ma mkhan po'i sngags dang rdzas kyi mthus
NK127(jo)001:9955: gzugs sna tshogs yongs su ston pa'i dpe de dag
NK127(jo)001:9956: gi rim pa dang mtshungs par /
NK127(jo)001:9957: tshong dpon gyi bu nor bzang gis kyang byang chub sems dpa' byams pa'i byin rlabs kyi mthu dang /
NK127(jo)001:9958: ye shes sgyu ma bsam gyis mi khyab pa la
NK127(jo)001:9959: zhugs pa'i byang chub sems dpa'i dbang dang byin gyi
NK127(jo)001:9960: rlabs kyis / ye shes chos thams cad shes pa sgyu ma'i stobs las mngon par sgrub pa'i mthus /
NK127(jo)001:9961: rnam par 'phrul pa'i spyod yul de dag yangs shing
NK127(jo)001:9962: rgya che ba gsal bar mthong zhing shes la nyams
NK127(jo)001:9963: su myong ba dang dpyad nas mtshan mar byas te
NK127(jo)001:9964: dmigs kyis rtogs par gyur to //
NK127(jo)001:9965: de nas byang chub sems dpa' byams pa khang pa
NK127(jo)001:9966: brtsegs pa de'i nang du song ste byin rlabs de
NK127(jo)001:9967: dag brtul nas nor bzang la smras pa /
NK127(jo)001:9968: rigs kyi bu 'di ni chos rnams kyi chos nyid
NK127(jo)001:9969: de chos thams cad ni rnam par bsgrubs na 'grub
NK127(jo)001:9971: byang chub sems dpa'i ye shes kyi byin gyi rlabs
NK127(jo)001:9972: te rang bzhin ma grub pa sgyu ma lta bu'o
NK127(jo)001:9973: zhes gsungs te se gol gyi sgras nor bzang ting
NK127(jo)001:9974: nge 'dzin de las bslangs nas de lta bu'i byang
NK127(jo)001:9975: chub sems dpa'i rnam par 'phrul pa mthong ngam zhes
NK127(jo)001:9977: 'phags pa dge ba'i bshes gnyen gyi byin gyis brlabs pa'i mthus mthong ngo //
NK127(jo)001:9978: rnam par thar pa 'di'i ming ci zhes bgyi /
NK127(jo)001:9980: 'di ni dus gsum gyi dmigs pa thams cad la
NK127(jo)001:9981: shes pa rab tu zhugs pa'i dran pa nyams pa
NK127(jo)001:9982: med pas brgyan pa'i snying po zhes bya ba ste
NK127(jo)001:9983: / rnam par thar pa 'di lta bu brjod du
NK127(jo)001:9984: med pa'i yang brjod du med pa dag ni tshe
NK127(jo)001:9985: gcig gis thogs pa'i byang chub sems dpas thob bo
NK127(jo)001:9987: 'phags pa rgyan de dag gang du mchi /
NK127(jo)001:9989: gang nas 'ong ba der te byang chub sems dpa'i byin rlabs las so //
NK127(jo)001:9990: de bas na 'gro 'ong med de gang du'ang mi
NK127(jo)001:9991: gnas kyang byang chub sems dpa'i ye shes sgyu ma
NK127(jo)001:9995: 'phags pa lam ji srid nas 'dir gshegs /
NK127(jo)001:9998: byang chub sems dpa' rnams 'gro ba dang 'ong ba
NK127(jo)001:9999: med pa la sogs pa'i tshul du 'gro ste mig
NK127(jo)001:10000: yor dang gzugs brnyan la sogs pa dang 'dra'o //
NK127(jo)001:10001: rigs kyi bur ni tshe'i sa yul phreng ba stobs
NK127(jo)001:10002: kyi grong rdal khang khyim can zhes bya bar tshong
NK127(jo)001:10003: dpon sa skyong zhes bya ba de sangs rgyas kyi
NK127(jo)001:10004: chos la bzhag nas tshe tshe sa zhes pa sku
NK127(jo)001:10005: tshe de la gang du 'khrungs pa'i sa la zer
NK127(jo)001:10007: sa'i mi rnams la snod bzhin du chos bstan pa byas te /
NK127(jo)001:10008: pha ma dang bram ze dang khyim bdag dang gnyen
NK127(jo)001:10009: bshes su gyur pa rnams theg pa chen po la
NK127(jo)001:10010: yang dag par bskul nas 'dir 'ongs so //
NK127(jo)001:10012: 'phags pa byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyi tshe'i sa gang lags /
NK127(jo)001:10014: byang chub kyi sems ni byang chub sems dpa'i rigs
NK127(jo)001:10015: su skyes pas byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyi tshe'i
NK127(jo)001:10016: sa'o // lhag bsam ni dge ba'i bshes gnyen gyi
NK127(jo)001:10017: rigs su skyes pas byang chub sems dpa'i tshe'i sa
NK127(jo)001:10018: yin pa sogs rnam grangs bcu dang /
NK127(jo)001:10019: gzhan yang thabs mkhas pa ni byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyi pha'o //
NK127(jo)001:10020: shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa ni ma'o //
NK127(jo)001:10021: zhes sogs byang chub sems dpa'i rigs kyi rgyud skyon
NK127(jo)001:10022: med pa la zhugs pas byis pa'i sa las ring
NK127(jo)001:10023: du 'das shing / sgyu ma lta bu'i spyod yul
NK127(jo)001:10024: gyis skye ba sogs la dbang thob par bstan nas
NK127(jo)001:10025: du 'das shing / 'di skad du / rigs kyi
NK127(jo)001:10026: bu de ltar nga ni 'gro ba'i skye gnas thams
NK127(jo)001:10027: cad kyi lus dang 'gro ba thams cad dang mnyam
NK127(jo)001:10029: nges tshig dang ming tha dad pa dang spyod lam
NK127(jo)001:10030: dang skye ba la sogs pa'i rnam par 'phrul pas
NK127(jo)001:10031: chos kyi dbyings rgyas par bkang ste /
NK127(jo)001:10032: sngon skal pa mnyam par spyod pa'i sems can byang
NK127(jo)001:10033: chub kyi sems stor ba rnams yongs su smin par
NK127(jo)001:10034: bya ba dang / lho phyogs kyi rgyud 'di'i yul
NK127(jo)001:10035: phreng ba stobs kyi grong rdal khang khyim dang ldan
NK127(jo)001:10036: pa zhes bya ba 'di'i bram ze'i rigs su skyes
NK127(jo)001:10037: pa rnams dang pha ma dang gnyen bshes su 'ong
NK127(jo)001:10039: rigs rgyud kyi khyad par gyis nga rgyal du gyur
NK127(jo)001:10040: pa 'di dag nga rgyal med par byas nas de
NK127(jo)001:10041: bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs su skyed pa'i don du 'dzam
NK127(jo)001:10042: bu'i gling 'dir skye bar bstan to //
NK127(jo)001:10043: de ltar nga lho phyogs kyi rgyud 'di na thabs
NK127(jo)001:10044: rnam pa 'di lta bus sems can 'dul bar byed
NK127(jo)001:10045: cing khang pa brtsegs pa 'di na 'dug go //
NK127(jo)001:10046: 'di nas shi 'phos nas kyang dga' ldan gyi lha'i
NK127(jo)001:10047: bu skal pa mnyam par spyod pa rnams smin par
NK127(jo)001:10048: bya ba dang / tshe gcig gis thogs pa'i byang
NK127(jo)001:10049: chub sems dpa' rnams dang yang dag par 'gro bar
NK127(jo)001:10050: bya ba dang / bya ba dang / de bzhin
NK127(jo)001:10051: gshegs pa sh+aakya thub pas bkye ba'i 'dul ba'i pad+mo
NK127(jo)001:10052: rnams kyang kha dbye ba la sogs pa'i phyir dga'
NK127(jo)001:10053: ldan gyi gnas su skye ba yongs su ston te
NK127(jo)001:10054: bya ba dang / bya ba dang / / bsam
NK127(jo)001:10055: pa yongs su rdzogs nas dus la bab pa na
NK127(jo)001:10056: thams cad mkhyen pa nyid kyang thob par byed kyis
NK127(jo)001:10057: bya ba dang / bya ba dang / / /
NK127(jo)001:10058: ngas byang chub thob nas kyang rigs kyi bu khyod
NK127(jo)001:10059: dang 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur par bcas pas da
NK127(jo)001:10060: dung du yang mthong bar 'gyur ro //
NK127(jo)001:10063: de bzhin gshegs pa sh+aakya'i rgyal po mya ngan las 'das nas /
NK127(jo)001:10067: rtags tsam 'dzin pa'i dus te lo lnga stong gis bstan pa rdzogs nas /
NK127(jo)001:10068: sku gdung gi dus zhes sku gdung rnams mchod pa'i gnas su byed pa tsam 'byung la /
NK127(jo)001:10069: de yang nub nas mi rnams kyi spyod pa ngan
NK127(jo)001:10070: zhing mi dge ba 'phel bas tshe lo bcu pa'i
NK127(jo)001:10072: de'i tshe mu ge dang nad dang mtshon gyi bskal
NK127(jo)001:10073: pas rim gyis zad par byas pa'i lhag ma'i mi
NK127(jo)001:10074: rnams yid byung nas dge ba'i las la 'jug pa
NK127(jo)001:10075: rim bzhin 'phel bas tshe lo yar 'phel bar 'gyur
NK127(jo)001:10076: zhing de'i tshe na bde ba dang ldan pa sgra
NK127(jo)001:10078: de las tshe mar bri nas brgyad khrir bab pa
NK127(jo)001:10079: na byang chub sems dpa' chen po byams pa 'a
NK127(jo)001:10080: di bskal pa grangs med pa bcu drug dang /
NK127(jo)001:10081: bskal pa 'bum phrag gcig lhag tsam du sbyin pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:10082: pha rol tu phyin pa sum cu rdzogs par byas
NK127(jo)001:10083: nas thams cad sgrol bzhin du skye ba'i lhag ma'i
NK127(jo)001:10084: lus sbyin pa chen po byas shing /
NK127(jo)001:10085: pha rol tu phyin pa yongs su rdzogs par byas
NK127(jo)001:10086: te lus zhig nas dga' ldan du skye ba rdzogs
NK127(jo)001:10087: par byas nas 'dzam bu'i gling du rgyal po'i pho
NK127(jo)001:10088: brang tog ldan zhes bya bar /
NK127(jo)001:10089: 'khor los sgyur ba'i rgyal po dung zhes bya ba'i
NK127(jo)001:10090: mdun na 'don du gyur pa bram ze'i rigs tshangs
NK127(jo)001:10091: bzang zhes bya ba yab dang /
NK127(jo)001:10092: tshangs ldan ma zhes bya ba'i yum gyi mngal du
NK127(jo)001:10093: zhugs pa na 'jig rten gyi khams stong phrag bcu
NK127(jo)001:10095: zla ba bcu 'das pa na drang srong lhung ba ri dwags rgyu ba'i gnas su bltams pa'i tshe /
NK127(jo)001:10096: rang gi bsod nams kyi mthus khang bzang rin chen
NK127(jo)001:10097: sna bdun las byas pa bzhi sa gzhi brtol te
NK127(jo)001:10098: byung ba'i nang du lha mo zla ba'i gdong can
NK127(jo)001:10099: la sogs pa / lha'i bu mo bzhin du mdzes
NK127(jo)001:10100: pa'i bud med mang po dang 'grogs te lo stong
NK127(jo)001:10101: phrag gcig tu lha'i bde ba myong bar byas nas
NK127(jo)001:10102: la sogs pa / / de'i nyin par rab tu
NK127(jo)001:10103: byung ba gcig mthong ba dang rin po che'i khang
NK127(jo)001:10104: bzang rnams la mi dga' zhing nges par 'byung 'dod
NK127(jo)001:10106: de'i tshe byams pa'i khang bzang de'i khor yug tu
NK127(jo)001:10107: stong gsum stong phrag bcu'i 'khor yug gi lha rnams
NK127(jo)001:10108: kyis lha'i me tog sogs bzung nas 'dus pa dang
NK127(jo)001:10109: / rgyal po dung la sogs pa skyes bu chen
NK127(jo)001:10110: po mchod pa'i tshogs thogs pa'i 'dus pas bskor zhing
NK127(jo)001:10111: nam mkha'i lha rnams kyis legs so'i sgra 'byin pas
NK127(jo)001:10112: 'og min gyi bar du sgra brgyud pas khyab par
NK127(jo)001:10113: / byed do // de'i tshe khang bzang de rdza
NK127(jo)001:10114: mkhan gyi 'khor lo ltar nam mkha' la 'gro zhing
NK127(jo)001:10115: zla ba rgyu skar gyis bskor ba bzhin du byang
NK127(jo)001:10116: chub sems dpa' byams pa btsun mo'i tshogs dang bcas
NK127(jo)001:10117: pa nam mkha' la bzhud do //
NK127(jo)001:10118: tshangs pa chen pos dpag tshad 'bum gyi tshad dang
NK127(jo)001:10119: mnyam pa'i gdugs dkar po 'dzin cing brgya byin lha'i
NK127(jo)001:10120: rgyal pos dung 'bud bzhin par dpal dang skal ba
NK127(jo)001:10121: bzang po dang ldan pa'i lha mo'i tshogs kyis bskor
NK127(jo)001:10122: nas rang gi byang chub kyi shing klu shing gi
NK127(jo)001:10124: byang chub shing de'i tshad ni khru brgya nyi shu
NK127(jo)001:10125: par gyur te yal ga'i mtho tshad de dang mnyam
NK127(jo)001:10126: la / me tog dri bsung mchog tu ldan pa /
NK127(jo)001:10127: bsung zhim pos dpag tshad bcu ru khyab pa'i me
NK127(jo)001:10128: tog lhung ba brtsegs pa'i byang chub snying por bzhugs
NK127(jo)001:10129: pa na de'i sa'i cha thams cad nyams dga' zhing
NK127(jo)001:10130: bya sna tshogs kyi sgra snyan pas mchod bzhin par
NK127(jo)001:10131: zhag bdun du bzhugs te rab tu byung bar mdzad
NK127(jo)001:10132: pa dang / de'i dngos po rnams tshangs pa chen pos mchod pa'i slad du len par byed do //
NK127(jo)001:10133: de'i 'khor ji snyed pa rnams kyang rab tu byung bar byed do //
NK127(jo)001:10134: de nas lha mo zla ba'i gdong can gyis shin
NK127(jo)001:10135: tu mngar ba'i 'o thug phul ba longs spyod pa'i
NK127(jo)001:10136: srod thun la byang chub shing gi drung du skyil
NK127(jo)001:10137: mo krung bcas te shar phyogs su gzigs nas bzhugs
NK127(jo)001:10138: pa'i mod la bla na med pa'i ye shes mngon
NK127(jo)001:10139: du mdzad cing / shing de'i drung du zhag bzhi bcu rtsa dgur bzhugs par mdzad do //
NK127(jo)001:10140: de nas tshangs pas gsol pa btab pa bzhin chos
NK127(jo)001:10141: kyi 'khor lo bskor ba'i ched du drang srong lhung
NK127(jo)001:10142: ba'i gnas su gshegs par mdzad pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:10143: de'i zhabs gang du bzhag pa thams cad du pad+ma 'dab ma khru sum cu pa /
NK127(jo)001:10145: ge sar khru nyi shu pa /
NK127(jo)001:10146: lte bar khru bcu drug pa 'byung zhing /
NK127(jo)001:10147: de bzhin gshegs pa de'i sku'i 'od kyis 'od gzhan
NK127(jo)001:10148: zil gyis mnan pas nyin mtshan mi phyed kyang bya
NK127(jo)001:10149: yi skad dang pad+mo kha phye ba dang zum pa
NK127(jo)001:10150: las nyin mtshan shes par byed do //
NK127(jo)001:10151: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das byams pa de'i sku'i tshad
NK127(jo)001:10152: ni mtho tshad du khru brgyad cu rtsa brgyad de
NK127(jo)001:10153: / 'di ltar zhabs nas pus mo'i bar dang /
NK127(jo)001:10156: de nas spyi gtsug gi bar du khru nyi shu rtsa gnyis re yod do //
NK127(jo)001:10157: dpung pa gnyis kyi bar du khru nyer lnga /
NK127(jo)001:10158: sgrog rus re'i dkyus su khru lnga /
NK127(jo)001:10159: snyan gnyis kyi rtse mo nas rtse mo'i bar la khru bdun /
NK127(jo)001:10160: spyan re re'i mchur khru lnga lnga /
NK127(jo)001:10161: smin ma gnyis kyi dkyus su khru lnga /
NK127(jo)001:10162: smin ma gnyis kyi dbus kyi bar la khru lnga /
NK127(jo)001:10164: ya mchu ma mchu gnyis kyi chur khru bcu bcu /
NK127(jo)001:10165: ljags kyi zlums su khru lnga /
NK127(jo)001:10167: gser gyi me long 'dra ba'i zhal gyi dkyil 'khor la khru nyer lnga /
NK127(jo)001:10169: phyag gnyis kyi ring du khru bzhi bcu rtsa bzhi ste /
NK127(jo)001:10170: dpe med pa'i sangs rgyas kyi rnam par rol pa'i
NK127(jo)001:10171: de bzhin gshegs pa des stong phrag bcu'i 'jig rten
NK127(jo)001:10172: gyi khor yug thams cad kyi lha rnams dang de'i
NK127(jo)001:10173: rjes su mi rnams kyi nang du chos kyi 'khor
NK127(jo)001:10175: de ltar byams pa de mthong bar 'dod pas da
NK127(jo)001:10176: ltar dkon mchog gsum la bya ba byed cing pha
NK127(jo)001:10177: rol tu phyin pa'i dge ba la ci nus su
NK127(jo)001:10179: rgyal tshab ma pham pa'i rtogs pa brjod pa'i skabs te bzhi pa'o ////
NK127(jo)001:10180: byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po nam mkha'i snying po la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK127(jo)001:10182: 'phags pa nam mkha'i snying po zhes bya ba theg pa chen po'i mdo las /
NK127(jo)001:10183: bcom ldan 'das ri kha la ti ka na nyan
NK127(jo)001:10184: thos dang byang chub sems dpa'i 'khor grangs med pa
NK127(jo)001:10185: dang thabs gcig tu bzhugs nas de bzhin gshegs pa'i
NK127(jo)001:10186: dpal gyi dam tshig lung bstan pa'i mthar phyin ma
NK127(jo)001:10188: nub phyogs nas brgya byin thogs pa'i nor bu rin
NK127(jo)001:10189: po che 'bum phrag du mas bskor ba'i yid bzhin
NK127(jo)001:10190: gyi nor bu rin po che snang ste /
NK127(jo)001:10191: de'i 'od kyis stong chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khams
NK127(jo)001:10192: 'di na gzugs su snang ba gang ji snyed pa
NK127(jo)001:10193: las de bzhin gshegs pa nyag gcig ma gtogs par
NK127(jo)001:10194: gzhan sems can gyi lus dang 'byung ba bzhi gang
NK127(jo)001:10195: yang mi snang bas thams cad nam mkha' mu med
NK127(jo)001:10196: pa'i rang bzhin du gyur pa na /
NK127(jo)001:10197: thams cad du phyogs gang dang gang du brtags pa
NK127(jo)001:10198: dang de bzhin gshegs pa'i sku 'ba' zhig lham mer
NK127(jo)001:10199: snang ba dang / nor bu rin po che'i snang
NK127(jo)001:10200: ba ma gtogs rang gzhan gyi lus dang nyi zla'i
NK127(jo)001:10201: 'od dang gzugs la sogs pa gang yang mi snang
NK127(jo)001:10202: snang ba dang / zhing / sems dang sems byung
NK127(jo)001:10203: rnams la'ang nga yir 'dzin pa dang skye mched drug
NK127(jo)001:10204: gi 'du shes mi 'byung bar gyur te /
NK127(jo)001:10205: de na byang chub sems dpa' sa bcu la gnas
NK127(jo)001:10206: pa dpa' bar 'gro ba'i ting 'dzin thob kyang skye
NK127(jo)001:10207: ba gcig gis thogs pa dang srid pa tha ma
NK127(jo)001:10208: pa rnams ma gtogs pa'i byang chub sems dpa' gzhan
NK127(jo)001:10209: dang nyan thos dang lha la sogs pa'i 'dus pa
NK127(jo)001:10210: de dag thams cad 'jigs shing dngangs la skyo bar
NK127(jo)001:10211: gyur te / pha rol tshu rol la rmongs nas
NK127(jo)001:10212: sems 'khrugs shing phan tshun mi mthong bas 'di lta
NK127(jo)001:10213: bu dang 'di ci'i rang bzhin zhes dri ba gang
NK127(jo)001:10215: de'i tshe byang chub sems dpa' chen po tshangs pa'i
NK127(jo)001:10216: gzer bu zhes bya bas bcom ldan 'das la btud
NK127(jo)001:10217: de / ltas chen po de'i tshul gyis 'khor 'di
NK127(jo)001:10218: rnams rmongs par gyur pa las dbugs 'byin par gsol
NK127(jo)001:10219: de / zhing / byang chub sems dpa' chen po
NK127(jo)001:10220: dag 'dir mchi zhing gtam zab mo 'byung bar 'tshal
NK127(jo)001:10222: de de bzhin no zhes sogs bka' stsal pa'i mod
NK127(jo)001:10223: la 'khor rnams kyis thams cad sngon bzhin du mthong
NK127(jo)001:10224: bar gyur to // de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis
NK127(jo)001:10225: phyag g.yas pa brkyangs te 'di skad ces bka' stsal
NK127(jo)001:10226: bar gyur to // to // nam mkha'i snying po
NK127(jo)001:10227: zhes bya ba'i byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen
NK127(jo)001:10228: bar gyur to // to // po / ting nge 'dzin rgya mtsho dang mtshungs pa /
NK127(jo)001:10229: byang chub sems dpa'i bslab pa ri rab dang mtshungs pa /
NK127(jo)001:10230: ye shes nam mkha' dang mtshungs pa /
NK127(jo)001:10232: bzod pa rdo rje dang mtshungs pa /
NK127(jo)001:10233: byang chub sems dpa' thams cad kyi rgyal mtshan gyi mchog lta bu /
NK127(jo)001:10234: mya ngan las 'das pa'i gnas su 'gro ba rnams kyi ded dpon lta bu /
NK127(jo)001:10235: dge rtsa thams cad kyi gter lta bu /
NK127(jo)001:10236: sdug bsngal ba thams cad kyi bum pa bzang po lta bu /
NK127(jo)001:10237: mun par chud pa rnams kyi nyi ma lta bu /
NK127(jo)001:10238: lam stor ba rnams kyi zla ba lta bu /
NK127(jo)001:10239: 'jigs pa rnams kyi ri rab lta bu /
NK127(jo)001:10240: nyon mongs pa'i nad kyis gdung ba rnams kyi sman bcud kyi sa len lta bu /
NK127(jo)001:10241: dge rtsa chad de ltung ba rnams kyi 'khar ba lta bu /
NK127(jo)001:10242: phreng bas 'tsho ba rnams kyi me tog lta bu /
NK127(jo)001:10243: sdom pa spyod pa rnams kyi me long lta bu /
NK127(jo)001:10244: ngo tsha shes shing khrel yod pa rnams kyi gos lta bu /
NK127(jo)001:10245: myang 'das la 'gro ba'i stegs bu lta bu /
NK127(jo)001:10246: pha rol tu 'gro ba'i gru lta bu /
NK127(jo)001:10247: mtho ris su 'gro ba'i them skas lta bu /
NK127(jo)001:10248: tshig ngan dang skur pas gdung ba rnams kyi gdugs lta bu /
NK127(jo)001:10249: pha rol rgol ba can rnams kyi ni seng ge lta bu /
NK127(jo)001:10250: char pa rnams kyi ni chu lta bu /
NK127(jo)001:10251: bdud kyi dgra rnams kyi ni go cha lta bu /
NK127(jo)001:10252: bslab pa 'khrugs pa rnams kyi ni mig 'byed pa lta bu /
NK127(jo)001:10253: dge ba'i rtsa ba'i lo thog thams cad kyi sa lta bu /
NK127(jo)001:10254: nad pa rnams kyi sman pa lta bu /
NK127(jo)001:10255: bkres pa rnams kyi 'bru lta bu /
NK127(jo)001:10256: skom pa rnams kyi chu shel lta bu /
NK127(jo)001:10257: ngal ba rnams kyi mal lta bu /
NK127(jo)001:10258: ting 'dzin ldan pa rnams kyi me shel lta bu /
NK127(jo)001:10259: byang chub kyi lam du zhugs pa rnams kyi shing rta lta bu /
NK127(jo)001:10260: skyed mos tshal na rtse ba rnams kyi rdzing lta bu /
NK127(jo)001:10261: byang chub kyi phyogs la brtson pa rnams kyi phreng ba lta bu /
NK127(jo)001:10263: rigs kyi bu de ni pha rol tu phyin pa rnams kyi 'bras bu lta bu /
NK127(jo)001:10264: sa bcu dang ldan pa rnams kyi yid bzhin nor bu lta bu /
NK127(jo)001:10265: dpa' bar 'gro ba'i ting nge 'dzin dang ldan pa rnams kyi shing yongs 'dus dang 'dra ba /
NK127(jo)001:10266: lta ba ngan pa'i sbyor ba thams cad gcod pa'i phyir mtshon lta bu /
NK127(jo)001:10267: bag chags kyi mtshams sbyor ba'i nyon mongs pa thams cad 'joms pa'i rdo rje lta bu /
NK127(jo)001:10268: bdud rnams kyis thub par dka' ba /
NK127(jo)001:10269: thabs dang ldan pa rnams kyi tshes grangs /
NK127(jo)001:10271: sangs rgyas kyi chos thams cad kyi gnas /
NK127(jo)001:10272: rang rgyal rnams kyi phreng ba dang mtshungs pa /
NK127(jo)001:10273: nyan thos thams cad kyi gos dang mtshungs pa /
NK127(jo)001:10274: lha rnams kyi mig lta bu /
NK127(jo)001:10275: mi rnams kyi lam lta bu /
NK127(jo)001:10278: dmyal ba pa rnams kyi mgon /
NK127(jo)001:10279: sems can thams cad kyi sbyin gnas kyi snod du gyur pa /
NK127(jo)001:10280: byang chub sems dpa' thams cad kyi shing rta lta bu /
NK127(jo)001:10281: dus gsum gshegs pa'i sangs rgyas thams cad kyi blon po lta bu /
NK127(jo)001:10282: chos kyi grong khyer gyi sgo srung ba yin te /
NK127(jo)001:10283: rigs kyi bu de ni sangs rgyas kyi chos ma 'dres pa bco brgyad kyi bar gyis ni brgyan /
NK127(jo)001:10284: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi ye shes thams cad dang ni ldan te /
NK127(jo)001:10285: de bzhin gshegs pa ma gtogs pa gzhan sems can
NK127(jo)001:10286: thams cad kyis mchod pa'i dam pa kun gyis rigs
NK127(jo)001:10287: kyi bu de mchod par bya ba yin gyis /
NK127(jo)001:10288: khyed rnams kyis de la bsu ba dang mchod pa
NK127(jo)001:10289: dang bkur stir gyis shig dang khyed thams cad kyang
NK127(jo)001:10290: de lta bu'i yon tan gyi khyad par thob par
NK127(jo)001:10292: 'khor der 'dus pa thams cad langs nas byang chub
NK127(jo)001:10293: sems dpa' chen po nam mkha'i snying po la logs
NK127(jo)001:10294: su thal mo sbyar te dga' bas lta zhing 'dug
NK127(jo)001:10295: nas / bdag cag gis rigs kyi bu 'di la
NK127(jo)001:10296: bkod pa'i mchog ji lta bu zhig gis bkur sti
NK127(jo)001:10298: byang chub sems dpa' nam mkha'i snying po'i mthus mi
NK127(jo)001:10299: mjed kyi zhing 'di thams cad rin po che sna
NK127(jo)001:10300: bdun las byas shing thams cad du mnyam pa dang
NK127(jo)001:10301: / rin po che sna bdun las byas pa'i shing la sogs pas brgyan cing /
NK127(jo)001:10302: ngan song gsum dang nad la sogs pa'i sdug bsngal thams cad rgyun chad de /
NK127(jo)001:10303: zas gos rgyan la sogs pa yongs su thob cing /
NK127(jo)001:10304: gzugs mchog tu bzang zhing bsam pa yongs su rdzogs la /
NK127(jo)001:10305: nyon mongs pa rab tu zhi zhing mchog gsum la shin tu dad par gyur te /
NK127(jo)001:10306: 'khor de'i sems can re re'i lag pa gnyis kar
NK127(jo)001:10307: yang nor bu rin po che thogs pa'i 'od kyis
NK127(jo)001:10308: mi mjed kyi zhing 'di thams cad snang zhing rol
NK127(jo)001:10310: nor bu sna tshogs dang gos rgyan me tog spos
NK127(jo)001:10311: phreng gdugs la sogs pa'i char chen po 'bab pa
NK127(jo)001:10312: dang / lha'i gos rgyan dang me tog dang tsan+dana
NK127(jo)001:10313: sbrul snying la sogs pas lam kun tu bkram pa'i
NK127(jo)001:10314: dang / g.yas g.yon du / rnam par rgyal byed
NK127(jo)001:10315: kyi khang pa dang 'dra ba'i rin chen sna bdun
NK127(jo)001:10316: pa'i khang bzang na 'dod pa'i dbang phyug gi chung
NK127(jo)001:10317: ma dam pa rang 'dra ba'i na chung tshogs kyi
NK127(jo)001:10318: yan lag lnga dang ldan pa'i sil snyan sgrogs shing
NK127(jo)001:10319: rtse dgar rol pa dag dang /
NK127(jo)001:10320: bcom ldan 'das kyi dbu'i steng du lha'i nor bu
NK127(jo)001:10321: rin po che las byas pa'i tshangs pa chen po'i
NK127(jo)001:10322: gdugs lta bu'i gdugs dpag tshad brgya tsam pa rin
NK127(jo)001:10323: po che'i d+r+wa ba'i skud pa dang mu tig gi
NK127(jo)001:10324: rgyan phreng can las lha las 'das pa'i sil snyan
NK127(jo)001:10326: rtsa shing me 'bras sogs sa la brten pa thams
NK127(jo)001:10327: cad las kyang de lta bu'i sgra snyan pa dag
NK127(jo)001:10328: gis bstod pa'i dbyangs byung zhing /
NK127(jo)001:10329: de gang gis thos pa de dag bla med byang chub las phyir mi ldog par gyur to //
NK127(jo)001:10330: de lta bu'i bkod pa chen po mthong bas 'khor
NK127(jo)001:10331: rnams shin tu ngo mtshar zhing skyes bu dam pa
NK127(jo)001:10332: de'i stan ji ltar bsham snyam pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:10333: de'i tshe bcom ldan 'das kyi spyan sngar rin chen
NK127(jo)001:10334: sna tshogs las byas pa'i me tog rgyang grags gcig
NK127(jo)001:10335: tsam pa la pad+ma'i stan 'bum phrag du mas bskor
NK127(jo)001:10336: ba byung ba'i gtso bo'i pad+mo de la nam mkha'i
NK127(jo)001:10337: snying po skyil mo krung bcas te 'dug cing de'i
NK127(jo)001:10338: spyi bor nor bu rin po che 'bar ba snang
NK127(jo)001:10339: ngo // nam mkha'i snying po 'khor gyi byang chub
NK127(jo)001:10340: sems dpa' chen po dpa' 'gro'i ting 'dzin thob pa
NK127(jo)001:10341: brgya byin thogs pa'i nor bu rin po ches brgyan
NK127(jo)001:10342: pa 'bum phrag mang po rnams kyang rang rang gi
NK127(jo)001:10343: lha'i stan la 'khod par snang ngo //
NK127(jo)001:10344: de'i tshe byang chub sems dpa' byams pas byang chub sems dpa' sman gyi rgyal po la smras pa /
NK127(jo)001:10345: byang chub sems dpa' grags chen rnams kyis sngon du
NK127(jo)001:10346: ston pa la phyag byas nas phyis rang gi stan
NK127(jo)001:10348: skyes bu dam pa 'dis bkod pa chen po bstan
NK127(jo)001:10349: nas ston pa la phyag kyang mi 'tshal bar stan
NK127(jo)001:10350: la 'dug par snang zhes smras pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:10351: sman pa'i rgyal pos smras pa /
NK127(jo)001:10352: skyes bu dam pa 'di ni sangs rgyas kyi chos
NK127(jo)001:10353: la gnas shing rtog pa kun la mi gnas pas
NK127(jo)001:10354: sems can du mi mthong yang /
NK127(jo)001:10355: sems can yongs su smin pa'i phyir thabs kyi spyod yul ston pa yin no zhes so //
NK127(jo)001:10356: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis byang chub sems dpa' sman pa'i rgyal po la legs so byin te /
NK127(jo)001:10357: skyes bu dam pa khyod ji skad smras pa de
NK127(jo)001:10358: bzhin te sems can thams cad kyis rgyun zhugs gcig
NK127(jo)001:10359: gi spyod yul dang sbyor ba dang rnam par grol
NK127(jo)001:10361: yongs su brtag pa bzung ste sems can thams cad
NK127(jo)001:10362: rgyun zhugs su gyur kyang de dag gis lan gcig
NK127(jo)001:10363: phyir 'ong ba'i spyod yul sogs mi shes pa dang
NK127(jo)001:10364: / de bzhin du sbyar te lan gcig phyir 'ong ba rnams kyis phyir mi 'ong dang /
NK127(jo)001:10365: des dgra bcom pa dang dgra bcom rnams kyis rang sangs rgyas kyi spyod yul sogs mi shes la /
NK127(jo)001:10366: sems can thams cad bse ru lta bu'i rang sangs
NK127(jo)001:10367: rgyas su gyur kyang des byang chub sems dpa' mi
NK127(jo)001:10368: skye ba'i chos la bzod pa thob pa gcig gi
NK127(jo)001:10369: spyod yul sogs mi shes shing /
NK127(jo)001:10370: sems can thams cad mi skye ba'i chos la bzod
NK127(jo)001:10371: pa thob pa'i byang sems su gyur kyang de dag
NK127(jo)001:10372: gis byang chub sems dpa' so sor rig pa thob
NK127(jo)001:10373: pa dang dpa' bar 'gro ba'i ting 'dzin thob pa
NK127(jo)001:10374: gcig gi spyod par mos pa dang don dam pa'i
NK127(jo)001:10375: bden pa la brtag pa'i byin gyi rlabs mi shes
NK127(jo)001:10376: so // rigs kyi bu byang chub sems dpa' chen
NK127(jo)001:10377: po nam mkha'i snying po 'dis mi skye ba'i chos
NK127(jo)001:10380: dpa' bar 'gro ba'i ting nge 'dzin thob nas bskal pa dpag tu med pa 'das te /
NK127(jo)001:10381: da lta nga'i 'dus pa chen po na 'khod pa
NK127(jo)001:10382: rnams kyi bsam pa dang bag la nyal shes nas
NK127(jo)001:10383: de dag gi don du nub phyogs nas 'dir 'ongs
NK127(jo)001:10384: shing / nyan rang rnams dang thun mong ma yin
NK127(jo)001:10385: pa'i mtha' yas pa'i nam mkha' mtha' yas skye mched
NK127(jo)001:10386: kyi ting nge 'dzin bstan te sems can thams cad
NK127(jo)001:10387: skyo bar byas nas de'i 'og tu sems can dpag
NK127(jo)001:10388: tu med pa smin par bya ba'i phyir kun rdzob
NK127(jo)001:10389: kyi bkod pa chen po dang ting nge 'dzin gyi
NK127(jo)001:10390: bkod pa chen po bstan to //
NK127(jo)001:10391: gal te rigs kyi bu 'dis don dam pa'i bden
NK127(jo)001:10392: pa mi skye ba'i bzod pa ston du zin na
NK127(jo)001:10393: lha dang bcas pa'i 'jig rten rmongs pas bslad par
NK127(jo)001:10394: 'gyur ro // byang chub sems dpa' sa brgyad pa
NK127(jo)001:10395: la gnas pa'i bar du yang myos shing bslad par
NK127(jo)001:10396: 'gyur bas 'di'i spyod yul dang sbyor ba'i mtshan ma
NK127(jo)001:10397: ston par mi nus te de ltar chos zab mo'i
NK127(jo)001:10399: rigs kyi bu 'di ni thabs shes pa /
NK127(jo)001:10400: sangs rgyas kyi chos thams cad la gnas pa /
NK127(jo)001:10402: ye shes gzhan la rag ma las pa la mkhas pa /
NK127(jo)001:10403: byang chub sems dpa' thams cad kyi rgyal mtshan gyi mchog rgyal po la 'os pa dang 'dra'o //
NK127(jo)001:10404: byang chub sems dpa' chen po nam mkha'i snying po
NK127(jo)001:10405: 'di ni sems can thams cad mtho ris dang thar
NK127(jo)001:10407: sems kyi nyon mongs pa'i nad las thar bar byed pa /
NK127(jo)001:10408: lus kyi dug 'byung ba chen po'i nad gso ba /
NK127(jo)001:10409: lta ba ngan pas bslad nas mtho ris dang thar
NK127(jo)001:10410: pa'i lam mi shes pa dag gis 'di la phyag
NK127(jo)001:10411: 'tshal zhing dri dang a ga rus bdugs te gsol
NK127(jo)001:10413: de dag gi bsam pa dang bag la nyal sogs
NK127(jo)001:10414: dang mtshams par sngon gyi dge rtsa ci 'dra bar
NK127(jo)001:10415: sems phyogs pa'i dge ba'i rtsa ba rnams sad pa'am
NK127(jo)001:10416: rmi lam du thabs mkhas pas ston cing /
NK127(jo)001:10417: thabs des lta ba dang smon lam dang skyabs ngan
NK127(jo)001:10418: pa sogs las myur du thar nas de'i sgo gsum
NK127(jo)001:10419: gyi spyod pa dang dge ba'i bshes gnyen dang smon
NK127(jo)001:10420: lam drang po thob pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:10421: myur du dri mi zhim pa dang nyon mongs pa
NK127(jo)001:10422: dang ngan song du 'gro ba'i las thams cad las
NK127(jo)001:10423: thar nas / bdag gi sems la dbang thob cing
NK127(jo)001:10424: zab mo'i bzod pa la gnas par 'gyur ba'i thabs
NK127(jo)001:10426: de bzhin du sems can lus la nad sna tshogs kyis gzir ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:10428: mig sogs dbang po 'tshe ba can dang /
NK127(jo)001:10429: yan lag gang rung nyams pa dag gis nad de dag zhi ba'i phyir gsol ba btab na /
NK127(jo)001:10430: de'i rmi lam na bram ze dang brgya byin dbyangs
NK127(jo)001:10431: can ma rgyal rigs blon po sman pa pha ma
NK127(jo)001:10432: khye'u bu mo la sogs pa'i gzugs kyis nad zhi
NK127(jo)001:10433: ba'i sman dang yo byad bstan pa'i sbyor ba dag
NK127(jo)001:10434: gis nad thams cad zhi bar 'gyur ro //
NK127(jo)001:10435: de bzhin du zhal ta pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:10437: longs spyod dang mi 'bral ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:10441: bu dang g.yog la sogs pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:10448: sems can rnams dang mthun pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:10449: sdig pa las thar ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:10455: sbyin pa sogs pha rol tu phyin pa drug 'dod
NK127(jo)001:10456: pa dag gis gsol ba btab na thabs ston cing
NK127(jo)001:10457: ji ltar 'dod pa'i don yid bzhin du 'grub par
NK127(jo)001:10458: mdzad pa dang / gzhan ser sna can sbyin pa
NK127(jo)001:10459: la 'god pa sogs phar phyin la rab tu gzhog
NK127(jo)001:10460: mdzad pa dang / pa dang / sems can gzhan
NK127(jo)001:10461: rdzogs pa'i byang chub dang thabs mkhas pa dang tshangs
NK127(jo)001:10462: pa'i gnas bzhi nas snying rje chen po'i bar la
NK127(jo)001:10463: 'god par 'dod pa dag gis byang chub sems dpa'
NK127(jo)001:10464: nam mkha'i snying po la gsol ba btab na /
NK127(jo)001:10465: de dag gi skal pa ji lta bu dang 'tshams
NK127(jo)001:10466: pa'i gzugs kyis de la thabs ston par byed cing
NK127(jo)001:10467: / thabs des tshegs chung ngus sems can tshad med pa dag /
NK127(jo)001:10468: theg pa la mi ga nas pa dang nyan rang
NK127(jo)001:10469: gi theg pa la gnas pa dag kyang bla med
NK127(jo)001:10470: theg chen las phyir mi ldog par gzhog cing /
NK127(jo)001:10471: ting nge 'dzin dang gzungs dang bzod pa sna tshogs
NK127(jo)001:10472: dang sa bcu la 'jog pa'i bar du nus te
NK127(jo)001:10473: / de ltar nam mkha'i snying po ni thabs dang
NK127(jo)001:10474: ye shes dang snying rje chen po bsam gyis mi
NK127(jo)001:10476: rigs kyi bu nam mkha'i tshad ni la las bzung nus kyi /
NK127(jo)001:10477: nam mkha'i snying po de'i thabs dang ye shes dang
NK127(jo)001:10478: snying rje chen po dang ting nge 'dzin gyii stobs
NK127(jo)001:10479: bskyed pa dang sems can yongs su smin par mdzad
NK127(jo)001:10480: pa'i tshad ni bzung mi nus te de ltar yon
NK127(jo)001:10481: tan bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang ldan no //
NK127(jo)001:10482: sems can gang g.yo sgyu med cing lta ba drang la yang dag pa'i nan tan dang ldan pa /
NK127(jo)001:10483: bdag mi bstod cing gzhan mi smod la phrag dog dang ser sna spangs ba /
NK127(jo)001:10484: tshur 'chos med cing lhag bsam dang ldan pa de
NK127(jo)001:10485: la rigs kyi bu 'di snying brtse bar byed de
NK127(jo)001:10486: / thabs dang ye shes dang brtson 'grus dang rtul
NK127(jo)001:10487: ba'i thabs ston cing des sdug bsngal las yongs su
NK127(jo)001:10488: thar nas bla med byang chub tu sems skye zhing
NK127(jo)001:10489: dge rtsa rnams byang chub tu bsngo ba dang bla
NK127(jo)001:10490: med byang chub las phyir mi ldog par 'gyur /
NK127(jo)001:10491: pha rol tu phyin pa drug yongs su rdzogs pa'i
NK127(jo)001:10492: phyir spro ba dang rtul ba chen por gyur nas
NK127(jo)001:10494: de ltar nam mkha'i snying po ni yon tan gyi
NK127(jo)001:10495: chos rtul ba bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang ldan
NK127(jo)001:10496: pas sems can thams cad yongs su smin par byed
NK127(jo)001:10498: de nas bcom ldan 'das la byang chub sems dpa' byams pas gsol pa /
NK127(jo)001:10499: bcom ldan 'das ci'i slad du rigs kyi bu 'di'i
NK127(jo)001:10500: mgo bo la yid bzhin gyi nor bu rin po
NK127(jo)001:10501: che 'chang zhing shin tu lham mer gda' la byang
NK127(jo)001:10502: chub sems dpa' gzhan de lta ma lags /
NK127(jo)001:10504: rigs kyi bu byang chub sems dpa' nam mkha'i snying
NK127(jo)001:10505: po snying rje chen po dang ldan pa sems can
NK127(jo)001:10506: la phan pa'i phyir zhugs pa sdug bsngal chen po
NK127(jo)001:10507: las thar bar byed pa ste /
NK127(jo)001:10508: sems can gang dag rtsa ba'i ltung ba byung ba /
NK127(jo)001:10510: dge rtsa thams cad sprug par byed pa /
NK127(jo)001:10511: mkhas pa thams cad kyis spangs pa'i sems can skyabs
NK127(jo)001:10512: dang mgon med pa rnams la nam mkha'i snying po
NK127(jo)001:10514: lta ba ngan pa'i thibs po sel zhing the tshom dang 'bral bar byed pa /
NK127(jo)001:10516: sdig pa dang dri mi zhim pa thams cad 'khru bar byed pa /
NK127(jo)001:10517: lam ngan pa las zlog pa /
NK127(jo)001:10518: mtho ris dang thar bar 'jog par byed pa ste /
NK127(jo)001:10519: sems can gang dag sems shin tu 'dod par 'jug pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:10520: shin tu khro zhing gnod sems dang 'chab pa dang ser snas 'khrug pa /
NK127(jo)001:10521: gti mug gi mun pas dkris shing rgyu med par smra ba /
NK127(jo)001:10522: 'jig rten pha rol la 'jigs par mi lta ba /
NK127(jo)001:10523: nor sog pas chog mi shes pa /
NK127(jo)001:10524: rtag tu mi dge bcu'i lam dang ldan pa rnams
NK127(jo)001:10525: kyi ngan song gi sgo gcod cing mtho ris dang
NK127(jo)001:10526: thar par gzhog par byed pa'o //
NK127(jo)001:10527: des na de bzhin gshegs pa rnams ma gtogs par
NK127(jo)001:10528: lha dang bcas pa'i 'jig rten thams cad kyis skyes
NK127(jo)001:10529: bu dam pa 'di la mchod par bya ba yin
NK127(jo)001:10530: no // de'i phyir dkon mchog gi dkor 'phrog pa
NK127(jo)001:10531: sogs rgyal rigs la 'byung nye ba'i ltung ba lnga
NK127(jo)001:10532: no // byung ba dang / de bzhin du blon po la 'byung nye ba lnga dang /
NK127(jo)001:10533: phal pa las dang po pa dag la 'byung nye ba'i ltung ba brgyad de /
NK127(jo)001:10534: de ltar byang chub sems dpa'i rtsa ba'i ltung ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:10535: nyan thos kyi rtsa ba'i ltung ba byung ba de
NK127(jo)001:10536: dag gi yul du byang chub sems dpa' nam mkha'i
NK127(jo)001:10537: snying po gzugs sna tshogs pa'i tshul gyis 'byung zhing
NK127(jo)001:10538: zab mo'i mdo sde dag bshad pas /
NK127(jo)001:10539: snying gi snod chag par gyur pa'i rgyal rigs la
NK127(jo)001:10540: sogs pa de dag gis sngon gyi las la 'gyod
NK127(jo)001:10541: cing ngo tsha bas 'chag cing spong bar byed la
NK127(jo)001:10542: dge ba'i lam la spro ba chen pos mtho ris
NK127(jo)001:10543: dang thar par gzhog par byed do //
NK127(jo)001:10544: de'i phyir ltung ba'i rtsa ba 'chag par 'dod pas
NK127(jo)001:10545: tho rangs kyi thun la a ga ru dang rgya
NK127(jo)001:10546: spos la sogs pa'i bdug pas bdugs la nam mkha'i
NK127(jo)001:10547: snying po'i mtshan nas brjod cing gsol ba btab na
NK127(jo)001:10548: / de'i skal pa ji lta ba bzhin du rmi
NK127(jo)001:10549: lam du sna tshogs pa'i gzugs gang yang rung bas
NK127(jo)001:10551: ltung ba las ldang ba'i thabs dang theg pa chen
NK127(jo)001:10552: po'i thabs mkhas pa ston cing ting nge 'dzin dang
NK127(jo)001:10553: bzod pa dang gzungs dang sa'i bar du 'jog par
NK127(jo)001:10554: byed cing / theg chen la brtan par gnas pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:10555: bla med byang chub las phyir mi ldog par phar
NK127(jo)001:10556: phyin drug yongs su rdzogs pa'i brtson pa mi phyed
NK127(jo)001:10557: par brtan pa thob pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:10558: ye shes dang thabs la mkhas pa gang gis byang
NK127(jo)001:10559: chub sems dpa' las dang po pa de dag de
NK127(jo)001:10560: nyid du byang chub kyi sems mi brjed pa zhes
NK127(jo)001:10561: bya ba'i ting nge 'dzin thob pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:10562: ring por mi thogs par 'tshang rgya bar byed par 'gyur ro //
NK127(jo)001:10563: de ltar ltung ba dang ldan pa rnams kyang de
NK127(jo)001:10564: las ldang zhing bla med byang chub la 'jog pas
NK127(jo)001:10565: na / nam mkha'i snying po 'di ni shin tu
NK127(jo)001:10566: dpa' ba las byung ba'i yid bzhin gyi nor bu
NK127(jo)001:10567: rin po che yan lag gi dam pa mgo bo
NK127(jo)001:10569: rigs kyi bu gzhan yang nam mkha'i snying po'i ming thos sam /
NK127(jo)001:10571: de la mchod pa byed dam /
NK127(jo)001:10575: mchod pa sna tshogs pas bkur stir byed /
NK127(jo)001:10577: bdag gi srog kyang 'bul bar byed na /
NK127(jo)001:10578: sems can de dag mes 'chi ba'i dus byed par mi 'gyur /
NK127(jo)001:10579: de bzhin du chu dang mtshon dang dug gis mi 'chi /
NK127(jo)001:10580: de dag tshe zad pa ma gtogs mi dang mi min sus kyang srog 'phrog par mi nus /
NK127(jo)001:10583: bkres skom gyis 'chi ba'i dus mi byed /
NK127(jo)001:10584: rgyal pos chad pas mi gcod /
NK127(jo)001:10585: 'chi ba'i dus la bab pa'i par du ltung ba'i rtsa ba mi 'byung /
NK127(jo)001:10586: de dag gi dbang po 'gags shing rnam par shes pa lus las ma 'phos pa'i bar der /
NK127(jo)001:10587: rang nyid gang la gus pa'i tshul dang mthun par
NK127(jo)001:10588: nam mkha'i snying po bram ze dang brgya byin la
NK127(jo)001:10589: sogs pa'i gzugs su bstan nas bden pa bzhi'i chos
NK127(jo)001:10590: bstan pa shes par byas te mtho ris su gzhol
NK127(jo)001:10591: ba dang / sangs rgyas dad pa la sangs rgyas
NK127(jo)001:10592: kyi gzugs su sprul nas chos bstan te de dag
NK127(jo)001:10593: sangs rgyas yid la byed pa'i sgras dga' zhing rangs
NK127(jo)001:10594: nas 'chi ba'i dus byas te sangs rgyas kyi zhing
NK127(jo)001:10595: yongs su dag par skye ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:10596: chos dang dge 'dun la dad pa la'ang de dang mthun pa'i chos ston par byed do //
NK127(jo)001:10597: gang yang ting nge 'dzin sna tshogs la sems kyi dbang shin tu bya bar 'dod pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:10598: sangs rgyas kyi bka' dang bstan bcos sna tshogs klog par 'dod cing dran pa sogs 'dod pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:10599: rgya mtsho chen po dang khung du 'jug par 'dod pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:10600: bcud dam pa spyod par 'dod pas nam mkha'i snying
NK127(jo)001:10601: po la gsol ba btab pas re ba de dag
NK127(jo)001:10603: nad dang brtson rar bcug pa bcings pa dang chad
NK127(jo)001:10604: pas gcod pa bsad pa la thug pa rnams dang
NK127(jo)001:10605: / me chu dug mtshon byad stems dang /
NK127(jo)001:10606: stag seng dang rkun po g.yon can gyi 'jigs pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:10607: mdza' ba dang bral ba dang mi mdza' ba dang
NK127(jo)001:10608: phrad pa la sogs pa'i sdug bsngal dang bral bar
NK127(jo)001:10609: 'dod pa dang / chos gos dang bsod snyoms sogs
NK127(jo)001:10610: yo byad dang longs spyod sna tshogs kyis phongs pa
NK127(jo)001:10611: 'dod pa dang / dag gis / byams pa'i sems
NK127(jo)001:10612: su byas te nam mkha'i snying po'i mtshan nas brjod
NK127(jo)001:10613: cing mchod pa ci nus su byas la gsol ba
NK127(jo)001:10614: 'dod pa dang / dag gis / btab na /
NK127(jo)001:10615: nam mkha'i snying po gzugs gang yang rung ba'i tshul
NK127(jo)001:10616: gyis de dag gi mdun du 'dug nas dbug 'byin
NK127(jo)001:10617: 'dod pa dang / dag gis / btab na /
NK127(jo)001:10618: par byed / sdug bsngal thams cad las thar bar
NK127(jo)001:10619: 'dod pa dang / dag gis / btab na /
NK127(jo)001:10620: par byed / byed / bsam pa thams cad yongs
NK127(jo)001:10622: yo byad thams cad phun sum tshogs par byed do //
NK127(jo)001:10623: rgyal po'i bu la las rgyal po chen por dbang bskur ba thob par sems pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:10624: de bzhin du bram ze dang khyim bdag gi gnas chen po dang /
NK127(jo)001:10625: bzo dang thos pa dang sgom pa la mos pa
NK127(jo)001:10626: dag gi gnas chen po'i bar du 'dod pa de
NK127(jo)001:10627: dag gis nam mkha'i snying po'i mtshan nas brjod cing
NK127(jo)001:10629: de'i lha'i rna bas gsan nas de dag la de
NK127(jo)001:10630: ltar thabs ston cing bsam pa yid bzhin du rdzogs
NK127(jo)001:10631: par 'gyur ro // rigs kyi bu de ltar nam
NK127(jo)001:10632: mkha'i snying po ni thabs kyi yon tan gyi chos
NK127(jo)001:10633: dang blo gros rgya mtsho chen po dang ldan te
NK127(jo)001:10634: par 'gyur ro // / rgya mtsho chen po'i chu'i thigs pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:10635: phyogs bcu nam mkha' mu med pa dag kyang la la zhig gis tshad bzung nus srid kyi /
NK127(jo)001:10636: byang chub sems dpa' chen po nam mkha'i snying pos
NK127(jo)001:10637: sems can yongs su smin par bya ba'i phyir rnam
NK127(jo)001:10638: pa sna tshogs su sprul pa'i tshad bzung mi nus
NK127(jo)001:10639: te / la lar sangs rgyas kyi gzugs su sprul
NK127(jo)001:10640: par byed pa nas dud 'gro dang sems can dmyal
NK127(jo)001:10641: ba pa rnams kyi nang du dud 'gro dang dmyal
NK127(jo)001:10642: ba pa'i sems can gyi gzugs kyi bar du sprul
NK127(jo)001:10643: te / par byed do // de ltar bram ze
NK127(jo)001:10644: la sogs pa ji lta bus 'dul ba'i gzugs sna
NK127(jo)001:10645: tshogs su sprul pa de yang kha cig la mngon
NK127(jo)001:10647: kha cig la rmi lam du sprul par byed /
NK127(jo)001:10648: kha cig la 'chi 'pho'i shes pa tha ma'i tshe sprul par byed do //
NK127(jo)001:10649: de dag gi sdig pa'i las sprug cing ngan song
NK127(jo)001:10650: las bsgral te mtho ris nas byang chub chen po'i
NK127(jo)001:10652: de ltar nam mkha'i snying po 'di ni thabs dang
NK127(jo)001:10653: ye shes dang sangs rgyas kyi yon tan chen po
NK127(jo)001:10654: dang ldan pa de'i phyir mgo bo la yid bzhin
NK127(jo)001:10655: gyi nor bu yod par snang ngo //
NK127(jo)001:10656: zhes gsungs pas 'khor thams cad kyis nam mkha'i snying
NK127(jo)001:10657: po la ngo mtshar thob nas mchod pa byas so
NK127(jo)001:10658: // nam mkha'i snying po des kyang de thams cad
NK127(jo)001:10659: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das la phul nas phyag byas
NK127(jo)001:10660: te chos kyi bka' mchid zhus shing gzungs smras pas
NK127(jo)001:10661: // / lha dang mi'i skye dgu dpag med grangs
NK127(jo)001:10662: med pas ting nge 'dzin dang gzungs dang bzod pa
NK127(jo)001:10663: sna tshogs dang sa bcu la ye shes skyes par
NK127(jo)001:10664: gyur te srog chags khris ni mi skye ba'i chos
NK127(jo)001:10666: bcom ldan 'das kyis nam mkha'i snying po la bka' stsal pa /
NK127(jo)001:10667: khyod ni 'jig rten gyi khams grangs med dpag tu
NK127(jo)001:10668: med par sems can rnams la snying rje'i dbang gis
NK127(jo)001:10669: grong dang grong khyer dang grong rdal dang ljongs dang
NK127(jo)001:10670: yul 'khor dang rgyal po'i pho brang du gzugs dang
NK127(jo)001:10671: cha lugs dang spyod pa sna tshogs kyis theg pa
NK127(jo)001:10672: chen po'i mdo sde sna tshogs 'chad pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:10673: sems can yongs su smin par bya ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:10674: rgyal rigs gdol pa nas dge sbyong gdol ba'i bar
NK127(jo)001:10675: du sdig pa'i chos spang ba dang dge ba'i chos
NK127(jo)001:10676: la bzhag par nus so zhes gsungs so //
NK127(jo)001:10677: thar pa chen po'i mdo las /
NK127(jo)001:10678: byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po nam mkha'i
NK127(jo)001:10679: snying po ni ma 'ongs pa'i dus na bskal pa
NK127(jo)001:10680: stong rnam par dag pa zhes bya ba dang 'jig
NK127(jo)001:10681: rten gyi khams longs spyod can zhes bya bar /
NK127(jo)001:10682: de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom pa yang dag par
NK127(jo)001:10683: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rgyan rnam par dag pa zhes
NK127(jo)001:10685: 'jig rten gyi khams der byang chub sems dpa' chen
NK127(jo)001:10686: po rnams theg pa chen po 'ba' zhig spyod do
NK127(jo)001:10687: // sems can gang dag nam mkha'i snying po'i mtshan
NK127(jo)001:10688: thos te phyag 'tshal zhing mchod pa byas na 'jig
NK127(jo)001:10689: rten gyi khams longs spyod can der skye bar 'gyur
NK127(jo)001:10690: // ro // gang la las theg pa chen po'i
NK127(jo)001:10691: chos bsgrubs na'ang mi skye ba'i chos la bzod pa
NK127(jo)001:10694: nam mkha'i snying po'i mtshan brgya rtsa brgyad kyi phan yon las /
NK127(jo)001:10695: de phyir ci ste rtag tu 'dod pa de kun //
NK127(jo)001:10696: 'dod na 'gro ba kun la gcig dpa' ba //
NK127(jo)001:10697: nam mkha'i snying po srid gsum mgon po la //
NK127(jo)001:10698: rtag tu brten cing sngags kyang bsten par bgyi //
NK127(jo)001:10700: mgon po nam mkha' snying po'i rtogs pa brjod pa'i skabs te lnga pa'o ////
NK127(jo)001:10701: byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po sa yi snying po la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK127(jo)001:10703: sa snying 'khor lo bcu ba'i mdo las /
NK127(jo)001:10704: bcom ldan ri kha la de ya zhes bya ba
NK127(jo)001:10705: drang srong thub pa mang po'i spyod yul gyi gnas
NK127(jo)001:10706: na dge slong gi dge 'dun dang byang chub sems
NK127(jo)001:10707: dpa'i dge 'dun chen po tshad med pa dang thabs
NK127(jo)001:10708: gcig tu bzhugs te zla ba'i snying po zhes bya
NK127(jo)001:10710: de'i tshe lho phyogs nas bsung gi sprin chen po
NK127(jo)001:10711: las bsung gi chung dang de bzhin du me tog
NK127(jo)001:10712: dang / rin po che'i lta rdzas kyi rgyan dang /
NK127(jo)001:10713: gos kyi sprin las de dag gi char babs pas ri de khyab cing /
NK127(jo)001:10714: char de las chos kyi sgra dbyangs sna tshogs grags pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:10715: 'khor de dag thams cad kyi lus la ji ltar
NK127(jo)001:10716: mos pa'i bsung dang rgyan la sogs pas brgyan cing
NK127(jo)001:10717: so so'i lag mthil gnyis na yid bzhin gyi nor
NK127(jo)001:10718: bu rin po che thogs shing de re re las
NK127(jo)001:10719: kyang rin chen sna tshogs char bzhin 'bebs pa dang
NK127(jo)001:10720: / nor bu rin po che de dag las 'od
NK127(jo)001:10721: zer sna tshogs byung bas phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas kyi
NK127(jo)001:10722: zhing gang g+aa'i klung gi bye ma snyed na de
NK127(jo)001:10723: bzhin gshegs pa 'khor mang po tshad med pas bsti
NK127(jo)001:10724: stang bcas te yongs su bskor ba mthong zhing /
NK127(jo)001:10725: 'od de dag gis zhing de snyed kyi sems can nad kyis sdug bsngal ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:10726: bsad pa la thug pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:10728: mi dge bar spyod pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:10730: chad pa sna tshogs kyis nyon mongs par gyur pa
NK127(jo)001:10731: la sogs pa thams cad 'od des reg ma thag
NK127(jo)001:10732: tu sdug bsngal dang bral la /
NK127(jo)001:10733: bgo ba dang rgyan dang dbyig la sogs pa bsam pa bzhin du 'byor pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:10734: mi dge bcu spongs shing gang 'dod pa de bzhin du thob pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:10735: sdug bsngal gyi gdung ba thams cad zhi nas rab tu bde ba dang ldan pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:10736: zhing de thams cad du 'od kyi snang bas sprin
NK127(jo)001:10737: dang rdul dang rlung dang rdzi char dang bkra mi
NK127(jo)001:10738: shis pa'i sgra la sogs pa yid du mi 'ong
NK127(jo)001:10739: ba'i yul thams cad dang 'jigs pa dang gnod pa
NK127(jo)001:10740: mang po med par gyur cing /
NK127(jo)001:10741: gzhan yang las ngan pa dang log pa'i ngag dang
NK127(jo)001:10742: bsam pa dang log par phyogs pa dang yongs su
NK127(jo)001:10743: bral te / sa gzhi lag mthil ltar mnyam la
NK127(jo)001:10744: bde ba'i yo byad thams cad kyis gang ba dang
NK127(jo)001:10745: bral te / / tsha grang gi gdung ba med
NK127(jo)001:10746: par rab tu zhi zhing bde bar gyur par mthong
NK127(jo)001:10747: bral te / / ngo // de'i tshe 'khor mang
NK127(jo)001:10748: po rnams kyi so so'i lus kyi sa'i khams lhag
NK127(jo)001:10749: par lci zhing mi theg pa tsam du gyur pa'i
NK127(jo)001:10751: rgyu rkyen ci zhig gis ltas 'di lta bur gyur snyam pa'i rtog pa skyes so //
NK127(jo)001:10752: de'i tshe 'khor de'i nang na brgya byin lha'i dbang
NK127(jo)001:10753: po dri ma med par skyes zhes bya bas bcom
NK127(jo)001:10754: ldan 'das la tshul de lta bu'i rgyu rkyen gang
NK127(jo)001:10756: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
NK127(jo)001:10757: byang chub sems dpa' chen po sa'i snying po zhes bya ba yod de /
NK127(jo)001:10758: sngon bskal pa chen po tshad med grangs med pa'i
NK127(jo)001:10759: bar du rnyogs pa lnga'i tshe sangs rgyas mi bzhugs
NK127(jo)001:10760: pa'i 'jig rten gyi khams su sems can yongs su
NK127(jo)001:10762: da ltar byang chub sems dpa'i 'khor mang po dang
NK127(jo)001:10763: bcas pa 'jig rten gyi khams 'dir nga la phyag
NK127(jo)001:10764: 'tshal ba dang mchod pa'i phyir dang 'khor gyi dkyil
NK127(jo)001:10765: 'khor rnams la lta ba'i phyir dge sbyong gi gzugs
NK127(jo)001:10766: kyis 'ong bas de'i mthus cho 'phrul 'di dag bstan
NK127(jo)001:10767: to // byang chub sems dpa' chen po sa yi
NK127(jo)001:10768: snying po zhes bya ba de tshad med grangs med
NK127(jo)001:10769: bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i yon tan gyis brgyan pas
NK127(jo)001:10770: nyan rang dang bcas pa'i 'jig rten thams cad kyis
NK127(jo)001:10772: byang chub sems dpa' de ni yon tan phul du gyur pa thams cad kyi gter du gyur pa'o //
NK127(jo)001:10773: de bzhin du rnam par grol ba'i rin po che'i 'byung gnas /
NK127(jo)001:10774: byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyi mig dag par byed pa /
NK127(jo)001:10775: mya ngan las 'das par 'gro ba'i ded dpon /
NK127(jo)001:10776: yid bzhin nor bu rin po che ltar 'dod dgu'i
NK127(jo)001:10777: char 'bebs pas re ba yongs su tshim par byed
NK127(jo)001:10778: pa / tshong pa mang po'i rin po che'i gling lta bu /
NK127(jo)001:10779: dge ba'i rtsa ba 'phel ba'i zhing gshim pa lta bu /
NK127(jo)001:10780: rnam grol gyi bde ba la 'jog pa'i snod lta bu /
NK127(jo)001:10781: yon tan rin po che'i 'byung gnas kyi bum pa bzang po lta bu /
NK127(jo)001:10782: dge ba'i nan tan can la snang bar byed pa'i nyi ma lta bu /
NK127(jo)001:10783: lam stor ba rnams la sgron me lta bu /
NK127(jo)001:10784: nyon mongs pa'i gdung ba sel ba'i zla ba lta bu /
NK127(jo)001:10785: rkang pa med pa la bzhon pa lta bu /
NK127(jo)001:10786: lam ring por 'gro ba'i stegs lta bu /
NK127(jo)001:10787: 'brog slad pa la lam ston pa lta bu /
NK127(jo)001:10788: smyos shing 'khrugs pa'i sman lta bu /
NK127(jo)001:10789: nad kyis gzir ba la sman pa mkhas pa dang phrad pa lta bu /
NK127(jo)001:10790: rgas shing 'khogs pa la rten dang 'khar ba lta bu /
NK127(jo)001:10791: ngal zhing dub pa la khri stan lta bu /
NK127(jo)001:10792: chu bo bzhi rgal ba'i zam pa lta bu /
NK127(jo)001:10793: pha rol tu 'gro ba'i gru gzings lta bu /
NK127(jo)001:10794: dge rtsa rnam gsum smin pa dang sa dang gzhi 'dren cing rgyun du 'bebs par byed pa /
NK127(jo)001:10795: sbyin pa gtong ba'i rgyun mi 'chad pa la 'khor lo ltar 'jug pa /
NK127(jo)001:10796: tshul khrims srung ba brtan pa'i ri rab lta bu /
NK127(jo)001:10797: brtson 'grus gzhig par dka' ba rdo rje lta bu /
NK127(jo)001:10798: bzod pa mi g.yo ba sa chen po lta bu /
NK127(jo)001:10799: bsam gtan zab pa gter lta bu /
NK127(jo)001:10800: mnyam par 'jog pas mdzes pa me tog gi phreng ba dam pa lta bu /
NK127(jo)001:10801: shes rab zab cing yangs pa rgya mtsho chen po lta bu /
NK127(jo)001:10802: cis kyang mi chags pa nam mkhar lta bu /
NK127(jo)001:10803: 'bras bu dam pa'i rgyu dang nye ba me tog rgyas pa lta bu /
NK127(jo)001:10804: mu stegs can 'dul ba seng ge'i rgyal po lta bu /
NK127(jo)001:10805: lha'i bdud yongs su 'joms pa klu'am glang po che lta bu /
NK127(jo)001:10806: nyon mongs pa'i sgra thams cad gcod pa lha'i ral gri lta bu /
NK127(jo)001:10807: 'du 'dzi mang pos skyo ba rang sangs rgyas kyi theg pa lta bu /
NK127(jo)001:10808: nyon mongs pa'i dri ma 'khrud pa'i chu dngas pa lta bu /
NK127(jo)001:10809: mi gtsang ba'i nyal nyil ser ba'i rlung drag po lta bu /
NK127(jo)001:10810: kun nas nyon mongs pas glags pa gcod pa mtshon rnon po lta bu /
NK127(jo)001:10811: 'jigs pa dang bag tsha ba kun las srung ba gnyen nam mdza' bo lta bu /
NK127(jo)001:10812: phas rgol gyi dgra las skyob pa 'obs sam mkhar lta bu /
NK127(jo)001:10813: nyam nga thams cad las sgrol bar byed pa pha ma lta bu /
NK127(jo)001:10814: zhan cing nyam chung ba rnams sbed pa nags stug po lta bu /
NK127(jo)001:10815: dbyar lam ring por 'gro ba la bsil grib kyi shing lta bu /
NK127(jo)001:10816: tsha ba dang skom gyis gdungs pa rnams la chu grang ba lta bu /
NK127(jo)001:10817: bkres pa rnams la 'bru zhim po lta bu /
NK127(jo)001:10818: gcer bu rnams la bgo ba'i gos byed pa /
NK127(jo)001:10819: tsha bas nyen pa rnams la sprin stug po /
NK127(jo)001:10820: dbul zhing phongs rnams la yid bzhin nor bu /
NK127(jo)001:10821: 'jigs pas skrag pa la skyabs dang gnas /
NK127(jo)001:10822: lo thog rnams la char pa /
NK127(jo)001:10823: chu rnyogs ma can la nor bu chu dwang du gyur pa /
NK127(jo)001:10824: sems can mang po'i dge rtsa mi 'gong bar byed
NK127(jo)001:10825: pas spyod yul dam pa ston cing 'khor spro ba
NK127(jo)001:10827: sems can rnams lhag pa'i 'dzem pa dang ngo tsha ba la skul zhing 'dzud pa /
NK127(jo)001:10828: bsod nams ye shes kyi tshogs sogs pa la de'i rgyan dang ldan par byed pa /
NK127(jo)001:10829: nyon mongs pa yongs su sel ba'i skyugs pa dang 'khru sman lta bu /
NK127(jo)001:10830: sems 'khrugs pa sdud pa ni mnyam par 'jog pa'i spyod yul lta bu /
NK127(jo)001:10831: spobs pa thogs pa med pa zo chun rgyud pa'i 'khor lo lta bu /
NK127(jo)001:10832: dmigs pa la sems sdud pa gzugs bzang po la rtog pa lta bu /
NK127(jo)001:10833: bzod pa brtan par byed pa ri rab lhun po lta bu /
NK127(jo)001:10834: gzungs zab cing rgya che ba rgya mtsho chen po lta bu /
NK127(jo)001:10835: rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa thogs pa med pa nam mkha' la lta bu'o //
NK127(jo)001:10836: sgrib pa'i bag chags thams cad yongs su sel ba
NK127(jo)001:10837: ji ltar nyi ma tsha bas 'khyag pa cham chom
NK127(jo)001:10839: rtag tu bsam gtan dang gzugs med pa dang yang
NK127(jo)001:10840: dag pa'i lam la rol zhing thams cad mkhyen pa'i
NK127(jo)001:10841: ye shes rin po che dam pa'i gling lta bur
NK127(jo)001:10842: gyur pas ched du ma brtsams kyang chos chen po'i
NK127(jo)001:10844: rigs kyi bu de ltar byang chub sems dpa' sems
NK127(jo)001:10845: dpa' chen po sa'i snying po ni de lta bu'i
NK127(jo)001:10846: yon tan gyi khyad par tshad med grangs med pa
NK127(jo)001:10847: bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang ldan pa'o zhes basngagasa
NK127(jo)001:10849: byang chub sems dpa' chen po sa'i snying po 'khor
NK127(jo)001:10850: byang chub sems dpa' bye ba khrag khrig brgya stong
NK127(jo)001:10851: phrag brgyad cu dang bcas pa lho phyogs nas rdzu
NK127(jo)001:10852: 'phrul gyi mthus dge sbyong gi gzugs kyis bcom ldan
NK127(jo)001:10854: zhabs gnyis la phyag 'tshal zhing mngon par bstod pas
NK127(jo)001:10855: bstod de mchod pa sna tshogs kyis mchod par byas
NK127(jo)001:10856: nas chos nyan pa'i phyir spyan sngar 'dug go //
NK127(jo)001:10857: de nas 'khor rnams kyis mchod pa'i tshogs kyis sa'i snying po la mchod cing btud do //
NK127(jo)001:10858: de'i tshe 'khor de'i nang na byang chub sems dpa'
NK127(jo)001:10859: chen po rigs par the tshom 'dri zhes bya bas
NK127(jo)001:10860: bcom ldan 'das la btud nas 'di skad ces gsol
NK127(jo)001:10861: to // bcom ldan rigs kyi bu 'di gang nas mchis /
NK127(jo)001:10862: zhing 'di nas ji srid cig na gnas /
NK127(jo)001:10863: yon tan dang dge ba'i rtsa ba ji tsam dang
NK127(jo)001:10864: ldan na bcom ldan 'das kyis bstod pa sna tshogs
NK127(jo)001:10865: kyis basngagasa la phyir yang bcom ldan 'das kyi yon
NK127(jo)001:10866: tan rgya mtsho bsam gyis mi khyab pa la 'dis
NK127(jo)001:10868: bdag gis sngon ma mthong bas ngo mtshar du gyur
NK127(jo)001:10869: na bcom ldan 'das kyis bdag la bshad du gsol
NK127(jo)001:10870: / bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
NK127(jo)001:10872: skyes bu chen po 'di'i yon tan dang dge ba'i
NK127(jo)001:10873: rtsa ba ci tsam de 'jig rten du bcas pa
NK127(jo)001:10874: lha dang mi'i 'khor thams cad kyis rtogs par nus
NK127(jo)001:10876: gal te de bzhin gshegs pas skyes bu chen po
NK127(jo)001:10877: de'i yon tan dang dge rtsa rgyas par bshad na
NK127(jo)001:10878: lha dang mir bcas pa'i 'jig rten thams cad mgo
NK127(jo)001:10879: rmongs te yid mi ches par 'gyur ro //
NK127(jo)001:10880: de nas byang chub sems dpa' rigs par the tshom
NK127(jo)001:10881: 'dri bas slar yang nan tan gyis gsol pa btab
NK127(jo)001:10882: pa dang / bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
NK127(jo)001:10883: legs par nyon la yid la zungs shig dang ngas khyod la phyogs tsam bshad par bya'o //
NK127(jo)001:10884: ji ltar skyes bu chen po de yon tan gyi
NK127(jo)001:10885: khyad par tshad med bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang
NK127(jo)001:10886: ldan te / 'di ltar dpa' bar 'gro ba'i ting
NK127(jo)001:10887: nge 'dzin gyi khyad par la bde bar gnas shing
NK127(jo)001:10888: de bzhin gshegs pa'i spyod yul yang shin tu rtogs
NK127(jo)001:10889: ldan te / par 'jug pa'o // mi skye ba'i
NK127(jo)001:10890: chos kyi bzod pa'i khyad par thob cing sangs rgyas
NK127(jo)001:10891: kyi chos thams cad la dbang du gyur pa'o //
NK127(jo)001:10892: thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyi sa la bzod
NK127(jo)001:10893: pa thob cing thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyi
NK127(jo)001:10894: rgya mtsho'i pha rol tu phyin pa'o //
NK127(jo)001:10895: seng ge rab tu bsgyings pa'i rgyal mtshan gyi ting
NK127(jo)001:10896: nge 'dzin la shin tu gnas shing thams cad mkhyen
NK127(jo)001:10897: pa'i ye shes kyi ri la rab tu 'dzegs pa'o
NK127(jo)001:10898: // mu stegs can dang phas kyi rgol ba thams cad shin tu choms pa ste /
NK127(jo)001:10899: sems can thams cad yongs su smin par bya ba'i
NK127(jo)001:10900: phyir sangs rgyas kyi zhing ji snyed pa thams cad
NK127(jo)001:10901: du de gnas par byed de /
NK127(jo)001:10902: skyes bu chen po de ji ltar gnas pa bzhin
NK127(jo)001:10903: du sangs rgyas kyi zhing rnams kyang de bzhin du
NK127(jo)001:10904: 'gyur te / gal te ye shes mngon par skyed
NK127(jo)001:10905: pa zhes bya ba'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par
NK127(jo)001:10906: 'gyur te / zhugs na / ting nge 'dzin de'i
NK127(jo)001:10907: mthus sangs rgyas kyi zhing de na gnas pa'i sems
NK127(jo)001:10908: can thams cad mthun par ting nge 'dzin rnams kyi
NK127(jo)001:10909: spyod yul kun mthong bar 'gyur ro //
NK127(jo)001:10910: de ji ltar gnas pa bzhin du sangs rgyas kyi zhing rnams kyang de bzhin du 'gyur ro //
NK127(jo)001:10911: gal te dpag tu med pa'i ye shes dang ldan
NK127(jo)001:10912: pa zhes bya ba'i ting nge 'dzin la zhugs na
NK127(jo)001:10913: / zhing de'i sems can thams cad kyis tshad med
NK127(jo)001:10914: pa'i mchod pa'i dam pas sangs rgyas bcom ldan bcom
NK127(jo)001:10915: ldan 'das la bsti stang dang bcas pas mchod par
NK127(jo)001:10916: / 'gyur ro // de bzhin du rnam par dag
NK127(jo)001:10917: pa'i ye shes phun sum tshogs pa zhes bya ba
NK127(jo)001:10918: / 'gyur ro // dang / khrel ba dang ngo
NK127(jo)001:10919: tsha ba dang ldan pa'i ye shes zhes bya ba
NK127(jo)001:10921: thams cad dang ldan pa gsal ba zhes bya ba
NK127(jo)001:10922: la sogs pa'i ting nge 'dzin tha dad pa dag
NK127(jo)001:10924: de ji ltar gnas pa bzhin du zhing de'i sems can thams cad kyang de bzhin du 'gyur te /
NK127(jo)001:10925: spyod yul gyi nyes pa mthong nas sems rnam par dag pa thob pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:10926: lhag pa'i 'dzem pa dang ldan pas mi dge ba'i
NK127(jo)001:10927: chos dang bral nas bsam pa mi nyams pa dang
NK127(jo)001:10928: / thabs mkhas pa'i rdzu 'phrul gyi mig la sogs pa'i mngon shes thob pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:10929: mya ngan dang yi mug rmugs pa thams cad bral ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:10930: mun pa dang bral te phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas mngon sum mthong ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:10931: log lta spangs nas sangs rgyas la skyabs su 'gro ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:10932: zhing de'i ri dang gcong rong sogs dang dug dang
NK127(jo)001:10933: gcan gzan sogs skyon thams cad med par sa gzhi
NK127(jo)001:10934: mnyam zhing mtshan ma bzang po du mas brgyan par
NK127(jo)001:10935: 'gyur ba dang / bdud kyi rgyal po 'khor bcas
NK127(jo)001:10936: skrag nas mchog gsum la skyabs su 'gro ba dang
NK127(jo)001:10937: 'gyur ba dang / / sems can rnams 'jig rten
NK127(jo)001:10938: pha rol gyi 'jigs pa dang bral zhing chos kyis
NK127(jo)001:10939: 'gyur ba dang / / spro ba dang / sems
NK127(jo)001:10940: can rnams bsam pa bzhin du zas skom 'tshal zhing
NK127(jo)001:10941: stobs dang ldan la nad thams cad bral ba dang
NK127(jo)001:10943: ji ltar mos pa bzhin khri stan dang gos rgyan
NK127(jo)001:10944: sogs yo byad yid du 'ong ba thams cad dang
NK127(jo)001:10946: ldan pa dang / lus sems bde zhing dgra dang
NK127(jo)001:10947: bcing ba med la 'dums zhing spro ba dang phar
NK127(jo)001:10949: rab tu dga' ba tshad med pa dang thogs pa
NK127(jo)001:10950: med pa'i ye shes dang ldan la dbang po tshang
NK127(jo)001:10951: zhing mi nyams pa thob pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:10952: mi dge ba'i chos la skyo zhing dge ba bcu
NK127(jo)001:10953: dang yang dag par 'byung ba'i lam gyis sems rab
NK127(jo)001:10955: snying rje'i sems kyis gcig la gcig phan par byed cing /
NK127(jo)001:10956: 'thab rtsod dang nad mug bral te /
NK127(jo)001:10957: dus min gyi rlung dang char sogs sdug bsngal ba'i reg bya thams cad zhi bar 'gyur ro //
NK127(jo)001:10958: de ltar ting nge 'dzin so so la zhugs pa'i
NK127(jo)001:10959: tshe yon tan sna tshogs pa de ltar byed do
NK127(jo)001:10960: // gal te rgya mtsho glog 'od ces bya ba'i
NK127(jo)001:10961: ting nge 'dzin la zhugs na de'i mthus sangs rgyas
NK127(jo)001:10962: kyi zhing de'i sa chen po thams cad rin chen
NK127(jo)001:10963: sna tshogs las byas pa nyes pa'i skyon thams cad
NK127(jo)001:10964: bral zhing rin po che'i shing dang rgyan dang rol
NK127(jo)001:10965: mo la sogs pa 'tsho ba'i yo byad dam pa
NK127(jo)001:10966: tshad med pa snyed kyis brgyan par 'gyur ro //
NK127(jo)001:10967: de bzhin du mdor na rigs kyi bu de ni
NK127(jo)001:10968: sems can mang po smin pa'i phyir nyin re zhing
NK127(jo)001:10969: snga dro'i dus su ting nge 'dzin gang g+aa'i klung
NK127(jo)001:10970: gi bye ma snyed la snyoms par zhugs te /
NK127(jo)001:10971: de las langs nas phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas kyi zhing
NK127(jo)001:10972: kun na 'dul ba'i sems can thams cad la ci
NK127(jo)001:10973: dang cis 'dul ba bzhin phan ba de'i don de
NK127(jo)001:10974: dang de dag gis yongs su smin par byed do
NK127(jo)001:10975: // rigs kyi bu 'di ni sngon bskal pa chen
NK127(jo)001:10976: po tshad dpag tu med pa'i bar du rnyogs pa
NK127(jo)001:10977: lnga'i tshe de bzhin gshegs pa ma bzhugs pa'i 'jig
NK127(jo)001:10978: rten gyi khams su sems can yongs su smin par
NK127(jo)001:10979: // byed do // phyi ma ma 'ongs pa'i dus
NK127(jo)001:10980: su 'jig rten gyi khams la lar mtshon gyi 'jigs
NK127(jo)001:10981: pa byung ste sems can yongs su gdung bar gyur
NK127(jo)001:10982: pa de lta bu mthong nas /
NK127(jo)001:10983: rigs kyi bu 'di snga dro'i dus kyi tshe ting
NK127(jo)001:10984: nge 'dzin rnams kyi mthus 'jigs pa de dag yongs
NK127(jo)001:10985: su bcil nas sems can rnams phan tshun byams pa'i
NK127(jo)001:10987: de bzhin du nad kyi 'jigs pa dang mu ge'i
NK127(jo)001:10988: 'jigs pa byung ba'i tshe yang sdug bsngal de thams
NK127(jo)001:10990: rigs kyi bu 'dis de ltar ting nge 'dzin mang
NK127(jo)001:10991: po'i shugs kyis tshad med dpag tu med bsam gyis
NK127(jo)001:10992: mi khyab pa'i phan pa dang bde bas sems can
NK127(jo)001:10994: 'dis sngon 'das pa'i dus na sangs rgyas bcom ldan
NK127(jo)001:10995: 'das tshad med grangs med pa gang g+aa'i klung gi
NK127(jo)001:10996: bye ma snyed las sems can thams cad skyob pa'i
NK127(jo)001:10997: don du zad mi shes pa'i yi dam chen po
NK127(jo)001:10998: bcas te / snying rje chen po dang mi 'phrog
NK127(jo)001:10999: pa'i brtson 'grus rab tu bskyed cing de gong nas
NK127(jo)001:11000: gong du 'phel ba'i shugs kyi skad cig tsam gyis
NK127(jo)001:11001: kyang so so'i skye bo tshad med pa bye ba
