NK127(jo)001:11002: khrag khrig btul te sdug bsngal sna tshogs las bsgral
NK127(jo)001:11003: nas ci dang ci 'dod pa dag gis re ba
NK127(jo)001:11004: yongs su rdzogs par byed do //
NK127(jo)001:11005: gnas gang dag na sems can 'dod pa sna tshogs
NK127(jo)001:11006: kyis sdug bsngal te 'dod pas gdung bar gyur pa
NK127(jo)001:11007: dag gis / sems rtse gcig tu byang sems sa'i
NK127(jo)001:11008: snying po'i mtshan nas brjod cing dmigs pas bsti stangs
NK127(jo)001:11009: dang bcas te mchod pa byas na /
NK127(jo)001:11010: ci dang ci 'dod pa thams cad thob pas sdug
NK127(jo)001:11011: bsngal dang bral te skal ba ji lta ba bzhin
NK127(jo)001:11012: du mtho ris kyi lhar skye ba nas mya ngan
NK127(jo)001:11013: las 'das pa'i bar du 'thob par 'gyur ro //
NK127(jo)001:11015: bza' btung dang 'go ba dang rgyan la sogs pas
NK127(jo)001:11016: phongs pas gsol ba btab na ci 'dod pa 'byor
NK127(jo)001:11017: zhing mya ngan las 'das pa'i bar du thob pa
NK127(jo)001:11018: dang / byams sdug dang bral zhing dgra sdang ba dang phrad pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:11019: lus sems nad dang sdug bsngal gyis gzir ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:11020: 'thab cing rtsod par gyur pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:11022: brdegs shing btsogs la gsod pa la thug pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:11023: lus sems dub cing mthu stobs dang mi ldan la nyam chung ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:11024: dbang po nyams shing ma tshang ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:11025: myos shing sems 'khrugs la 'byung po'i gdon gyis brlabs pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:11026: chags sdang sogs nyon mongs pa sna tshogs kyi lus sems gdungs te mi 'pho bar gyur pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:11027: me chu rlung dang g.yang sar lhung ba la sogs pa'i 'jigs pas sems bsdangs shing 'khum pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:11028: sbrul gdug pa dang gcan gzan dang dug sna tshogs kyis zin pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:11029: 'byung po'i gdon gyis btab ste rtag pa'i rims la
NK127(jo)001:11030: sogs pa rims sna tshogs kyis 'dar zhing dran pa
NK127(jo)001:11031: nyams pa dang / gnod sbyin srin po sogs mi
NK127(jo)001:11032: dang mi ma yin pa dang gcan gzan khro bo
NK127(jo)001:11033: dang sngags dang byad dang g.yul ngor lhags pa gzhan
NK127(jo)001:11034: yang 'jigs pa rnam pa sna tshogs kyis dkris te
NK127(jo)001:11035: lus sems gdung bar gyur pa na de dag gis
NK127(jo)001:11036: nyams pa dang / / sa'i snying po'i mtshan brjod
NK127(jo)001:11037: cing mchod na mi bde ba de dag thams cad
NK127(jo)001:11038: dang myur du bral nas yid la ji ltar re
NK127(jo)001:11039: ba'i bde ba thob par byed do //
NK127(jo)001:11040: gang dag mang du thos pa dang mos pa dang
NK127(jo)001:11041: tshul khrims dang bsam gtan dang mngon shes dang shes
NK127(jo)001:11042: rab dang rnam par grol ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:11043: gzugs dam pa la sogs pa'i 'dod yon lnga dang /
NK127(jo)001:11044: khe dang rnyed pa'am grags pa bsod nams dang bzos 'tsho ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:11045: me tog dang 'bras bu dang skyed tshal dang khri
NK127(jo)001:11046: stan dang gding ba dang nor dang 'bru dang nad
NK127(jo)001:11047: kyi rkyen sman dang yul rgyu bar 'dod pa dang
NK127(jo)001:11048: / khang khyim bran khol tshon rtsi char pa chu
NK127(jo)001:11049: dang lo tog dro ba dang bsil ba bsil yab
NK127(jo)001:11050: dang rlung bsil ba me dang bzhon pa bu dang
NK127(jo)001:11052: gang zhig thabs mkhas pa'am bsod nams bya ba dang yid gzhungs par 'dod pa'am /
NK127(jo)001:11053: de ma yin pa gzhan 'jig rten dang 'jig rten
NK127(jo)001:11054: las 'das pa'i don gyi dngos po rnam pa sna
NK127(jo)001:11055: tshogs la 'dod pa'i phyir re zhing gdung ba de
NK127(jo)001:11056: dag gis / sems rtse gcig tu byang chub sems
NK127(jo)001:11057: dpa' sa'i snying po'i mtshan brjod cing dmigs pas bsti
NK127(jo)001:11058: stang dang bcas te mchod pa byas na /
NK127(jo)001:11059: rigs kyi bu de'i ting nge 'dzin dam pa'i yon
NK127(jo)001:11060: tan dang mthu dang gzi brjid kyi shugs kyi de
NK127(jo)001:11061: dag thams cad sdug bsngal gyi gdung ba dang bral
NK127(jo)001:11062: te / re ba thams cad yongs su rdzogs nas
NK127(jo)001:11063: skal ba ji lta ba bzhin du mtho ris kyi
NK127(jo)001:11064: lhar skye ba nas mya ngan las 'das pa'i bar
NK127(jo)001:11066: gnas gang na zhing gshim pa'am mi gshim pa la
NK127(jo)001:11067: sa bon btab nas nan tan byas kyang rung ma
NK127(jo)001:11069: sems rtse gcig pas sa'i snying po'i mtshan brjod cing
NK127(jo)001:11070: mchod pa byas na de'i lo thog legs shing 'bras
NK127(jo)001:11073: rigs kyi bu 'di ni sngon bskal pa chen po
NK127(jo)001:11074: tshad med grangs med pa'i bar du sangs rgyas tshad
NK127(jo)001:11075: med grangs med pa dag la brtson 'grus chen po'i
NK127(jo)001:11076: sbyor ba dang brtan pa'i yi dam bcas pa'i smon
NK127(jo)001:11077: lam gyi dbang gis sems can yongs su smin pa'i
NK127(jo)001:11078: phyir / rtag tu sa chen po thams cad yongs
NK127(jo)001:11079: su 'dzin pa dang rtag tu sa bon gyi tshogs
NK127(jo)001:11080: thams cad yongs su 'dzin cing rtag tu sems can
NK127(jo)001:11081: thams cad kyi yid bzhin du spyod par byed do
NK127(jo)001:11082: phyir / // rigs kyi bu de'i rdzu 'phrul gyi
NK127(jo)001:11083: mthus sa chen po 'di las skye ba'i rtsa shing
NK127(jo)001:11084: myu gu la sogs pa rgyas par skye zhing 'bras
NK127(jo)001:11085: bu smin te grungs la mngar zhing snum pa dang
NK127(jo)001:11087: yang sems can gang dag dug gsum po drag la
NK127(jo)001:11088: rno bas mi dge bcu'i las lam mngon du spyod
NK127(jo)001:11089: pa dag gis sa'i snying po'i mtshan nas brjod na
NK127(jo)001:11090: nyon mongs pa zhi zhing mi dge ba'i lam dang
NK127(jo)001:11091: bral te dge ba'i las dang ldan zhing byams pa
NK127(jo)001:11092: dang snying rje dang phan pa dang bde ba'i sems
NK127(jo)001:11094: de ltar rigs kyi bu 'di de lta bu'i yon
NK127(jo)001:11095: tan dam pa dang ting nge 'dzin dang mthu dang
NK127(jo)001:11096: gzi brjid kyi shugs dang shin tu brtson pa'i ting
NK127(jo)001:11097: nge 'dzin gyis skad cig thang cig tu sangs rgyas
NK127(jo)001:11098: kyi zhing tshad med grangs med par phyin nas /
NK127(jo)001:11099: zhing de re rer yang skad cig la sems can
NK127(jo)001:11100: tshad med grangs med gang g+aa'i klung gi bye ma
NK127(jo)001:11101: snyed sdug bsngal las bsgral nas bde ba thob par
NK127(jo)001:11102: byas te mya ngan las 'das pa'i bar du thob
NK127(jo)001:11103: par byed do // de ltar rigs kyi bu de
NK127(jo)001:11104: ni yon tan dang smon lam brtan pa dang shin
NK127(jo)001:11105: tu 'bad pa'i brtson 'grus bsam gyis mi khyab pa
NK127(jo)001:11106: par byed do // dang ldan te / sems can
NK127(jo)001:11107: yongs su smin pa'i phyir phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten gyi
NK127(jo)001:11108: khams su kha cig la ni tshangs pa chen po'i
NK127(jo)001:11109: rgyal po'i lus kyis cis 'dul ba'i chos ston to
NK127(jo)001:11110: par byed do // dang ldan te / // de bzhin du dbang phyug chen po dang /
NK127(jo)001:11111: 'dod pa'i khams kyi gzhan sprul dbang byed la sogs pa'i lha'i ris drug gi gzugs dang /
NK127(jo)001:11112: sangs rgyas dang byang sems dang nyan rang dang 'khor los sgyur ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:11113: rgyal rigs la sogs pa rigs bzhi dang /
NK127(jo)001:11114: skyes pa dang bud med dang khye'u dang bu mo'i gzugs dang /
NK127(jo)001:11115: dri za dang lha ma yin dang gnod sbyin dang /
NK127(jo)001:11116: mi ma yin pa ji snyed pa'i gzugs dang /
NK127(jo)001:11117: seng ge dang rta dang khyu mchog dang glang po
NK127(jo)001:11118: la sogs pa'i dud 'gro rnam pa sna tshogs dang
NK127(jo)001:11119: / yi dwags dang gshin rje dang dmyal ba'i srung
NK127(jo)001:11120: ma dang dmyal ba pa'i sems can gyi lus kyi
NK127(jo)001:11121: bar gyi lus rnam pa sna tshogs tshad med grangs
NK127(jo)001:11122: med pa'i gzugs kyis skye bo mang po la skal
NK127(jo)001:11123: ba ji lta ba bzhin du chos bstan pas theg
NK127(jo)001:11124: pa gsum las phyir mi ldog pa'i sa la 'dzud
NK127(jo)001:11125: / par byed do // rigs kyi bu skyes bu
NK127(jo)001:11126: chen po de ni de ltar bsam gyis mi khyab
NK127(jo)001:11127: pa'i yon tan dang ldan te de ni yon tan
NK127(jo)001:11128: mchog tu gyur pa dang phul du gyur pa'i gter
NK127(jo)001:11129: / par byed do // yin no // rnam par
NK127(jo)001:11130: grol ba rin po che thams cad kyi 'byung gnas
NK127(jo)001:11131: / par byed do // yin no // yin no
NK127(jo)001:11132: // byang chub sems dpa' mang po'i mig yongs su
NK127(jo)001:11134: mya ngan las 'das pa'i grong khyer du 'gro ba'i ded dpon yin no //
NK127(jo)001:11135: de ltar ched du ma byas par gong du rgyas
NK127(jo)001:11136: par bshad pa'i yon tan chen po las chos kyi
NK127(jo)001:11137: 'khor lo chen po rab tu bskor ba yin no
NK127(jo)001:11139: rigs kyi bu gal te 'ga' zhig gis byams pa'am /
NK127(jo)001:11141: kun tu spyan ras gzigs sam /
NK127(jo)001:11142: kun tu bzang po la sogs pa byang chub sems
NK127(jo)001:11143: dpa' sems dpa' chen po gang g+aa'i klung gi bye
NK127(jo)001:11144: ma snyed la bskal pa brgya'i bar du sems rtse
NK127(jo)001:11145: gcig pas skyabs su song ste de dag gi mtshan
NK127(jo)001:11146: nas brjod cing dmigs pas bsti stang dang bcas pas
NK127(jo)001:11147: mchod cing phyag 'tshal ba dang 'dod pa'i re ba'i
NK127(jo)001:11148: phyir smon lam btab pa bas /
NK127(jo)001:11149: 'ga' zhig gis skad cig thang cig yud tsam cig
NK127(jo)001:11150: tu sems rtse gcig pas byang chub sems dpa' sems
NK127(jo)001:11151: dpa' chen po sa yi snying po'i mtshan nas brjod
NK127(jo)001:11152: cing dmigs pas bsti stang dang bcas pas mchod pa
NK127(jo)001:11153: dang phyag byas na re ba'i smon lam thams cad
NK127(jo)001:11154: myur du 'grub cing rdzogs par 'gyur ro //
NK127(jo)001:11156: byang chub sems dpa' chen po sa'i snying po 'di
NK127(jo)001:11157: ni sems can thams cad la phan pa dang bde
NK127(jo)001:11159: sems can rnams kyi smon lam gang yin pa yongs
NK127(jo)001:11160: su rdzoogs par byed pa dper na yid bzhin gyi
NK127(jo)001:11161: nor bu rin po che'i gter dang 'dra'o //
NK127(jo)001:11162: de ltar skyes bu chen po 'di ni sems can
NK127(jo)001:11163: yongs su smin par bya ba'i phyir yun ring po
NK127(jo)001:11164: nas smon lam chen po shin tu brtan pa dang
NK127(jo)001:11165: snying rje chen po dang shin tu 'bad pa'i brtson
NK127(jo)001:11167: byang chub sems dpa' kun las khyad par du 'phags
NK127(jo)001:11168: pa yin pas khyed kyis bsti stang dang bcas pas
NK127(jo)001:11169: mchod par bya'o // zhes gsungs pas /
NK127(jo)001:11170: phyogs bcu nas 'dus pa'i byang chub sems dpa' chen po rnams dang /
NK127(jo)001:11171: nyan thos dang lha la sogs pa 'khor 'dus pa chen po thams cad stan las langs te /
NK127(jo)001:11172: so so nas rin po che'i me tog la sogs
NK127(jo)001:11173: pa mchod pa'i rnam pa tshad med pa dag bstod
NK127(jo)001:11174: pa'i dbyangs dang bcas pas byang chub sems dpa' sa
NK127(jo)001:11175: yi snying po la bsti stang dang bcas pas mchod
NK127(jo)001:11176: pa byas so // sa'i snying pos kyang rnam pa
NK127(jo)001:11177: sna tshogs pa'i lha rdzas kyi mchod pa'i yo byad
NK127(jo)001:11178: de rnams bcom ldan 'das la phul nas tshigs su
NK127(jo)001:11180: lha dang klu dang gnod sbyin mi rnams dang //
NK127(jo)001:11181: phyogs bcu'i byang chub sems dpa'i mchod pa rnams //
NK127(jo)001:11182: yon tan chen po 'jig rten gtso la 'bul //
NK127(jo)001:11183: mchog gi mchod pa 'di dag bzhes su gsol //
NK127(jo)001:11184: zhes byas nas bcom ldan 'das kyi zhabs la spyi bos phyag 'tshal ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:11185: bcom ldan 'das kyis tshigs su bcad de bka' stsal pa /
NK127(jo)001:11186: brtan pa'i blo dang rnam dag sems bskyed nas //
NK127(jo)001:11187: sems can tshad med pa yi sdug bsngal bcil //
NK127(jo)001:11188: rin chen dag ltar bde ba 'byung bar mthong //
NK127(jo)001:11189: rdo rje bzhin du the tshom d+r+wa ba gcod //
NK127(jo)001:11190: snying rje chen po'i blo can brtson 'grus kyis //
NK127(jo)001:11191: mchod pa dam pa bcom ldan 'das la dbul //
NK127(jo)001:11192: rgya mtsho ye shes sems can sdug bsngal sgrol //
NK127(jo)001:11193: 'jigs pa med pas srid pa'i pha rol phyin //
NK127(jo)001:11195: de nas byang chub sems dpa' sa'i snying po stan las langs te bcom ldan 'das la gsol pa /
NK127(jo)001:11196: bdag gis bcom ldan 'das kyi nye gnas 'khor bzhi la sogs pa'i dran pa 'phel ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:11197: 'tsho ba dang lus bde ba dang gzugs dang stobs
NK127(jo)001:11198: dang grags pa dang dge ba'i rtsa ba dang lam
NK127(jo)001:11199: 'bras dang yo byad thams cad dang /
NK127(jo)001:11200: slob ma dang phar phyin sogs 'phel zhing bkra shis
NK127(jo)001:11201: pa'i slad du thos pa 'dzin pa'i rig sngags chen
NK127(jo)001:11202: po'i gzungs kyi tshigs sangs rgyas tshad med pa las
NK127(jo)001:11204: phan yon tshad med pa dang ldan pa'i gzungs smras
NK127(jo)001:11205: pa'i mod la ri kha la te ya rab tu
NK127(jo)001:11206: g.yos nas lta'i rol mo bye ba mang po ma
NK127(jo)001:11208: lha'i spos dang me tog dang rin po che tshad
NK127(jo)001:11209: med pa char bzhin babs pas 'khor mang po de
NK127(jo)001:11210: dag ngo mtshar rmad du gyur ro //
NK127(jo)001:11211: de'i tshe 'khor de na lha mo bkra shis chen mo dang /
NK127(jo)001:11212: dpal ldan lha mo chen mo sogs 'byung ba chen
NK127(jo)001:11213: po bzhi la dbang du gyur pa stong phrag bco
NK127(jo)001:11214: brgyad 'dug pa ni stan las langs nas bcom ldan
NK127(jo)001:11215: 'das kyi zhabs la phyag 'tshal te gsol pa /
NK127(jo)001:11217: bde bar gshegs pa bdag gis 'byung ba chen po
NK127(jo)001:11218: bzhi la dbang bsgyur mod kyi 'byung ba bzhi'i thog
NK127(jo)001:11219: ma dang bar ma dang tha ma'i skye ba dang
NK127(jo)001:11220: 'gags pa dang mthun pa dang mi mthun pa'i phyogs
NK127(jo)001:11221: mi 'tshal te / skyes bu chen po 'di ni
NK127(jo)001:11222: shes rab kyi phar phyin phra ba shin tu zab
NK127(jo)001:11223: mo thob pas 'byung ba bzhi'i thog mtha' bar gyi
NK127(jo)001:11224: mtshan nyid dang skye 'gags dang mthun pa dang mi
NK127(jo)001:11225: mthun pa'i phyogs la shin tu mkhas so //
NK127(jo)001:11227: yid bzhin gyi nor bu rin po che ni yon
NK127(jo)001:11228: tan mang po dang ldan pas rin chen sna tshogs
NK127(jo)001:11229: char bzhin babs nas sems can mang po la sbyin
NK127(jo)001:11230: pa de bzhin du rigs kyi bu 'di yang byang
NK127(jo)001:11231: chub yan lag gi rin po che sna tshogs char
NK127(jo)001:11232: bzhin 'bebs te sems can rnams la sbyin no //
NK127(jo)001:11234: rin po che'i gling ni rin po che rnam pa
NK127(jo)001:11235: sna tshogs kyis yongs su gang ba bzhin du rigs
NK127(jo)001:11236: kyi bu 'di yang byang chub kyi yan lag gi
NK127(jo)001:11237: rin po che sna tshogs dang ldan no //
NK127(jo)001:11238: 'di lta ste lha rdzas kyi shing pa ri tsi
NK127(jo)001:11239: tra la bsung dang me tog gis mdzes pa bzhin
NK127(jo)001:11240: du rigs kyi bu 'di yang sangs rgyas kyi chos
NK127(jo)001:11241: rin po che rnam pa sna tshogs kyis rab tu
NK127(jo)001:11242: mdzes so // 'di lta ste seng ge'i rgyal po
NK127(jo)001:11243: ni ri dwags thams cad kyi zil gyis mi non
NK127(jo)001:11244: cing mi skrag pa bzhin du rigs kyi bu 'di
NK127(jo)001:11245: yang sems can thams cad kyis bag tsha ba'am zil
NK127(jo)001:11247: 'di lta ste ji ltar nyi ma gsal bas 'jig
NK127(jo)001:11248: rten gyi mun pa thams cad yongs su sel ba
NK127(jo)001:11249: bzhin du rigs kyi bu 'di yang ngan par lta
NK127(jo)001:11250: ba'i ma rig pa'i mun pa thams cad sel ba'o
NK127(jo)001:11251: // 'di lta ste nam mkha'i zla ba ni mtshan
NK127(jo)001:11252: mo'i dus su lam stor ba'i sems can thams cad
NK127(jo)001:11253: la bde ba'i lam ston te gang dga' bar 'gro
NK127(jo)001:11254: ba phyin par 'gyur ba bzhin du rigs kyi bu
NK127(jo)001:11255: 'di yang ma rig pa'i mtshan mor theg pa gsum
NK127(jo)001:11256: las phyogs bslad de 'khor ba'i 'brog dgon par 'khyams
NK127(jo)001:11257: pa'i sems can thams cad la theg pa gsum gyis
NK127(jo)001:11258: yang dag pa'i lam ston cing skal pa ji lta
NK127(jo)001:11259: ba bzhin du thabs kyis yang dag par 'byung ba'i
NK127(jo)001:11261: 'di lta ste sa chen po ni sa bon gyi
NK127(jo)001:11262: tshogs thams cad dang rtsi shing lo thog dang sa'i
NK127(jo)001:11263: khams su gtogs pa'i sems can thams cad kyi rten
NK127(jo)001:11264: du gyur pa ltar rigs kyi bu 'di la yang
NK127(jo)001:11265: byang chub kyi yan lag khyad par can gyi chos
NK127(jo)001:11266: thams cad rten cing gnas so //
NK127(jo)001:11267: 'di lta ste rin po che chen po'i ri rab
NK127(jo)001:11268: ri'i rgyal po ni shin tu brtan zhing ma god
NK127(jo)001:11269: ma nyams pa bzhin du rigs kyi bu 'di yang
NK127(jo)001:11270: sangs rgyas kyi ma 'dres pa'i chos thams cad la
NK127(jo)001:11271: shin tu gnas shing sems can thams cad mi gtong
NK127(jo)001:11272: ba'i phyir mi nyams pa dang dge ba'i rtsa ba
NK127(jo)001:11273: thams cad la gtong ba'i phyir ma god pa'o //
NK127(jo)001:11274: 'di lta ste nam mkha' la sems can thams cad
NK127(jo)001:11275: spyod pa bzhin du rigs kyi bu 'di yang sems
NK127(jo)001:11276: can thams cad de la longs spyod do //
NK127(jo)001:11277: rigs kyi bu 'di ni de ltar yon tan tshad med dpag tu med pa dang ldan no //
NK127(jo)001:11278: zhes gsungs pas 'khor rnams kyis byang chub sems dpa'
NK127(jo)001:11279: sa'i snying po'i yon tan tshad med pa'i basngagasa pa
NK127(jo)001:11280: thos nas ngo mtshar rmad du gyur te bkur sti
NK127(jo)001:11281: dang rim gro byas nas rab tu dga' bas sems
NK127(jo)001:11282: rtse gcig tu byang chub sems dpa' sa'i snying po
NK127(jo)001:11284: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis don de gsal bar bzlas pa'i phyir bka' stsal pa /
NK127(jo)001:11285: skyes bu yang dag sa yi snying po ni //
NK127(jo)001:11286: yon tan mang po phun sum tshogs par ldan //
NK127(jo)001:11287: dge sbyong cha lugs 'dzin zhing ston byed pa //
NK127(jo)001:11288: ston pa chen po la ni phyag 'tshal lhags //
NK127(jo)001:11289: zhes sogs sngar gsungs pa'i yon tan gyi khyad par rnams slar yang tshigs su bcad pas gsung zhing /
NK127(jo)001:11290: gal te bskal pa mang po brgya yi bar //
NK127(jo)001:11291: de yi yon tan basngagasa shing rab bstod des //
NK127(jo)001:11292: mthar phyin rdzogs par 'gyur ba shin tu dka' //
NK127(jo)001:11293: de bas kun gyis bsti stang bcas pas mchod //
NK127(jo)001:11295: de nas byang chub sems dpa' chen po sa'i snying
NK127(jo)001:11296: pos bcom ldan 'das la rnyogs pa lnga'i 'jig rten
NK127(jo)001:11297: du thugs rje chen pos chos kyi 'khor lo ji
NK127(jo)001:11298: lta bur bskor ba sogs dam pa'i chos kyi bka'
NK127(jo)001:11300: bde bar gshegs pas 'khor lo chen po bcu'i tshul
NK127(jo)001:11301: gyis chos bstan pas sems can tshad grangs med dpag
NK127(jo)001:11302: tu med pa'i don byas shing /
NK127(jo)001:11303: byang chub sems dpa' nam mkha'i snying po la chos
NK127(jo)001:11304: de gtad nas de 'dzin pa rnams la nor nyams
NK127(jo)001:11305: pa dang / gnod pa thams cad dang mi dge
NK127(jo)001:11306: ba'i las dang 'phya skur sogs nyes pa bcu las
NK127(jo)001:11307: srung ba'i chos rnam pa bcus srung bar gyis zhes
NK127(jo)001:11308: gdams par mdzad pa na des kyang de bzhin du
NK127(jo)001:11310: rgyal ba'i myu gu sa yi snying po'i rtogs pa brjod pa'i skabs te drug pa'o ////
NK127(jo)001:11311: byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po sgrib pa
NK127(jo)001:11312: thams cad rnam par sel ba la phyag 'tshal lo
NK127(jo)001:11314: byang chub sems dpa' chen po 'di ni bsam gyis
NK127(jo)001:11315: mi khyab pa'i rnam par thar pa la gnas pa
NK127(jo)001:11316: ste / sangs rgyas 'gro ba zhes bya ba theg pa chen po'i mdo las gsungs pa /
NK127(jo)001:11317: shar phyogs 'jig rten gyi khams kun tu 'od ces
NK127(jo)001:11318: bya ba na de bzhin gshegs pa 'jug srid kyi
NK127(jo)001:11319: rgyal po'i sangs rgyas kyi zhing du phyogs bcu'i sangs
NK127(jo)001:11320: rgyas gang g+aa'i klung gi bye ma snyed 'dus nas
NK127(jo)001:11321: chos kyi rnam grangs 'gro bar mdzad pa na /
NK127(jo)001:11322: der 'agro'o snyam du 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa
NK127(jo)001:11323: mi mjed 'di nas zhing der skad cig gis dong
NK127(jo)001:11324: ba dang / de bzhin gshegs pa de'i g.yas phyogs
NK127(jo)001:11325: na sring mo the tshom sel ba zhes bya ba
NK127(jo)001:11326: skyil krung du 'dug cing kun tu zla ba'i 'od
NK127(jo)001:11327: dri ma med par snang ba zhes bya ba'i ting
NK127(jo)001:11328: nge 'dzin la mnyam par bzhag par gyur to //
NK127(jo)001:11329: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa 'jug sred kyi rgyal
NK127(jo)001:11330: pos sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa'i spyod yul
NK127(jo)001:11331: bsam gyis mi khyab pa bstan pa sogs kyi dgos
NK127(jo)001:11332: pa'i dbang gis 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa ri
NK127(jo)001:11333: khor yug gi rtse mor ma tshor bar 'phangs so
NK127(jo)001:11334: // de nas 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pas rang
NK127(jo)001:11335: gi rdzu 'phrul gyi stobs bskyed de phyogs bcu'i sangs
NK127(jo)001:11336: rgyas kyi zhing mu med par song yang sangs rgyas
NK127(jo)001:11337: kyi 'khor der skra'i rtse mo'i cha tsam yang 'gro
NK127(jo)001:11338: ma nus nas slar der 'dug ste yid la mi
NK127(jo)001:11339: byed pa'i dran pa nye bar bzhag pa la gnas
NK127(jo)001:11340: shing chos bstan pas lha'i bu bzhi khri nyis stong
NK127(jo)001:11341: mi skye ba'i chos la bzod pa thob par byas
NK127(jo)001:11342: // so // de nas sangs rgyas 'gro ba zin
NK127(jo)001:11343: nas de bzhin gshegs pa 'jug sred kyi rgyal po'i
NK127(jo)001:11344: phyag g.yas pa'i mthil nas 'od byung bas 'jam dpal
NK127(jo)001:11345: bskul te zhing der phyin cing de bzhin gshegs pa
NK127(jo)001:11347: bdag ni 'khor de las phyir phyungs shing sring mo
NK127(jo)001:11348: 'di ni ma 'phangs na 'di ni dge ba'i rtsa
NK127(jo)001:11350: 'dis ji srid cig nas sems bskyed cing ting 'dzin 'di thob ces zhus pa la /
NK127(jo)001:11351: de bzhin gshegs pa des bka' stsal pa /
NK127(jo)001:11352: 'jam dpal sring mo 'di ni ting nge 'dzin 'di
NK127(jo)001:11353: la gnas pas 'du shes dang yid la byed pa
NK127(jo)001:11354: thams cad bral ba'i tshul gyis phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas
NK127(jo)001:11355: grangs med pa mthong zhing chos nyan te gzhan la
NK127(jo)001:11356: ston kyang 'du shes cung zad kyang med do //
NK127(jo)001:11357: bskal pa'i bar du brjod kyang 'di'i yon tan mi zad do //
NK127(jo)001:11358: 'jam dpal khyod kyis sring mo 'di ting 'dzin 'di las slongs la dri ba dris shig gsungs pas /
NK127(jo)001:11359: 'jam dpal gyis de bslang bar 'dod pas se gol tha mal pa'i sgra dang /
NK127(jo)001:11360: phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten mu med par thos pa'i se gol gyi sgra dang /
NK127(jo)001:11361: stong chen po'i 'jig rten khams kyi sil snyan thams cad rang 'khrol bar gyur pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:11362: sprul pa'i sil snyan tshad med pa'i sgras phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten mu med par khyab pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:11363: 'jig rten khams kyi ri thams cad thal mo brdab
NK127(jo)001:11364: pa bzhin du phan tshun 'thab pa'i sgra 'jigs su
NK127(jo)001:11365: rung bas 'jig rten mu med pa bkang yang slong
NK127(jo)001:11366: ma nus so // de nas byin gyis brlabs pa'i
NK127(jo)001:11367: stobs kyis sring mo de'i lag pa nas drangs te
NK127(jo)001:11368: bskyod pas 'og phyogs kyi zhing grangs med pa g.yo
NK127(jo)001:11369: bar byas kyang ting nge 'dzin de las skra rtse
NK127(jo)001:11370: tsam yang g.yo ma nus la /
NK127(jo)001:11371: shugs kyis bteg pas zhing tshad med par gyen du 'phangs pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:11372: yang sring mo de gnas pa'i phyogs khor yug dang
NK127(jo)001:11373: bcas pa lag mthil g.yas par bzhag ste tshangs pa'i
NK127(jo)001:11374: 'jig rten gyi bar du 'phangs nas slar bzhag pa
NK127(jo)001:11375: dang / sring mo de lag pa g.yas par bzhag
NK127(jo)001:11376: nas shar la sogs pa phyogs bcu re re zhing
NK127(jo)001:11377: sangs rgyas kyi zhing gang g+aa'i klung gi bye ma
NK127(jo)001:11378: snyed du song ste sil snyan dang ri'i sgra de
NK127(jo)001:11379: dag 'byin cing me tog gi char phabs kyang ting
NK127(jo)001:11380: nge 'dzin de las bslang ma nus nas slar 'khor
NK127(jo)001:11381: dang / der 'dug go // 'jam dpal gyi rdzu
NK127(jo)001:11382: 'phrul de dag gis phyogs bcu po thams cad du
NK127(jo)001:11383: sems can tshad med grangs med pa yongs su smin
NK127(jo)001:11384: dang / der 'dug go // par byas so //
NK127(jo)001:11385: de nas 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pas de bzhin
NK127(jo)001:11386: gshegs pa de la byang chub sems dpa'i spyod pa
NK127(jo)001:11387: ngo mtshar che'o zhes gsol pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:11389: de de bzhin te byang chub sems dpa'i spyod yul bsam gyis mi khyab bo //
NK127(jo)001:11390: yongs su brtag pa bzung na stong chen po'i 'jig
NK127(jo)001:11391: rten gyi khams gnyis rnga bo cher gyur pa skyes
NK127(jo)001:11392: bu stobs dang ldan pas stong gcig gi 'jig rten
NK127(jo)001:11393: dang mnyam pa'i dbyu gus bskal pa las lhag par
NK127(jo)001:11394: sring mo 'di'i mdun du brdungs kyang sgra de rna
NK127(jo)001:11395: bar grags par yang mi 'gyur na slong bar ga
NK127(jo)001:11400: byang chub sems dpa' chen po sgrib pa thams cad
NK127(jo)001:11401: rnam par sel ba ma gtogs par gzhan gang gis
NK127(jo)001:11403: byang chub sems dpa' chen po 'di'i mtshan brjod pa
NK127(jo)001:11404: tsam gyis sa chen po rnam pa drug tu g.yos
NK127(jo)001:11405: shing de'i mtshan brjod na zhing gzhan du yang sa
NK127(jo)001:11408: byang chub sems dpa' chen po de da lta gang na bzhugs /
NK127(jo)001:11409: 'dir 'ongs nas mthong ba dang sring mo 'di yang
NK127(jo)001:11410: ting nge 'dzin las slong bar 'tshal zhes zhus pa
NK127(jo)001:11411: dang / 'og phyogs gang g+aa'i klung gi bye ma
NK127(jo)001:11412: snyed kyi sangs rgyas kyi zhing 'das pa na 'jig
NK127(jo)001:11413: rten khams sna tshogs kyi rgyal mtshan zhes bya ba
NK127(jo)001:11414: dang / der / de bzhin gshegs pa seng ge
NK127(jo)001:11415: dang ngang pa dang ba glang gi phung po'i sgra
NK127(jo)001:11416: bsgrags pa zhes bya ba'i drung na 'dug pa'i sgrib
NK127(jo)001:11417: pa thams cad rnam par sel ba de sangs rgyas
NK127(jo)001:11418: 'od kyis bskul bas 'khor byang chub sems dpa' lnga
NK127(jo)001:11419: 'bum dang bcas pa skad cig gis 'ongs shing de
NK127(jo)001:11420: bzhin gshegs pa'i zhabs la phyag byas nas steng gi
NK127(jo)001:11421: bar snang la 'dug ste lus thams cad sun 'byin
NK127(jo)001:11422: pa zhes bya ba'i ting nge 'dzin la mnyam par
NK127(jo)001:11423: bzhag nas me tog gi char 'bebs pa sogs rdzu
NK127(jo)001:11425: 'khor rnams dang 'jam dpal gyis de'i lus ma mthong
NK127(jo)001:11426: ba ni ting nge 'dzin de lta bu'i mathu'o zhes
NK127(jo)001:11427: de bzhin gshegs pas gsungs pa las /
NK127(jo)001:11428: ting nge 'dzin bsgrub par bya'o snyam du 'jam dpal
NK127(jo)001:11429: gyis bsams pa de sgrib pa thams cad rnam par
NK127(jo)001:11430: sel bas shes nas 'di skad du /
NK127(jo)001:11431: ting nge 'dzin 'di ni gcig pur ma zad de
NK127(jo)001:11432: rgya mtsho chen po'i chu'i thigs pa bzhin du lus
NK127(jo)001:11433: sun 'byin pa'i ting nge 'dzin de snyed la bdag
NK127(jo)001:11434: 'jug ldang byed pa de'i ming tsam yang khyod kyis
NK127(jo)001:11435: mi shes so zhes sgra thos pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:11436: byang chub sems dpa' gzhan gyis bskal pa bye ba
NK127(jo)001:11437: khrag khrig gis kyang 'grub par dka' ba'i ting nge
NK127(jo)001:11438: 'dzin de 'jam dpal gyis se gol gtogs pa gcig
NK127(jo)001:11439: tsam gyis bsgrub par byas so //
NK127(jo)001:11440: de nas 'jam dpal gyis byang chub sems dpa' de
NK127(jo)001:11441: mthong bar mdzod ces de bzhin gshegs pa la gsol
NK127(jo)001:11442: ba na / sangs rgyas kyi bkas byang chub sems
NK127(jo)001:11443: dpa' chen po sgrib pa thams cad rnam par sel
NK127(jo)001:11444: ba 'khor dang bcas pa'i lus snang bar byas pa
NK127(jo)001:11445: ba na / dang / sgrib pa thams cad rnam
NK127(jo)001:11446: par sel ba de la 'jam dpal gyis sring mo
NK127(jo)001:11447: 'di ting 'dzin las slongs shig ces smras pas /
NK127(jo)001:11448: sgrib pa rnam sel gyis bdag gis 'di slong nus
NK127(jo)001:11449: mod kyi 'on kyang de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad
NK127(jo)001:11450: mkhyen pa nyid kyis bslang bar 'tshal zhes zhus pa
NK127(jo)001:11451: dang / de bzhin gshegs pa 'jug sred kyi rgyal
NK127(jo)001:11452: po ting nge 'dzin gyi sems las ldang byed ces
NK127(jo)001:11453: bya ba'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs pas
NK127(jo)001:11455: gzhan yang 'jig rten der mnyam par bzhag pa ji snyed pa'ang langs par mdzad do //
NK127(jo)001:11456: de nas sring mo de la 'jam dpal gyis khyod
NK127(jo)001:11457: ji srid cig nas byang chub tu sems bskyed pa
NK127(jo)001:11459: brjod du med pa'i don las brtsams te shin tu
NK127(jo)001:11460: zab pa'i chos bshad pa'i spobs pa la ngo mtshar
NK127(jo)001:11461: du gyur nas / 'jam dpal gyis de bzhin gshegs pa la gsol pa /
NK127(jo)001:11462: bcom ldan 'das sring mo 'dis ci tsam nas sems bskyed pa lags zhes sogs zhus pa la /
NK127(jo)001:11464: sring mo 'dis byang chub kyi phyir spyad nas bskal
NK127(jo)001:11465: pa grangs med pa bye ba khrag khrig brgya stong
NK127(jo)001:11466: phrag dgu bcu rtsa dgu 'das pa'i 'og tu 'jam
NK127(jo)001:11467: dpal khyod kyis byang chub tu sems bskyed do //
NK127(jo)001:11468: 'dis dang por de bzhin gshegs pa dgon mchog 'byung ba'i drung du sems bskyed do //
NK127(jo)001:11469: sangs rgyas de'i zhing gi yon tan bkod pa de
NK127(jo)001:11470: dag bskal pa gang g+aa'i klung gi bye ma snyed
NK127(jo)001:11471: du bshad kyang cha tsam du bshad mi nus so
NK127(jo)001:11472: // de'i tshe sring mo 'di 'khor los sgyur ba'i
NK127(jo)001:11473: rgyal po sgra dang bral ba zhes bya bar gyur
NK127(jo)001:11475: 'di la bud med ces mi bya ste sgyu ma'i
NK127(jo)001:11476: ting 'dzin thob pas ji ltar 'dod par lus sprul
NK127(jo)001:11477: par byed do // sring mo 'di ni stong chen
NK127(jo)001:11478: po'i 'jig rten gyi khams na rdul dang yal 'dab
NK127(jo)001:11479: ji snyed yod pa de snyed kyi bskal pa grangs
NK127(jo)001:11480: med pa brgya phrag stong gis bla med byang chub
NK127(jo)001:11482: kun tu snang ba sbyin pa zhes bya ba'i de
NK127(jo)001:11483: bzhin gshegs par 'gyur zhing de'i zhing ni de bzhin
NK127(jo)001:11484: gshegs pa dkon mchog 'byung ba'i zhing ji 'dra bar
NK127(jo)001:11485: 'gyur ro // de nas sgrib pa thams cad rnam par sel bas 'di skad du /
NK127(jo)001:11486: 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa 'di ni da dung
NK127(jo)001:11487: bgyid pa dang bgyi ba mang ste 'das pa dang
NK127(jo)001:11488: ma 'ongs pa'i chos rnams la'ang rnam par rtog par
NK127(jo)001:11489: bgyid do // 'jam dpal gyis smras pa /
NK127(jo)001:11490: rigs kyi bu de de bzhin te bdag ni byed
NK127(jo)001:11491: pa mang la de dag ni chos kyi dbyings mi
NK127(jo)001:11492: zad pa'i phyir byed pa mi zad par 'gyur ro
NK127(jo)001:11493: // de bzhin gshegs pa 'jug sred kyi rgyal pos bka' stsal pa /
NK127(jo)001:11494: 'jam dpal khyod 'di dang ma rtsod cig /
NK127(jo)001:11495: sgrib pa thams cad rnam par sel ba 'di ni
NK127(jo)001:11496: spobs pa bsam gyis mi khyab ste 'di'i ting nge
NK127(jo)001:11497: 'dzin gyi ming tsam yang khyod kyis mi shes so
NK127(jo)001:11498: // stong chen po'i 'jig rten khams kyi sems can
NK127(jo)001:11499: ji snyed pa 'jam dpal dang 'dra bar gyur du
NK127(jo)001:11500: zin kyang des sring mo 'di'i ting nge 'dzin la
NK127(jo)001:11501: 'jug ldang gi ming yang mi shes pas de'i ting
NK127(jo)001:11502: 'dzin dang rnam 'phrul dang cho 'phrul dang ye shes
NK127(jo)001:11503: kyi brgya phrag stong gi char yang mi phod do
NK127(jo)001:11504: // // stong chen po'i 'jig rten khoms kyi sems
NK127(jo)001:11505: can ji snyed yod pa ting 'dzin dang ye shes
NK127(jo)001:11506: kyi mthu sring mo 'di 'dra bar gyur kyang des
NK127(jo)001:11507: byang chub sems dpa' chen po sgrib pa thams cad
NK127(jo)001:11508: rnam par sel ba'i ting 'dzin dang ye shes dang
NK127(jo)001:11509: stobs dang rnam par 'phrul pa'i brgya phrag stong gi
NK127(jo)001:11511: sgrib pa thams cad rnam par sel ba de gang
NK127(jo)001:11512: la 'jug ldang byed pa'i ting nge 'dzin de'i ming
NK127(jo)001:11513: tsam yang sring mo 'dis mi shes so //
NK127(jo)001:11514: gal te sems can thams cad ting nge 'dzin dang
NK127(jo)001:11515: ye shes mnyam par bzhag pas sgrib pa thams cad
NK127(jo)001:11516: rnam par sel ba dang 'dra bar gyur kyang des
NK127(jo)001:11517: de bzhin gshegs pa'i gom pa 'dor 'jog tsam mi
NK127(jo)001:11518: shes te de ltar sangs rgyas kyi ye shes ni
NK127(jo)001:11520: sring mo 'dis 'jam dpal byang chub tu sems bskyed
NK127(jo)001:11521: du bcug la 'jam dpal ci 'dra ba'i byang chub
NK127(jo)001:11522: sems dpa'i gang g+aa'i klung gi bye ma snyed phyogs
NK127(jo)001:11523: bcu re re zhing yang sems bskyed du bcug pa
NK127(jo)001:11524: dag yod do // sgrib pa thams cad rnam par
NK127(jo)001:11525: sel bas sring mo 'di byang chub tu sems bskyed
NK127(jo)001:11526: du bcug ste sring mo 'di ji 'dra ba'i byang
NK127(jo)001:11527: chub sems dpa' gang g+aa'i klung gi bye ma snyed
NK127(jo)001:11528: cig phyogs bcu re re bzhin du yang sems bskyed
NK127(jo)001:11529: dag yod do // du bcug go // nga yang
NK127(jo)001:11530: 'das pa'i dus na de bzhin gshegs pa ri rab
NK127(jo)001:11531: rgyal mtshan gyi gsung rab las sgrib pa thams cad
NK127(jo)001:11532: rnam par sel bas bla med byang chub tu sems
NK127(jo)001:11534: nga ji 'dra ba'i de bzhin gshegs pa gang g+aa'i
NK127(jo)001:11535: klung gi bye ma snyed phyogs bcur yang sems bskyed
NK127(jo)001:11536: du bcug ste de dag da ltar bzhugs shing 'tsho
NK127(jo)001:11537: gzhes la / dpag tu med pa dag kyang yongs su mya ngan las 'das so //
NK127(jo)001:11538: bud med gang gis sring mo the tshom sel ba de'am /
NK127(jo)001:11539: byang chub sems dpa' sgrib pa thams cad rnam par sel ba'am /
NK127(jo)001:11540: de bzhin gshegs pa 'jug sred kyi rgyal po'i mtshan
NK127(jo)001:11541: thos na de nyid de'i lus kyi tha mar 'gyur
NK127(jo)001:11542: te bla med byang chub tu myur bar 'tshang rgya'o
NK127(jo)001:11543: // tshe 'phos nas kyang sangs rgyas 'byung pa mnyes par byed pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:11544: mi khom pa brgyad spong pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:11547: skyes bu chen po'i mtshan sum cu rtsa gnyis thob pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:11548: mngal du mi gnas par 'gyur te /
NK127(jo)001:11549: de dag gis bdag cag gi ming thos pa'i bud
NK127(jo)001:11550: med gang dag yon tan 'di lta bu dang ldan
NK127(jo)001:11551: par gyur cig ces smon lam btab pa'i phyir ro
NK127(jo)001:11553: 'phags pa dkon mchog sprin zhes bya ba theg pa chen po'i mdo las /
NK127(jo)001:11554: bcom ldan 'das ga ya ma go'i ri la nyan
NK127(jo)001:11555: thos dang byang chub sems dpa'i dge 'dun la sogs
NK127(jo)001:11556: thams cad dang ldan pa'i 'khor gyi tshogs mang pos
NK127(jo)001:11558: bcom ldan 'das kyi dbu'i gtsug nas 'od zer snang
NK127(jo)001:11559: ba zhes bya bas phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten khyab par
NK127(jo)001:11560: byas te bcom ldan 'das kyi zhal gyi sgor zhugs
NK127(jo)001:11561: so // de'i tshe shar phyogs su sangs rgyas kyi
NK127(jo)001:11562: zhing 'di nas 'jig rten gyi khams gang g+aa'i klung
NK127(jo)001:11563: gi bye ma snyed 'das pa na /
NK127(jo)001:11564: pad+ma can zhes bya ba'i 'jig rten gyi khams na bde bar gshegs pa pad+ma'i sprin zhes bya bas /
NK127(jo)001:11565: theg pa gsum gyi ming yang med par theg pa gcig las brtsams te chos ston la /
NK127(jo)001:11566: zhing de'i sems can thams cad rdzogs pa'i byang chub
NK127(jo)001:11567: las phyir mi ldog pa'i byang chub sems dpa' sha
NK127(jo)001:11568: stag go // 'jig rten gyi khams de na byang
NK127(jo)001:11569: chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po sgrib pa thams
NK127(jo)001:11570: cad rnam par sel ba zhes bya ba de'i ming
NK127(jo)001:11571: thos pa tsam gyis sems can rnams kyi sgrib pa
NK127(jo)001:11572: thams cad zad par 'gyur ba zhig gnas te /
NK127(jo)001:11573: de 'od zer des reg nas bskul bas rang gi
NK127(jo)001:11574: gnas nas phyungs te bcom ldan 'das pad+ma'i spyan ga
NK127(jo)001:11575: la ba der song nas 'di lta bu'i 'od zer
NK127(jo)001:11576: yid du 'ong ba lus sems sim par byed pa
NK127(jo)001:11577: 'di su'i mthu lags zhes zhus pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:11579: rigs kyi bu 'di nas nub phyogs su mi mjed
NK127(jo)001:11580: ces bya ba'i 'jig rten gyi khams na de bzhin
NK127(jo)001:11581: gshegs pa sh+aakya thub pa zhes bya ba de'i mtshan
NK127(jo)001:11582: thos pa tsam gyis sems can rnams bla na med
NK127(jo)001:11583: pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub las phyir
NK127(jo)001:11584: mi ldog par 'gyur ba zhig bzhugs te des 'od
NK127(jo)001:11585: 'di btang ngo // sgrib pa thams cad rnam par sel bas gsol ba /
NK127(jo)001:11586: bcom ldan 'das bdag mi mjed der de bzhin gshegs
NK127(jo)001:11587: pa de la phyag bya ba dang mchod pa bgyi
NK127(jo)001:11588: ba'i slad du mchi'o zhes zhus pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:11589: byang chub sems dpa' gzhan 'od kyis bskul ba de dag gis kyang de bzhin gsol ba la /
NK127(jo)001:11590: de bzhin gshegs pa des bka' stsal pa /
NK127(jo)001:11591: rigs kyi bu dag de'i dus la bab par shes
NK127(jo)001:11592: na khyed dengs shig /'jig rten gyi khams der bag
NK127(jo)001:11593: yod par gnas par gyis shig /
NK127(jo)001:11595: 'jig rten de'i sems can rnams ni nyon mongs pa mang ba /
NK127(jo)001:11596: pha la phar mi 'dzin pa sogs dang /
NK127(jo)001:11597: chos min 'dod pa mang ba sogs ngan pa'i ngang
NK127(jo)001:11598: tshul can de 'dra ba dag gi nang na de
NK127(jo)001:11599: bzhin gshegs pa de chos ston to //
NK127(jo)001:11600: byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyis gsol pa /
NK127(jo)001:11601: bcom ldan 'das gang 'di 'dra ba'i sems can rnams
NK127(jo)001:11602: kyi nang na chos ston pa ni de bzhin gshegs
NK127(jo)001:11603: pa de dka' ba mdzad pa lags so //
NK127(jo)001:11606: gang de ltar kun nas nyon mongs pa'i 'jig rten
NK127(jo)001:11607: gyi khams na dge sems gcig bskyed pa yang dka'
NK127(jo)001:11609: gang yongs su dag pa'i 'jig rten na sems can dag pa yod pa lta ci mtshar gyi /
NK127(jo)001:11610: 'jig rten gyi khams nyon mongs can der se gol gtogs pa srid du dad pa rnyed pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:11611: mchog gsum la skyabs su 'gro ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:11613: chags bral gyi sems dang snying rje'i sems kyis bla
NK127(jo)001:11614: na med pa'i byang chub tu sems bskyed pa 'di
NK127(jo)001:11615: ni ches ngo mtshar ro zhes gsungs shing /
NK127(jo)001:11616: byang chub sems dpa' rnams mchod pa'i bkod pa du ma dang bcas nas zhing 'dir lhags so //
NK127(jo)001:11617: der byang chub sems dpa' sgrib pa thams cad rnam par sel bas 'khor kun la smras pa /
NK127(jo)001:11618: grogs po dag mi mjed kyi 'jig rten de'i sems can rnams ni sdug bsngal ba yin no //
NK127(jo)001:11619: des na sems can de dag la bde ba mchog
NK127(jo)001:11620: gis bstab par 'gyur ba'i rdzu 'phrul mngon par 'du
NK127(jo)001:11621: bya ba legs par mngon no zhes smras pa la
NK127(jo)001:11622: / 'khor gyi byang sems de kun gyis legs so zhes smras nas de ltar mnyan no //
NK127(jo)001:11623: de nas byang chub sems dpa' chen po sgrib pa
NK127(jo)001:11624: thams cad rnam par sel bas rdzu 'phrul mngon par
NK127(jo)001:11625: 'du bya bas rang gi lus las 'od dwang ba
NK127(jo)001:11626: dri ma med pa rnam par dag cing yid du
NK127(jo)001:11627: 'ong ba lus sems shin tu dga' bar byed pa
NK127(jo)001:11628: byung ste / 'od des stong gsum gyi stong chen
NK127(jo)001:11629: po'i 'jig rten gyi khams kun khyab cing snang bar
NK127(jo)001:11630: gyur pas sems can dmyal ba dang byol song dang
NK127(jo)001:11631: gshin rje'i 'jig rten pa'i lus su gnas pa de
NK127(jo)001:11632: dag 'od des reg pas sdug bsngal gyi tshor ba
NK127(jo)001:11633: thams cad dang bral te bde zhing /
NK127(jo)001:11634: khro ba dang gnod sems dang yang bral nas phan tshun pha mar 'du shes par gyur pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:11635: 'jig rten gyi khams 'di'i bar gyi mun pa mun
NK127(jo)001:11636: nag gang dag nyi zla'i 'od kyis gsal bar ma
NK127(jo)001:11637: gyur pa thams cad khyab nas snang bar gyur te
NK127(jo)001:11638: der skyes pa gcig gis gcig mthong bar gyur pa
NK127(jo)001:11639: dang / stong chen po'i 'jig rten 'di'i khor yug
NK127(jo)001:11640: la sogs pa'i ri gang dag yod pa'ang 'od des
NK127(jo)001:11642: steng du tshangs pa'i 'jig rten dang 'og tu mnar
NK127(jo)001:11643: med pa'i sems can yan chad 'od des snang bar
NK127(jo)001:11644: ma byas pa gang yang med pa de lta bu'i
NK127(jo)001:11646: 'khor gyi sems dpa' de dag gis rdzu 'phrul mngon par 'du byas pas /
NK127(jo)001:11647: sems can rnams zas gos nor sogs 'dod pa ji snyed pa dag tshim par byas /
NK127(jo)001:11648: dbang po ma tshang ba thams cad dbang po thob /
NK127(jo)001:11649: smyos pa rnams dran pa rnyed pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:11650: sdug bsngal ba rnams bde bar gyur /
NK127(jo)001:11651: sbrum ma rnams bde bar btsa' ba de lta bu byas so //
NK127(jo)001:11652: de nas sgrib pa thams cad rnam par sel ba
NK127(jo)001:11653: la sogs pa'i byang chub sems dpa' de dag ga
NK127(jo)001:11654: ya mgo'i ri ga la ba der nye ba dang
NK127(jo)001:11655: / stong gsum gyi stong chen po'i 'jig rten gyi
NK127(jo)001:11656: khams 'di rin po che'i d+r+wa bas khebs par snang
NK127(jo)001:11657: / ba dang / steng gi bar snang las kyang lha'i pad+ma'i char dang me tog gi char dang /
NK127(jo)001:11658: lha'i shing thog gi sprin rnams dang /
NK127(jo)001:11659: de bzhin du lha rdzas kyi phreng ba dang spos
NK127(jo)001:11660: dang gos dang phye ma dang chos gos dang gdugs
NK127(jo)001:11661: dang rgyal mtshan dang ba dan gyi sprin chen po'i
NK127(jo)001:11662: char rab tu babs pas sems can gang la reg
NK127(jo)001:11663: pa de thams cad bde bar gyur cing /
NK127(jo)001:11664: ga ya mgo'i ri la shing tha mal ba dang
NK127(jo)001:11665: sa phyogs tha mal pa gang yod pa thams cad
NK127(jo)001:11666: mi snang bar gyur nas sa phyogs de dag na
NK127(jo)001:11672: a ga ru'i shing rnams kun tu snang ste kun tu bzang por snang bar gyur to //
NK127(jo)001:11673: bar snang las lha'i sil snyan dag sgra 'byin cing sil snyan de dag las 'di ltar /
NK127(jo)001:11674: lum pi'i tshal rab mchog tu gang skyes pa //
NK127(jo)001:11675: mnyam med gzhar yang nyon mongs dbang mi 'gyur //
NK127(jo)001:11676: nam mkha' mtshungs mnyam de la phyag 'tshal du //
NK127(jo)001:11677: ri bo mchog rab 'di la bdag cag lhags //
NK127(jo)001:11678: byang chub mchog sus byang chub shing dbang drung //
NK127(jo)001:11679: bdud kyi sde stobs bcom nas sangs rgyas pa //
NK127(jo)001:11680: dri med gzi ldan de la phyag 'tshal du //
NK127(jo)001:11681: ri bo mchog rab 'di la bdag cag lhag /
NK127(jo)001:11682: chos tshul 'di dag sgyu ma smig rgyu dang //
NK127(jo)001:11683: chu zla 'dra bar gang gis rtogs gyur pa //
NK127(jo)001:11684: bsod nams zhing rab de la phyag 'tshal du //
NK127(jo)001:11685: ri bo mchog rab 'di la bdag cag lhags //
NK127(jo)001:11686: zhes pa la sogs pa'i tshigs su bcad pa de
NK127(jo)001:11687: dag byung ma thag tu moo gal gyi bu chen
NK127(jo)001:11688: po stan las langs te bcom ldan 'das la thal
NK127(jo)001:11689: mo sbyar bas btud nas 'di skad ces gsol to
NK127(jo)001:11690: // bcom ldan 'das sngon ma thos ma mthong ba'i snga ltas gda' ba 'di su'i lags /
NK127(jo)001:11692: 'di nas shar phyogs su 'jig rten gyi khams gang
NK127(jo)001:11693: g+aa'i klung gi bye ma snyed 'das pa na 'jig
NK127(jo)001:11694: rten gyi khams pad+ma can zhes bya ba der de
NK127(jo)001:11695: bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom pa yang dag par rdzogs
NK127(jo)001:11696: pa'i sangs rgyas pad+ma'i spyan zhes bya ba'i drung nas
NK127(jo)001:11697: / byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po sgrib
NK127(jo)001:11698: pa thams cad rnam par sel ba zhes bya ba
NK127(jo)001:11699: byang chub sems dpa' bye ba khrag khrig brgya stong
NK127(jo)001:11700: dang bcas te mi mjed 'dir 'ong ba de dag
NK127(jo)001:11701: gi snga ltas so zhes bka' stsal ma thag tu
NK127(jo)001:11702: / / byang chub sems dpa' chen po sgrib pa
NK127(jo)001:11703: thams cad rnam par sel ba 'khor dang bcas pa
NK127(jo)001:11704: byang chub sems dpa'i rdzu 'phrul gyi mthu chen pos
NK127(jo)001:11705: bcom ldan 'das kyi spyan sngar phyin te phyag 'tshal
NK127(jo)001:11706: / / nas / grags chen shes rab chen po pa //
NK127(jo)001:11707: thub chen dpa' bo chen po pa //
NK127(jo)001:11708: srid pa'i mya ngan rgal ba po //
NK127(jo)001:11709: nyon mongs brgal la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK127(jo)001:11710: thams cad du yang tha le ste //
NK127(jo)001:11711: kun nas rab tu lhang nger bzhugs //
NK127(jo)001:11712: kun nas rnam par grol ba po //
NK127(jo)001:11713: phyag 'tshal mi mtshungs mtshungs med la //
NK127(jo)001:11714: rab tu mi sgul ri bo bzhin //
NK127(jo)001:11715: gting tshod yangs pa rgya mtsho 'dra //
NK127(jo)001:11716: mu stegs kun nas mi bskyod pa //
NK127(jo)001:11717: chos rgyal khyod la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK127(jo)001:11718: chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba na //
NK127(jo)001:11719: gzod nas zhi zhing ma skyes pa //
NK127(jo)001:11720: rang bzhin mya ngan 'das pa yi //
NK127(jo)001:11721: chos rnams mgon po khyod kyis bstan //
NK127(jo)001:11722: zhes pa la sogs pa tshigs su bcad pas mngon par bstod nas pad+ma'i snying po la 'khod do //
NK127(jo)001:11723: de nas byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po
NK127(jo)001:11724: sgrib pa thams cad rnam par sel ba stan las
NK127(jo)001:11725: langs te bla gos phrag pa gcig tu gzar nas
NK127(jo)001:11726: pus mo g.yas pa'i lha nga pad+ma'i snying po la
NK127(jo)001:11727: btsugs te / bcom ldan 'das ga la ba de
NK127(jo)001:11728: logs su thal mo sbyar bas btud nas 'di skad
NK127(jo)001:11729: btsugs te / ces / bcom ldan 'das kyis skabs
NK127(jo)001:11730: phye na bdag rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas la phyogs 'ga'
NK127(jo)001:11731: zhig zhu'o zhes gsol ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:11732: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
NK127(jo)001:11733: skyes bu dam pa khyod la de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis rtag tu skabs phyes kyi /
NK127(jo)001:11734: de bzhin gshegs pa la ci 'dod pa dris shig
NK127(jo)001:11735: dang dri ba de lung bstan pas ngas khyod kyi
NK127(jo)001:11737: sgrib pa thams cad rnam par sel bas gsol pa /
NK127(jo)001:11738: bcom ldan 'das ji ltar na byang chub sems dpa'i
NK127(jo)001:11739: sbyin pa phun sum tshogs pa nas ye shes kyi
NK127(jo)001:11740: bar phun sum tshogs pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:11741: ji ltar na byang chub sems dpa' sa dang mtshungs pa la sogs pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:11742: rgya che ba dang rnam par dag pa la sogs
NK127(jo)001:11743: pa rdzogs pa'i byang chub tu mngon par rdzogs par
NK127(jo)001:11744: 'tshang rgya ba'i bar gyi theg pa chen po'i don
NK127(jo)001:11746: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das kyis don de dag re
NK127(jo)001:11747: rer yang chos bcu'i sgo nas rgya cher gtan la
NK127(jo)001:11748: phab ste gsungs pas sems can gyi tshogs tshad med
NK127(jo)001:11749: grangs med pa yongs su dag cing smin par gyur
NK127(jo)001:11750: to // rgyal sras sgrib pa rnam sel gyi rtogs pa brjod pa'i skabs te bdun pa'o ////
NK127(jo)001:11751: byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po kun tu bzang po la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK127(jo)001:11753: sangs rgyas phal po che zhes pa shin tu rgyas pa'i sde snod las gsungs pa /
NK127(jo)001:11754: de la byang chub sems dpa' kun tu bzang po'i rnam par thar pa ni /
NK127(jo)001:11755: tshul rgya mtsho bsam gyis mi khyab pas de bzhin
NK127(jo)001:11756: gshegs pa'i yon tan rgya mtsho la 'jug pa ste
NK127(jo)001:11757: / 'di ltar sangs rgyas kyi zhing thams cad yongs
NK127(jo)001:11758: su dag par bya ba dang 'gro ba 'dul ba
NK127(jo)001:11759: la mthar thug par mngon par sgrub pa zhes bya
NK127(jo)001:11760: ba'i rnam par thar pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:11761: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi zhabs kyi drung
NK127(jo)001:11762: du phyin pas yon tan gyi tshogs thams cad kyi
NK127(jo)001:11763: yul zhes bya ba'i rnam par thar pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:11764: byang chub sems dpa' thams cad kyi sa nas sar
NK127(jo)001:11765: smon lam rgya mtshos rab tu gnas pa 'byung ba
NK127(jo)001:11766: zhes bya ba'i rnam par thar pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:11767: sgo thams cad nas chos kyi dbyings su bdag gi
NK127(jo)001:11768: lus kyi sprin rdul snyed mtha' yas pas rgyas par
NK127(jo)001:11769: 'gengs pa zhes bya ba'i rnam par thar pa dang
NK127(jo)001:11770: / zhing thams cad du rang gi ming bsam gyis
NK127(jo)001:11771: mi khyab pa'i 'khor lo sgrogs pa'i byin gyi rlabs
NK127(jo)001:11772: zhes bya ba'i rnam par thar pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:11773: rdul shin tu phra ba thams cad kyi sbubs su
NK127(jo)001:11774: byang chub sems dpa'i yul dang rnam par 'phrul pa
NK127(jo)001:11775: mtha' dang dbus med par yang dag par ston pa
NK127(jo)001:11776: zhes bya ba'i rnam par thar pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:11777: dus gsum gyi bskal pa skad cig gcig cig tu
NK127(jo)001:11778: ston pas 'byung ba dang 'jig pa rab tu 'byung
NK127(jo)001:11779: ba zhes bya ba'i rnam par thar pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:11780: byang chub sems dpa' thams cad kyi dbang po rgya
NK127(jo)001:11781: mtsho'i yul phan tshun du 'jug pa yang dag par
NK127(jo)001:11782: ston pa zhes bya ba'i rnam par thar pa dang
NK127(jo)001:11783: / gang 'di chos kyi dbyings mtha' dang dbus med
NK127(jo)001:11784: pa rang gi lus kyi sprul pas rgyas par rnam
NK127(jo)001:11785: par 'phrul pa'i byin gyi rlabs zhes bya ba'i rnam
NK127(jo)001:11787: gang 'di byang chub sems dpa'i chos thams cad kyi
NK127(jo)001:11788: tshul phan tshun du ston pa rgya chen pos thams
NK127(jo)001:11789: cad mkhyen pa nyid kyi tshul la 'jug pa zhes
NK127(jo)001:11790: bya ba'i rnam par thar pa dang ldan pa'o //
NK127(jo)001:11791: de nas bcom ldan 'das rnam par snang mdzad kyi
NK127(jo)001:11792: spyan sngar seng ge'i khri pad+ma'i snying po can la
NK127(jo)001:11793: byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po kun tu
NK127(jo)001:11795: sangs rgyas thams cad de bzhin gshegs pa rnam par
NK127(jo)001:11796: snang mdzad kyi sku'i snying po zhes bya ba'i ting
NK127(jo)001:11797: nge 'dzin mnyam pa nyid kyi rjes su song bas
NK127(jo)001:11798: chos kyi dbyings kyis klas par khyab cing yon tan
NK127(jo)001:11799: bsam gyis mi khyab pa la snyoms par zhugs pa
NK127(jo)001:11800: de bzhin du / chos kyi dbyings nam mkha'i mtha'
NK127(jo)001:11801: klas pa'i phyogs rgya mtsho'i zhing thams cad kyi rdul
NK127(jo)001:11802: phra rab re re'i khongs su zhing rgya mtsho'i rdul
NK127(jo)001:11803: snyed kyi sangs rgyas re re'i drung du yang de
NK127(jo)001:11804: ltar lus rdul snyed kyis mnyam par bzhag go //
NK127(jo)001:11805: de'i tshe phyogs bcu'i zhing 'byams klas pa'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis zhal bstan te /
NK127(jo)001:11806: rigs kyi bu khyod de lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin la mnyam par bzhag pa legs so //
NK127(jo)001:11807: rigs kyi bu khyod la sangs rgyas rnam par snang
NK127(jo)001:11808: mdzad kyi sngon gyi smon lam gyi byin gyi rlabs
NK127(jo)001:11809: dang / khyod kyi smon lam dang spyod pa yongs su dag pa'i mthus /
NK127(jo)001:11810: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis kyang sangs rgyas
NK127(jo)001:11811: kyi spyod yul bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i stobs la
NK127(jo)001:11812: 'jug pa'i phyir ye shes tshad med pas byin gyis
NK127(jo)001:11813: brlabs so zhes phyag gser gyi mdog can kun tu
NK127(jo)001:11814: bzang po'i spyi bor bzhag go //
NK127(jo)001:11815: 'dir ji lta bar zhing khams rgya mtsho bsam gyis mi khyab pa kun tu'ang de bzhin te /
NK127(jo)001:11816: kun tu bzang po la de bzhin gshegs pa'i phyag
NK127(jo)001:11817: rgya mtsho'i sprin rnams spyi bor bzhag ma thag tu
NK127(jo)001:11818: / ting nge 'dzin de las ldang ba'i sgo rgya
NK127(jo)001:11819: mtsho 'jig rten gyi khams rgya mtsho'i rdul phra ba
NK127(jo)001:11820: snyed bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i sgo sna tshogs dang
NK127(jo)001:11821: ldan pa'i sgo nas ting nge 'dzin de las langs
NK127(jo)001:11822: / so // de'i de ma thag tu byang chub
NK127(jo)001:11823: sems dpa' de dag kyang ting nge 'dzin dang gzungs
NK127(jo)001:11824: la sogs pa tshad med pa'i yon tan gyi sgo
NK127(jo)001:11825: 'jig rten gyi khams rgya mtsho'i rdul shin tu phra
NK127(jo)001:11826: ba snyed la zhugs par gyur te /
NK127(jo)001:11827: zhing 'dir ji lta ba bzhin du 'jig rten gyi
NK127(jo)001:11828: khams rgya mtsho thams cad du rdul phra ba'i khongs
NK127(jo)001:11829: kun tu yang byang chub sems dpa' rgya mtsho de
NK127(jo)001:11830: ltar zhugs so // de ltar sangs rgyas kyi mthu
NK127(jo)001:11831: dang byang chub sems dpa' kun tu bzang po'i ting
NK127(jo)001:11832: nge 'dzin gyi chos nyid rab tu thob pas /
NK127(jo)001:11833: phyogs bcu'i zhing rgya mtsho ma lus pa g.yos shing
NK127(jo)001:11834: rin po che'i rgyan thams cad kyis brgyan par byas
NK127(jo)001:11835: te chos rgya mtsho'i sgra dbyangs byung ngo //
NK127(jo)001:11836: de bzhin gshegs pa'i 'khor rgya mtsho thams cad du /
NK127(jo)001:11837: nor bu'i rgyal po mtshan dang ldan pa'i gser dpal
NK127(jo)001:11838: gyi rgyal mtshan gyi dpal la sogs pa nor bu'i
NK127(jo)001:11839: rgyal po chen po bcu'i sprin gyi char mngon par
NK127(jo)001:11840: babs shing / de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi
NK127(jo)001:11841: ba spu'i sgo dang 'od zer thams cad las 'di
NK127(jo)001:11842: babs shing / ltar / zhing rnams 'byam klas kun na kun tu bzang po de /
NK127(jo)001:11843: dbang po yid du 'ong la rab tu 'jug pa
NK127(jo)001:11844: mthong kun tu rnam 'phrul rnam pa 'di 'dra ston
NK127(jo)001:11845: par byed / ting 'dzin yul la 'jug pa mtha' dang dbus med do //
NK127(jo)001:11846: zhes pa la sogs pa tshigs su bcad pa'i sgra byung ngo //
NK127(jo)001:11847: de nas 'khor thams cad kyis thal mo sbyar te
NK127(jo)001:11848: kun tu bzang po la lta zhing tshigs su bcad
NK127(jo)001:11850: de nas kun tu bzang po sangs rgyas kyi byin
NK127(jo)001:11851: gyi rlabs kyis 'jig rten gyi khams thams cad du
NK127(jo)001:11852: sems can rnams kyi bsam pa rgya mtsho dang /
NK127(jo)001:11853: sangs rgyas kyi chos rgya mtsho dang /
NK127(jo)001:11854: smon lam rgya mtsho la sogs pa thams cad du
NK127(jo)001:11855: bltas nas 'khor rnams la sangs rgyas kyi ye shes
NK127(jo)001:11856: dang yon tan bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i tshul las
NK127(jo)001:11857: brtsams te chos bstan par mdzad do //
NK127(jo)001:11858: yang mdo de las gsungs pa /
NK127(jo)001:11859: byang chub sems dpa' kun tu mig gis bcom ldan
NK127(jo)001:11860: 'das rnam par snang mdzad la ting nge 'dzin dang
NK127(jo)001:11861: rnam thar du dang ldan pa'i byang chub sems dpa'
NK127(jo)001:11862: rnams kun tu bzang po'i sgo dang spyod pa la
NK127(jo)001:11863: 'jug pa dang / smon lam du dang ldan pa
NK127(jo)001:11864: rnams ting nge 'dzin dang rnam par thar pa la
NK127(jo)001:11866: ting nge 'dzin gyi khyad par gyi gnas thob pa sogs zhus pa na /
NK127(jo)001:11867: bcom ldan 'das kyis byang chub sems dpa' kun tu mig la 'di skad ces bka' stsal to //
NK127(jo)001:11868: kun tu mig khyod kyis de ltar 'das pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:11870: da ltar byung ba'i byang chub sems dpa'i dkyil 'khor thams cad dang /
NK127(jo)001:11871: de bzhin gshegs pa'i dkyil 'khor thams cad kyi don
NK127(jo)001:11872: du de bzhin gshegs pa la don 'dri bar sems
NK127(jo)001:11874: kun tu mig de bas na byang chub sems dpa'
NK127(jo)001:11875: kun tu bzang po bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i byang
NK127(jo)001:11876: chub sems dpa'i rnam par 'phrul pa dang ldan pa
NK127(jo)001:11877: / byang chub sems dpa' khyu mchog gi mthu bsgrub par dka' ba dang ldan pa /
NK127(jo)001:11878: byang chub sems dpa'i spyod pa la 'jug pa tshad med pas mngon par byung ba /
NK127(jo)001:11879: byang chub sems dpa'i cho 'phrul dang rnam par 'phrul pa la shin tu bslabs pa /
NK127(jo)001:11880: byang chub sems dpa'i smon lam bsgrub par dka' bas rnam par sbyangs pa /
NK127(jo)001:11881: byang chub sems dpa'i 'byung ba phyir mi ldog pa dang ldan pa /
NK127(jo)001:11882: pha rol tu phyin pa'i tshul mtha' yas pas rnam par sbyangs pa /
NK127(jo)001:11883: gzungs thob par bya ba mu med pa dang ldan pa tha dad pa yang dag par shes pa /
NK127(jo)001:11884: zad mi shes pas thogs pa med par rnam par dag pa /
NK127(jo)001:11885: 'gro ba thams cad la skyo ba med pa thob
NK127(jo)001:11886: pa'i snying rje chen pos phyi ma'i mur thug pa'i
NK127(jo)001:11887: smon lam dang ldan pa de nyid 'khor 'dir 'dus
NK127(jo)001:11888: te 'dug pa yin gyis de la dris shig /
NK127(jo)001:11889: des ting nge 'dzin dang rnam par 'phrul pa ston to //
NK127(jo)001:11890: de nas der 'dus pa'i byang chub sems dpa'i 'khor
NK127(jo)001:11891: de dag gis byang chub sems dpa' kun tu bzang
NK127(jo)001:11892: po'i ming thos ma thag tu byang chub sems dpa'i
NK127(jo)001:11893: ting nge 'dzin bsam gyis mi khyab pa mngon du
NK127(jo)001:11894: gyur to // chags pa med pa'i sems rnam par phye bas kyang byin gyis brlabs par gyur to //
NK127(jo)001:11895: ye shes bsam gyis mi khyab pa la rab tu gzhol ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:11896: ye shes mi 'phrog pa'i spyod yul dang /
NK127(jo)001:11897: de bzhin gshegs pa grangs med pa mthong zhing rnam par dmigs pa mngon du gyur pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:11898: de bzhin gshegs pa'i stobs tshad med pa khong du chud pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:11899: de bzhin gshegs pa dang rgyud kyi tshul gcig pa rjes su rtogs pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:11900: dus gsum mtha' yas pa la 'jug pa khong du chud pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:11901: bsod nams zad mi shes pa'i byin thob pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:11902: rnam par 'phrul pa rgya mtsho bzang po yongs su
NK127(jo)001:11903: rdzogs par bya ba khong du chud par gyur nas
NK127(jo)001:11904: de dag thams cad kyis rim gro dang rjed pa
NK127(jo)001:11905: dang bcas pas de bzhin gshegs pa'i 'khor gyi dkyil
NK127(jo)001:11906: 'khor thams cad du lta bar gyur na yang /
NK127(jo)001:11907: de bzhin gshegs pa'i byin gyi rlabs dang byang chub
NK127(jo)001:11908: sems dpa' kun tu bzang po'i rdzu 'phrul gyi khyu
NK127(jo)001:11909: mchog gi mthus kun tu bzang po'i lus dang gang
NK127(jo)001:11910: na gnas pa'i stan yang ma mthong ngo //
NK127(jo)001:11911: de nas byang chub sems dpa' kun tu mig gis bcom ldan 'das la zhus pa /
NK127(jo)001:11912: byang chub sems dpa' kun tu bzang po da lta lta ga la mchis /
NK127(jo)001:11914: 'di nyid na nga'i zhabs kyi drung na 'dug cing ma g.yos so //
NK127(jo)001:11915: de nas byang chub sems dpa' kun tu mig dang
NK127(jo)001:11916: byang chub sems dpa'i 'khor de dag thams cad kyis
NK127(jo)001:11917: kyang 'khor gyi dkyil 'khor thams cad la bltas nas
NK127(jo)001:11919: bcom ldan 'das bdag cag gis kun tu bzang po'i stan yang ma mthong ngo //
NK127(jo)001:11921: rigs kyi bu dag khyed kyis kun tu bzang po'i
NK127(jo)001:11922: lus ma mthong zhing stan yang ma mthong ba ni
NK127(jo)001:11923: de de bzhin te yus so //
NK127(jo)001:11925: 'di ltar byang chub sems dpa' kun tu bzang po
NK127(jo)001:11926: de ni brjod du med cing zab pa la gnas
NK127(jo)001:11927: pa ste / 'di ltar ye shes kyi dbyings mtha' yas pa la 'jug pa la zhugs pa'o //
NK127(jo)001:11928: seng ge rnam par bsgyings pa'i ting nge 'dzin rab tu thob pa'o //
NK127(jo)001:11929: sangs rgyas kyi cho 'phrul bla na med pa rab tu thob pa'o //
NK127(jo)001:11930: chags pa med pa'i mthas rnam par dag pa'i de bzhin gshegs pa'i stobs bcus grub pa'o //
NK127(jo)001:11931: chos kyi dbyings dam pa'i lus dang ldan pa'o //
NK127(jo)001:11932: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi byin gyi rlabs la gnas pa'o //
NK127(jo)001:11933: 'das pa dang ma byon pa dang da ltar byung
NK127(jo)001:11934: ba'i sangs rgyas thams cad dang ye shes tha mi
NK127(jo)001:11935: dad pa'i rgyun dang ldan pa'o //
NK127(jo)001:11937: byang chub sems dpa' kun tu bzang po 'di ni sems skad cig gi matha'i rjes su 'brang ba'o //
NK127(jo)001:11938: de nas byang chub sems dpa' kun tu mig gis
NK127(jo)001:11939: de bzhin gshegs pa las kun tu bzang po'i yon
NK127(jo)001:11940: tan rnam par dag pa thos ma thag tu byang
NK127(jo)001:11941: chub sems dpa'i ting nge 'dzin grangs med pa brgya
NK127(jo)001:11942: stong phrag bcu la mnyam par bzhag ste /
NK127(jo)001:11943: byang chub sems dpa' kun tu bzang po mngon par 'dod cing mthong bar bya ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:11944: gsol ba gdab pa'i bsam pas tshol zhing yongs su btsal te /
NK127(jo)001:11945: zhib tu zhib cing brtags pas dpyod pa rjes su rtog cing rnam par bltas kyang ma mthong la /
NK127(jo)001:11946: byang chub sems dpa'i 'khor de dag gis kyang ma mthong nas /
NK127(jo)001:11947: kun tu mig gis bcom ldan 'das la de ltar ma mthong ba'i tshul zhus pas /
NK127(jo)001:11949: khyod kyis kun tu bzang po de mi mthong ste /
NK127(jo)001:11950: ci'i phyir na kun tu bzang po ni byang chub
NK127(jo)001:11951: sems dpa'i rnam par thar pa bsam gyis mi khyab
NK127(jo)001:11953: ji ltar sgyu ma'i gzugs kyi rnam pa mang po
NK127(jo)001:11954: sgyu ma'i sngags kyi yi ge gang la gnas pa
NK127(jo)001:11955: yang dmigs par mi nus na /
NK127(jo)001:11956: byang chub sems dpa' kun tu bzang po'i lus ngag
NK127(jo)001:11957: yid kyi gsang ba la 'jug pa dang mthong bar
NK127(jo)001:11958: mi nus pa lta ci smos te /
NK127(jo)001:11959: byang chub sems dpa' kun tu bzang po ni zab
NK127(jo)001:11960: cing bsam gyis mi khyab pa rnam par spyod pa'o
NK127(jo)001:11961: // tshad med cing tshad las 'das pa ste ye shes rdo rje'i blo dang ldan pa'o //
NK127(jo)001:11962: chos kyi dbyings mtha' dang dbus med pa la yang dag par gnas pa'o //
NK127(jo)001:11963: 'jig rten gyi khams thams cad du gnas pa med
NK127(jo)001:11964: par spyod cing sems can thams cad kyi lus dang
NK127(jo)001:11965: gzugs kyi rjes su zhugs pa'o //
NK127(jo)001:11966: blang ba med pa'i chos kyi tshul dang ldan pa'o //
NK127(jo)001:11967: mi zad cing tha mi dad pa'i rdzu 'phrul dang
NK127(jo)001:11968: khyu mchog gi mthu la lhun gyis grub par gnas
NK127(jo)001:11970: chos kyi dbyings khong du chud pa dang ldan pa'o //
NK127(jo)001:11971: rigs kyi bu de ltar byang chub sems dpa' kun tu bzang po ni blta na don yod pa'o //
NK127(jo)001:11973: de bzhin du mnyan pa dang thos pa dang bsnyen
NK127(jo)001:11974: bkur byas pa dang bsams pa dang rjes su dran
NK127(jo)001:11975: pa dang dad pa dang brtags pa dang btsal ba
NK127(jo)001:11976: dang de'i rjes su smon lam gdab pa ni don
NK127(jo)001:11977: yod pa'o // de nas byang chub sems dpa' kun
NK127(jo)001:11978: tu mig dang byang chub sems dpa'i 'khor de dag
NK127(jo)001:11979: thams cad kyis kun tu bzang po mthong bar 'dod
NK127(jo)001:11980: cing thal mo sbyar te bcom ldan 'das dang kun
NK127(jo)001:11981: tu bzang po la lus kyis phyag 'tshal zhing ngag
NK127(jo)001:11982: tu'ang phyag 'tshal ba'i tshig brjod do //
NK127(jo)001:11983: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
NK127(jo)001:11984: rigs kyi bu dag byang chub sems dpa' chen po
NK127(jo)001:11985: kun tu bzang po la phyag 'tshol la gsol ba
NK127(jo)001:11986: thob cig / phyogs thams cad du mngon du gyis
NK127(jo)001:11987: la kun tu mig gi las su byin gyis rlob
NK127(jo)001:11988: thob cig / pa dang / kun tu bzang po
NK127(jo)001:11989: la dmigs nas chos kyi dbyings thams cad mngon du
NK127(jo)001:11990: bya ba'i sems kyis byin gyi brlab pa bgyis te
NK127(jo)001:11991: thob cig / pa dang / / chos thams cad
NK127(jo)001:11992: la 'dod chags dang bral bar khong du chud pas
NK127(jo)001:11993: kun tu bzang po dang smon lam gcig par byung
NK127(jo)001:11994: zhing gnyis su med pa la mnyam par zhog la
NK127(jo)001:11996: gyi khams thams cad du lus las mngon par byung
NK127(jo)001:11997: bar byin gyis brlabs shing dbang po tha mi dad
NK127(jo)001:11998: pa'i rjes su 'brang bas kun tu bzang po'i smon
NK127(jo)001:11999: lam kun tu 'gro ba yongs su sbyang bar gyis
NK127(jo)001:12000: thob cig / pa dang / / / shig dang
NK127(jo)001:12001: / byang chub sems dpa' kun tu bzang po mthong
NK127(jo)001:12002: thob cig / pa dang / / / shig dang
NK127(jo)001:12003: / bar 'gyur ro // de nas byang chub sems
NK127(jo)001:12004: dpa' kun tu mig byang chub sems dpa'i 'khor de
NK127(jo)001:12005: dag dang bcas pas spyi bos gtugs te phyag 'tshal
NK127(jo)001:12006: nas kun tu bzang po la gsol ba btab ma
NK127(jo)001:12007: thag tu byang chub sems dpa' de dag thams cad
NK127(jo)001:12008: kyis kun tu bzang po de bzhin gshegs pa'i zhabs
NK127(jo)001:12009: drung na gnas shing pad+mo'i stan la 'dug pa mthong
NK127(jo)001:12011: 'khor de'i byang sems rnams kyi lus las kyang 'byung bar snang ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:12012: 'jig rten gyi khams rgyud 'byams klas pa dag nas kyang 'ong bar snang ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:12013: sangs rgyas gcig nas gcig tu brgyud pa thams cad yang dag par ston pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:12014: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi phrin las 'jig rten gyi khams thams cad rab tu brjod pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:12015: byang chub sems dpa' spyod pa thams cad rab tu ston pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:12016: thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyi lam snang bar byed pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:12017: byang chub sems dpa'i rnam par 'phrul pa thams cad yang dag par ston pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:12018: byang chub sems dpa'i khyu mchog gi mthu dbyung ba thams cad yang dag par brjod pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:12019: de bzhin gshegs pa tshad med pa'i dus gsum rab
NK127(jo)001:12020: tu ston pa de lta bu'i rnam par 'phrul pa
NK127(jo)001:12021: dag kun tu bzang pos bstan to //
NK127(jo)001:12022: rnam 'phrul de mthong bas 'khor thams cad dga' zhing
NK127(jo)001:12023: mgu ste dmigs pa thams cad kyis btud pa'i rjes
NK127(jo)001:12024: su byang chub sems dpa' kun tu bzang po la
NK127(jo)001:12025: phyag 'tshal to // de'i tshe me tog sna tshogs pa'i sprin gyi char dang /
NK127(jo)001:12026: de bzhin du phreng ba sna tshogs kyi sprin la
NK127(jo)001:12027: sogs pa sprin gyi char stong phrag bcu mngon par
NK127(jo)001:12028: babs so // 'jig rten gyi khams brjod du med pa rnam pa drug tu g.yos so //
NK127(jo)001:12029: rol mo rnams kyi sgra dang lha rnams kyi dbyangs mang po yang byung ngo //
NK127(jo)001:12030: snang ba chen pos khyab pa dang sems can rnams
NK127(jo)001:12031: rnam par dag pa dang ngan song rnams rgyun chad
NK127(jo)001:12032: pa dang / byang chub sems dpa' brjod du med
NK127(jo)001:12033: pa'i yang brjod du med pa rnams kun tu bzang
NK127(jo)001:12034: po'i spyod pa la zhugs pa dang grub pa dang
NK127(jo)001:12035: smon lam yongs su rdzogs par byas nas bla med
NK127(jo)001:12036: byang chub tu mngon par sangs rgyas par gyur to
NK127(jo)001:12037: pa dang / // de nas kun tu mig gis bcom ldan 'das la gsol pa /
NK127(jo)001:12038: bcom ldan 'das byang chub sems dpa' kun tu bzang
NK127(jo)001:12039: po ni bdag nyid che ba la mngon par spyod
NK127(jo)001:12040: pa'o // mtshungs pa ma mchis pa dang yongs su
NK127(jo)001:12041: mi chod pa dang slar mi ldog pa dang mnyam
NK127(jo)001:12042: pa nyid rjes su rtogs pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:12043: gzhan gyis mi zlog pa dang chos thams cad tha
NK127(jo)001:12044: mi dad pa dang chos thams cad ma 'dres pa
NK127(jo)001:12045: dang sems can thams cad kyi sems byin gyis rlabs
NK127(jo)001:12046: mkhas pa la rnam par spyod pa'o //
NK127(jo)001:12047: kun tu bzang po ni chos thams cad kyi dbang
NK127(jo)001:12048: dang ting nge 'dzin dang rnam par thar pa la
NK127(jo)001:12050: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
NK127(jo)001:12051: de de bzhin te kun tu bzang po ni yon tan grangs med pas rnam par dag pa /
NK127(jo)001:12052: yon tan mtshungs pa med pas brgyan pa /
NK127(jo)001:12053: yon tan tshad med pa'i rin po che dang ldan pa /
NK127(jo)001:12054: yon tan bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i 'byung gnas kyi rgya mtsho /
NK127(jo)001:12055: yon tan dpag tu med pa'i mtshan nyid /
NK127(jo)001:12056: yon tan mu med pa'i sprin /
NK127(jo)001:12057: yon tan mtshams med pas basngagasa shing bstod pa /
NK127(jo)001:12058: chos rin po che zad mi shes pa ste /
NK127(jo)001:12059: kun tu bzang po ni sangs rgyas thams cad kyis yon tan brjod cing basngagasa pa mi zad pa'o //
NK127(jo)001:12060: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis kun tu bzang po la bka' stsal pa /
NK127(jo)001:12061: khyod kyis byang chub sems dpa' kun tu mig sogs byang chub sems dpa'i 'khor thams cad la /
NK127(jo)001:12062: byang chub sems dpa' kun tu bzang po'i spyod pa
NK127(jo)001:12063: dang smon lam yongs su rdzogs pa dang ldan pa'i
NK127(jo)001:12065: yon tan basngagasa pa tshad med pa can /
NK127(jo)001:12066: de dang ldan na byang chub sems dpa' yin yang
NK127(jo)001:12067: sangs rgyas dang de bzhin gshegs pa dang stobs bcu
NK127(jo)001:12068: pa zhes bya bar brjod par 'os pa de nyid
NK127(jo)001:12070: kun tu bzang po des de bzhin gshegs pa'i bka'
NK127(jo)001:12071: bzhin du 'khor rnams la rmad du byung ba'i chos
NK127(jo)001:12072: kyi tshul chen po de bstan cing /
NK127(jo)001:12073: ji ltar sems can rnams kyi sems kyi sgo mu med pa ste /
NK127(jo)001:12074: don dam par skye ba med kyang tha snyad tsam
NK127(jo)001:12075: du skye ba dang skye bar 'gyur ba mtha' med
NK127(jo)001:12076: pa dang thug pa med pa tshad gzhal du med
NK127(jo)001:12077: pa de snyed du byang chub sems dpa' kun tu
NK127(jo)001:12078: bzang pos chos kyi sgo khong du chud pa'o //
NK127(jo)001:12079: ji ltar klu rnams kyis char chen po thigs pa
NK127(jo)001:12080: re re zhing ba ru ra'i 'bras bu tsam gyi
NK127(jo)001:12081: rgyun phab kyang de la zad pa med la sngar
NK127(jo)001:12082: babs pa phyis mi 'bab kyang sprin gyi 'du bya
NK127(jo)001:12083: ba mi zad pa de bzhin du /
NK127(jo)001:12084: byang chub sems dpa' kun tu bzang po'i ting nge
NK127(jo)001:12085: 'dzin dang ye shes dang chos kyi sgo dang sangs
NK127(jo)001:12086: rgyas la lta ba dang rnam par 'phrul pa'i sgo
NK127(jo)001:12087: la sogs pa la zad pa dang mtshams dang mu
NK127(jo)001:12088: med la phyir ldog pa dang rgyun chad pa dang
NK127(jo)001:12090: ji ltar me ni shing yod pa srid du 'bar
NK127(jo)001:12091: ba bzhin du byang chub sems dpa' yang ci tsam
NK127(jo)001:12092: du sems can gyi khams dang chos kyi dbyings la
NK127(jo)001:12093: sogs pa'i 'jug pa srid du mthar thug pa med
NK127(jo)001:12094: par rnam par rol pa ston pa'i tshul gyis kun
NK127(jo)001:12095: tu bzang po'i spyod pa bstan to //
NK127(jo)001:12096: de nas de bzhin gshegs pas byang chub sems dpa' sems kyi rgyal po la bka' stsal pa /
NK127(jo)001:12097: brjod du med pa'i rdul rnams kun bzung ste //
NK127(jo)001:12098: bskal par kun tu bzang po bstod byas kyang //
NK127(jo)001:12099: kun tu bzang po de basngagasa mthar mi 'jug /
NK127(jo)001:12100: brjod du med pa'i kun tu bzang po rnams //
NK127(jo)001:12101: skra rtse re re kun la yang dag 'jug /
NK127(jo)001:12102: skra rtse gcig bzhin yul rnams kun la ste //
NK127(jo)001:12103: chos dbyings ma lus ji snyed de bzhin no //
NK127(jo)001:12105: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyi zhal gyi sgo nas
NK127(jo)001:12106: mi bsnyengs pa'i mthar phyin pa zhes bya ba'i 'khor
NK127(jo)001:12107: gyi 'od zer khrag khrig brgya stong grangs med pa
NK127(jo)001:12109: des 'jig rten gyi khams 'byams klas pa thams cad
NK127(jo)001:12110: snang bar byas nas 'jig rten de dag la g.yas
NK127(jo)001:12111: phyogs su lan bcur bskor te de bzhin gshegs pa'i
NK127(jo)001:12112: rnam 'phrul bstan pa dang ngan song gi rgyud zhi
NK127(jo)001:12113: ba dang / bdud zil gyis gnon pa dang sangs
NK127(jo)001:12114: rgyas kyi 'khor gyi dkyil 'khor rnam par bkod pa
NK127(jo)001:12115: la sogs pas 'jig rten gyi khams chos kyi dbyings
NK127(jo)001:12116: kyis klas pa nam mkha'i mthas gtugs pa 'byams klas
NK127(jo)001:12117: pa thams cad rgyas par khyab par byas nas phyir
NK127(jo)001:12118: ba dang / 'ongs te / byang chub sems dpa'i
NK127(jo)001:12119: 'khor gyi dkyil 'khor thams cad la g.yas phyogs su
NK127(jo)001:12120: bskor nas byang chub sems dpa' kun tu bzang po'i
NK127(jo)001:12122: 'od des kun tu bzang po la reg ma thag
NK127(jo)001:12123: tu de'i lus kyi gdan seng ge'i khri de sngon
NK127(jo)001:12124: las brgya phrag stong 'gyur du bzang zhing 'phags te
NK127(jo)001:12125: / de bzhin gshegs pa'i seng ge'i gdan ma gtogs par gzhan kun las 'phags so //
NK127(jo)001:12126: de nas byang chub sems dpa' de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs su byung ba'i dpal gyis dris pa la /
NK127(jo)001:12127: kun tu bzang pos de bzhin gshegs pa skye ba
NK127(jo)001:12128: 'byung ba bstan pa zhes bya ba'i chos kyi rnam
NK127(jo)001:12129: grangs ngo mtshar rmad du byung ba /
NK127(jo)001:12130: sangs rgyas rnams kyi skye ba 'byung ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:12131: sku gsung thugs kyi gnas dang /
NK127(jo)001:12133: mngon par byang chub pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:12134: chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:12135: yongs su mya ngan las 'das pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:12136: sangs rgyas rnams mthong zhing thos pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:12137: de bzhin gshegs pa dang 'grogs pas dge rtsa bskyed pa'i tshul rnams bstan pa na /
NK127(jo)001:12138: sangs rgyas kyi mthus phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten gyi khams
NK127(jo)001:12139: bye ba khrag khrig brgya stong brjod du med pa'i
NK127(jo)001:12140: rdul phra rab snyed kyi 'jig rten khams rnam pa
NK127(jo)001:12142: lha rdzas kyi me tog dang na bza' dang gdugs
NK127(jo)001:12143: dang rgyal mtshan la sogs pa'i sprin gyi char dang
NK127(jo)001:12144: / byang chub sems dpa' dang sangs rgyas kyi gsung
NK127(jo)001:12145: gi legs so'i sgra dbyangs chen po'i sprin gyi char
NK127(jo)001:12147: phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten gyi khams bye ba khrag khrig
NK127(jo)001:12148: brgya stong brjod du med pa brgyad cu'i rdul phra
NK127(jo)001:12149: ba snyed kyi pha rol nas /
NK127(jo)001:12150: sangs rgyas kyi zhing bye ba khrag khrig brgya stong
NK127(jo)001:12151: brjod du med pa brgyad cu'i rdul shin tu phra
NK127(jo)001:12152: ba snyed kyi byang chub sems dpa' de thams cad
NK127(jo)001:12153: kyang mtshan kun tu bzang por mthun pa sha stag
NK127(jo)001:12154: 'ongs nas de dag gis bdag cag gi zhing rnams
NK127(jo)001:12155: su'ang tshig dang yi ge 'di kho na ltar chos
NK127(jo)001:12156: bstan no zhes sogs shin tu basngagasa pa brjod cing
NK127(jo)001:12158: chos 'di bstan pas byang chub sems dpa' sangs rgyas
NK127(jo)001:12159: kyi zhing brgya phrag stong gi rdul shin tu phra
NK127(jo)001:12160: ba snyed kyis byang chub sems dpa'i ting 'dzin dang
NK127(jo)001:12161: mngon shes thams cad thob nas rdzogs pa'i byang chub
NK127(jo)001:12162: tu tshe gcig gis thogs par lung bstan thob pa
NK127(jo)001:12163: dang / sangs rgyas kyi zhing brgya phrag stong gi
NK127(jo)001:12164: rdul shin tu phra ba snyed kyis sems can rnams
NK127(jo)001:12165: kyis bla med rdzogs byang du sems bskyed cing ma
NK127(jo)001:12166: 'ongs pa na sangs rgyas kyi yul phun sum tshogs
NK127(jo)001:12167: pa zhes bya ba'i sangs rgyas su lung bstan thob
NK127(jo)001:12168: dang / pa dang / ma 'ongs pa na chos
NK127(jo)001:12169: 'di yang ji ltar gling bzhi ba'i sems can rnams
NK127(jo)001:12170: kyis shes shing dul bar gyur pa de bzhin du
NK127(jo)001:12171: dang / pa dang / / phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten
NK127(jo)001:12172: gyi khams nam mkha'i mthar thug pa ma lus pa
NK127(jo)001:12173: thams cad du yang sems can rnams rnam par dul
NK127(jo)001:12174: dang / pa dang / / bar 'gyur ro // zhes dang /
NK127(jo)001:12175: de bzhin du sangs rgyas kyi zhing bye ba khrag
NK127(jo)001:12176: khrig brgya stong brjod du med pa phrag bcu'i rdul
NK127(jo)001:12177: phra ba snyed kyi byang chub sems dpa' kun tu
NK127(jo)001:12178: bzang por mtshan mthun pa rnams kyis kyang basngagasa so
NK127(jo)001:12179: // de nas yang byang chub sems dpa'i 'khor gyi
NK127(jo)001:12180: 'dus pa chen po'i dbus su byang chub sems dpa'
NK127(jo)001:12181: kun tu bzang po de nyid sangs rgyas phal po
NK127(jo)001:12182: che zhes bya ba'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par
NK127(jo)001:12184: phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten chos kyi dbyings dang nam mkha'i
NK127(jo)001:12185: mthas gtugs pa thams cad rnam pa drug tu g.yos
NK127(jo)001:12186: shing rab tu bskyod de dag kun gyis go bar
NK127(jo)001:12187: byas nas ting nge 'dzin de las langs pa dang
NK127(jo)001:12188: / byang chub sems dpa' chen po kun tu shes
NK127(jo)001:12189: rab kyis byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyi rgyu mthun
NK127(jo)001:12190: / pa dang / ngo mtshar gyi 'du shes dang /
NK127(jo)001:12191: spyod pa nas yongs su mya ngan las 'das pa'i
NK127(jo)001:12192: bar gyi dri ba brgya phrag gnyis las lhag pa
NK127(jo)001:12193: dris pa la / byang chub sems dpa' kun tu
NK127(jo)001:12194: bzang pos de der yang rnam grangs bcus legs par
NK127(jo)001:12195: bshad pa'i byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyi spyod pa
NK127(jo)001:12196: yongs su sbyong ba zhes bya ba'i chos kyi sgo
NK127(jo)001:12197: dris pa la / bstan pa na / 'jig rten
NK127(jo)001:12198: gyi khams tshad med grangs med pa rnams g.yos shing
NK127(jo)001:12199: snang ba chen pos khyab ste /
NK127(jo)001:12200: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams kyis kyang
NK127(jo)001:12201: dgyes pa'i zhal kun tu bzang po la bstan nas
NK127(jo)001:12202: legs so'i basngagasa pa rgya cher brjod par mdzad do
NK127(jo)001:12203: // de nas tshong dpon gyi bu nor bu bzang
NK127(jo)001:12204: pos nam mkha'i dbyings ltar bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i
NK127(jo)001:12205: spyod yul rgya mtsho brnyes shing /
NK127(jo)001:12206: byang chub sems dpa' kun tu bzang po mthong bar
NK127(jo)001:12207: dga' bas skom ste de bzhin gshegs pa'i gdan seng
NK127(jo)001:12208: ge'i khri la mngon par bltas te 'dug pa dang
NK127(jo)001:12209: / de'i bsam pa rnam par dag pa'i mthu dang /
NK127(jo)001:12210: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi byin gyi rlabs dang /
NK127(jo)001:12211: byang chub sems dpa' kun tu bzang po'i sngon gyi
NK127(jo)001:12212: dge rtsa dang skal pa mthun pas kun tu bzang
NK127(jo)001:12213: po mthong bar 'gyur ba'i snga ltas bcu byung ste
NK127(jo)001:12214: / 'di ltar sangs rgyas kyi zhing thams cad snying
NK127(jo)001:12215: po byang chub kyi rgyan rnam par dag pas dag
NK127(jo)001:12217: zhing thams cad du mi khom pa dang ngan song med pa sogs dang /
NK127(jo)001:12218: rgyan bkod pa tshad med pa dang sems can rnams
NK127(jo)001:12219: yongs su dag par gyur pa de lta bu'i ltas
NK127(jo)001:12220: dang / gzhan yang kun tu bzang po mthong ba'i
NK127(jo)001:12221: ltas zhing thams cad kyi rdul phra ba re re
NK127(jo)001:12222: la yang de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi 'od
NK127(jo)001:12223: zer gyi d+r+wa ba mang po snang ba sogs bkod
NK127(jo)001:12224: pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i sprin rnam par rol
NK127(jo)001:12226: byang chub sems dpa' kun tu bzang po mthong ba'i skabs phye la /
NK127(jo)001:12227: de mthong na thams cad mkhyen pa nyid thob pa dang 'dra bar sems shing /
NK127(jo)001:12228: mi ldog pa'i rnam thar bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i
NK127(jo)001:12229: shugs thob pas byang chub sems dpa' kun tu bzang
NK127(jo)001:12230: po de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad dang mnyam pa
NK127(jo)001:12231: nyid thob pa / dus gsum mnyam pa nyid kyi rjes su song ba /
NK127(jo)001:12232: bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i yul mi 'phrog pa'i spyod yul can /
NK127(jo)001:12233: mu med pa'i ye shes kyi yul dang ldan pa /
NK127(jo)001:12234: byang chub sems dpa' thams cad kyis rnam par blta ba /
NK127(jo)001:12235: 'jig rten thams cad zil gyis gnon pa /
NK127(jo)001:12236: 'khor gyi dkyil 'khor thams cad kyis rjes su 'brang ba /
NK127(jo)001:12237: mngon par 'phags pa'i yul dang ldan pa de /
NK127(jo)001:12238: bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa rnam par snang
NK127(jo)001:12239: mdzad kyi spyan sngar byang chub sems dpa'i 'khor rgya
NK127(jo)001:12240: mtsho'i dbus na seng ge'i khri rin po che'i pad+mo
NK127(jo)001:12241: chen po'i snying po can la 'dug pa mthong ste
NK127(jo)001:12242: / de'i ba spu'i bu ga thams cad kyi sgo
NK127(jo)001:12243: re re nas kyang 'jig rten gyi khams thams cad
NK127(jo)001:12244: kyi rdul phra rab snyed kyi 'od zer gyi sprin
NK127(jo)001:12246: 'jig rten gyi khams chos kyi dbyings kyis klas pa
NK127(jo)001:12247: nam mkha'i mthas gtugs pa thams cad snang bar byas
NK127(jo)001:12248: nas sems can rnams kyi sdug bsngal zhi bar byed
NK127(jo)001:12249: pa dang / de'i lus kyi dkyil 'khor las sangs
NK127(jo)001:12250: rgyas kyi zhing rdul shin tu phra ba snyed kyi
NK127(jo)001:12251: sprin kha dog sna tshogs pa can mang po 'thon
NK127(jo)001:12252: pa dang / te / byang chub sems dpa' thams
NK127(jo)001:12253: cad kyi dga' ba dang mos pa'i shugs rgya chen
NK127(jo)001:12254: po 'phel bar byed pa mthong ngo //
NK127(jo)001:12255: de'i spyi bo dang phrag pa'i lhun gnyis dang ba
NK127(jo)001:12256: spu'i sgo thams cad nas kyang spos kyi 'od 'phro
NK127(jo)001:12257: ba'i sprin gyi char kha dog sna tshogs pa mang
NK127(jo)001:12258: po 'thon nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi
NK127(jo)001:12259: 'khor gyi dkyil 'khor rgyas par bkang ste mngon par
NK127(jo)001:12261: ba spu'i bu ga thams cad las ni ba spu'i
NK127(jo)001:12262: sgo re re nas kyang me tog gi sprin gyi
NK127(jo)001:12263: char dang / spos sna tshogs kyi shing gi sprin dang /
NK127(jo)001:12264: gos sna tshogs kyi sprin dang /
NK127(jo)001:12265: lnga ldi dang phreng ba sna tshogs kyi sprin dang /
NK127(jo)001:12266: mu tig sna tshogs kyi sprin dang /
NK127(jo)001:12267: yid bzhin gyi nor bu rin po che'i sprin dang /
NK127(jo)001:12268: rin po che'i shing gi sprin dang /
NK127(jo)001:12269: gzugs khams kyi lha'i ris dang /
NK127(jo)001:12270: tshangs pa'i rgyud du gtogs pa'i lha'i ris dang /
NK127(jo)001:12271: 'dod pa'i khams kyi lha'i ris dbang po'i lus kyi sprin rnams dang /
NK127(jo)001:12272: sangs rgyas kyi zhing dag pa dang ma dag pa
