NK127(jo)001:12273: sna tshogs par ston pa'i sprin dang sangs rgyas kyi
NK127(jo)001:12274: zhing dag par sangs rgyas kyi sku byang chub sems
NK127(jo)001:12275: dpa'i 'khor dang bcas pa'i sprin dang /
NK127(jo)001:12276: sems can thams cad lus kyi sprin dang /
NK127(jo)001:12277: byang chub sems dpa'i lus kyi sprin dang /
NK127(jo)001:12278: kun tu bzang po'i spyod pa'i sprin dang /
NK127(jo)001:12279: kun tu bzang po'i spyod pa'i sprin la sogs pa
NK127(jo)001:12280: re rer yang sangs rgyas kyi zhing thams cad kyi
NK127(jo)001:12281: rdul shin tu phra ba snyed kyi sprin mngon par
NK127(jo)001:12282: 'thon nas de re res kyang chos kyi dbyings dang
NK127(jo)001:12283: nam mkha'i mtha' klas pa'i zhing thams cad rgyas par
NK127(jo)001:12284: bkang ste de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad mchod cing
NK127(jo)001:12285: basngagasa pa dang chos 'dzin pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:12286: sems can gyi khams rgya mtsho thabs sna tshogs kyis smin cing grol bar byed pa mthong ngo //
NK127(jo)001:12287: de lta bu mthong nas tshong dpon gyi bu nor
NK127(jo)001:12288: bzang nyid dga' mgu rangs te yid bde ba skyes
NK127(jo)001:12289: nas de bas kyang shas cher byang chub sems dpa'
NK127(jo)001:12290: kun tu bzang po'i lus dang yan lag re re
NK127(jo)001:12291: dang / yan lag rnam par phye ba re re dang /
NK127(jo)001:12292: lus kyi cha re re nas ba spu'i bu ga
NK127(jo)001:12293: re re rnam par phye ba re re'i bar du
NK127(jo)001:12294: yang / stong chen po'i 'jig rten rlung gi phung
NK127(jo)001:12295: po nas gzugs dang gzugs med pa'i bar du snod
NK127(jo)001:12296: dang bcud kyi rnam pa dus dang bcas pa gzugs
NK127(jo)001:12297: brnyan gyi tshul du mthong ngo //
NK127(jo)001:12298: 'jig rten 'di la ji lta ba bzhin du phyogs
NK127(jo)001:12299: bcu'i 'jig rten gyi khams thams cad sangs rgyas 'byung
NK127(jo)001:12300: ba dang bcas byang chub sems dpa'i 'khor dang bcas
NK127(jo)001:12301: pa'ang mthong ngo // mi mjed 'jig rten khams 'di'i
NK127(jo)001:12302: sngon gyi mur thug pa'i 'jig rten brgyud mar byung
NK127(jo)001:12303: ba ji snyed pa sangs rgyas 'byung ba dang byang
NK127(jo)001:12304: chub sems dpa' dang sems can ji snyed pa gnas
NK127(jo)001:12305: dang bcas pa de thams cad kyang kun tu bzang
NK127(jo)001:12306: po'i skyes bu chen po'i mtshan re re na yang
NK127(jo)001:12307: pa'ang mthong ngo // mthong la / de bzhin du
NK127(jo)001:12308: phyi ma'i mur thug pa'i sangs rgyas kyi zhing 'byams
NK127(jo)001:12310: de bzhin du phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten gyi khams thams
NK127(jo)001:12311: cad kyi sngon dang phyi ma'i matha'i mur thug pa
NK127(jo)001:12312: gcig nas gcig tu brgyud pa thams cad kyang /
NK127(jo)001:12313: kun tu bzang po'i lus kyi mtshan re re dang
NK127(jo)001:12314: ba spu'i bu ga re re nas phan tshun ma
NK127(jo)001:12316: ji ltar kun tu bzang po de bzhin gshegs pa
NK127(jo)001:12317: rnam par snang mdzad kyi drung na 'dug pa de
NK127(jo)001:12318: bzhin du / shar phyogs 'jig rten gyi khams pad+mo'i
NK127(jo)001:12319: dpal na de bzhin gshegs pa bzang po'i dpal gyi
NK127(jo)001:12320: drung du yang rnam par rtse ba 'di nyid ston
NK127(jo)001:12321: cing 'dug pa sogs phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten gyi khams
NK127(jo)001:12322: thams cad kyi de bzhin gshegs pa'i drung na 'dug
NK127(jo)001:12323: bzhin du / pa dang / phyogs bcu'i zhing thams
NK127(jo)001:12324: cad kyi rdul shin tu phra ba re re'i khongs
NK127(jo)001:12325: su yang sangs rgyas kyi dkyil 'khor chos kyi dbyings
NK127(jo)001:12326: ltar rgya che ba dag na byang chub sems dpa'
NK127(jo)001:12327: kun tu bzang po de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad
NK127(jo)001:12328: kyi zhabs kyi drung na seng ge'i khri pad+mo chen
NK127(jo)001:12329: po'i snying po can la 'dug cing rnam par rtse
NK127(jo)001:12330: ba 'di nyid ston pa mthong ngo //
NK127(jo)001:12331: de'i lus kyi cha re re las kyang dus gsum
NK127(jo)001:12332: du byung ba'i dmigs pa thams cad gzugs brnyan gyi
NK127(jo)001:12334: zhing thams cad dang sangs rgyas thams cad dang byang chub sems dpa' mtha' dag snang zhing /
NK127(jo)001:12335: sangs rgyas kyi dbyangs dang sems can thams cad kyi
NK127(jo)001:12336: sgra dang sangs rgyas thams cad kyi chos kyi 'khor
NK127(jo)001:12337: lo bskor ba dang gdams ngag bstan pa'i cho 'phrul
NK127(jo)001:12338: thams cad dang / byang chub sems dpa' yang dag
NK127(jo)001:12339: par bsdu ba dang sangs rgyas kyi rnam par rol
NK127(jo)001:12340: pa dag kyang thos par gyur to //
NK127(jo)001:12341: des de ltar kun tu bzang po'i rnam par rtse ba mthong zhing thos nas /
NK127(jo)001:12342: sems kyi skad cig gcig la sangs rgyas kyi zhing
NK127(jo)001:12343: thams cad du lus kyis rgyas par 'gengs pa dang
NK127(jo)001:12344: / de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi zhabs kyi drung du 'gro ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:12345: mchod cing rim gro bya ba nas skad cig gcig
NK127(jo)001:12346: la byang chub sems dpa' kun tu bzang po'i spyod
NK127(jo)001:12347: pa mngon sum rab tu shes pa'i bar gyi ye
NK127(jo)001:12348: shes kyi pha rol tu phyin pa bcu thob par
NK127(jo)001:12349: gyur to // de lta bu'i spyod pa dang ldan
NK127(jo)001:12350: pa nor bzang gi spyi bor kun tu bzang po'i
NK127(jo)001:12351: phyag g.yas pa brkyangs te bzhag ma thag tu ting
NK127(jo)001:12352: nge 'dzin gyi sgo sangs rgyas kyi zhing thams cad
NK127(jo)001:12353: kyi rdul shin tu phra ba snyed la zhugs par
NK127(jo)001:12354: gyur to // gyur te / ting nge 'dzin re
NK127(jo)001:12355: re las kyang 'jig rten gyi khams rgya mtsho sangs
NK127(jo)001:12356: rgyas kyi zhing gi rdul phra ba snyed sngon chad
NK127(jo)001:12357: ma mthong ba dag la zhugs par gyur to //
NK127(jo)001:12358: de'i thams cad mkhyen pa nyid kyi tshogs zhing gi
NK127(jo)001:12359: rdul phra ba snyed rdzogs pa dang thams cad mkhyen
NK127(jo)001:12360: pa'i chos de snyed rab tu byung bar gyur to
NK127(jo)001:12361: // thams cad mkhyen pa nyid la gnas pa dang
NK127(jo)001:12362: de'i lam dang de'i shugs drag po de snyed kyis
NK127(jo)001:12364: smon lam rgya mtsho dang byang chub sems dpa'i spyod
NK127(jo)001:12365: pa dang sangs rgyas thams cad kyi ye shes kyi
NK127(jo)001:12366: snang ba rnams re re nas sangs rgyas kyi zhing
NK127(jo)001:12367: gi rdul shin tu phra ba snyed kyang mngon du
NK127(jo)001:12368: gyur to // ji ltar mi mjed 'jig rten gyi
NK127(jo)001:12369: khams 'dir byang chub sems dpa' kun tu bzang po
NK127(jo)001:12370: de bzhin gshegs pa rnam par snang mdzad kyi spyan
NK127(jo)001:12371: snga na 'dug pas phyag brkyangs te tshong dpon gyi
NK127(jo)001:12372: bu nor bzang gi spyi bor bzhag pa de bzhin
NK127(jo)001:12373: gyur to // du / phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten gyi
NK127(jo)001:12374: khams thams cad kyi de bzhin gshegs pa'i drung na
NK127(jo)001:12375: bzhugs pa'i kun tu bzang po dang /
NK127(jo)001:12376: 'jig rten gyi khams de thams cad kyi rdul shin
NK127(jo)001:12377: tu phra ba'i khongs su chud pa'i 'jig rten gyi
NK127(jo)001:12378: khams dag gi de bzhin gshegs pa'i drung na bzhugs
NK127(jo)001:12379: pa'i kun tu bzang po thams cad kyi phyag brkyangs
NK127(jo)001:12380: pas nor bzang gi mgo la reg pas nor bzang
NK127(jo)001:12381: yang chos kyi sgo mang po de snyed la tshul
NK127(jo)001:12382: sna tshogs kyis zhugs par gyur to //
NK127(jo)001:12383: de nas byang chub sems dpa' kun tu bzang pos nor bzang la 'di skad du /
NK127(jo)001:12384: rigs kyi bu khyod kyis nga'i rnam par 'phrul pa mthong mod /
NK127(jo)001:12386: 'phags pa mthong ste de ltar shin tu bsam gyis
NK127(jo)001:12387: mi khyab pa'i rnam par thar pa 'di ni de
NK127(jo)001:12388: bzhin gshegs pas mkhyen grang ngo //
NK127(jo)001:12389: kun tu bzang po des smras pa /
NK127(jo)001:12390: rigs kyi bu ngas thams cad mkhyen pa 'dod pas
NK127(jo)001:12391: bskal pa sangs rgyas kyi zhing brjod du med pa'i
NK127(jo)001:12392: yang brjod du med pa'i rdul shin tu phra ba
NK127(jo)001:12393: snyed cig tu rnam par spyad de byang chub kyi
NK127(jo)001:12394: sems sbyangs shing / bskal pa re rer yang sangs
NK127(jo)001:12395: rgyas kyi zhing brjod du med pa'i yang brjod du
NK127(jo)001:12396: med pa'i du ma phra ba snyed kyi sangs rgyas
NK127(jo)001:12397: mchod pa dang de snyed kyi smon lam sbyangs pa
NK127(jo)001:12398: sems sbyangs shing / dang / sangs rgyas kyi chos
NK127(jo)001:12399: kyi phyir bskal pa re re la'ang zhing gi rdul
NK127(jo)001:12400: de snyed kyi mgo dang yan lag dang lus dang
NK127(jo)001:12401: rgyal srid chen po la sogs pa phangs pa med
NK127(jo)001:12402: sems sbyangs shing / dang / par btang ngo //
NK127(jo)001:12403: sangs rgyas de snyed la mchod pa thams cad kyang
NK127(jo)001:12404: de snyed du phul zhing dam pa'i chos bzung la
NK127(jo)001:12405: sems sbyangs shing / dang / par btang ngo //
NK127(jo)001:12406: / bskal pa de snyed du'ang de bzhin gshegs pa'i
NK127(jo)001:12407: bstan pa la mi mthun pa'i sems bskyed ba dang
NK127(jo)001:12408: khong khro ba'am bdag tu 'dzin pa dang bdag yongs
NK127(jo)001:12409: su bskyang ba'i sems dang 'khor bar skyo ba'i sems
NK127(jo)001:12410: la sogs pa 'ga' yang ma bskyed cing /
NK127(jo)001:12411: byang chub kyi sems dang ye shes gzhan gyis mi
NK127(jo)001:12412: thub cing brgal bar dka' ba'i snying po bskyed do
NK127(jo)001:12413: // rigs kyi bu nga'i sngon gyi rdzogs smin sbyang
NK127(jo)001:12414: ba dang dam chos srung ba'i don du lus srog
NK127(jo)001:12415: btang ba'i sbyor ba de dag bstan na bskal pa
NK127(jo)001:12416: rgya mtsho thams cad du yang zad par mi 'gyur
NK127(jo)001:12417: // ro // ngas chos rgya mtsho de snyed cig las kyang tshig dang yi ge 'ga' tsam yang /
NK127(jo)001:12418: sems can thams cad yongs su bskyab pa dang sangs
NK127(jo)001:12419: rgyas kyi chos rdzogs pa'i phyir 'khor los sgyur ba'i
NK127(jo)001:12420: rgyal srid da nga bdog pa thams cad btang bas
NK127(jo)001:12422: de lta bu'i sngon gyi sbyor ba bstan na bskal
NK127(jo)001:12423: pa rgya mtsho sangs rgyas kyi zhing brjod du med
NK127(jo)001:12424: pa'i yang brjod du med pa'i rdul phra ba snyed
NK127(jo)001:12426: ngas de lta bu'i tshogs kyi stobs dang /
NK127(jo)001:12427: de bzhin du dge ba'i rtsa ba dang mos pa
NK127(jo)001:12428: dang shes rab dang snying rje dang dge ba'i bshes
NK127(jo)001:12429: gnyen gyis yongs su bzung ba dang smon lam dang
NK127(jo)001:12430: brtson 'grus dang mngon shes dang chos thams cad khong
NK127(jo)001:12432: de bzhin gshegs pa'i byin rlabs kyi stobs kyis chos
NK127(jo)001:12433: kyi lus yongs su dag pa dus gsum du tha
NK127(jo)001:12434: mi dad pa thob par gyur to //
NK127(jo)001:12435: bla na med pa'i gzugs kyi lus 'jig rten thams
NK127(jo)001:12436: cad las 'phags pa 'gro ba thams cad kyi bsam
NK127(jo)001:12437: pa bzhin du rnam par dmigs pa thams cad du
NK127(jo)001:12439: sangs rgyas kyi zhing thams cad du rab tu gzhol ba /
NK127(jo)001:12440: thams cad du rab tu gnas pa /
NK127(jo)001:12441: rnam par 'phrul pa thams cad du ston pa /
NK127(jo)001:12442: 'gro ba thams cad kyi yid du 'ong ba yang yongs su sbyangs so //
NK127(jo)001:12443: rigs kyi bu ngas lus thob pa phun sum tshogs pa /
NK127(jo)001:12444: bskal pa rgya mtsho mtha' yas pas yongs su grub pa /
NK127(jo)001:12445: bskal pa bye ba khrag khrig brgya stong mang pos
NK127(jo)001:12446: 'byung bar dka' ba mthong bar dka' ba 'di la
NK127(jo)001:12447: ltos / rigs kyi bu nga ni dge ba'i rtsa
NK127(jo)001:12448: ba ma bskyed pa'i sems can rnams kyi rna lam
NK127(jo)001:12449: du yang mi 'ong na mthong bar lta ci zhig
NK127(jo)001:12450: ltos / smos / sems can gang dag nga'i ming
NK127(jo)001:12451: thos pa tsam gyis bla med rdzogs pa'i byang chub
NK127(jo)001:12452: las phyir mi ldog par 'gyur ba yod do //
NK127(jo)001:12453: mthong ba tsam dang reg pa tsam dang bskyel ba
NK127(jo)001:12454: tsam dang rjes su 'brang ba tsam dang rmi lam
NK127(jo)001:12455: du mthong ba tsam dang rmi lam du ming thos
NK127(jo)001:12456: pa tsam gyis kyang bla med byang chub las phyir
NK127(jo)001:12457: mi ldog par 'gyur ba yod do //
NK127(jo)001:12458: sems can la las nga nyin zhag gcig tu dran par byas na yongs su smin par 'gyur ro //
NK127(jo)001:12459: la las zhag bdun la sogs pa nas zla ba
NK127(jo)001:12460: dang lo dang bskal pa gcig nas bskal pa sangs
NK127(jo)001:12461: rgyas kyi zhing brjod du med pa'i yang brjod du
NK127(jo)001:12462: med pa'i rdul shin tu phra ba snyed kyi bar
NK127(jo)001:12463: du nga rjes su dran par byas na yongs su
NK127(jo)001:12465: la las tshe gcig tu nga rjes su dran pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:12466: la las tshe'i rgyud sangs rgyas kyi zhing brjod du
NK127(jo)001:12467: med pa'i yang brjod du med pa'i rdul phra ba
NK127(jo)001:12468: snyed kyis yongs su smin par 'gyur la /
NK127(jo)001:12469: sems can la la nga'i 'od mthong ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:12470: de bzhin du 'od zer bkye ba mthong ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:12472: gzugs kyi lus bstan pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:12473: dga' bar byas pas smin par 'gyur te /
NK127(jo)001:12474: de ltar thabs kyi tshul sangs rgyas kyi zhing gi
NK127(jo)001:12475: rdul shin tu phra ba snyeed kyis sems can rnams
NK127(jo)001:12476: bla med byang chub las phyir mi ldog par 'gyur
NK127(jo)001:12477: ro // rigs kyi bu gang gis nga'i zhing dag
NK127(jo)001:12478: pa thos pa de rnams sangs rgyas kyi zhing dag
NK127(jo)001:12479: par skyel nga'i lus yongs su dag pa mthong ba
NK127(jo)001:12480: de dag nga'i lus lta bur skye bar 'a gyur
NK127(jo)001:12481: gyis rigs kyi bu nga'i lus rnam par dag pa
NK127(jo)001:12483: de nas tshong dpon gyi bu nor bzang gis byang
NK127(jo)001:12484: chub sems dpa' kun tu bzang po'i lus la bsam
NK127(jo)001:12485: pa dang / ba spu'i bu ga re re la
NK127(jo)001:12486: yang sangs rgyas kyi zhing rgya mtsho brjod du med
NK127(jo)001:12487: pa'i yang brjod du med pa'i sangs rgyas rnams byang
NK127(jo)001:12488: chub sems dpa' rgya mtsho'i 'khor dang bcas pa dang
NK127(jo)001:12489: pa dang / / zhing gi gzhi sna tshogs dang dbyibs dang rgyan sna tshogs dang /
NK127(jo)001:12490: de bzhin du khor yug dang sprin dang nam mkha' dang sangs rgyas 'byung ba la sogs pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:12491: chos kyi 'khor lo sna tshogs dang ldan par mthong ngo //
NK127(jo)001:12492: ba spu'i bu ga re re la ji lta ba
NK127(jo)001:12493: bzhin du ba spu'i bu ga thams cad dang mtshan
NK127(jo)001:12494: dpe dang yan lag nying lag thams cad la'ang de
NK127(jo)001:12495: bzhin te / zhing rgya mtsho re re nas kyang
NK127(jo)001:12496: sangs rgyas kyi sprul pa'i sprin sangs rgyas kyi zhing
NK127(jo)001:12497: thams cad kyi rdul phra ba snyed kyis phyogs bcur
NK127(jo)001:12498: rgyas par bkang ste sems can rnams byang chub tu
NK127(jo)001:12499: yongs su smin par mdzad pa mthong ngo //
NK127(jo)001:12500: de nas tshong dpon gyi bu nor bzang byang chub
NK127(jo)001:12501: sems dpa' kun tu bzang po'i gdams ngag dang rjes
NK127(jo)001:12502: su bstan pas / byang chub sems dpa' kun tu
NK127(jo)001:12503: bzang po'i lus kyi khongs su gtogs pa'i 'jig rten
NK127(jo)001:12504: thams cad du zhugs te sems can yongs su smin
NK127(jo)001:12506: de ltar nor bzang gis sngon chad dge ba'i bshes
NK127(jo)001:12507: gnyen sangs rgyas kyi zhing gi rdul phra ba snyed
NK127(jo)001:12508: cig gi drung du phyin te mthong ba dang bsnyen
NK127(jo)001:12509: bkur bas ye shes kyi snang ba thob pa dang
NK127(jo)001:12510: dge rtsa bsags pa de dag gis ni 'di ltar
NK127(jo)001:12511: kun tu bzang po mthong ste dge ba'i rtsa ba
NK127(jo)001:12512: bsags pa de'i brgya dang stong dang brgya phrag stong
NK127(jo)001:12513: gi cha dang grangs dang cha dang bgrang ba dang
NK127(jo)001:12514: dper bya ba dang rgyur bya ba tsam du'ang mi
NK127(jo)001:12515: mthong ngo // des dang po sems bskyed pa nas
NK127(jo)001:12516: bzung ste kun tu bzang po mthong ba'i bar der
NK127(jo)001:12517: sangs rgyas kyi zhing rgya mtsho gcig nas gcig tu
NK127(jo)001:12518: brgyud pa ji snyed cig la zhugs par gyur pa
NK127(jo)001:12519: mthong ngo // de bas / kun tu bzang po'i
NK127(jo)001:12520: ba spu'i bu ga re rer yang sangs rgyas kyi
NK127(jo)001:12521: zhing rgya mtsho gcig nas gcig tu brgyud pa mang
NK127(jo)001:12522: mthong ngo // de bas / po la / sangs
NK127(jo)001:12523: rgyas kyi zhing brjod du med pa'i yang brjod du
NK127(jo)001:12524: med pa'i rdul phra ba snyed kyi bar du sems
NK127(jo)001:12525: kyi skad cig gcig gis zhugs par gyur te /
NK127(jo)001:12526: de bzhin du ba spu'i bu ga ma lus pa
NK127(jo)001:12527: thams cad la yang sems kyi skad cig re re
NK127(jo)001:12528: la / 'jig rten gyi khams brjod du med pa'i
NK127(jo)001:12529: yang brjod du med pa'i rdul phra ba snyed rnam
NK127(jo)001:12530: par gnon pa phyi ma'i matha'i mur thug pa'i bskal
NK127(jo)001:12531: par byin gyis brlabs pa 'jig rten gyi khams rgya
NK127(jo)001:12532: mtsho rgyas par 'gengs pas zhugs kyang /
NK127(jo)001:12533: zhing rgya mtsho la gcig nas gcig tu brgyud pa'i mthar phyin par ma gyur te /
NK127(jo)001:12534: zhing rgya mtsho'i lhun dang bye brag dang bsdu ba
NK127(jo)001:12535: dang 'grub pa dang 'jig pa la sogs pa dang
NK127(jo)001:12536: / sangs rgyas 'byung ba dang byang chub sems dpa'i 'khor gyi tshul thams cad dang /
NK127(jo)001:12537: sems can gyi khams dang dbang po mtha' yas pa la 'jug cing smin pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:12538: byang chub sems dpa'i rnam par 'phrul pa zab mo sogs kyi mthar phyin par ma gyur te /
NK127(jo)001:12539: des zhing la lar ni bskal pa brgyar spyad pa
NK127(jo)001:12540: nas bskal pa sangs rgyas kyi zhing brjod du med
NK127(jo)001:12541: pa'i yang brjod du med pa'i bar du spyad par
NK127(jo)001:12542: gyur te zhing de dag nas kyang g.yos pa med
NK127(jo)001:12543: do // sems kyi skad cig re re la zhing
NK127(jo)001:12544: mtha' dang dbus med pa'i sems can smin par byed
NK127(jo)001:12545: do // par gyur te / des de ltar mthar
NK127(jo)001:12546: gyis byang chub sems dpa' kun tu bzang po'i spyod
NK127(jo)001:12547: pa dang smon lam rgya mtsho mnyam pa nyid kyi
NK127(jo)001:12549: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad dang mnyam pa nyid dang /
NK127(jo)001:12550: zhing thams cad du lus kyis rgyas par dgang ba mnyam pa nyid dang /
NK127(jo)001:12551: mngon par 'tshang rgya ba'i rnam par 'phrul pa yongs
NK127(jo)001:12552: su bstan pas rgyas par dgang pa mnyam pa nyid
NK127(jo)001:12553: dang / de bzhin du chos kyi 'khor lo bskor
NK127(jo)001:12554: ba dang so so yang dag par rig pa dang
NK127(jo)001:12556: dbyangs kyi yan lag thams cad kyi sbyor ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:12558: sangs rgyas kyi rnam par spyod pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:12560: snying rje chen po rnams mnyam pa nyid dang /
NK127(jo)001:12561: byang chub sems dpa'i rnam par thar pa bsam gyis
NK127(jo)001:12562: mi khyab pa'i rnam par 'phrul pa mnyam pa nyid
NK127(jo)001:12563: kyang rjes su thob par gyur to //
NK127(jo)001:12564: de nas byang chub sems dpa' kun tu bzang pos bskal pa 'byams klas pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:12565: 'jig rten gyi khams gcig nas gcig tu brgyud pa'i
NK127(jo)001:12566: sangs rgyas kyi zhing brjod du med pa'i yang brjod
NK127(jo)001:12567: du med pa'i rdul phra ba snyed de dag brnan
NK127(jo)001:12568: te mngon par brjod pa'i phyir kun tu bzang po'i
NK127(jo)001:12569: spyod pa'i smon lam tshigs su bcad pa'i dbyangs kyis
NK127(jo)001:12572: snying rje pad+ma dkar po las /
NK127(jo)001:12573: rgyal po rtsibs kyi mu khyud kyi bu brgyad pa
NK127(jo)001:12574: gnod pa med pa zhes bya bas de bzhin gshegs
NK127(jo)001:12575: pa rin chen snying po'i drung du gsol pa /
NK127(jo)001:12576: btsun pa bcom ldan 'das bdag gi ji srid du
NK127(jo)001:12577: sangs rgyas kyi zhing nyon mongs pa can khri rgyal
NK127(jo)001:12578: bu bdun pa byang chub sems dpa' seng ge spos
NK127(jo)001:12579: kyis yongs su bzung ba'i sangs rgyas kyi zhing dri
NK127(jo)001:12580: sngo snang ba rdul bral ji 'dra bar gyur ba
NK127(jo)001:12581: de ltar yongs su dag par 'god par 'gyur zhes
NK127(jo)001:12582: / de ltar dge rtsa bskyed pa dang bsam pa dag pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:12583: theg chen la zhugs pa'i byang sems dag gis khyab
NK127(jo)001:12584: par gnas par 'gyur ba srid du byang chub sems
NK127(jo)001:12585: dpar gyur cing / sangs rgyas kyi zhing nyon mongs
NK127(jo)001:12586: pa can du byang chub sems dpa'i spyad pa spyod
NK127(jo)001:12587: nas slad kyis bdag bla med byang chub tu 'tshang
NK127(jo)001:12589: bcom ldan 'das bdag gis ci nas kyang byang chub
NK127(jo)001:12590: sems dpa' gzhan dag mi spyod pa de lta bu'i
NK127(jo)001:12592: bcom ldan 'das bdag lo bdun po 'di la gcig
NK127(jo)001:12593: pu dben par mchis nas sangs rgyas kyi yon tan
NK127(jo)001:12594: dang byang chub sems dpa'i yon tan yongs su dag
NK127(jo)001:12595: pa dang / sangs rgyas kyi zhing gi yon tan yongs su dag pa la sems shing mchis na /
NK127(jo)001:12596: bdag gis ting nge 'dzin snang ba bkod pa la
NK127(jo)001:12597: sogs pa byang chub sems dpa'i ting nge 'dzin nyi
NK127(jo)001:12598: khri chig stong bskyed cing thob ste sgom pa gang
NK127(jo)001:12600: btsun pa bcom ldan 'das bdag byang chub sems dpar
NK127(jo)001:12601: gyur pa'i byang chub sems dpa'i spyod pa lags so
NK127(jo)001:12602: // sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das gang dag phyogs bcu'i
NK127(jo)001:12603: 'jig rten gyi khams mtha' yas mu ma mchis pa
NK127(jo)001:12604: dag na bzhugs te 'tsho zhing gzhes la sems can
NK127(jo)001:12605: rnams la sman pa dang bde ba'i phyir chos ston
NK127(jo)001:12607: gang dag dus gsum las yang dag par 'das pa'i
NK127(jo)001:12608: sangs rgyas kyi zhing rgyal mtshan gyi rtse mo'i dpung
NK127(jo)001:12609: rgyan ces bgyi ba rgyal ba rnams kyis yongs su
NK127(jo)001:12610: gtams la de dag mthong zhing der 'jug par gyur
NK127(jo)001:12611: cig / ting nge 'dzin des bdag gis sangs rgyas
NK127(jo)001:12612: bcom ldan 'das byang chub sems dpa' dang nyan thos
NK127(jo)001:12613: kyi tshogs kyis bskor ba rdul phra rab kyi rdul
NK127(jo)001:12615: ting nge 'dzin gyi mthus bdag gnas ma mchis par
NK127(jo)001:12616: sangs rgyas kyi zhing rdul phra rab kyi rdul snyed
NK127(jo)001:12617: kyi lus kyis sangs rgyas de dag re re la
NK127(jo)001:12619: re re la yang bdag gi lus re res rin
NK127(jo)001:12620: po che dang me tog sna tshogs dang spos dang
NK127(jo)001:12621: me tog gi phreng ba dang phye ma dang byug
NK127(jo)001:12622: pa dang rol mo'i sgra sna tshogs bla na ma
NK127(jo)001:12624: bkod pa bla na ma mchis pa thams cad kyis mchod par gyur cig /
NK127(jo)001:12625: sangs rgyas kyi zhing gcig tu yang bdag bskal pa rgya mtsho'i bye ma snyed du spyod pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:12626: gang gi tshe bdag gis lus thams cad rnam par
NK127(jo)001:12627: 'jig pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyis skad cig gcig la
NK127(jo)001:12628: sangs rgyas re re'i sangs rgyas kyi spyod yul sangs
NK127(jo)001:12629: rgyas kyi zhing gi rdul phra rab kyi rdul snyed
NK127(jo)001:12631: ting nge 'dzin yon tan 'byung gnas kyi mthus de
NK127(jo)001:12632: dag re re la sangs rgyas kyi zhing gi rdul
NK127(jo)001:12633: phra rab kyi rdul snyed kyi bstod pa bla na
NK127(jo)001:12634: ma mchis pas bstod pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:12635: bdag gis mig mi 'dzum pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyis
NK127(jo)001:12636: rdul gcig gi steng du sems kyi skad cig gi
NK127(jo)001:12637: tshad tsam gyis rgyal ba rnams kyis gtams pa'i sangs
NK127(jo)001:12638: rgyas kyi zhing thams cad mthong ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:12639: bdag gis nyon mongs pa ma mchis pa'i ting nge
NK127(jo)001:12640: 'dzin gyis sems kyi skad cig gcig gis sangs rgyas
NK127(jo)001:12641: kyi zhing thams cad dag na 'das pa dang ma
NK127(jo)001:12642: 'ongs pa dang da ltar byung ba'i byang chub sems
NK127(jo)001:12643: dpa' rnams dang sangs rgyas kyi zhing gi yon tan
NK127(jo)001:12644: bkod pa dag mthong ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:12645: bdag dpa' bar 'gro ba'i ting nge 'dzin gyis sems
NK127(jo)001:12646: can dmyal ba rnams su zhugs te sems can dmyal
NK127(jo)001:12647: ba'i lus su sprul nas dmyal ba'i sems can rnams
NK127(jo)001:12648: la chos ston pa dang byang chub yang dag par
NK127(jo)001:12649: 'dzin du bcug pas sems can de dag byang chub
NK127(jo)001:12650: tu sems bskyed par gyur cig /
NK127(jo)001:12651: de nas shi 'phos te mi rnams dang skal pa
NK127(jo)001:12652: mnyam par skyes nas sangs rgyas gang dag bzhugs pa
NK127(jo)001:12653: de dag las chos nyan te phyir mi ldog pa'i
NK127(jo)001:12654: sa la gnas par gyur cig /
NK127(jo)001:12655: de bzhin du dud 'gro dang yi dwags dang gnod
NK127(jo)001:12656: sbyin dang srin po dang lha ma yin dang klu
NK127(jo)001:12657: dang mi'am ci dang lto 'phye chen po dang sha
NK127(jo)001:12658: za dang / srul po dang lus srul po dang
NK127(jo)001:12659: mi gdol pa dang tshong ba dang smad 'tshong ma
NK127(jo)001:12660: rnams la'ang de bzhin du chos bstan pas phyir mi
NK127(jo)001:12662: sems can rigs ji lta bur skyes pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:12663: lus ji lta bu thob pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:12664: las kyi rkyen ji lta bus bde ba'am sdug bsngal gyi tshor pa myong ba rnams dang /
NK127(jo)001:12665: bzo dang las kyi gnas ji lta bu la chags
NK127(jo)001:12666: pa rnams la de lta bu'i lus su sprul nas
NK127(jo)001:12667: bzo dang las kyi gnas de lta bu la brtson
NK127(jo)001:12669: de lta bu'i yi ge brjod pas sems can rnams
NK127(jo)001:12670: kyi sems mgu bar bgyis nas chos ston pa dang
NK127(jo)001:12671: / bla med byang chub 'dzin du 'jug cing de
NK127(jo)001:12672: la btsud pa dang rab tu 'god par byas nas
NK127(jo)001:12673: rdzogs byang las phyir mi ldog pa la 'god par
NK127(jo)001:12674: / gyur cig / btsun pa bcom ldan 'das bdag
NK127(jo)001:12675: gis phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas kyi zhing stong phrag bcu
NK127(jo)001:12676: po thams cad dag na sems can gang yod pa
NK127(jo)001:12677: thams cad kyi sems kyi rgyud la ci nas kyang
NK127(jo)001:12678: sngon gyi las dang nyon mongs pa'i lhag ma ma
NK127(jo)001:12680: sems can 'ag'i sems kyi rgyud kyi lam yang bdud
NK127(jo)001:12681: bzhis rtogs par mi 'gyur pa de ltar sems can
NK127(jo)001:12682: gyi rgyud yongs su spyod par 'gyur ba de srid
NK127(jo)001:12683: du bdag gis byang chub kyi spyod pa spyad par
NK127(jo)001:12684: bagyi'o // de'i slad du bdag gis sangs rgyas kyi
NK127(jo)001:12685: zhing khri yang de bzhin gshegs pa snang ba rdul
NK127(jo)001:12686: bral spos mtho dbang phyug rgyal po skar ma'i sangs
NK127(jo)001:12687: rgyas kyi zhing dri sngo snang ba rdul bral gyi
NK127(jo)001:12688: yon tan bkod pa ci 'dra ba de ltar yongs
NK127(jo)001:12689: su dag par 'jog par gyur cig /
NK127(jo)001:12690: de bzhin du bdag gis rang gi sangs rgyas kyi
NK127(jo)001:12691: zhing dang bdag gi 'khor yang ji ltar byang chub
NK127(jo)001:12692: sems dpa' seng ge spos kyis smon lam btab pa
NK127(jo)001:12694: btsun pa bcom ldan 'das gal te bdag gi re
NK127(jo)001:12695: ba 'di yongs su rdzogs par 'gyur ba lta na
NK127(jo)001:12696: / de'i slad du phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas kyi zhing
NK127(jo)001:12697: dag gi sems can rnams kyi sdug bsngal thams cad
NK127(jo)001:12699: thams cad kyang sems mnyen pa dang las su rung ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:12700: rang rang gi gling bzhi pa dag na sangs rgyas bzhugs pa mthong ba dang /
NK127(jo)001:12701: sems can de dag la rin po che sna tshogs
NK127(jo)001:12702: dang me tog dang spos dang byug pa dang phye
NK127(jo)001:12703: ma dang gdugs dang rgyal mtshan dang ba dan dag
NK127(jo)001:12705: des sangs rgyas de dag mchod cing bla med byang chub tu sems bskyed par gyur cig /
NK127(jo)001:12706: bcom ldan 'das bdag gis kyang ting nge 'dzin snang
NK127(jo)001:12707: ba bkod pa'i mthus bdag nyid kyis de thams cad
NK127(jo)001:12709: tshig de brjod ma thag tu smon lam ji ltar
NK127(jo)001:12710: btab pa bzhin du gyur pa bdag nyid kyis mthong
NK127(jo)001:12711: ba dang bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
NK127(jo)001:12712: rigs kyi bu legs so legs so //
NK127(jo)001:12713: rigs kyi bu khyod ni sangs rgyas kyi zhing gi
NK127(jo)001:12714: kho ra khor yug tu sangs rgyas kyi zhing yongs
NK127(jo)001:12715: su dag pa khri 'jog par 'gyur ro //
NK127(jo)001:12716: sems can dpag med grangs med pa dag gi sems kyi rgyud yongs su dag par byed pa dang /
NK127(jo)001:12717: sangs rgyas dpag med grangs med pa dag la mchod
NK127(jo)001:12718: pa dpag med grangs med pa dag byed par spro
NK127(jo)001:12720: rigs kyi bu de'i phyir khyod kun tu bzang po zhes bya bar gyur cig /
NK127(jo)001:12721: kun tu bzang po khyod ni ma 'ongs pa'i dus
NK127(jo)001:12722: na bskal pa grangs med pa gang g+aa'i klung gcig
NK127(jo)001:12724: bskal pa grangs med gnyis pa la bab pa na
NK127(jo)001:12725: byang phyogs logs su sangs rgyas kyi zhing 'di nas
NK127(jo)001:12726: sangs rgyas kyi zhing gang g+aa'i klung drug cu'i bye
NK127(jo)001:12728: 'jig rten gyi khams ye shes kyi chu shin tu rnam par dag pa'i yon tan zhes bya bar /
NK127(jo)001:12729: bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs
NK127(jo)001:12730: rgyas ye shes rdo rje rnam par bsgyings pa'i dbang
NK127(jo)001:12731: phyug tog ces bya bar 'tshang rgya bar 'gyur ro
NK127(jo)001:12733: 'phags mchog kun tu bzang po'i rtogs pa brjod pa'i skabs te brgyad pa'o ////
NK127(jo)001:12734: de ltar rgyal sras sems dpa' chen po 'di dag
NK127(jo)001:12735: gi rnam par thar pa'i tshul 'di dang 'di lta
NK127(jo)001:12736: bu la dang ba'i dad pa cung zad tsam skyes
NK127(jo)001:12737: pa'ang dge ba'i tshogs dpag tu med pa'i gzhir gyur
NK127(jo)001:12738: cing / dwang ba'i dad pa la brten nas tshul
NK127(jo)001:12739: de lta bu rang gis bsgrub par 'dod pa'i dad
NK127(jo)001:12740: pa skyes pa ni theg pa chen po'i lam gyi
NK127(jo)001:12741: cing / rtsa ba ste / byang chub sems dpa'i
NK127(jo)001:12742: rnam thar rgya mtsho lta bu nyams 'og tu chud
NK127(jo)001:12743: pa med par sangs rgyas su 'gyur ba ni gnas
NK127(jo)001:12744: med par ci nas kyang shes dgos la /
NK127(jo)001:12745: 'dod pa'i dad pas lam la tshul bzhin zhugs pas
NK127(jo)001:12746: theg chen gyi lam dang 'bras bu la yid ches
NK127(jo)001:12747: pa'i dad pa mi 'phrog pa stobs su gyur te
NK127(jo)001:12748: / rim gyis rgyal sras sems dpa' chen po 'di
NK127(jo)001:12749: rnams dang mnyam pa'i skal pa can du gyur nas
NK127(jo)001:12750: rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes thob par
NK127(jo)001:12751: / 'gyur ba'i phyir / dad pa'i rgyu dang rkyen
NK127(jo)001:12752: du dmigs nas nye ba'i sras chen po brgyad kyi
NK127(jo)001:12754: de bzhin gshegs pa'i gsung rab rin po che'i mdzod
NK127(jo)001:12755: rnams las btus te mi pham rnam par rgyal bas
NK127(jo)001:12756: phyogs gcig tu bkod pa 'dis nam mkha' dang mnyam
NK127(jo)001:12757: pa'i sems can thams cad kyis rgyal sras sems dpa'
NK127(jo)001:12758: brgyad dang mnyam pa nyid du gyur pa'i yon tan
NK127(jo)001:12759: gyi chos kun la dbang 'byor bar gyur cig //
NK127(jo)001:12760: nye ba'i sras chen brgyad kyi thugs bskyed dang //
NK127(jo)001:12761: mdzad pa smon lam mkhyen brtse nus pa'i tshul //
NK127(jo)001:12762: bla med ye shes sgyu 'phrul ji 'dra ba //
NK127(jo)001:12763: de 'dra kho nar bdag sogs 'gyur bar shog /
NK127(jo)001:12767: rnam dkar yon tan dge legs nyin byed dbang //
NK127(jo)001:12768: nye bar 'dren byed dad pa'i skya rengs te //
NK127(jo)001:12769: dad gus rlan gyis gos min yid can khams //
NK127(jo)001:12770: thugs rje'i byin 'od rno yang smin nus min //
NK127(jo)001:12771: de phyir rgyas 'gyur sa bon gso ba'i phyir //
NK127(jo)001:12772: thabs mkhas ded dpon 'jam dbyangs a dzi tas //
NK127(jo)001:12773: rtogs brjod skal bzang dga' ster nor bu'i phreng //
NK127(jo)001:12774: mdo rgyud rin chen gling nas phyogs gcig spel //
NK127(jo)001:12775: bskal mang thos dka' thos pa don ldan gtam //
NK127(jo)001:12776: 'di mthong gang dag rgyal sras rjes slob ste //
NK127(jo)001:12777: mtha' gnyis las 'das theg chen lam gyi lus //
NK127(jo)001:12778: yongs rdzogs srid zhir mi gnas byang chub brnyes //
NK127(jo)001:12779: ngo mtshar chos sprin khyab par 'phro ba'i gnas //
NK127(jo)001:12780: 'di yang chos mdzod yongs 'du'i tshal du bskrun //
NK127(jo)001:12781: bsod nams dpag yas gang des 'brel thogs 'gro //
NK127(jo)001:12782: rgyal sras spyod pa rgya mtsho'i rjes slob shog /
NK127(jo)001:12783: bdag kyang skye kun 'jam dbyangs bla ma yi //
NK127(jo)001:12784: gsung gi snang bas skyong zhing chos mig gsal //
NK127(jo)001:12785: dad dang nges 'byung snying rjes rgyud phyug nas //
NK127(jo)001:12786: theg chen lam gyis gdul bya 'gyur bar shog //
